EMU_exr  = EMU_exr(-1)  * ( ( (EMU_inft  - usa_inft)  / 100  + 1) )  * ((  - 5  * ( (EMU_INT  - usa_INT)  - (EMU_INT(-1)  - usa_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD EMU_EXR  EMU_EXR_A

EMU_INT  = EMU_INT(-1)  + (USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1))
@ADD EMU_INT  EMU_INT_A

EMU_INFT  = EMU_INFT(-1)
@ADD EMU_INFT  EMU_INFT_A

DLOG(AFG_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(AFG_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AFG_MTD)  + 0.4 * (AFG_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (AFG_YER / AFG_YFT  - AFG_YER(-1) / AFG_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + AFG_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + AFG_GCARB / AFG_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (AFG_PREM - AFG_PREM(-1)) / 100

AFG_YED  = AFG_YED(-1) * AFG_HIC / AFG_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_INT  = AFG_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_LTI  = AFG_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (AFG_INT - AFG_INT(-1))  + (AFG_PREM  - AFG_PREM(-1)) / 100

AFG_PREM  = AFG_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (AFG_GDNRATIO(-1)  - AFG_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(AFG_LNN)  = DLOG(AFG_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(AFG_LNN(-1))  - LOG(AFG_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(AFG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AFG_LNNF)  = DLOG(AFG_LNN)

AFG_FUELSH  = AFG_FUELSH(-1)

AFG_TAXR  = AFG_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( AFG_GLNT(-1)  - AFG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * AFG_YEN(-1) / ( ( AFG_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (AFG_YER(-2)  + AFG_GDI(-2)) * AFG_YED(-2) * (AFG_LNN(-1) / AFG_LNN(-2)  + AFG_TECHL(-1) - AFG_TECHL(-2) ) ) + AFG_REMIT(-1)  + AFG_EXPSP(-1) ) * AFG_SOLV

AFG_CTAXR  = AFG_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( AFG_GLNT(-1)  - AFG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * AFG_YEN(-1) / ( AFG_PROF(-1) ) * AFG_SOLV

(AFG_OGC)  = AFG_OGC(-1) * (AFG_YFT / AFG_YFT(-1) * AFG_YED / AFG_YED(-1))

AFG_USER  = (AFG_LTI  - AFG_INFT  + AFG_DEP * 100) / (1  - AFG_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (AFG_GCARB / AFG_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY AFG_XTN  = AFG_XTD$ * AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") * AFG_XTR

@IDENTITY AFG_YEN  = AFG_YER  * AFG_YED

@IDENTITY AFG_MTN  = AFG_MTD  * AFG_MTR

@IDENTITY AFG_XTN$  = AFG_XTN / AFG_EXR

@IDENTITY AFG_YEN$  = AFG_YEN / AFG_EXR

@IDENTITY AFG_MTN$  = AFG_MTN / AFG_EXR

@IDENTITY AFG_MTR$  = AFG_MTR$(-1) * AFG_MTR / AFG_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_XTR$  = AFG_XTR$(-1) * AFG_XTR / AFG_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_YER$  = AFG_YER$(-1) * AFG_YER / AFG_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_YFT$  = AFG_YFT$(-1) * AFG_YFT / AFG_YFT(-1)

AFG_POPT  = AFG_POPT(-1)  - AFG_LIVES

AFG_POPWA  = AFG_POPWA(-1) * AFG_POPT / AFG_POPT(-1)

AFG_SCR  = AFG_SCR(-1)  + ((AFG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (AFG_YFT(-1) / AFG_YER(-1)  - AFG_YFT(-2) / AFG_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY AFG_ITR  = AFG_IGR  + AFG_IPR

@IDENTITY AFG_YER  = AFG_PCR  + AFG_GCR  + AFG_ITR  + AFG_SCR  + AFG_XTR  - AFG_MTR

@IDENTITY AFG_PROF  = (AFG_YEN - AFG_ITAX) * (1 - AFG_LABSH)

@IDENTITY AFG_GDI  = AFG_YER  - AFG_XTR  + AFG_MTR  + AFG_XTN  / ((AFG_YEN  - AFG_XTN  + AFG_MTN)  / (AFG_YER  - AFG_XTR  + AFG_MTR))  - AFG_MTN  / ((AFG_YEN  - AFG_XTN  + AFG_MTN)  / (AFG_YER  - AFG_XTR  + AFG_MTR))

@IDENTITY AFG_RPDI  = AFG_LABSH * 0.5 * (AFG_YER(-1)  + AFG_GDI(-1)) * AFG_YED(-1) / AFG_HIC(-1) * (AFG_LNN / AFG_LNN(-1)  + AFG_TECHL - AFG_TECHL(-1)) + AFG_REMIT / AFG_HIC  + AFG_EXPSP / AFG_HIC  - AFG_TAX / AFG_HIC

DLOG(AFG_YFT)  = (1 - AFG_ALPHA - AFG_LABSH) * DLOG(AFG_K(-1) / AFG_LFN(-1))  + (1 - AFG_ALPHA) * DLOG(AFG_LFN)  + AFG_LABSH * D(AFG_TECHL)  + AFG_ALPHA * (DLOG(AFG_EC)  + D(AFG_EFF) )  - ( AFG_CLIMLOSS / AFG_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (AFG_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY AFG_K  = AFG_K(-1) * (1 - AFG_DEP) + AFG_ITR

DLOG(AFG_MTD)  = (1  - AFG_OMS) * ( DLOG(AFG_CMUD)  + DLOG(AFG_EXR) )  + AFG_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AFG_EXR) )

DLOG(AFG_XTD$)  = (1  - AFG_OXS) * DLOG(AFG_XTDNO$)  + AFG_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

AFG_INFT  = 0.95 * AFG_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

AFG_OXS  = AFG_OXS(-1)

AFG_OMS  = AFG_OMS(-1) * ((AFG_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * AFG_EXR(-1) / AFG_MTN(-1)) / (AFG_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * AFG_EXR(-2) / AFG_MTN(-2)))^0.25

AFG_CXS  = AFG_CXS(-1)

AFG_FINC  = AFG_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_CAN  = AFG_XTN / AFG_EXR  - AFG_MTN / AFG_EXR  + AFG_REMIT / AFG_EXR  + AFG_CANOTH

@IDENTITY AFG_CANRATIO  = AFG_CAN / AFG_YEN$ * 100

AFG_CANOTH  = AFG_CANOTH(-1)  + ((AFG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (AFG_YEN$  / AFG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + AFG_REVG / AFG_EXR  - AFG_REVG(-1) / AFG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(AFG_EFEX)  =  - LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.336544853E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007791823191 * DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001134733265 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01608387791 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001118286565 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001504244494 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4064484863 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001002801378 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009582072833 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006093259916 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3048797666 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001835604104 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009872148488 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009162652606 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00328085387 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0213592287 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 5.911134311E-05 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.593843419E-05 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01979713488 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01123667688 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1552769797 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * AFG_EXR

AFG_GINT  = AFG_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (AFG_LTI  - AFG_LTI(-1))

AFG_GDN  = AFG_GDN(-1) * (AFG_GDFXSH  * (AFG_EXR  / AFG_EXR(-1))  + (1  - AFG_GDFXSH))  - AFG_GLN

@IDENTITY AFG_GDNRATIO  = AFG_GDN / AFG_YEN * 100

AFG_GDFXSH  = ( AFG_GDFXSH(-1) * (AFG_EXR / AFG_EXR(-1) )) / (AFG_GDFXSH(-1) * (AFG_EXR / AFG_EXR(-1))  + 1 - AFG_GDFXSH(-1) )

AFG_TOURSH  = AFG_TOURSH(-1)

AFG_LOCK  = 0

AFG_GCARBR  = AFG_GCARBR(-1)

AFG_GTRADER  = AFG_GTRADER(-1)

AFG_ITAXR  = AFG_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_REV  = AFG_TAX  + AFG_CTAX  + AFG_ITAX  + AFG_GTRADE  + AFG_REVG  + AFG_GCARB  + AFG_GCOM  + AFG_GOTH

@IDENTITY AFG_TAX  = AFG_TAXR * (AFG_LABSH * 0.5 * (AFG_YER(-1)  + AFG_GDI(-1)) * AFG_YED(-1) * (AFG_LNN / AFG_LNN(-1)  + AFG_TECHL - AFG_TECHL(-1)) + AFG_REMIT  + AFG_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY AFG_CTAX  = AFG_CTAXR * AFG_PROF

@IDENTITY AFG_ITAX  = AFG_ITAXR * (AFG_PCR * AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY AFG_GTRADE  = AFG_GTRADER * AFG_XTN

AFG_REVG  = AFG_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (AFG_YER$ / AFG_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - AFG_YER$(-1) / AFG_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * AFG_EXR / AFG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_GCARB  = AFG_GCARBR * AFG_CO2 * AFG_EXR / 1000

AFG_GCOM  = AFG_GCOM(-1) * ( AFG_OILC / (AFG_OILC + AFG_GASC + AFG_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + AFG_GASC / (AFG_OILC + AFG_GASC + AFG_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + AFG_COALC / (AFG_OILC + AFG_GASC + AFG_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

AFG_GOTH  = AFG_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_EXP  = AFG_EXPE  + AFG_EXPH  + AFG_EXPSP  + AFG_OGC  + AFG_OGI  + AFG_GIP

AFG_EXPE  = AFG_EXPE(-1) * (AFG_YFT / AFG_YFT(-1)) * (AFG_YED / AFG_YED(-1))

AFG_EXPH = AFG_EXPH(-1) * (AFG_YFT / AFG_YFT(-1)) * (AFG_YED / AFG_YED(-1))

AFG_EXPSP  = AFG_EXPSP(-1) * (AFG_YFT / AFG_YFT(-1)) * (AFG_YED / AFG_YED(-1)) * (AFG_POPT - AFG_LNN) / (AFG_POPT(-1) - AFG_LNN(-1))

DLOG(AFG_OGI)  = DLOG(AFG_YFT)  + DLOG(AFG_YED)

AFG_GCR  = AFG_GCR(-1)  + ( AFG_OGC / AFG_YED - AFG_OGC(-1) / AFG_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (AFG_EXPH ) / AFG_YED  - (AFG_EXPH(-1) ) / AFG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (AFG_EXPE ) / AFG_YED  - (AFG_EXPE(-1) ) / AFG_YED(-1) )

AFG_IGR  = AFG_IGR(-1) + (AFG_OGI / AFG_YED - AFG_OGI(-1) / AFG_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (AFG_EXPH ) / AFG_YED  - (AFG_EXPH(-1) ) / AFG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (AFG_EXPE ) / AFG_YED  - (AFG_EXPE(-1) ) / AFG_YED(-1) )

AFG_GIP  = ( AFG_GIP(-1)  + ( AFG_GDN(-1) - AFG_GDN(-2) ) * AFG_GINT(-1) / 100  + AFG_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( AFG_GINT(-1) / 100 - AFG_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (AFG_GDFXSH * (AFG_EXR / AFG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - AFG_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY AFG_GLN  = AFG_REV  - AFG_EXP

@IDENTITY AFG_GLNRATIO  = AFG_GLN / AFG_YEN * 100

AFG_GLNT  = AFG_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

AFG_TFP  = AFG_LABSH * (AFG_TECHL  - AFG_TECHL(-1))

AFG_LABSH  = AFG_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY AFG_LFN  = AFG_LRX * AFG_POPWA

AFG_LRX  = AFG_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(AFG_YER(-1) / AFG_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY AFG_URX  = (1 - AFG_LNN / AFG_LFN) * 100

AFG_URXF  = AFG_URXF(-1) * AFG_URX / AFG_URX(-1) * AFG_LNN / AFG_LNNF / (AFG_LNN(-1) / AFG_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(AFG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(AFG_PCR  / AFG_POPT)

AFG_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(AFG_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

AFG_HEAD19  = AFG_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AFG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI^2)  , AFG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AFG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AFG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

AFG_HEAD55  = AFG_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AFG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI^2)  , AFG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AFG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AFG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(AFG_XTR)  = DLOG(AFG_WDR)  + (1  - AFG_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(AFG_XTDNO$  / AFG_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * AFG_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(AFG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (AFG_EXPH(-1) / AFG_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (AFG_EXPH(-1) / AFG_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(AFG_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(AFG_PM25)

AFG_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( AFG_EXPSP / AFG_YEN )

DLOG(AFG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - AFG_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (AFG_FINC - AFG_FINC(-1))

DLOG(AFG_PCR)  = 0.101131534600011  +  - 0.382047463237769 * (LOG(AFG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(AFG_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (AFG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(AFG_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.7)  * DLOG(AFG_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(AFG_HIC)  - AFG_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * AFG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * AFG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(AFG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(AFG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AFG_IPR)  =  - 0.275900236236157  - 0.1 * (LOG(AFG_IPR(-1)  / AFG_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * AFG_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * AFG_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(AFG_PCR  + AFG_GCR(-1) + AFG_IGR(-1) + AFG_XTN  / AFG_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(AFG_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (AFG_USER - AFG_USER(-1))  - (0 * AFG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * AFG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - AFG_FUELSH - AFG_TOURSH)) * AFG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * AFG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * AFG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - AFG_FUELSH - AFG_TOURSH)) * AFG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(AFG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(AFG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AFG_MTR)  =  - 0.0799531462217802  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(AFG_MTR(-1))  - LOG(AFG_PCR(-1) + AFG_ITR(-1) + AFG_GCR(-1) + AFG_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(AFG_YFT(-1) / AFG_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(AFG_CMUD(-1) * AFG_EXR(-1)  / AFG_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * AFG_OMS * LOG(AFG_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.087020626405894  * DLOG(AFG_XTR)  + 0.704029610365194  * DLOG(AFG_PCR)  + 0.0630543492367893  * DLOG(AFG_IPR)  + 0.0686747563933368  * DLOG(AFG_GCR + AFG_IGR)

AFG_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * AFG_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * AFG_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * AFG_OILC

AFG_POIL  = AFG_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( AFG_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - AFG_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

AFG_PG  = AFG_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( AFG_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - AFG_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

AFG_PC  = AFG_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( AFG_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - AFG_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(AFG_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

AFG_PE  = AFG_PE(-1) * ( AFG_OILC(-1) / (AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) * AFG_POIL / AFG_POIL(-1)  + AFG_GASC(-1) / (AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) * AFG_PG / AFG_PG(-1)  + AFG_COALC(-1) / (AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) * AFG_PC / AFG_PC(-1)  + AFG_RC(-1) / (AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) * AFG_PR / AFG_PR(-1) )

D(AFG_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(AFG_PM25)  = 0.2 * (AFG_COALC(-1) / AFG_EC(-1) - AFG_COALC(-2) / AFG_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (AFG_COALC(-2) / AFG_EC(-2) - AFG_COALC(-3) / AFG_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (AFG_OILC(-1) / AFG_EC(-1) - AFG_OILC(-2) / AFG_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (AFG_OILC(-2) / AFG_EC(-2) - AFG_OILC(-3) / AFG_EC(-3))

DLOG(AFG_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(AFG_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(AFG_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(AFG_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AFG_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AFG_PE * AFG_EXR / AFG_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AFG_PE(-1) * AFG_EXR(-1) / AFG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AFG_PE(-2) * AFG_EXR(-2) / AFG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AFG_PE(-3) * AFG_EXR(-3) / AFG_HIC(-3))  - (AFG_EFF - AFG_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(AFG_COALC)  = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(AFG_COALC(-1) / AFG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.18354485717481 * LOG(AFG_PE(-1) / AFG_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) / AFG_EC(-1))

DLOG(AFG_GASC)  = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(AFG_GASC(-1) / AFG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.041061064589045 * LOG(AFG_PE(-1) / AFG_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) / AFG_EC(-1))

DLOG(AFG_RC)  = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( AFG_RC(-1) / AFG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.18354485717481 * LOG(AFG_PE(-1) / AFG_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) / AFG_EC(-1))

DLOG(AFG_OILC)  = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( AFG_OILC(-1) / AFG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.18354485717481 * LOG(AFG_PE(-1) / AFG_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AFG_COALC(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1) + AFG_OILC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)) / AFG_EC(-1))

AFG_EXR  = AFG_EXR(-1) * ( (AFG_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(ARM_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(ARM_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(ARM_MTD)  + 0.4 * (ARM_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (ARM_YER / ARM_YFT  - ARM_YER(-1) / ARM_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + ARM_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + ARM_GCARB / ARM_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (ARM_PREM - ARM_PREM(-1)) / 100

ARM_YED  = ARM_YED(-1) * ARM_HIC / ARM_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_INT  = ARM_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_LTI  = ARM_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (ARM_INT - ARM_INT(-1))  + (ARM_PREM  - ARM_PREM(-1)) / 100

ARM_PREM  = ARM_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (ARM_GDNRATIO(-1)  - ARM_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(ARM_LNN)  = DLOG(ARM_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(ARM_LNN(-1))  - LOG(ARM_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(ARM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(ARM_LNNF)  = DLOG(ARM_LNN)

ARM_FUELSH  = ARM_FUELSH(-1)

ARM_TAXR  = ARM_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( ARM_GLNT(-1)  - ARM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * ARM_YEN(-1) / ( ( ARM_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (ARM_YER(-2)  + ARM_GDI(-2)) * ARM_YED(-2) * (ARM_LNN(-1) / ARM_LNN(-2)  + ARM_TECHL(-1) - ARM_TECHL(-2) ) ) + ARM_REMIT(-1)  + ARM_EXPSP(-1) ) * ARM_SOLV

ARM_CTAXR  = ARM_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( ARM_GLNT(-1)  - ARM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * ARM_YEN(-1) / ( ARM_PROF(-1) ) * ARM_SOLV

(ARM_OGC)  = ARM_OGC(-1) * (ARM_YFT / ARM_YFT(-1) * ARM_YED / ARM_YED(-1))

ARM_USER  = (ARM_LTI  - ARM_INFT  + ARM_DEP * 100) / (1  - ARM_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (ARM_GCARB / ARM_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY ARM_XTN  = ARM_XTD$ * ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") * ARM_XTR

@IDENTITY ARM_YEN  = ARM_YER  * ARM_YED

@IDENTITY ARM_MTN  = ARM_MTD  * ARM_MTR

@IDENTITY ARM_XTN$  = ARM_XTN / ARM_EXR

@IDENTITY ARM_YEN$  = ARM_YEN / ARM_EXR

@IDENTITY ARM_MTN$  = ARM_MTN / ARM_EXR

@IDENTITY ARM_MTR$  = ARM_MTR$(-1) * ARM_MTR / ARM_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_XTR$  = ARM_XTR$(-1) * ARM_XTR / ARM_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_YER$  = ARM_YER$(-1) * ARM_YER / ARM_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_YFT$  = ARM_YFT$(-1) * ARM_YFT / ARM_YFT(-1)

ARM_POPT  = ARM_POPT(-1)  - ARM_LIVES

ARM_POPWA  = ARM_POPWA(-1) * ARM_POPT / ARM_POPT(-1)

ARM_SCR  = ARM_SCR(-1)  + ((ARM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (ARM_YFT(-1) / ARM_YER(-1)  - ARM_YFT(-2) / ARM_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY ARM_ITR  = ARM_IGR  + ARM_IPR

@IDENTITY ARM_YER  = ARM_PCR  + ARM_GCR  + ARM_ITR  + ARM_SCR  + ARM_XTR  - ARM_MTR

@IDENTITY ARM_PROF  = (ARM_YEN - ARM_ITAX) * (1 - ARM_LABSH)

@IDENTITY ARM_GDI  = ARM_YER  - ARM_XTR  + ARM_MTR  + ARM_XTN  / ((ARM_YEN  - ARM_XTN  + ARM_MTN)  / (ARM_YER  - ARM_XTR  + ARM_MTR))  - ARM_MTN  / ((ARM_YEN  - ARM_XTN  + ARM_MTN)  / (ARM_YER  - ARM_XTR  + ARM_MTR))

@IDENTITY ARM_RPDI  = ARM_LABSH * 0.5 * (ARM_YER(-1)  + ARM_GDI(-1)) * ARM_YED(-1) / ARM_HIC(-1) * (ARM_LNN / ARM_LNN(-1)  + ARM_TECHL - ARM_TECHL(-1)) + ARM_REMIT / ARM_HIC  + ARM_EXPSP / ARM_HIC  - ARM_TAX / ARM_HIC

DLOG(ARM_YFT)  = (1 - ARM_ALPHA - ARM_LABSH) * DLOG(ARM_K(-1) / ARM_LFN(-1))  + (1 - ARM_ALPHA) * DLOG(ARM_LFN)  + ARM_LABSH * D(ARM_TECHL)  + ARM_ALPHA * (DLOG(ARM_EC)  + D(ARM_EFF) )  - ( ARM_CLIMLOSS / ARM_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (ARM_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY ARM_K  = ARM_K(-1) * (1 - ARM_DEP) + ARM_ITR

DLOG(ARM_MTD)  = (1  - ARM_OMS) * ( DLOG(ARM_CMUD)  + DLOG(ARM_EXR) )  + ARM_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(ARM_EXR) )

DLOG(ARM_XTD$)  = (1  - ARM_OXS) * DLOG(ARM_XTDNO$)  + ARM_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

ARM_INFT  = 0.95 * ARM_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

ARM_OXS  = ARM_OXS(-1)

ARM_OMS  = ARM_OMS(-1) * ((ARM_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * ARM_EXR(-1) / ARM_MTN(-1)) / (ARM_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * ARM_EXR(-2) / ARM_MTN(-2)))^0.25

ARM_CXS  = ARM_CXS(-1)

ARM_FINC  = ARM_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_CAN  = ARM_XTN / ARM_EXR  - ARM_MTN / ARM_EXR  + ARM_REMIT / ARM_EXR  + ARM_CANOTH

@IDENTITY ARM_CANRATIO  = ARM_CAN / ARM_YEN$ * 100

ARM_CANOTH  = ARM_CANOTH(-1)  + ((ARM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (ARM_YEN$  / ARM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + ARM_REVG / ARM_EXR  - ARM_REVG(-1) / ARM_EXR(-1)
