ARM_GINT  = ARM_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (ARM_LTI  - ARM_LTI(-1))

ARM_GDN  = ARM_GDN(-1) * (ARM_GDFXSH  * (ARM_EXR  / ARM_EXR(-1))  + (1  - ARM_GDFXSH))  - ARM_GLN

@IDENTITY ARM_GDNRATIO  = ARM_GDN / ARM_YEN * 100

ARM_GDFXSH  = ( ARM_GDFXSH(-1) * (ARM_EXR / ARM_EXR(-1) )) / (ARM_GDFXSH(-1) * (ARM_EXR / ARM_EXR(-1))  + 1 - ARM_GDFXSH(-1) )

ARM_TOURSH  = ARM_TOURSH(-1)

ARM_LOCK  = 0

ARM_GCARBR  = ARM_GCARBR(-1)

ARM_GTRADER  = ARM_GTRADER(-1)

ARM_ITAXR  = ARM_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_REV  = ARM_TAX  + ARM_CTAX  + ARM_ITAX  + ARM_GTRADE  + ARM_REVG  + ARM_GCARB  + ARM_GCOM  + ARM_GOTH

@IDENTITY ARM_TAX  = ARM_TAXR * (ARM_LABSH * 0.5 * (ARM_YER(-1)  + ARM_GDI(-1)) * ARM_YED(-1) * (ARM_LNN / ARM_LNN(-1)  + ARM_TECHL - ARM_TECHL(-1)) + ARM_REMIT  + ARM_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY ARM_CTAX  = ARM_CTAXR * ARM_PROF

@IDENTITY ARM_ITAX  = ARM_ITAXR * (ARM_PCR * ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY ARM_GTRADE  = ARM_GTRADER * ARM_XTN

ARM_REVG  = ARM_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (ARM_YER$ / ARM_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - ARM_YER$(-1) / ARM_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * ARM_EXR / ARM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_GCARB  = ARM_GCARBR * ARM_CO2 * ARM_EXR / 1000

ARM_GCOM  = ARM_GCOM(-1) * ( ARM_OILC / (ARM_OILC + ARM_GASC + ARM_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + ARM_GASC / (ARM_OILC + ARM_GASC + ARM_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + ARM_COALC / (ARM_OILC + ARM_GASC + ARM_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

ARM_GOTH  = ARM_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_EXP  = ARM_EXPE  + ARM_EXPH  + ARM_EXPSP  + ARM_OGC  + ARM_OGI  + ARM_GIP

ARM_EXPE  = ARM_EXPE(-1) * (ARM_YFT / ARM_YFT(-1)) * (ARM_YED / ARM_YED(-1))

ARM_EXPH = ARM_EXPH(-1) * (ARM_YFT / ARM_YFT(-1)) * (ARM_YED / ARM_YED(-1))

ARM_EXPSP  = ARM_EXPSP(-1) * (ARM_YFT / ARM_YFT(-1)) * (ARM_YED / ARM_YED(-1)) * (ARM_POPT - ARM_LNN) / (ARM_POPT(-1) - ARM_LNN(-1))

DLOG(ARM_OGI)  = DLOG(ARM_YFT)  + DLOG(ARM_YED)

ARM_GCR  = ARM_GCR(-1)  + ( ARM_OGC / ARM_YED - ARM_OGC(-1) / ARM_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (ARM_EXPH ) / ARM_YED  - (ARM_EXPH(-1) ) / ARM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (ARM_EXPE ) / ARM_YED  - (ARM_EXPE(-1) ) / ARM_YED(-1) )

ARM_IGR  = ARM_IGR(-1) + (ARM_OGI / ARM_YED - ARM_OGI(-1) / ARM_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (ARM_EXPH ) / ARM_YED  - (ARM_EXPH(-1) ) / ARM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (ARM_EXPE ) / ARM_YED  - (ARM_EXPE(-1) ) / ARM_YED(-1) )

ARM_GIP  = ( ARM_GIP(-1)  + ( ARM_GDN(-1) - ARM_GDN(-2) ) * ARM_GINT(-1) / 100  + ARM_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( ARM_GINT(-1) / 100 - ARM_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (ARM_GDFXSH * (ARM_EXR / ARM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - ARM_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY ARM_GLN  = ARM_REV  - ARM_EXP

@IDENTITY ARM_GLNRATIO  = ARM_GLN / ARM_YEN * 100

ARM_GLNT  = ARM_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

ARM_TFP  = ARM_LABSH * (ARM_TECHL  - ARM_TECHL(-1))

ARM_LABSH  = ARM_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY ARM_LFN  = ARM_LRX * ARM_POPWA

ARM_LRX  = ARM_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(ARM_YER(-1) / ARM_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY ARM_URX  = (1 - ARM_LNN / ARM_LFN) * 100

ARM_URXF  = ARM_URXF(-1) * ARM_URX / ARM_URX(-1) * ARM_LNN / ARM_LNNF / (ARM_LNN(-1) / ARM_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(ARM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(ARM_PCR  / ARM_POPT)

ARM_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(ARM_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

ARM_HEAD19  = ARM_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(ARM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI^2)  , ARM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(ARM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , ARM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

ARM_HEAD55  = ARM_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(ARM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI^2)  , ARM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(ARM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , ARM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(ARM_XTR)  = DLOG(ARM_WDR)  + (1  - ARM_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(ARM_XTDNO$  / ARM_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * ARM_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(ARM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (ARM_EXPH(-1) / ARM_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (ARM_EXPH(-1) / ARM_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(ARM_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(ARM_PM25)

ARM_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( ARM_EXPSP / ARM_YEN )

DLOG(ARM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - ARM_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (ARM_FINC - ARM_FINC(-1))

DLOG(ARM_PCR)  =  - 0.112804719497627  +  - 0.363235759678418 * (LOG(ARM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(ARM_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (ARM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.327631910608178  * DLOG(ARM_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.327631910608178)  * DLOG(ARM_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(ARM_HIC)  - ARM_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * ARM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * ARM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(ARM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(ARM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(ARM_IPR)  =  - 0.159507250424168  - 0.1 * (LOG(ARM_IPR(-1)  / ARM_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * ARM_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * ARM_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(ARM_PCR  + ARM_GCR(-1) + ARM_IGR(-1) + ARM_XTN  / ARM_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(ARM_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (ARM_USER - ARM_USER(-1))  - (0 * ARM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * ARM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - ARM_FUELSH - ARM_TOURSH)) * ARM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * ARM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * ARM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - ARM_FUELSH - ARM_TOURSH)) * ARM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(ARM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(ARM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(ARM_MTR)  =  - 0.0682491596901092  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(ARM_MTR(-1))  - LOG(ARM_PCR(-1) + ARM_ITR(-1) + ARM_GCR(-1) + ARM_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(ARM_YFT(-1) / ARM_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(ARM_CMUD(-1) * ARM_EXR(-1)  / ARM_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * ARM_OMS * LOG(ARM_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.378278262013938  * DLOG(ARM_XTR)  + 0.654538694759853  * DLOG(ARM_PCR)  + 0.123294751564653  * DLOG(ARM_IPR)  + 0.0136486981657467  * DLOG(ARM_GCR + ARM_IGR)

ARM_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * ARM_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * ARM_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * ARM_OILC

ARM_POIL  = ARM_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( ARM_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - ARM_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

ARM_PG  = ARM_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( ARM_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - ARM_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

ARM_PC  = ARM_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( ARM_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - ARM_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(ARM_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

ARM_PE  = ARM_PE(-1) * ( ARM_OILC(-1) / (ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) * ARM_POIL / ARM_POIL(-1)  + ARM_GASC(-1) / (ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) * ARM_PG / ARM_PG(-1)  + ARM_COALC(-1) / (ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) * ARM_PC / ARM_PC(-1)  + ARM_RC(-1) / (ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) * ARM_PR / ARM_PR(-1) )

D(ARM_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(ARM_PM25)  = 0.2 * (ARM_COALC(-1) / ARM_EC(-1) - ARM_COALC(-2) / ARM_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (ARM_COALC(-2) / ARM_EC(-2) - ARM_COALC(-3) / ARM_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (ARM_OILC(-1) / ARM_EC(-1) - ARM_OILC(-2) / ARM_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (ARM_OILC(-2) / ARM_EC(-2) - ARM_OILC(-3) / ARM_EC(-3))

DLOG(ARM_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(ARM_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(ARM_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(ARM_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(ARM_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(ARM_PE * ARM_EXR / ARM_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(ARM_PE(-1) * ARM_EXR(-1) / ARM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(ARM_PE(-2) * ARM_EXR(-2) / ARM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(ARM_PE(-3) * ARM_EXR(-3) / ARM_HIC(-3))  - (ARM_EFF - ARM_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(ARM_COALC)  = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(ARM_COALC(-1) / ARM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.01 * LOG(ARM_PE(-1) / ARM_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) / ARM_EC(-1))

DLOG(ARM_GASC)  = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(ARM_GASC(-1) / ARM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.738325939050689 * LOG(ARM_PE(-1) / ARM_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) / ARM_EC(-1))

DLOG(ARM_RC)  = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( ARM_RC(-1) / ARM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.157329390489485 * LOG(ARM_PE(-1) / ARM_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) / ARM_EC(-1))

DLOG(ARM_OILC)  = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( ARM_OILC(-1) / ARM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.157329390489485 * LOG(ARM_PE(-1) / ARM_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((ARM_COALC(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1) + ARM_OILC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)) / ARM_EC(-1))

ARM_EXR  = ARM_EXR(-1) * ( (ARM_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(AUS_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(AUS_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AUS_MTD)  + 0.4 * (AUS_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (AUS_YER / AUS_YFT  - AUS_YER(-1) / AUS_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + AUS_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + AUS_GCARB / AUS_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (AUS_PREM - AUS_PREM(-1)) / 100

AUS_YED  = AUS_YED(-1) * AUS_HIC / AUS_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_INT  = AUS_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_LTI  = AUS_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (AUS_INT - AUS_INT(-1))  + (AUS_PREM  - AUS_PREM(-1)) / 100

AUS_PREM  = AUS_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (AUS_GDNRATIO(-1)  - AUS_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(AUS_LNN)  = DLOG(AUS_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(AUS_LNN(-1))  - LOG(AUS_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(AUS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AUS_LNNF)  = DLOG(AUS_LNN)

AUS_FUELSH  = AUS_FUELSH(-1)

AUS_TAXR  = AUS_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( AUS_GLNT(-1)  - AUS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * AUS_YEN(-1) / ( ( AUS_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (AUS_YER(-2)  + AUS_GDI(-2)) * AUS_YED(-2) * (AUS_LNN(-1) / AUS_LNN(-2)  + AUS_TECHL(-1) - AUS_TECHL(-2) ) ) + AUS_REMIT(-1)  + AUS_EXPSP(-1) ) * AUS_SOLV

AUS_CTAXR  = AUS_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( AUS_GLNT(-1)  - AUS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * AUS_YEN(-1) / ( AUS_PROF(-1) ) * AUS_SOLV

(AUS_OGC)  = AUS_OGC(-1) * (AUS_YFT / AUS_YFT(-1) * AUS_YED / AUS_YED(-1))

AUS_USER  = (AUS_LTI  - AUS_INFT  + AUS_DEP * 100) / (1  - AUS_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (AUS_GCARB / AUS_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY AUS_XTN  = AUS_XTD$ * AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") * AUS_XTR

@IDENTITY AUS_YEN  = AUS_YER  * AUS_YED

@IDENTITY AUS_MTN  = AUS_MTD  * AUS_MTR

@IDENTITY AUS_XTN$  = AUS_XTN / AUS_EXR

@IDENTITY AUS_YEN$  = AUS_YEN / AUS_EXR

@IDENTITY AUS_MTN$  = AUS_MTN / AUS_EXR

@IDENTITY AUS_MTR$  = AUS_MTR$(-1) * AUS_MTR / AUS_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_XTR$  = AUS_XTR$(-1) * AUS_XTR / AUS_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_YER$  = AUS_YER$(-1) * AUS_YER / AUS_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_YFT$  = AUS_YFT$(-1) * AUS_YFT / AUS_YFT(-1)

AUS_POPT  = AUS_POPT(-1)  - AUS_LIVES

AUS_POPWA  = AUS_POPWA(-1) * AUS_POPT / AUS_POPT(-1)

AUS_SCR  = AUS_SCR(-1)  + ((AUS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (AUS_YFT(-1) / AUS_YER(-1)  - AUS_YFT(-2) / AUS_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY AUS_ITR  = AUS_IGR  + AUS_IPR

@IDENTITY AUS_YER  = AUS_PCR  + AUS_GCR  + AUS_ITR  + AUS_SCR  + AUS_XTR  - AUS_MTR

@IDENTITY AUS_PROF  = (AUS_YEN - AUS_ITAX) * (1 - AUS_LABSH)

@IDENTITY AUS_GDI  = AUS_YER  - AUS_XTR  + AUS_MTR  + AUS_XTN  / ((AUS_YEN  - AUS_XTN  + AUS_MTN)  / (AUS_YER  - AUS_XTR  + AUS_MTR))  - AUS_MTN  / ((AUS_YEN  - AUS_XTN  + AUS_MTN)  / (AUS_YER  - AUS_XTR  + AUS_MTR))

@IDENTITY AUS_RPDI  = AUS_LABSH * 0.5 * (AUS_YER(-1)  + AUS_GDI(-1)) * AUS_YED(-1) / AUS_HIC(-1) * (AUS_LNN / AUS_LNN(-1)  + AUS_TECHL - AUS_TECHL(-1)) + AUS_REMIT / AUS_HIC  + AUS_EXPSP / AUS_HIC  - AUS_TAX / AUS_HIC

DLOG(AUS_YFT)  = (1 - AUS_ALPHA - AUS_LABSH) * DLOG(AUS_K(-1) / AUS_LFN(-1))  + (1 - AUS_ALPHA) * DLOG(AUS_LFN)  + AUS_LABSH * D(AUS_TECHL)  + AUS_ALPHA * (DLOG(AUS_EC)  + D(AUS_EFF) )  - ( AUS_CLIMLOSS / AUS_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (AUS_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY AUS_K  = AUS_K(-1) * (1 - AUS_DEP) + AUS_ITR

DLOG(AUS_MTD)  = (1  - AUS_OMS) * ( DLOG(AUS_CMUD)  + DLOG(AUS_EXR) )  + AUS_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AUS_EXR) )

DLOG(AUS_XTD$)  = (1  - AUS_OXS) * DLOG(AUS_XTDNO$)  + AUS_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

AUS_INFT  = 0.95 * AUS_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

AUS_OXS  = AUS_OXS(-1)

AUS_OMS  = AUS_OMS(-1) * ((AUS_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * AUS_EXR(-1) / AUS_MTN(-1)) / (AUS_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * AUS_EXR(-2) / AUS_MTN(-2)))^0.25

AUS_CXS  = AUS_CXS(-1)

AUS_FINC  = AUS_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_CAN  = AUS_XTN / AUS_EXR  - AUS_MTN / AUS_EXR  + AUS_REMIT / AUS_EXR  + AUS_CANOTH

@IDENTITY AUS_CANRATIO  = AUS_CAN / AUS_YEN$ * 100

AUS_CANOTH  = AUS_CANOTH(-1)  + ((AUS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (AUS_YEN$  / AUS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + AUS_REVG / AUS_EXR  - AUS_REVG(-1) / AUS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(AUS_EFEX)  =  - LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.611239407E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.173684783E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.797983113E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00303136053 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.051298827E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000634326481 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003350093352 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.2398852565 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00279386334 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.865013071E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02176742655 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03226637678 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02101054799 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004082103184 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0897765712 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.006568948E-05 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.233487247E-05 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.022606783E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.146766584E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000797761901 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02165573316 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001169513361 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.950590576E-05 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.787291679E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002102131967 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000109796137 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03653257036 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00149245951 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01040966857 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005037399063 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05229646643 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001338245698 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001400003564 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04942192144 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002878731013 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001115665366 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.134001487E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03271267985 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003183986711 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001318164997 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003301654554 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.070456466E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.557646119E-06 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001807213633 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01297213871 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1120656165 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03019606599 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01271152989 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03597405176 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01324688879 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0108209302 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01270624398 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008366080287 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0190449413 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00962791189 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03854792507 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02254309326 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03133192416 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(AUS_REFEX )  =  - LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.611239407E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.173684783E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.797983113E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00303136053 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.051298827E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000634326481 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003350093352 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.2398852565 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00279386334 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.865013071E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02176742655 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03226637678 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02101054799 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0004082103184 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0897765712 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.006568948E-05 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.233487247E-05 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.022606783E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.146766584E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000797761901 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02165573316 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001169513361 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.950590576E-05 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.787291679E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002102131967 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000109796137 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03653257036 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00149245951 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01040966857 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005037399063 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05229646643 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001338245698 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001400003564 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04942192144 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002878731013 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001115665366 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.134001487E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03271267985 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003183986711 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001318164997 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003301654554 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.070456466E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.557646119E-06 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001807213633 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01297213871 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1120656165 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03019606599 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01271152989 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03597405176 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01324688879 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0108209302 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01270624398 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008366080287 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0190449413 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00962791189 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03854792507 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02254309326 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03133192416 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

AUS_REMIT  = AUS_REMIT(-1) / AUS_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001909970491 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 5.725821599E-05 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01266634299 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02716902349 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02560936728 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004384343396 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01345977063 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 4.089872571E-05 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2303334434 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0188972194 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01937781624 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001384421865 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01181363699 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04359395173 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02733057345 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000243347418 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000271976526 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01100380215 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 3.476391685E-05 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008179745142 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001881341383 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004192119385 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007194085852 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02156065259 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1282420443 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008216553995 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00872574313 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001075636486 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02009622862 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008772776664 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02310369015 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001134939638 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008895472842 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1495462913 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004192119385 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001284219987 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002547990612 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01398531926 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07907530436 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06329659602 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009715492292 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * AUS_EXR

AUS_GINT  = AUS_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 6 * (AUS_LTI  - AUS_LTI(-1))

AUS_GDN  = AUS_GDN(-1) * (AUS_GDFXSH  * (AUS_EXR  / AUS_EXR(-1))  + (1  - AUS_GDFXSH))  - AUS_GLN

@IDENTITY AUS_GDNRATIO  = AUS_GDN / AUS_YEN * 100

AUS_GDFXSH  = ( AUS_GDFXSH(-1) * (AUS_EXR / AUS_EXR(-1) )) / (AUS_GDFXSH(-1) * (AUS_EXR / AUS_EXR(-1))  + 1 - AUS_GDFXSH(-1) )

AUS_TOURSH  = AUS_TOURSH(-1)

AUS_LOCK  = 0

AUS_GCARBR  = AUS_GCARBR(-1)

AUS_GTRADER  = AUS_GTRADER(-1)

AUS_ITAXR  = AUS_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_REV  = AUS_TAX  + AUS_CTAX  + AUS_ITAX  + AUS_GTRADE  + AUS_REVG  + AUS_GCARB  + AUS_GCOM  + AUS_GOTH

@IDENTITY AUS_TAX  = AUS_TAXR * (AUS_LABSH * 0.5 * (AUS_YER(-1)  + AUS_GDI(-1)) * AUS_YED(-1) * (AUS_LNN / AUS_LNN(-1)  + AUS_TECHL - AUS_TECHL(-1)) + AUS_REMIT  + AUS_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY AUS_CTAX  = AUS_CTAXR * AUS_PROF

@IDENTITY AUS_ITAX  = AUS_ITAXR * (AUS_PCR * AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY AUS_GTRADE  = AUS_GTRADER * AUS_XTN

AUS_REVG  = AUS_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (AUS_YER$ / AUS_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - AUS_YER$(-1) / AUS_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * AUS_EXR / AUS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_GCARB  = AUS_GCARBR * AUS_CO2 * AUS_EXR / 1000

AUS_GCOM  = AUS_GCOM(-1) * ( AUS_OILC / (AUS_OILC + AUS_GASC + AUS_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + AUS_GASC / (AUS_OILC + AUS_GASC + AUS_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + AUS_COALC / (AUS_OILC + AUS_GASC + AUS_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

AUS_GOTH  = AUS_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_EXP  = AUS_EXPE  + AUS_EXPH  + AUS_EXPSP  + AUS_OGC  + AUS_OGI  + AUS_GIP

AUS_EXPE  = AUS_EXPE(-1) * (AUS_YFT / AUS_YFT(-1)) * (AUS_YED / AUS_YED(-1))

AUS_EXPH = AUS_EXPH(-1) * (AUS_YFT / AUS_YFT(-1)) * (AUS_YED / AUS_YED(-1))

AUS_EXPSP  = AUS_EXPSP(-1) * (AUS_YFT / AUS_YFT(-1)) * (AUS_YED / AUS_YED(-1)) * (AUS_POPT - AUS_LNN) / (AUS_POPT(-1) - AUS_LNN(-1))

DLOG(AUS_OGI)  = DLOG(AUS_YFT)  + DLOG(AUS_YED)

AUS_GCR  = AUS_GCR(-1)  + ( AUS_OGC / AUS_YED - AUS_OGC(-1) / AUS_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (AUS_EXPH ) / AUS_YED  - (AUS_EXPH(-1) ) / AUS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (AUS_EXPE ) / AUS_YED  - (AUS_EXPE(-1) ) / AUS_YED(-1) )

AUS_IGR  = AUS_IGR(-1) + (AUS_OGI / AUS_YED - AUS_OGI(-1) / AUS_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (AUS_EXPH ) / AUS_YED  - (AUS_EXPH(-1) ) / AUS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (AUS_EXPE ) / AUS_YED  - (AUS_EXPE(-1) ) / AUS_YED(-1) )

AUS_GIP  = ( AUS_GIP(-1)  + ( AUS_GDN(-1) - AUS_GDN(-2) ) * AUS_GINT(-1) / 100  + AUS_GDN(-7) / 6 * ( AUS_GINT(-1) / 100 - AUS_GINT(-7) / 100 ) ) * (AUS_GDFXSH * (AUS_EXR / AUS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - AUS_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY AUS_GLN  = AUS_REV  - AUS_EXP

@IDENTITY AUS_GLNRATIO  = AUS_GLN / AUS_YEN * 100

AUS_GLNT  = AUS_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

AUS_TFP  = AUS_LABSH * (AUS_TECHL  - AUS_TECHL(-1))

AUS_LABSH  = AUS_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY AUS_LFN  = AUS_LRX * AUS_POPWA

AUS_LRX  = AUS_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(AUS_YER(-1) / AUS_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY AUS_URX  = (1 - AUS_LNN / AUS_LFN) * 100

AUS_URXF  = AUS_URXF(-1) * AUS_URX / AUS_URX(-1) * AUS_LNN / AUS_LNNF / (AUS_LNN(-1) / AUS_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(AUS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(AUS_PCR  / AUS_POPT)

AUS_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(AUS_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

AUS_HEAD19  = AUS_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI^2)  , AUS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

AUS_HEAD55  = AUS_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI^2)  , AUS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(AUS_XTR)  = DLOG(AUS_WDR)  + (1  - AUS_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(AUS_XTDNO$  / AUS_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * AUS_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(AUS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (AUS_EXPH(-1) / AUS_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (AUS_EXPH(-1) / AUS_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(AUS_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(AUS_PM25)

AUS_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( AUS_EXPSP / AUS_YEN )

DLOG(AUS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - AUS_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (AUS_FINC - AUS_FINC(-1))

DLOG(AUS_PCR)  =  - 0.168649883462853  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(AUS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(AUS_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (AUS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(AUS_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(AUS_POPT)  +  - 0.25401877374724 * (DLOG(AUS_HIC)  - AUS_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * AUS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * AUS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(AUS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(AUS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AUS_IPR)  =  - 0.171333732314088  - 0.1 * (LOG(AUS_IPR(-1)  / AUS_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * AUS_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * AUS_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(AUS_PCR  + AUS_GCR(-1) + AUS_IGR(-1) + AUS_XTN  / AUS_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(AUS_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (AUS_USER - AUS_USER(-1))  - (0 * AUS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * AUS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - AUS_FUELSH - AUS_TOURSH)) * AUS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * AUS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * AUS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - AUS_FUELSH - AUS_TOURSH)) * AUS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(AUS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(AUS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AUS_MTR)  =  - 0.297914154772917  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(AUS_MTR(-1))  - LOG(AUS_PCR(-1) + AUS_ITR(-1) + AUS_GCR(-1) + AUS_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(AUS_YFT(-1) / AUS_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(AUS_CMUD(-1) * AUS_EXR(-1)  / AUS_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * AUS_OMS * LOG(AUS_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.0882534168436125  * DLOG(AUS_XTR)  + 1  * DLOG(AUS_PCR)  + 0.329171700279113  * DLOG(AUS_IPR)  + 0.376236587580347  * DLOG(AUS_GCR + AUS_IGR)

AUS_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * AUS_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * AUS_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * AUS_OILC

AUS_POIL  = AUS_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( AUS_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - AUS_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

AUS_PG  = AUS_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( AUS_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - AUS_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

AUS_PC  = AUS_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( AUS_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - AUS_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(AUS_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

AUS_PE  = AUS_PE(-1) * ( AUS_OILC(-1) / (AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) * AUS_POIL / AUS_POIL(-1)  + AUS_GASC(-1) / (AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) * AUS_PG / AUS_PG(-1)  + AUS_COALC(-1) / (AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) * AUS_PC / AUS_PC(-1)  + AUS_RC(-1) / (AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) * AUS_PR / AUS_PR(-1) )

D(AUS_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(AUS_PM25)  = 0.2 * (AUS_COALC(-1) / AUS_EC(-1) - AUS_COALC(-2) / AUS_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (AUS_COALC(-2) / AUS_EC(-2) - AUS_COALC(-3) / AUS_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (AUS_OILC(-1) / AUS_EC(-1) - AUS_OILC(-2) / AUS_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (AUS_OILC(-2) / AUS_EC(-2) - AUS_OILC(-3) / AUS_EC(-3))

DLOG(AUS_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(AUS_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(AUS_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(AUS_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AUS_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AUS_PE * AUS_EXR / AUS_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AUS_PE(-1) * AUS_EXR(-1) / AUS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AUS_PE(-2) * AUS_EXR(-2) / AUS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AUS_PE(-3) * AUS_EXR(-3) / AUS_HIC(-3))  - (AUS_EFF - AUS_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(AUS_COALC)  = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(AUS_COALC(-1) / AUS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.0856697118456187 * LOG(AUS_PE(-1) / AUS_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) / AUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(AUS_GASC)  = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(AUS_GASC(-1) / AUS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.301837014408889 * LOG(AUS_PE(-1) / AUS_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) / AUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(AUS_RC)  = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( AUS_RC(-1) / AUS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.0856697118456187 * LOG(AUS_PE(-1) / AUS_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) / AUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(AUS_OILC)  = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( AUS_OILC(-1) / AUS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.0856697118456187 * LOG(AUS_PE(-1) / AUS_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AUS_COALC(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1) + AUS_OILC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)) / AUS_EC(-1))

AUS_EXR  = AUS_EXR(-1) * ( ( (AUS_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (AUS_INT  - USA_INT)  - (AUS_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(AZE_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(AZE_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AZE_MTD)  + 0.4 * (AZE_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (AZE_YER / AZE_YFT  - AZE_YER(-1) / AZE_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + AZE_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + AZE_GCARB / AZE_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (AZE_PREM - AZE_PREM(-1)) / 100

AZE_YED  = AZE_YED(-1) * AZE_HIC / AZE_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_INT  = AZE_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_LTI  = AZE_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (AZE_INT - AZE_INT(-1))  + (AZE_PREM  - AZE_PREM(-1)) / 100

AZE_PREM  = AZE_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (AZE_GDNRATIO(-1)  - AZE_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(AZE_LNN)  = DLOG(AZE_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(AZE_LNN(-1))  - LOG(AZE_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(AZE_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AZE_LNNF)  = DLOG(AZE_LNN)

AZE_FUELSH  = AZE_FUELSH(-1)

AZE_TAXR  = AZE_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( AZE_GLNT(-1)  - AZE_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * AZE_YEN(-1) / ( ( AZE_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (AZE_YER(-2)  + AZE_GDI(-2)) * AZE_YED(-2) * (AZE_LNN(-1) / AZE_LNN(-2)  + AZE_TECHL(-1) - AZE_TECHL(-2) ) ) + AZE_REMIT(-1)  + AZE_EXPSP(-1) ) * AZE_SOLV

AZE_CTAXR  = AZE_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( AZE_GLNT(-1)  - AZE_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * AZE_YEN(-1) / ( AZE_PROF(-1) ) * AZE_SOLV

(AZE_OGC)  = AZE_OGC(-1) * (AZE_YFT / AZE_YFT(-1) * AZE_YED / AZE_YED(-1))

AZE_USER  = (AZE_LTI  - AZE_INFT  + AZE_DEP * 100) / (1  - AZE_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (AZE_GCARB / AZE_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY AZE_XTN  = AZE_XTD$ * AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") * AZE_XTR

@IDENTITY AZE_YEN  = AZE_YER  * AZE_YED

@IDENTITY AZE_MTN  = AZE_MTD  * AZE_MTR

@IDENTITY AZE_XTN$  = AZE_XTN / AZE_EXR

@IDENTITY AZE_YEN$  = AZE_YEN / AZE_EXR

@IDENTITY AZE_MTN$  = AZE_MTN / AZE_EXR

@IDENTITY AZE_MTR$  = AZE_MTR$(-1) * AZE_MTR / AZE_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_XTR$  = AZE_XTR$(-1) * AZE_XTR / AZE_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_YER$  = AZE_YER$(-1) * AZE_YER / AZE_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_YFT$  = AZE_YFT$(-1) * AZE_YFT / AZE_YFT(-1)

AZE_POPT  = AZE_POPT(-1)  - AZE_LIVES

AZE_POPWA  = AZE_POPWA(-1) * AZE_POPT / AZE_POPT(-1)

AZE_SCR  = AZE_SCR(-1)  + ((AZE_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (AZE_YFT(-1) / AZE_YER(-1)  - AZE_YFT(-2) / AZE_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY AZE_ITR  = AZE_IGR  + AZE_IPR

@IDENTITY AZE_YER  = AZE_PCR  + AZE_GCR  + AZE_ITR  + AZE_SCR  + AZE_XTR  - AZE_MTR

@IDENTITY AZE_PROF  = (AZE_YEN - AZE_ITAX) * (1 - AZE_LABSH)

@IDENTITY AZE_GDI  = AZE_YER  - AZE_XTR  + AZE_MTR  + AZE_XTN  / ((AZE_YEN  - AZE_XTN  + AZE_MTN)  / (AZE_YER  - AZE_XTR  + AZE_MTR))  - AZE_MTN  / ((AZE_YEN  - AZE_XTN  + AZE_MTN)  / (AZE_YER  - AZE_XTR  + AZE_MTR))

@IDENTITY AZE_RPDI  = AZE_LABSH * 0.5 * (AZE_YER(-1)  + AZE_GDI(-1)) * AZE_YED(-1) / AZE_HIC(-1) * (AZE_LNN / AZE_LNN(-1)  + AZE_TECHL - AZE_TECHL(-1)) + AZE_REMIT / AZE_HIC  + AZE_EXPSP / AZE_HIC  - AZE_TAX / AZE_HIC

DLOG(AZE_YFT)  = (1 - AZE_ALPHA - AZE_LABSH) * DLOG(AZE_K(-1) / AZE_LFN(-1))  + (1 - AZE_ALPHA) * DLOG(AZE_LFN)  + AZE_LABSH * D(AZE_TECHL)  + AZE_ALPHA * (DLOG(AZE_EC)  + D(AZE_EFF) )  - ( AZE_CLIMLOSS / AZE_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (AZE_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY AZE_K  = AZE_K(-1) * (1 - AZE_DEP) + AZE_ITR

DLOG(AZE_MTD)  = (1  - AZE_OMS) * ( DLOG(AZE_CMUD)  + DLOG(AZE_EXR) )  + AZE_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AZE_EXR) )

DLOG(AZE_XTD$)  = (1  - AZE_OXS) * DLOG(AZE_XTDNO$)  + AZE_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

AZE_INFT  = 0.95 * AZE_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

AZE_OXS  = AZE_OXS(-1)

AZE_OMS  = AZE_OMS(-1) * ((AZE_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * AZE_EXR(-1) / AZE_MTN(-1)) / (AZE_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * AZE_EXR(-2) / AZE_MTN(-2)))^0.25

AZE_CXS  = AZE_CXS(-1)

AZE_FINC  = AZE_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_CAN  = AZE_XTN / AZE_EXR  - AZE_MTN / AZE_EXR  + AZE_REMIT / AZE_EXR  + AZE_CANOTH

@IDENTITY AZE_CANRATIO  = AZE_CAN / AZE_YEN$ * 100

AZE_CANOTH  = AZE_CANOTH(-1)  + ((AZE_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (AZE_YEN$  / AZE_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + AZE_REVG / AZE_EXR  - AZE_REVG(-1) / AZE_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(AZE_EFEX)  =  - LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003860037162 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000301933095 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002733881218 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002668419502 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.489103222E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.035798001E-06 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.481846657E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0310147413 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.4874335E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04235500765 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006756693813 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02479724539 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01432033931 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009806726641 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003581447381 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005656968751 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.900812259E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002189638539 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.908181577E-07 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007222203898 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.194743477E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.504725369E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.102933993E-06 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.964015575E-06 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003217377993 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001613182657 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.86475372E-07 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.505030348E-06 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003657738758 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09683909297 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.44421522E-07 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004491342927 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.955931298E-12 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003345803113 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001917896795 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009011381223 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.26045703E-10 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.90168148E-06 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1178405666 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01083746215 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00100928834 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.110948633E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00193674113 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04476940111 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06410654915 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0280257491 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03826012962 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09975151744 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01387742679 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03112110934 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009022871157 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0245576827 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001843774102 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1567287798 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01773115806 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07830342441 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(AZE_REFEX )  =  - LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003860037162 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000301933095 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002733881218 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002668419502 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.489103222E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.035798001E-06 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.481846657E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0310147413 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.4874335E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04235500765 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006756693813 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02479724539 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01432033931 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009806726641 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003581447381 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005656968751 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.900812259E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002189638539 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.908181577E-07 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007222203898 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.194743477E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.504725369E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.102933993E-06 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.964015575E-06 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003217377993 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001613182657 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.86475372E-07 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.505030348E-06 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003657738758 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.09683909297 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.44421522E-07 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004491342927 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.955931298E-12 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003345803113 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001917896795 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009011381223 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.26045703E-10 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.90168148E-06 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1178405666 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01083746215 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00100928834 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.110948633E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00193674113 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04476940111 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06410654915 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0280257491 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03826012962 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.09975151744 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01387742679 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03112110934 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009022871157 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0245576827 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001843774102 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1567287798 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01773115806 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07830342441 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

AZE_REMIT  = AZE_REMIT(-1) / AZE_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1655793353 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002750258073 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005128450411 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003968267609 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01758945247 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003207249408 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003277190061 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001393304752 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008954807662 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005330344514 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03916827199 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003889650987 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005850385291 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5811001679 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001063196227 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003838737365 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01968696203 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01974585626 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02482563191 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 9.038839577E-06 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0926909334 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002414819068 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01147347473 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * AZE_EXR

AZE_GINT  = AZE_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 7 * (AZE_LTI  - AZE_LTI(-1))

AZE_GDN  = AZE_GDN(-1) * (AZE_GDFXSH  * (AZE_EXR  / AZE_EXR(-1))  + (1  - AZE_GDFXSH))  - AZE_GLN

@IDENTITY AZE_GDNRATIO  = AZE_GDN / AZE_YEN * 100

AZE_GDFXSH  = ( AZE_GDFXSH(-1) * (AZE_EXR / AZE_EXR(-1) )) / (AZE_GDFXSH(-1) * (AZE_EXR / AZE_EXR(-1))  + 1 - AZE_GDFXSH(-1) )

AZE_TOURSH  = AZE_TOURSH(-1)

AZE_LOCK  = 0

AZE_GCARBR  = AZE_GCARBR(-1)

AZE_GTRADER  = AZE_GTRADER(-1)

AZE_ITAXR  = AZE_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_REV  = AZE_TAX  + AZE_CTAX  + AZE_ITAX  + AZE_GTRADE  + AZE_REVG  + AZE_GCARB  + AZE_GCOM  + AZE_GOTH

@IDENTITY AZE_TAX  = AZE_TAXR * (AZE_LABSH * 0.5 * (AZE_YER(-1)  + AZE_GDI(-1)) * AZE_YED(-1) * (AZE_LNN / AZE_LNN(-1)  + AZE_TECHL - AZE_TECHL(-1)) + AZE_REMIT  + AZE_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY AZE_CTAX  = AZE_CTAXR * AZE_PROF

@IDENTITY AZE_ITAX  = AZE_ITAXR * (AZE_PCR * AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY AZE_GTRADE  = AZE_GTRADER * AZE_XTN

AZE_REVG  = AZE_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (AZE_YER$ / AZE_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - AZE_YER$(-1) / AZE_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * AZE_EXR / AZE_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_GCARB  = AZE_GCARBR * AZE_CO2 * AZE_EXR / 1000

AZE_GCOM  = AZE_GCOM(-1) * ( AZE_OILC / (AZE_OILC + AZE_GASC + AZE_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + AZE_GASC / (AZE_OILC + AZE_GASC + AZE_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + AZE_COALC / (AZE_OILC + AZE_GASC + AZE_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

AZE_GOTH  = AZE_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_EXP  = AZE_EXPE  + AZE_EXPH  + AZE_EXPSP  + AZE_OGC  + AZE_OGI  + AZE_GIP

AZE_EXPE  = AZE_EXPE(-1) * (AZE_YFT / AZE_YFT(-1)) * (AZE_YED / AZE_YED(-1))

AZE_EXPH = AZE_EXPH(-1) * (AZE_YFT / AZE_YFT(-1)) * (AZE_YED / AZE_YED(-1))

AZE_EXPSP  = AZE_EXPSP(-1) * (AZE_YFT / AZE_YFT(-1)) * (AZE_YED / AZE_YED(-1)) * (AZE_POPT - AZE_LNN) / (AZE_POPT(-1) - AZE_LNN(-1))

DLOG(AZE_OGI)  = DLOG(AZE_YFT)  + DLOG(AZE_YED)

AZE_GCR  = AZE_GCR(-1)  + ( AZE_OGC / AZE_YED - AZE_OGC(-1) / AZE_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (AZE_EXPH ) / AZE_YED  - (AZE_EXPH(-1) ) / AZE_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (AZE_EXPE ) / AZE_YED  - (AZE_EXPE(-1) ) / AZE_YED(-1) )

AZE_IGR  = AZE_IGR(-1) + (AZE_OGI / AZE_YED - AZE_OGI(-1) / AZE_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (AZE_EXPH ) / AZE_YED  - (AZE_EXPH(-1) ) / AZE_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (AZE_EXPE ) / AZE_YED  - (AZE_EXPE(-1) ) / AZE_YED(-1) )

AZE_GIP  = ( AZE_GIP(-1)  + ( AZE_GDN(-1) - AZE_GDN(-2) ) * AZE_GINT(-1) / 100  + AZE_GDN(-8) / 7 * ( AZE_GINT(-1) / 100 - AZE_GINT(-8) / 100 ) ) * (AZE_GDFXSH * (AZE_EXR / AZE_EXR(-1))  + (1 - AZE_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY AZE_GLN  = AZE_REV  - AZE_EXP

@IDENTITY AZE_GLNRATIO  = AZE_GLN / AZE_YEN * 100

AZE_GLNT  = AZE_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

AZE_TFP  = AZE_LABSH * (AZE_TECHL  - AZE_TECHL(-1))

AZE_LABSH  = AZE_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY AZE_LFN  = AZE_LRX * AZE_POPWA

AZE_LRX  = AZE_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(AZE_YER(-1) / AZE_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY AZE_URX  = (1 - AZE_LNN / AZE_LFN) * 100

AZE_URXF  = AZE_URXF(-1) * AZE_URX / AZE_URX(-1) * AZE_LNN / AZE_LNNF / (AZE_LNN(-1) / AZE_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(AZE_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(AZE_PCR  / AZE_POPT)

AZE_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(AZE_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

AZE_HEAD19  = AZE_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AZE_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI^2)  , AZE_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AZE_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AZE_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

AZE_HEAD55  = AZE_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AZE_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI^2)  , AZE_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AZE_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AZE_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(AZE_XTR)  = DLOG(AZE_WDR)  + (1  - AZE_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(AZE_XTDNO$  / AZE_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * AZE_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(AZE_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (AZE_EXPH(-1) / AZE_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (AZE_EXPH(-1) / AZE_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(AZE_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(AZE_PM25)

AZE_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( AZE_EXPSP / AZE_YEN )

DLOG(AZE_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - AZE_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (AZE_FINC - AZE_FINC(-1))

DLOG(AZE_PCR)  = 0.0711719769959563  +  - 0.166360079460578 * (LOG(AZE_PCR(-1))  - LOG(AZE_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (AZE_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(AZE_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(AZE_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(AZE_HIC)  - AZE_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * AZE_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * AZE_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(AZE_YFT(-1))  - LOG(AZE_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AZE_IPR)  =  - 0.215921415627733  - 0.1 * (LOG(AZE_IPR(-1)  / AZE_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * AZE_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * AZE_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(AZE_PCR  + AZE_GCR(-1) + AZE_IGR(-1) + AZE_XTN  / AZE_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(AZE_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (AZE_USER - AZE_USER(-1))  - (0 * AZE_FUELSH  + 0.26 * AZE_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - AZE_FUELSH - AZE_TOURSH)) * AZE_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * AZE_FUELSH  + 0.26 * AZE_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - AZE_FUELSH - AZE_TOURSH)) * AZE_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(AZE_YFT(-1))  - LOG(AZE_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(AZE_MTR)  =  - 0.249232734989191  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(AZE_MTR(-1))  - LOG(AZE_PCR(-1) + AZE_ITR(-1) + AZE_GCR(-1) + AZE_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(AZE_YFT(-1) / AZE_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(AZE_CMUD(-1) * AZE_EXR(-1)  / AZE_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * AZE_OMS * LOG(AZE_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.193582746513772  * DLOG(AZE_XTR)  + 0.628223294235873  * DLOG(AZE_PCR)  + 0.107505937943245  * DLOG(AZE_IPR)  + 0.25430765502625  * DLOG(AZE_GCR + AZE_IGR)

AZE_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * AZE_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * AZE_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * AZE_OILC

AZE_POIL  = AZE_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( AZE_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - AZE_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

AZE_PG  = AZE_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( AZE_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - AZE_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

AZE_PC  = AZE_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( AZE_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - AZE_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(AZE_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

AZE_PE  = AZE_PE(-1) * ( AZE_OILC(-1) / (AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) * AZE_POIL / AZE_POIL(-1)  + AZE_GASC(-1) / (AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) * AZE_PG / AZE_PG(-1)  + AZE_COALC(-1) / (AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) * AZE_PC / AZE_PC(-1)  + AZE_RC(-1) / (AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) * AZE_PR / AZE_PR(-1) )

D(AZE_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(AZE_PM25)  = 0.2 * (AZE_COALC(-1) / AZE_EC(-1) - AZE_COALC(-2) / AZE_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (AZE_COALC(-2) / AZE_EC(-2) - AZE_COALC(-3) / AZE_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (AZE_OILC(-1) / AZE_EC(-1) - AZE_OILC(-2) / AZE_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (AZE_OILC(-2) / AZE_EC(-2) - AZE_OILC(-3) / AZE_EC(-3))

DLOG(AZE_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(AZE_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(AZE_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(AZE_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AZE_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AZE_PE * AZE_EXR / AZE_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AZE_PE(-1) * AZE_EXR(-1) / AZE_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AZE_PE(-2) * AZE_EXR(-2) / AZE_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(AZE_PE(-3) * AZE_EXR(-3) / AZE_HIC(-3))  - (AZE_EFF - AZE_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(AZE_COALC)  = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(AZE_COALC(-1) / AZE_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(AZE_PE(-1) / AZE_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) / AZE_EC(-1))

DLOG(AZE_GASC)  = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(AZE_GASC(-1) / AZE_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.64724229375059 * LOG(AZE_PE(-1) / AZE_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) / AZE_EC(-1))

DLOG(AZE_RC)  = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( AZE_RC(-1) / AZE_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0247986844471068 * LOG(AZE_PE(-1) / AZE_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) / AZE_EC(-1))

DLOG(AZE_OILC)  = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( AZE_OILC(-1) / AZE_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0247986844471068 * LOG(AZE_PE(-1) / AZE_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((AZE_COALC(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1) + AZE_OILC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)) / AZE_EC(-1))

DLOG(AZE_EXR) = LOG(((AZE_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.328758782191299*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((AZE_INT - USA_INT) - (AZE_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@INNOV AZE_EXR  0.331077671530484

DLOG(BGD_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(BGD_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(BGD_MTD)  + 0.4 * (BGD_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (BGD_YER / BGD_YFT  - BGD_YER(-1) / BGD_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + BGD_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + BGD_GCARB / BGD_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (BGD_PREM - BGD_PREM(-1)) / 100

BGD_YED  = BGD_YED(-1) * BGD_HIC / BGD_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_INT  = BGD_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_LTI  = BGD_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (BGD_INT - BGD_INT(-1))  + (BGD_PREM  - BGD_PREM(-1)) / 100

BGD_PREM  = BGD_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (BGD_GDNRATIO(-1)  - BGD_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(BGD_LNN)  = DLOG(BGD_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(BGD_LNN(-1))  - LOG(BGD_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(BGD_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BGD_LNNF)  = DLOG(BGD_LNN)

BGD_FUELSH  = BGD_FUELSH(-1)

BGD_TAXR  = BGD_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( BGD_GLNT(-1)  - BGD_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * BGD_YEN(-1) / ( ( BGD_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (BGD_YER(-2)  + BGD_GDI(-2)) * BGD_YED(-2) * (BGD_LNN(-1) / BGD_LNN(-2)  + BGD_TECHL(-1) - BGD_TECHL(-2) ) ) + BGD_REMIT(-1)  + BGD_EXPSP(-1) ) * BGD_SOLV

BGD_CTAXR  = BGD_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( BGD_GLNT(-1)  - BGD_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * BGD_YEN(-1) / ( BGD_PROF(-1) ) * BGD_SOLV

(BGD_OGC)  = BGD_OGC(-1) * (BGD_YFT / BGD_YFT(-1) * BGD_YED / BGD_YED(-1))

BGD_USER  = (BGD_LTI  - BGD_INFT  + BGD_DEP * 100) / (1  - BGD_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (BGD_GCARB / BGD_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY BGD_XTN  = BGD_XTD$ * BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") * BGD_XTR

@IDENTITY BGD_YEN  = BGD_YER  * BGD_YED

@IDENTITY BGD_MTN  = BGD_MTD  * BGD_MTR

@IDENTITY BGD_XTN$  = BGD_XTN / BGD_EXR

@IDENTITY BGD_YEN$  = BGD_YEN / BGD_EXR

@IDENTITY BGD_MTN$  = BGD_MTN / BGD_EXR

@IDENTITY BGD_MTR$  = BGD_MTR$(-1) * BGD_MTR / BGD_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_XTR$  = BGD_XTR$(-1) * BGD_XTR / BGD_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_YER$  = BGD_YER$(-1) * BGD_YER / BGD_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_YFT$  = BGD_YFT$(-1) * BGD_YFT / BGD_YFT(-1)

BGD_POPT  = BGD_POPT(-1)  - BGD_LIVES

BGD_POPWA  = BGD_POPWA(-1) * BGD_POPT / BGD_POPT(-1)

BGD_SCR  = BGD_SCR(-1)  + ((BGD_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (BGD_YFT(-1) / BGD_YER(-1)  - BGD_YFT(-2) / BGD_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY BGD_ITR  = BGD_IGR  + BGD_IPR

@IDENTITY BGD_YER  = BGD_PCR  + BGD_GCR  + BGD_ITR  + BGD_SCR  + BGD_XTR  - BGD_MTR

@IDENTITY BGD_PROF  = (BGD_YEN - BGD_ITAX) * (1 - BGD_LABSH)

@IDENTITY BGD_GDI  = BGD_YER  - BGD_XTR  + BGD_MTR  + BGD_XTN  / ((BGD_YEN  - BGD_XTN  + BGD_MTN)  / (BGD_YER  - BGD_XTR  + BGD_MTR))  - BGD_MTN  / ((BGD_YEN  - BGD_XTN  + BGD_MTN)  / (BGD_YER  - BGD_XTR  + BGD_MTR))

@IDENTITY BGD_RPDI  = BGD_LABSH * 0.5 * (BGD_YER(-1)  + BGD_GDI(-1)) * BGD_YED(-1) / BGD_HIC(-1) * (BGD_LNN / BGD_LNN(-1)  + BGD_TECHL - BGD_TECHL(-1)) + BGD_REMIT / BGD_HIC  + BGD_EXPSP / BGD_HIC  - BGD_TAX / BGD_HIC

DLOG(BGD_YFT)  = (1 - BGD_ALPHA - BGD_LABSH) * DLOG(BGD_K(-1) / BGD_LFN(-1))  + (1 - BGD_ALPHA) * DLOG(BGD_LFN)  + BGD_LABSH * D(BGD_TECHL)  + BGD_ALPHA * (DLOG(BGD_EC)  + D(BGD_EFF) )  - ( BGD_CLIMLOSS / BGD_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (BGD_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY BGD_K  = BGD_K(-1) * (1 - BGD_DEP) + BGD_ITR

DLOG(BGD_MTD)  = (1  - BGD_OMS) * ( DLOG(BGD_CMUD)  + DLOG(BGD_EXR) )  + BGD_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(BGD_EXR) )

DLOG(BGD_XTD$)  = (1  - BGD_OXS) * DLOG(BGD_XTDNO$)  + BGD_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

BGD_INFT  = 0.95 * BGD_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

BGD_OXS  = BGD_OXS(-1)

BGD_OMS  = BGD_OMS(-1) * ((BGD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * BGD_EXR(-1) / BGD_MTN(-1)) / (BGD_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * BGD_EXR(-2) / BGD_MTN(-2)))^0.25

BGD_CXS  = BGD_CXS(-1)

BGD_FINC  = BGD_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_CAN  = BGD_XTN / BGD_EXR  - BGD_MTN / BGD_EXR  + BGD_REMIT / BGD_EXR  + BGD_CANOTH

@IDENTITY BGD_CANRATIO  = BGD_CAN / BGD_YEN$ * 100

BGD_CANOTH  = BGD_CANOTH(-1)  + ((BGD_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (BGD_YEN$  / BGD_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + BGD_REVG / BGD_EXR  - BGD_REVG(-1) / BGD_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(BGD_EFEX)  =  - LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001148166962 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001888943479 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01067601733 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003477998003 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003621601143 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01167763519 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01247116677 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08685774619 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05306896318 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04374334384 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

BGD_REMIT  = BGD_REMIT(-1) / BGD_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004522758392 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003275857775 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 5.383612424E-06 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000353001068 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006873360745 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008962825891 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002206422108 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006648530516 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03481686731 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 7.29558156E-05 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2994071139 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004372772289 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01152229198 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001936445832 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001598359241 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004963064343 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001390219567 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01547459882 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001920435582 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 6.512436321E-05 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002064776728 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01684020421 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 1.580577325E-05 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 5.497036488E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01418397918 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 1.594365887E-05 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008551122526 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 1.185681933E-05 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 5.969311114E-05 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0333579214 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 6.672389795E-05 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002123636827 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00655339012 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005870246994 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5414810306 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * BGD_EXR

BGD_GINT  = BGD_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (BGD_LTI  - BGD_LTI(-1))

BGD_GDN  = BGD_GDN(-1) * (BGD_GDFXSH  * (BGD_EXR  / BGD_EXR(-1))  + (1  - BGD_GDFXSH))  - BGD_GLN

@IDENTITY BGD_GDNRATIO  = BGD_GDN / BGD_YEN * 100

BGD_GDFXSH  = ( BGD_GDFXSH(-1) * (BGD_EXR / BGD_EXR(-1) )) / (BGD_GDFXSH(-1) * (BGD_EXR / BGD_EXR(-1))  + 1 - BGD_GDFXSH(-1) )

BGD_TOURSH  = BGD_TOURSH(-1)

BGD_LOCK  = 0

BGD_GCARBR  = BGD_GCARBR(-1)

BGD_GTRADER  = BGD_GTRADER(-1)

BGD_ITAXR  = BGD_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_REV  = BGD_TAX  + BGD_CTAX  + BGD_ITAX  + BGD_GTRADE  + BGD_REVG  + BGD_GCARB  + BGD_GCOM  + BGD_GOTH

@IDENTITY BGD_TAX  = BGD_TAXR * (BGD_LABSH * 0.5 * (BGD_YER(-1)  + BGD_GDI(-1)) * BGD_YED(-1) * (BGD_LNN / BGD_LNN(-1)  + BGD_TECHL - BGD_TECHL(-1)) + BGD_REMIT  + BGD_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY BGD_CTAX  = BGD_CTAXR * BGD_PROF

@IDENTITY BGD_ITAX  = BGD_ITAXR * (BGD_PCR * BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY BGD_GTRADE  = BGD_GTRADER * BGD_XTN

BGD_REVG  = BGD_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (BGD_YER$ / BGD_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - BGD_YER$(-1) / BGD_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * BGD_EXR / BGD_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_GCARB  = BGD_GCARBR * BGD_CO2 * BGD_EXR / 1000

BGD_GCOM  = BGD_GCOM(-1) * ( BGD_OILC / (BGD_OILC + BGD_GASC + BGD_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + BGD_GASC / (BGD_OILC + BGD_GASC + BGD_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + BGD_COALC / (BGD_OILC + BGD_GASC + BGD_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

BGD_GOTH  = BGD_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_EXP  = BGD_EXPE  + BGD_EXPH  + BGD_EXPSP  + BGD_OGC  + BGD_OGI  + BGD_GIP

BGD_EXPE  = BGD_EXPE(-1) * (BGD_YFT / BGD_YFT(-1)) * (BGD_YED / BGD_YED(-1))

BGD_EXPH = BGD_EXPH(-1) * (BGD_YFT / BGD_YFT(-1)) * (BGD_YED / BGD_YED(-1))

BGD_EXPSP  = BGD_EXPSP(-1) * (BGD_YFT / BGD_YFT(-1)) * (BGD_YED / BGD_YED(-1)) * (BGD_POPT - BGD_LNN) / (BGD_POPT(-1) - BGD_LNN(-1))

DLOG(BGD_OGI)  = DLOG(BGD_YFT)  + DLOG(BGD_YED)

BGD_GCR  = BGD_GCR(-1)  + ( BGD_OGC / BGD_YED - BGD_OGC(-1) / BGD_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (BGD_EXPH ) / BGD_YED  - (BGD_EXPH(-1) ) / BGD_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (BGD_EXPE ) / BGD_YED  - (BGD_EXPE(-1) ) / BGD_YED(-1) )

BGD_IGR  = BGD_IGR(-1) + (BGD_OGI / BGD_YED - BGD_OGI(-1) / BGD_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (BGD_EXPH ) / BGD_YED  - (BGD_EXPH(-1) ) / BGD_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (BGD_EXPE ) / BGD_YED  - (BGD_EXPE(-1) ) / BGD_YED(-1) )

BGD_GIP  = ( BGD_GIP(-1)  + ( BGD_GDN(-1) - BGD_GDN(-2) ) * BGD_GINT(-1) / 100  + BGD_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( BGD_GINT(-1) / 100 - BGD_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (BGD_GDFXSH * (BGD_EXR / BGD_EXR(-1))  + (1 - BGD_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY BGD_GLN  = BGD_REV  - BGD_EXP

@IDENTITY BGD_GLNRATIO  = BGD_GLN / BGD_YEN * 100

BGD_GLNT  = BGD_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

BGD_TFP  = BGD_LABSH * (BGD_TECHL  - BGD_TECHL(-1))

BGD_LABSH  = BGD_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY BGD_LFN  = BGD_LRX * BGD_POPWA

BGD_LRX  = BGD_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(BGD_YER(-1) / BGD_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY BGD_URX  = (1 - BGD_LNN / BGD_LFN) * 100

BGD_URXF  = BGD_URXF(-1) * BGD_URX / BGD_URX(-1) * BGD_LNN / BGD_LNNF / (BGD_LNN(-1) / BGD_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(BGD_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(BGD_PCR  / BGD_POPT)

BGD_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(BGD_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

BGD_HEAD19  = BGD_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BGD_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI^2)  , BGD_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BGD_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BGD_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

BGD_HEAD55  = BGD_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BGD_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI^2)  , BGD_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BGD_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BGD_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(BGD_XTR)  = DLOG(BGD_WDR)  + (1  - BGD_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(BGD_XTDNO$  / BGD_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * BGD_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(BGD_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (BGD_EXPH(-1) / BGD_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (BGD_EXPH(-1) / BGD_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(BGD_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(BGD_PM25)

BGD_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( BGD_EXPSP / BGD_YEN )

DLOG(BGD_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - BGD_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (BGD_FINC - BGD_FINC(-1))

DLOG(BGD_PCR)  =  - 0.00138501418482672  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(BGD_PCR(-1))  - LOG(BGD_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (BGD_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(BGD_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(BGD_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(BGD_HIC)  - BGD_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * BGD_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * BGD_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(BGD_YFT(-1))  - LOG(BGD_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BGD_IPR)  =  - 0.121920457841063  - 0.1 * (LOG(BGD_IPR(-1)  / BGD_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * BGD_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * BGD_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(BGD_PCR  + BGD_GCR(-1) + BGD_IGR(-1) + BGD_XTN  / BGD_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(BGD_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (BGD_USER - BGD_USER(-1))  - (0 * BGD_FUELSH  + 0.26 * BGD_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - BGD_FUELSH - BGD_TOURSH)) * BGD_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * BGD_FUELSH  + 0.26 * BGD_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - BGD_FUELSH - BGD_TOURSH)) * BGD_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(BGD_YFT(-1))  - LOG(BGD_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BGD_MTR)  =  - 0.268079852388585  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(BGD_MTR(-1))  - LOG(BGD_PCR(-1) + BGD_ITR(-1) + BGD_GCR(-1) + BGD_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(BGD_YFT(-1) / BGD_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(BGD_CMUD(-1) * BGD_EXR(-1)  / BGD_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * BGD_OMS * LOG(BGD_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.405174656102725  * DLOG(BGD_XTR)  + 1  * DLOG(BGD_PCR)  + 0.471520548879983  * DLOG(BGD_IPR)  + 0.180055771799804  * DLOG(BGD_GCR + BGD_IGR)

BGD_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * BGD_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * BGD_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * BGD_OILC

BGD_POIL  = BGD_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( BGD_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - BGD_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

BGD_PG  = BGD_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( BGD_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - BGD_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

BGD_PC  = BGD_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( BGD_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - BGD_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(BGD_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

BGD_PE  = BGD_PE(-1) * ( BGD_OILC(-1) / (BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) * BGD_POIL / BGD_POIL(-1)  + BGD_GASC(-1) / (BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) * BGD_PG / BGD_PG(-1)  + BGD_COALC(-1) / (BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) * BGD_PC / BGD_PC(-1)  + BGD_RC(-1) / (BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) * BGD_PR / BGD_PR(-1) )

D(BGD_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(BGD_PM25)  = 0.2 * (BGD_COALC(-1) / BGD_EC(-1) - BGD_COALC(-2) / BGD_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (BGD_COALC(-2) / BGD_EC(-2) - BGD_COALC(-3) / BGD_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (BGD_OILC(-1) / BGD_EC(-1) - BGD_OILC(-2) / BGD_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (BGD_OILC(-2) / BGD_EC(-2) - BGD_OILC(-3) / BGD_EC(-3))

DLOG(BGD_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(BGD_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(BGD_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(BGD_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(BGD_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BGD_PE * BGD_EXR / BGD_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BGD_PE(-1) * BGD_EXR(-1) / BGD_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BGD_PE(-2) * BGD_EXR(-2) / BGD_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BGD_PE(-3) * BGD_EXR(-3) / BGD_HIC(-3))  - (BGD_EFF - BGD_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(BGD_COALC)  = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(BGD_COALC(-1) / BGD_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.0063709486606635 * LOG(BGD_PE(-1) / BGD_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) / BGD_EC(-1))

DLOG(BGD_GASC)  = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(BGD_GASC(-1) / BGD_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.703461639964873 * LOG(BGD_PE(-1) / BGD_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) / BGD_EC(-1))

DLOG(BGD_RC)  = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( BGD_RC(-1) / BGD_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(BGD_PE(-1) / BGD_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) / BGD_EC(-1))

DLOG(BGD_OILC)  = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( BGD_OILC(-1) / BGD_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(BGD_PE(-1) / BGD_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BGD_COALC(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1) + BGD_OILC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)) / BGD_EC(-1))

BGD_EXR  = BGD_EXR(-1) * ( (BGD_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(BTN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(BTN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(BTN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (BTN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (BTN_YER / BTN_YFT  - BTN_YER(-1) / BTN_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + BTN_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + BTN_GCARB / BTN_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (BTN_PREM - BTN_PREM(-1)) / 100

BTN_YED  = BTN_YED(-1) * BTN_HIC / BTN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_INT  = BTN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_LTI  = BTN_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (BTN_INT - BTN_INT(-1))  + (BTN_PREM  - BTN_PREM(-1)) / 100

BTN_PREM  = BTN_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (BTN_GDNRATIO(-1)  - BTN_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(BTN_LNN)  = DLOG(BTN_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(BTN_LNN(-1))  - LOG(BTN_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(BTN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BTN_LNNF)  = DLOG(BTN_LNN)

BTN_FUELSH  = BTN_FUELSH(-1)

BTN_TAXR  = BTN_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( BTN_GLNT(-1)  - BTN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * BTN_YEN(-1) / ( ( BTN_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (BTN_YER(-2)  + BTN_GDI(-2)) * BTN_YED(-2) * (BTN_LNN(-1) / BTN_LNN(-2)  + BTN_TECHL(-1) - BTN_TECHL(-2) ) ) + BTN_REMIT(-1)  + BTN_EXPSP(-1) ) * BTN_SOLV

BTN_CTAXR  = BTN_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( BTN_GLNT(-1)  - BTN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * BTN_YEN(-1) / ( BTN_PROF(-1) ) * BTN_SOLV

(BTN_OGC)  = BTN_OGC(-1) * (BTN_YFT / BTN_YFT(-1) * BTN_YED / BTN_YED(-1))

BTN_USER  = (BTN_LTI  - BTN_INFT  + BTN_DEP * 100) / (1  - BTN_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (BTN_GCARB / BTN_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY BTN_XTN  = BTN_XTD$ * BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") * BTN_XTR

@IDENTITY BTN_YEN  = BTN_YER  * BTN_YED

@IDENTITY BTN_MTN  = BTN_MTD  * BTN_MTR

@IDENTITY BTN_XTN$  = BTN_XTN / BTN_EXR

@IDENTITY BTN_YEN$  = BTN_YEN / BTN_EXR

@IDENTITY BTN_MTN$  = BTN_MTN / BTN_EXR

@IDENTITY BTN_MTR$  = BTN_MTR$(-1) * BTN_MTR / BTN_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_XTR$  = BTN_XTR$(-1) * BTN_XTR / BTN_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_YER$  = BTN_YER$(-1) * BTN_YER / BTN_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_YFT$  = BTN_YFT$(-1) * BTN_YFT / BTN_YFT(-1)

BTN_POPT  = BTN_POPT(-1)  - BTN_LIVES

BTN_POPWA  = BTN_POPWA(-1) * BTN_POPT / BTN_POPT(-1)

BTN_SCR  = BTN_SCR(-1)  + ((BTN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (BTN_YFT(-1) / BTN_YER(-1)  - BTN_YFT(-2) / BTN_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY BTN_ITR  = BTN_IGR  + BTN_IPR

@IDENTITY BTN_YER  = BTN_PCR  + BTN_GCR  + BTN_ITR  + BTN_SCR  + BTN_XTR  - BTN_MTR

@IDENTITY BTN_PROF  = (BTN_YEN - BTN_ITAX) * (1 - BTN_LABSH)

@IDENTITY BTN_GDI  = BTN_YER  - BTN_XTR  + BTN_MTR  + BTN_XTN  / ((BTN_YEN  - BTN_XTN  + BTN_MTN)  / (BTN_YER  - BTN_XTR  + BTN_MTR))  - BTN_MTN  / ((BTN_YEN  - BTN_XTN  + BTN_MTN)  / (BTN_YER  - BTN_XTR  + BTN_MTR))

@IDENTITY BTN_RPDI  = BTN_LABSH * 0.5 * (BTN_YER(-1)  + BTN_GDI(-1)) * BTN_YED(-1) / BTN_HIC(-1) * (BTN_LNN / BTN_LNN(-1)  + BTN_TECHL - BTN_TECHL(-1)) + BTN_REMIT / BTN_HIC  + BTN_EXPSP / BTN_HIC  - BTN_TAX / BTN_HIC

DLOG(BTN_YFT)  = (1 - BTN_ALPHA - BTN_LABSH) * DLOG(BTN_K(-1) / BTN_LFN(-1))  + (1 - BTN_ALPHA) * DLOG(BTN_LFN)  + BTN_LABSH * D(BTN_TECHL)  + BTN_ALPHA * (DLOG(BTN_EC)  + D(BTN_EFF) )  - ( BTN_CLIMLOSS / BTN_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (BTN_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY BTN_K  = BTN_K(-1) * (1 - BTN_DEP) + BTN_ITR

DLOG(BTN_MTD)  = (1  - BTN_OMS) * ( DLOG(BTN_CMUD)  + DLOG(BTN_EXR) )  + BTN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(BTN_EXR) )

DLOG(BTN_XTD$)  = (1  - BTN_OXS) * DLOG(BTN_XTDNO$)  + BTN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

BTN_INFT  = 0.95 * BTN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

BTN_OXS  = BTN_OXS(-1)

BTN_OMS  = BTN_OMS(-1) * ((BTN_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * BTN_EXR(-1) / BTN_MTN(-1)) / (BTN_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * BTN_EXR(-2) / BTN_MTN(-2)))^0.25

BTN_CXS  = BTN_CXS(-1)

BTN_FINC  = BTN_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_CAN  = BTN_XTN / BTN_EXR  - BTN_MTN / BTN_EXR  + BTN_REMIT / BTN_EXR  + BTN_CANOTH

@IDENTITY BTN_CANRATIO  = BTN_CAN / BTN_YEN$ * 100

BTN_CANOTH  = BTN_CANOTH(-1)  + ((BTN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (BTN_YEN$  / BTN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + BTN_REVG / BTN_EXR  - BTN_REVG(-1) / BTN_EXR(-1)
