BTN_ITAXR  = BTN_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_REV  = BTN_TAX  + BTN_CTAX  + BTN_ITAX  + BTN_GTRADE  + BTN_REVG  + BTN_GCARB  + BTN_GCOM  + BTN_GOTH

@IDENTITY BTN_TAX  = BTN_TAXR * (BTN_LABSH * 0.5 * (BTN_YER(-1)  + BTN_GDI(-1)) * BTN_YED(-1) * (BTN_LNN / BTN_LNN(-1)  + BTN_TECHL - BTN_TECHL(-1)) + BTN_REMIT  + BTN_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY BTN_CTAX  = BTN_CTAXR * BTN_PROF

@IDENTITY BTN_ITAX  = BTN_ITAXR * (BTN_PCR * BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY BTN_GTRADE  = BTN_GTRADER * BTN_XTN

BTN_REVG  = BTN_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (BTN_YER$ / BTN_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - BTN_YER$(-1) / BTN_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * BTN_EXR / BTN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_GCARB  = BTN_GCARBR * BTN_CO2 * BTN_EXR / 1000

BTN_GCOM  = BTN_GCOM(-1) * ( BTN_OILC / (BTN_OILC + BTN_GASC + BTN_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + BTN_GASC / (BTN_OILC + BTN_GASC + BTN_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + BTN_COALC / (BTN_OILC + BTN_GASC + BTN_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

BTN_GOTH  = BTN_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_EXP  = BTN_EXPE  + BTN_EXPH  + BTN_EXPSP  + BTN_OGC  + BTN_OGI  + BTN_GIP

BTN_EXPE  = BTN_EXPE(-1) * (BTN_YFT / BTN_YFT(-1)) * (BTN_YED / BTN_YED(-1))

BTN_EXPH = BTN_EXPH(-1) * (BTN_YFT / BTN_YFT(-1)) * (BTN_YED / BTN_YED(-1))

BTN_EXPSP  = BTN_EXPSP(-1) * (BTN_YFT / BTN_YFT(-1)) * (BTN_YED / BTN_YED(-1)) * (BTN_POPT - BTN_LNN) / (BTN_POPT(-1) - BTN_LNN(-1))

DLOG(BTN_OGI)  = DLOG(BTN_YFT)  + DLOG(BTN_YED)

BTN_GCR  = BTN_GCR(-1)  + ( BTN_OGC / BTN_YED - BTN_OGC(-1) / BTN_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (BTN_EXPH ) / BTN_YED  - (BTN_EXPH(-1) ) / BTN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (BTN_EXPE ) / BTN_YED  - (BTN_EXPE(-1) ) / BTN_YED(-1) )

BTN_IGR  = BTN_IGR(-1) + (BTN_OGI / BTN_YED - BTN_OGI(-1) / BTN_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (BTN_EXPH ) / BTN_YED  - (BTN_EXPH(-1) ) / BTN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (BTN_EXPE ) / BTN_YED  - (BTN_EXPE(-1) ) / BTN_YED(-1) )

BTN_GIP  = ( BTN_GIP(-1)  + ( BTN_GDN(-1) - BTN_GDN(-2) ) * BTN_GINT(-1) / 100  + BTN_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( BTN_GINT(-1) / 100 - BTN_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (BTN_GDFXSH * (BTN_EXR / BTN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - BTN_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY BTN_GLN  = BTN_REV  - BTN_EXP

@IDENTITY BTN_GLNRATIO  = BTN_GLN / BTN_YEN * 100

BTN_GLNT  = BTN_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

BTN_TFP  = BTN_LABSH * (BTN_TECHL  - BTN_TECHL(-1))

BTN_LABSH  = BTN_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY BTN_LFN  = BTN_LRX * BTN_POPWA

BTN_LRX  = BTN_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(BTN_YER(-1) / BTN_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY BTN_URX  = (1 - BTN_LNN / BTN_LFN) * 100

BTN_URXF  = BTN_URXF(-1) * BTN_URX / BTN_URX(-1) * BTN_LNN / BTN_LNNF / (BTN_LNN(-1) / BTN_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(BTN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(BTN_PCR  / BTN_POPT)

BTN_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(BTN_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

BTN_HEAD19  = BTN_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BTN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI^2)  , BTN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BTN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BTN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

BTN_HEAD55  = BTN_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BTN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI^2)  , BTN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BTN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BTN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(BTN_XTR)  = DLOG(BTN_WDR)  + (1  - BTN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(BTN_XTDNO$  / BTN_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * BTN_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(BTN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (BTN_EXPH(-1) / BTN_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (BTN_EXPH(-1) / BTN_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(BTN_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(BTN_PM25)

BTN_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( BTN_EXPSP / BTN_YEN )

DLOG(BTN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - BTN_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (BTN_FINC - BTN_FINC(-1))

DLOG(BTN_PCR)  =  - 0.36298337594476  +  - 0.380963411356238 * (LOG(BTN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(BTN_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (BTN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(BTN_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.7)  * DLOG(BTN_POPT)  +  - 1 * (DLOG(BTN_HIC)  - BTN_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * BTN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * BTN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(BTN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(BTN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BTN_IPR)  =  - 0.063486598424185  - 0.1 * (LOG(BTN_IPR(-1)  / BTN_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * BTN_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * BTN_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(BTN_PCR  + BTN_GCR(-1) + BTN_IGR(-1) + BTN_XTN  / BTN_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(BTN_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (BTN_USER - BTN_USER(-1))  - (0 * BTN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * BTN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - BTN_FUELSH - BTN_TOURSH)) * BTN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * BTN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * BTN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - BTN_FUELSH - BTN_TOURSH)) * BTN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(BTN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(BTN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BTN_MTR)  =  - 0.0873059936765669  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(BTN_MTR(-1))  - LOG(BTN_PCR(-1) + BTN_ITR(-1) + BTN_GCR(-1) + BTN_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(BTN_YFT(-1) / BTN_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(BTN_CMUD(-1) * BTN_EXR(-1)  / BTN_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * BTN_OMS * LOG(BTN_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.34669832272015  * DLOG(BTN_XTR)  + 0.321840112099003  * DLOG(BTN_PCR)  + 0.286912869105868  * DLOG(BTN_IPR)  + 0.00495398799395036  * DLOG(BTN_GCR + BTN_IGR)

BTN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * BTN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * BTN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * BTN_OILC

BTN_POIL  = BTN_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( BTN_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - BTN_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

BTN_PG  = BTN_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( BTN_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - BTN_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

BTN_PC  = BTN_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( BTN_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - BTN_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(BTN_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

BTN_PE  = BTN_PE(-1) * ( BTN_OILC(-1) / (BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) * BTN_POIL / BTN_POIL(-1)  + BTN_GASC(-1) / (BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) * BTN_PG / BTN_PG(-1)  + BTN_COALC(-1) / (BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) * BTN_PC / BTN_PC(-1)  + BTN_RC(-1) / (BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) * BTN_PR / BTN_PR(-1) )

D(BTN_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(BTN_PM25)  = 0.2 * (BTN_COALC(-1) / BTN_EC(-1) - BTN_COALC(-2) / BTN_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (BTN_COALC(-2) / BTN_EC(-2) - BTN_COALC(-3) / BTN_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (BTN_OILC(-1) / BTN_EC(-1) - BTN_OILC(-2) / BTN_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (BTN_OILC(-2) / BTN_EC(-2) - BTN_OILC(-3) / BTN_EC(-3))

DLOG(BTN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(BTN_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(BTN_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(BTN_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(BTN_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BTN_PE * BTN_EXR / BTN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BTN_PE(-1) * BTN_EXR(-1) / BTN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BTN_PE(-2) * BTN_EXR(-2) / BTN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BTN_PE(-3) * BTN_EXR(-3) / BTN_HIC(-3))  - (BTN_EFF - BTN_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(BTN_COALC)  = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(BTN_COALC(-1) / BTN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.865789933500646 * LOG(BTN_PE(-1) / BTN_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) / BTN_EC(-1))

DLOG(BTN_GASC)  = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(BTN_GASC(-1) / BTN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.01 * LOG(BTN_PE(-1) / BTN_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) / BTN_EC(-1))

DLOG(BTN_RC)  = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( BTN_RC(-1) / BTN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.865789933500646 * LOG(BTN_PE(-1) / BTN_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) / BTN_EC(-1))

DLOG(BTN_OILC)  = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( BTN_OILC(-1) / BTN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.865789933500646 * LOG(BTN_PE(-1) / BTN_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BTN_COALC(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1) + BTN_OILC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)) / BTN_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY BTN_EXR  = BTN_EXR(-1) * IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1)

DLOG(BRN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(BRN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(BRN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (BRN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (BRN_YER / BRN_YFT  - BRN_YER(-1) / BRN_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + BRN_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + BRN_GCARB / BRN_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (BRN_PREM - BRN_PREM(-1)) / 100

BRN_YED  = BRN_YED(-1) * BRN_HIC / BRN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_INT  = BRN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_LTI  = BRN_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (BRN_INT - BRN_INT(-1))  + (BRN_PREM  - BRN_PREM(-1)) / 100

BRN_PREM  = BRN_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (BRN_GDNRATIO(-1)  - BRN_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(BRN_LNN)  = DLOG(BRN_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(BRN_LNN(-1))  - LOG(BRN_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(BRN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BRN_LNNF)  = DLOG(BRN_LNN)

BRN_FUELSH  = BRN_FUELSH(-1)

BRN_TAXR  = BRN_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( BRN_GLNT(-1)  - BRN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * BRN_YEN(-1) / ( ( BRN_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (BRN_YER(-2)  + BRN_GDI(-2)) * BRN_YED(-2) * (BRN_LNN(-1) / BRN_LNN(-2)  + BRN_TECHL(-1) - BRN_TECHL(-2) ) ) + BRN_REMIT(-1)  + BRN_EXPSP(-1) ) * BRN_SOLV

BRN_CTAXR  = BRN_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( BRN_GLNT(-1)  - BRN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * BRN_YEN(-1) / ( BRN_PROF(-1) ) * BRN_SOLV

(BRN_OGC)  = BRN_OGC(-1) * (BRN_YFT / BRN_YFT(-1) * BRN_YED / BRN_YED(-1))

BRN_USER  = (BRN_LTI  - BRN_INFT  + BRN_DEP * 100) / (1  - BRN_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (BRN_GCARB / BRN_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY BRN_XTN  = BRN_XTD$ * BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") * BRN_XTR

@IDENTITY BRN_YEN  = BRN_YER  * BRN_YED

@IDENTITY BRN_MTN  = BRN_MTD  * BRN_MTR

@IDENTITY BRN_XTN$  = BRN_XTN / BRN_EXR

@IDENTITY BRN_YEN$  = BRN_YEN / BRN_EXR

@IDENTITY BRN_MTN$  = BRN_MTN / BRN_EXR

@IDENTITY BRN_MTR$  = BRN_MTR$(-1) * BRN_MTR / BRN_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_XTR$  = BRN_XTR$(-1) * BRN_XTR / BRN_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_YER$  = BRN_YER$(-1) * BRN_YER / BRN_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_YFT$  = BRN_YFT$(-1) * BRN_YFT / BRN_YFT(-1)

BRN_POPT  = BRN_POPT(-1)  - BRN_LIVES

BRN_POPWA  = BRN_POPWA(-1) * BRN_POPT / BRN_POPT(-1)

BRN_SCR  = BRN_SCR(-1)  + ((BRN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (BRN_YFT(-1) / BRN_YER(-1)  - BRN_YFT(-2) / BRN_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY BRN_ITR  = BRN_IGR  + BRN_IPR

@IDENTITY BRN_YER  = BRN_PCR  + BRN_GCR  + BRN_ITR  + BRN_SCR  + BRN_XTR  - BRN_MTR

@IDENTITY BRN_PROF  = (BRN_YEN - BRN_ITAX) * (1 - BRN_LABSH)

@IDENTITY BRN_GDI  = BRN_YER  - BRN_XTR  + BRN_MTR  + BRN_XTN  / ((BRN_YEN  - BRN_XTN  + BRN_MTN)  / (BRN_YER  - BRN_XTR  + BRN_MTR))  - BRN_MTN  / ((BRN_YEN  - BRN_XTN  + BRN_MTN)  / (BRN_YER  - BRN_XTR  + BRN_MTR))

@IDENTITY BRN_RPDI  = BRN_LABSH * 0.5 * (BRN_YER(-1)  + BRN_GDI(-1)) * BRN_YED(-1) / BRN_HIC(-1) * (BRN_LNN / BRN_LNN(-1)  + BRN_TECHL - BRN_TECHL(-1)) + BRN_REMIT / BRN_HIC  + BRN_EXPSP / BRN_HIC  - BRN_TAX / BRN_HIC

DLOG(BRN_YFT)  = (1 - BRN_ALPHA - BRN_LABSH) * DLOG(BRN_K(-1) / BRN_LFN(-1))  + (1 - BRN_ALPHA) * DLOG(BRN_LFN)  + BRN_LABSH * D(BRN_TECHL)  + BRN_ALPHA * (DLOG(BRN_EC)  + D(BRN_EFF) )  - ( BRN_CLIMLOSS / BRN_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (BRN_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY BRN_K  = BRN_K(-1) * (1 - BRN_DEP) + BRN_ITR

DLOG(BRN_MTD)  = (1  - BRN_OMS) * ( DLOG(BRN_CMUD)  + DLOG(BRN_EXR) )  + BRN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(BRN_EXR) )

DLOG(BRN_XTD$)  = (1  - BRN_OXS) * DLOG(BRN_XTDNO$)  + BRN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

BRN_INFT  = 0.95 * BRN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

BRN_OXS  = BRN_OXS(-1)

BRN_OMS  = BRN_OMS(-1) * ((BRN_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * BRN_EXR(-1) / BRN_MTN(-1)) / (BRN_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * BRN_EXR(-2) / BRN_MTN(-2)))^0.25

BRN_CXS  = BRN_CXS(-1)

BRN_FINC  = BRN_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_CAN  = BRN_XTN / BRN_EXR  - BRN_MTN / BRN_EXR  + BRN_REMIT / BRN_EXR  + BRN_CANOTH

@IDENTITY BRN_CANRATIO  = BRN_CAN / BRN_YEN$ * 100

BRN_CANOTH  = BRN_CANOTH(-1)  + ((BRN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (BRN_YEN$  / BRN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + BRN_REVG / BRN_EXR  - BRN_REVG(-1) / BRN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(BRN_EFEX)  =  - LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.004356052E-07 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.430989856E-09 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03316291519 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.999717436E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001364989541 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.593575531E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005807914383 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09950005384 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.162950961E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.087730563E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002293972551 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05793704321 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01568450589 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.596885102E-05 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.2039591008 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.988464914E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.180490629E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.287960264E-07 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.023101926E-06 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.657941745E-06 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.08062989097 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.093542068E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.332083243E-07 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.724822962E-08 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001010553048 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.390749075E-08 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1581466607 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.47122685E-06 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.927237624E-05 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.667819036E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06320151631 * "2015"))  + 0.006527030133 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03020342083 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0133736139 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01415987029 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04083499787 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002999763643 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01002495988 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008990212535 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004473037967 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02747299495 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001341746389 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008588455421 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002027958056 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003853844307 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(BRN_REFEX )  =  - LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.004356052E-07 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.430989856E-09 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03316291519 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.999717436E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001364989541 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.593575531E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005807914383 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.09950005384 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.162950961E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.087730563E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002293972551 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05793704321 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01568450589 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.596885102E-05 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.2039591008 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.988464914E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.180490629E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.287960264E-07 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.023101926E-06 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.657941745E-06 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08062989097 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.093542068E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.332083243E-07 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.724822962E-08 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.035296598E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.460746768E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01684499473 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.87487141E-05 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002938258368 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003806748152 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.09506947566 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001010553048 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.390749075E-08 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1581466607 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.47122685E-06 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.927237624E-05 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.667819036E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06320151631 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.961334585E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.87119766E-07 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005663274576 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.32278253E-08 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.525811621E-09 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.473013761E-07 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006527030133 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03020342083 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0133736139 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01415987029 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04083499787 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002999763643 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01002495988 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008990212535 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004473037967 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02747299495 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001341746389 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008588455421 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002027958056 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003853844307 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

BRN_REMIT  = 0

BRN_GINT  = BRN_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (BRN_LTI  - BRN_LTI(-1))

BRN_GDN  = BRN_GDN(-1) * (BRN_GDFXSH  * (BRN_EXR  / BRN_EXR(-1))  + (1  - BRN_GDFXSH))  - BRN_GLN

@IDENTITY BRN_GDNRATIO  = BRN_GDN / BRN_YEN * 100

BRN_GDFXSH  = ( BRN_GDFXSH(-1) * (BRN_EXR / BRN_EXR(-1) )) / (BRN_GDFXSH(-1) * (BRN_EXR / BRN_EXR(-1))  + 1 - BRN_GDFXSH(-1) )

BRN_TOURSH  = BRN_TOURSH(-1)

BRN_LOCK  = 0

BRN_GCARBR  = BRN_GCARBR(-1)

BRN_GTRADER  = BRN_GTRADER(-1)

BRN_ITAXR  = BRN_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_REV  = BRN_TAX  + BRN_CTAX  + BRN_ITAX  + BRN_GTRADE  + BRN_REVG  + BRN_GCARB  + BRN_GCOM  + BRN_GOTH

@IDENTITY BRN_TAX  = BRN_TAXR * (BRN_LABSH * 0.5 * (BRN_YER(-1)  + BRN_GDI(-1)) * BRN_YED(-1) * (BRN_LNN / BRN_LNN(-1)  + BRN_TECHL - BRN_TECHL(-1)) + BRN_REMIT  + BRN_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY BRN_CTAX  = BRN_CTAXR * BRN_PROF

@IDENTITY BRN_ITAX  = BRN_ITAXR * (BRN_PCR * BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY BRN_GTRADE  = BRN_GTRADER * BRN_XTN

BRN_REVG  = BRN_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (BRN_YER$ / BRN_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - BRN_YER$(-1) / BRN_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * BRN_EXR / BRN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_GCARB  = BRN_GCARBR * BRN_CO2 * BRN_EXR / 1000

BRN_GCOM  = BRN_GCOM(-1) * ( BRN_OILC / (BRN_OILC + BRN_GASC + BRN_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + BRN_GASC / (BRN_OILC + BRN_GASC + BRN_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + BRN_COALC / (BRN_OILC + BRN_GASC + BRN_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

BRN_GOTH  = BRN_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_EXP  = BRN_EXPE  + BRN_EXPH  + BRN_EXPSP  + BRN_OGC  + BRN_OGI  + BRN_GIP

BRN_EXPE  = BRN_EXPE(-1) * (BRN_YFT / BRN_YFT(-1)) * (BRN_YED / BRN_YED(-1))

BRN_EXPH = BRN_EXPH(-1) * (BRN_YFT / BRN_YFT(-1)) * (BRN_YED / BRN_YED(-1))

BRN_EXPSP  = BRN_EXPSP(-1) * (BRN_YFT / BRN_YFT(-1)) * (BRN_YED / BRN_YED(-1)) * (BRN_POPT - BRN_LNN) / (BRN_POPT(-1) - BRN_LNN(-1))

DLOG(BRN_OGI)  = DLOG(BRN_YFT)  + DLOG(BRN_YED)

BRN_GCR  = BRN_GCR(-1)  + ( BRN_OGC / BRN_YED - BRN_OGC(-1) / BRN_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (BRN_EXPH ) / BRN_YED  - (BRN_EXPH(-1) ) / BRN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (BRN_EXPE ) / BRN_YED  - (BRN_EXPE(-1) ) / BRN_YED(-1) )

BRN_IGR  = BRN_IGR(-1) + (BRN_OGI / BRN_YED - BRN_OGI(-1) / BRN_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (BRN_EXPH ) / BRN_YED  - (BRN_EXPH(-1) ) / BRN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (BRN_EXPE ) / BRN_YED  - (BRN_EXPE(-1) ) / BRN_YED(-1) )

BRN_GIP  = ( BRN_GIP(-1)  + ( BRN_GDN(-1) - BRN_GDN(-2) ) * BRN_GINT(-1) / 100  + BRN_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( BRN_GINT(-1) / 100 - BRN_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (BRN_GDFXSH * (BRN_EXR / BRN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - BRN_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY BRN_GLN  = BRN_REV  - BRN_EXP

@IDENTITY BRN_GLNRATIO  = BRN_GLN / BRN_YEN * 100

BRN_GLNT  = BRN_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

BRN_TFP  = BRN_LABSH * (BRN_TECHL  - BRN_TECHL(-1))

BRN_LABSH  = BRN_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY BRN_LFN  = BRN_LRX * BRN_POPWA

BRN_LRX  = BRN_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(BRN_YER(-1) / BRN_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY BRN_URX  = (1 - BRN_LNN / BRN_LFN) * 100

BRN_URXF  = BRN_URXF(-1) * BRN_URX / BRN_URX(-1) * BRN_LNN / BRN_LNNF / (BRN_LNN(-1) / BRN_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(BRN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(BRN_PCR  / BRN_POPT)

BRN_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(BRN_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

BRN_HEAD19  = BRN_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI^2)  , BRN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

BRN_HEAD55  = BRN_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI^2)  , BRN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(BRN_XTR)  = DLOG(BRN_WDR)  + (1  - BRN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(BRN_XTDNO$  / BRN_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * BRN_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(BRN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (BRN_EXPH(-1) / BRN_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (BRN_EXPH(-1) / BRN_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(BRN_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(BRN_PM25)

BRN_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( BRN_EXPSP / BRN_YEN )

DLOG(BRN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - BRN_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (BRN_FINC - BRN_FINC(-1))

DLOG(BRN_PCR)  =  - 0.16650568166279  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(BRN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(BRN_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (BRN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(BRN_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(BRN_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(BRN_HIC)  - BRN_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * BRN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * BRN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(BRN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(BRN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BRN_IPR)  =  - 0.123949030516964  - 0.1 * (LOG(BRN_IPR(-1)  / BRN_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * BRN_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * BRN_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(BRN_PCR  + BRN_GCR(-1) + BRN_IGR(-1) + BRN_XTN  / BRN_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(BRN_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (BRN_USER - BRN_USER(-1))  - (0 * BRN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * BRN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - BRN_FUELSH - BRN_TOURSH)) * BRN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * BRN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * BRN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - BRN_FUELSH - BRN_TOURSH)) * BRN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(BRN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(BRN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(BRN_MTR)  =  - 0.217532601528424  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(BRN_MTR(-1))  - LOG(BRN_PCR(-1) + BRN_ITR(-1) + BRN_GCR(-1) + BRN_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(BRN_YFT(-1) / BRN_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(BRN_CMUD(-1) * BRN_EXR(-1)  / BRN_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * BRN_OMS * LOG(BRN_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.404364328161406  * DLOG(BRN_XTR)  + 0.171510970707175  * DLOG(BRN_PCR)  + 0.341356842289251  * DLOG(BRN_IPR)  + 0.26610069570081  * DLOG(BRN_GCR + BRN_IGR)

BRN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * BRN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * BRN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * BRN_OILC

BRN_POIL  = BRN_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( BRN_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - BRN_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

BRN_PG  = BRN_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( BRN_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - BRN_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

BRN_PC  = BRN_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( BRN_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - BRN_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(BRN_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

BRN_PE  = BRN_PE(-1) * ( BRN_OILC(-1) / (BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) * BRN_POIL / BRN_POIL(-1)  + BRN_GASC(-1) / (BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) * BRN_PG / BRN_PG(-1)  + BRN_COALC(-1) / (BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) * BRN_PC / BRN_PC(-1)  + BRN_RC(-1) / (BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) * BRN_PR / BRN_PR(-1) )

D(BRN_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(BRN_PM25)  = 0.2 * (BRN_COALC(-1) / BRN_EC(-1) - BRN_COALC(-2) / BRN_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (BRN_COALC(-2) / BRN_EC(-2) - BRN_COALC(-3) / BRN_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (BRN_OILC(-1) / BRN_EC(-1) - BRN_OILC(-2) / BRN_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (BRN_OILC(-2) / BRN_EC(-2) - BRN_OILC(-3) / BRN_EC(-3))

DLOG(BRN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(BRN_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(BRN_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(BRN_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(BRN_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BRN_PE * BRN_EXR / BRN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BRN_PE(-1) * BRN_EXR(-1) / BRN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BRN_PE(-2) * BRN_EXR(-2) / BRN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(BRN_PE(-3) * BRN_EXR(-3) / BRN_HIC(-3))  - (BRN_EFF - BRN_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(BRN_COALC)  = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(BRN_COALC(-1) / BRN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(BRN_PE(-1) / BRN_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) / BRN_EC(-1))

DLOG(BRN_GASC)  = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(BRN_GASC(-1) / BRN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.738826645928014 * LOG(BRN_PE(-1) / BRN_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) / BRN_EC(-1))

DLOG(BRN_RC)  = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( BRN_RC(-1) / BRN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(BRN_PE(-1) / BRN_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) / BRN_EC(-1))

DLOG(BRN_OILC)  = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( BRN_OILC(-1) / BRN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(BRN_PE(-1) / BRN_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((BRN_COALC(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1) + BRN_OILC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)) / BRN_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY BRN_EXR  = BRN_EXR(-1) * SGP_EXR / SGP_EXR(-1)

DLOG(KHM_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(KHM_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KHM_MTD)  + 0.4 * (KHM_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (KHM_YER / KHM_YFT  - KHM_YER(-1) / KHM_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + KHM_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + KHM_GCARB / KHM_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (KHM_PREM - KHM_PREM(-1)) / 100

KHM_YED  = KHM_YED(-1) * KHM_HIC / KHM_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_INT  = KHM_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_LTI  = KHM_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (KHM_INT - KHM_INT(-1))  + (KHM_PREM  - KHM_PREM(-1)) / 100

KHM_PREM  = KHM_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (KHM_GDNRATIO(-1)  - KHM_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(KHM_LNN)  = DLOG(KHM_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(KHM_LNN(-1))  - LOG(KHM_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(KHM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KHM_LNNF)  = DLOG(KHM_LNN)

KHM_FUELSH  = KHM_FUELSH(-1)

KHM_TAXR  = KHM_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KHM_GLNT(-1)  - KHM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KHM_YEN(-1) / ( ( KHM_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (KHM_YER(-2)  + KHM_GDI(-2)) * KHM_YED(-2) * (KHM_LNN(-1) / KHM_LNN(-2)  + KHM_TECHL(-1) - KHM_TECHL(-2) ) ) + KHM_REMIT(-1)  + KHM_EXPSP(-1) ) * KHM_SOLV

KHM_CTAXR  = KHM_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KHM_GLNT(-1)  - KHM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KHM_YEN(-1) / ( KHM_PROF(-1) ) * KHM_SOLV

(KHM_OGC)  = KHM_OGC(-1) * (KHM_YFT / KHM_YFT(-1) * KHM_YED / KHM_YED(-1))

KHM_USER  = (KHM_LTI  - KHM_INFT  + KHM_DEP * 100) / (1  - KHM_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (KHM_GCARB / KHM_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY KHM_XTN  = KHM_XTD$ * KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") * KHM_XTR

@IDENTITY KHM_YEN  = KHM_YER  * KHM_YED

@IDENTITY KHM_MTN  = KHM_MTD  * KHM_MTR

@IDENTITY KHM_XTN$  = KHM_XTN / KHM_EXR

@IDENTITY KHM_YEN$  = KHM_YEN / KHM_EXR

@IDENTITY KHM_MTN$  = KHM_MTN / KHM_EXR

@IDENTITY KHM_MTR$  = KHM_MTR$(-1) * KHM_MTR / KHM_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_XTR$  = KHM_XTR$(-1) * KHM_XTR / KHM_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_YER$  = KHM_YER$(-1) * KHM_YER / KHM_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_YFT$  = KHM_YFT$(-1) * KHM_YFT / KHM_YFT(-1)

KHM_POPT  = KHM_POPT(-1)  - KHM_LIVES

KHM_POPWA  = KHM_POPWA(-1) * KHM_POPT / KHM_POPT(-1)

KHM_SCR  = KHM_SCR(-1)  + ((KHM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KHM_YFT(-1) / KHM_YER(-1)  - KHM_YFT(-2) / KHM_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY KHM_ITR  = KHM_IGR  + KHM_IPR

@IDENTITY KHM_YER  = KHM_PCR  + KHM_GCR  + KHM_ITR  + KHM_SCR  + KHM_XTR  - KHM_MTR

@IDENTITY KHM_PROF  = (KHM_YEN - KHM_ITAX) * (1 - KHM_LABSH)

@IDENTITY KHM_GDI  = KHM_YER  - KHM_XTR  + KHM_MTR  + KHM_XTN  / ((KHM_YEN  - KHM_XTN  + KHM_MTN)  / (KHM_YER  - KHM_XTR  + KHM_MTR))  - KHM_MTN  / ((KHM_YEN  - KHM_XTN  + KHM_MTN)  / (KHM_YER  - KHM_XTR  + KHM_MTR))

@IDENTITY KHM_RPDI  = KHM_LABSH * 0.5 * (KHM_YER(-1)  + KHM_GDI(-1)) * KHM_YED(-1) / KHM_HIC(-1) * (KHM_LNN / KHM_LNN(-1)  + KHM_TECHL - KHM_TECHL(-1)) + KHM_REMIT / KHM_HIC  + KHM_EXPSP / KHM_HIC  - KHM_TAX / KHM_HIC

DLOG(KHM_YFT)  = (1 - KHM_ALPHA - KHM_LABSH) * DLOG(KHM_K(-1) / KHM_LFN(-1))  + (1 - KHM_ALPHA) * DLOG(KHM_LFN)  + KHM_LABSH * D(KHM_TECHL)  + KHM_ALPHA * (DLOG(KHM_EC)  + D(KHM_EFF) )  - ( KHM_CLIMLOSS / KHM_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (KHM_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY KHM_K  = KHM_K(-1) * (1 - KHM_DEP) + KHM_ITR

DLOG(KHM_MTD)  = (1  - KHM_OMS) * ( DLOG(KHM_CMUD)  + DLOG(KHM_EXR) )  + KHM_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KHM_EXR) )

DLOG(KHM_XTD$)  = (1  - KHM_OXS) * DLOG(KHM_XTDNO$)  + KHM_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

KHM_INFT  = 0.95 * KHM_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

KHM_OXS  = KHM_OXS(-1)

KHM_OMS  = KHM_OMS(-1) * ((KHM_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * KHM_EXR(-1) / KHM_MTN(-1)) / (KHM_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * KHM_EXR(-2) / KHM_MTN(-2)))^0.25

KHM_CXS  = KHM_CXS(-1)

KHM_FINC  = KHM_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_CAN  = KHM_XTN / KHM_EXR  - KHM_MTN / KHM_EXR  + KHM_REMIT / KHM_EXR  + KHM_CANOTH

@IDENTITY KHM_CANRATIO  = KHM_CAN / KHM_YEN$ * 100

KHM_CANOTH  = KHM_CANOTH(-1)  + ((KHM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KHM_YEN$  / KHM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KHM_REVG / KHM_EXR  - KHM_REVG(-1) / KHM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(KHM_EFEX)  =  - LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.631309992E-07 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.165533252E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007307358602 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.125752719E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002024018871 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.950045064E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002423169862 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.148563999 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.892214896E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.665851957E-07 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0319363792 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005782947548 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01439276781 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.799372067E-05 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05026341001 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001099592875 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.483521206E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.584719949E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008033030633 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002160807448 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01130776888 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.137297689E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.356120826E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.926034644E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.195093856E-06 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006697743818 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008910518512 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.447451586E-05 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001576058053 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02623921159 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001920683678 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.293778346E-07 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05447677014 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.2493396E-07 * @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.547527831E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.205401186E-07 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001540846935 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03219885134 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009755395749 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008761460309 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001471605193 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001126606022 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02029792216 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(KHM_REFEX )  =  - LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.631309992E-07 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.165533252E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007307358602 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.125752719E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002024018871 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.950045064E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002423169862 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.148563999 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.892214896E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.665851957E-07 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0319363792 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005782947548 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01439276781 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.799372067E-05 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05026341001 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001099592875 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.483521206E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.584719949E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008033030633 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002160807448 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01130776888 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.137297689E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.356120826E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.926034644E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.195093856E-06 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006697743818 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008910518512 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.447451586E-05 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001576058053 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02623921159 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001920683678 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.293778346E-07 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05447677014 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.2493396E-07 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003094696279 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.016387226E-08 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1734092955 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.547527831E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.205401186E-07 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001540846935 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.961243194E-06 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.507483877E-07 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.522167701E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07429130913 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1381143167 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05091450916 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01773175788 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03219885134 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009755395749 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008761460309 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001471605193 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001126606022 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02029792216 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001868525887 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05704793176 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0470234563 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004988951526 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

KHM_REMIT  = KHM_REMIT(-1) / KHM_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03685643201 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01169452623 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003191171051 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000366198817 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001172710018 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06831857211 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 4.998527089E-05 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001375041781 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002938873823 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01459684479 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007846101321 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01577212824 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008099962325 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006719138499 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 2.835843096E-05 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 9.653034302E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 4.105437803E-05 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5971666249 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 9.737125292E-06 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2081201666 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00162926707 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 1.784972958E-05 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002928481155 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02531057053 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 5.130790949E-06 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * KHM_EXR

KHM_GINT  = KHM_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (KHM_LTI  - KHM_LTI(-1))

KHM_GDN  = KHM_GDN(-1) * (KHM_GDFXSH  * (KHM_EXR  / KHM_EXR(-1))  + (1  - KHM_GDFXSH))  - KHM_GLN

@IDENTITY KHM_GDNRATIO  = KHM_GDN / KHM_YEN * 100

KHM_GDFXSH  = ( KHM_GDFXSH(-1) * (KHM_EXR / KHM_EXR(-1) )) / (KHM_GDFXSH(-1) * (KHM_EXR / KHM_EXR(-1))  + 1 - KHM_GDFXSH(-1) )

KHM_TOURSH  = KHM_TOURSH(-1)

KHM_LOCK  = 0

KHM_GCARBR  = KHM_GCARBR(-1)

KHM_GTRADER  = KHM_GTRADER(-1)

KHM_ITAXR  = KHM_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_REV  = KHM_TAX  + KHM_CTAX  + KHM_ITAX  + KHM_GTRADE  + KHM_REVG  + KHM_GCARB  + KHM_GCOM  + KHM_GOTH

@IDENTITY KHM_TAX  = KHM_TAXR * (KHM_LABSH * 0.5 * (KHM_YER(-1)  + KHM_GDI(-1)) * KHM_YED(-1) * (KHM_LNN / KHM_LNN(-1)  + KHM_TECHL - KHM_TECHL(-1)) + KHM_REMIT  + KHM_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY KHM_CTAX  = KHM_CTAXR * KHM_PROF

@IDENTITY KHM_ITAX  = KHM_ITAXR * (KHM_PCR * KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY KHM_GTRADE  = KHM_GTRADER * KHM_XTN

KHM_REVG  = KHM_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (KHM_YER$ / KHM_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - KHM_YER$(-1) / KHM_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * KHM_EXR / KHM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_GCARB  = KHM_GCARBR * KHM_CO2 * KHM_EXR / 1000

KHM_GCOM  = KHM_GCOM(-1) * ( KHM_OILC / (KHM_OILC + KHM_GASC + KHM_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + KHM_GASC / (KHM_OILC + KHM_GASC + KHM_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + KHM_COALC / (KHM_OILC + KHM_GASC + KHM_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

KHM_GOTH  = KHM_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_EXP  = KHM_EXPE  + KHM_EXPH  + KHM_EXPSP  + KHM_OGC  + KHM_OGI  + KHM_GIP

KHM_EXPE  = KHM_EXPE(-1) * (KHM_YFT / KHM_YFT(-1)) * (KHM_YED / KHM_YED(-1))

KHM_EXPH = KHM_EXPH(-1) * (KHM_YFT / KHM_YFT(-1)) * (KHM_YED / KHM_YED(-1))

KHM_EXPSP  = KHM_EXPSP(-1) * (KHM_YFT / KHM_YFT(-1)) * (KHM_YED / KHM_YED(-1)) * (KHM_POPT - KHM_LNN) / (KHM_POPT(-1) - KHM_LNN(-1))

DLOG(KHM_OGI)  = DLOG(KHM_YFT)  + DLOG(KHM_YED)

KHM_GCR  = KHM_GCR(-1)  + ( KHM_OGC / KHM_YED - KHM_OGC(-1) / KHM_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (KHM_EXPH ) / KHM_YED  - (KHM_EXPH(-1) ) / KHM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KHM_EXPE ) / KHM_YED  - (KHM_EXPE(-1) ) / KHM_YED(-1) )

KHM_IGR  = KHM_IGR(-1) + (KHM_OGI / KHM_YED - KHM_OGI(-1) / KHM_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (KHM_EXPH ) / KHM_YED  - (KHM_EXPH(-1) ) / KHM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KHM_EXPE ) / KHM_YED  - (KHM_EXPE(-1) ) / KHM_YED(-1) )

KHM_GIP  = ( KHM_GIP(-1)  + ( KHM_GDN(-1) - KHM_GDN(-2) ) * KHM_GINT(-1) / 100  + KHM_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( KHM_GINT(-1) / 100 - KHM_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (KHM_GDFXSH * (KHM_EXR / KHM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KHM_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY KHM_GLN  = KHM_REV  - KHM_EXP

@IDENTITY KHM_GLNRATIO  = KHM_GLN / KHM_YEN * 100

KHM_GLNT  = KHM_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

KHM_TFP  = KHM_LABSH * (KHM_TECHL  - KHM_TECHL(-1))

KHM_LABSH  = KHM_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY KHM_LFN  = KHM_LRX * KHM_POPWA

KHM_LRX  = KHM_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(KHM_YER(-1) / KHM_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY KHM_URX  = (1 - KHM_LNN / KHM_LFN) * 100

KHM_URXF  = KHM_URXF(-1) * KHM_URX / KHM_URX(-1) * KHM_LNN / KHM_LNNF / (KHM_LNN(-1) / KHM_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(KHM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KHM_PCR  / KHM_POPT)

KHM_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(KHM_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

KHM_HEAD19  = KHM_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KHM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI^2)  , KHM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KHM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KHM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

KHM_HEAD55  = KHM_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KHM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI^2)  , KHM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KHM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KHM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(KHM_XTR)  = DLOG(KHM_WDR)  + (1  - KHM_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(KHM_XTDNO$  / KHM_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * KHM_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(KHM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (KHM_EXPH(-1) / KHM_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (KHM_EXPH(-1) / KHM_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(KHM_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(KHM_PM25)

KHM_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( KHM_EXPSP / KHM_YEN )

DLOG(KHM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - KHM_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (KHM_FINC - KHM_FINC(-1))

DLOG(KHM_PCR)  = 0.0606552427796278  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(KHM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KHM_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (KHM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KHM_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(KHM_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(KHM_HIC)  - KHM_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * KHM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * KHM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KHM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KHM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KHM_IPR)  =  - 0.180263535670664  - 0.1 * (LOG(KHM_IPR(-1)  / KHM_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * KHM_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * KHM_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(KHM_PCR  + KHM_GCR(-1) + KHM_IGR(-1) + KHM_XTN  / KHM_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(KHM_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (KHM_USER - KHM_USER(-1))  - (0 * KHM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KHM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KHM_FUELSH - KHM_TOURSH)) * KHM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * KHM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KHM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KHM_FUELSH - KHM_TOURSH)) * KHM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KHM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KHM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KHM_MTR)  =  - 0.0305781525560725  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(KHM_MTR(-1))  - LOG(KHM_PCR(-1) + KHM_ITR(-1) + KHM_GCR(-1) + KHM_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(KHM_YFT(-1) / KHM_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(KHM_CMUD(-1) * KHM_EXR(-1)  / KHM_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * KHM_OMS * LOG(KHM_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.20449230437208  * DLOG(KHM_XTR)  + 0.461272293403523  * DLOG(KHM_PCR)  + 0.106569638324094  * DLOG(KHM_IPR)  + 0.00197584863464838  * DLOG(KHM_GCR + KHM_IGR)

KHM_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * KHM_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * KHM_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * KHM_OILC

KHM_POIL  = KHM_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( KHM_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - KHM_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

KHM_PG  = KHM_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( KHM_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - KHM_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

KHM_PC  = KHM_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( KHM_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - KHM_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(KHM_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

KHM_PE  = KHM_PE(-1) * ( KHM_OILC(-1) / (KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) * KHM_POIL / KHM_POIL(-1)  + KHM_GASC(-1) / (KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) * KHM_PG / KHM_PG(-1)  + KHM_COALC(-1) / (KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) * KHM_PC / KHM_PC(-1)  + KHM_RC(-1) / (KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) * KHM_PR / KHM_PR(-1) )

D(KHM_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(KHM_PM25)  = 0.2 * (KHM_COALC(-1) / KHM_EC(-1) - KHM_COALC(-2) / KHM_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (KHM_COALC(-2) / KHM_EC(-2) - KHM_COALC(-3) / KHM_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (KHM_OILC(-1) / KHM_EC(-1) - KHM_OILC(-2) / KHM_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (KHM_OILC(-2) / KHM_EC(-2) - KHM_OILC(-3) / KHM_EC(-3))

DLOG(KHM_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(KHM_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(KHM_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(KHM_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KHM_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KHM_PE * KHM_EXR / KHM_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KHM_PE(-1) * KHM_EXR(-1) / KHM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KHM_PE(-2) * KHM_EXR(-2) / KHM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KHM_PE(-3) * KHM_EXR(-3) / KHM_HIC(-3))  - (KHM_EFF - KHM_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(KHM_COALC)  = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KHM_COALC(-1) / KHM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.646806576796427 * LOG(KHM_PE(-1) / KHM_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) / KHM_EC(-1))

DLOG(KHM_GASC)  = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KHM_GASC(-1) / KHM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.01 * LOG(KHM_PE(-1) / KHM_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) / KHM_EC(-1))

DLOG(KHM_RC)  = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KHM_RC(-1) / KHM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.646806576796427 * LOG(KHM_PE(-1) / KHM_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) / KHM_EC(-1))

DLOG(KHM_OILC)  = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KHM_OILC(-1) / KHM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.646806576796427 * LOG(KHM_PE(-1) / KHM_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KHM_COALC(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1) + KHM_OILC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)) / KHM_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY KHM_EXR  = KHM_EXR(-1)

DLOG(CHN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(CHN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(CHN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (CHN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (CHN_YER / CHN_YFT  - CHN_YER(-1) / CHN_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + CHN_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + CHN_GCARB / CHN_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (CHN_PREM - CHN_PREM(-1)) / 100

CHN_YED  = CHN_YED(-1) * CHN_HIC / CHN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_INT  = CHN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_LTI  = CHN_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (CHN_INT - CHN_INT(-1))  + (CHN_PREM  - CHN_PREM(-1)) / 100

CHN_PREM  = CHN_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (CHN_GDNRATIO(-1)  - CHN_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(CHN_LNN)  = DLOG(CHN_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(CHN_LNN(-1))  - LOG(CHN_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(CHN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(CHN_LNNF)  = DLOG(CHN_LNN)

CHN_FUELSH  = CHN_FUELSH(-1)

CHN_TAXR  = CHN_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( CHN_GLNT(-1)  - CHN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * CHN_YEN(-1) / ( ( CHN_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (CHN_YER(-2)  + CHN_GDI(-2)) * CHN_YED(-2) * (CHN_LNN(-1) / CHN_LNN(-2)  + CHN_TECHL(-1) - CHN_TECHL(-2) ) ) + CHN_REMIT(-1)  + CHN_EXPSP(-1) ) * CHN_SOLV

CHN_CTAXR  = CHN_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( CHN_GLNT(-1)  - CHN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * CHN_YEN(-1) / ( CHN_PROF(-1) ) * CHN_SOLV

(CHN_OGC)  = CHN_OGC(-1) * (CHN_YFT / CHN_YFT(-1) * CHN_YED / CHN_YED(-1))

CHN_USER  = (CHN_LTI  - CHN_INFT  + CHN_DEP * 100) / (1  - CHN_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (CHN_GCARB / CHN_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY CHN_XTN  = CHN_XTD$ * CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") * CHN_XTR

@IDENTITY CHN_YEN  = CHN_YER  * CHN_YED

@IDENTITY CHN_MTN  = CHN_MTD  * CHN_MTR

@IDENTITY CHN_XTN$  = CHN_XTN / CHN_EXR

@IDENTITY CHN_YEN$  = CHN_YEN / CHN_EXR

@IDENTITY CHN_MTN$  = CHN_MTN / CHN_EXR

@IDENTITY CHN_MTR$  = CHN_MTR$(-1) * CHN_MTR / CHN_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_XTR$  = CHN_XTR$(-1) * CHN_XTR / CHN_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_YER$  = CHN_YER$(-1) * CHN_YER / CHN_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_YFT$  = CHN_YFT$(-1) * CHN_YFT / CHN_YFT(-1)

CHN_POPT  = CHN_POPT(-1)  - CHN_LIVES

CHN_POPWA  = CHN_POPWA(-1) * CHN_POPT / CHN_POPT(-1)

CHN_SCR  = CHN_SCR(-1)  + ((CHN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (CHN_YFT(-1) / CHN_YER(-1)  - CHN_YFT(-2) / CHN_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY CHN_ITR  = CHN_IGR  + CHN_IPR

@IDENTITY CHN_YER  = CHN_PCR  + CHN_GCR  + CHN_ITR  + CHN_SCR  + CHN_XTR  - CHN_MTR

@IDENTITY CHN_PROF  = (CHN_YEN - CHN_ITAX) * (1 - CHN_LABSH)

@IDENTITY CHN_GDI  = CHN_YER  - CHN_XTR  + CHN_MTR  + CHN_XTN  / ((CHN_YEN  - CHN_XTN  + CHN_MTN)  / (CHN_YER  - CHN_XTR  + CHN_MTR))  - CHN_MTN  / ((CHN_YEN  - CHN_XTN  + CHN_MTN)  / (CHN_YER  - CHN_XTR  + CHN_MTR))

@IDENTITY CHN_RPDI  = CHN_LABSH * 0.5 * (CHN_YER(-1)  + CHN_GDI(-1)) * CHN_YED(-1) / CHN_HIC(-1) * (CHN_LNN / CHN_LNN(-1)  + CHN_TECHL - CHN_TECHL(-1)) + CHN_REMIT / CHN_HIC  + CHN_EXPSP / CHN_HIC  - CHN_TAX / CHN_HIC

DLOG(CHN_YFT)  = (1 - CHN_ALPHA - CHN_LABSH) * DLOG(CHN_K(-1) / CHN_LFN(-1))  + (1 - CHN_ALPHA) * DLOG(CHN_LFN)  + CHN_LABSH * D(CHN_TECHL)  + CHN_ALPHA * (DLOG(CHN_EC)  + D(CHN_EFF) )  - ( CHN_CLIMLOSS / CHN_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (CHN_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY CHN_K  = CHN_K(-1) * (1 - CHN_DEP) + CHN_ITR

DLOG(CHN_MTD)  = (1  - CHN_OMS) * ( DLOG(CHN_CMUD)  + DLOG(CHN_EXR) )  + CHN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(CHN_EXR) )

DLOG(CHN_XTD$)  = (1  - CHN_OXS) * DLOG(CHN_XTDNO$)  + CHN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

CHN_INFT  = 0.95 * CHN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

CHN_OXS  = CHN_OXS(-1)

CHN_OMS  = CHN_OMS(-1) * ((CHN_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * CHN_EXR(-1) / CHN_MTN(-1)) / (CHN_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * CHN_EXR(-2) / CHN_MTN(-2)))^0.25

CHN_CXS  = CHN_CXS(-1)

CHN_FINC  = CHN_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_CAN  = CHN_XTN / CHN_EXR  - CHN_MTN / CHN_EXR  + CHN_REMIT / CHN_EXR  + CHN_CANOTH

@IDENTITY CHN_CANRATIO  = CHN_CAN / CHN_YEN$ * 100

CHN_CANOTH  = CHN_CANOTH(-1)  + ((CHN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (CHN_YEN$  / CHN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + CHN_REVG / CHN_EXR  - CHN_REVG(-1) / CHN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(CHN_EFEX)  =  - LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.81340423E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001308406467 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007110980958 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03390031764 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02782455658 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04541624174 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07136399514 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05058447559 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

CHN_REMIT  = CHN_REMIT(-1) / CHN_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04590600625 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 3.844707109E-05 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01558437209 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001058019685 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 8.690386128E-05 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001958378434 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01014557552 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009211764883 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 3.07244895E-05 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01534401903 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 2.286473637E-05 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2442736921 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005642230961 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006466433254 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001198144252 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01848784946 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06658174108 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004829237804 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 2.706255906E-05 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001384388335 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06510101923 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002691965446 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 2.581214379E-05 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03364129102 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004264094702 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008183967943 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005260084127 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006514674797 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002178759293 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009796372537 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003230626481 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005099489032 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04340496264 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01343982502 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 2.681365721E-05 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001070891364 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 1.500498324E-05 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002067620935 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2535937552 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001726466227 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007715955371 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 9.556745279E-06 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 6.073445598E-06 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007241708915 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03154248463 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07572157154 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001626748495 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * CHN_EXR

CHN_GINT  = CHN_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 7 * (CHN_LTI  - CHN_LTI(-1))

CHN_GDN  = CHN_GDN(-1) * (CHN_GDFXSH  * (CHN_EXR  / CHN_EXR(-1))  + (1  - CHN_GDFXSH))  - CHN_GLN

@IDENTITY CHN_GDNRATIO  = CHN_GDN / CHN_YEN * 100

CHN_GDFXSH  = ( CHN_GDFXSH(-1) * (CHN_EXR / CHN_EXR(-1) )) / (CHN_GDFXSH(-1) * (CHN_EXR / CHN_EXR(-1))  + 1 - CHN_GDFXSH(-1) )

CHN_TOURSH  = CHN_TOURSH(-1)

CHN_LOCK  = 0

CHN_GCARBR  = CHN_GCARBR(-1)

CHN_GTRADER  = CHN_GTRADER(-1)

CHN_ITAXR  = CHN_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_REV  = CHN_TAX  + CHN_CTAX  + CHN_ITAX  + CHN_GTRADE  + CHN_REVG  + CHN_GCARB  + CHN_GCOM  + CHN_GOTH

@IDENTITY CHN_TAX  = CHN_TAXR * (CHN_LABSH * 0.5 * (CHN_YER(-1)  + CHN_GDI(-1)) * CHN_YED(-1) * (CHN_LNN / CHN_LNN(-1)  + CHN_TECHL - CHN_TECHL(-1)) + CHN_REMIT  + CHN_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY CHN_CTAX  = CHN_CTAXR * CHN_PROF

@IDENTITY CHN_ITAX  = CHN_ITAXR * (CHN_PCR * CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY CHN_GTRADE  = CHN_GTRADER * CHN_XTN

CHN_REVG  = CHN_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (CHN_YER$ / CHN_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - CHN_YER$(-1) / CHN_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * CHN_EXR / CHN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_GCARB  = CHN_GCARBR * CHN_CO2 * CHN_EXR / 1000

CHN_GCOM  = CHN_GCOM(-1) * ( CHN_OILC / (CHN_OILC + CHN_GASC + CHN_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + CHN_GASC / (CHN_OILC + CHN_GASC + CHN_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + CHN_COALC / (CHN_OILC + CHN_GASC + CHN_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

CHN_GOTH  = CHN_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_EXP  = CHN_EXPE  + CHN_EXPH  + CHN_EXPSP  + CHN_OGC  + CHN_OGI  + CHN_GIP

CHN_EXPE  = CHN_EXPE(-1) * (CHN_YFT / CHN_YFT(-1)) * (CHN_YED / CHN_YED(-1))

CHN_EXPH = CHN_EXPH(-1) * (CHN_YFT / CHN_YFT(-1)) * (CHN_YED / CHN_YED(-1))

CHN_EXPSP  = CHN_EXPSP(-1) * (CHN_YFT / CHN_YFT(-1)) * (CHN_YED / CHN_YED(-1)) * (CHN_POPT - CHN_LNN) / (CHN_POPT(-1) - CHN_LNN(-1))

DLOG(CHN_OGI)  = DLOG(CHN_YFT)  + DLOG(CHN_YED)

CHN_GCR  = CHN_GCR(-1)  + ( CHN_OGC / CHN_YED - CHN_OGC(-1) / CHN_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (CHN_EXPH ) / CHN_YED  - (CHN_EXPH(-1) ) / CHN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (CHN_EXPE ) / CHN_YED  - (CHN_EXPE(-1) ) / CHN_YED(-1) )

CHN_IGR  = CHN_IGR(-1) + (CHN_OGI / CHN_YED - CHN_OGI(-1) / CHN_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (CHN_EXPH ) / CHN_YED  - (CHN_EXPH(-1) ) / CHN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (CHN_EXPE ) / CHN_YED  - (CHN_EXPE(-1) ) / CHN_YED(-1) )

CHN_GIP  = ( CHN_GIP(-1)  + ( CHN_GDN(-1) - CHN_GDN(-2) ) * CHN_GINT(-1) / 100  + CHN_GDN(-8) / 7 * ( CHN_GINT(-1) / 100 - CHN_GINT(-8) / 100 ) ) * (CHN_GDFXSH * (CHN_EXR / CHN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - CHN_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY CHN_GLN  = CHN_REV  - CHN_EXP

@IDENTITY CHN_GLNRATIO  = CHN_GLN / CHN_YEN * 100

CHN_GLNT  = CHN_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

CHN_TFP  = CHN_LABSH * (CHN_TECHL  - CHN_TECHL(-1))

CHN_LABSH  = CHN_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY CHN_LFN  = CHN_LRX * CHN_POPWA

CHN_LRX  = CHN_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(CHN_YER(-1) / CHN_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY CHN_URX  = (1 - CHN_LNN / CHN_LFN) * 100

CHN_URXF  = CHN_URXF(-1) * CHN_URX / CHN_URX(-1) * CHN_LNN / CHN_LNNF / (CHN_LNN(-1) / CHN_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(CHN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(CHN_PCR  / CHN_POPT)

CHN_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(CHN_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

CHN_HEAD19  = CHN_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(CHN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI^2)  , CHN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(CHN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , CHN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

CHN_HEAD55  = CHN_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(CHN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI^2)  , CHN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(CHN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , CHN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(CHN_XTR)  = DLOG(CHN_WDR)  + (1  - CHN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(CHN_XTDNO$  / CHN_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * CHN_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(CHN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (CHN_EXPH(-1) / CHN_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (CHN_EXPH(-1) / CHN_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(CHN_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(CHN_PM25)

CHN_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( CHN_EXPSP / CHN_YEN )

DLOG(CHN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - CHN_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (CHN_FINC - CHN_FINC(-1))

DLOG(CHN_PCR)  =  - 0.119816808720004  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(CHN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(CHN_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (CHN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.511396272819086  * DLOG(CHN_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.511396272819086)  * DLOG(CHN_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(CHN_HIC)  - CHN_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * CHN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * CHN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(CHN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(CHN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(CHN_IPR)  =  - 0.0983649158255412  - 0.1 * (LOG(CHN_IPR(-1)  / CHN_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * CHN_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * CHN_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(CHN_PCR  + CHN_GCR(-1) + CHN_IGR(-1) + CHN_XTN  / CHN_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(CHN_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (CHN_USER - CHN_USER(-1))  - (0 * CHN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * CHN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - CHN_FUELSH - CHN_TOURSH)) * CHN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * CHN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * CHN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - CHN_FUELSH - CHN_TOURSH)) * CHN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(CHN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(CHN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(CHN_MTR)  =  - 0.298511390736107  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(CHN_MTR(-1))  - LOG(CHN_PCR(-1) + CHN_ITR(-1) + CHN_GCR(-1) + CHN_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(CHN_YFT(-1) / CHN_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(CHN_CMUD(-1) * CHN_EXR(-1)  / CHN_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * CHN_OMS * LOG(CHN_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.359118909250563  * DLOG(CHN_XTR)  + 0.847474859631386  * DLOG(CHN_PCR)  + 0.0743446614147129  * DLOG(CHN_IPR)  + 0.125864107984382  * DLOG(CHN_GCR + CHN_IGR)

CHN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * CHN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * CHN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * CHN_OILC

CHN_POIL  = CHN_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( CHN_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - CHN_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

CHN_PG  = CHN_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( CHN_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - CHN_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

CHN_PC  = CHN_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( CHN_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - CHN_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(CHN_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

CHN_PE  = CHN_PE(-1) * ( CHN_OILC(-1) / (CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) * CHN_POIL / CHN_POIL(-1)  + CHN_GASC(-1) / (CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) * CHN_PG / CHN_PG(-1)  + CHN_COALC(-1) / (CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) * CHN_PC / CHN_PC(-1)  + CHN_RC(-1) / (CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) * CHN_PR / CHN_PR(-1) )

D(CHN_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(CHN_PM25)  = 0.2 * (CHN_COALC(-1) / CHN_EC(-1) - CHN_COALC(-2) / CHN_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (CHN_COALC(-2) / CHN_EC(-2) - CHN_COALC(-3) / CHN_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (CHN_OILC(-1) / CHN_EC(-1) - CHN_OILC(-2) / CHN_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (CHN_OILC(-2) / CHN_EC(-2) - CHN_OILC(-3) / CHN_EC(-3))

DLOG(CHN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(CHN_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(CHN_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(CHN_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(CHN_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(CHN_PE * CHN_EXR / CHN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(CHN_PE(-1) * CHN_EXR(-1) / CHN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(CHN_PE(-2) * CHN_EXR(-2) / CHN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(CHN_PE(-3) * CHN_EXR(-3) / CHN_HIC(-3))  - (CHN_EFF - CHN_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(CHN_COALC)  = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(CHN_COALC(-1) / CHN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.148584889681805 * LOG(CHN_PE(-1) / CHN_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) / CHN_EC(-1))

DLOG(CHN_GASC)  = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(CHN_GASC(-1) / CHN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.0780809630541316 * LOG(CHN_PE(-1) / CHN_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) / CHN_EC(-1))

DLOG(CHN_RC)  = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( CHN_RC(-1) / CHN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.148584889681805 * LOG(CHN_PE(-1) / CHN_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) / CHN_EC(-1))

DLOG(CHN_OILC)  = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( CHN_OILC(-1) / CHN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.148584889681805 * LOG(CHN_PE(-1) / CHN_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((CHN_COALC(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1) + CHN_OILC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)) / CHN_EC(-1))

CHN_EXR  = CHN_EXR(-1) * ( (CHN_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(FJI_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(FJI_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(FJI_MTD)  + 0.4 * (FJI_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (FJI_YER / FJI_YFT  - FJI_YER(-1) / FJI_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + FJI_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + FJI_GCARB / FJI_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (FJI_PREM - FJI_PREM(-1)) / 100

FJI_YED  = FJI_YED(-1) * FJI_HIC / FJI_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_INT  = FJI_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_LTI  = FJI_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (FJI_INT - FJI_INT(-1))  + (FJI_PREM  - FJI_PREM(-1)) / 100

FJI_PREM  = FJI_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (FJI_GDNRATIO(-1)  - FJI_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(FJI_LNN)  = DLOG(FJI_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(FJI_LNN(-1))  - LOG(FJI_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(FJI_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(FJI_LNNF)  = DLOG(FJI_LNN)

FJI_FUELSH  = FJI_FUELSH(-1)

FJI_TAXR  = FJI_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( FJI_GLNT(-1)  - FJI_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * FJI_YEN(-1) / ( ( FJI_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (FJI_YER(-2)  + FJI_GDI(-2)) * FJI_YED(-2) * (FJI_LNN(-1) / FJI_LNN(-2)  + FJI_TECHL(-1) - FJI_TECHL(-2) ) ) + FJI_REMIT(-1)  + FJI_EXPSP(-1) ) * FJI_SOLV

FJI_CTAXR  = FJI_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( FJI_GLNT(-1)  - FJI_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * FJI_YEN(-1) / ( FJI_PROF(-1) ) * FJI_SOLV

(FJI_OGC)  = FJI_OGC(-1) * (FJI_YFT / FJI_YFT(-1) * FJI_YED / FJI_YED(-1))

FJI_USER  = (FJI_LTI  - FJI_INFT  + FJI_DEP * 100) / (1  - FJI_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (FJI_GCARB / FJI_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY FJI_XTN  = FJI_XTD$ * FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") * FJI_XTR

@IDENTITY FJI_YEN  = FJI_YER  * FJI_YED

@IDENTITY FJI_MTN  = FJI_MTD  * FJI_MTR

@IDENTITY FJI_XTN$  = FJI_XTN / FJI_EXR

@IDENTITY FJI_YEN$  = FJI_YEN / FJI_EXR

@IDENTITY FJI_MTN$  = FJI_MTN / FJI_EXR

@IDENTITY FJI_MTR$  = FJI_MTR$(-1) * FJI_MTR / FJI_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_XTR$  = FJI_XTR$(-1) * FJI_XTR / FJI_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_YER$  = FJI_YER$(-1) * FJI_YER / FJI_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_YFT$  = FJI_YFT$(-1) * FJI_YFT / FJI_YFT(-1)

FJI_POPT  = FJI_POPT(-1)  - FJI_LIVES

FJI_POPWA  = FJI_POPWA(-1) * FJI_POPT / FJI_POPT(-1)

FJI_SCR  = FJI_SCR(-1)  + ((FJI_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (FJI_YFT(-1) / FJI_YER(-1)  - FJI_YFT(-2) / FJI_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY FJI_ITR  = FJI_IGR  + FJI_IPR

@IDENTITY FJI_YER  = FJI_PCR  + FJI_GCR  + FJI_ITR  + FJI_SCR  + FJI_XTR  - FJI_MTR

@IDENTITY FJI_PROF  = (FJI_YEN - FJI_ITAX) * (1 - FJI_LABSH)

@IDENTITY FJI_GDI  = FJI_YER  - FJI_XTR  + FJI_MTR  + FJI_XTN  / ((FJI_YEN  - FJI_XTN  + FJI_MTN)  / (FJI_YER  - FJI_XTR  + FJI_MTR))  - FJI_MTN  / ((FJI_YEN  - FJI_XTN  + FJI_MTN)  / (FJI_YER  - FJI_XTR  + FJI_MTR))

@IDENTITY FJI_RPDI  = FJI_LABSH * 0.5 * (FJI_YER(-1)  + FJI_GDI(-1)) * FJI_YED(-1) / FJI_HIC(-1) * (FJI_LNN / FJI_LNN(-1)  + FJI_TECHL - FJI_TECHL(-1)) + FJI_REMIT / FJI_HIC  + FJI_EXPSP / FJI_HIC  - FJI_TAX / FJI_HIC

DLOG(FJI_YFT)  = (1 - FJI_ALPHA - FJI_LABSH) * DLOG(FJI_K(-1) / FJI_LFN(-1))  + (1 - FJI_ALPHA) * DLOG(FJI_LFN)  + FJI_LABSH * D(FJI_TECHL)  + FJI_ALPHA * (DLOG(FJI_EC)  + D(FJI_EFF) )  - ( FJI_CLIMLOSS / FJI_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (FJI_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY FJI_K  = FJI_K(-1) * (1 - FJI_DEP) + FJI_ITR

DLOG(FJI_MTD)  = (1  - FJI_OMS) * ( DLOG(FJI_CMUD)  + DLOG(FJI_EXR) )  + FJI_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(FJI_EXR) )

DLOG(FJI_XTD$)  = (1  - FJI_OXS) * DLOG(FJI_XTDNO$)  + FJI_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

FJI_INFT  = 0.95 * FJI_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

FJI_OXS  = FJI_OXS(-1)

FJI_OMS  = FJI_OMS(-1) * ((FJI_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * FJI_EXR(-1) / FJI_MTN(-1)) / (FJI_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * FJI_EXR(-2) / FJI_MTN(-2)))^0.25

FJI_CXS  = FJI_CXS(-1)

FJI_FINC  = FJI_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_CAN  = FJI_XTN / FJI_EXR  - FJI_MTN / FJI_EXR  + FJI_REMIT / FJI_EXR  + FJI_CANOTH

@IDENTITY FJI_CANRATIO  = FJI_CAN / FJI_YEN$ * 100

FJI_CANOTH  = FJI_CANOTH(-1)  + ((FJI_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (FJI_YEN$  / FJI_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + FJI_REVG / FJI_EXR  - FJI_REVG(-1) / FJI_EXR(-1)
