FJI_GINT  = FJI_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (FJI_LTI  - FJI_LTI(-1))

FJI_GDN  = FJI_GDN(-1) * (FJI_GDFXSH  * (FJI_EXR  / FJI_EXR(-1))  + (1  - FJI_GDFXSH))  - FJI_GLN

@IDENTITY FJI_GDNRATIO  = FJI_GDN / FJI_YEN * 100

FJI_GDFXSH  = ( FJI_GDFXSH(-1) * (FJI_EXR / FJI_EXR(-1) )) / (FJI_GDFXSH(-1) * (FJI_EXR / FJI_EXR(-1))  + 1 - FJI_GDFXSH(-1) )

FJI_TOURSH  = FJI_TOURSH(-1)

FJI_LOCK  = 0

FJI_GCARBR  = FJI_GCARBR(-1)

FJI_GTRADER  = FJI_GTRADER(-1)

FJI_ITAXR  = FJI_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_REV  = FJI_TAX  + FJI_CTAX  + FJI_ITAX  + FJI_GTRADE  + FJI_REVG  + FJI_GCARB  + FJI_GCOM  + FJI_GOTH

@IDENTITY FJI_TAX  = FJI_TAXR * (FJI_LABSH * 0.5 * (FJI_YER(-1)  + FJI_GDI(-1)) * FJI_YED(-1) * (FJI_LNN / FJI_LNN(-1)  + FJI_TECHL - FJI_TECHL(-1)) + FJI_REMIT  + FJI_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY FJI_CTAX  = FJI_CTAXR * FJI_PROF

@IDENTITY FJI_ITAX  = FJI_ITAXR * (FJI_PCR * FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY FJI_GTRADE  = FJI_GTRADER * FJI_XTN

FJI_REVG  = FJI_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (FJI_YER$ / FJI_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - FJI_YER$(-1) / FJI_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * FJI_EXR / FJI_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_GCARB  = FJI_GCARBR * FJI_CO2 * FJI_EXR / 1000

FJI_GCOM  = FJI_GCOM(-1) * ( FJI_OILC / (FJI_OILC + FJI_GASC + FJI_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + FJI_GASC / (FJI_OILC + FJI_GASC + FJI_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + FJI_COALC / (FJI_OILC + FJI_GASC + FJI_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

FJI_GOTH  = FJI_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_EXP  = FJI_EXPE  + FJI_EXPH  + FJI_EXPSP  + FJI_OGC  + FJI_OGI  + FJI_GIP

FJI_EXPE  = FJI_EXPE(-1) * (FJI_YFT / FJI_YFT(-1)) * (FJI_YED / FJI_YED(-1))

FJI_EXPH = FJI_EXPH(-1) * (FJI_YFT / FJI_YFT(-1)) * (FJI_YED / FJI_YED(-1))

FJI_EXPSP  = FJI_EXPSP(-1) * (FJI_YFT / FJI_YFT(-1)) * (FJI_YED / FJI_YED(-1)) * (FJI_POPT - FJI_LNN) / (FJI_POPT(-1) - FJI_LNN(-1))

DLOG(FJI_OGI)  = DLOG(FJI_YFT)  + DLOG(FJI_YED)

FJI_GCR  = FJI_GCR(-1)  + ( FJI_OGC / FJI_YED - FJI_OGC(-1) / FJI_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (FJI_EXPH ) / FJI_YED  - (FJI_EXPH(-1) ) / FJI_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (FJI_EXPE ) / FJI_YED  - (FJI_EXPE(-1) ) / FJI_YED(-1) )

FJI_IGR  = FJI_IGR(-1) + (FJI_OGI / FJI_YED - FJI_OGI(-1) / FJI_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (FJI_EXPH ) / FJI_YED  - (FJI_EXPH(-1) ) / FJI_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (FJI_EXPE ) / FJI_YED  - (FJI_EXPE(-1) ) / FJI_YED(-1) )

FJI_GIP  = ( FJI_GIP(-1)  + ( FJI_GDN(-1) - FJI_GDN(-2) ) * FJI_GINT(-1) / 100  + FJI_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( FJI_GINT(-1) / 100 - FJI_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (FJI_GDFXSH * (FJI_EXR / FJI_EXR(-1))  + (1 - FJI_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY FJI_GLN  = FJI_REV  - FJI_EXP

@IDENTITY FJI_GLNRATIO  = FJI_GLN / FJI_YEN * 100

FJI_GLNT  = FJI_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

FJI_TFP  = FJI_LABSH * (FJI_TECHL  - FJI_TECHL(-1))

FJI_LABSH  = FJI_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY FJI_LFN  = FJI_LRX * FJI_POPWA

FJI_LRX  = FJI_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(FJI_YER(-1) / FJI_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY FJI_URX  = (1 - FJI_LNN / FJI_LFN) * 100

FJI_URXF  = FJI_URXF(-1) * FJI_URX / FJI_URX(-1) * FJI_LNN / FJI_LNNF / (FJI_LNN(-1) / FJI_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(FJI_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(FJI_PCR  / FJI_POPT)

FJI_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(FJI_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

FJI_HEAD19  = FJI_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FJI_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI^2)  , FJI_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FJI_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FJI_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

FJI_HEAD55  = FJI_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FJI_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI^2)  , FJI_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FJI_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FJI_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(FJI_XTR)  = DLOG(FJI_WDR)  + (1  - FJI_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(FJI_XTDNO$  / FJI_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * FJI_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(FJI_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (FJI_EXPH(-1) / FJI_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (FJI_EXPH(-1) / FJI_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(FJI_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(FJI_PM25)

FJI_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( FJI_EXPSP / FJI_YEN )

DLOG(FJI_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - FJI_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (FJI_FINC - FJI_FINC(-1))

DLOG(FJI_PCR)  =  - 0.062623224407904  +  - 0.139836045984125 * (LOG(FJI_PCR(-1))  - LOG(FJI_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (FJI_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(FJI_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(FJI_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(FJI_HIC)  - FJI_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * FJI_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * FJI_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(FJI_YFT(-1))  - LOG(FJI_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(FJI_IPR)  =  - 0.216019164618519  - 0.1 * (LOG(FJI_IPR(-1)  / FJI_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * FJI_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * FJI_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(FJI_PCR  + FJI_GCR(-1) + FJI_IGR(-1) + FJI_XTN  / FJI_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(FJI_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (FJI_USER - FJI_USER(-1))  - (0 * FJI_FUELSH  + 0.26 * FJI_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - FJI_FUELSH - FJI_TOURSH)) * FJI_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * FJI_FUELSH  + 0.26 * FJI_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - FJI_FUELSH - FJI_TOURSH)) * FJI_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(FJI_YFT(-1))  - LOG(FJI_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(FJI_MTR)  =  - 0.141797007300518  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(FJI_MTR(-1))  - LOG(FJI_PCR(-1) + FJI_ITR(-1) + FJI_GCR(-1) + FJI_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(FJI_YFT(-1) / FJI_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(FJI_CMUD(-1) * FJI_EXR(-1)  / FJI_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * FJI_OMS * LOG(FJI_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.545488617593963  * DLOG(FJI_XTR)  + 0.452224808499374  * DLOG(FJI_PCR)  + 0.114918206844888  * DLOG(FJI_IPR)  + 0.153228826212495  * DLOG(FJI_GCR + FJI_IGR)

FJI_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * FJI_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * FJI_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * FJI_OILC

FJI_POIL  = FJI_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( FJI_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - FJI_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

FJI_PG  = FJI_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( FJI_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - FJI_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

FJI_PC  = FJI_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( FJI_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - FJI_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(FJI_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

FJI_PE  = FJI_PE(-1) * ( FJI_OILC(-1) / (FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) * FJI_POIL / FJI_POIL(-1)  + FJI_GASC(-1) / (FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) * FJI_PG / FJI_PG(-1)  + FJI_COALC(-1) / (FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) * FJI_PC / FJI_PC(-1)  + FJI_RC(-1) / (FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) * FJI_PR / FJI_PR(-1) )

D(FJI_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(FJI_PM25)  = 0.2 * (FJI_COALC(-1) / FJI_EC(-1) - FJI_COALC(-2) / FJI_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (FJI_COALC(-2) / FJI_EC(-2) - FJI_COALC(-3) / FJI_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (FJI_OILC(-1) / FJI_EC(-1) - FJI_OILC(-2) / FJI_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (FJI_OILC(-2) / FJI_EC(-2) - FJI_OILC(-3) / FJI_EC(-3))

DLOG(FJI_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(FJI_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(FJI_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(FJI_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(FJI_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FJI_PE * FJI_EXR / FJI_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FJI_PE(-1) * FJI_EXR(-1) / FJI_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FJI_PE(-2) * FJI_EXR(-2) / FJI_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FJI_PE(-3) * FJI_EXR(-3) / FJI_HIC(-3))  - (FJI_EFF - FJI_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(FJI_COALC)  = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(FJI_COALC(-1) / FJI_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(FJI_PE(-1) / FJI_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) / FJI_EC(-1))

DLOG(FJI_GASC)  = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(FJI_GASC(-1) / FJI_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(FJI_PE(-1) / FJI_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) / FJI_EC(-1))

DLOG(FJI_RC)  = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( FJI_RC(-1) / FJI_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.311468182345051 * LOG(FJI_PE(-1) / FJI_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) / FJI_EC(-1))

DLOG(FJI_OILC)  = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( FJI_OILC(-1) / FJI_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.311468182345051 * LOG(FJI_PE(-1) / FJI_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FJI_COALC(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1) + FJI_OILC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)) / FJI_EC(-1))

DLOG(FJI_EXR)  = 0.27515648644854 * LOG(1)  + 0.149169285223102 * DLOG(AUS_EXR)  + 0.358510828571463 * DLOG(NZL_EXR)  + 0.217163399756895 * DLOG(EMU_EXR)

DLOG(GEO_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(GEO_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(GEO_MTD)  + 0.4 * (GEO_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (GEO_YER / GEO_YFT  - GEO_YER(-1) / GEO_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + GEO_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + GEO_GCARB / GEO_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (GEO_PREM - GEO_PREM(-1)) / 100

GEO_YED  = GEO_YED(-1) * GEO_HIC / GEO_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_INT  = GEO_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_LTI  = GEO_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (GEO_INT - GEO_INT(-1))  + (GEO_PREM  - GEO_PREM(-1)) / 100

GEO_PREM  = GEO_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (GEO_GDNRATIO(-1)  - GEO_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(GEO_LNN)  = DLOG(GEO_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(GEO_LNN(-1))  - LOG(GEO_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(GEO_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(GEO_LNNF)  = DLOG(GEO_LNN)

GEO_FUELSH  = GEO_FUELSH(-1)

GEO_TAXR  = GEO_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( GEO_GLNT(-1)  - GEO_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * GEO_YEN(-1) / ( ( GEO_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (GEO_YER(-2)  + GEO_GDI(-2)) * GEO_YED(-2) * (GEO_LNN(-1) / GEO_LNN(-2)  + GEO_TECHL(-1) - GEO_TECHL(-2) ) ) + GEO_REMIT(-1)  + GEO_EXPSP(-1) ) * GEO_SOLV

GEO_CTAXR  = GEO_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( GEO_GLNT(-1)  - GEO_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * GEO_YEN(-1) / ( GEO_PROF(-1) ) * GEO_SOLV

(GEO_OGC)  = GEO_OGC(-1) * (GEO_YFT / GEO_YFT(-1) * GEO_YED / GEO_YED(-1))

GEO_USER  = (GEO_LTI  - GEO_INFT  + GEO_DEP * 100) / (1  - GEO_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (GEO_GCARB / GEO_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY GEO_XTN  = GEO_XTD$ * GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") * GEO_XTR

@IDENTITY GEO_YEN  = GEO_YER  * GEO_YED

@IDENTITY GEO_MTN  = GEO_MTD  * GEO_MTR

@IDENTITY GEO_XTN$  = GEO_XTN / GEO_EXR

@IDENTITY GEO_YEN$  = GEO_YEN / GEO_EXR

@IDENTITY GEO_MTN$  = GEO_MTN / GEO_EXR

@IDENTITY GEO_MTR$  = GEO_MTR$(-1) * GEO_MTR / GEO_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_XTR$  = GEO_XTR$(-1) * GEO_XTR / GEO_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_YER$  = GEO_YER$(-1) * GEO_YER / GEO_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_YFT$  = GEO_YFT$(-1) * GEO_YFT / GEO_YFT(-1)

GEO_POPT  = GEO_POPT(-1)  - GEO_LIVES

GEO_POPWA  = GEO_POPWA(-1) * GEO_POPT / GEO_POPT(-1)

GEO_SCR  = GEO_SCR(-1)  + ((GEO_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (GEO_YFT(-1) / GEO_YER(-1)  - GEO_YFT(-2) / GEO_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY GEO_ITR  = GEO_IGR  + GEO_IPR

@IDENTITY GEO_YER  = GEO_PCR  + GEO_GCR  + GEO_ITR  + GEO_SCR  + GEO_XTR  - GEO_MTR

@IDENTITY GEO_PROF  = (GEO_YEN - GEO_ITAX) * (1 - GEO_LABSH)

@IDENTITY GEO_GDI  = GEO_YER  - GEO_XTR  + GEO_MTR  + GEO_XTN  / ((GEO_YEN  - GEO_XTN  + GEO_MTN)  / (GEO_YER  - GEO_XTR  + GEO_MTR))  - GEO_MTN  / ((GEO_YEN  - GEO_XTN  + GEO_MTN)  / (GEO_YER  - GEO_XTR  + GEO_MTR))

@IDENTITY GEO_RPDI  = GEO_LABSH * 0.5 * (GEO_YER(-1)  + GEO_GDI(-1)) * GEO_YED(-1) / GEO_HIC(-1) * (GEO_LNN / GEO_LNN(-1)  + GEO_TECHL - GEO_TECHL(-1)) + GEO_REMIT / GEO_HIC  + GEO_EXPSP / GEO_HIC  - GEO_TAX / GEO_HIC

DLOG(GEO_YFT)  = (1 - GEO_ALPHA - GEO_LABSH) * DLOG(GEO_K(-1) / GEO_LFN(-1))  + (1 - GEO_ALPHA) * DLOG(GEO_LFN)  + GEO_LABSH * D(GEO_TECHL)  + GEO_ALPHA * (DLOG(GEO_EC)  + D(GEO_EFF) )  - ( GEO_CLIMLOSS / GEO_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (GEO_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY GEO_K  = GEO_K(-1) * (1 - GEO_DEP) + GEO_ITR

DLOG(GEO_MTD)  = (1  - GEO_OMS) * ( DLOG(GEO_CMUD)  + DLOG(GEO_EXR) )  + GEO_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(GEO_EXR) )

DLOG(GEO_XTD$)  = (1  - GEO_OXS) * DLOG(GEO_XTDNO$)  + GEO_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

GEO_INFT  = 0.95 * GEO_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

GEO_OXS  = GEO_OXS(-1)

GEO_OMS  = GEO_OMS(-1) * ((GEO_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * GEO_EXR(-1) / GEO_MTN(-1)) / (GEO_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * GEO_EXR(-2) / GEO_MTN(-2)))^0.25

GEO_CXS  = GEO_CXS(-1)

GEO_FINC  = GEO_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_CAN  = GEO_XTN / GEO_EXR  - GEO_MTN / GEO_EXR  + GEO_REMIT / GEO_EXR  + GEO_CANOTH

@IDENTITY GEO_CANRATIO  = GEO_CAN / GEO_YEN$ * 100

GEO_CANOTH  = GEO_CANOTH(-1)  + ((GEO_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (GEO_YEN$  / GEO_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + GEO_REVG / GEO_EXR  - GEO_REVG(-1) / GEO_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_GDNRATIO  = GEO_GDN / GEO_YEN * 100

@IDENTITY GEO_TAX  = GEO_TAXR * (GEO_LABSH * 0.5 * (GEO_YER(-1)  + GEO_GDI(-1)) * GEO_YED(-1) * (GEO_LNN / GEO_LNN(-1)  + GEO_TECHL - GEO_TECHL(-1)) + GEO_REMIT  + GEO_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY GEO_GTRADE  = GEO_GTRADER * GEO_XTN

@IDENTITY GEO_GCARB  = GEO_GCARBR * GEO_CO2 * GEO_EXR / 1000

GEO_GCOM  = GEO_GCOM(-1) * ( GEO_OILC / (GEO_OILC + GEO_GASC + GEO_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + GEO_GASC / (GEO_OILC + GEO_GASC + GEO_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + GEO_COALC / (GEO_OILC + GEO_GASC + GEO_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

GEO_GOTH  = GEO_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_EXP  = GEO_EXPE  + GEO_EXPH  + GEO_EXPSP  + GEO_OGC  + GEO_OGI  + GEO_GIP

GEO_EXPE  = GEO_EXPE(-1) * (GEO_YFT / GEO_YFT(-1)) * (GEO_YED / GEO_YED(-1))

GEO_EXPH = GEO_EXPH(-1) * (GEO_YFT / GEO_YFT(-1)) * (GEO_YED / GEO_YED(-1))

GEO_EXPSP  = GEO_EXPSP(-1) * (GEO_YFT / GEO_YFT(-1)) * (GEO_YED / GEO_YED(-1)) * (GEO_POPT - GEO_LNN) / (GEO_POPT(-1) - GEO_LNN(-1))

DLOG(GEO_OGI)  = DLOG(GEO_YFT)  + DLOG(GEO_YED)

GEO_GCR  = GEO_GCR(-1)  + ( GEO_OGC / GEO_YED - GEO_OGC(-1) / GEO_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (GEO_EXPH ) / GEO_YED  - (GEO_EXPH(-1) ) / GEO_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (GEO_EXPE ) / GEO_YED  - (GEO_EXPE(-1) ) / GEO_YED(-1) )

GEO_IGR  = GEO_IGR(-1) + (GEO_OGI / GEO_YED - GEO_OGI(-1) / GEO_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (GEO_EXPH ) / GEO_YED  - (GEO_EXPH(-1) ) / GEO_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (GEO_EXPE ) / GEO_YED  - (GEO_EXPE(-1) ) / GEO_YED(-1) )

GEO_GIP  = ( GEO_GIP(-1)  + ( GEO_GDN(-1) - GEO_GDN(-2) ) * GEO_GINT(-1) / 100  + GEO_GDN(-3) / 2 * ( GEO_GINT(-1) / 100 - GEO_GINT(-3) / 100 ) ) * (GEO_GDFXSH * (GEO_EXR / GEO_EXR(-1))  + (1 - GEO_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY GEO_GLN  = GEO_REV  - GEO_EXP

@IDENTITY GEO_GLNRATIO  = GEO_GLN / GEO_YEN * 100

GEO_GLNT  = GEO_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

GEO_TFP  = GEO_LABSH * (GEO_TECHL  - GEO_TECHL(-1))

GEO_LABSH  = GEO_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY GEO_LFN  = GEO_LRX * GEO_POPWA

GEO_LRX  = GEO_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(GEO_YER(-1) / GEO_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY GEO_URX  = (1 - GEO_LNN / GEO_LFN) * 100

GEO_URXF  = GEO_URXF(-1) * GEO_URX / GEO_URX(-1) * GEO_LNN / GEO_LNNF / (GEO_LNN(-1) / GEO_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(GEO_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(GEO_PCR  / GEO_POPT)

GEO_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(GEO_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

GEO_HEAD19  = GEO_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(GEO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI^2)  , GEO_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(GEO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , GEO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

GEO_HEAD55  = GEO_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(GEO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI^2)  , GEO_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(GEO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , GEO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(GEO_XTR)  = DLOG(GEO_WDR)  + (1  - GEO_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(GEO_XTDNO$  / GEO_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * GEO_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(GEO_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (GEO_EXPH(-1) / GEO_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (GEO_EXPH(-1) / GEO_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(GEO_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(GEO_PM25)

GEO_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( GEO_EXPSP / GEO_YEN )

DLOG(GEO_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - GEO_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (GEO_FINC - GEO_FINC(-1))

DLOG(GEO_PCR)  = 0.01857202878297  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(GEO_PCR(-1))  - LOG(GEO_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (GEO_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(GEO_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(GEO_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(GEO_HIC)  - GEO_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * GEO_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * GEO_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(GEO_YFT(-1))  - LOG(GEO_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(GEO_IPR)  =  - 0.180255947114851  - 0.1 * (LOG(GEO_IPR(-1)  / GEO_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * GEO_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * GEO_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(GEO_PCR  + GEO_GCR(-1) + GEO_IGR(-1) + GEO_XTN  / GEO_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(GEO_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (GEO_USER - GEO_USER(-1))  - (0 * GEO_FUELSH  + 0.26 * GEO_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - GEO_FUELSH - GEO_TOURSH)) * GEO_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * GEO_FUELSH  + 0.26 * GEO_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - GEO_FUELSH - GEO_TOURSH)) * GEO_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(GEO_YFT(-1))  - LOG(GEO_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(GEO_MTR)  =  - 0.164186845370144  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(GEO_MTR(-1))  - LOG(GEO_PCR(-1) + GEO_ITR(-1) + GEO_GCR(-1) + GEO_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(GEO_YFT(-1) / GEO_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(GEO_CMUD(-1) * GEO_EXR(-1)  / GEO_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * GEO_OMS * LOG(GEO_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.448562757181386  * DLOG(GEO_XTR)  + 0.499024538926933  * DLOG(GEO_PCR)  + 0.117894237327515  * DLOG(GEO_IPR)  + 0.00328508499295207  * DLOG(GEO_GCR + GEO_IGR)

GEO_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * GEO_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * GEO_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * GEO_OILC

GEO_POIL  = GEO_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( GEO_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - GEO_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

GEO_PG  = GEO_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( GEO_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - GEO_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

GEO_PC  = GEO_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( GEO_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - GEO_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(GEO_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

GEO_PE  = GEO_PE(-1) * ( GEO_OILC(-1) / (GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) * GEO_POIL / GEO_POIL(-1)  + GEO_GASC(-1) / (GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) * GEO_PG / GEO_PG(-1)  + GEO_COALC(-1) / (GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) * GEO_PC / GEO_PC(-1)  + GEO_RC(-1) / (GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) * GEO_PR / GEO_PR(-1) )

D(GEO_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(GEO_PM25)  = 0.2 * (GEO_COALC(-1) / GEO_EC(-1) - GEO_COALC(-2) / GEO_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (GEO_COALC(-2) / GEO_EC(-2) - GEO_COALC(-3) / GEO_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (GEO_OILC(-1) / GEO_EC(-1) - GEO_OILC(-2) / GEO_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (GEO_OILC(-2) / GEO_EC(-2) - GEO_OILC(-3) / GEO_EC(-3))

DLOG(GEO_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(GEO_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(GEO_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(GEO_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(GEO_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(GEO_PE * GEO_EXR / GEO_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(GEO_PE(-1) * GEO_EXR(-1) / GEO_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(GEO_PE(-2) * GEO_EXR(-2) / GEO_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(GEO_PE(-3) * GEO_EXR(-3) / GEO_HIC(-3))  - (GEO_EFF - GEO_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(GEO_COALC)  = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(GEO_COALC(-1) / GEO_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.285552418167313 * LOG(GEO_PE(-1) / GEO_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) / GEO_EC(-1))

DLOG(GEO_GASC)  = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(GEO_GASC(-1) / GEO_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.398737025013728 * LOG(GEO_PE(-1) / GEO_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) / GEO_EC(-1))

DLOG(GEO_RC)  = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( GEO_RC(-1) / GEO_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.285552418167313 * LOG(GEO_PE(-1) / GEO_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) / GEO_EC(-1))

DLOG(GEO_OILC)  = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( GEO_OILC(-1) / GEO_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.285552418167313 * LOG(GEO_PE(-1) / GEO_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((GEO_COALC(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1) + GEO_OILC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)) / GEO_EC(-1))

GEO_EXR  = GEO_EXR(-1) * ( ( (GEO_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (GEO_INT  - USA_INT)  - (GEO_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(HKG_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(HKG_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(HKG_MTD)  + 0.4 * (HKG_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (HKG_YER / HKG_YFT  - HKG_YER(-1) / HKG_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + HKG_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + HKG_GCARB / HKG_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (HKG_PREM - HKG_PREM(-1)) / 100

HKG_YED  = HKG_YED(-1) * HKG_HIC / HKG_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_INT  = HKG_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_LTI  = HKG_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (HKG_INT - HKG_INT(-1))  + (HKG_PREM  - HKG_PREM(-1)) / 100

HKG_PREM  = HKG_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (HKG_GDNRATIO(-1)  - HKG_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(HKG_LNN)  = DLOG(HKG_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(HKG_LNN(-1))  - LOG(HKG_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(HKG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(HKG_LNNF)  = DLOG(HKG_LNN)

HKG_FUELSH  = HKG_FUELSH(-1)

HKG_TAXR  = HKG_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( HKG_GLNT(-1)  - HKG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * HKG_YEN(-1) / ( ( HKG_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (HKG_YER(-2)  + HKG_GDI(-2)) * HKG_YED(-2) * (HKG_LNN(-1) / HKG_LNN(-2)  + HKG_TECHL(-1) - HKG_TECHL(-2) ) ) + HKG_REMIT(-1)  + HKG_EXPSP(-1) ) * HKG_SOLV

HKG_CTAXR  = HKG_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( HKG_GLNT(-1)  - HKG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * HKG_YEN(-1) / ( HKG_PROF(-1) ) * HKG_SOLV

(HKG_OGC)  = HKG_OGC(-1) * (HKG_YFT / HKG_YFT(-1) * HKG_YED / HKG_YED(-1))

HKG_USER  = (HKG_LTI  - HKG_INFT  + HKG_DEP * 100) / (1  - HKG_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (HKG_GCARB / HKG_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY HKG_XTN  = HKG_XTD$ * HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") * HKG_XTR

@IDENTITY HKG_YEN  = HKG_YER  * HKG_YED

@IDENTITY HKG_MTN  = HKG_MTD  * HKG_MTR

@IDENTITY HKG_XTN$  = HKG_XTN / HKG_EXR

@IDENTITY HKG_YEN$  = HKG_YEN / HKG_EXR

@IDENTITY HKG_MTN$  = HKG_MTN / HKG_EXR

@IDENTITY HKG_MTR$  = HKG_MTR$(-1) * HKG_MTR / HKG_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_XTR$  = HKG_XTR$(-1) * HKG_XTR / HKG_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_YER$  = HKG_YER$(-1) * HKG_YER / HKG_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_YFT$  = HKG_YFT$(-1) * HKG_YFT / HKG_YFT(-1)

HKG_POPT  = HKG_POPT(-1)  - HKG_LIVES

HKG_POPWA  = HKG_POPWA(-1) * HKG_POPT / HKG_POPT(-1)

HKG_SCR  = HKG_SCR(-1)  + ((HKG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (HKG_YFT(-1) / HKG_YER(-1)  - HKG_YFT(-2) / HKG_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY HKG_ITR  = HKG_IGR  + HKG_IPR

@IDENTITY HKG_YER  = HKG_PCR  + HKG_GCR  + HKG_ITR  + HKG_SCR  + HKG_XTR  - HKG_MTR

@IDENTITY HKG_PROF  = (HKG_YEN - HKG_ITAX) * (1 - HKG_LABSH)

@IDENTITY HKG_GDI  = HKG_YER  - HKG_XTR  + HKG_MTR  + HKG_XTN  / ((HKG_YEN  - HKG_XTN  + HKG_MTN)  / (HKG_YER  - HKG_XTR  + HKG_MTR))  - HKG_MTN  / ((HKG_YEN  - HKG_XTN  + HKG_MTN)  / (HKG_YER  - HKG_XTR  + HKG_MTR))

@IDENTITY HKG_RPDI  = HKG_LABSH * 0.5 * (HKG_YER(-1)  + HKG_GDI(-1)) * HKG_YED(-1) / HKG_HIC(-1) * (HKG_LNN / HKG_LNN(-1)  + HKG_TECHL - HKG_TECHL(-1)) + HKG_REMIT / HKG_HIC  + HKG_EXPSP / HKG_HIC  - HKG_TAX / HKG_HIC

DLOG(HKG_YFT)  = (1 - HKG_ALPHA - HKG_LABSH) * DLOG(HKG_K(-1) / HKG_LFN(-1))  + (1 - HKG_ALPHA) * DLOG(HKG_LFN)  + HKG_LABSH * D(HKG_TECHL)  + HKG_ALPHA * (DLOG(HKG_EC)  + D(HKG_EFF) )  - ( HKG_CLIMLOSS / HKG_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (HKG_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY HKG_K  = HKG_K(-1) * (1 - HKG_DEP) + HKG_ITR

DLOG(HKG_MTD)  = (1  - HKG_OMS) * ( DLOG(HKG_CMUD)  + DLOG(HKG_EXR) )  + HKG_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(HKG_EXR) )

DLOG(HKG_XTD$)  = (1  - HKG_OXS) * DLOG(HKG_XTDNO$)  + HKG_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

HKG_INFT  = 0.95 * HKG_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

HKG_OXS  = HKG_OXS(-1)

HKG_OMS  = HKG_OMS(-1) * ((HKG_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * HKG_EXR(-1) / HKG_MTN(-1)) / (HKG_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * HKG_EXR(-2) / HKG_MTN(-2)))^0.25

HKG_CXS  = HKG_CXS(-1)

HKG_FINC  = HKG_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_CAN  = HKG_XTN / HKG_EXR  - HKG_MTN / HKG_EXR  + HKG_REMIT / HKG_EXR  + HKG_CANOTH

@IDENTITY HKG_CANRATIO  = HKG_CAN / HKG_YEN$ * 100

HKG_CANOTH  = HKG_CANOTH(-1)  + ((HKG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (HKG_YEN$  / HKG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + HKG_REVG / HKG_EXR  - HKG_REVG(-1) / HKG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(HKG_EFEX)  =  - LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.263107884E-06 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.160797823E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009651918488 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.97036536E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001387625687 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.961158346E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.945606089E-05 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006492152649 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.5005655984 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.103726327E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.331553666E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02936768945 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004572994325 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004717571741 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04299216829 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.715213938E-05 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.34671469E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.964880787E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.006482169E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0207752753 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009309559236 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.922963987E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.166542203E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.866429882E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002362011459 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001661035036 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001148547992 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004549248834 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.782422405E-05 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009014641725 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03339033172 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003056764648 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.147536562E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04891613771 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.097072559E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005411485399 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.109427081E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01886795819 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.412140388E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.535869621E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001311858011 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.114319619E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.418557118E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.467033026E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0116677783 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07022221273 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01466285047 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009187638436 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01609563123 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007711849122 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00708820736 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001395411843 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02146330799 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04030863285 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004754473639 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.019789253 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01754148137 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02078680094 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(HKG_REFEX )  =  - LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.263107884E-06 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006492152649 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.5005655984 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02936768945 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004572994325 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0004717571741 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009309559236 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.922963987E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.166542203E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.866429882E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.147536562E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04891613771 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.097072559E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005411485399 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.109427081E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01886795819 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.412140388E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.535869621E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001311858011 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.114319619E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.418557118E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.467033026E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0116677783 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07022221273 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01466285047 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009187638436 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01609563123 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007711849122 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00708820736 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001395411843 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02146330799 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04030863285 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004754473639 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.019789253 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01754148137 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02078680094 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

HKG_REMIT  = HKG_REMIT(-1) / HKG_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1228999082 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008337022229 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008676349201 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000636714655 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1125015064 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000401600461 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001512356167 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02904890729 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004384561995 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008971195109 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000327888984 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 7.371147703E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07340538282 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001532690367 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001105672155 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3077708343 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00144372824 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 7.62532521E-06 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001605130957 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003363941909 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3182434967 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 5.210638893E-05 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * HKG_EXR

HKG_GINT  = HKG_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (HKG_LTI  - HKG_LTI(-1))

HKG_GDN  = HKG_GDN(-1) * (HKG_GDFXSH  * (HKG_EXR  / HKG_EXR(-1))  + (1  - HKG_GDFXSH))  - HKG_GLN

@IDENTITY HKG_GDNRATIO  = HKG_GDN / HKG_YEN * 100

HKG_GDFXSH  = ( HKG_GDFXSH(-1) * (HKG_EXR / HKG_EXR(-1) )) / (HKG_GDFXSH(-1) * (HKG_EXR / HKG_EXR(-1))  + 1 - HKG_GDFXSH(-1) )

HKG_TOURSH  = HKG_TOURSH(-1)

HKG_LOCK  = 0

HKG_GCARBR  = HKG_GCARBR(-1)

HKG_GTRADER  = HKG_GTRADER(-1)

HKG_ITAXR  = HKG_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_REV  = HKG_TAX  + HKG_CTAX  + HKG_ITAX  + HKG_GTRADE  + HKG_REVG  + HKG_GCARB  + HKG_GCOM  + HKG_GOTH

@IDENTITY HKG_TAX  = HKG_TAXR * (HKG_LABSH * 0.5 * (HKG_YER(-1)  + HKG_GDI(-1)) * HKG_YED(-1) * (HKG_LNN / HKG_LNN(-1)  + HKG_TECHL - HKG_TECHL(-1)) + HKG_REMIT  + HKG_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY HKG_CTAX  = HKG_CTAXR * HKG_PROF

@IDENTITY HKG_ITAX  = HKG_ITAXR * (HKG_PCR * HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY HKG_GTRADE  = HKG_GTRADER * HKG_XTN

HKG_REVG  = HKG_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (HKG_YER$ / HKG_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - HKG_YER$(-1) / HKG_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * HKG_EXR / HKG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_GCARB  = HKG_GCARBR * HKG_CO2 * HKG_EXR / 1000

HKG_GCOM  = HKG_GCOM(-1) * ( HKG_OILC / (HKG_OILC + HKG_GASC + HKG_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + HKG_GASC / (HKG_OILC + HKG_GASC + HKG_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + HKG_COALC / (HKG_OILC + HKG_GASC + HKG_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

HKG_GOTH  = HKG_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_EXP  = HKG_EXPE  + HKG_EXPH  + HKG_EXPSP  + HKG_OGC  + HKG_OGI  + HKG_GIP

HKG_EXPE  = HKG_EXPE(-1) * (HKG_YFT / HKG_YFT(-1)) * (HKG_YED / HKG_YED(-1))

HKG_EXPH = HKG_EXPH(-1) * (HKG_YFT / HKG_YFT(-1)) * (HKG_YED / HKG_YED(-1))

HKG_EXPSP  = HKG_EXPSP(-1) * (HKG_YFT / HKG_YFT(-1)) * (HKG_YED / HKG_YED(-1)) * (HKG_POPT - HKG_LNN) / (HKG_POPT(-1) - HKG_LNN(-1))

DLOG(HKG_OGI)  = DLOG(HKG_YFT)  + DLOG(HKG_YED)

HKG_GCR  = HKG_GCR(-1)  + ( HKG_OGC / HKG_YED - HKG_OGC(-1) / HKG_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (HKG_EXPH ) / HKG_YED  - (HKG_EXPH(-1) ) / HKG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (HKG_EXPE ) / HKG_YED  - (HKG_EXPE(-1) ) / HKG_YED(-1) )

HKG_IGR  = HKG_IGR(-1) + (HKG_OGI / HKG_YED - HKG_OGI(-1) / HKG_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (HKG_EXPH ) / HKG_YED  - (HKG_EXPH(-1) ) / HKG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (HKG_EXPE ) / HKG_YED  - (HKG_EXPE(-1) ) / HKG_YED(-1) )

HKG_GIP  = ( HKG_GIP(-1)  + ( HKG_GDN(-1) - HKG_GDN(-2) ) * HKG_GINT(-1) / 100  + HKG_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( HKG_GINT(-1) / 100 - HKG_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (HKG_GDFXSH * (HKG_EXR / HKG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - HKG_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY HKG_GLN  = HKG_REV  - HKG_EXP

@IDENTITY HKG_GLNRATIO  = HKG_GLN / HKG_YEN * 100

HKG_GLNT  = HKG_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

HKG_TFP  = HKG_LABSH * (HKG_TECHL  - HKG_TECHL(-1))

HKG_LABSH  = HKG_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY HKG_LFN  = HKG_LRX * HKG_POPWA

HKG_LRX  = HKG_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(HKG_YER(-1) / HKG_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY HKG_URX  = (1 - HKG_LNN / HKG_LFN) * 100

HKG_URXF  = HKG_URXF(-1) * HKG_URX / HKG_URX(-1) * HKG_LNN / HKG_LNNF / (HKG_LNN(-1) / HKG_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(HKG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(HKG_PCR  / HKG_POPT)

HKG_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(HKG_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

HKG_HEAD19  = HKG_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(HKG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI^2)  , HKG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(HKG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , HKG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

HKG_HEAD55  = HKG_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(HKG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI^2)  , HKG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(HKG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , HKG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(HKG_XTR)  = DLOG(HKG_WDR)  + (1  - HKG_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(HKG_XTDNO$  / HKG_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * HKG_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(HKG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (HKG_EXPH(-1) / HKG_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (HKG_EXPH(-1) / HKG_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(HKG_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(HKG_PM25)

HKG_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( HKG_EXPSP / HKG_YEN )

DLOG(HKG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - HKG_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (HKG_FINC - HKG_FINC(-1))

DLOG(HKG_PCR)  =  - 0.130300672533793  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(HKG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(HKG_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (HKG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(HKG_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(HKG_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(HKG_HIC)  - HKG_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * HKG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * HKG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(HKG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(HKG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(HKG_IPR)  =  - 0.195178153977651  - 0.1 * (LOG(HKG_IPR(-1)  / HKG_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * HKG_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * HKG_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(HKG_PCR  + HKG_GCR(-1) + HKG_IGR(-1) + HKG_XTN  / HKG_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(HKG_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (HKG_USER - HKG_USER(-1))  - (0 * HKG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * HKG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - HKG_FUELSH - HKG_TOURSH)) * HKG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * HKG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * HKG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - HKG_FUELSH - HKG_TOURSH)) * HKG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(HKG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(HKG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(HKG_MTR)  =  - 0.0319498464646193  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(HKG_MTR(-1))  - LOG(HKG_PCR(-1) + HKG_ITR(-1) + HKG_GCR(-1) + HKG_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(HKG_YFT(-1) / HKG_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(HKG_CMUD(-1) * HKG_EXR(-1)  / HKG_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * HKG_OMS * LOG(HKG_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.603557011199539  * DLOG(HKG_XTR)  + 0.136253923999226  * DLOG(HKG_PCR)  + 0.0438731955266474  * DLOG(HKG_IPR)  + 0.0261520917680544  * DLOG(HKG_GCR + HKG_IGR)

HKG_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * HKG_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * HKG_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * HKG_OILC

HKG_POIL  = HKG_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( HKG_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - HKG_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

HKG_PG  = HKG_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( HKG_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - HKG_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

HKG_PC  = HKG_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( HKG_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - HKG_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(HKG_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

HKG_PE  = HKG_PE(-1) * ( HKG_OILC(-1) / (HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) * HKG_POIL / HKG_POIL(-1)  + HKG_GASC(-1) / (HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) * HKG_PG / HKG_PG(-1)  + HKG_COALC(-1) / (HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) * HKG_PC / HKG_PC(-1)  + HKG_RC(-1) / (HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) * HKG_PR / HKG_PR(-1) )

D(HKG_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(HKG_PM25)  = 0.2 * (HKG_COALC(-1) / HKG_EC(-1) - HKG_COALC(-2) / HKG_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (HKG_COALC(-2) / HKG_EC(-2) - HKG_COALC(-3) / HKG_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (HKG_OILC(-1) / HKG_EC(-1) - HKG_OILC(-2) / HKG_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (HKG_OILC(-2) / HKG_EC(-2) - HKG_OILC(-3) / HKG_EC(-3))

DLOG(HKG_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(HKG_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(HKG_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(HKG_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(HKG_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(HKG_PE * HKG_EXR / HKG_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(HKG_PE(-1) * HKG_EXR(-1) / HKG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(HKG_PE(-2) * HKG_EXR(-2) / HKG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(HKG_PE(-3) * HKG_EXR(-3) / HKG_HIC(-3))  - (HKG_EFF - HKG_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(HKG_COALC)  = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(HKG_COALC(-1) / HKG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.000990514168328198 * LOG(HKG_PE(-1) / HKG_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) / HKG_EC(-1))

DLOG(HKG_GASC)  = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(HKG_GASC(-1) / HKG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.0903726260246108 * LOG(HKG_PE(-1) / HKG_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) / HKG_EC(-1))

DLOG(HKG_RC)  = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( HKG_RC(-1) / HKG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(HKG_PE(-1) / HKG_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) / HKG_EC(-1))

DLOG(HKG_OILC)  = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( HKG_OILC(-1) / HKG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(HKG_PE(-1) / HKG_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((HKG_COALC(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1) + HKG_OILC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)) / HKG_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY HKG_EXR  = HKG_EXR(-1)

DLOG(IND_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(IND_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IND_MTD)  + 0.4 * (IND_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (IND_YER / IND_YFT  - IND_YER(-1) / IND_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + IND_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + IND_GCARB / IND_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (IND_PREM - IND_PREM(-1)) / 100

IND_YED  = IND_YED(-1) * IND_HIC / IND_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_INT  = IND_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_LTI  = IND_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (IND_INT - IND_INT(-1))  + (IND_PREM  - IND_PREM(-1)) / 100

IND_PREM  = IND_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (IND_GDNRATIO(-1)  - IND_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(IND_LNN)  = DLOG(IND_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(IND_LNN(-1))  - LOG(IND_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(IND_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IND_LNNF)  = DLOG(IND_LNN)

IND_FUELSH  = IND_FUELSH(-1)

IND_TAXR  = IND_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( IND_GLNT(-1)  - IND_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * IND_YEN(-1) / ( ( IND_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (IND_YER(-2)  + IND_GDI(-2)) * IND_YED(-2) * (IND_LNN(-1) / IND_LNN(-2)  + IND_TECHL(-1) - IND_TECHL(-2) ) ) + IND_REMIT(-1)  + IND_EXPSP(-1) ) * IND_SOLV

IND_CTAXR  = IND_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( IND_GLNT(-1)  - IND_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * IND_YEN(-1) / ( IND_PROF(-1) ) * IND_SOLV

(IND_OGC)  = IND_OGC(-1) * (IND_YFT / IND_YFT(-1) * IND_YED / IND_YED(-1))

IND_USER  = (IND_LTI  - IND_INFT  + IND_DEP * 100) / (1  - IND_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (IND_GCARB / IND_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY IND_XTN  = IND_XTD$ * IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") * IND_XTR

@IDENTITY IND_YEN  = IND_YER  * IND_YED

@IDENTITY IND_MTN  = IND_MTD  * IND_MTR

@IDENTITY IND_XTN$  = IND_XTN / IND_EXR

@IDENTITY IND_YEN$  = IND_YEN / IND_EXR

@IDENTITY IND_MTN$  = IND_MTN / IND_EXR

@IDENTITY IND_MTR$  = IND_MTR$(-1) * IND_MTR / IND_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_XTR$  = IND_XTR$(-1) * IND_XTR / IND_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_YER$  = IND_YER$(-1) * IND_YER / IND_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_YFT$  = IND_YFT$(-1) * IND_YFT / IND_YFT(-1)

IND_POPT  = IND_POPT(-1)  - IND_LIVES

IND_POPWA  = IND_POPWA(-1) * IND_POPT / IND_POPT(-1)

IND_SCR  = IND_SCR(-1)  + ((IND_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (IND_YFT(-1) / IND_YER(-1)  - IND_YFT(-2) / IND_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY IND_ITR  = IND_IGR  + IND_IPR

@IDENTITY IND_YER  = IND_PCR  + IND_GCR  + IND_ITR  + IND_SCR  + IND_XTR  - IND_MTR

@IDENTITY IND_PROF  = (IND_YEN - IND_ITAX) * (1 - IND_LABSH)

@IDENTITY IND_GDI  = IND_YER  - IND_XTR  + IND_MTR  + IND_XTN  / ((IND_YEN  - IND_XTN  + IND_MTN)  / (IND_YER  - IND_XTR  + IND_MTR))  - IND_MTN  / ((IND_YEN  - IND_XTN  + IND_MTN)  / (IND_YER  - IND_XTR  + IND_MTR))

@IDENTITY IND_RPDI  = IND_LABSH * 0.5 * (IND_YER(-1)  + IND_GDI(-1)) * IND_YED(-1) / IND_HIC(-1) * (IND_LNN / IND_LNN(-1)  + IND_TECHL - IND_TECHL(-1)) + IND_REMIT / IND_HIC  + IND_EXPSP / IND_HIC  - IND_TAX / IND_HIC

DLOG(IND_YFT)  = (1 - IND_ALPHA - IND_LABSH) * DLOG(IND_K(-1) / IND_LFN(-1))  + (1 - IND_ALPHA) * DLOG(IND_LFN)  + IND_LABSH * D(IND_TECHL)  + IND_ALPHA * (DLOG(IND_EC)  + D(IND_EFF) )  - ( IND_CLIMLOSS / IND_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (IND_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY IND_K  = IND_K(-1) * (1 - IND_DEP) + IND_ITR

DLOG(IND_MTD)  = (1  - IND_OMS) * ( DLOG(IND_CMUD)  + DLOG(IND_EXR) )  + IND_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IND_EXR) )

DLOG(IND_XTD$)  = (1  - IND_OXS) * DLOG(IND_XTDNO$)  + IND_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

IND_INFT  = 0.95 * IND_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

IND_OXS  = IND_OXS(-1)

IND_OMS  = IND_OMS(-1) * ((IND_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * IND_EXR(-1) / IND_MTN(-1)) / (IND_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * IND_EXR(-2) / IND_MTN(-2)))^0.25

IND_CXS  = IND_CXS(-1)

IND_FINC  = IND_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_CAN  = IND_XTN / IND_EXR  - IND_MTN / IND_EXR  + IND_REMIT / IND_EXR  + IND_CANOTH

@IDENTITY IND_CANRATIO  = IND_CAN / IND_YEN$ * 100

IND_CANOTH  = IND_CANOTH(-1)  + ((IND_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (IND_YEN$  / IND_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + IND_REVG / IND_EXR  - IND_REVG(-1) / IND_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(IND_EFEX)  =  - LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001181302713 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.101045769E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01868476931 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009443803593 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009394112217 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001666275843 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006417324621 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001535264759 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09792703775 * LOG(CHN_EXR / "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02144325668 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02052618422 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01846887967 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008864857155 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.353118311E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.936548094E-05 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000267683536 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002484877689 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01597399425 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009862217714 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.172881953E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04068203461 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , 0.1928177137 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(IND_REFEX )  =  - LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001181302713 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , 0.02144325668 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02052618422 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006176550575 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003194726329 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0243259981 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009862217714 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.172881953E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04068203461 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.396021725E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008607395815 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.492618519E-05 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01510376832 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.909955781E-06 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.000191863E-06 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008698797257 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002336131735 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002666826374 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.555564946E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01085415867 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1323941262 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02776578849 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01598800519 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02319583688 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01030989498 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01018544468 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008678251117 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02199896912 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007249211727 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06830661286 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0470487494 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04927546706 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1928177137 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

IND_REMIT  = IND_REMIT(-1) / IND_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02818993499 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001824424568 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008547160889 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002695603947 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001592335768 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000928310011 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004818376435 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001350547261 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003635805832 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0571498505 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001484805305 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006146028699 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00145063839 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008868370663 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001677393622 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 5.236549285E-06 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004301630406 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01834745847 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001173864096 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001997662575 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 5.701847543E-06 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004165805794 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001594815521 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04373717121 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004943629788 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006131904341 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 1.862484024E-05 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003636039275 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01285292869 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 1.214663494E-05 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002860841739 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 2.812620802E-05 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 1.403611149E-05 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 5.144712986E-05 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1698871474 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 9.401092493E-06 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 9.03169789E-05 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.778953092E-07 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008818804672 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01043038354 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04267274469 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5589541455 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * IND_EXR

IND_GINT  = IND_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 6 * (IND_LTI  - IND_LTI(-1))

IND_GDN  = IND_GDN(-1) * (IND_GDFXSH  * (IND_EXR  / IND_EXR(-1))  + (1  - IND_GDFXSH))  - IND_GLN

@IDENTITY IND_GDNRATIO  = IND_GDN / IND_YEN * 100

IND_GDFXSH  = ( IND_GDFXSH(-1) * (IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1) )) / (IND_GDFXSH(-1) * (IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1))  + 1 - IND_GDFXSH(-1) )

IND_TOURSH  = IND_TOURSH(-1)

IND_LOCK  = 0

IND_GCARBR  = IND_GCARBR(-1)

IND_GTRADER  = IND_GTRADER(-1)

IND_ITAXR  = IND_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_REV  = IND_TAX  + IND_CTAX  + IND_ITAX  + IND_GTRADE  + IND_REVG  + IND_GCARB  + IND_GCOM  + IND_GOTH

@IDENTITY IND_TAX  = IND_TAXR * (IND_LABSH * 0.5 * (IND_YER(-1)  + IND_GDI(-1)) * IND_YED(-1) * (IND_LNN / IND_LNN(-1)  + IND_TECHL - IND_TECHL(-1)) + IND_REMIT  + IND_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY IND_CTAX  = IND_CTAXR * IND_PROF

@IDENTITY IND_ITAX  = IND_ITAXR * (IND_PCR * IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY IND_GTRADE  = IND_GTRADER * IND_XTN

IND_REVG  = IND_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (IND_YER$ / IND_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - IND_YER$(-1) / IND_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_GCARB  = IND_GCARBR * IND_CO2 * IND_EXR / 1000

IND_GCOM  = IND_GCOM(-1) * ( IND_OILC / (IND_OILC + IND_GASC + IND_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + IND_GASC / (IND_OILC + IND_GASC + IND_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + IND_COALC / (IND_OILC + IND_GASC + IND_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

IND_GOTH  = IND_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_EXP  = IND_EXPE  + IND_EXPH  + IND_EXPSP  + IND_OGC  + IND_OGI  + IND_GIP

IND_EXPE  = IND_EXPE(-1) * (IND_YFT / IND_YFT(-1)) * (IND_YED / IND_YED(-1))

IND_EXPH = IND_EXPH(-1) * (IND_YFT / IND_YFT(-1)) * (IND_YED / IND_YED(-1))

IND_EXPSP  = IND_EXPSP(-1) * (IND_YFT / IND_YFT(-1)) * (IND_YED / IND_YED(-1)) * (IND_POPT - IND_LNN) / (IND_POPT(-1) - IND_LNN(-1))

DLOG(IND_OGI)  = DLOG(IND_YFT)  + DLOG(IND_YED)

IND_GCR  = IND_GCR(-1)  + ( IND_OGC / IND_YED - IND_OGC(-1) / IND_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (IND_EXPH ) / IND_YED  - (IND_EXPH(-1) ) / IND_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (IND_EXPE ) / IND_YED  - (IND_EXPE(-1) ) / IND_YED(-1) )

IND_IGR  = IND_IGR(-1) + (IND_OGI / IND_YED - IND_OGI(-1) / IND_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (IND_EXPH ) / IND_YED  - (IND_EXPH(-1) ) / IND_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (IND_EXPE ) / IND_YED  - (IND_EXPE(-1) ) / IND_YED(-1) )

IND_GIP  = ( IND_GIP(-1)  + ( IND_GDN(-1) - IND_GDN(-2) ) * IND_GINT(-1) / 100  + IND_GDN(-7) / 6 * ( IND_GINT(-1) / 100 - IND_GINT(-7) / 100 ) ) * (IND_GDFXSH * (IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1))  + (1 - IND_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY IND_GLN  = IND_REV  - IND_EXP

@IDENTITY IND_GLNRATIO  = IND_GLN / IND_YEN * 100

IND_GLNT  = IND_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

IND_TFP  = IND_LABSH * (IND_TECHL  - IND_TECHL(-1))

IND_LABSH  = IND_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY IND_LFN  = IND_LRX * IND_POPWA

IND_LRX  = IND_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(IND_YER(-1) / IND_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY IND_URX  = (1 - IND_LNN / IND_LFN) * 100

IND_URXF  = IND_URXF(-1) * IND_URX / IND_URX(-1) * IND_LNN / IND_LNNF / (IND_LNN(-1) / IND_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(IND_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(IND_PCR  / IND_POPT)

IND_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(IND_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

IND_HEAD19  = IND_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IND_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI^2)  , IND_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IND_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IND_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

IND_HEAD55  = IND_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IND_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI^2)  , IND_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IND_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IND_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(IND_XTR)  = DLOG(IND_WDR)  + (1  - IND_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(IND_XTDNO$  / IND_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * IND_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(IND_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (IND_EXPH(-1) / IND_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (IND_EXPH(-1) / IND_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(IND_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(IND_PM25)

IND_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( IND_EXPSP / IND_YEN )

DLOG(IND_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - IND_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (IND_FINC - IND_FINC(-1))

DLOG(IND_PCR)  =  - 0.0438173267444409  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(IND_PCR(-1))  - LOG(IND_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (IND_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(IND_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(IND_POPT)  +  - 0.260001664557042 * (DLOG(IND_HIC)  - IND_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * IND_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * IND_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(IND_YFT(-1))  - LOG(IND_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IND_IPR)  =  - 0.119557883124889  - 0.1 * (LOG(IND_IPR(-1)  / IND_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * IND_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * IND_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(IND_PCR  + IND_GCR(-1) + IND_IGR(-1) + IND_XTN  / IND_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(IND_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (IND_USER - IND_USER(-1))  - (0 * IND_FUELSH  + 0.26 * IND_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - IND_FUELSH - IND_TOURSH)) * IND_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * IND_FUELSH  + 0.26 * IND_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - IND_FUELSH - IND_TOURSH)) * IND_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(IND_YFT(-1))  - LOG(IND_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IND_MTR)  =  - 0.283573591984895  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(IND_MTR(-1))  - LOG(IND_PCR(-1) + IND_ITR(-1) + IND_GCR(-1) + IND_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(IND_YFT(-1) / IND_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(IND_CMUD(-1) * IND_EXR(-1)  / IND_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * IND_OMS * LOG(IND_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.509442478612983  * DLOG(IND_XTR)  + 1  * DLOG(IND_PCR)  + 0.306460517753028  * DLOG(IND_IPR)  + 0.260727338360449  * DLOG(IND_GCR + IND_IGR)

IND_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * IND_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * IND_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * IND_OILC

IND_POIL  = IND_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( IND_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - IND_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

IND_PG  = IND_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( IND_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - IND_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

IND_PC  = IND_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( IND_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - IND_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(IND_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

IND_PE  = IND_PE(-1) * ( IND_OILC(-1) / (IND_OILC(-1) + IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) * IND_POIL / IND_POIL(-1)  + IND_GASC(-1) / (IND_OILC(-1) + IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) * IND_PG / IND_PG(-1)  + IND_COALC(-1) / (IND_OILC(-1) + IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) * IND_PC / IND_PC(-1)  + IND_RC(-1) / (IND_OILC(-1) + IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) * IND_PR / IND_PR(-1) )

D(IND_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(IND_PM25)  = 0.2 * (IND_COALC(-1) / IND_EC(-1) - IND_COALC(-2) / IND_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (IND_COALC(-2) / IND_EC(-2) - IND_COALC(-3) / IND_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (IND_OILC(-1) / IND_EC(-1) - IND_OILC(-2) / IND_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (IND_OILC(-2) / IND_EC(-2) - IND_OILC(-3) / IND_EC(-3))

DLOG(IND_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(IND_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(IND_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(IND_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IND_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IND_PE * IND_EXR / IND_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IND_PE(-1) * IND_EXR(-1) / IND_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IND_PE(-2) * IND_EXR(-2) / IND_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IND_PE(-3) * IND_EXR(-3) / IND_HIC(-3))  - (IND_EFF - IND_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(IND_COALC)  = DLOG(IND_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(IND_COALC(-1) / IND_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.0896335560905016 * LOG(IND_PE(-1) / IND_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_OILC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) / IND_EC(-1))

DLOG(IND_GASC)  = DLOG(IND_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(IND_GASC(-1) / IND_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.0630810895400433 * LOG(IND_PE(-1) / IND_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_OILC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) / IND_EC(-1))

DLOG(IND_RC)  = DLOG(IND_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( IND_RC(-1) / IND_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0896335560905016 * LOG(IND_PE(-1) / IND_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_OILC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) / IND_EC(-1))

DLOG(IND_OILC)  = DLOG(IND_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( IND_OILC(-1) / IND_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0896335560905016 * LOG(IND_PE(-1) / IND_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IND_COALC(-1) + IND_GASC(-1) + IND_OILC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)) / IND_EC(-1))

IND_EXR  = IND_EXR(-1) * ( (IND_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(IDN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(IDN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IDN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (IDN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (IDN_YER / IDN_YFT  - IDN_YER(-1) / IDN_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + IDN_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + IDN_GCARB / IDN_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (IDN_PREM - IDN_PREM(-1)) / 100

IDN_YED  = IDN_YED(-1) * IDN_HIC / IDN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_INT  = IDN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_LTI  = IDN_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (IDN_INT - IDN_INT(-1))  + (IDN_PREM  - IDN_PREM(-1)) / 100

IDN_PREM  = IDN_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (IDN_GDNRATIO(-1)  - IDN_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(IDN_LNN)  = DLOG(IDN_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(IDN_LNN(-1))  - LOG(IDN_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(IDN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IDN_LNNF)  = DLOG(IDN_LNN)

IDN_FUELSH  = IDN_FUELSH(-1)

IDN_TAXR  = IDN_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( IDN_GLNT(-1)  - IDN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * IDN_YEN(-1) / ( ( IDN_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (IDN_YER(-2)  + IDN_GDI(-2)) * IDN_YED(-2) * (IDN_LNN(-1) / IDN_LNN(-2)  + IDN_TECHL(-1) - IDN_TECHL(-2) ) ) + IDN_REMIT(-1)  + IDN_EXPSP(-1) ) * IDN_SOLV

IDN_CTAXR  = IDN_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( IDN_GLNT(-1)  - IDN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * IDN_YEN(-1) / ( IDN_PROF(-1) ) * IDN_SOLV

(IDN_OGC)  = IDN_OGC(-1) * (IDN_YFT / IDN_YFT(-1) * IDN_YED / IDN_YED(-1))

IDN_USER  = (IDN_LTI  - IDN_INFT  + IDN_DEP * 100) / (1  - IDN_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (IDN_GCARB / IDN_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY IDN_XTN  = IDN_XTD$ * IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") * IDN_XTR

@IDENTITY IDN_YEN  = IDN_YER  * IDN_YED

@IDENTITY IDN_MTN  = IDN_MTD  * IDN_MTR

@IDENTITY IDN_XTN$  = IDN_XTN / IDN_EXR

@IDENTITY IDN_YEN$  = IDN_YEN / IDN_EXR

@IDENTITY IDN_MTN$  = IDN_MTN / IDN_EXR

@IDENTITY IDN_MTR$  = IDN_MTR$(-1) * IDN_MTR / IDN_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_XTR$  = IDN_XTR$(-1) * IDN_XTR / IDN_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_YER$  = IDN_YER$(-1) * IDN_YER / IDN_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_YFT$  = IDN_YFT$(-1) * IDN_YFT / IDN_YFT(-1)

IDN_POPT  = IDN_POPT(-1)  - IDN_LIVES

IDN_POPWA  = IDN_POPWA(-1) * IDN_POPT / IDN_POPT(-1)

IDN_SCR  = IDN_SCR(-1)  + ((IDN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (IDN_YFT(-1) / IDN_YER(-1)  - IDN_YFT(-2) / IDN_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY IDN_ITR  = IDN_IGR  + IDN_IPR

@IDENTITY IDN_YER  = IDN_PCR  + IDN_GCR  + IDN_ITR  + IDN_SCR  + IDN_XTR  - IDN_MTR

@IDENTITY IDN_PROF  = (IDN_YEN - IDN_ITAX) * (1 - IDN_LABSH)

@IDENTITY IDN_GDI  = IDN_YER  - IDN_XTR  + IDN_MTR  + IDN_XTN  / ((IDN_YEN  - IDN_XTN  + IDN_MTN)  / (IDN_YER  - IDN_XTR  + IDN_MTR))  - IDN_MTN  / ((IDN_YEN  - IDN_XTN  + IDN_MTN)  / (IDN_YER  - IDN_XTR  + IDN_MTR))

@IDENTITY IDN_RPDI  = IDN_LABSH * 0.5 * (IDN_YER(-1)  + IDN_GDI(-1)) * IDN_YED(-1) / IDN_HIC(-1) * (IDN_LNN / IDN_LNN(-1)  + IDN_TECHL - IDN_TECHL(-1)) + IDN_REMIT / IDN_HIC  + IDN_EXPSP / IDN_HIC  - IDN_TAX / IDN_HIC

DLOG(IDN_YFT)  = (1 - IDN_ALPHA - IDN_LABSH) * DLOG(IDN_K(-1) / IDN_LFN(-1))  + (1 - IDN_ALPHA) * DLOG(IDN_LFN)  + IDN_LABSH * D(IDN_TECHL)  + IDN_ALPHA * (DLOG(IDN_EC)  + D(IDN_EFF) )  - ( IDN_CLIMLOSS / IDN_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (IDN_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY IDN_K  = IDN_K(-1) * (1 - IDN_DEP) + IDN_ITR

DLOG(IDN_MTD)  = (1  - IDN_OMS) * ( DLOG(IDN_CMUD)  + DLOG(IDN_EXR) )  + IDN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IDN_EXR) )

DLOG(IDN_XTD$)  = (1  - IDN_OXS) * DLOG(IDN_XTDNO$)  + IDN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

IDN_INFT  = 0.95 * IDN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

IDN_OXS  = IDN_OXS(-1)

IDN_OMS  = IDN_OMS(-1) * ((IDN_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * IDN_EXR(-1) / IDN_MTN(-1)) / (IDN_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * IDN_EXR(-2) / IDN_MTN(-2)))^0.25

IDN_CXS  = IDN_CXS(-1)

IDN_FINC  = IDN_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_CAN  = IDN_XTN / IDN_EXR  - IDN_MTN / IDN_EXR  + IDN_REMIT / IDN_EXR  + IDN_CANOTH

@IDENTITY IDN_CANRATIO  = IDN_CAN / IDN_YEN$ * 100

IDN_CANOTH  = IDN_CANOTH(-1)  + ((IDN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (IDN_YEN$  / IDN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + IDN_REVG / IDN_EXR  - IDN_REVG(-1) / IDN_EXR(-1)
