IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005127254756 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006970715056 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 2.138532984E-05 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007959995127 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2393884735 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03440893237 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001153868619 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006583909419 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002469609572 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 3.434608517E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04230137622 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002172195078 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006148099874 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001147085331 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 5.852977438E-05 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0276034815 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001518952456 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.960246267E-07 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002921488805 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003069848026 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004103957982 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.52019641 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * IDN_EXR

IDN_GINT  = IDN_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 12 * (IDN_LTI  - IDN_LTI(-1))

IDN_GDN  = IDN_GDN(-1) * (IDN_GDFXSH  * (IDN_EXR  / IDN_EXR(-1))  + (1  - IDN_GDFXSH))  - IDN_GLN

@IDENTITY IDN_GDNRATIO  = IDN_GDN / IDN_YEN * 100

IDN_GDFXSH  = ( IDN_GDFXSH(-1) * (IDN_EXR / IDN_EXR(-1) )) / (IDN_GDFXSH(-1) * (IDN_EXR / IDN_EXR(-1))  + 1 - IDN_GDFXSH(-1) )

IDN_TOURSH  = IDN_TOURSH(-1)

IDN_LOCK  = 0

IDN_GCARBR  = IDN_GCARBR(-1)

IDN_GTRADER  = IDN_GTRADER(-1)

IDN_ITAXR  = IDN_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_REV  = IDN_TAX  + IDN_CTAX  + IDN_ITAX  + IDN_GTRADE  + IDN_REVG  + IDN_GCARB  + IDN_GCOM  + IDN_GOTH

@IDENTITY IDN_TAX  = IDN_TAXR * (IDN_LABSH * 0.5 * (IDN_YER(-1)  + IDN_GDI(-1)) * IDN_YED(-1) * (IDN_LNN / IDN_LNN(-1)  + IDN_TECHL - IDN_TECHL(-1)) + IDN_REMIT  + IDN_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY IDN_CTAX  = IDN_CTAXR * IDN_PROF

@IDENTITY IDN_ITAX  = IDN_ITAXR * (IDN_PCR * IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY IDN_GTRADE  = IDN_GTRADER * IDN_XTN

IDN_REVG  = IDN_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (IDN_YER$ / IDN_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - IDN_YER$(-1) / IDN_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * IDN_EXR / IDN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_GCARB  = IDN_GCARBR * IDN_CO2 * IDN_EXR / 1000

IDN_GCOM  = IDN_GCOM(-1) * ( IDN_OILC / (IDN_OILC + IDN_GASC + IDN_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + IDN_GASC / (IDN_OILC + IDN_GASC + IDN_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + IDN_COALC / (IDN_OILC + IDN_GASC + IDN_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

IDN_GOTH  = IDN_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_EXP  = IDN_EXPE  + IDN_EXPH  + IDN_EXPSP  + IDN_OGC  + IDN_OGI  + IDN_GIP

IDN_EXPE  = IDN_EXPE(-1) * (IDN_YFT / IDN_YFT(-1)) * (IDN_YED / IDN_YED(-1))

IDN_EXPH = IDN_EXPH(-1) * (IDN_YFT / IDN_YFT(-1)) * (IDN_YED / IDN_YED(-1))

IDN_EXPSP  = IDN_EXPSP(-1) * (IDN_YFT / IDN_YFT(-1)) * (IDN_YED / IDN_YED(-1)) * (IDN_POPT - IDN_LNN) / (IDN_POPT(-1) - IDN_LNN(-1))

DLOG(IDN_OGI)  = DLOG(IDN_YFT)  + DLOG(IDN_YED)

IDN_GCR  = IDN_GCR(-1)  + ( IDN_OGC / IDN_YED - IDN_OGC(-1) / IDN_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (IDN_EXPH ) / IDN_YED  - (IDN_EXPH(-1) ) / IDN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (IDN_EXPE ) / IDN_YED  - (IDN_EXPE(-1) ) / IDN_YED(-1) )

IDN_IGR  = IDN_IGR(-1) + (IDN_OGI / IDN_YED - IDN_OGI(-1) / IDN_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (IDN_EXPH ) / IDN_YED  - (IDN_EXPH(-1) ) / IDN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (IDN_EXPE ) / IDN_YED  - (IDN_EXPE(-1) ) / IDN_YED(-1) )

IDN_GIP  = ( IDN_GIP(-1)  + ( IDN_GDN(-1) - IDN_GDN(-2) ) * IDN_GINT(-1) / 100  + IDN_GDN(-13) / 12 * ( IDN_GINT(-1) / 100 - IDN_GINT(-13) / 100 ) ) * (IDN_GDFXSH * (IDN_EXR / IDN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - IDN_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY IDN_GLN  = IDN_REV  - IDN_EXP

@IDENTITY IDN_GLNRATIO  = IDN_GLN / IDN_YEN * 100

IDN_GLNT  = IDN_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

IDN_TFP  = IDN_LABSH * (IDN_TECHL  - IDN_TECHL(-1))

IDN_LABSH  = IDN_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY IDN_LFN  = IDN_LRX * IDN_POPWA

IDN_LRX  = IDN_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(IDN_YER(-1) / IDN_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY IDN_URX  = (1 - IDN_LNN / IDN_LFN) * 100

IDN_URXF  = IDN_URXF(-1) * IDN_URX / IDN_URX(-1) * IDN_LNN / IDN_LNNF / (IDN_LNN(-1) / IDN_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(IDN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(IDN_PCR  / IDN_POPT)

IDN_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(IDN_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

IDN_HEAD19  = IDN_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IDN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI^2)  , IDN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IDN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IDN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

IDN_HEAD55  = IDN_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IDN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI^2)  , IDN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IDN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IDN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(IDN_XTR)  = DLOG(IDN_WDR)  + (1  - IDN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(IDN_XTDNO$  / IDN_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * IDN_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(IDN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (IDN_EXPH(-1) / IDN_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (IDN_EXPH(-1) / IDN_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(IDN_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(IDN_PM25)

IDN_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( IDN_EXPSP / IDN_YEN )

DLOG(IDN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - IDN_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (IDN_FINC - IDN_FINC(-1))

DLOG(IDN_PCR)  = 0.00745088241794261  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(IDN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(IDN_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (IDN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(IDN_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(IDN_POPT)  +  - 0.116463960973309 * (DLOG(IDN_HIC)  - IDN_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * IDN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * IDN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(IDN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(IDN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IDN_IPR)  =  - 0.101195475154581  - 0.1 * (LOG(IDN_IPR(-1)  / IDN_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * IDN_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * IDN_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(IDN_PCR  + IDN_GCR(-1) + IDN_IGR(-1) + IDN_XTN  / IDN_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(IDN_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (IDN_USER - IDN_USER(-1))  - (0 * IDN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * IDN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - IDN_FUELSH - IDN_TOURSH)) * IDN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * IDN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * IDN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - IDN_FUELSH - IDN_TOURSH)) * IDN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(IDN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(IDN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IDN_MTR)  =  - 0.144462254737126  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(IDN_MTR(-1))  - LOG(IDN_PCR(-1) + IDN_ITR(-1) + IDN_GCR(-1) + IDN_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(IDN_YFT(-1) / IDN_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(IDN_CMUD(-1) * IDN_EXR(-1)  / IDN_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * IDN_OMS * LOG(IDN_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.603845341306364  * DLOG(IDN_XTR)  + 0.17140747184891  * DLOG(IDN_PCR)  + 0.429475424023451  * DLOG(IDN_IPR)  + 0.00622075190399036  * DLOG(IDN_GCR + IDN_IGR)

IDN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * IDN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * IDN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * IDN_OILC

IDN_POIL  = IDN_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( IDN_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - IDN_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

IDN_PG  = IDN_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( IDN_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - IDN_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

IDN_PC  = IDN_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( IDN_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - IDN_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(IDN_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

IDN_PE  = IDN_PE(-1) * ( IDN_OILC(-1) / (IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) * IDN_POIL / IDN_POIL(-1)  + IDN_GASC(-1) / (IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) * IDN_PG / IDN_PG(-1)  + IDN_COALC(-1) / (IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) * IDN_PC / IDN_PC(-1)  + IDN_RC(-1) / (IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) * IDN_PR / IDN_PR(-1) )

D(IDN_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(IDN_PM25)  = 0.2 * (IDN_COALC(-1) / IDN_EC(-1) - IDN_COALC(-2) / IDN_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (IDN_COALC(-2) / IDN_EC(-2) - IDN_COALC(-3) / IDN_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (IDN_OILC(-1) / IDN_EC(-1) - IDN_OILC(-2) / IDN_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (IDN_OILC(-2) / IDN_EC(-2) - IDN_OILC(-3) / IDN_EC(-3))

DLOG(IDN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(IDN_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(IDN_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(IDN_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IDN_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IDN_PE * IDN_EXR / IDN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IDN_PE(-1) * IDN_EXR(-1) / IDN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IDN_PE(-2) * IDN_EXR(-2) / IDN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IDN_PE(-3) * IDN_EXR(-3) / IDN_HIC(-3))  - (IDN_EFF - IDN_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(IDN_COALC)  = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(IDN_COALC(-1) / IDN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.0609006041006758 * LOG(IDN_PE(-1) / IDN_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) / IDN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IDN_GASC)  = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(IDN_GASC(-1) / IDN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.177014750883236 * LOG(IDN_PE(-1) / IDN_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) / IDN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IDN_RC)  = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( IDN_RC(-1) / IDN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0609006041006758 * LOG(IDN_PE(-1) / IDN_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) / IDN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IDN_OILC)  = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( IDN_OILC(-1) / IDN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0609006041006758 * LOG(IDN_PE(-1) / IDN_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IDN_COALC(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1) + IDN_OILC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)) / IDN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IDN_EXR) = LOG(((IDN_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.181497309578076*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((IDN_INT - USA_INT) - (IDN_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@INNOV IDN_EXR  0.193154217375848

DLOG(IRN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(IRN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IRN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (IRN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (IRN_YER / IRN_YFT  - IRN_YER(-1) / IRN_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + IRN_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + IRN_GCARB / IRN_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (IRN_PREM - IRN_PREM(-1)) / 100

IRN_YED  = IRN_YED(-1) * IRN_HIC / IRN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_INT  = IRN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_LTI  = IRN_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (IRN_INT - IRN_INT(-1))  + (IRN_PREM  - IRN_PREM(-1)) / 100

IRN_PREM  = IRN_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (IRN_GDNRATIO(-1)  - IRN_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(IRN_LNN)  = DLOG(IRN_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(IRN_LNN(-1))  - LOG(IRN_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(IRN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IRN_LNNF)  = DLOG(IRN_LNN)

IRN_FUELSH  = IRN_FUELSH(-1)

IRN_TAXR  = IRN_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( IRN_GLNT(-1)  - IRN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * IRN_YEN(-1) / ( ( IRN_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (IRN_YER(-2)  + IRN_GDI(-2)) * IRN_YED(-2) * (IRN_LNN(-1) / IRN_LNN(-2)  + IRN_TECHL(-1) - IRN_TECHL(-2) ) ) + IRN_REMIT(-1)  + IRN_EXPSP(-1) ) * IRN_SOLV

IRN_CTAXR  = IRN_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( IRN_GLNT(-1)  - IRN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * IRN_YEN(-1) / ( IRN_PROF(-1) ) * IRN_SOLV

(IRN_OGC)  = IRN_OGC(-1) * (IRN_YFT / IRN_YFT(-1) * IRN_YED / IRN_YED(-1))

IRN_USER  = (IRN_LTI  - IRN_INFT  + IRN_DEP * 100) / (1  - IRN_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (IRN_GCARB / IRN_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY IRN_XTN  = IRN_XTD$ * IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") * IRN_XTR

@IDENTITY IRN_YEN  = IRN_YER  * IRN_YED

@IDENTITY IRN_MTN  = IRN_MTD  * IRN_MTR

@IDENTITY IRN_XTN$  = IRN_XTN / IRN_EXR

@IDENTITY IRN_YEN$  = IRN_YEN / IRN_EXR

@IDENTITY IRN_MTN$  = IRN_MTN / IRN_EXR

@IDENTITY IRN_MTR$  = IRN_MTR$(-1) * IRN_MTR / IRN_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_XTR$  = IRN_XTR$(-1) * IRN_XTR / IRN_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_YER$  = IRN_YER$(-1) * IRN_YER / IRN_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_YFT$  = IRN_YFT$(-1) * IRN_YFT / IRN_YFT(-1)

IRN_POPT  = IRN_POPT(-1)  - IRN_LIVES

IRN_POPWA  = IRN_POPWA(-1) * IRN_POPT / IRN_POPT(-1)

IRN_SCR  = IRN_SCR(-1)  + ((IRN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (IRN_YFT(-1) / IRN_YER(-1)  - IRN_YFT(-2) / IRN_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY IRN_ITR  = IRN_IGR  + IRN_IPR

@IDENTITY IRN_YER  = IRN_PCR  + IRN_GCR  + IRN_ITR  + IRN_SCR  + IRN_XTR  - IRN_MTR

@IDENTITY IRN_PROF  = (IRN_YEN - IRN_ITAX) * (1 - IRN_LABSH)

@IDENTITY IRN_GDI  = IRN_YER  - IRN_XTR  + IRN_MTR  + IRN_XTN  / ((IRN_YEN  - IRN_XTN  + IRN_MTN)  / (IRN_YER  - IRN_XTR  + IRN_MTR))  - IRN_MTN  / ((IRN_YEN  - IRN_XTN  + IRN_MTN)  / (IRN_YER  - IRN_XTR  + IRN_MTR))

@IDENTITY IRN_RPDI  = IRN_LABSH * 0.5 * (IRN_YER(-1)  + IRN_GDI(-1)) * IRN_YED(-1) / IRN_HIC(-1) * (IRN_LNN / IRN_LNN(-1)  + IRN_TECHL - IRN_TECHL(-1)) + IRN_REMIT / IRN_HIC  + IRN_EXPSP / IRN_HIC  - IRN_TAX / IRN_HIC

DLOG(IRN_YFT)  = (1 - IRN_ALPHA - IRN_LABSH) * DLOG(IRN_K(-1) / IRN_LFN(-1))  + (1 - IRN_ALPHA) * DLOG(IRN_LFN)  + IRN_LABSH * D(IRN_TECHL)  + IRN_ALPHA * (DLOG(IRN_EC)  + D(IRN_EFF) )  - ( IRN_CLIMLOSS / IRN_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (IRN_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY IRN_K  = IRN_K(-1) * (1 - IRN_DEP) + IRN_ITR

DLOG(IRN_MTD)  = (1  - IRN_OMS) * ( DLOG(IRN_CMUD)  + DLOG(IRN_EXR) )  + IRN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IRN_EXR) )

DLOG(IRN_XTD$)  = (1  - IRN_OXS) * DLOG(IRN_XTDNO$)  + IRN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

IRN_INFT  = 0.95 * IRN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

IRN_OXS  = IRN_OXS(-1)

IRN_OMS  = IRN_OMS(-1) * ((IRN_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * IRN_EXR(-1) / IRN_MTN(-1)) / (IRN_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * IRN_EXR(-2) / IRN_MTN(-2)))^0.25

IRN_CXS  = IRN_CXS(-1)

IRN_FINC  = IRN_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_CAN  = IRN_XTN / IRN_EXR  - IRN_MTN / IRN_EXR  + IRN_REMIT / IRN_EXR  + IRN_CANOTH

@IDENTITY IRN_CANRATIO  = IRN_CAN / IRN_YEN$ * 100

IRN_CANOTH  = IRN_CANOTH(-1)  + ((IRN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (IRN_YEN$  / IRN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + IRN_REVG / IRN_EXR  - IRN_REVG(-1) / IRN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_GDNRATIO  = IRN_GDN / IRN_YEN * 100

IRN_GDFXSH  = ( IRN_GDFXSH(-1) * (IRN_EXR / IRN_EXR(-1) )) / (IRN_GDFXSH(-1) * (IRN_EXR / IRN_EXR(-1))  + 1 - IRN_GDFXSH(-1) )

@IDENTITY IRN_TAX  = IRN_TAXR * (IRN_LABSH * 0.5 * (IRN_YER(-1)  + IRN_GDI(-1)) * IRN_YED(-1) * (IRN_LNN / IRN_LNN(-1)  + IRN_TECHL - IRN_TECHL(-1)) + IRN_REMIT  + IRN_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY IRN_CTAX  = IRN_CTAXR * IRN_PROF

@IDENTITY IRN_ITAX  = IRN_ITAXR * (IRN_PCR * IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY IRN_GTRADE  = IRN_GTRADER * IRN_XTN

IRN_REVG  = IRN_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (IRN_YER$ / IRN_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - IRN_YER$(-1) / IRN_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * IRN_EXR / IRN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_GCARB  = IRN_GCARBR * IRN_CO2 * IRN_EXR / 1000

IRN_GCOM  = IRN_GCOM(-1) * ( IRN_OILC / (IRN_OILC + IRN_GASC + IRN_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + IRN_GASC / (IRN_OILC + IRN_GASC + IRN_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + IRN_COALC / (IRN_OILC + IRN_GASC + IRN_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

IRN_GOTH  = IRN_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_EXP  = IRN_EXPE  + IRN_EXPH  + IRN_EXPSP  + IRN_OGC  + IRN_OGI  + IRN_GIP

IRN_EXPE  = IRN_EXPE(-1) * (IRN_YFT / IRN_YFT(-1)) * (IRN_YED / IRN_YED(-1))

IRN_EXPH = IRN_EXPH(-1) * (IRN_YFT / IRN_YFT(-1)) * (IRN_YED / IRN_YED(-1))

IRN_EXPSP  = IRN_EXPSP(-1) * (IRN_YFT / IRN_YFT(-1)) * (IRN_YED / IRN_YED(-1)) * (IRN_POPT - IRN_LNN) / (IRN_POPT(-1) - IRN_LNN(-1))

DLOG(IRN_OGI)  = DLOG(IRN_YFT)  + DLOG(IRN_YED)

IRN_GCR  = IRN_GCR(-1)  + ( IRN_OGC / IRN_YED - IRN_OGC(-1) / IRN_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (IRN_EXPH ) / IRN_YED  - (IRN_EXPH(-1) ) / IRN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (IRN_EXPE ) / IRN_YED  - (IRN_EXPE(-1) ) / IRN_YED(-1) )

IRN_IGR  = IRN_IGR(-1) + (IRN_OGI / IRN_YED - IRN_OGI(-1) / IRN_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (IRN_EXPH ) / IRN_YED  - (IRN_EXPH(-1) ) / IRN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (IRN_EXPE ) / IRN_YED  - (IRN_EXPE(-1) ) / IRN_YED(-1) )

IRN_GIP  = ( IRN_GIP(-1)  + ( IRN_GDN(-1) - IRN_GDN(-2) ) * IRN_GINT(-1) / 100  + IRN_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( IRN_GINT(-1) / 100 - IRN_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (IRN_GDFXSH * (IRN_EXR / IRN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - IRN_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY IRN_GLN  = IRN_REV  - IRN_EXP

@IDENTITY IRN_GLNRATIO  = IRN_GLN / IRN_YEN * 100

IRN_GLNT  = IRN_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

IRN_TFP  = IRN_LABSH * (IRN_TECHL  - IRN_TECHL(-1))

IRN_LABSH  = IRN_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY IRN_LFN  = IRN_LRX * IRN_POPWA

IRN_LRX  = IRN_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(IRN_YER(-1) / IRN_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY IRN_URX  = (1 - IRN_LNN / IRN_LFN) * 100

IRN_URXF  = IRN_URXF(-1) * IRN_URX / IRN_URX(-1) * IRN_LNN / IRN_LNNF / (IRN_LNN(-1) / IRN_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(IRN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(IRN_PCR  / IRN_POPT)

IRN_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(IRN_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

IRN_HEAD19  = IRN_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI^2)  , IRN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

IRN_HEAD55  = IRN_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI^2)  , IRN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(IRN_XTR)  = DLOG(IRN_WDR)  + (1  - IRN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(IRN_XTDNO$  / IRN_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * IRN_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(IRN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (IRN_EXPH(-1) / IRN_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (IRN_EXPH(-1) / IRN_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(IRN_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(IRN_PM25)

IRN_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( IRN_EXPSP / IRN_YEN )

DLOG(IRN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - IRN_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (IRN_FINC - IRN_FINC(-1))

DLOG(IRN_PCR)  =  - 0.105498894572598  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(IRN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(IRN_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (IRN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(IRN_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(IRN_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(IRN_HIC)  - IRN_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * IRN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * IRN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(IRN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(IRN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IRN_IPR)  =  - 0.177715075903757  - 0.1 * (LOG(IRN_IPR(-1)  / IRN_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * IRN_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * IRN_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(IRN_PCR  + IRN_GCR(-1) + IRN_IGR(-1) + IRN_XTN  / IRN_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(IRN_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (IRN_USER - IRN_USER(-1))  - (0 * IRN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * IRN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - IRN_FUELSH - IRN_TOURSH)) * IRN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * IRN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * IRN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - IRN_FUELSH - IRN_TOURSH)) * IRN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(IRN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(IRN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(IRN_MTR)  =  - 0.0990367690359576  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(IRN_MTR(-1))  - LOG(IRN_PCR(-1) + IRN_ITR(-1) + IRN_GCR(-1) + IRN_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(IRN_YFT(-1) / IRN_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(IRN_CMUD(-1) * IRN_EXR(-1)  / IRN_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * IRN_OMS * LOG(IRN_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.136283278609399  * DLOG(IRN_XTR)  + 0.959060648266274  * DLOG(IRN_PCR)  + 0.461126429537456  * DLOG(IRN_IPR)  + 0.256007934759823  * DLOG(IRN_GCR + IRN_IGR)

IRN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * IRN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * IRN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * IRN_OILC

IRN_POIL  = IRN_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( IRN_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - IRN_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

IRN_PG  = IRN_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( IRN_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - IRN_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

IRN_PC  = IRN_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( IRN_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - IRN_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(IRN_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

IRN_PE  = IRN_PE(-1) * ( IRN_OILC(-1) / (IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) * IRN_POIL / IRN_POIL(-1)  + IRN_GASC(-1) / (IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) * IRN_PG / IRN_PG(-1)  + IRN_COALC(-1) / (IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) * IRN_PC / IRN_PC(-1)  + IRN_RC(-1) / (IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) * IRN_PR / IRN_PR(-1) )

D(IRN_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(IRN_PM25)  = 0.2 * (IRN_COALC(-1) / IRN_EC(-1) - IRN_COALC(-2) / IRN_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (IRN_COALC(-2) / IRN_EC(-2) - IRN_COALC(-3) / IRN_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (IRN_OILC(-1) / IRN_EC(-1) - IRN_OILC(-2) / IRN_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (IRN_OILC(-2) / IRN_EC(-2) - IRN_OILC(-3) / IRN_EC(-3))

DLOG(IRN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(IRN_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(IRN_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(IRN_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IRN_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IRN_PE * IRN_EXR / IRN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IRN_PE(-1) * IRN_EXR(-1) / IRN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IRN_PE(-2) * IRN_EXR(-2) / IRN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(IRN_PE(-3) * IRN_EXR(-3) / IRN_HIC(-3))  - (IRN_EFF - IRN_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(IRN_COALC)  = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(IRN_COALC(-1) / IRN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(IRN_PE(-1) / IRN_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) / IRN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IRN_GASC)  = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(IRN_GASC(-1) / IRN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.652165036981829 * LOG(IRN_PE(-1) / IRN_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) / IRN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IRN_RC)  = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( IRN_RC(-1) / IRN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.025944822948987 * LOG(IRN_PE(-1) / IRN_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) / IRN_EC(-1))

DLOG(IRN_OILC)  = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( IRN_OILC(-1) / IRN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.025944822948987 * LOG(IRN_PE(-1) / IRN_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((IRN_COALC(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1) + IRN_OILC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)) / IRN_EC(-1))

IRN_EXR  = IRN_EXR(-1) * ( (IRN_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(JPN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(JPN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(JPN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (JPN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (JPN_YER / JPN_YFT  - JPN_YER(-1) / JPN_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + JPN_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + JPN_GCARB / JPN_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (JPN_PREM - JPN_PREM(-1)) / 100

JPN_YED  = JPN_YED(-1) * JPN_HIC / JPN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_INT  = JPN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_LTI  = JPN_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (JPN_INT - JPN_INT(-1))  + (JPN_PREM  - JPN_PREM(-1)) / 100

JPN_PREM  = JPN_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (JPN_GDNRATIO(-1)  - JPN_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(JPN_LNN)  = DLOG(JPN_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(JPN_LNN(-1))  - LOG(JPN_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(JPN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(JPN_LNNF)  = DLOG(JPN_LNN)

JPN_FUELSH  = JPN_FUELSH(-1)

JPN_TAXR  = JPN_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( JPN_GLNT(-1)  - JPN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * JPN_YEN(-1) / ( ( JPN_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (JPN_YER(-2)  + JPN_GDI(-2)) * JPN_YED(-2) * (JPN_LNN(-1) / JPN_LNN(-2)  + JPN_TECHL(-1) - JPN_TECHL(-2) ) ) + JPN_REMIT(-1)  + JPN_EXPSP(-1) ) * JPN_SOLV

JPN_CTAXR  = JPN_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( JPN_GLNT(-1)  - JPN_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * JPN_YEN(-1) / ( JPN_PROF(-1) ) * JPN_SOLV

(JPN_OGC)  = JPN_OGC(-1) * (JPN_YFT / JPN_YFT(-1) * JPN_YED / JPN_YED(-1))

JPN_USER  = (JPN_LTI  - JPN_INFT  + JPN_DEP * 100) / (1  - JPN_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (JPN_GCARB / JPN_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY JPN_XTN  = JPN_XTD$ * JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") * JPN_XTR

@IDENTITY JPN_YEN  = JPN_YER  * JPN_YED

@IDENTITY JPN_MTN  = JPN_MTD  * JPN_MTR

@IDENTITY JPN_XTN$  = JPN_XTN / JPN_EXR

@IDENTITY JPN_YEN$  = JPN_YEN / JPN_EXR

@IDENTITY JPN_MTN$  = JPN_MTN / JPN_EXR

@IDENTITY JPN_MTR$  = JPN_MTR$(-1) * JPN_MTR / JPN_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_XTR$  = JPN_XTR$(-1) * JPN_XTR / JPN_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_YER$  = JPN_YER$(-1) * JPN_YER / JPN_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_YFT$  = JPN_YFT$(-1) * JPN_YFT / JPN_YFT(-1)

JPN_POPT  = JPN_POPT(-1)  - JPN_LIVES

JPN_POPWA  = JPN_POPWA(-1) * JPN_POPT / JPN_POPT(-1)

JPN_SCR  = JPN_SCR(-1)  + ((JPN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (JPN_YFT(-1) / JPN_YER(-1)  - JPN_YFT(-2) / JPN_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY JPN_ITR  = JPN_IGR  + JPN_IPR

@IDENTITY JPN_YER  = JPN_PCR  + JPN_GCR  + JPN_ITR  + JPN_SCR  + JPN_XTR  - JPN_MTR

@IDENTITY JPN_PROF  = (JPN_YEN - JPN_ITAX) * (1 - JPN_LABSH)

@IDENTITY JPN_GDI  = JPN_YER  - JPN_XTR  + JPN_MTR  + JPN_XTN  / ((JPN_YEN  - JPN_XTN  + JPN_MTN)  / (JPN_YER  - JPN_XTR  + JPN_MTR))  - JPN_MTN  / ((JPN_YEN  - JPN_XTN  + JPN_MTN)  / (JPN_YER  - JPN_XTR  + JPN_MTR))

@IDENTITY JPN_RPDI  = JPN_LABSH * 0.5 * (JPN_YER(-1)  + JPN_GDI(-1)) * JPN_YED(-1) / JPN_HIC(-1) * (JPN_LNN / JPN_LNN(-1)  + JPN_TECHL - JPN_TECHL(-1)) + JPN_REMIT / JPN_HIC  + JPN_EXPSP / JPN_HIC  - JPN_TAX / JPN_HIC

DLOG(JPN_YFT)  = (1 - JPN_ALPHA - JPN_LABSH) * DLOG(JPN_K(-1) / JPN_LFN(-1))  + (1 - JPN_ALPHA) * DLOG(JPN_LFN)  + JPN_LABSH * D(JPN_TECHL)  + JPN_ALPHA * (DLOG(JPN_EC)  + D(JPN_EFF) )  - ( JPN_CLIMLOSS / JPN_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (JPN_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY JPN_K  = JPN_K(-1) * (1 - JPN_DEP) + JPN_ITR

DLOG(JPN_MTD)  = (1  - JPN_OMS) * ( DLOG(JPN_CMUD)  + DLOG(JPN_EXR) )  + JPN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(JPN_EXR) )

DLOG(JPN_XTD$)  = (1  - JPN_OXS) * DLOG(JPN_XTDNO$)  + JPN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

JPN_INFT  = 0.95 * JPN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

JPN_OXS  = JPN_OXS(-1)

JPN_OMS  = JPN_OMS(-1) * ((JPN_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * JPN_EXR(-1) / JPN_MTN(-1)) / (JPN_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * JPN_EXR(-2) / JPN_MTN(-2)))^0.25

JPN_CXS  = JPN_CXS(-1)

JPN_FINC  = JPN_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_CAN  = JPN_XTN / JPN_EXR  - JPN_MTN / JPN_EXR  + JPN_REMIT / JPN_EXR  + JPN_CANOTH

@IDENTITY JPN_CANRATIO  = JPN_CAN / JPN_YEN$ * 100

JPN_CANOTH  = JPN_CANOTH(-1)  + ((JPN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (JPN_YEN$  / JPN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + JPN_REVG / JPN_EXR  - JPN_REVG(-1) / JPN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(JPN_EFEX)  =  - LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.535430695E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.654660933E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03117273613 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.178552592E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001575601763 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.250325508E-05 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001354612688 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008001296172 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1858952538 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.899081787E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001181319763 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03366624658 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01107426524 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02195985887 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003639782919 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008120081535 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.417312705E-05 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.938086966E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001596017357 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001907438313 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01775430011 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.375545102E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.733246495E-05 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003452821946 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008317630482 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.779053932E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003486788959 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001176310137 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001349018512 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01453625003 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05551632681 * LOG(KOR_EXR / JPN_REMIT  = JPN_REMIT(-1) / JPN_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05513343721 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01321572774 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1002170675 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001340258124 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0076141651 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06472272792 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02162383256 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0200794146 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 7.239350453E-05 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04189333844 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01420170464 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01616331732 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007141521393 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009965767684 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009254629092 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001242429064 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02371767735 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 7.337179513E-05 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001213080346 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003541411978 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005948006858 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005958610298 * PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009704642769 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07919947224 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000100763932 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002901609925 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3491729356 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006544764126 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.521846166E-05 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 5.77191455E-05 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002177674879 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03347359042 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1036666557 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001675811801 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * JPN_EXR

JPN_GINT  = JPN_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 9 * (JPN_LTI  - JPN_LTI(-1))

JPN_GDN  = JPN_GDN(-1) * (JPN_GDFXSH  * (JPN_EXR  / JPN_EXR(-1))  + (1  - JPN_GDFXSH))  - JPN_GLN

@IDENTITY JPN_GDNRATIO  = JPN_GDN / JPN_YEN * 100

JPN_GDFXSH  = ( JPN_GDFXSH(-1) * (JPN_EXR / JPN_EXR(-1) )) / (JPN_GDFXSH(-1) * (JPN_EXR / JPN_EXR(-1))  + 1 - JPN_GDFXSH(-1) )

JPN_TOURSH  = JPN_TOURSH(-1)

JPN_LOCK  = 0

JPN_GCARBR  = JPN_GCARBR(-1)

JPN_GTRADER  = JPN_GTRADER(-1)

JPN_ITAXR  = JPN_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_REV  = JPN_TAX  + JPN_CTAX  + JPN_ITAX  + JPN_GTRADE  + JPN_REVG  + JPN_GCARB  + JPN_GCOM  + JPN_GOTH

@IDENTITY JPN_TAX  = JPN_TAXR * (JPN_LABSH * 0.5 * (JPN_YER(-1)  + JPN_GDI(-1)) * JPN_YED(-1) * (JPN_LNN / JPN_LNN(-1)  + JPN_TECHL - JPN_TECHL(-1)) + JPN_REMIT  + JPN_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY JPN_CTAX  = JPN_CTAXR * JPN_PROF

@IDENTITY JPN_ITAX  = JPN_ITAXR * (JPN_PCR * JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY JPN_GTRADE  = JPN_GTRADER * JPN_XTN

JPN_REVG  = JPN_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (JPN_YER$ / JPN_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - JPN_YER$(-1) / JPN_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * JPN_EXR / JPN_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_GCARB  = JPN_GCARBR * JPN_CO2 * JPN_EXR / 1000

JPN_GCOM  = JPN_GCOM(-1) * ( JPN_OILC / (JPN_OILC + JPN_GASC + JPN_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + JPN_GASC / (JPN_OILC + JPN_GASC + JPN_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + JPN_COALC / (JPN_OILC + JPN_GASC + JPN_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

JPN_GOTH  = JPN_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_EXP  = JPN_EXPE  + JPN_EXPH  + JPN_EXPSP  + JPN_OGC  + JPN_OGI  + JPN_GIP

JPN_EXPE  = JPN_EXPE(-1) * (JPN_YFT / JPN_YFT(-1)) * (JPN_YED / JPN_YED(-1))

JPN_EXPH = JPN_EXPH(-1) * (JPN_YFT / JPN_YFT(-1)) * (JPN_YED / JPN_YED(-1))

JPN_EXPSP  = JPN_EXPSP(-1) * (JPN_YFT / JPN_YFT(-1)) * (JPN_YED / JPN_YED(-1)) * (JPN_POPT - JPN_LNN) / (JPN_POPT(-1) - JPN_LNN(-1))

DLOG(JPN_OGI)  = DLOG(JPN_YFT)  + DLOG(JPN_YED)

JPN_GCR  = JPN_GCR(-1)  + ( JPN_OGC / JPN_YED - JPN_OGC(-1) / JPN_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (JPN_EXPH ) / JPN_YED  - (JPN_EXPH(-1) ) / JPN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (JPN_EXPE ) / JPN_YED  - (JPN_EXPE(-1) ) / JPN_YED(-1) )

JPN_IGR  = JPN_IGR(-1) + (JPN_OGI / JPN_YED - JPN_OGI(-1) / JPN_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (JPN_EXPH ) / JPN_YED  - (JPN_EXPH(-1) ) / JPN_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (JPN_EXPE ) / JPN_YED  - (JPN_EXPE(-1) ) / JPN_YED(-1) )

JPN_GIP  = ( JPN_GIP(-1)  + ( JPN_GDN(-1) - JPN_GDN(-2) ) * JPN_GINT(-1) / 100  + JPN_GDN(-10) / 9 * ( JPN_GINT(-1) / 100 - JPN_GINT(-10) / 100 ) ) * (JPN_GDFXSH * (JPN_EXR / JPN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - JPN_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY JPN_GLN  = JPN_REV  - JPN_EXP

@IDENTITY JPN_GLNRATIO  = JPN_GLN / JPN_YEN * 100

JPN_GLNT  = JPN_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

JPN_TFP  = JPN_LABSH * (JPN_TECHL  - JPN_TECHL(-1))

JPN_LABSH  = JPN_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY JPN_LFN  = JPN_LRX * JPN_POPWA

JPN_LRX  = JPN_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(JPN_YER(-1) / JPN_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY JPN_URX  = (1 - JPN_LNN / JPN_LFN) * 100

JPN_URXF  = JPN_URXF(-1) * JPN_URX / JPN_URX(-1) * JPN_LNN / JPN_LNNF / (JPN_LNN(-1) / JPN_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(JPN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(JPN_PCR  / JPN_POPT)

JPN_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(JPN_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

JPN_HEAD19  = JPN_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(JPN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI^2)  , JPN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(JPN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , JPN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

JPN_HEAD55  = JPN_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(JPN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI^2)  , JPN_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(JPN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , JPN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(JPN_XTR)  = DLOG(JPN_WDR)  + (1  - JPN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(JPN_XTDNO$  / JPN_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * JPN_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(JPN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (JPN_EXPH(-1) / JPN_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (JPN_EXPH(-1) / JPN_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(JPN_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(JPN_PM25)

JPN_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( JPN_EXPSP / JPN_YEN )

DLOG(JPN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - JPN_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (JPN_FINC - JPN_FINC(-1))

DLOG(JPN_PCR)  =  - 0.341505877165664  +  - 0.186986689088607 * (LOG(JPN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(JPN_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (JPN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(JPN_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(JPN_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(JPN_HIC)  - JPN_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * JPN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * JPN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(JPN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(JPN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(JPN_IPR)  =  - 0.198165239232214  - 0.1 * (LOG(JPN_IPR(-1)  / JPN_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * JPN_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * JPN_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(JPN_PCR  + JPN_GCR(-1) + JPN_IGR(-1) + JPN_XTN  / JPN_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(JPN_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (JPN_USER - JPN_USER(-1))  - (0 * JPN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * JPN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - JPN_FUELSH - JPN_TOURSH)) * JPN_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * JPN_FUELSH  + 0.26 * JPN_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - JPN_FUELSH - JPN_TOURSH)) * JPN_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(JPN_YFT(-1))  - LOG(JPN_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(JPN_MTR)  =  - 0.2483037854444  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(JPN_MTR(-1))  - LOG(JPN_PCR(-1) + JPN_ITR(-1) + JPN_GCR(-1) + JPN_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(JPN_YFT(-1) / JPN_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(JPN_CMUD(-1) * JPN_EXR(-1)  / JPN_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * JPN_OMS * LOG(JPN_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.307177960821141  * DLOG(JPN_XTR)  + 0.156250151515036  * DLOG(JPN_PCR)  + 0.521584467015757  * DLOG(JPN_IPR)  + 0.0137394056990098  * DLOG(JPN_GCR + JPN_IGR)

JPN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * JPN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * JPN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * JPN_OILC

JPN_POIL  = JPN_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( JPN_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - JPN_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

JPN_PG  = JPN_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( JPN_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - JPN_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

JPN_PC  = JPN_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( JPN_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - JPN_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(JPN_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

JPN_PE  = JPN_PE(-1) * ( JPN_OILC(-1) / (JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) * JPN_POIL / JPN_POIL(-1)  + JPN_GASC(-1) / (JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) * JPN_PG / JPN_PG(-1)  + JPN_COALC(-1) / (JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) * JPN_PC / JPN_PC(-1)  + JPN_RC(-1) / (JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) * JPN_PR / JPN_PR(-1) )

D(JPN_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(JPN_PM25)  = 0.2 * (JPN_COALC(-1) / JPN_EC(-1) - JPN_COALC(-2) / JPN_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (JPN_COALC(-2) / JPN_EC(-2) - JPN_COALC(-3) / JPN_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (JPN_OILC(-1) / JPN_EC(-1) - JPN_OILC(-2) / JPN_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (JPN_OILC(-2) / JPN_EC(-2) - JPN_OILC(-3) / JPN_EC(-3))

DLOG(JPN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(JPN_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(JPN_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(JPN_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(JPN_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(JPN_PE * JPN_EXR / JPN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(JPN_PE(-1) * JPN_EXR(-1) / JPN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(JPN_PE(-2) * JPN_EXR(-2) / JPN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(JPN_PE(-3) * JPN_EXR(-3) / JPN_HIC(-3))  - (JPN_EFF - JPN_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(JPN_COALC)  = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(JPN_COALC(-1) / JPN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.125506941833827 * LOG(JPN_PE(-1) / JPN_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) / JPN_EC(-1))

DLOG(JPN_GASC)  = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(JPN_GASC(-1) / JPN_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.208440408830797 * LOG(JPN_PE(-1) / JPN_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) / JPN_EC(-1))

DLOG(JPN_RC)  = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( JPN_RC(-1) / JPN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.125506941833827 * LOG(JPN_PE(-1) / JPN_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) / JPN_EC(-1))

DLOG(JPN_OILC)  = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( JPN_OILC(-1) / JPN_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.125506941833827 * LOG(JPN_PE(-1) / JPN_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((JPN_COALC(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1) + JPN_OILC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)) / JPN_EC(-1))

JPN_EXR  = JPN_EXR(-1) * ( ( (JPN_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (JPN_INT  - USA_INT)  - (JPN_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(KAZ_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(KAZ_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KAZ_MTD)  + 0.4 * (KAZ_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (KAZ_YER / KAZ_YFT  - KAZ_YER(-1) / KAZ_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + KAZ_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + KAZ_GCARB / KAZ_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (KAZ_PREM - KAZ_PREM(-1)) / 100

KAZ_YED  = KAZ_YED(-1) * KAZ_HIC / KAZ_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_INT  = KAZ_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_LTI  = KAZ_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (KAZ_INT - KAZ_INT(-1))  + (KAZ_PREM  - KAZ_PREM(-1)) / 100

KAZ_PREM  = KAZ_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (KAZ_GDNRATIO(-1)  - KAZ_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(KAZ_LNN)  = DLOG(KAZ_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(KAZ_LNN(-1))  - LOG(KAZ_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(KAZ_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KAZ_LNNF)  = DLOG(KAZ_LNN)

KAZ_FUELSH  = KAZ_FUELSH(-1)

KAZ_TAXR  = KAZ_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KAZ_GLNT(-1)  - KAZ_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KAZ_YEN(-1) / ( ( KAZ_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (KAZ_YER(-2)  + KAZ_GDI(-2)) * KAZ_YED(-2) * (KAZ_LNN(-1) / KAZ_LNN(-2)  + KAZ_TECHL(-1) - KAZ_TECHL(-2) ) ) + KAZ_REMIT(-1)  + KAZ_EXPSP(-1) ) * KAZ_SOLV

KAZ_CTAXR  = KAZ_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KAZ_GLNT(-1)  - KAZ_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KAZ_YEN(-1) / ( KAZ_PROF(-1) ) * KAZ_SOLV

(KAZ_OGC)  = KAZ_OGC(-1) * (KAZ_YFT / KAZ_YFT(-1) * KAZ_YED / KAZ_YED(-1))

KAZ_USER  = (KAZ_LTI  - KAZ_INFT  + KAZ_DEP * 100) / (1  - KAZ_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (KAZ_GCARB / KAZ_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY KAZ_XTN  = KAZ_XTD$ * KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") * KAZ_XTR

@IDENTITY KAZ_YEN  = KAZ_YER  * KAZ_YED

@IDENTITY KAZ_MTN  = KAZ_MTD  * KAZ_MTR

@IDENTITY KAZ_XTN$  = KAZ_XTN / KAZ_EXR

@IDENTITY KAZ_YEN$  = KAZ_YEN / KAZ_EXR

@IDENTITY KAZ_MTN$  = KAZ_MTN / KAZ_EXR

@IDENTITY KAZ_MTR$  = KAZ_MTR$(-1) * KAZ_MTR / KAZ_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_XTR$  = KAZ_XTR$(-1) * KAZ_XTR / KAZ_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_YER$  = KAZ_YER$(-1) * KAZ_YER / KAZ_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_YFT$  = KAZ_YFT$(-1) * KAZ_YFT / KAZ_YFT(-1)

KAZ_POPT  = KAZ_POPT(-1)  - KAZ_LIVES

KAZ_POPWA  = KAZ_POPWA(-1) * KAZ_POPT / KAZ_POPT(-1)

KAZ_SCR  = KAZ_SCR(-1)  + ((KAZ_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KAZ_YFT(-1) / KAZ_YER(-1)  - KAZ_YFT(-2) / KAZ_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY KAZ_ITR  = KAZ_IGR  + KAZ_IPR

@IDENTITY KAZ_YER  = KAZ_PCR  + KAZ_GCR  + KAZ_ITR  + KAZ_SCR  + KAZ_XTR  - KAZ_MTR

@IDENTITY KAZ_PROF  = (KAZ_YEN - KAZ_ITAX) * (1 - KAZ_LABSH)

@IDENTITY KAZ_GDI  = KAZ_YER  - KAZ_XTR  + KAZ_MTR  + KAZ_XTN  / ((KAZ_YEN  - KAZ_XTN  + KAZ_MTN)  / (KAZ_YER  - KAZ_XTR  + KAZ_MTR))  - KAZ_MTN  / ((KAZ_YEN  - KAZ_XTN  + KAZ_MTN)  / (KAZ_YER  - KAZ_XTR  + KAZ_MTR))

@IDENTITY KAZ_RPDI  = KAZ_LABSH * 0.5 * (KAZ_YER(-1)  + KAZ_GDI(-1)) * KAZ_YED(-1) / KAZ_HIC(-1) * (KAZ_LNN / KAZ_LNN(-1)  + KAZ_TECHL - KAZ_TECHL(-1)) + KAZ_REMIT / KAZ_HIC  + KAZ_EXPSP / KAZ_HIC  - KAZ_TAX / KAZ_HIC

DLOG(KAZ_YFT)  = (1 - KAZ_ALPHA - KAZ_LABSH) * DLOG(KAZ_K(-1) / KAZ_LFN(-1))  + (1 - KAZ_ALPHA) * DLOG(KAZ_LFN)  + KAZ_LABSH * D(KAZ_TECHL)  + KAZ_ALPHA * (DLOG(KAZ_EC)  + D(KAZ_EFF) )  - ( KAZ_CLIMLOSS / KAZ_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (KAZ_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY KAZ_K  = KAZ_K(-1) * (1 - KAZ_DEP) + KAZ_ITR

DLOG(KAZ_MTD)  = (1  - KAZ_OMS) * ( DLOG(KAZ_CMUD)  + DLOG(KAZ_EXR) )  + KAZ_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KAZ_EXR) )

DLOG(KAZ_XTD$)  = (1  - KAZ_OXS) * DLOG(KAZ_XTDNO$)  + KAZ_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

KAZ_INFT  = 0.95 * KAZ_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

KAZ_OXS  = KAZ_OXS(-1)

KAZ_OMS  = KAZ_OMS(-1) * ((KAZ_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * KAZ_EXR(-1) / KAZ_MTN(-1)) / (KAZ_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * KAZ_EXR(-2) / KAZ_MTN(-2)))^0.25

KAZ_CXS  = KAZ_CXS(-1)

KAZ_FINC  = KAZ_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_CAN  = KAZ_XTN / KAZ_EXR  - KAZ_MTN / KAZ_EXR  + KAZ_REMIT / KAZ_EXR  + KAZ_CANOTH

@IDENTITY KAZ_CANRATIO  = KAZ_CAN / KAZ_YEN$ * 100

KAZ_CANOTH  = KAZ_CANOTH(-1)  + ((KAZ_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KAZ_YEN$  / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KAZ_REVG / KAZ_EXR  - KAZ_REVG(-1) / KAZ_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(KAZ_EFEX)  =  - LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005347949632 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001449441856 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002987662748 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002220143864 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.088803017E-05 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.504111317E-09 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.269705159E-07 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.008290527E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1951052988 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.497829207E-08 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001739277762 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001307486404 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009135358038 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000215148483 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008244069745 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01395532169 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.030616038E-09 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007117699266 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.939774248E-06 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.454308584E-06 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006064025241 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.709057191E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.853825257E-08 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001244637777 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.091907807E-07 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.816215432E-07 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.422422604E-05 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005291170964 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.278105074E-07 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.237739376E-05 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01510009724 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.2108888939 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.957543633E-08 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001667285817 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.733476777E-07 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001178611046 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003578358603 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006815744043 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.122622343E-07 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02536992606 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005411136057 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02410919096 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.447149737E-08 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003432522408 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02466296448 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02385336289 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0359862108 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03672071317 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09882661421 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04438679798 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002492722479 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03518668444 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005214891727 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001391357449 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1391385317 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008014330834 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0110247223 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(KAZ_REFEX )  =  - LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005347949632 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001449441856 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002987662748 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002220143864 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.088803017E-05 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.504111317E-09 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.269705159E-07 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.008290527E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1951052988 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.497829207E-08 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001739277762 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001307486404 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009135358038 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000215148483 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008244069745 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01395532169 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.030616038E-09 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007117699266 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.939774248E-06 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.454308584E-06 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006064025241 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.709057191E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.853825257E-08 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001244637777 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.091907807E-07 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.816215432E-07 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.422422604E-05 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005291170964 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.278105074E-07 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.237739376E-05 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01510009724 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.2108888939 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.957543633E-08 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001667285817 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.733476777E-07 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001178611046 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003578358603 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006815744043 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.122622343E-07 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02536992606 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005411136057 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02410919096 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.447149737E-08 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003432522408 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02466296448 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02385336289 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0359862108 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03672071317 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.09882661421 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04438679798 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002492722479 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03518668444 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005214891727 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001391357449 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1391385317 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008014330834 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0110247223 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

KAZ_REMIT  = KAZ_REMIT(-1) / KAZ_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001863258298 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003088324452 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005195594527 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006820178968 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001199456511 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.206910125 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006643047673 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001377611183 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003102952986 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005756366075 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001694308974 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009286671206 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0036826903 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004144428087 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 4.715811922E-05 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 4.678092425E-05 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.6354633454 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001811999472 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003635275886 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003100820318 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007568014718 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02350499061 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.331823641E-05 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.09477989807 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002144615582 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0040964933 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * KAZ_EXR

KAZ_GINT  = KAZ_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 14 * (KAZ_LTI  - KAZ_LTI(-1))

KAZ_GDN  = KAZ_GDN(-1) * (KAZ_GDFXSH  * (KAZ_EXR  / KAZ_EXR(-1))  + (1  - KAZ_GDFXSH))  - KAZ_GLN

@IDENTITY KAZ_GDNRATIO  = KAZ_GDN / KAZ_YEN * 100

KAZ_GDFXSH  = ( KAZ_GDFXSH(-1) * (KAZ_EXR / KAZ_EXR(-1) )) / (KAZ_GDFXSH(-1) * (KAZ_EXR / KAZ_EXR(-1))  + 1 - KAZ_GDFXSH(-1) )

KAZ_TOURSH  = KAZ_TOURSH(-1)

KAZ_LOCK  = 0

KAZ_GCARBR  = KAZ_GCARBR(-1)

KAZ_GTRADER  = KAZ_GTRADER(-1)

KAZ_ITAXR  = KAZ_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_REV  = KAZ_TAX  + KAZ_CTAX  + KAZ_ITAX  + KAZ_GTRADE  + KAZ_REVG  + KAZ_GCARB  + KAZ_GCOM  + KAZ_GOTH

@IDENTITY KAZ_TAX  = KAZ_TAXR * (KAZ_LABSH * 0.5 * (KAZ_YER(-1)  + KAZ_GDI(-1)) * KAZ_YED(-1) * (KAZ_LNN / KAZ_LNN(-1)  + KAZ_TECHL - KAZ_TECHL(-1)) + KAZ_REMIT  + KAZ_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY KAZ_CTAX  = KAZ_CTAXR * KAZ_PROF

@IDENTITY KAZ_ITAX  = KAZ_ITAXR * (KAZ_PCR * KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY KAZ_GTRADE  = KAZ_GTRADER * KAZ_XTN

KAZ_REVG  = KAZ_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (KAZ_YER$ / KAZ_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - KAZ_YER$(-1) / KAZ_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * KAZ_EXR / KAZ_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_GCARB  = KAZ_GCARBR * KAZ_CO2 * KAZ_EXR / 1000

KAZ_GCOM  = KAZ_GCOM(-1) * ( KAZ_OILC / (KAZ_OILC + KAZ_GASC + KAZ_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + KAZ_GASC / (KAZ_OILC + KAZ_GASC + KAZ_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + KAZ_COALC / (KAZ_OILC + KAZ_GASC + KAZ_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

KAZ_GOTH  = KAZ_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_EXP  = KAZ_EXPE  + KAZ_EXPH  + KAZ_EXPSP  + KAZ_OGC  + KAZ_OGI  + KAZ_GIP

KAZ_EXPE  = KAZ_EXPE(-1) * (KAZ_YFT / KAZ_YFT(-1)) * (KAZ_YED / KAZ_YED(-1))

KAZ_EXPH = KAZ_EXPH(-1) * (KAZ_YFT / KAZ_YFT(-1)) * (KAZ_YED / KAZ_YED(-1))

KAZ_EXPSP  = KAZ_EXPSP(-1) * (KAZ_YFT / KAZ_YFT(-1)) * (KAZ_YED / KAZ_YED(-1)) * (KAZ_POPT - KAZ_LNN) / (KAZ_POPT(-1) - KAZ_LNN(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_OGI)  = DLOG(KAZ_YFT)  + DLOG(KAZ_YED)

KAZ_GCR  = KAZ_GCR(-1)  + ( KAZ_OGC / KAZ_YED - KAZ_OGC(-1) / KAZ_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (KAZ_EXPH ) / KAZ_YED  - (KAZ_EXPH(-1) ) / KAZ_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KAZ_EXPE ) / KAZ_YED  - (KAZ_EXPE(-1) ) / KAZ_YED(-1) )

KAZ_IGR  = KAZ_IGR(-1) + (KAZ_OGI / KAZ_YED - KAZ_OGI(-1) / KAZ_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (KAZ_EXPH ) / KAZ_YED  - (KAZ_EXPH(-1) ) / KAZ_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KAZ_EXPE ) / KAZ_YED  - (KAZ_EXPE(-1) ) / KAZ_YED(-1) )

KAZ_GIP  = ( KAZ_GIP(-1)  + ( KAZ_GDN(-1) - KAZ_GDN(-2) ) * KAZ_GINT(-1) / 100  + KAZ_GDN(-15) / 14 * ( KAZ_GINT(-1) / 100 - KAZ_GINT(-15) / 100 ) ) * (KAZ_GDFXSH * (KAZ_EXR / KAZ_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KAZ_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY KAZ_GLN  = KAZ_REV  - KAZ_EXP

@IDENTITY KAZ_GLNRATIO  = KAZ_GLN / KAZ_YEN * 100

KAZ_GLNT  = KAZ_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

KAZ_TFP  = KAZ_LABSH * (KAZ_TECHL  - KAZ_TECHL(-1))

KAZ_LABSH  = KAZ_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY KAZ_LFN  = KAZ_LRX * KAZ_POPWA

KAZ_LRX  = KAZ_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(KAZ_YER(-1) / KAZ_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY KAZ_URX  = (1 - KAZ_LNN / KAZ_LFN) * 100

KAZ_URXF  = KAZ_URXF(-1) * KAZ_URX / KAZ_URX(-1) * KAZ_LNN / KAZ_LNNF / (KAZ_LNN(-1) / KAZ_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KAZ_PCR  / KAZ_POPT)

KAZ_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(KAZ_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

KAZ_HEAD19  = KAZ_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI^2)  , KAZ_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KAZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

KAZ_HEAD55  = KAZ_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI^2)  , KAZ_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KAZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(KAZ_XTR)  = DLOG(KAZ_WDR)  + (1  - KAZ_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(KAZ_XTDNO$  / KAZ_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * KAZ_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(KAZ_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (KAZ_EXPH(-1) / KAZ_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (KAZ_EXPH(-1) / KAZ_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(KAZ_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(KAZ_PM25)

KAZ_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( KAZ_EXPSP / KAZ_YEN )

DLOG(KAZ_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - KAZ_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (KAZ_FINC - KAZ_FINC(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_PCR)  =  - 0.0179228372829119  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(KAZ_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KAZ_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (KAZ_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KAZ_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(KAZ_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(KAZ_HIC)  - KAZ_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * KAZ_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * KAZ_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KAZ_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KAZ_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KAZ_IPR)  =  - 0.148558224171824  - 0.1 * (LOG(KAZ_IPR(-1)  / KAZ_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * KAZ_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * KAZ_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(KAZ_PCR  + KAZ_GCR(-1) + KAZ_IGR(-1) + KAZ_XTN  / KAZ_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(KAZ_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (KAZ_USER - KAZ_USER(-1))  - (0 * KAZ_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KAZ_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KAZ_FUELSH - KAZ_TOURSH)) * KAZ_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * KAZ_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KAZ_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KAZ_FUELSH - KAZ_TOURSH)) * KAZ_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KAZ_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KAZ_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KAZ_MTR)  =  - 0.153974732176398  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(KAZ_MTR(-1))  - LOG(KAZ_PCR(-1) + KAZ_ITR(-1) + KAZ_GCR(-1) + KAZ_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(KAZ_YFT(-1) / KAZ_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(KAZ_CMUD(-1) * KAZ_EXR(-1)  / KAZ_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * KAZ_OMS * LOG(KAZ_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.608819054088144  * DLOG(KAZ_XTR)  + 0.112964523918026  * DLOG(KAZ_PCR)  + 0.375771246571348  * DLOG(KAZ_IPR)  + 0.0647991589052041  * DLOG(KAZ_GCR + KAZ_IGR)

KAZ_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * KAZ_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * KAZ_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * KAZ_OILC

KAZ_POIL  = KAZ_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( KAZ_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - KAZ_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

KAZ_PG  = KAZ_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( KAZ_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - KAZ_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

KAZ_PC  = KAZ_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( KAZ_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - KAZ_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(KAZ_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

KAZ_PE  = KAZ_PE(-1) * ( KAZ_OILC(-1) / (KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) * KAZ_POIL / KAZ_POIL(-1)  + KAZ_GASC(-1) / (KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) * KAZ_PG / KAZ_PG(-1)  + KAZ_COALC(-1) / (KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) * KAZ_PC / KAZ_PC(-1)  + KAZ_RC(-1) / (KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) * KAZ_PR / KAZ_PR(-1) )

D(KAZ_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(KAZ_PM25)  = 0.2 * (KAZ_COALC(-1) / KAZ_EC(-1) - KAZ_COALC(-2) / KAZ_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (KAZ_COALC(-2) / KAZ_EC(-2) - KAZ_COALC(-3) / KAZ_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (KAZ_OILC(-1) / KAZ_EC(-1) - KAZ_OILC(-2) / KAZ_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (KAZ_OILC(-2) / KAZ_EC(-2) - KAZ_OILC(-3) / KAZ_EC(-3))

DLOG(KAZ_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(KAZ_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(KAZ_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(KAZ_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KAZ_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KAZ_PE * KAZ_EXR / KAZ_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KAZ_PE(-1) * KAZ_EXR(-1) / KAZ_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KAZ_PE(-2) * KAZ_EXR(-2) / KAZ_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KAZ_PE(-3) * KAZ_EXR(-3) / KAZ_HIC(-3))  - (KAZ_EFF - KAZ_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(KAZ_COALC)  = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KAZ_COALC(-1) / KAZ_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.0310546386687403 * LOG(KAZ_PE(-1) / KAZ_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) / KAZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_GASC)  = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KAZ_GASC(-1) / KAZ_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.207917605033355 * LOG(KAZ_PE(-1) / KAZ_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) / KAZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_RC)  = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KAZ_RC(-1) / KAZ_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0310546386687403 * LOG(KAZ_PE(-1) / KAZ_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) / KAZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_OILC)  = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KAZ_OILC(-1) / KAZ_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0310546386687403 * LOG(KAZ_PE(-1) / KAZ_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KAZ_COALC(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1) + KAZ_OILC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)) / KAZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KAZ_EXR) = LOG(((KAZ_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.391738101908071*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((KAZ_INT - USA_INT) - (KAZ_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@INNOV KAZ_EXR  0.241346341472955

DLOG(KIR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(KIR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KIR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (KIR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (KIR_YER / KIR_YFT  - KIR_YER(-1) / KIR_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + KIR_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + KIR_GCARB / KIR_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (KIR_PREM - KIR_PREM(-1)) / 100

KIR_YED  = KIR_YED(-1) * KIR_HIC / KIR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_INT  = KIR_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_LTI  = KIR_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (KIR_INT - KIR_INT(-1))  + (KIR_PREM  - KIR_PREM(-1)) / 100

KIR_PREM  = KIR_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (KIR_GDNRATIO(-1)  - KIR_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(KIR_LNN)  = DLOG(KIR_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(KIR_LNN(-1))  - LOG(KIR_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(KIR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KIR_LNNF)  = DLOG(KIR_LNN)

KIR_FUELSH  = KIR_FUELSH(-1)

KIR_TAXR  = KIR_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KIR_GLNT(-1)  - KIR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KIR_YEN(-1) / ( ( KIR_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (KIR_YER(-2)  + KIR_GDI(-2)) * KIR_YED(-2) * (KIR_LNN(-1) / KIR_LNN(-2)  + KIR_TECHL(-1) - KIR_TECHL(-2) ) ) + KIR_REMIT(-1)  + KIR_EXPSP(-1) ) * KIR_SOLV

KIR_CTAXR  = KIR_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KIR_GLNT(-1)  - KIR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KIR_YEN(-1) / ( KIR_PROF(-1) ) * KIR_SOLV

(KIR_OGC)  = KIR_OGC(-1) * (KIR_YFT / KIR_YFT(-1) * KIR_YED / KIR_YED(-1))

KIR_USER  = (KIR_LTI  - KIR_INFT  + KIR_DEP * 100) / (1  - KIR_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (KIR_GCARB / KIR_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY KIR_XTN  = KIR_XTD$ * KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") * KIR_XTR

@IDENTITY KIR_YEN  = KIR_YER  * KIR_YED

@IDENTITY KIR_MTN  = KIR_MTD  * KIR_MTR

@IDENTITY KIR_XTN$  = KIR_XTN / KIR_EXR

@IDENTITY KIR_YEN$  = KIR_YEN / KIR_EXR

@IDENTITY KIR_MTN$  = KIR_MTN / KIR_EXR

@IDENTITY KIR_MTR$  = KIR_MTR$(-1) * KIR_MTR / KIR_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_XTR$  = KIR_XTR$(-1) * KIR_XTR / KIR_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_YER$  = KIR_YER$(-1) * KIR_YER / KIR_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_YFT$  = KIR_YFT$(-1) * KIR_YFT / KIR_YFT(-1)

KIR_POPT  = KIR_POPT(-1)  - KIR_LIVES

KIR_POPWA  = KIR_POPWA(-1) * KIR_POPT / KIR_POPT(-1)

KIR_SCR  = KIR_SCR(-1)  + ((KIR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KIR_YFT(-1) / KIR_YER(-1)  - KIR_YFT(-2) / KIR_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY KIR_ITR  = KIR_IGR  + KIR_IPR

@IDENTITY KIR_YER  = KIR_PCR  + KIR_GCR  + KIR_ITR  + KIR_SCR  + KIR_XTR  - KIR_MTR

@IDENTITY KIR_PROF  = (KIR_YEN - KIR_ITAX) * (1 - KIR_LABSH)

@IDENTITY KIR_GDI  = KIR_YER  - KIR_XTR  + KIR_MTR  + KIR_XTN  / ((KIR_YEN  - KIR_XTN  + KIR_MTN)  / (KIR_YER  - KIR_XTR  + KIR_MTR))  - KIR_MTN  / ((KIR_YEN  - KIR_XTN  + KIR_MTN)  / (KIR_YER  - KIR_XTR  + KIR_MTR))

@IDENTITY KIR_RPDI  = KIR_LABSH * 0.5 * (KIR_YER(-1)  + KIR_GDI(-1)) * KIR_YED(-1) / KIR_HIC(-1) * (KIR_LNN / KIR_LNN(-1)  + KIR_TECHL - KIR_TECHL(-1)) + KIR_REMIT / KIR_HIC  + KIR_EXPSP / KIR_HIC  - KIR_TAX / KIR_HIC

DLOG(KIR_YFT)  = (1 - KIR_ALPHA - KIR_LABSH) * DLOG(KIR_K(-1) / KIR_LFN(-1))  + (1 - KIR_ALPHA) * DLOG(KIR_LFN)  + KIR_LABSH * D(KIR_TECHL)  + KIR_ALPHA * (DLOG(KIR_EC)  + D(KIR_EFF) )  - ( KIR_CLIMLOSS / KIR_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (KIR_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY KIR_K  = KIR_K(-1) * (1 - KIR_DEP) + KIR_ITR

DLOG(KIR_MTD)  = (1  - KIR_OMS) * ( DLOG(KIR_CMUD)  + DLOG(KIR_EXR) )  + KIR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KIR_EXR) )

DLOG(KIR_XTD$)  = (1  - KIR_OXS) * DLOG(KIR_XTDNO$)  + KIR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

KIR_INFT  = 0.95 * KIR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

KIR_OXS  = KIR_OXS(-1)

KIR_OMS  = KIR_OMS(-1) * ((KIR_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * KIR_EXR(-1) / KIR_MTN(-1)) / (KIR_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * KIR_EXR(-2) / KIR_MTN(-2)))^0.25

KIR_CXS  = KIR_CXS(-1)

KIR_FINC  = KIR_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_CAN  = KIR_XTN / KIR_EXR  - KIR_MTN / KIR_EXR  + KIR_REMIT / KIR_EXR  + KIR_CANOTH

@IDENTITY KIR_CANRATIO  = KIR_CAN / KIR_YEN$ * 100

KIR_CANOTH  = KIR_CANOTH(-1)  + ((KIR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KIR_YEN$  / KIR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KIR_REVG / KIR_EXR  - KIR_REVG(-1) / KIR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(KIR_EFEX)  =  - LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.747586428E-06 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.719290987E-08 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  +
