0.0007591332966 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.205655206E-09 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.336169899E-10 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004552317063 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01988724486 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05099120345 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002744349895 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001419184846 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01402561269 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003221207955 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005504448521 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.946098987E-05 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003313032346 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009856012687 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006610044543 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01825193905 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04652246688 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002260370542 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

KIR_REMIT  = KIR_REMIT(-1) / KIR_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1670966373 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002391833155 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002030695417 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002534109617 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004344551446 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004822449085 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3195044539 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005481828745 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4799173062 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002427651886 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002319085424 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009710607544 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006074072328 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0155489098 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * KIR_EXR

KIR_GINT  = KIR_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (KIR_LTI  - KIR_LTI(-1))

KIR_GDN  = KIR_GDN(-1) * (KIR_GDFXSH  * (KIR_EXR  / KIR_EXR(-1))  + (1  - KIR_GDFXSH))  - KIR_GLN

@IDENTITY KIR_GDNRATIO  = KIR_GDN / KIR_YEN * 100

KIR_GDFXSH  = ( KIR_GDFXSH(-1) * (KIR_EXR / KIR_EXR(-1) )) / (KIR_GDFXSH(-1) * (KIR_EXR / KIR_EXR(-1))  + 1 - KIR_GDFXSH(-1) )

KIR_TOURSH  = KIR_TOURSH(-1)

KIR_LOCK  = 0

KIR_GCARBR  = KIR_GCARBR(-1)

KIR_GTRADER  = KIR_GTRADER(-1)

KIR_ITAXR  = KIR_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_REV  = KIR_TAX  + KIR_CTAX  + KIR_ITAX  + KIR_GTRADE  + KIR_REVG  + KIR_GCARB  + KIR_GCOM  + KIR_GOTH

@IDENTITY KIR_TAX  = KIR_TAXR * (KIR_LABSH * 0.5 * (KIR_YER(-1)  + KIR_GDI(-1)) * KIR_YED(-1) * (KIR_LNN / KIR_LNN(-1)  + KIR_TECHL - KIR_TECHL(-1)) + KIR_REMIT  + KIR_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY KIR_CTAX  = KIR_CTAXR * KIR_PROF

@IDENTITY KIR_ITAX  = KIR_ITAXR * (KIR_PCR * KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY KIR_GTRADE  = KIR_GTRADER * KIR_XTN

KIR_REVG  = KIR_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (KIR_YER$ / KIR_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - KIR_YER$(-1) / KIR_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * KIR_EXR / KIR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_GCARB  = KIR_GCARBR * KIR_CO2 * KIR_EXR / 1000

KIR_GCOM  = KIR_GCOM(-1) * ( KIR_OILC / (KIR_OILC + KIR_GASC + KIR_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + KIR_GASC / (KIR_OILC + KIR_GASC + KIR_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + KIR_COALC / (KIR_OILC + KIR_GASC + KIR_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

KIR_GOTH  = KIR_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_EXP  = KIR_EXPE  + KIR_EXPH  + KIR_EXPSP  + KIR_OGC  + KIR_OGI  + KIR_GIP

KIR_EXPE  = KIR_EXPE(-1) * (KIR_YFT / KIR_YFT(-1)) * (KIR_YED / KIR_YED(-1))

KIR_EXPH = KIR_EXPH(-1) * (KIR_YFT / KIR_YFT(-1)) * (KIR_YED / KIR_YED(-1))

KIR_EXPSP  = KIR_EXPSP(-1) * (KIR_YFT / KIR_YFT(-1)) * (KIR_YED / KIR_YED(-1)) * (KIR_POPT - KIR_LNN) / (KIR_POPT(-1) - KIR_LNN(-1))

DLOG(KIR_OGI)  = DLOG(KIR_YFT)  + DLOG(KIR_YED)

KIR_GCR  = KIR_GCR(-1)  + ( KIR_OGC / KIR_YED - KIR_OGC(-1) / KIR_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (KIR_EXPH ) / KIR_YED  - (KIR_EXPH(-1) ) / KIR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KIR_EXPE ) / KIR_YED  - (KIR_EXPE(-1) ) / KIR_YED(-1) )

KIR_IGR  = KIR_IGR(-1) + (KIR_OGI / KIR_YED - KIR_OGI(-1) / KIR_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (KIR_EXPH ) / KIR_YED  - (KIR_EXPH(-1) ) / KIR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KIR_EXPE ) / KIR_YED  - (KIR_EXPE(-1) ) / KIR_YED(-1) )

KIR_GIP  = ( KIR_GIP(-1)  + ( KIR_GDN(-1) - KIR_GDN(-2) ) * KIR_GINT(-1) / 100  + KIR_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( KIR_GINT(-1) / 100 - KIR_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (KIR_GDFXSH * (KIR_EXR / KIR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KIR_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY KIR_GLN  = KIR_REV  - KIR_EXP

@IDENTITY KIR_GLNRATIO  = KIR_GLN / KIR_YEN * 100

KIR_GLNT  = KIR_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

KIR_TFP  = KIR_LABSH * (KIR_TECHL  - KIR_TECHL(-1))

KIR_LABSH  = KIR_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY KIR_LFN  = KIR_LRX * KIR_POPWA

KIR_LRX  = KIR_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(KIR_YER(-1) / KIR_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY KIR_URX  = (1 - KIR_LNN / KIR_LFN) * 100

KIR_URXF  = KIR_URXF(-1) * KIR_URX / KIR_URX(-1) * KIR_LNN / KIR_LNNF / (KIR_LNN(-1) / KIR_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(KIR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KIR_PCR  / KIR_POPT)

KIR_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(KIR_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

KIR_HEAD19  = KIR_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KIR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI^2)  , KIR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KIR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KIR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

KIR_HEAD55  = KIR_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KIR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI^2)  , KIR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KIR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KIR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(KIR_XTR)  = DLOG(KIR_WDR)  + (1  - KIR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(KIR_XTDNO$  / KIR_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * KIR_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(KIR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (KIR_EXPH(-1) / KIR_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (KIR_EXPH(-1) / KIR_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(KIR_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(KIR_PM25)

KIR_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( KIR_EXPSP / KIR_YEN )

DLOG(KIR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - KIR_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (KIR_FINC - KIR_FINC(-1))

DLOG(KIR_PCR)  = 0.000773704835931013  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(KIR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KIR_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (KIR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KIR_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(KIR_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(KIR_HIC)  - KIR_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * KIR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * KIR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KIR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KIR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KIR_IPR)  =  - 0.11839869936907  - 0.1 * (LOG(KIR_IPR(-1)  / KIR_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * KIR_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * KIR_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(KIR_PCR  + KIR_GCR(-1) + KIR_IGR(-1) + KIR_XTN  / KIR_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(KIR_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (KIR_USER - KIR_USER(-1))  - (0 * KIR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KIR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KIR_FUELSH - KIR_TOURSH)) * KIR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * KIR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KIR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KIR_FUELSH - KIR_TOURSH)) * KIR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KIR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KIR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KIR_MTR)  =  - 0.116766565412622  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(KIR_MTR(-1))  - LOG(KIR_PCR(-1) + KIR_ITR(-1) + KIR_GCR(-1) + KIR_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(KIR_YFT(-1) / KIR_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(KIR_CMUD(-1) * KIR_EXR(-1)  / KIR_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * KIR_OMS * LOG(KIR_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.0929257991201662  * DLOG(KIR_XTR)  + 0.393632668276858  * DLOG(KIR_PCR)  + 0.156770822215016  * DLOG(KIR_IPR)  + 0.171318239272567  * DLOG(KIR_GCR + KIR_IGR)

KIR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * KIR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * KIR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * KIR_OILC

KIR_POIL  = KIR_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( KIR_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - KIR_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

KIR_PG  = KIR_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( KIR_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - KIR_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

KIR_PC  = KIR_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( KIR_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - KIR_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(KIR_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

KIR_PE  = KIR_PE(-1) * ( KIR_OILC(-1) / (KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) * KIR_POIL / KIR_POIL(-1)  + KIR_GASC(-1) / (KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) * KIR_PG / KIR_PG(-1)  + KIR_COALC(-1) / (KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) * KIR_PC / KIR_PC(-1)  + KIR_RC(-1) / (KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) * KIR_PR / KIR_PR(-1) )

D(KIR_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(KIR_PM25)  = 0.2 * (KIR_COALC(-1) / KIR_EC(-1) - KIR_COALC(-2) / KIR_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (KIR_COALC(-2) / KIR_EC(-2) - KIR_COALC(-3) / KIR_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (KIR_OILC(-1) / KIR_EC(-1) - KIR_OILC(-2) / KIR_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (KIR_OILC(-2) / KIR_EC(-2) - KIR_OILC(-3) / KIR_EC(-3))

DLOG(KIR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(KIR_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(KIR_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(KIR_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KIR_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KIR_PE * KIR_EXR / KIR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KIR_PE(-1) * KIR_EXR(-1) / KIR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KIR_PE(-2) * KIR_EXR(-2) / KIR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KIR_PE(-3) * KIR_EXR(-3) / KIR_HIC(-3))  - (KIR_EFF - KIR_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(KIR_COALC)  = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KIR_COALC(-1) / KIR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(KIR_PE(-1) / KIR_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) / KIR_EC(-1))

DLOG(KIR_GASC)  = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KIR_GASC(-1) / KIR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(KIR_PE(-1) / KIR_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) / KIR_EC(-1))

DLOG(KIR_RC)  = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KIR_RC(-1) / KIR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0423805821732056 * LOG(KIR_PE(-1) / KIR_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) / KIR_EC(-1))

DLOG(KIR_OILC)  = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KIR_OILC(-1) / KIR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0423805821732056 * LOG(KIR_PE(-1) / KIR_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KIR_COALC(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1) + KIR_OILC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)) / KIR_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY KIR_EXR  = AUS_EXR

DLOG(KGZ_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(KGZ_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KGZ_MTD)  + 0.4 * (KGZ_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (KGZ_YER / KGZ_YFT  - KGZ_YER(-1) / KGZ_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + KGZ_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + KGZ_GCARB / KGZ_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (KGZ_PREM - KGZ_PREM(-1)) / 100

KGZ_YED  = KGZ_YED(-1) * KGZ_HIC / KGZ_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_INT  = KGZ_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_LTI  = KGZ_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (KGZ_INT - KGZ_INT(-1))  + (KGZ_PREM  - KGZ_PREM(-1)) / 100

KGZ_PREM  = KGZ_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (KGZ_GDNRATIO(-1)  - KGZ_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(KGZ_LNN)  = DLOG(KGZ_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(KGZ_LNN(-1))  - LOG(KGZ_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(KGZ_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KGZ_LNNF)  = DLOG(KGZ_LNN)

KGZ_FUELSH  = KGZ_FUELSH(-1)

KGZ_TAXR  = KGZ_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KGZ_GLNT(-1)  - KGZ_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KGZ_YEN(-1) / ( ( KGZ_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (KGZ_YER(-2)  + KGZ_GDI(-2)) * KGZ_YED(-2) * (KGZ_LNN(-1) / KGZ_LNN(-2)  + KGZ_TECHL(-1) - KGZ_TECHL(-2) ) ) + KGZ_REMIT(-1)  + KGZ_EXPSP(-1) ) * KGZ_SOLV

KGZ_CTAXR  = KGZ_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KGZ_GLNT(-1)  - KGZ_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KGZ_YEN(-1) / ( KGZ_PROF(-1) ) * KGZ_SOLV

(KGZ_OGC)  = KGZ_OGC(-1) * (KGZ_YFT / KGZ_YFT(-1) * KGZ_YED / KGZ_YED(-1))

KGZ_USER  = (KGZ_LTI  - KGZ_INFT  + KGZ_DEP * 100) / (1  - KGZ_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (KGZ_GCARB / KGZ_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY KGZ_XTN  = KGZ_XTD$ * KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") * KGZ_XTR

@IDENTITY KGZ_YEN  = KGZ_YER  * KGZ_YED

@IDENTITY KGZ_MTN  = KGZ_MTD  * KGZ_MTR

@IDENTITY KGZ_XTN$  = KGZ_XTN / KGZ_EXR

@IDENTITY KGZ_YEN$  = KGZ_YEN / KGZ_EXR

@IDENTITY KGZ_MTN$  = KGZ_MTN / KGZ_EXR

@IDENTITY KGZ_MTR$  = KGZ_MTR$(-1) * KGZ_MTR / KGZ_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_XTR$  = KGZ_XTR$(-1) * KGZ_XTR / KGZ_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_YER$  = KGZ_YER$(-1) * KGZ_YER / KGZ_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_YFT$  = KGZ_YFT$(-1) * KGZ_YFT / KGZ_YFT(-1)

KGZ_POPT  = KGZ_POPT(-1)  - KGZ_LIVES

KGZ_POPWA  = KGZ_POPWA(-1) * KGZ_POPT / KGZ_POPT(-1)

KGZ_SCR  = KGZ_SCR(-1)  + ((KGZ_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KGZ_YFT(-1) / KGZ_YER(-1)  - KGZ_YFT(-2) / KGZ_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY KGZ_ITR  = KGZ_IGR  + KGZ_IPR

@IDENTITY KGZ_YER  = KGZ_PCR  + KGZ_GCR  + KGZ_ITR  + KGZ_SCR  + KGZ_XTR  - KGZ_MTR

@IDENTITY KGZ_PROF  = (KGZ_YEN - KGZ_ITAX) * (1 - KGZ_LABSH)

@IDENTITY KGZ_GDI  = KGZ_YER  - KGZ_XTR  + KGZ_MTR  + KGZ_XTN  / ((KGZ_YEN  - KGZ_XTN  + KGZ_MTN)  / (KGZ_YER  - KGZ_XTR  + KGZ_MTR))  - KGZ_MTN  / ((KGZ_YEN  - KGZ_XTN  + KGZ_MTN)  / (KGZ_YER  - KGZ_XTR  + KGZ_MTR))

@IDENTITY KGZ_RPDI  = KGZ_LABSH * 0.5 * (KGZ_YER(-1)  + KGZ_GDI(-1)) * KGZ_YED(-1) / KGZ_HIC(-1) * (KGZ_LNN / KGZ_LNN(-1)  + KGZ_TECHL - KGZ_TECHL(-1)) + KGZ_REMIT / KGZ_HIC  + KGZ_EXPSP / KGZ_HIC  - KGZ_TAX / KGZ_HIC

DLOG(KGZ_YFT)  = (1 - KGZ_ALPHA - KGZ_LABSH) * DLOG(KGZ_K(-1) / KGZ_LFN(-1))  + (1 - KGZ_ALPHA) * DLOG(KGZ_LFN)  + KGZ_LABSH * D(KGZ_TECHL)  + KGZ_ALPHA * (DLOG(KGZ_EC)  + D(KGZ_EFF) )  - ( KGZ_CLIMLOSS / KGZ_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (KGZ_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY KGZ_K  = KGZ_K(-1) * (1 - KGZ_DEP) + KGZ_ITR

DLOG(KGZ_MTD)  = (1  - KGZ_OMS) * ( DLOG(KGZ_CMUD)  + DLOG(KGZ_EXR) )  + KGZ_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KGZ_EXR) )

DLOG(KGZ_XTD$)  = (1  - KGZ_OXS) * DLOG(KGZ_XTDNO$)  + KGZ_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

KGZ_INFT  = 0.95 * KGZ_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

KGZ_OXS  = KGZ_OXS(-1)

KGZ_OMS  = KGZ_OMS(-1) * ((KGZ_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * KGZ_EXR(-1) / KGZ_MTN(-1)) / (KGZ_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * KGZ_EXR(-2) / KGZ_MTN(-2)))^0.25

KGZ_CXS  = KGZ_CXS(-1)

KGZ_FINC  = KGZ_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_CAN  = KGZ_XTN / KGZ_EXR  - KGZ_MTN / KGZ_EXR  + KGZ_REMIT / KGZ_EXR  + KGZ_CANOTH

@IDENTITY KGZ_CANRATIO  = KGZ_CAN / KGZ_YEN$ * 100

KGZ_CANOTH  = KGZ_CANOTH(-1)  + ((KGZ_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KGZ_YEN$  / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KGZ_REVG / KGZ_EXR  - KGZ_REVG(-1) / KGZ_EXR(-1)

* MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 9.985946588E-05 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.7659232424 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01009520069 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002770825767 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005447082159 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006302587513 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01493952176 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 6.615543324E-05 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05115446995 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002480828081 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004132027574 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * KGZ_EXR

KGZ_GINT  = KGZ_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (KGZ_LTI  - KGZ_LTI(-1))

KGZ_GDN  = KGZ_GDN(-1) * (KGZ_GDFXSH  * (KGZ_EXR  / KGZ_EXR(-1))  + (1  - KGZ_GDFXSH))  - KGZ_GLN

@IDENTITY KGZ_GDNRATIO  = KGZ_GDN / KGZ_YEN * 100

KGZ_GDFXSH  = ( KGZ_GDFXSH(-1) * (KGZ_EXR / KGZ_EXR(-1) )) / (KGZ_GDFXSH(-1) * (KGZ_EXR / KGZ_EXR(-1))  + 1 - KGZ_GDFXSH(-1) )

KGZ_TOURSH  = KGZ_TOURSH(-1)

KGZ_LOCK  = 0

KGZ_GCARBR  = KGZ_GCARBR(-1)

KGZ_GTRADER  = KGZ_GTRADER(-1)

KGZ_ITAXR  = KGZ_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_REV  = KGZ_TAX  + KGZ_CTAX  + KGZ_ITAX  + KGZ_GTRADE  + KGZ_REVG  + KGZ_GCARB  + KGZ_GCOM  + KGZ_GOTH

@IDENTITY KGZ_TAX  = KGZ_TAXR * (KGZ_LABSH * 0.5 * (KGZ_YER(-1)  + KGZ_GDI(-1)) * KGZ_YED(-1) * (KGZ_LNN / KGZ_LNN(-1)  + KGZ_TECHL - KGZ_TECHL(-1)) + KGZ_REMIT  + KGZ_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY KGZ_CTAX  = KGZ_CTAXR * KGZ_PROF

@IDENTITY KGZ_ITAX  = KGZ_ITAXR * (KGZ_PCR * KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY KGZ_GTRADE  = KGZ_GTRADER * KGZ_XTN

KGZ_REVG  = KGZ_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (KGZ_YER$ / KGZ_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - KGZ_YER$(-1) / KGZ_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * KGZ_EXR / KGZ_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_GCARB  = KGZ_GCARBR * KGZ_CO2 * KGZ_EXR / 1000

KGZ_GCOM  = KGZ_GCOM(-1) * ( KGZ_OILC / (KGZ_OILC + KGZ_GASC + KGZ_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + KGZ_GASC / (KGZ_OILC + KGZ_GASC + KGZ_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + KGZ_COALC / (KGZ_OILC + KGZ_GASC + KGZ_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

KGZ_GOTH  = KGZ_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_EXP  = KGZ_EXPE  + KGZ_EXPH  + KGZ_EXPSP  + KGZ_OGC  + KGZ_OGI  + KGZ_GIP

KGZ_EXPE  = KGZ_EXPE(-1) * (KGZ_YFT / KGZ_YFT(-1)) * (KGZ_YED / KGZ_YED(-1))

KGZ_EXPH = KGZ_EXPH(-1) * (KGZ_YFT / KGZ_YFT(-1)) * (KGZ_YED / KGZ_YED(-1))

KGZ_EXPSP  = KGZ_EXPSP(-1) * (KGZ_YFT / KGZ_YFT(-1)) * (KGZ_YED / KGZ_YED(-1)) * (KGZ_POPT - KGZ_LNN) / (KGZ_POPT(-1) - KGZ_LNN(-1))

DLOG(KGZ_OGI)  = DLOG(KGZ_YFT)  + DLOG(KGZ_YED)

KGZ_GCR  = KGZ_GCR(-1)  + ( KGZ_OGC / KGZ_YED - KGZ_OGC(-1) / KGZ_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (KGZ_EXPH ) / KGZ_YED  - (KGZ_EXPH(-1) ) / KGZ_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KGZ_EXPE ) / KGZ_YED  - (KGZ_EXPE(-1) ) / KGZ_YED(-1) )

KGZ_IGR  = KGZ_IGR(-1) + (KGZ_OGI / KGZ_YED - KGZ_OGI(-1) / KGZ_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (KGZ_EXPH ) / KGZ_YED  - (KGZ_EXPH(-1) ) / KGZ_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KGZ_EXPE ) / KGZ_YED  - (KGZ_EXPE(-1) ) / KGZ_YED(-1) )

KGZ_GIP  = ( KGZ_GIP(-1)  + ( KGZ_GDN(-1) - KGZ_GDN(-2) ) * KGZ_GINT(-1) / 100  + KGZ_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( KGZ_GINT(-1) / 100 - KGZ_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (KGZ_GDFXSH * (KGZ_EXR / KGZ_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KGZ_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY KGZ_GLN  = KGZ_REV  - KGZ_EXP

@IDENTITY KGZ_GLNRATIO  = KGZ_GLN / KGZ_YEN * 100

KGZ_GLNT  = KGZ_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

KGZ_TFP  = KGZ_LABSH * (KGZ_TECHL  - KGZ_TECHL(-1))

KGZ_LABSH  = KGZ_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY KGZ_LFN  = KGZ_LRX * KGZ_POPWA

KGZ_LRX  = KGZ_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(KGZ_YER(-1) / KGZ_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY KGZ_URX  = (1 - KGZ_LNN / KGZ_LFN) * 100

KGZ_URXF  = KGZ_URXF(-1) * KGZ_URX / KGZ_URX(-1) * KGZ_LNN / KGZ_LNNF / (KGZ_LNN(-1) / KGZ_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(KGZ_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KGZ_PCR  / KGZ_POPT)

KGZ_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(KGZ_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

KGZ_HEAD19  = KGZ_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI^2)  , KGZ_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KGZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

KGZ_HEAD55  = KGZ_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI^2)  , KGZ_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KGZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(KGZ_XTR)  = DLOG(KGZ_WDR)  + (1  - KGZ_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(KGZ_XTDNO$  / KGZ_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * KGZ_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(KGZ_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (KGZ_EXPH(-1) / KGZ_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (KGZ_EXPH(-1) / KGZ_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(KGZ_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(KGZ_PM25)

KGZ_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( KGZ_EXPSP / KGZ_YEN )

DLOG(KGZ_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - KGZ_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (KGZ_FINC - KGZ_FINC(-1))

DLOG(KGZ_PCR)  =  - 0.00117109066888045  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(KGZ_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KGZ_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (KGZ_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(KGZ_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.7)  * DLOG(KGZ_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(KGZ_HIC)  - KGZ_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * KGZ_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * KGZ_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KGZ_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KGZ_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KGZ_IPR)  =  - 0.0761686083646704  - 0.1 * (LOG(KGZ_IPR(-1)  / KGZ_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * KGZ_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * KGZ_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(KGZ_PCR  + KGZ_GCR(-1) + KGZ_IGR(-1) + KGZ_XTN  / KGZ_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(KGZ_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (KGZ_USER - KGZ_USER(-1))  - (0 * KGZ_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KGZ_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KGZ_FUELSH - KGZ_TOURSH)) * KGZ_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * KGZ_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KGZ_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KGZ_FUELSH - KGZ_TOURSH)) * KGZ_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KGZ_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KGZ_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KGZ_MTR)  =  - 0.0766531517172287  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(KGZ_MTR(-1))  - LOG(KGZ_PCR(-1) + KGZ_ITR(-1) + KGZ_GCR(-1) + KGZ_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(KGZ_YFT(-1) / KGZ_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(KGZ_CMUD(-1) * KGZ_EXR(-1)  / KGZ_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * KGZ_OMS * LOG(KGZ_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.263252703233848  * DLOG(KGZ_XTR)  + 0.461324747490342  * DLOG(KGZ_PCR)  + 0.153680428336707  * DLOG(KGZ_IPR)  + 0.125288512080703  * DLOG(KGZ_GCR + KGZ_IGR)

KGZ_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * KGZ_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * KGZ_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * KGZ_OILC

KGZ_POIL  = KGZ_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( KGZ_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - KGZ_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

KGZ_PG  = KGZ_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( KGZ_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - KGZ_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

KGZ_PC  = KGZ_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( KGZ_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - KGZ_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(KGZ_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

KGZ_PE  = KGZ_PE(-1) * ( KGZ_OILC(-1) / (KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) * KGZ_POIL / KGZ_POIL(-1)  + KGZ_GASC(-1) / (KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) * KGZ_PG / KGZ_PG(-1)  + KGZ_COALC(-1) / (KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) * KGZ_PC / KGZ_PC(-1)  + KGZ_RC(-1) / (KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) * KGZ_PR / KGZ_PR(-1) )

D(KGZ_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(KGZ_PM25)  = 0.2 * (KGZ_COALC(-1) / KGZ_EC(-1) - KGZ_COALC(-2) / KGZ_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (KGZ_COALC(-2) / KGZ_EC(-2) - KGZ_COALC(-3) / KGZ_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (KGZ_OILC(-1) / KGZ_EC(-1) - KGZ_OILC(-2) / KGZ_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (KGZ_OILC(-2) / KGZ_EC(-2) - KGZ_OILC(-3) / KGZ_EC(-3))

DLOG(KGZ_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(KGZ_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(KGZ_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(KGZ_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KGZ_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KGZ_PE * KGZ_EXR / KGZ_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KGZ_PE(-1) * KGZ_EXR(-1) / KGZ_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KGZ_PE(-2) * KGZ_EXR(-2) / KGZ_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KGZ_PE(-3) * KGZ_EXR(-3) / KGZ_HIC(-3))  - (KGZ_EFF - KGZ_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(KGZ_COALC)  = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KGZ_COALC(-1) / KGZ_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.232195610258277 * LOG(KGZ_PE(-1) / KGZ_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) / KGZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KGZ_GASC)  = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KGZ_GASC(-1) / KGZ_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.0651670183541028 * LOG(KGZ_PE(-1) / KGZ_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) / KGZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KGZ_RC)  = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KGZ_RC(-1) / KGZ_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.232195610258277 * LOG(KGZ_PE(-1) / KGZ_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) / KGZ_EC(-1))

DLOG(KGZ_OILC)  = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KGZ_OILC(-1) / KGZ_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.232195610258277 * LOG(KGZ_PE(-1) / KGZ_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KGZ_COALC(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1) + KGZ_OILC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)) / KGZ_EC(-1))

KGZ_EXR  = KGZ_EXR(-1) * ( (KGZ_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(LAO_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(LAO_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(LAO_MTD)  + 0.4 * (LAO_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (LAO_YER / LAO_YFT  - LAO_YER(-1) / LAO_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + LAO_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + LAO_GCARB / LAO_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (LAO_PREM - LAO_PREM(-1)) / 100

LAO_YED  = LAO_YED(-1) * LAO_HIC / LAO_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_INT  = LAO_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_LTI  = LAO_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (LAO_INT - LAO_INT(-1))  + (LAO_PREM  - LAO_PREM(-1)) / 100

LAO_PREM  = LAO_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (LAO_GDNRATIO(-1)  - LAO_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(LAO_LNN)  = DLOG(LAO_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(LAO_LNN(-1))  - LOG(LAO_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(LAO_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(LAO_LNNF)  = DLOG(LAO_LNN)

LAO_FUELSH  = LAO_FUELSH(-1)

LAO_TAXR  = LAO_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( LAO_GLNT(-1)  - LAO_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * LAO_YEN(-1) / ( ( LAO_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (LAO_YER(-2)  + LAO_GDI(-2)) * LAO_YED(-2) * (LAO_LNN(-1) / LAO_LNN(-2)  + LAO_TECHL(-1) - LAO_TECHL(-2) ) ) + LAO_REMIT(-1)  + LAO_EXPSP(-1) ) * LAO_SOLV

LAO_CTAXR  = LAO_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( LAO_GLNT(-1)  - LAO_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * LAO_YEN(-1) / ( LAO_PROF(-1) ) * LAO_SOLV

(LAO_OGC)  = LAO_OGC(-1) * (LAO_YFT / LAO_YFT(-1) * LAO_YED / LAO_YED(-1))

LAO_USER  = (LAO_LTI  - LAO_INFT  + LAO_DEP * 100) / (1  - LAO_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (LAO_GCARB / LAO_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY LAO_XTN  = LAO_XTD$ * LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") * LAO_XTR

@IDENTITY LAO_YEN  = LAO_YER  * LAO_YED

@IDENTITY LAO_MTN  = LAO_MTD  * LAO_MTR

@IDENTITY LAO_XTN$  = LAO_XTN / LAO_EXR

@IDENTITY LAO_YEN$  = LAO_YEN / LAO_EXR

@IDENTITY LAO_MTN$  = LAO_MTN / LAO_EXR

@IDENTITY LAO_MTR$  = LAO_MTR$(-1) * LAO_MTR / LAO_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_XTR$  = LAO_XTR$(-1) * LAO_XTR / LAO_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_YER$  = LAO_YER$(-1) * LAO_YER / LAO_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_YFT$  = LAO_YFT$(-1) * LAO_YFT / LAO_YFT(-1)

LAO_POPT  = LAO_POPT(-1)  - LAO_LIVES

LAO_POPWA  = LAO_POPWA(-1) * LAO_POPT / LAO_POPT(-1)

LAO_SCR  = LAO_SCR(-1)  + ((LAO_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (LAO_YFT(-1) / LAO_YER(-1)  - LAO_YFT(-2) / LAO_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY LAO_ITR  = LAO_IGR  + LAO_IPR

@IDENTITY LAO_YER  = LAO_PCR  + LAO_GCR  + LAO_ITR  + LAO_SCR  + LAO_XTR  - LAO_MTR

@IDENTITY LAO_PROF  = (LAO_YEN - LAO_ITAX) * (1 - LAO_LABSH)

@IDENTITY LAO_GDI  = LAO_YER  - LAO_XTR  + LAO_MTR  + LAO_XTN  / ((LAO_YEN  - LAO_XTN  + LAO_MTN)  / (LAO_YER  - LAO_XTR  + LAO_MTR))  - LAO_MTN  / ((LAO_YEN  - LAO_XTN  + LAO_MTN)  / (LAO_YER  - LAO_XTR  + LAO_MTR))

@IDENTITY LAO_RPDI  = LAO_LABSH * 0.5 * (LAO_YER(-1)  + LAO_GDI(-1)) * LAO_YED(-1) / LAO_HIC(-1) * (LAO_LNN / LAO_LNN(-1)  + LAO_TECHL - LAO_TECHL(-1)) + LAO_REMIT / LAO_HIC  + LAO_EXPSP / LAO_HIC  - LAO_TAX / LAO_HIC

DLOG(LAO_YFT)  = (1 - LAO_ALPHA - LAO_LABSH) * DLOG(LAO_K(-1) / LAO_LFN(-1))  + (1 - LAO_ALPHA) * DLOG(LAO_LFN)  + LAO_LABSH * D(LAO_TECHL)  + LAO_ALPHA * (DLOG(LAO_EC)  + D(LAO_EFF) )  - ( LAO_CLIMLOSS / LAO_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (LAO_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY LAO_K  = LAO_K(-1) * (1 - LAO_DEP) + LAO_ITR

DLOG(LAO_MTD)  = (1  - LAO_OMS) * ( DLOG(LAO_CMUD)  + DLOG(LAO_EXR) )  + LAO_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(LAO_EXR) )

DLOG(LAO_XTD$)  = (1  - LAO_OXS) * DLOG(LAO_XTDNO$)  + LAO_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

LAO_INFT  = 0.95 * LAO_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

LAO_OXS  = LAO_OXS(-1)

LAO_OMS  = LAO_OMS(-1) * ((LAO_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * LAO_EXR(-1) / LAO_MTN(-1)) / (LAO_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * LAO_EXR(-2) / LAO_MTN(-2)))^0.25

LAO_CXS  = LAO_CXS(-1)

LAO_FINC  = LAO_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_CAN  = LAO_XTN / LAO_EXR  - LAO_MTN / LAO_EXR  + LAO_REMIT / LAO_EXR  + LAO_CANOTH

@IDENTITY LAO_CANRATIO  = LAO_CAN / LAO_YEN$ * 100
