LAO_REVG  = LAO_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (LAO_YER$ / LAO_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - LAO_YER$(-1) / LAO_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * LAO_EXR / LAO_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_GCARB  = LAO_GCARBR * LAO_CO2 * LAO_EXR / 1000

LAO_GCOM  = LAO_GCOM(-1) * ( LAO_OILC / (LAO_OILC + LAO_GASC + LAO_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + LAO_GASC / (LAO_OILC + LAO_GASC + LAO_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + LAO_COALC / (LAO_OILC + LAO_GASC + LAO_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

LAO_GOTH  = LAO_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_EXP  = LAO_EXPE  + LAO_EXPH  + LAO_EXPSP  + LAO_OGC  + LAO_OGI  + LAO_GIP

LAO_EXPE  = LAO_EXPE(-1) * (LAO_YFT / LAO_YFT(-1)) * (LAO_YED / LAO_YED(-1))

LAO_EXPH = LAO_EXPH(-1) * (LAO_YFT / LAO_YFT(-1)) * (LAO_YED / LAO_YED(-1))

LAO_EXPSP  = LAO_EXPSP(-1) * (LAO_YFT / LAO_YFT(-1)) * (LAO_YED / LAO_YED(-1)) * (LAO_POPT - LAO_LNN) / (LAO_POPT(-1) - LAO_LNN(-1))

DLOG(LAO_OGI)  = DLOG(LAO_YFT)  + DLOG(LAO_YED)

LAO_GCR  = LAO_GCR(-1)  + ( LAO_OGC / LAO_YED - LAO_OGC(-1) / LAO_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (LAO_EXPH ) / LAO_YED  - (LAO_EXPH(-1) ) / LAO_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (LAO_EXPE ) / LAO_YED  - (LAO_EXPE(-1) ) / LAO_YED(-1) )

LAO_IGR  = LAO_IGR(-1) + (LAO_OGI / LAO_YED - LAO_OGI(-1) / LAO_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (LAO_EXPH ) / LAO_YED  - (LAO_EXPH(-1) ) / LAO_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (LAO_EXPE ) / LAO_YED  - (LAO_EXPE(-1) ) / LAO_YED(-1) )

LAO_GIP  = ( LAO_GIP(-1)  + ( LAO_GDN(-1) - LAO_GDN(-2) ) * LAO_GINT(-1) / 100  + LAO_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( LAO_GINT(-1) / 100 - LAO_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (LAO_GDFXSH * (LAO_EXR / LAO_EXR(-1))  + (1 - LAO_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY LAO_GLN  = LAO_REV  - LAO_EXP

@IDENTITY LAO_GLNRATIO  = LAO_GLN / LAO_YEN * 100

LAO_GLNT  = LAO_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

LAO_TFP  = LAO_LABSH * (LAO_TECHL  - LAO_TECHL(-1))

LAO_LABSH  = LAO_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY LAO_LFN  = LAO_LRX * LAO_POPWA

LAO_LRX  = LAO_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(LAO_YER(-1) / LAO_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY LAO_URX  = (1 - LAO_LNN / LAO_LFN) * 100

LAO_URXF  = LAO_URXF(-1) * LAO_URX / LAO_URX(-1) * LAO_LNN / LAO_LNNF / (LAO_LNN(-1) / LAO_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(LAO_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(LAO_PCR  / LAO_POPT)

LAO_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(LAO_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

LAO_HEAD19  = LAO_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LAO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI^2)  , LAO_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LAO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LAO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

LAO_HEAD55  = LAO_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LAO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI^2)  , LAO_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LAO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LAO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(LAO_XTR)  = DLOG(LAO_WDR)  + (1  - LAO_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(LAO_XTDNO$  / LAO_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * LAO_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(LAO_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (LAO_EXPH(-1) / LAO_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (LAO_EXPH(-1) / LAO_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(LAO_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(LAO_PM25)

LAO_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( LAO_EXPSP / LAO_YEN )

DLOG(LAO_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - LAO_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (LAO_FINC - LAO_FINC(-1))

DLOG(LAO_PCR)  = 0.042349671314828  +  - 0.120893439168605 * (LOG(LAO_PCR(-1))  - LOG(LAO_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (LAO_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.410188216224751  * DLOG(LAO_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.410188216224751)  * DLOG(LAO_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(LAO_HIC)  - LAO_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * LAO_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * LAO_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(LAO_YFT(-1))  - LOG(LAO_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(LAO_IPR)  =  - 0.11674499689721  - 0.1 * (LOG(LAO_IPR(-1)  / LAO_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * LAO_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * LAO_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(LAO_PCR  + LAO_GCR(-1) + LAO_IGR(-1) + LAO_XTN  / LAO_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(LAO_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (LAO_USER - LAO_USER(-1))  - (0 * LAO_FUELSH  + 0.26 * LAO_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - LAO_FUELSH - LAO_TOURSH)) * LAO_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * LAO_FUELSH  + 0.26 * LAO_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - LAO_FUELSH - LAO_TOURSH)) * LAO_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(LAO_YFT(-1))  - LOG(LAO_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(LAO_MTR)  =  - 0.0854829172419966  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(LAO_MTR(-1))  - LOG(LAO_PCR(-1) + LAO_ITR(-1) + LAO_GCR(-1) + LAO_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(LAO_YFT(-1) / LAO_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(LAO_CMUD(-1) * LAO_EXR(-1)  / LAO_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * LAO_OMS * LOG(LAO_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.419649961403359  * DLOG(LAO_XTR)  + 0.552345063071986  * DLOG(LAO_PCR)  + 0.0842284028698427  * DLOG(LAO_IPR)  + 0.15840952466155  * DLOG(LAO_GCR + LAO_IGR)

LAO_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * LAO_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * LAO_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * LAO_OILC

LAO_POIL  = LAO_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( LAO_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - LAO_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

LAO_PG  = LAO_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( LAO_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - LAO_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

LAO_PC  = LAO_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( LAO_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - LAO_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(LAO_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

LAO_PE  = LAO_PE(-1) * ( LAO_OILC(-1) / (LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) * LAO_POIL / LAO_POIL(-1)  + LAO_GASC(-1) / (LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) * LAO_PG / LAO_PG(-1)  + LAO_COALC(-1) / (LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) * LAO_PC / LAO_PC(-1)  + LAO_RC(-1) / (LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) * LAO_PR / LAO_PR(-1) )

D(LAO_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(LAO_PM25)  = 0.2 * (LAO_COALC(-1) / LAO_EC(-1) - LAO_COALC(-2) / LAO_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (LAO_COALC(-2) / LAO_EC(-2) - LAO_COALC(-3) / LAO_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (LAO_OILC(-1) / LAO_EC(-1) - LAO_OILC(-2) / LAO_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (LAO_OILC(-2) / LAO_EC(-2) - LAO_OILC(-3) / LAO_EC(-3))

DLOG(LAO_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(LAO_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(LAO_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(LAO_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(LAO_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LAO_PE * LAO_EXR / LAO_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LAO_PE(-1) * LAO_EXR(-1) / LAO_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LAO_PE(-2) * LAO_EXR(-2) / LAO_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LAO_PE(-3) * LAO_EXR(-3) / LAO_HIC(-3))  - (LAO_EFF - LAO_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(LAO_COALC)  = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(LAO_COALC(-1) / LAO_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.590937696106446 * LOG(LAO_PE(-1) / LAO_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) / LAO_EC(-1))

DLOG(LAO_GASC)  = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(LAO_GASC(-1) / LAO_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(LAO_PE(-1) / LAO_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) / LAO_EC(-1))

DLOG(LAO_RC)  = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( LAO_RC(-1) / LAO_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.590937696106446 * LOG(LAO_PE(-1) / LAO_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) / LAO_EC(-1))

DLOG(LAO_OILC)  = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( LAO_OILC(-1) / LAO_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.590937696106446 * LOG(LAO_PE(-1) / LAO_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LAO_COALC(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1) + LAO_OILC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)) / LAO_EC(-1))

LAO_EXR  = LAO_EXR(-1) * ( (LAO_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(MAC_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(MAC_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MAC_MTD)  + 0.4 * (MAC_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (MAC_YER / MAC_YFT  - MAC_YER(-1) / MAC_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + MAC_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + MAC_GCARB / MAC_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (MAC_PREM - MAC_PREM(-1)) / 100

MAC_YED  = MAC_YED(-1) * MAC_HIC / MAC_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_INT  = MAC_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_LTI  = MAC_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (MAC_INT - MAC_INT(-1))  + (MAC_PREM  - MAC_PREM(-1)) / 100

MAC_PREM  = MAC_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (MAC_GDNRATIO(-1)  - MAC_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(MAC_LNN)  = DLOG(MAC_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(MAC_LNN(-1))  - LOG(MAC_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(MAC_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MAC_LNNF)  = DLOG(MAC_LNN)

MAC_FUELSH  = MAC_FUELSH(-1)

MAC_ITAXR  = MAC_ITAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MAC_GLNT(-1)  - MAC_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MAC_YEN(-1) / ( MAC_PCR  * MAC_HIC  / @ELEM(MAC_HIC  , "2015" ) ) * MAC_SOLV

MAC_CTAXR  = MAC_CTAXR(-1)

(MAC_OGC)  = MAC_OGC(-1) * (MAC_YFT / MAC_YFT(-1) * MAC_YED / MAC_YED(-1))

MAC_USER  = (MAC_LTI  - MAC_INFT  + MAC_DEP * 100) / (1  - MAC_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (MAC_GCARB / MAC_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY MAC_XTN  = MAC_XTD$ * MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") * MAC_XTR

@IDENTITY MAC_YEN  = MAC_YER  * MAC_YED

@IDENTITY MAC_MTN  = MAC_MTD  * MAC_MTR

@IDENTITY MAC_XTN$  = MAC_XTN / MAC_EXR

@IDENTITY MAC_YEN$  = MAC_YEN / MAC_EXR

@IDENTITY MAC_MTN$  = MAC_MTN / MAC_EXR

@IDENTITY MAC_MTR$  = MAC_MTR$(-1) * MAC_MTR / MAC_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_XTR$  = MAC_XTR$(-1) * MAC_XTR / MAC_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_YER$  = MAC_YER$(-1) * MAC_YER / MAC_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_YFT$  = MAC_YFT$(-1) * MAC_YFT / MAC_YFT(-1)

MAC_POPT  = MAC_POPT(-1)  - MAC_LIVES

MAC_POPWA  = MAC_POPWA(-1) * MAC_POPT / MAC_POPT(-1)

MAC_SCR  = MAC_SCR(-1)  + ((MAC_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MAC_YFT(-1) / MAC_YER(-1)  - MAC_YFT(-2) / MAC_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY MAC_ITR  = MAC_IGR  + MAC_IPR

@IDENTITY MAC_YER  = MAC_PCR  + MAC_GCR  + MAC_ITR  + MAC_SCR  + MAC_XTR  - MAC_MTR

@IDENTITY MAC_PROF  = (MAC_YEN - MAC_ITAX) * (1 - MAC_LABSH)

@IDENTITY MAC_GDI  = MAC_YER  - MAC_XTR  + MAC_MTR  + MAC_XTN  / ((MAC_YEN  - MAC_XTN  + MAC_MTN)  / (MAC_YER  - MAC_XTR  + MAC_MTR))  - MAC_MTN  / ((MAC_YEN  - MAC_XTN  + MAC_MTN)  / (MAC_YER  - MAC_XTR  + MAC_MTR))

@IDENTITY MAC_RPDI  = MAC_LABSH * 0.5 * (MAC_YER(-1)  + MAC_GDI(-1)) * MAC_YED(-1) / MAC_HIC(-1) * (MAC_LNN / MAC_LNN(-1)  + MAC_TECHL - MAC_TECHL(-1)) + MAC_REMIT / MAC_HIC  + MAC_EXPSP / MAC_HIC  - MAC_TAX / MAC_HIC

DLOG(MAC_YFT)  = (1 - MAC_ALPHA - MAC_LABSH) * DLOG(MAC_K(-1) / MAC_LFN(-1))  + (1 - MAC_ALPHA) * DLOG(MAC_LFN)  + MAC_LABSH * D(MAC_TECHL)  + MAC_ALPHA * (DLOG(MAC_EC)  + D(MAC_EFF) )  - ( MAC_CLIMLOSS / MAC_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (MAC_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY MAC_K  = MAC_K(-1) * (1 - MAC_DEP) + MAC_ITR

DLOG(MAC_MTD)  = (1  - MAC_OMS) * ( DLOG(MAC_CMUD)  + DLOG(MAC_EXR) )  + MAC_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MAC_EXR) )

DLOG(MAC_XTD$)  = (1  - MAC_OXS) * DLOG(MAC_XTDNO$)  + MAC_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

MAC_INFT  = 0.95 * MAC_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

MAC_OXS  = MAC_OXS(-1)

MAC_OMS  = MAC_OMS(-1) * ((MAC_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * MAC_EXR(-1) / MAC_MTN(-1)) / (MAC_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * MAC_EXR(-2) / MAC_MTN(-2)))^0.25

MAC_CXS  = MAC_CXS(-1)

MAC_FINC  = MAC_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_CAN  = MAC_XTN / MAC_EXR  - MAC_MTN / MAC_EXR  + MAC_REMIT / MAC_EXR  + MAC_CANOTH

@IDENTITY MAC_CANRATIO  = MAC_CAN / MAC_YEN$ * 100

MAC_CANOTH  = MAC_CANOTH(-1)  + ((MAC_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MAC_YEN$  / MAC_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MAC_REVG / MAC_EXR  - MAC_REVG(-1) / MAC_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(MAC_EFEX)  =  - LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.651579196E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005492607565 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004213122009 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.806716828E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.008503661E-06 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006820525482 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.2310217654 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.594120246E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.914398148E-07 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.3225859951 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002954423549 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001926861147 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.808108886E-06 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03782194615 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.677917007E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.768611602E-09 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.263808242E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003762139481 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.787189281E-07 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.024256533E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001808341913 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.043591616E-07 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001736888623 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.659381622E-05 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.738260328E-06 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001781209593 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01027278867 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001984197066 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00711739173 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000224526466 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003074782973 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.821994684E-08 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005785688316 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.189381384E-06 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005741596844 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.910737522E-07 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.854291295E-08 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007186990178 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02290733433 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01079378922 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0389976305 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008198790013 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03837643645 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009317015046 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001996128542 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03436652643 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007984986531 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1605722265 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01345853737 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006773822035 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004062933231 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(MAC_REFEX )  =  - LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.651579196E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005492607565 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0004213122009 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.806716828E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.008503661E-06 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0006820525482 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.2310217654 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.594120246E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.914398148E-07 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.3225859951 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002954423549 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001926861147 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.808108886E-06 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03782194615 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.677917007E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.768611602E-09 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.263808242E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003762139481 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.787189281E-07 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.024256533E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001808341913 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.043591616E-07 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001736888623 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.659381622E-05 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.738260328E-06 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001781209593 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01027278867 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001984197066 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00711739173 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000224526466 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003074782973 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.821994684E-08 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005785688316 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.189381384E-06 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005741596844 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.910737522E-07 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.854291295E-08 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007186990178 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02290733433 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01079378922 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0389976305 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008198790013 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03837643645 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009317015046 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001996128542 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03436652643 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007984986531 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1605722265 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01345853737 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006773822035 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004062933231 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

MAC_REMIT  = MAC_REMIT(-1) / MAC_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02238691429 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1777358739 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001461763911 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5149355728 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 7.308819553E-06 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1473238757 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07024506472 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01584552079 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051359075 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 1.461763911E-05 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * MAC_EXR

MAC_GINT  = MAC_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (MAC_LTI  - MAC_LTI(-1))

MAC_GDN  = MAC_GDN(-1) * (MAC_GDFXSH  * (MAC_EXR  / MAC_EXR(-1))  + (1  - MAC_GDFXSH))  - MAC_GLN

@IDENTITY MAC_GDNRATIO  = MAC_GDN / MAC_YEN * 100

MAC_GDFXSH  = ( MAC_GDFXSH(-1) * (MAC_EXR / MAC_EXR(-1) )) / (MAC_GDFXSH(-1) * (MAC_EXR / MAC_EXR(-1))  + 1 - MAC_GDFXSH(-1) )

MAC_TOURSH  = MAC_TOURSH(-1)

MAC_LOCK  = 0

MAC_GCARBR  = MAC_GCARBR(-1)

MAC_GTRADER  = MAC_GTRADER(-1)

MAC_TAXR  = MAC_TAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_REV  = MAC_TAX  + MAC_CTAX  + MAC_ITAX  + MAC_GTRADE  + MAC_REVG  + MAC_GCARB  + MAC_GCOM  + MAC_GOTH

@IDENTITY MAC_TAX  = MAC_TAXR * (MAC_LABSH * 0.5 * (MAC_YER(-1)  + MAC_GDI(-1)) * MAC_YED(-1) * (MAC_LNN / MAC_LNN(-1)  + MAC_TECHL - MAC_TECHL(-1)) + MAC_REMIT  + MAC_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY MAC_CTAX  = MAC_CTAXR * MAC_PROF

@IDENTITY MAC_ITAX  = MAC_ITAXR * (MAC_PCR * MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY MAC_GTRADE  = MAC_GTRADER * MAC_XTN

MAC_REVG  = MAC_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (MAC_YER$ / MAC_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - MAC_YER$(-1) / MAC_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * MAC_EXR / MAC_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_GCARB  = MAC_GCARBR * MAC_CO2 * MAC_EXR / 1000

MAC_GCOM  = MAC_GCOM(-1) * ( MAC_OILC / (MAC_OILC + MAC_GASC + MAC_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + MAC_GASC / (MAC_OILC + MAC_GASC + MAC_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + MAC_COALC / (MAC_OILC + MAC_GASC + MAC_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

MAC_GOTH  = MAC_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_EXP  = MAC_EXPE  + MAC_EXPH  + MAC_EXPSP  + MAC_OGC  + MAC_OGI  + MAC_GIP

MAC_EXPE  = MAC_EXPE(-1) * (MAC_YFT / MAC_YFT(-1)) * (MAC_YED / MAC_YED(-1))

MAC_EXPH = MAC_EXPH(-1) * (MAC_YFT / MAC_YFT(-1)) * (MAC_YED / MAC_YED(-1))

MAC_EXPSP  = MAC_EXPSP(-1) * (MAC_YFT / MAC_YFT(-1)) * (MAC_YED / MAC_YED(-1)) * (MAC_POPT - MAC_LNN) / (MAC_POPT(-1) - MAC_LNN(-1))

DLOG(MAC_OGI)  = DLOG(MAC_YFT)  + DLOG(MAC_YED)

MAC_GCR  = MAC_GCR(-1)  + ( MAC_OGC / MAC_YED - MAC_OGC(-1) / MAC_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (MAC_EXPH ) / MAC_YED  - (MAC_EXPH(-1) ) / MAC_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MAC_EXPE ) / MAC_YED  - (MAC_EXPE(-1) ) / MAC_YED(-1) )

MAC_IGR  = MAC_IGR(-1) + (MAC_OGI / MAC_YED - MAC_OGI(-1) / MAC_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (MAC_EXPH ) / MAC_YED  - (MAC_EXPH(-1) ) / MAC_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MAC_EXPE ) / MAC_YED  - (MAC_EXPE(-1) ) / MAC_YED(-1) )

MAC_GIP  = ( MAC_GIP(-1)  + ( MAC_GDN(-1) - MAC_GDN(-2) ) * MAC_GINT(-1) / 100  + MAC_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( MAC_GINT(-1) / 100 - MAC_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (MAC_GDFXSH * (MAC_EXR / MAC_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MAC_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY MAC_GLN  = MAC_REV  - MAC_EXP

@IDENTITY MAC_GLNRATIO  = MAC_GLN / MAC_YEN * 100

MAC_GLNT  = MAC_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

MAC_TFP  = MAC_LABSH * (MAC_TECHL  - MAC_TECHL(-1))

MAC_LABSH  = MAC_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY MAC_LFN  = MAC_LRX * MAC_POPWA

MAC_LRX  = MAC_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(MAC_YER(-1) / MAC_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY MAC_URX  = (1 - MAC_LNN / MAC_LFN) * 100

MAC_URXF  = MAC_URXF(-1) * MAC_URX / MAC_URX(-1) * MAC_LNN / MAC_LNNF / (MAC_LNN(-1) / MAC_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(MAC_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MAC_PCR  / MAC_POPT)

MAC_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(MAC_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

MAC_HEAD19  = MAC_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MAC_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI^2)  , MAC_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MAC_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MAC_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

MAC_HEAD55  = MAC_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MAC_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI^2)  , MAC_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MAC_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MAC_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(MAC_XTR)  = DLOG(MAC_WDR)  + (1  - MAC_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(MAC_XTDNO$  / MAC_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * MAC_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(MAC_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (MAC_EXPH(-1) / MAC_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (MAC_EXPH(-1) / MAC_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(MAC_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(MAC_PM25)

MAC_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( MAC_EXPSP / MAC_YEN )

DLOG(MAC_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - MAC_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (MAC_FINC - MAC_FINC(-1))

DLOG(MAC_PCR)  =  - 0.103308784402089  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(MAC_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MAC_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (MAC_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MAC_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(MAC_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(MAC_HIC)  - MAC_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * MAC_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * MAC_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MAC_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MAC_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MAC_IPR)  =  - 0.204172797399459  - 0.1 * (LOG(MAC_IPR(-1)  / MAC_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * MAC_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * MAC_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(MAC_PCR  + MAC_GCR(-1) + MAC_IGR(-1) + MAC_XTN  / MAC_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(MAC_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (MAC_USER - MAC_USER(-1))  - (0 * MAC_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MAC_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MAC_FUELSH - MAC_TOURSH)) * MAC_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * MAC_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MAC_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MAC_FUELSH - MAC_TOURSH)) * MAC_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MAC_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MAC_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MAC_MTR)  =  - 0.171430969070008  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(MAC_MTR(-1))  - LOG(MAC_PCR(-1) + MAC_ITR(-1) + MAC_GCR(-1) + MAC_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(MAC_YFT(-1) / MAC_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(MAC_CMUD(-1) * MAC_EXR(-1)  / MAC_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * MAC_OMS * LOG(MAC_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.391895987424806  * DLOG(MAC_XTR)  + 0.278979540240576  * DLOG(MAC_PCR)  + 0.174231890588947  * DLOG(MAC_IPR)  + 0.0436199145890905  * DLOG(MAC_GCR + MAC_IGR)

MAC_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * MAC_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * MAC_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * MAC_OILC

MAC_POIL  = MAC_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( MAC_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - MAC_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

MAC_PG  = MAC_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( MAC_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - MAC_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

MAC_PC  = MAC_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( MAC_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - MAC_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(MAC_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

MAC_PE  = MAC_PE(-1) * ( MAC_OILC(-1) / (MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) * MAC_POIL / MAC_POIL(-1)  + MAC_GASC(-1) / (MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) * MAC_PG / MAC_PG(-1)  + MAC_COALC(-1) / (MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) * MAC_PC / MAC_PC(-1)  + MAC_RC(-1) / (MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) * MAC_PR / MAC_PR(-1) )

D(MAC_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(MAC_PM25)  = 0.2 * (MAC_COALC(-1) / MAC_EC(-1) - MAC_COALC(-2) / MAC_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (MAC_COALC(-2) / MAC_EC(-2) - MAC_COALC(-3) / MAC_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (MAC_OILC(-1) / MAC_EC(-1) - MAC_OILC(-2) / MAC_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (MAC_OILC(-2) / MAC_EC(-2) - MAC_OILC(-3) / MAC_EC(-3))

DLOG(MAC_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(MAC_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(MAC_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(MAC_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MAC_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MAC_PE * MAC_EXR / MAC_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MAC_PE(-1) * MAC_EXR(-1) / MAC_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MAC_PE(-2) * MAC_EXR(-2) / MAC_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MAC_PE(-3) * MAC_EXR(-3) / MAC_HIC(-3))  - (MAC_EFF - MAC_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(MAC_COALC)  = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MAC_COALC(-1) / MAC_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(MAC_PE(-1) / MAC_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) / MAC_EC(-1))

DLOG(MAC_GASC)  = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MAC_GASC(-1) / MAC_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.0111987685488077 * LOG(MAC_PE(-1) / MAC_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) / MAC_EC(-1))

DLOG(MAC_RC)  = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MAC_RC(-1) / MAC_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0702496088749822 * LOG(MAC_PE(-1) / MAC_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) / MAC_EC(-1))

DLOG(MAC_OILC)  = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MAC_OILC(-1) / MAC_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0702496088749822 * LOG(MAC_PE(-1) / MAC_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MAC_COALC(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1) + MAC_OILC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)) / MAC_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY MAC_EXR  = MAC_EXR(-1) * HKG_EXR / HKG_EXR(-1)

DLOG(MYS_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(MYS_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MYS_MTD)  + 0.4 * (MYS_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (MYS_YER / MYS_YFT  - MYS_YER(-1) / MYS_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + MYS_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + MYS_GCARB / MYS_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (MYS_PREM - MYS_PREM(-1)) / 100

MYS_YED  = MYS_YED(-1) * MYS_HIC / MYS_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_INT  = MYS_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_LTI  = MYS_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (MYS_INT - MYS_INT(-1))  + (MYS_PREM  - MYS_PREM(-1)) / 100

MYS_PREM  = MYS_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (MYS_GDNRATIO(-1)  - MYS_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(MYS_LNN)  = DLOG(MYS_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(MYS_LNN(-1))  - LOG(MYS_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(MYS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MYS_LNNF)  = DLOG(MYS_LNN)

MYS_FUELSH  = MYS_FUELSH(-1)

MYS_TAXR  = MYS_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MYS_GLNT(-1)  - MYS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MYS_YEN(-1) / ( ( MYS_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (MYS_YER(-2)  + MYS_GDI(-2)) * MYS_YED(-2) * (MYS_LNN(-1) / MYS_LNN(-2)  + MYS_TECHL(-1) - MYS_TECHL(-2) ) ) + MYS_REMIT(-1)  + MYS_EXPSP(-1) ) * MYS_SOLV

MYS_CTAXR  = MYS_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MYS_GLNT(-1)  - MYS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MYS_YEN(-1) / ( MYS_PROF(-1) ) * MYS_SOLV

(MYS_OGC)  = MYS_OGC(-1) * (MYS_YFT / MYS_YFT(-1) * MYS_YED / MYS_YED(-1))

MYS_USER  = (MYS_LTI  - MYS_INFT  + MYS_DEP * 100) / (1  - MYS_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (MYS_GCARB / MYS_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY MYS_XTN  = MYS_XTD$ * MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") * MYS_XTR

@IDENTITY MYS_YEN  = MYS_YER  * MYS_YED

@IDENTITY MYS_MTN  = MYS_MTD  * MYS_MTR

@IDENTITY MYS_XTN$  = MYS_XTN / MYS_EXR

@IDENTITY MYS_YEN$  = MYS_YEN / MYS_EXR

@IDENTITY MYS_MTN$  = MYS_MTN / MYS_EXR

@IDENTITY MYS_MTR$  = MYS_MTR$(-1) * MYS_MTR / MYS_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_XTR$  = MYS_XTR$(-1) * MYS_XTR / MYS_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_YER$  = MYS_YER$(-1) * MYS_YER / MYS_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_YFT$  = MYS_YFT$(-1) * MYS_YFT / MYS_YFT(-1)

MYS_POPT  = MYS_POPT(-1)  - MYS_LIVES

MYS_POPWA  = MYS_POPWA(-1) * MYS_POPT / MYS_POPT(-1)

MYS_SCR  = MYS_SCR(-1)  + ((MYS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MYS_YFT(-1) / MYS_YER(-1)  - MYS_YFT(-2) / MYS_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY MYS_ITR  = MYS_IGR  + MYS_IPR

@IDENTITY MYS_YER  = MYS_PCR  + MYS_GCR  + MYS_ITR  + MYS_SCR  + MYS_XTR  - MYS_MTR

@IDENTITY MYS_PROF  = (MYS_YEN - MYS_ITAX) * (1 - MYS_LABSH)

@IDENTITY MYS_GDI  = MYS_YER  - MYS_XTR  + MYS_MTR  + MYS_XTN  / ((MYS_YEN  - MYS_XTN  + MYS_MTN)  / (MYS_YER  - MYS_XTR  + MYS_MTR))  - MYS_MTN  / ((MYS_YEN  - MYS_XTN  + MYS_MTN)  / (MYS_YER  - MYS_XTR  + MYS_MTR))

@IDENTITY MYS_RPDI  = MYS_LABSH * 0.5 * (MYS_YER(-1)  + MYS_GDI(-1)) * MYS_YED(-1) / MYS_HIC(-1) * (MYS_LNN / MYS_LNN(-1)  + MYS_TECHL - MYS_TECHL(-1)) + MYS_REMIT / MYS_HIC  + MYS_EXPSP / MYS_HIC  - MYS_TAX / MYS_HIC

DLOG(MYS_YFT)  = (1 - MYS_ALPHA - MYS_LABSH) * DLOG(MYS_K(-1) / MYS_LFN(-1))  + (1 - MYS_ALPHA) * DLOG(MYS_LFN)  + MYS_LABSH * D(MYS_TECHL)  + MYS_ALPHA * (DLOG(MYS_EC)  + D(MYS_EFF) )  - ( MYS_CLIMLOSS / MYS_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (MYS_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY MYS_K  = MYS_K(-1) * (1 - MYS_DEP) + MYS_ITR

DLOG(MYS_MTD)  = (1  - MYS_OMS) * ( DLOG(MYS_CMUD)  + DLOG(MYS_EXR) )  + MYS_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MYS_EXR) )

DLOG(MYS_XTD$)  = (1  - MYS_OXS) * DLOG(MYS_XTDNO$)  + MYS_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

MYS_INFT  = 0.95 * MYS_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

MYS_OXS  = MYS_OXS(-1)

MYS_OMS  = MYS_OMS(-1) * ((MYS_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * MYS_EXR(-1) / MYS_MTN(-1)) / (MYS_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * MYS_EXR(-2) / MYS_MTN(-2)))^0.25

MYS_CXS  = MYS_CXS(-1)

MYS_FINC  = MYS_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_CAN  = MYS_XTN / MYS_EXR  - MYS_MTN / MYS_EXR  + MYS_REMIT / MYS_EXR  + MYS_CANOTH

@IDENTITY MYS_CANRATIO  = MYS_CAN / MYS_YEN$ * 100

MYS_CANOTH  = MYS_CANOTH(-1)  + ((MYS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MYS_YEN$  / MYS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MYS_REVG / MYS_EXR  - MYS_REVG(-1) / MYS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(MYS_EFEX)  =  - LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002176931319 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.403705698E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02990821339 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.559840678E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003050559104 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.309949174E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002129971506 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007159636793 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1709592435 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001544280761 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.990523159E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02899613686 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03809724435 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0333669538 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001974055867 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07061699409 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001403418538 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.394579424E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.367905463E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.126181385E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007546528092 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003315742937 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.049176516E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.208374643E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001707983948 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.777854846E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004027119929 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002368348422 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001851157279 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01169785829 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03545695038 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003296951997 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.235773973E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1930423019 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001306879861 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001358208439 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.844345018E-06 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0563067659 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.923873084E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.596301856E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005252218831 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.484650036E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002283936139 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.351938254E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01933352754 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07969870144 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02688761736 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008773721444 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01192445366 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005025851616 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01438703388 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001847049176 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006032533892 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03328741061 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01354459641 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02171839192 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02365213874 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03518144303 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(MYS_REFEX )  =  - LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002176931319 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.403705698E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02990821339 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.559840678E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003050559104 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.309949174E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002129971506 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007159636793 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1709592435 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001544280761 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.990523159E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02899613686 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03809724435 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0333669538 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001974055867 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07061699409 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001403418538 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.394579424E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.367905463E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.126181385E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007546528092 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003315742937 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.049176516E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.208374643E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001707983948 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.777854846E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004027119929 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002368348422 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001851157279 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01169785829 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03545695038 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003296951997 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.235773973E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1930423019 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001306879861 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001358208439 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.844345018E-06 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0563067659 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.923873084E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.596301856E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005252218831 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.484650036E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002283936139 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.351938254E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01933352754 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07969870144 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02688761736 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008773721444 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01192445366 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005025851616 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01438703388 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001847049176 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006032533892 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03328741061 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01354459641 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02171839192 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02365213874 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03518144303 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

MYS_REMIT  = MYS_REMIT(-1) / MYS_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.08318283794 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1238358744 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003643336231 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 6.482280934E-06 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001394730164 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005917242113 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002776532787 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001437757714 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03197061473 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008904596817 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001069036164 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006845288667 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002081814514 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003514018944 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005253249907 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 9.453326363E-05 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 9.345288347E-05 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 4.699653677E-05 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00203586917 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009185490953 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004310716821 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002798184603 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008146066374 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.6430769073 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004429018448 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 9.345288347E-05 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002128348907 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03794770003 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.781330545E-06 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000572692986 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003025258498 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01522334265 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007041377665 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * MYS_EXR

MYS_GINT  = MYS_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 9 * (MYS_LTI  - MYS_LTI(-1))

MYS_GDN  = MYS_GDN(-1) * (MYS_GDFXSH  * (MYS_EXR  / MYS_EXR(-1))  + (1  - MYS_GDFXSH))  - MYS_GLN

@IDENTITY MYS_GDNRATIO  = MYS_GDN / MYS_YEN * 100

MYS_GDFXSH  = ( MYS_GDFXSH(-1) * (MYS_EXR / MYS_EXR(-1) )) / (MYS_GDFXSH(-1) * (MYS_EXR / MYS_EXR(-1))  + 1 - MYS_GDFXSH(-1) )

MYS_TOURSH  = MYS_TOURSH(-1)

MYS_LOCK  = 0

MYS_GCARBR  = MYS_GCARBR(-1)

MYS_GTRADER  = MYS_GTRADER(-1)

MYS_ITAXR  = MYS_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_REV  = MYS_TAX  + MYS_CTAX  + MYS_ITAX  + MYS_GTRADE  + MYS_REVG  + MYS_GCARB  + MYS_GCOM  + MYS_GOTH

@IDENTITY MYS_TAX  = MYS_TAXR * (MYS_LABSH * 0.5 * (MYS_YER(-1)  + MYS_GDI(-1)) * MYS_YED(-1) * (MYS_LNN / MYS_LNN(-1)  + MYS_TECHL - MYS_TECHL(-1)) + MYS_REMIT  + MYS_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY MYS_CTAX  = MYS_CTAXR * MYS_PROF

@IDENTITY MYS_ITAX  = MYS_ITAXR * (MYS_PCR * MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY MYS_GTRADE  = MYS_GTRADER * MYS_XTN

MYS_REVG  = MYS_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (MYS_YER$ / MYS_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - MYS_YER$(-1) / MYS_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * MYS_EXR / MYS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_GCARB  = MYS_GCARBR * MYS_CO2 * MYS_EXR / 1000

MYS_GCOM  = MYS_GCOM(-1) * ( MYS_OILC / (MYS_OILC + MYS_GASC + MYS_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + MYS_GASC / (MYS_OILC + MYS_GASC + MYS_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + MYS_COALC / (MYS_OILC + MYS_GASC + MYS_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

MYS_GOTH  = MYS_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_EXP  = MYS_EXPE  + MYS_EXPH  + MYS_EXPSP  + MYS_OGC  + MYS_OGI  + MYS_GIP

MYS_EXPE  = MYS_EXPE(-1) * (MYS_YFT / MYS_YFT(-1)) * (MYS_YED / MYS_YED(-1))

MYS_EXPH = MYS_EXPH(-1) * (MYS_YFT / MYS_YFT(-1)) * (MYS_YED / MYS_YED(-1))

MYS_EXPSP  = MYS_EXPSP(-1) * (MYS_YFT / MYS_YFT(-1)) * (MYS_YED / MYS_YED(-1)) * (MYS_POPT - MYS_LNN) / (MYS_POPT(-1) - MYS_LNN(-1))

DLOG(MYS_OGI)  = DLOG(MYS_YFT)  + DLOG(MYS_YED)

MYS_GCR  = MYS_GCR(-1)  + ( MYS_OGC / MYS_YED - MYS_OGC(-1) / MYS_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (MYS_EXPH ) / MYS_YED  - (MYS_EXPH(-1) ) / MYS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MYS_EXPE ) / MYS_YED  - (MYS_EXPE(-1) ) / MYS_YED(-1) )

MYS_IGR  = MYS_IGR(-1) + (MYS_OGI / MYS_YED - MYS_OGI(-1) / MYS_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (MYS_EXPH ) / MYS_YED  - (MYS_EXPH(-1) ) / MYS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MYS_EXPE ) / MYS_YED  - (MYS_EXPE(-1) ) / MYS_YED(-1) )

MYS_GIP  = ( MYS_GIP(-1)  + ( MYS_GDN(-1) - MYS_GDN(-2) ) * MYS_GINT(-1) / 100  + MYS_GDN(-10) / 9 * ( MYS_GINT(-1) / 100 - MYS_GINT(-10) / 100 ) ) * (MYS_GDFXSH * (MYS_EXR / MYS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MYS_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY MYS_GLN  = MYS_REV  - MYS_EXP

@IDENTITY MYS_GLNRATIO  = MYS_GLN / MYS_YEN * 100

MYS_GLNT  = MYS_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

MYS_TFP  = MYS_LABSH * (MYS_TECHL  - MYS_TECHL(-1))

MYS_LABSH  = MYS_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY MYS_LFN  = MYS_LRX * MYS_POPWA

MYS_LRX  = MYS_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(MYS_YER(-1) / MYS_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY MYS_URX  = (1 - MYS_LNN / MYS_LFN) * 100

MYS_URXF  = MYS_URXF(-1) * MYS_URX / MYS_URX(-1) * MYS_LNN / MYS_LNNF / (MYS_LNN(-1) / MYS_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(MYS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MYS_PCR  / MYS_POPT)

MYS_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(MYS_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

MYS_HEAD19  = MYS_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MYS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI^2)  , MYS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MYS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MYS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

MYS_HEAD55  = MYS_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MYS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI^2)  , MYS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MYS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MYS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(MYS_XTR)  = DLOG(MYS_WDR)  + (1  - MYS_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(MYS_XTDNO$  / MYS_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * MYS_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(MYS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (MYS_EXPH(-1) / MYS_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (MYS_EXPH(-1) / MYS_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(MYS_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(MYS_PM25)

MYS_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( MYS_EXPSP / MYS_YEN )

DLOG(MYS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - MYS_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (MYS_FINC - MYS_FINC(-1))

DLOG(MYS_PCR)  =  - 0.0594160015415822  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(MYS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MYS_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (MYS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MYS_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(MYS_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(MYS_HIC)  - MYS_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * MYS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * MYS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MYS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MYS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MYS_IPR)  =  - 0.15966442747723  - 0.1 * (LOG(MYS_IPR(-1)  / MYS_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * MYS_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * MYS_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(MYS_PCR  + MYS_GCR(-1) + MYS_IGR(-1) + MYS_XTN  / MYS_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(MYS_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (MYS_USER - MYS_USER(-1))  - (0 * MYS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MYS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MYS_FUELSH - MYS_TOURSH)) * MYS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * MYS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MYS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MYS_FUELSH - MYS_TOURSH)) * MYS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MYS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MYS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MYS_MTR)  =  - 0.135514355285183  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(MYS_MTR(-1))  - LOG(MYS_PCR(-1) + MYS_ITR(-1) + MYS_GCR(-1) + MYS_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(MYS_YFT(-1) / MYS_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(MYS_CMUD(-1) * MYS_EXR(-1)  / MYS_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * MYS_OMS * LOG(MYS_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.670582883433918  * DLOG(MYS_XTR)  + 0.355070905932157  * DLOG(MYS_PCR)  + 0.138891582732119  * DLOG(MYS_IPR)  + 0.119145993761767  * DLOG(MYS_GCR + MYS_IGR)

MYS_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * MYS_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * MYS_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * MYS_OILC

MYS_POIL  = MYS_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( MYS_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - MYS_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

MYS_PG  = MYS_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( MYS_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - MYS_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

MYS_PC  = MYS_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( MYS_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - MYS_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(MYS_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

MYS_PE  = MYS_PE(-1) * ( MYS_OILC(-1) / (MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) * MYS_POIL / MYS_POIL(-1)  + MYS_GASC(-1) / (MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) * MYS_PG / MYS_PG(-1)  + MYS_COALC(-1) / (MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) * MYS_PC / MYS_PC(-1)  + MYS_RC(-1) / (MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) * MYS_PR / MYS_PR(-1) )

D(MYS_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(MYS_PM25)  = 0.2 * (MYS_COALC(-1) / MYS_EC(-1) - MYS_COALC(-2) / MYS_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (MYS_COALC(-2) / MYS_EC(-2) - MYS_COALC(-3) / MYS_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (MYS_OILC(-1) / MYS_EC(-1) - MYS_OILC(-2) / MYS_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (MYS_OILC(-2) / MYS_EC(-2) - MYS_OILC(-3) / MYS_EC(-3))

DLOG(MYS_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(MYS_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(MYS_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(MYS_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MYS_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MYS_PE * MYS_EXR / MYS_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MYS_PE(-1) * MYS_EXR(-1) / MYS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MYS_PE(-2) * MYS_EXR(-2) / MYS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MYS_PE(-3) * MYS_EXR(-3) / MYS_HIC(-3))  - (MYS_EFF - MYS_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(MYS_COALC)  = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MYS_COALC(-1) / MYS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.0638664041232334 * LOG(MYS_PE(-1) / MYS_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) / MYS_EC(-1))

DLOG(MYS_GASC)  = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MYS_GASC(-1) / MYS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.357206343277103 * LOG(MYS_PE(-1) / MYS_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) / MYS_EC(-1))

DLOG(MYS_RC)  = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MYS_RC(-1) / MYS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.0638664041232334 * LOG(MYS_PE(-1) / MYS_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) / MYS_EC(-1))

DLOG(MYS_OILC)  = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MYS_OILC(-1) / MYS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.0638664041232334 * LOG(MYS_PE(-1) / MYS_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MYS_COALC(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1) + MYS_OILC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)) / MYS_EC(-1))

MYS_EXR  = MYS_EXR(-1) * ( ( (MYS_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (MYS_INT  - USA_INT)  - (MYS_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(MDV_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(MDV_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MDV_MTD)  + 0.4 * (MDV_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (MDV_YER / MDV_YFT  - MDV_YER(-1) / MDV_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + MDV_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + MDV_GCARB / MDV_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (MDV_PREM - MDV_PREM(-1)) / 100

MDV_YED  = MDV_YED(-1) * MDV_HIC / MDV_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_INT  = MDV_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_LTI  = MDV_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (MDV_INT - MDV_INT(-1))  + (MDV_PREM  - MDV_PREM(-1)) / 100

MDV_PREM  = MDV_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (MDV_GDNRATIO(-1)  - MDV_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(MDV_LNN)  = DLOG(MDV_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(MDV_LNN(-1))  - LOG(MDV_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(MDV_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MDV_LNNF)  = DLOG(MDV_LNN)

MDV_FUELSH  = MDV_FUELSH(-1)

MDV_TAXR  = MDV_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MDV_GLNT(-1)  - MDV_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MDV_YEN(-1) / ( ( MDV_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (MDV_YER(-2)  + MDV_GDI(-2)) * MDV_YED(-2) * (MDV_LNN(-1) / MDV_LNN(-2)  + MDV_TECHL(-1) - MDV_TECHL(-2) ) ) + MDV_REMIT(-1)  + MDV_EXPSP(-1) ) * MDV_SOLV

MDV_CTAXR  = MDV_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MDV_GLNT(-1)  - MDV_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MDV_YEN(-1) / ( MDV_PROF(-1) ) * MDV_SOLV

(MDV_OGC)  = MDV_OGC(-1) * (MDV_YFT / MDV_YFT(-1) * MDV_YED / MDV_YED(-1))

MDV_USER  = (MDV_LTI  - MDV_INFT  + MDV_DEP * 100) / (1  - MDV_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (MDV_GCARB / MDV_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY MDV_XTN  = MDV_XTD$ * MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") * MDV_XTR

@IDENTITY MDV_YEN  = MDV_YER  * MDV_YED

@IDENTITY MDV_MTN  = MDV_MTD  * MDV_MTR

@IDENTITY MDV_XTN$  = MDV_XTN / MDV_EXR

@IDENTITY MDV_YEN$  = MDV_YEN / MDV_EXR

@IDENTITY MDV_MTN$  = MDV_MTN / MDV_EXR

@IDENTITY MDV_MTR$  = MDV_MTR$(-1) * MDV_MTR / MDV_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_XTR$  = MDV_XTR$(-1) * MDV_XTR / MDV_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_YER$  = MDV_YER$(-1) * MDV_YER / MDV_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_YFT$  = MDV_YFT$(-1) * MDV_YFT / MDV_YFT(-1)

MDV_POPT  = MDV_POPT(-1)  - MDV_LIVES

MDV_POPWA  = MDV_POPWA(-1) * MDV_POPT / MDV_POPT(-1)

MDV_SCR  = MDV_SCR(-1)  + ((MDV_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MDV_YFT(-1) / MDV_YER(-1)  - MDV_YFT(-2) / MDV_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY MDV_ITR  = MDV_IGR  + MDV_IPR

@IDENTITY MDV_YER  = MDV_PCR  + MDV_GCR  + MDV_ITR  + MDV_SCR  + MDV_XTR  - MDV_MTR

@IDENTITY MDV_PROF  = (MDV_YEN - MDV_ITAX) * (1 - MDV_LABSH)

@IDENTITY MDV_GDI  = MDV_YER  - MDV_XTR  + MDV_MTR  + MDV_XTN  / ((MDV_YEN  - MDV_XTN  + MDV_MTN)  / (MDV_YER  - MDV_XTR  + MDV_MTR))  - MDV_MTN  / ((MDV_YEN  - MDV_XTN  + MDV_MTN)  / (MDV_YER  - MDV_XTR  + MDV_MTR))

@IDENTITY MDV_RPDI  = MDV_LABSH * 0.5 * (MDV_YER(-1)  + MDV_GDI(-1)) * MDV_YED(-1) / MDV_HIC(-1) * (MDV_LNN / MDV_LNN(-1)  + MDV_TECHL - MDV_TECHL(-1)) + MDV_REMIT / MDV_HIC  + MDV_EXPSP / MDV_HIC  - MDV_TAX / MDV_HIC

DLOG(MDV_YFT)  = (1 - MDV_ALPHA - MDV_LABSH) * DLOG(MDV_K(-1) / MDV_LFN(-1))  + (1 - MDV_ALPHA) * DLOG(MDV_LFN)  + MDV_LABSH * D(MDV_TECHL)  + MDV_ALPHA * (DLOG(MDV_EC)  + D(MDV_EFF) )  - ( MDV_CLIMLOSS / MDV_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (MDV_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY MDV_K  = MDV_K(-1) * (1 - MDV_DEP) + MDV_ITR

DLOG(MDV_MTD)  = (1  - MDV_OMS) * ( DLOG(MDV_CMUD)  + DLOG(MDV_EXR) )  + MDV_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MDV_EXR) )

DLOG(MDV_XTD$)  = (1  - MDV_OXS) * DLOG(MDV_XTDNO$)  + MDV_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

MDV_INFT  = 0.95 * MDV_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

MDV_OXS  = MDV_OXS(-1)

MDV_OMS  = MDV_OMS(-1) * ((MDV_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * MDV_EXR(-1) / MDV_MTN(-1)) / (MDV_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * MDV_EXR(-2) / MDV_MTN(-2)))^0.25

MDV_CXS  = MDV_CXS(-1)

MDV_FINC  = MDV_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_CAN  = MDV_XTN / MDV_EXR  - MDV_MTN / MDV_EXR  + MDV_REMIT / MDV_EXR  + MDV_CANOTH

@IDENTITY MDV_CANRATIO  = MDV_CAN / MDV_YEN$ * 100

MDV_CANOTH  = MDV_CANOTH(-1)  + ((MDV_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MDV_YEN$  / MDV_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MDV_REVG / MDV_EXR  - MDV_REVG(-1) / MDV_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(MDV_EFEX)  =  - LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.72046576E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.469545363E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + @IDENTITY LOG(MDV_REFEX )  =  - LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.72046576E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1190909858 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

MDV_REMIT  = MDV_REMIT(-1) / MDV_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4262191929 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05859514124 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005013513763 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1422561287 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007050779234 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02464611292 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01169762461 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008612062147 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03428091978 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01305557972 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.08003146838 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.08996031812 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04462193716 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05395922125 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * MDV_EXR

MDV_GINT  = MDV_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (MDV_LTI  - MDV_LTI(-1))

MDV_GDN  = MDV_GDN(-1) * (MDV_GDFXSH  * (MDV_EXR  / MDV_EXR(-1))  + (1  - MDV_GDFXSH))  - MDV_GLN

@IDENTITY MDV_GDNRATIO  = MDV_GDN / MDV_YEN * 100

MDV_GDFXSH  = ( MDV_GDFXSH(-1) * (MDV_EXR / MDV_EXR(-1) )) / (MDV_GDFXSH(-1) * (MDV_EXR / MDV_EXR(-1))  + 1 - MDV_GDFXSH(-1) )

MDV_TOURSH  = MDV_TOURSH(-1)

MDV_LOCK  = 0

MDV_GCARBR  = MDV_GCARBR(-1)

MDV_GTRADER  = MDV_GTRADER(-1)

MDV_ITAXR  = MDV_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_REV  = MDV_TAX  + MDV_CTAX  + MDV_ITAX  + MDV_GTRADE  + MDV_REVG  + MDV_GCARB  + MDV_GCOM  + MDV_GOTH

@IDENTITY MDV_TAX  = MDV_TAXR * (MDV_LABSH * 0.5 * (MDV_YER(-1)  + MDV_GDI(-1)) * MDV_YED(-1) * (MDV_LNN / MDV_LNN(-1)  + MDV_TECHL - MDV_TECHL(-1)) + MDV_REMIT  + MDV_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY MDV_CTAX  = MDV_CTAXR * MDV_PROF

@IDENTITY MDV_ITAX  = MDV_ITAXR * (MDV_PCR * MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY MDV_GTRADE  = MDV_GTRADER * MDV_XTN

MDV_REVG  = MDV_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (MDV_YER$ / MDV_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - MDV_YER$(-1) / MDV_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * MDV_EXR / MDV_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_GCARB  = MDV_GCARBR * MDV_CO2 * MDV_EXR / 1000

MDV_GCOM  = MDV_GCOM(-1) * ( MDV_OILC / (MDV_OILC + MDV_GASC + MDV_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + MDV_GASC / (MDV_OILC + MDV_GASC + MDV_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + MDV_COALC / (MDV_OILC + MDV_GASC + MDV_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

MDV_GOTH  = MDV_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_EXP  = MDV_EXPE  + MDV_EXPH  + MDV_EXPSP  + MDV_OGC  + MDV_OGI  + MDV_GIP

MDV_EXPE  = MDV_EXPE(-1) * (MDV_YFT / MDV_YFT(-1)) * (MDV_YED / MDV_YED(-1))

MDV_EXPH = MDV_EXPH(-1) * (MDV_YFT / MDV_YFT(-1)) * (MDV_YED / MDV_YED(-1))

MDV_EXPSP  = MDV_EXPSP(-1) * (MDV_YFT / MDV_YFT(-1)) * (MDV_YED / MDV_YED(-1)) * (MDV_POPT - MDV_LNN) / (MDV_POPT(-1) - MDV_LNN(-1))

DLOG(MDV_OGI)  = DLOG(MDV_YFT)  + DLOG(MDV_YED)

MDV_GCR  = MDV_GCR(-1)  + ( MDV_OGC / MDV_YED - MDV_OGC(-1) / MDV_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (MDV_EXPH ) / MDV_YED  - (MDV_EXPH(-1) ) / MDV_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MDV_EXPE ) / MDV_YED  - (MDV_EXPE(-1) ) / MDV_YED(-1) )

MDV_IGR  = MDV_IGR(-1) + (MDV_OGI / MDV_YED - MDV_OGI(-1) / MDV_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (MDV_EXPH ) / MDV_YED  - (MDV_EXPH(-1) ) / MDV_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MDV_EXPE ) / MDV_YED  - (MDV_EXPE(-1) ) / MDV_YED(-1) )

MDV_GIP  = ( MDV_GIP(-1)  + ( MDV_GDN(-1) - MDV_GDN(-2) ) * MDV_GINT(-1) / 100  + MDV_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( MDV_GINT(-1) / 100 - MDV_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (MDV_GDFXSH * (MDV_EXR / MDV_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MDV_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY MDV_GLN  = MDV_REV  - MDV_EXP

@IDENTITY MDV_GLNRATIO  = MDV_GLN / MDV_YEN * 100

MDV_GLNT  = MDV_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

MDV_TFP  = MDV_LABSH * (MDV_TECHL  - MDV_TECHL(-1))

MDV_LABSH  = MDV_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY MDV_LFN  = MDV_LRX * MDV_POPWA

MDV_LRX  = MDV_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(MDV_YER(-1) / MDV_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY MDV_URX  = (1 - MDV_LNN / MDV_LFN) * 100

MDV_URXF  = MDV_URXF(-1) * MDV_URX / MDV_URX(-1) * MDV_LNN / MDV_LNNF / (MDV_LNN(-1) / MDV_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(MDV_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MDV_PCR  / MDV_POPT)

MDV_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(MDV_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

MDV_HEAD19  = MDV_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MDV_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI^2)  , MDV_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MDV_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MDV_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

MDV_HEAD55  = MDV_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MDV_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI^2)  , MDV_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MDV_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MDV_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(MDV_XTR)  = DLOG(MDV_WDR)  + (1  - MDV_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(MDV_XTDNO$  / MDV_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * MDV_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(MDV_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (MDV_EXPH(-1) / MDV_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (MDV_EXPH(-1) / MDV_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(MDV_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(MDV_PM25)

MDV_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( MDV_EXPSP / MDV_YEN )

DLOG(MDV_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - MDV_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (MDV_FINC - MDV_FINC(-1))

DLOG(MDV_PCR)  =  - 0.260079881898787  +  - 0.304120129931178 * (LOG(MDV_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MDV_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (MDV_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MDV_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(MDV_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(MDV_HIC)  - MDV_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * MDV_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * MDV_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MDV_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MDV_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MDV_IPR)  =  - 0.190722529580731  - 0.1 * (LOG(MDV_IPR(-1)  / MDV_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * MDV_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * MDV_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(MDV_PCR  + MDV_GCR(-1) + MDV_IGR(-1) + MDV_XTN  / MDV_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(MDV_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (MDV_USER - MDV_USER(-1))  - (0 * MDV_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MDV_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MDV_FUELSH - MDV_TOURSH)) * MDV_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * MDV_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MDV_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MDV_FUELSH - MDV_TOURSH)) * MDV_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MDV_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MDV_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MDV_MTR)  =  - 0.104542169783053  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(MDV_MTR(-1))  - LOG(MDV_PCR(-1) + MDV_ITR(-1) + MDV_GCR(-1) + MDV_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(MDV_YFT(-1) / MDV_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(MDV_CMUD(-1) * MDV_EXR(-1)  / MDV_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * MDV_OMS * LOG(MDV_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.386170031998704  * DLOG(MDV_XTR)  + 0.251961940410328  * DLOG(MDV_PCR)  + 0.103670975930968  * DLOG(MDV_IPR)  + 0.135899559095378  * DLOG(MDV_GCR + MDV_IGR)

MDV_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * MDV_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * MDV_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * MDV_OILC

MDV_POIL  = MDV_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( MDV_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - MDV_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

MDV_PG  = MDV_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( MDV_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - MDV_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

MDV_PC  = MDV_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( MDV_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - MDV_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(MDV_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

MDV_PE  = MDV_PE(-1) * ( MDV_OILC(-1) / (MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) * MDV_POIL / MDV_POIL(-1)  + MDV_GASC(-1) / (MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) * MDV_PG / MDV_PG(-1)  + MDV_COALC(-1) / (MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) * MDV_PC / MDV_PC(-1)  + MDV_RC(-1) / (MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) * MDV_PR / MDV_PR(-1) )

D(MDV_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(MDV_PM25)  = 0.2 * (MDV_COALC(-1) / MDV_EC(-1) - MDV_COALC(-2) / MDV_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (MDV_COALC(-2) / MDV_EC(-2) - MDV_COALC(-3) / MDV_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (MDV_OILC(-1) / MDV_EC(-1) - MDV_OILC(-2) / MDV_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (MDV_OILC(-2) / MDV_EC(-2) - MDV_OILC(-3) / MDV_EC(-3))

DLOG(MDV_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(MDV_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(MDV_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(MDV_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MDV_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MDV_PE * MDV_EXR / MDV_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MDV_PE(-1) * MDV_EXR(-1) / MDV_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MDV_PE(-2) * MDV_EXR(-2) / MDV_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MDV_PE(-3) * MDV_EXR(-3) / MDV_HIC(-3))  - (MDV_EFF - MDV_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(MDV_COALC)  = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MDV_COALC(-1) / MDV_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(MDV_PE(-1) / MDV_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) / MDV_EC(-1))

DLOG(MDV_GASC)  = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MDV_GASC(-1) / MDV_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(MDV_PE(-1) / MDV_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) / MDV_EC(-1))

DLOG(MDV_RC)  = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MDV_RC(-1) / MDV_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.0100581120626052 * LOG(MDV_PE(-1) / MDV_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) / MDV_EC(-1))

DLOG(MDV_OILC)  = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MDV_OILC(-1) / MDV_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.0100581120626052 * LOG(MDV_PE(-1) / MDV_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MDV_COALC(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1) + MDV_OILC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)) / MDV_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY MDV_EXR  = MDV_EXR(-1)

DLOG(FSM_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(FSM_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(FSM_MTD)  + 0.4 * (FSM_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (FSM_YER / FSM_YFT  - FSM_YER(-1) / FSM_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + FSM_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + FSM_GCARB / FSM_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (FSM_PREM - FSM_PREM(-1)) / 100

FSM_YED  = FSM_YED(-1) * FSM_HIC / FSM_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_INT  = FSM_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_LTI  = FSM_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (FSM_INT - FSM_INT(-1))  + (FSM_PREM  - FSM_PREM(-1)) / 100

FSM_PREM  = FSM_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (FSM_GDNRATIO(-1)  - FSM_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(FSM_LNN)  = DLOG(FSM_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(FSM_LNN(-1))  - LOG(FSM_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(FSM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(FSM_LNNF)  = DLOG(FSM_LNN)

FSM_FUELSH  = FSM_FUELSH(-1)

FSM_TAXR  = FSM_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( FSM_GLNT(-1)  - FSM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * FSM_YEN(-1) / ( ( FSM_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (FSM_YER(-2)  + FSM_GDI(-2)) * FSM_YED(-2) * (FSM_LNN(-1) / FSM_LNN(-2)  + FSM_TECHL(-1) - FSM_TECHL(-2) ) ) + FSM_REMIT(-1)  + FSM_EXPSP(-1) ) * FSM_SOLV

FSM_CTAXR  = FSM_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( FSM_GLNT(-1)  - FSM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * FSM_YEN(-1) / ( FSM_PROF(-1) ) * FSM_SOLV

(FSM_OGC)  = FSM_OGC(-1) * (FSM_YFT / FSM_YFT(-1) * FSM_YED / FSM_YED(-1))

FSM_USER  = (FSM_LTI  - FSM_INFT  + FSM_DEP * 100) / (1  - FSM_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (FSM_GCARB / FSM_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY FSM_XTN  = FSM_XTD$ * FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") * FSM_XTR

@IDENTITY FSM_YEN  = FSM_YER  * FSM_YED

@IDENTITY FSM_MTN  = FSM_MTD  * FSM_MTR

@IDENTITY FSM_XTN$  = FSM_XTN / FSM_EXR

@IDENTITY FSM_YEN$  = FSM_YEN / FSM_EXR

@IDENTITY FSM_MTN$  = FSM_MTN / FSM_EXR

@IDENTITY FSM_MTR$  = FSM_MTR$(-1) * FSM_MTR / FSM_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_XTR$  = FSM_XTR$(-1) * FSM_XTR / FSM_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_YER$  = FSM_YER$(-1) * FSM_YER / FSM_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_YFT$  = FSM_YFT$(-1) * FSM_YFT / FSM_YFT(-1)

FSM_POPT  = FSM_POPT(-1)  - FSM_LIVES

FSM_POPWA  = FSM_POPWA(-1) * FSM_POPT / FSM_POPT(-1)

FSM_SCR  = FSM_SCR(-1)  + ((FSM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (FSM_YFT(-1) / FSM_YER(-1)  - FSM_YFT(-2) / FSM_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY FSM_ITR  = FSM_IGR  + FSM_IPR

@IDENTITY FSM_YER  = FSM_PCR  + FSM_GCR  + FSM_ITR  + FSM_SCR  + FSM_XTR  - FSM_MTR

@IDENTITY FSM_PROF  = (FSM_YEN - FSM_ITAX) * (1 - FSM_LABSH)

@IDENTITY FSM_GDI  = FSM_YER  - FSM_XTR  + FSM_MTR  + FSM_XTN  / ((FSM_YEN  - FSM_XTN  + FSM_MTN)  / (FSM_YER  - FSM_XTR  + FSM_MTR))  - FSM_MTN  / ((FSM_YEN  - FSM_XTN  + FSM_MTN)  / (FSM_YER  - FSM_XTR  + FSM_MTR))

@IDENTITY FSM_RPDI  = FSM_LABSH * 0.5 * (FSM_YER(-1)  + FSM_GDI(-1)) * FSM_YED(-1) / FSM_HIC(-1) * (FSM_LNN / FSM_LNN(-1)  + FSM_TECHL - FSM_TECHL(-1)) + FSM_REMIT / FSM_HIC  + FSM_EXPSP / FSM_HIC  - FSM_TAX / FSM_HIC

DLOG(FSM_YFT)  = (1 - FSM_ALPHA - FSM_LABSH) * DLOG(FSM_K(-1) / FSM_LFN(-1))  + (1 - FSM_ALPHA) * DLOG(FSM_LFN)  + FSM_LABSH * D(FSM_TECHL)  + FSM_ALPHA * (DLOG(FSM_EC)  + D(FSM_EFF) )  - ( FSM_CLIMLOSS / FSM_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (FSM_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY FSM_K  = FSM_K(-1) * (1 - FSM_DEP) + FSM_ITR

DLOG(FSM_MTD)  = (1  - FSM_OMS) * ( DLOG(FSM_CMUD)  + DLOG(FSM_EXR) )  + FSM_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(FSM_EXR) )

DLOG(FSM_XTD$)  = (1  - FSM_OXS) * DLOG(FSM_XTDNO$)  + FSM_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

FSM_INFT  = 0.95 * FSM_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

FSM_OXS  = FSM_OXS(-1)

FSM_OMS  = FSM_OMS(-1) * ((FSM_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * FSM_EXR(-1) / FSM_MTN(-1)) / (FSM_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * FSM_EXR(-2) / FSM_MTN(-2)))^0.25

FSM_CXS  = FSM_CXS(-1)

FSM_FINC  = FSM_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_CAN  = FSM_XTN / FSM_EXR  - FSM_MTN / FSM_EXR  + FSM_REMIT / FSM_EXR  + FSM_CANOTH

@IDENTITY FSM_CANRATIO  = FSM_CAN / FSM_YEN$ * 100

FSM_CANOTH  = FSM_CANOTH(-1)  + ((FSM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (FSM_YEN$  / FSM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + FSM_REVG / FSM_EXR  - FSM_REVG(-1) / FSM_EXR(-1)
