FSM_REMIT  = FSM_REMIT(-1) / FSM_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001484535208 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001355138886 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 4.994774624E-05 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 4.372389524E-05 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 3.776408137E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.9944700528 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002495368911 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002218105699 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002988489001 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003008265979 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * FSM_EXR

FSM_GINT  = FSM_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (FSM_LTI  - FSM_LTI(-1))

FSM_GDN  = FSM_GDN(-1) * (FSM_GDFXSH  * (FSM_EXR  / FSM_EXR(-1))  + (1  - FSM_GDFXSH))  - FSM_GLN

@IDENTITY FSM_GDNRATIO  = FSM_GDN / FSM_YEN * 100

FSM_GDFXSH  = ( FSM_GDFXSH(-1) * (FSM_EXR / FSM_EXR(-1) )) / (FSM_GDFXSH(-1) * (FSM_EXR / FSM_EXR(-1))  + 1 - FSM_GDFXSH(-1) )

FSM_TOURSH  = FSM_TOURSH(-1)

FSM_LOCK  = 0

FSM_GCARBR  = FSM_GCARBR(-1)

FSM_GTRADER  = FSM_GTRADER(-1)

FSM_ITAXR  = FSM_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_REV  = FSM_TAX  + FSM_CTAX  + FSM_ITAX  + FSM_GTRADE  + FSM_REVG  + FSM_GCARB  + FSM_GCOM  + FSM_GOTH

@IDENTITY FSM_TAX  = FSM_TAXR * (FSM_LABSH * 0.5 * (FSM_YER(-1)  + FSM_GDI(-1)) * FSM_YED(-1) * (FSM_LNN / FSM_LNN(-1)  + FSM_TECHL - FSM_TECHL(-1)) + FSM_REMIT  + FSM_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY FSM_CTAX  = FSM_CTAXR * FSM_PROF

@IDENTITY FSM_ITAX  = FSM_ITAXR * (FSM_PCR * FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY FSM_GTRADE  = FSM_GTRADER * FSM_XTN

FSM_REVG  = FSM_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (FSM_YER$ / FSM_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - FSM_YER$(-1) / FSM_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * FSM_EXR / FSM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_GCARB  = FSM_GCARBR * FSM_CO2 * FSM_EXR / 1000

FSM_GCOM  = FSM_GCOM(-1) * ( FSM_OILC / (FSM_OILC + FSM_GASC + FSM_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + FSM_GASC / (FSM_OILC + FSM_GASC + FSM_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + FSM_COALC / (FSM_OILC + FSM_GASC + FSM_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

FSM_GOTH  = FSM_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_EXP  = FSM_EXPE  + FSM_EXPH  + FSM_EXPSP  + FSM_OGC  + FSM_OGI  + FSM_GIP

FSM_EXPE  = FSM_EXPE(-1) * (FSM_YFT / FSM_YFT(-1)) * (FSM_YED / FSM_YED(-1))

FSM_EXPH = FSM_EXPH(-1) * (FSM_YFT / FSM_YFT(-1)) * (FSM_YED / FSM_YED(-1))

FSM_EXPSP  = FSM_EXPSP(-1) * (FSM_YFT / FSM_YFT(-1)) * (FSM_YED / FSM_YED(-1)) * (FSM_POPT - FSM_LNN) / (FSM_POPT(-1) - FSM_LNN(-1))

DLOG(FSM_OGI)  = DLOG(FSM_YFT)  + DLOG(FSM_YED)

FSM_GCR  = FSM_GCR(-1)  + ( FSM_OGC / FSM_YED - FSM_OGC(-1) / FSM_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (FSM_EXPH ) / FSM_YED  - (FSM_EXPH(-1) ) / FSM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (FSM_EXPE ) / FSM_YED  - (FSM_EXPE(-1) ) / FSM_YED(-1) )

FSM_IGR  = FSM_IGR(-1) + (FSM_OGI / FSM_YED - FSM_OGI(-1) / FSM_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (FSM_EXPH ) / FSM_YED  - (FSM_EXPH(-1) ) / FSM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (FSM_EXPE ) / FSM_YED  - (FSM_EXPE(-1) ) / FSM_YED(-1) )

FSM_GIP  = ( FSM_GIP(-1)  + ( FSM_GDN(-1) - FSM_GDN(-2) ) * FSM_GINT(-1) / 100  + FSM_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( FSM_GINT(-1) / 100 - FSM_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (FSM_GDFXSH * (FSM_EXR / FSM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - FSM_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY FSM_GLN  = FSM_REV  - FSM_EXP

@IDENTITY FSM_GLNRATIO  = FSM_GLN / FSM_YEN * 100

FSM_GLNT  = FSM_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

FSM_TFP  = FSM_LABSH * (FSM_TECHL  - FSM_TECHL(-1))

FSM_LABSH  = FSM_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY FSM_LFN  = FSM_LRX * FSM_POPWA

FSM_LRX  = FSM_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(FSM_YER(-1) / FSM_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY FSM_URX  = (1 - FSM_LNN / FSM_LFN) * 100

FSM_URXF  = FSM_URXF(-1) * FSM_URX / FSM_URX(-1) * FSM_LNN / FSM_LNNF / (FSM_LNN(-1) / FSM_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(FSM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(FSM_PCR  / FSM_POPT)

FSM_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(FSM_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

FSM_HEAD19  = FSM_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI^2)  , FSM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

FSM_HEAD55  = FSM_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI^2)  , FSM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(FSM_XTR)  = DLOG(FSM_WDR)  + (1  - FSM_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(FSM_XTDNO$  / FSM_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * FSM_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(FSM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (FSM_EXPH(-1) / FSM_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (FSM_EXPH(-1) / FSM_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(FSM_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(FSM_PM25)

FSM_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( FSM_EXPSP / FSM_YEN )

DLOG(FSM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - FSM_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (FSM_FINC - FSM_FINC(-1))

DLOG(FSM_PCR)  =  - 0.146156419169935  +  - 0.1686675892431 * (LOG(FSM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(FSM_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (FSM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.628450427003872  * DLOG(FSM_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.628450427003872)  * DLOG(FSM_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(FSM_HIC)  - FSM_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * FSM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * FSM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(FSM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(FSM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(FSM_IPR)  =  - 0.149469122778689  - 0.1 * (LOG(FSM_IPR(-1)  / FSM_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * FSM_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * FSM_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(FSM_PCR  + FSM_GCR(-1) + FSM_IGR(-1) + FSM_XTN  / FSM_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(FSM_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (FSM_USER - FSM_USER(-1))  - (0 * FSM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * FSM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - FSM_FUELSH - FSM_TOURSH)) * FSM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * FSM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * FSM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - FSM_FUELSH - FSM_TOURSH)) * FSM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(FSM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(FSM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(FSM_MTR)  =  - 0.124510838125463  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(FSM_MTR(-1))  - LOG(FSM_PCR(-1) + FSM_ITR(-1) + FSM_GCR(-1) + FSM_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(FSM_YFT(-1) / FSM_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(FSM_CMUD(-1) * FSM_EXR(-1)  / FSM_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * FSM_OMS * LOG(FSM_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.104500712196606  * DLOG(FSM_XTR)  + 0.371211282324113  * DLOG(FSM_PCR)  + 0.144951242674359  * DLOG(FSM_IPR)  + 0.261492812765416  * DLOG(FSM_GCR + FSM_IGR)

FSM_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * FSM_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * FSM_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * FSM_OILC

FSM_POIL  = FSM_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( FSM_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - FSM_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

FSM_PG  = FSM_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( FSM_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - FSM_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

FSM_PC  = FSM_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( FSM_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - FSM_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(FSM_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

FSM_PE  = FSM_PE(-1) * ( FSM_OILC(-1) / (FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) * FSM_POIL / FSM_POIL(-1)  + FSM_GASC(-1) / (FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) * FSM_PG / FSM_PG(-1)  + FSM_COALC(-1) / (FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) * FSM_PC / FSM_PC(-1)  + FSM_RC(-1) / (FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) * FSM_PR / FSM_PR(-1) )

D(FSM_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(FSM_PM25)  = 0.2 * (FSM_COALC(-1) / FSM_EC(-1) - FSM_COALC(-2) / FSM_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (FSM_COALC(-2) / FSM_EC(-2) - FSM_COALC(-3) / FSM_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (FSM_OILC(-1) / FSM_EC(-1) - FSM_OILC(-2) / FSM_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (FSM_OILC(-2) / FSM_EC(-2) - FSM_OILC(-3) / FSM_EC(-3))

DLOG(FSM_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(FSM_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(FSM_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(FSM_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(FSM_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FSM_PE * FSM_EXR / FSM_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FSM_PE(-1) * FSM_EXR(-1) / FSM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FSM_PE(-2) * FSM_EXR(-2) / FSM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(FSM_PE(-3) * FSM_EXR(-3) / FSM_HIC(-3))  - (FSM_EFF - FSM_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(FSM_COALC)  = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(FSM_COALC(-1) / FSM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(FSM_PE(-1) / FSM_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) / FSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(FSM_GASC)  = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(FSM_GASC(-1) / FSM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.1 / 0.01 * LOG(FSM_PE(-1) / FSM_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) / FSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(FSM_RC)  = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( FSM_RC(-1) / FSM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.0119175966870218 * LOG(FSM_PE(-1) / FSM_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) / FSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(FSM_OILC)  = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( FSM_OILC(-1) / FSM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.1 / 0.0119175966870218 * LOG(FSM_PE(-1) / FSM_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((FSM_COALC(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1) + FSM_OILC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)) / FSM_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY FSM_EXR  = 1

DLOG(MNG_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(MNG_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MNG_MTD)  + 0.4 * (MNG_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (MNG_YER / MNG_YFT  - MNG_YER(-1) / MNG_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + MNG_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + MNG_GCARB / MNG_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (MNG_PREM - MNG_PREM(-1)) / 100

MNG_YED  = MNG_YED(-1) * MNG_HIC / MNG_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_INT  = MNG_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_LTI  = MNG_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (MNG_INT - MNG_INT(-1))  + (MNG_PREM  - MNG_PREM(-1)) / 100

MNG_PREM  = MNG_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (MNG_GDNRATIO(-1)  - MNG_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(MNG_LNN)  = DLOG(MNG_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(MNG_LNN(-1))  - LOG(MNG_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(MNG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MNG_LNNF)  = DLOG(MNG_LNN)

MNG_FUELSH  = MNG_FUELSH(-1)

MNG_TAXR  = MNG_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MNG_GLNT(-1)  - MNG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MNG_YEN(-1) / ( ( MNG_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (MNG_YER(-2)  + MNG_GDI(-2)) * MNG_YED(-2) * (MNG_LNN(-1) / MNG_LNN(-2)  + MNG_TECHL(-1) - MNG_TECHL(-2) ) ) + MNG_REMIT(-1)  + MNG_EXPSP(-1) ) * MNG_SOLV

MNG_CTAXR  = MNG_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MNG_GLNT(-1)  - MNG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MNG_YEN(-1) / ( MNG_PROF(-1) ) * MNG_SOLV

(MNG_OGC)  = MNG_OGC(-1) * (MNG_YFT / MNG_YFT(-1) * MNG_YED / MNG_YED(-1))

MNG_USER  = (MNG_LTI  - MNG_INFT  + MNG_DEP * 100) / (1  - MNG_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (MNG_GCARB / MNG_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY MNG_XTN  = MNG_XTD$ * MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") * MNG_XTR

@IDENTITY MNG_YEN  = MNG_YER  * MNG_YED

@IDENTITY MNG_MTN  = MNG_MTD  * MNG_MTR

@IDENTITY MNG_XTN$  = MNG_XTN / MNG_EXR

@IDENTITY MNG_YEN$  = MNG_YEN / MNG_EXR

@IDENTITY MNG_MTN$  = MNG_MTN / MNG_EXR

@IDENTITY MNG_MTR$  = MNG_MTR$(-1) * MNG_MTR / MNG_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_XTR$  = MNG_XTR$(-1) * MNG_XTR / MNG_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_YER$  = MNG_YER$(-1) * MNG_YER / MNG_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_YFT$  = MNG_YFT$(-1) * MNG_YFT / MNG_YFT(-1)

MNG_POPT  = MNG_POPT(-1)  - MNG_LIVES

MNG_POPWA  = MNG_POPWA(-1) * MNG_POPT / MNG_POPT(-1)

MNG_SCR  = MNG_SCR(-1)  + ((MNG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MNG_YFT(-1) / MNG_YER(-1)  - MNG_YFT(-2) / MNG_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY MNG_ITR  = MNG_IGR  + MNG_IPR

@IDENTITY MNG_YER  = MNG_PCR  + MNG_GCR  + MNG_ITR  + MNG_SCR  + MNG_XTR  - MNG_MTR

@IDENTITY MNG_PROF  = (MNG_YEN - MNG_ITAX) * (1 - MNG_LABSH)

@IDENTITY MNG_GDI  = MNG_YER  - MNG_XTR  + MNG_MTR  + MNG_XTN  / ((MNG_YEN  - MNG_XTN  + MNG_MTN)  / (MNG_YER  - MNG_XTR  + MNG_MTR))  - MNG_MTN  / ((MNG_YEN  - MNG_XTN  + MNG_MTN)  / (MNG_YER  - MNG_XTR  + MNG_MTR))

@IDENTITY MNG_RPDI  = MNG_LABSH * 0.5 * (MNG_YER(-1)  + MNG_GDI(-1)) * MNG_YED(-1) / MNG_HIC(-1) * (MNG_LNN / MNG_LNN(-1)  + MNG_TECHL - MNG_TECHL(-1)) + MNG_REMIT / MNG_HIC  + MNG_EXPSP / MNG_HIC  - MNG_TAX / MNG_HIC

DLOG(MNG_YFT)  = (1 - MNG_ALPHA - MNG_LABSH) * DLOG(MNG_K(-1) / MNG_LFN(-1))  + (1 - MNG_ALPHA) * DLOG(MNG_LFN)  + MNG_LABSH * D(MNG_TECHL)  + MNG_ALPHA * (DLOG(MNG_EC)  + D(MNG_EFF) )  - ( MNG_CLIMLOSS / MNG_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (MNG_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY MNG_K  = MNG_K(-1) * (1 - MNG_DEP) + MNG_ITR

DLOG(MNG_MTD)  = (1  - MNG_OMS) * ( DLOG(MNG_CMUD)  + DLOG(MNG_EXR) )  + MNG_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MNG_EXR) )

DLOG(MNG_XTD$)  = (1  - MNG_OXS) * DLOG(MNG_XTDNO$)  + MNG_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

MNG_INFT  = 0.95 * MNG_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

MNG_OXS  = MNG_OXS(-1)

MNG_OMS  = MNG_OMS(-1) * ((MNG_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * MNG_EXR(-1) / MNG_MTN(-1)) / (MNG_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * MNG_EXR(-2) / MNG_MTN(-2)))^0.25

MNG_CXS  = MNG_CXS(-1)

MNG_FINC  = MNG_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_CAN  = MNG_XTN / MNG_EXR  - MNG_MTN / MNG_EXR  + MNG_REMIT / MNG_EXR  + MNG_CANOTH

@IDENTITY MNG_CANRATIO  = MNG_CAN / MNG_YEN$ * 100

MNG_CANOTH  = MNG_CANOTH(-1)  + ((MNG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MNG_YEN$  / MNG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MNG_REVG / MNG_EXR  - MNG_REVG(-1) / MNG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(MNG_EFEX)  =  - LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.198001397E-07 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.633040748E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003258733498 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.751333796E-05 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006033458986 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.601397291E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.175801509E-08 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.38731143E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.5747364976 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.156555109E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004698707688 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004186546436 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003092984541 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001061962222 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004212737301 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04774353882 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0100139159 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.293712746E-11 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005199218763 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.585574634E-06 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.142591215E-05 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001810660254 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.560050157E-10 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.180924121E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.230096007E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.189619474E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002276886314 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.48954451E-05 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.170796784E-06 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004688809378 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0326026488 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006066909114 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0560972936 * LOG(GBR_EXR / MNG_REMIT  = MNG_REMIT(-1) / MNG_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01139929139 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001716977643 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01048472653 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05588121582 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01812836502 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008786879264 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003289065129 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3742297957 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007362972878 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2638380786 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003690136001 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002936005787 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007389816238 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004127541369 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2197263704 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01015187215 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005756772586 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * MNG_EXR

MNG_GINT  = MNG_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 4 * (MNG_LTI  - MNG_LTI(-1))

MNG_GDN  = MNG_GDN(-1) * (MNG_GDFXSH  * (MNG_EXR  / MNG_EXR(-1))  + (1  - MNG_GDFXSH))  - MNG_GLN

@IDENTITY MNG_GDNRATIO  = MNG_GDN / MNG_YEN * 100

MNG_GDFXSH  = ( MNG_GDFXSH(-1) * (MNG_EXR / MNG_EXR(-1) )) / (MNG_GDFXSH(-1) * (MNG_EXR / MNG_EXR(-1))  + 1 - MNG_GDFXSH(-1) )

MNG_TOURSH  = MNG_TOURSH(-1)

MNG_LOCK  = 0

MNG_GCARBR  = MNG_GCARBR(-1)

MNG_GTRADER  = MNG_GTRADER(-1)

MNG_ITAXR  = MNG_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_REV  = MNG_TAX  + MNG_CTAX  + MNG_ITAX  + MNG_GTRADE  + MNG_REVG  + MNG_GCARB  + MNG_GCOM  + MNG_GOTH

@IDENTITY MNG_TAX  = MNG_TAXR * (MNG_LABSH * 0.5 * (MNG_YER(-1)  + MNG_GDI(-1)) * MNG_YED(-1) * (MNG_LNN / MNG_LNN(-1)  + MNG_TECHL - MNG_TECHL(-1)) + MNG_REMIT  + MNG_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY MNG_CTAX  = MNG_CTAXR * MNG_PROF

@IDENTITY MNG_ITAX  = MNG_ITAXR * (MNG_PCR * MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY MNG_GTRADE  = MNG_GTRADER * MNG_XTN

MNG_REVG  = MNG_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (MNG_YER$ / MNG_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - MNG_YER$(-1) / MNG_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * MNG_EXR / MNG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_GCARB  = MNG_GCARBR * MNG_CO2 * MNG_EXR / 1000

MNG_GCOM  = MNG_GCOM(-1) * ( MNG_OILC / (MNG_OILC + MNG_GASC + MNG_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + MNG_GASC / (MNG_OILC + MNG_GASC + MNG_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + MNG_COALC / (MNG_OILC + MNG_GASC + MNG_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

MNG_GOTH  = MNG_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_EXP  = MNG_EXPE  + MNG_EXPH  + MNG_EXPSP  + MNG_OGC  + MNG_OGI  + MNG_GIP

MNG_EXPE  = MNG_EXPE(-1) * (MNG_YFT / MNG_YFT(-1)) * (MNG_YED / MNG_YED(-1))

MNG_EXPH = MNG_EXPH(-1) * (MNG_YFT / MNG_YFT(-1)) * (MNG_YED / MNG_YED(-1))

MNG_EXPSP  = MNG_EXPSP(-1) * (MNG_YFT / MNG_YFT(-1)) * (MNG_YED / MNG_YED(-1)) * (MNG_POPT - MNG_LNN) / (MNG_POPT(-1) - MNG_LNN(-1))

DLOG(MNG_OGI)  = DLOG(MNG_YFT)  + DLOG(MNG_YED)

MNG_GCR  = MNG_GCR(-1)  + ( MNG_OGC / MNG_YED - MNG_OGC(-1) / MNG_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (MNG_EXPH ) / MNG_YED  - (MNG_EXPH(-1) ) / MNG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MNG_EXPE ) / MNG_YED  - (MNG_EXPE(-1) ) / MNG_YED(-1) )

MNG_IGR  = MNG_IGR(-1) + (MNG_OGI / MNG_YED - MNG_OGI(-1) / MNG_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (MNG_EXPH ) / MNG_YED  - (MNG_EXPH(-1) ) / MNG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MNG_EXPE ) / MNG_YED  - (MNG_EXPE(-1) ) / MNG_YED(-1) )

MNG_GIP  = ( MNG_GIP(-1)  + ( MNG_GDN(-1) - MNG_GDN(-2) ) * MNG_GINT(-1) / 100  + MNG_GDN(-5) / 4 * ( MNG_GINT(-1) / 100 - MNG_GINT(-5) / 100 ) ) * (MNG_GDFXSH * (MNG_EXR / MNG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MNG_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY MNG_GLN  = MNG_REV  - MNG_EXP

@IDENTITY MNG_GLNRATIO  = MNG_GLN / MNG_YEN * 100

MNG_GLNT  = MNG_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

MNG_TFP  = MNG_LABSH * (MNG_TECHL  - MNG_TECHL(-1))

MNG_LABSH  = MNG_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY MNG_LFN  = MNG_LRX * MNG_POPWA

MNG_LRX  = MNG_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(MNG_YER(-1) / MNG_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY MNG_URX  = (1 - MNG_LNN / MNG_LFN) * 100

MNG_URXF  = MNG_URXF(-1) * MNG_URX / MNG_URX(-1) * MNG_LNN / MNG_LNNF / (MNG_LNN(-1) / MNG_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(MNG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MNG_PCR  / MNG_POPT)

MNG_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(MNG_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

MNG_HEAD19  = MNG_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI^2)  , MNG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

MNG_HEAD55  = MNG_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI^2)  , MNG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(MNG_XTR)  = DLOG(MNG_WDR)  + (1  - MNG_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(MNG_XTDNO$  / MNG_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * MNG_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(MNG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (MNG_EXPH(-1) / MNG_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (MNG_EXPH(-1) / MNG_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(MNG_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(MNG_PM25)

MNG_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( MNG_EXPSP / MNG_YEN )

DLOG(MNG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - MNG_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (MNG_FINC - MNG_FINC(-1))

DLOG(MNG_PCR)  =  - 0.0947911682196147  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(MNG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MNG_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (MNG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MNG_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(MNG_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(MNG_HIC)  - MNG_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * MNG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * MNG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MNG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MNG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MNG_IPR)  =  - 0.132206748297085  - 0.1 * (LOG(MNG_IPR(-1)  / MNG_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * MNG_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * MNG_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(MNG_PCR  + MNG_GCR(-1) + MNG_IGR(-1) + MNG_XTN  / MNG_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(MNG_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (MNG_USER - MNG_USER(-1))  - (0 * MNG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MNG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MNG_FUELSH - MNG_TOURSH)) * MNG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * MNG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MNG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MNG_FUELSH - MNG_TOURSH)) * MNG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MNG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MNG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MNG_MTR)  =  - 0.0770428625305756  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(MNG_MTR(-1))  - LOG(MNG_PCR(-1) + MNG_ITR(-1) + MNG_GCR(-1) + MNG_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(MNG_YFT(-1) / MNG_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(MNG_CMUD(-1) * MNG_EXR(-1)  / MNG_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * MNG_OMS * LOG(MNG_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.260512693670601  * DLOG(MNG_XTR)  + 0.405187448575298  * DLOG(MNG_PCR)  + 0.171431562317769  * DLOG(MNG_IPR)  + 0.133232312566925  * DLOG(MNG_GCR + MNG_IGR)

MNG_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * MNG_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * MNG_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * MNG_OILC

MNG_POIL  = MNG_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( MNG_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - MNG_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

MNG_PG  = MNG_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( MNG_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - MNG_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

MNG_PC  = MNG_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( MNG_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - MNG_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(MNG_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

MNG_PE  = MNG_PE(-1) * ( MNG_OILC(-1) / (MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) * MNG_POIL / MNG_POIL(-1)  + MNG_GASC(-1) / (MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) * MNG_PG / MNG_PG(-1)  + MNG_COALC(-1) / (MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) * MNG_PC / MNG_PC(-1)  + MNG_RC(-1) / (MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) * MNG_PR / MNG_PR(-1) )

D(MNG_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(MNG_PM25)  = 0.2 * (MNG_COALC(-1) / MNG_EC(-1) - MNG_COALC(-2) / MNG_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (MNG_COALC(-2) / MNG_EC(-2) - MNG_COALC(-3) / MNG_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (MNG_OILC(-1) / MNG_EC(-1) - MNG_OILC(-2) / MNG_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (MNG_OILC(-2) / MNG_EC(-2) - MNG_OILC(-3) / MNG_EC(-3))

DLOG(MNG_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(MNG_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(MNG_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(MNG_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MNG_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MNG_PE * MNG_EXR / MNG_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MNG_PE(-1) * MNG_EXR(-1) / MNG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MNG_PE(-2) * MNG_EXR(-2) / MNG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MNG_PE(-3) * MNG_EXR(-3) / MNG_HIC(-3))  - (MNG_EFF - MNG_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(MNG_COALC)  = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MNG_COALC(-1) / MNG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.0341690938492059 * LOG(MNG_PE(-1) / MNG_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) / MNG_EC(-1))

DLOG(MNG_GASC)  = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MNG_GASC(-1) / MNG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(MNG_PE(-1) / MNG_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) / MNG_EC(-1))

DLOG(MNG_RC)  = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MNG_RC(-1) / MNG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0341690938492059 * LOG(MNG_PE(-1) / MNG_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) / MNG_EC(-1))

DLOG(MNG_OILC)  = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MNG_OILC(-1) / MNG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0341690938492059 * LOG(MNG_PE(-1) / MNG_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MNG_COALC(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1) + MNG_OILC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)) / MNG_EC(-1))

MNG_EXR  = MNG_EXR(-1) * ( ( (MNG_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (MNG_INT  - USA_INT)  - (MNG_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(MMR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(MMR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MMR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (MMR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (MMR_YER / MMR_YFT  - MMR_YER(-1) / MMR_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + MMR_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + MMR_GCARB / MMR_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (MMR_PREM - MMR_PREM(-1)) / 100

MMR_YED  = MMR_YED(-1) * MMR_HIC / MMR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_INT  = MMR_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_LTI  = MMR_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (MMR_INT - MMR_INT(-1))  + (MMR_PREM  - MMR_PREM(-1)) / 100

MMR_PREM  = MMR_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (MMR_GDNRATIO(-1)  - MMR_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(MMR_LNN)  = DLOG(MMR_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(MMR_LNN(-1))  - LOG(MMR_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(MMR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MMR_LNNF)  = DLOG(MMR_LNN)

MMR_FUELSH  = MMR_FUELSH(-1)

MMR_TAXR  = MMR_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MMR_GLNT(-1)  - MMR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MMR_YEN(-1) / ( ( MMR_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (MMR_YER(-2)  + MMR_GDI(-2)) * MMR_YED(-2) * (MMR_LNN(-1) / MMR_LNN(-2)  + MMR_TECHL(-1) - MMR_TECHL(-2) ) ) + MMR_REMIT(-1)  + MMR_EXPSP(-1) ) * MMR_SOLV

MMR_CTAXR  = MMR_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( MMR_GLNT(-1)  - MMR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * MMR_YEN(-1) / ( MMR_PROF(-1) ) * MMR_SOLV

(MMR_OGC)  = MMR_OGC(-1) * (MMR_YFT / MMR_YFT(-1) * MMR_YED / MMR_YED(-1))

MMR_USER  = (MMR_LTI  - MMR_INFT  + MMR_DEP * 100) / (1  - MMR_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (MMR_GCARB / MMR_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY MMR_XTN  = MMR_XTD$ * MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") * MMR_XTR

@IDENTITY MMR_YEN  = MMR_YER  * MMR_YED

@IDENTITY MMR_MTN  = MMR_MTD  * MMR_MTR

@IDENTITY MMR_XTN$  = MMR_XTN / MMR_EXR

@IDENTITY MMR_YEN$  = MMR_YEN / MMR_EXR

@IDENTITY MMR_MTN$  = MMR_MTN / MMR_EXR

@IDENTITY MMR_MTR$  = MMR_MTR$(-1) * MMR_MTR / MMR_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_XTR$  = MMR_XTR$(-1) * MMR_XTR / MMR_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_YER$  = MMR_YER$(-1) * MMR_YER / MMR_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_YFT$  = MMR_YFT$(-1) * MMR_YFT / MMR_YFT(-1)

MMR_POPT  = MMR_POPT(-1)  - MMR_LIVES

MMR_POPWA  = MMR_POPWA(-1) * MMR_POPT / MMR_POPT(-1)

MMR_SCR  = MMR_SCR(-1)  + ((MMR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MMR_YFT(-1) / MMR_YER(-1)  - MMR_YFT(-2) / MMR_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY MMR_ITR  = MMR_IGR  + MMR_IPR

@IDENTITY MMR_YER  = MMR_PCR  + MMR_GCR  + MMR_ITR  + MMR_SCR  + MMR_XTR  - MMR_MTR

@IDENTITY MMR_PROF  = (MMR_YEN - MMR_ITAX) * (1 - MMR_LABSH)

@IDENTITY MMR_GDI  = MMR_YER  - MMR_XTR  + MMR_MTR  + MMR_XTN  / ((MMR_YEN  - MMR_XTN  + MMR_MTN)  / (MMR_YER  - MMR_XTR  + MMR_MTR))  - MMR_MTN  / ((MMR_YEN  - MMR_XTN  + MMR_MTN)  / (MMR_YER  - MMR_XTR  + MMR_MTR))

@IDENTITY MMR_RPDI  = MMR_LABSH * 0.5 * (MMR_YER(-1)  + MMR_GDI(-1)) * MMR_YED(-1) / MMR_HIC(-1) * (MMR_LNN / MMR_LNN(-1)  + MMR_TECHL - MMR_TECHL(-1)) + MMR_REMIT / MMR_HIC  + MMR_EXPSP / MMR_HIC  - MMR_TAX / MMR_HIC

DLOG(MMR_YFT)  = (1 - MMR_ALPHA - MMR_LABSH) * DLOG(MMR_K(-1) / MMR_LFN(-1))  + (1 - MMR_ALPHA) * DLOG(MMR_LFN)  + MMR_LABSH * D(MMR_TECHL)  + MMR_ALPHA * (DLOG(MMR_EC)  + D(MMR_EFF) )  - ( MMR_CLIMLOSS / MMR_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (MMR_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY MMR_K  = MMR_K(-1) * (1 - MMR_DEP) + MMR_ITR

DLOG(MMR_MTD)  = (1  - MMR_OMS) * ( DLOG(MMR_CMUD)  + DLOG(MMR_EXR) )  + MMR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MMR_EXR) )

DLOG(MMR_XTD$)  = (1  - MMR_OXS) * DLOG(MMR_XTDNO$)  + MMR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

MMR_INFT  = 0.95 * MMR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

MMR_OXS  = MMR_OXS(-1)

MMR_OMS  = MMR_OMS(-1) * ((MMR_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * MMR_EXR(-1) / MMR_MTN(-1)) / (MMR_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * MMR_EXR(-2) / MMR_MTN(-2)))^0.25

MMR_CXS  = MMR_CXS(-1)

MMR_FINC  = MMR_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_CAN  = MMR_XTN / MMR_EXR  - MMR_MTN / MMR_EXR  + MMR_REMIT / MMR_EXR  + MMR_CANOTH

@IDENTITY MMR_CANRATIO  = MMR_CAN / MMR_YEN$ * 100

MMR_CANOTH  = MMR_CANOTH(-1)  + ((MMR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MMR_YEN$  / MMR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MMR_REVG / MMR_EXR  - MMR_REVG(-1) / MMR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(MMR_EFEX)  =  - LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001554005392 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.669662571E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004051090689 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.932697057E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001897427049 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.016330416E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.487467865E-05 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.119178712E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.3856000898 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.773682423E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.971690988E-07 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01026567312 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0614511369 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02200240473 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001626809665 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04616360356 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.936132441E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.498143426E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.391075213E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.922047775E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005061593437 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02383297154 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.435182617E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.951240321E-06 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.368177506E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008740305099 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001416690241 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.711795785E-05 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001319505499 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02726530018 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004822059078 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001529185385 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09635968912 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.863975092E-06 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005233355425 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.000581249E-06 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1961991811 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.693720268E-06 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.642647898E-06 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009809527937 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.423938318E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.679998259E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.149816499E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01325441108 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01172376068 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009720720744 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007169493125 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005633266871 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003764717881 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003253900329 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005063908138 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008445906404 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007543057519 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003339114523 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01546537113 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0110773187 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.018922893 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(MMR_REFEX )  =  - LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001554005392 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.669662571E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004051090689 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.932697057E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001897427049 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.016330416E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.487467865E-05 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.119178712E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.3856000898 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.773682423E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.971690988E-07 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01026567312 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0614511369 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02200240473 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001626809665 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04616360356 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.936132441E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.498143426E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.391075213E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.922047775E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005061593437 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02383297154 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.435182617E-06 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.951240321E-06 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.368177506E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008740305099 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001416690241 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.711795785E-05 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001319505499 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02726530018 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004822059078 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001529185385 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.09635968912 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.863975092E-06 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005233355425 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.000581249E-06 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1961991811 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.693720268E-06 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.642647898E-06 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0009809527937 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.423938318E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.679998259E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.149816499E-06 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01325441108 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01172376068 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009720720744 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007169493125 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005633266871 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003764717881 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003253900329 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005063908138 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008445906404 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007543057519 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003339114523 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01546537113 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0110773187 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.018922893 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

MMR_REMIT  = MMR_REMIT(-1) / MMR_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009852631051 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04077013956 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 8.824098398E-06 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001201238198 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01118713026 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000430353063 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001768121001 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003758358746 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01173917872 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001108079239 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001214347328 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 3.988419544E-05 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 1.078941811E-05 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001777053584 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 6.308751367E-05 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 1.336376094E-05 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02678184694 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004238628234 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0008107281586 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02058281852 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001046778798 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001918628289 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5378897519 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05374410709 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002197893785 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 3.966864234E-07 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 6.797332832E-05 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003517912041 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002342086581 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2711641089 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * MMR_EXR

MMR_GINT  = MMR_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (MMR_LTI  - MMR_LTI(-1))

MMR_GDN  = MMR_GDN(-1) * (MMR_GDFXSH  * (MMR_EXR  / MMR_EXR(-1))  + (1  - MMR_GDFXSH))  - MMR_GLN

@IDENTITY MMR_GDNRATIO  = MMR_GDN / MMR_YEN * 100

MMR_GDFXSH  = ( MMR_GDFXSH(-1) * (MMR_EXR / MMR_EXR(-1) )) / (MMR_GDFXSH(-1) * (MMR_EXR / MMR_EXR(-1))  + 1 - MMR_GDFXSH(-1) )

MMR_TOURSH  = MMR_TOURSH(-1)

MMR_LOCK  = 0

MMR_GCARBR  = MMR_GCARBR(-1)

MMR_GTRADER  = MMR_GTRADER(-1)

MMR_ITAXR  = MMR_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_REV  = MMR_TAX  + MMR_CTAX  + MMR_ITAX  + MMR_GTRADE  + MMR_REVG  + MMR_GCARB  + MMR_GCOM  + MMR_GOTH

@IDENTITY MMR_TAX  = MMR_TAXR * (MMR_LABSH * 0.5 * (MMR_YER(-1)  + MMR_GDI(-1)) * MMR_YED(-1) * (MMR_LNN / MMR_LNN(-1)  + MMR_TECHL - MMR_TECHL(-1)) + MMR_REMIT  + MMR_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY MMR_CTAX  = MMR_CTAXR * MMR_PROF

@IDENTITY MMR_ITAX  = MMR_ITAXR * (MMR_PCR * MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY MMR_GTRADE  = MMR_GTRADER * MMR_XTN

MMR_REVG  = MMR_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (MMR_YER$ / MMR_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - MMR_YER$(-1) / MMR_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * MMR_EXR / MMR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_GCARB  = MMR_GCARBR * MMR_CO2 * MMR_EXR / 1000

MMR_GCOM  = MMR_GCOM(-1) * ( MMR_OILC / (MMR_OILC + MMR_GASC + MMR_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + MMR_GASC / (MMR_OILC + MMR_GASC + MMR_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + MMR_COALC / (MMR_OILC + MMR_GASC + MMR_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

MMR_GOTH  = MMR_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_EXP  = MMR_EXPE  + MMR_EXPH  + MMR_EXPSP  + MMR_OGC  + MMR_OGI  + MMR_GIP

MMR_EXPE  = MMR_EXPE(-1) * (MMR_YFT / MMR_YFT(-1)) * (MMR_YED / MMR_YED(-1))

MMR_EXPH = MMR_EXPH(-1) * (MMR_YFT / MMR_YFT(-1)) * (MMR_YED / MMR_YED(-1))

MMR_EXPSP  = MMR_EXPSP(-1) * (MMR_YFT / MMR_YFT(-1)) * (MMR_YED / MMR_YED(-1)) * (MMR_POPT - MMR_LNN) / (MMR_POPT(-1) - MMR_LNN(-1))

DLOG(MMR_OGI)  = DLOG(MMR_YFT)  + DLOG(MMR_YED)

MMR_GCR  = MMR_GCR(-1)  + ( MMR_OGC / MMR_YED - MMR_OGC(-1) / MMR_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (MMR_EXPH ) / MMR_YED  - (MMR_EXPH(-1) ) / MMR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MMR_EXPE ) / MMR_YED  - (MMR_EXPE(-1) ) / MMR_YED(-1) )

MMR_IGR  = MMR_IGR(-1) + (MMR_OGI / MMR_YED - MMR_OGI(-1) / MMR_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (MMR_EXPH ) / MMR_YED  - (MMR_EXPH(-1) ) / MMR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (MMR_EXPE ) / MMR_YED  - (MMR_EXPE(-1) ) / MMR_YED(-1) )

MMR_GIP  = ( MMR_GIP(-1)  + ( MMR_GDN(-1) - MMR_GDN(-2) ) * MMR_GINT(-1) / 100  + MMR_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( MMR_GINT(-1) / 100 - MMR_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (MMR_GDFXSH * (MMR_EXR / MMR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MMR_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY MMR_GLN  = MMR_REV  - MMR_EXP

@IDENTITY MMR_GLNRATIO  = MMR_GLN / MMR_YEN * 100

MMR_GLNT  = MMR_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

MMR_TFP  = MMR_LABSH * (MMR_TECHL  - MMR_TECHL(-1))

MMR_LABSH  = MMR_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY MMR_LFN  = MMR_LRX * MMR_POPWA

MMR_LRX  = MMR_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(MMR_YER(-1) / MMR_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY MMR_URX  = (1 - MMR_LNN / MMR_LFN) * 100

MMR_URXF  = MMR_URXF(-1) * MMR_URX / MMR_URX(-1) * MMR_LNN / MMR_LNNF / (MMR_LNN(-1) / MMR_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(MMR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MMR_PCR  / MMR_POPT)

MMR_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(MMR_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

MMR_HEAD19  = MMR_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MMR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI^2)  , MMR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MMR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MMR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

MMR_HEAD55  = MMR_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MMR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI^2)  , MMR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MMR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MMR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(MMR_XTR)  = DLOG(MMR_WDR)  + (1  - MMR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(MMR_XTDNO$  / MMR_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * MMR_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(MMR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (MMR_EXPH(-1) / MMR_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (MMR_EXPH(-1) / MMR_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(MMR_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(MMR_PM25)

MMR_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( MMR_EXPSP / MMR_YEN )

DLOG(MMR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - MMR_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (MMR_FINC - MMR_FINC(-1))

DLOG(MMR_PCR)  =  - 0.0101208745414079  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(MMR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MMR_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (MMR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.543784131035776  * DLOG(MMR_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.543784131035776)  * DLOG(MMR_POPT)  +  - 0.268201003401917 * (DLOG(MMR_HIC)  - MMR_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * MMR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * MMR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MMR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MMR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MMR_IPR)  =  - 0.0672466181104722  - 0.1 * (LOG(MMR_IPR(-1)  / MMR_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * MMR_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * MMR_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(MMR_PCR  + MMR_GCR(-1) + MMR_IGR(-1) + MMR_XTN  / MMR_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(MMR_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (MMR_USER - MMR_USER(-1))  - (0 * MMR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MMR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MMR_FUELSH - MMR_TOURSH)) * MMR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * MMR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * MMR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - MMR_FUELSH - MMR_TOURSH)) * MMR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(MMR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(MMR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(MMR_MTR)  =  - 0.16098561198167  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(MMR_MTR(-1))  - LOG(MMR_PCR(-1) + MMR_ITR(-1) + MMR_GCR(-1) + MMR_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(MMR_YFT(-1) / MMR_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(MMR_CMUD(-1) * MMR_EXR(-1)  / MMR_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * MMR_OMS * LOG(MMR_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.289400075201086  * DLOG(MMR_XTR)  + 0.110796258056772  * DLOG(MMR_PCR)  + 0.310552700093614  * DLOG(MMR_IPR)  + 0.0283095821597151  * DLOG(MMR_GCR + MMR_IGR)

MMR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * MMR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * MMR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * MMR_OILC

MMR_POIL  = MMR_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( MMR_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - MMR_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

MMR_PG  = MMR_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( MMR_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - MMR_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

MMR_PC  = MMR_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( MMR_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - MMR_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(MMR_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

MMR_PE  = MMR_PE(-1) * ( MMR_OILC(-1) / (MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) * MMR_POIL / MMR_POIL(-1)  + MMR_GASC(-1) / (MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) * MMR_PG / MMR_PG(-1)  + MMR_COALC(-1) / (MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) * MMR_PC / MMR_PC(-1)  + MMR_RC(-1) / (MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) * MMR_PR / MMR_PR(-1) )

D(MMR_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(MMR_PM25)  = 0.2 * (MMR_COALC(-1) / MMR_EC(-1) - MMR_COALC(-2) / MMR_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (MMR_COALC(-2) / MMR_EC(-2) - MMR_COALC(-3) / MMR_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (MMR_OILC(-1) / MMR_EC(-1) - MMR_OILC(-2) / MMR_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (MMR_OILC(-2) / MMR_EC(-2) - MMR_OILC(-3) / MMR_EC(-3))

DLOG(MMR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(MMR_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(MMR_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(MMR_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MMR_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MMR_PE * MMR_EXR / MMR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MMR_PE(-1) * MMR_EXR(-1) / MMR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MMR_PE(-2) * MMR_EXR(-2) / MMR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(MMR_PE(-3) * MMR_EXR(-3) / MMR_HIC(-3))  - (MMR_EFF - MMR_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(MMR_COALC)  = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MMR_COALC(-1) / MMR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.612974262850422 * LOG(MMR_PE(-1) / MMR_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) / MMR_EC(-1))

DLOG(MMR_GASC)  = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(MMR_GASC(-1) / MMR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.145639493450298 * LOG(MMR_PE(-1) / MMR_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) / MMR_EC(-1))

DLOG(MMR_RC)  = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MMR_RC(-1) / MMR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.612974262850422 * LOG(MMR_PE(-1) / MMR_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) / MMR_EC(-1))

DLOG(MMR_OILC)  = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( MMR_OILC(-1) / MMR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.612974262850422 * LOG(MMR_PE(-1) / MMR_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((MMR_COALC(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1) + MMR_OILC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)) / MMR_EC(-1))

MMR_EXR  = MMR_EXR(-1) * ( (MMR_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(NPL_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(NPL_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(NPL_MTD)  + 0.4 * (NPL_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (NPL_YER / NPL_YFT  - NPL_YER(-1) / NPL_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + NPL_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + NPL_GCARB / NPL_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (NPL_PREM - NPL_PREM(-1)) / 100

NPL_YED  = NPL_YED(-1) * NPL_HIC / NPL_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_INT  = NPL_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_LTI  = NPL_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (NPL_INT - NPL_INT(-1))  + (NPL_PREM  - NPL_PREM(-1)) / 100

NPL_PREM  = NPL_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (NPL_GDNRATIO(-1)  - NPL_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(NPL_LNN)  = DLOG(NPL_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(NPL_LNN(-1))  - LOG(NPL_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(NPL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(NPL_LNNF)  = DLOG(NPL_LNN)

NPL_FUELSH  = NPL_FUELSH(-1)

NPL_TAXR  = NPL_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( NPL_GLNT(-1)  - NPL_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * NPL_YEN(-1) / ( ( NPL_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (NPL_YER(-2)  + NPL_GDI(-2)) * NPL_YED(-2) * (NPL_LNN(-1) / NPL_LNN(-2)  + NPL_TECHL(-1) - NPL_TECHL(-2) ) ) + NPL_REMIT(-1)  + NPL_EXPSP(-1) ) * NPL_SOLV

NPL_CTAXR  = NPL_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( NPL_GLNT(-1)  - NPL_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * NPL_YEN(-1) / ( NPL_PROF(-1) ) * NPL_SOLV

(NPL_OGC)  = NPL_OGC(-1) * (NPL_YFT / NPL_YFT(-1) * NPL_YED / NPL_YED(-1))

NPL_USER  = (NPL_LTI  - NPL_INFT  + NPL_DEP * 100) / (1  - NPL_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (NPL_GCARB / NPL_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY NPL_XTN  = NPL_XTD$ * NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") * NPL_XTR

@IDENTITY NPL_YEN  = NPL_YER  * NPL_YED

@IDENTITY NPL_MTN  = NPL_MTD  * NPL_MTR

@IDENTITY NPL_XTN$  = NPL_XTN / NPL_EXR

@IDENTITY NPL_YEN$  = NPL_YEN / NPL_EXR

@IDENTITY NPL_MTN$  = NPL_MTN / NPL_EXR

@IDENTITY NPL_MTR$  = NPL_MTR$(-1) * NPL_MTR / NPL_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_XTR$  = NPL_XTR$(-1) * NPL_XTR / NPL_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_YER$  = NPL_YER$(-1) * NPL_YER / NPL_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_YFT$  = NPL_YFT$(-1) * NPL_YFT / NPL_YFT(-1)

NPL_POPT  = NPL_POPT(-1)  - NPL_LIVES

NPL_POPWA  = NPL_POPWA(-1) * NPL_POPT / NPL_POPT(-1)

NPL_SCR  = NPL_SCR(-1)  + ((NPL_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (NPL_YFT(-1) / NPL_YER(-1)  - NPL_YFT(-2) / NPL_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY NPL_ITR  = NPL_IGR  + NPL_IPR

@IDENTITY NPL_YER  = NPL_PCR  + NPL_GCR  + NPL_ITR  + NPL_SCR  + NPL_XTR  - NPL_MTR

@IDENTITY NPL_PROF  = (NPL_YEN - NPL_ITAX) * (1 - NPL_LABSH)

@IDENTITY NPL_GDI  = NPL_YER  - NPL_XTR  + NPL_MTR  + NPL_XTN  / ((NPL_YEN  - NPL_XTN  + NPL_MTN)  / (NPL_YER  - NPL_XTR  + NPL_MTR))  - NPL_MTN  / ((NPL_YEN  - NPL_XTN  + NPL_MTN)  / (NPL_YER  - NPL_XTR  + NPL_MTR))

@IDENTITY NPL_RPDI  = NPL_LABSH * 0.5 * (NPL_YER(-1)  + NPL_GDI(-1)) * NPL_YED(-1) / NPL_HIC(-1) * (NPL_LNN / NPL_LNN(-1)  + NPL_TECHL - NPL_TECHL(-1)) + NPL_REMIT / NPL_HIC  + NPL_EXPSP / NPL_HIC  - NPL_TAX / NPL_HIC

DLOG(NPL_YFT)  = (1 - NPL_ALPHA - NPL_LABSH) * DLOG(NPL_K(-1) / NPL_LFN(-1))  + (1 - NPL_ALPHA) * DLOG(NPL_LFN)  + NPL_LABSH * D(NPL_TECHL)  + NPL_ALPHA * (DLOG(NPL_EC)  + D(NPL_EFF) )  - ( NPL_CLIMLOSS / NPL_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (NPL_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY NPL_K  = NPL_K(-1) * (1 - NPL_DEP) + NPL_ITR

DLOG(NPL_MTD)  = (1  - NPL_OMS) * ( DLOG(NPL_CMUD)  + DLOG(NPL_EXR) )  + NPL_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(NPL_EXR) )

DLOG(NPL_XTD$)  = (1  - NPL_OXS) * DLOG(NPL_XTDNO$)  + NPL_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

NPL_INFT  = 0.95 * NPL_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

NPL_OXS  = NPL_OXS(-1)

NPL_OMS  = NPL_OMS(-1) * ((NPL_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * NPL_EXR(-1) / NPL_MTN(-1)) / (NPL_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * NPL_EXR(-2) / NPL_MTN(-2)))^0.25

NPL_CXS  = NPL_CXS(-1)

NPL_FINC  = NPL_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_CAN  = NPL_XTN / NPL_EXR  - NPL_MTN / NPL_EXR  + NPL_REMIT / NPL_EXR  + NPL_CANOTH

@IDENTITY NPL_CANRATIO  = NPL_CAN / NPL_YEN$ * 100

NPL_CANOTH  = NPL_CANOTH(-1)  + ((NPL_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (NPL_YEN$  / NPL_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + NPL_REVG / NPL_EXR  - NPL_REVG(-1) / NPL_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(NPL_EFEX)  =  - LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004541353971 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.32598453E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.440959266E-07 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.939448088E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.915328504E-07 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003749260391 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02584604389 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01852767607 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004804335839 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01522983388 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003411485672 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003740399978 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001209027413 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008296156065 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001237428355 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002425449605 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01913764855 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007311199317 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04428294303 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

NPL_REMIT  = NPL_REMIT(-1) / NPL_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01541915231 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009219002189 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001799640799 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002140397869 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005300640678 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007893571178 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001718193425 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006217983391 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02063654602 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005078877147 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1469802163 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002723071754 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006867735908 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 1.091501292E-05 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005033838819 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02736028743 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000790214378 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006324761713 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 2.017589877E-05 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 6.287544755E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002865472418 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 6.045278913E-06 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04757757308 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004976357321 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 2.311958555E-07 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001118141272 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006152756651 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002057755697 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.7044736411 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * NPL_EXR

NPL_GINT  = NPL_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (NPL_LTI  - NPL_LTI(-1))

NPL_GDN  = NPL_GDN(-1) * (NPL_GDFXSH  * (NPL_EXR  / NPL_EXR(-1))  + (1  - NPL_GDFXSH))  - NPL_GLN

@IDENTITY NPL_GDNRATIO  = NPL_GDN / NPL_YEN * 100

NPL_GDFXSH  = ( NPL_GDFXSH(-1) * (NPL_EXR / NPL_EXR(-1) )) / (NPL_GDFXSH(-1) * (NPL_EXR / NPL_EXR(-1))  + 1 - NPL_GDFXSH(-1) )

NPL_TOURSH  = NPL_TOURSH(-1)

NPL_LOCK  = 0

NPL_GCARBR  = NPL_GCARBR(-1)

NPL_GTRADER  = NPL_GTRADER(-1)

NPL_ITAXR  = NPL_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_REV  = NPL_TAX  + NPL_CTAX  + NPL_ITAX  + NPL_GTRADE  + NPL_REVG  + NPL_GCARB  + NPL_GCOM  + NPL_GOTH

@IDENTITY NPL_TAX  = NPL_TAXR * (NPL_LABSH * 0.5 * (NPL_YER(-1)  + NPL_GDI(-1)) * NPL_YED(-1) * (NPL_LNN / NPL_LNN(-1)  + NPL_TECHL - NPL_TECHL(-1)) + NPL_REMIT  + NPL_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY NPL_CTAX  = NPL_CTAXR * NPL_PROF

@IDENTITY NPL_ITAX  = NPL_ITAXR * (NPL_PCR * NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY NPL_GTRADE  = NPL_GTRADER * NPL_XTN

NPL_REVG  = NPL_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (NPL_YER$ / NPL_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - NPL_YER$(-1) / NPL_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * NPL_EXR / NPL_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_GCARB  = NPL_GCARBR * NPL_CO2 * NPL_EXR / 1000

NPL_GCOM  = NPL_GCOM(-1) * ( NPL_OILC / (NPL_OILC + NPL_GASC + NPL_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + NPL_GASC / (NPL_OILC + NPL_GASC + NPL_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + NPL_COALC / (NPL_OILC + NPL_GASC + NPL_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

NPL_GOTH  = NPL_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_EXP  = NPL_EXPE  + NPL_EXPH  + NPL_EXPSP  + NPL_OGC  + NPL_OGI  + NPL_GIP

NPL_EXPE  = NPL_EXPE(-1) * (NPL_YFT / NPL_YFT(-1)) * (NPL_YED / NPL_YED(-1))

NPL_EXPH = NPL_EXPH(-1) * (NPL_YFT / NPL_YFT(-1)) * (NPL_YED / NPL_YED(-1))

NPL_EXPSP  = NPL_EXPSP(-1) * (NPL_YFT / NPL_YFT(-1)) * (NPL_YED / NPL_YED(-1)) * (NPL_POPT - NPL_LNN) / (NPL_POPT(-1) - NPL_LNN(-1))

DLOG(NPL_OGI)  = DLOG(NPL_YFT)  + DLOG(NPL_YED)

NPL_GCR  = NPL_GCR(-1)  + ( NPL_OGC / NPL_YED - NPL_OGC(-1) / NPL_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (NPL_EXPH ) / NPL_YED  - (NPL_EXPH(-1) ) / NPL_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (NPL_EXPE ) / NPL_YED  - (NPL_EXPE(-1) ) / NPL_YED(-1) )

NPL_IGR  = NPL_IGR(-1) + (NPL_OGI / NPL_YED - NPL_OGI(-1) / NPL_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (NPL_EXPH ) / NPL_YED  - (NPL_EXPH(-1) ) / NPL_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (NPL_EXPE ) / NPL_YED  - (NPL_EXPE(-1) ) / NPL_YED(-1) )

NPL_GIP  = ( NPL_GIP(-1)  + ( NPL_GDN(-1) - NPL_GDN(-2) ) * NPL_GINT(-1) / 100  + NPL_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( NPL_GINT(-1) / 100 - NPL_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (NPL_GDFXSH * (NPL_EXR / NPL_EXR(-1))  + (1 - NPL_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY NPL_GLN  = NPL_REV  - NPL_EXP

@IDENTITY NPL_GLNRATIO  = NPL_GLN / NPL_YEN * 100

NPL_GLNT  = NPL_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

NPL_TFP  = NPL_LABSH * (NPL_TECHL  - NPL_TECHL(-1))

NPL_LABSH  = NPL_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY NPL_LFN  = NPL_LRX * NPL_POPWA

NPL_LRX  = NPL_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(NPL_YER(-1) / NPL_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY NPL_URX  = (1 - NPL_LNN / NPL_LFN) * 100

NPL_URXF  = NPL_URXF(-1) * NPL_URX / NPL_URX(-1) * NPL_LNN / NPL_LNNF / (NPL_LNN(-1) / NPL_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(NPL_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(NPL_PCR  / NPL_POPT)

NPL_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(NPL_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

NPL_HEAD19  = NPL_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(NPL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI^2)  , NPL_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(NPL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , NPL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

NPL_HEAD55  = NPL_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(NPL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI^2)  , NPL_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(NPL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , NPL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(NPL_XTR)  = DLOG(NPL_WDR)  + (1  - NPL_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(NPL_XTDNO$  / NPL_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * NPL_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(NPL_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (NPL_EXPH(-1) / NPL_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (NPL_EXPH(-1) / NPL_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(NPL_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(NPL_PM25)

NPL_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( NPL_EXPSP / NPL_YEN )

DLOG(NPL_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - NPL_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (NPL_FINC - NPL_FINC(-1))

DLOG(NPL_PCR)  =  - 0.0157352713745779  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(NPL_PCR(-1))  - LOG(NPL_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (NPL_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.360774081461919  * DLOG(NPL_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.360774081461919)  * DLOG(NPL_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(NPL_HIC)  - NPL_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * NPL_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * NPL_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(NPL_YFT(-1))  - LOG(NPL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(NPL_IPR)  =  - 0.128077323130565  - 0.1 * (LOG(NPL_IPR(-1)  / NPL_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * NPL_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * NPL_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(NPL_PCR  + NPL_GCR(-1) + NPL_IGR(-1) + NPL_XTN  / NPL_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(NPL_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (NPL_USER - NPL_USER(-1))  - (0 * NPL_FUELSH  + 0.26 * NPL_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - NPL_FUELSH - NPL_TOURSH)) * NPL_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * NPL_FUELSH  + 0.26 * NPL_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - NPL_FUELSH - NPL_TOURSH)) * NPL_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(NPL_YFT(-1))  - LOG(NPL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(NPL_MTR)  =  - 0.117107768203921  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(NPL_MTR(-1))  - LOG(NPL_PCR(-1) + NPL_ITR(-1) + NPL_GCR(-1) + NPL_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(NPL_YFT(-1) / NPL_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(NPL_CMUD(-1) * NPL_EXR(-1)  / NPL_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * NPL_OMS * LOG(NPL_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.138989667792474  * DLOG(NPL_XTR)  + 0.172841508881056  * DLOG(NPL_PCR)  + 0.252863096913819  * DLOG(NPL_IPR)  + 0.129401039961588  * DLOG(NPL_GCR + NPL_IGR)

NPL_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * NPL_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * NPL_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * NPL_OILC

NPL_POIL  = NPL_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( NPL_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - NPL_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

NPL_PG  = NPL_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( NPL_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - NPL_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

NPL_PC  = NPL_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( NPL_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - NPL_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(NPL_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

NPL_PE  = NPL_PE(-1) * ( NPL_OILC(-1) / (NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) * NPL_POIL / NPL_POIL(-1)  + NPL_GASC(-1) / (NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) * NPL_PG / NPL_PG(-1)  + NPL_COALC(-1) / (NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) * NPL_PC / NPL_PC(-1)  + NPL_RC(-1) / (NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) * NPL_PR / NPL_PR(-1) )

D(NPL_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(NPL_PM25)  = 0.2 * (NPL_COALC(-1) / NPL_EC(-1) - NPL_COALC(-2) / NPL_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (NPL_COALC(-2) / NPL_EC(-2) - NPL_COALC(-3) / NPL_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (NPL_OILC(-1) / NPL_EC(-1) - NPL_OILC(-2) / NPL_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (NPL_OILC(-2) / NPL_EC(-2) - NPL_OILC(-3) / NPL_EC(-3))

DLOG(NPL_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(NPL_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(NPL_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(NPL_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(NPL_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NPL_PE * NPL_EXR / NPL_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NPL_PE(-1) * NPL_EXR(-1) / NPL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NPL_PE(-2) * NPL_EXR(-2) / NPL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NPL_PE(-3) * NPL_EXR(-3) / NPL_HIC(-3))  - (NPL_EFF - NPL_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(NPL_COALC)  = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(NPL_COALC(-1) / NPL_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.849447051233303 * LOG(NPL_PE(-1) / NPL_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) / NPL_EC(-1))

DLOG(NPL_GASC)  = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(NPL_GASC(-1) / NPL_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.01 * LOG(NPL_PE(-1) / NPL_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) / NPL_EC(-1))

DLOG(NPL_RC)  = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( NPL_RC(-1) / NPL_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.849447051233303 * LOG(NPL_PE(-1) / NPL_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) / NPL_EC(-1))

DLOG(NPL_OILC)  = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( NPL_OILC(-1) / NPL_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.849447051233303 * LOG(NPL_PE(-1) / NPL_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NPL_COALC(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1) + NPL_OILC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)) / NPL_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY NPL_EXR  = NPL_EXR(-1) * IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1)

DLOG(NZL_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(NZL_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(NZL_MTD)  + 0.4 * (NZL_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (NZL_YER / NZL_YFT  - NZL_YER(-1) / NZL_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + NZL_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + NZL_GCARB / NZL_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (NZL_PREM - NZL_PREM(-1)) / 100

NZL_YED  = NZL_YED(-1) * NZL_HIC / NZL_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_INT  = NZL_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_LTI  = NZL_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (NZL_INT - NZL_INT(-1))  + (NZL_PREM  - NZL_PREM(-1)) / 100

NZL_PREM  = NZL_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (NZL_GDNRATIO(-1)  - NZL_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(NZL_LNN)  = DLOG(NZL_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(NZL_LNN(-1))  - LOG(NZL_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(NZL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(NZL_LNNF)  = DLOG(NZL_LNN)

NZL_FUELSH  = NZL_FUELSH(-1)

NZL_TAXR  = NZL_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( NZL_GLNT(-1)  - NZL_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * NZL_YEN(-1) / ( ( NZL_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (NZL_YER(-2)  + NZL_GDI(-2)) * NZL_YED(-2) * (NZL_LNN(-1) / NZL_LNN(-2)  + NZL_TECHL(-1) - NZL_TECHL(-2) ) ) + NZL_REMIT(-1)  + NZL_EXPSP(-1) ) * NZL_SOLV

NZL_CTAXR  = NZL_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( NZL_GLNT(-1)  - NZL_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * NZL_YEN(-1) / ( NZL_PROF(-1) ) * NZL_SOLV

(NZL_OGC)  = NZL_OGC(-1) * (NZL_YFT / NZL_YFT(-1) * NZL_YED / NZL_YED(-1))

NZL_USER  = (NZL_LTI  - NZL_INFT  + NZL_DEP * 100) / (1  - NZL_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (NZL_GCARB / NZL_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY NZL_XTN  = NZL_XTD$ * NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") * NZL_XTR

@IDENTITY NZL_YEN  = NZL_YER  * NZL_YED

@IDENTITY NZL_MTN  = NZL_MTD  * NZL_MTR

@IDENTITY NZL_XTN$  = NZL_XTN / NZL_EXR

@IDENTITY NZL_YEN$  = NZL_YEN / NZL_EXR

@IDENTITY NZL_MTN$  = NZL_MTN / NZL_EXR

@IDENTITY NZL_MTR$  = NZL_MTR$(-1) * NZL_MTR / NZL_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_XTR$  = NZL_XTR$(-1) * NZL_XTR / NZL_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_YER$  = NZL_YER$(-1) * NZL_YER / NZL_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_YFT$  = NZL_YFT$(-1) * NZL_YFT / NZL_YFT(-1)

NZL_POPT  = NZL_POPT(-1)  - NZL_LIVES

NZL_POPWA  = NZL_POPWA(-1) * NZL_POPT / NZL_POPT(-1)

NZL_SCR  = NZL_SCR(-1)  + ((NZL_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (NZL_YFT(-1) / NZL_YER(-1)  - NZL_YFT(-2) / NZL_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY NZL_ITR  = NZL_IGR  + NZL_IPR

@IDENTITY NZL_YER  = NZL_PCR  + NZL_GCR  + NZL_ITR  + NZL_SCR  + NZL_XTR  - NZL_MTR

@IDENTITY NZL_PROF  = (NZL_YEN - NZL_ITAX) * (1 - NZL_LABSH)

@IDENTITY NZL_GDI  = NZL_YER  - NZL_XTR  + NZL_MTR  + NZL_XTN  / ((NZL_YEN  - NZL_XTN  + NZL_MTN)  / (NZL_YER  - NZL_XTR  + NZL_MTR))  - NZL_MTN  / ((NZL_YEN  - NZL_XTN  + NZL_MTN)  / (NZL_YER  - NZL_XTR  + NZL_MTR))

@IDENTITY NZL_RPDI  = NZL_LABSH * 0.5 * (NZL_YER(-1)  + NZL_GDI(-1)) * NZL_YED(-1) / NZL_HIC(-1) * (NZL_LNN / NZL_LNN(-1)  + NZL_TECHL - NZL_TECHL(-1)) + NZL_REMIT / NZL_HIC  + NZL_EXPSP / NZL_HIC  - NZL_TAX / NZL_HIC

DLOG(NZL_YFT)  = (1 - NZL_ALPHA - NZL_LABSH) * DLOG(NZL_K(-1) / NZL_LFN(-1))  + (1 - NZL_ALPHA) * DLOG(NZL_LFN)  + NZL_LABSH * D(NZL_TECHL)  + NZL_ALPHA * (DLOG(NZL_EC)  + D(NZL_EFF) )  - ( NZL_CLIMLOSS / NZL_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (NZL_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY NZL_K  = NZL_K(-1) * (1 - NZL_DEP) + NZL_ITR

DLOG(NZL_MTD)  = (1  - NZL_OMS) * ( DLOG(NZL_CMUD)  + DLOG(NZL_EXR) )  + NZL_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(NZL_EXR) )

DLOG(NZL_XTD$)  = (1  - NZL_OXS) * DLOG(NZL_XTDNO$)  + NZL_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

NZL_INFT  = 0.95 * NZL_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

NZL_OXS  = NZL_OXS(-1)

NZL_OMS  = NZL_OMS(-1) * ((NZL_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * NZL_EXR(-1) / NZL_MTN(-1)) / (NZL_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * NZL_EXR(-2) / NZL_MTN(-2)))^0.25

NZL_CXS  = NZL_CXS(-1)

NZL_FINC  = NZL_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_CAN  = NZL_XTN / NZL_EXR  - NZL_MTN / NZL_EXR  + NZL_REMIT / NZL_EXR  + NZL_CANOTH

@IDENTITY NZL_CANRATIO  = NZL_CAN / NZL_YEN$ * 100

NZL_CANOTH  = NZL_CANOTH(-1)  + ((NZL_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (NZL_YEN$  / NZL_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + NZL_REVG / NZL_EXR  - NZL_REVG(-1) / NZL_EXR(-1)
