0.0001095473213 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005037609148 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002989997475 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002292760995 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001391895376 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002319825627 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005541805665 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0388438274 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004021031087 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004920607914 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003871531213 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006994586013 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01734781496 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001211464494 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * NZL_EXR

NZL_GINT  = NZL_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 7 * (NZL_LTI  - NZL_LTI(-1))

NZL_GDN  = NZL_GDN(-1) * (NZL_GDFXSH  * (NZL_EXR  / NZL_EXR(-1))  + (1  - NZL_GDFXSH))  - NZL_GLN

@IDENTITY NZL_GDNRATIO  = NZL_GDN / NZL_YEN * 100

NZL_GDFXSH  = ( NZL_GDFXSH(-1) * (NZL_EXR / NZL_EXR(-1) )) / (NZL_GDFXSH(-1) * (NZL_EXR / NZL_EXR(-1))  + 1 - NZL_GDFXSH(-1) )

NZL_TOURSH  = NZL_TOURSH(-1)

NZL_LOCK  = 0

NZL_GCARBR  = NZL_GCARBR(-1)

NZL_GTRADER  = NZL_GTRADER(-1)

NZL_ITAXR  = NZL_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_REV  = NZL_TAX  + NZL_CTAX  + NZL_ITAX  + NZL_GTRADE  + NZL_REVG  + NZL_GCARB  + NZL_GCOM  + NZL_GOTH

@IDENTITY NZL_TAX  = NZL_TAXR * (NZL_LABSH * 0.5 * (NZL_YER(-1)  + NZL_GDI(-1)) * NZL_YED(-1) * (NZL_LNN / NZL_LNN(-1)  + NZL_TECHL - NZL_TECHL(-1)) + NZL_REMIT  + NZL_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY NZL_CTAX  = NZL_CTAXR * NZL_PROF

@IDENTITY NZL_ITAX  = NZL_ITAXR * (NZL_PCR * NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY NZL_GTRADE  = NZL_GTRADER * NZL_XTN

NZL_REVG  = NZL_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (NZL_YER$ / NZL_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - NZL_YER$(-1) / NZL_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * NZL_EXR / NZL_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_GCARB  = NZL_GCARBR * NZL_CO2 * NZL_EXR / 1000

NZL_GCOM  = NZL_GCOM(-1) * ( NZL_OILC / (NZL_OILC + NZL_GASC + NZL_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + NZL_GASC / (NZL_OILC + NZL_GASC + NZL_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + NZL_COALC / (NZL_OILC + NZL_GASC + NZL_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

NZL_GOTH  = NZL_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_EXP  = NZL_EXPE  + NZL_EXPH  + NZL_EXPSP  + NZL_OGC  + NZL_OGI  + NZL_GIP

NZL_EXPE  = NZL_EXPE(-1) * (NZL_YFT / NZL_YFT(-1)) * (NZL_YED / NZL_YED(-1))

NZL_EXPH = NZL_EXPH(-1) * (NZL_YFT / NZL_YFT(-1)) * (NZL_YED / NZL_YED(-1))

NZL_EXPSP  = NZL_EXPSP(-1) * (NZL_YFT / NZL_YFT(-1)) * (NZL_YED / NZL_YED(-1)) * (NZL_POPT - NZL_LNN) / (NZL_POPT(-1) - NZL_LNN(-1))

DLOG(NZL_OGI)  = DLOG(NZL_YFT)  + DLOG(NZL_YED)

NZL_GCR  = NZL_GCR(-1)  + ( NZL_OGC / NZL_YED - NZL_OGC(-1) / NZL_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (NZL_EXPH ) / NZL_YED  - (NZL_EXPH(-1) ) / NZL_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (NZL_EXPE ) / NZL_YED  - (NZL_EXPE(-1) ) / NZL_YED(-1) )

NZL_IGR  = NZL_IGR(-1) + (NZL_OGI / NZL_YED - NZL_OGI(-1) / NZL_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (NZL_EXPH ) / NZL_YED  - (NZL_EXPH(-1) ) / NZL_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (NZL_EXPE ) / NZL_YED  - (NZL_EXPE(-1) ) / NZL_YED(-1) )

NZL_GIP  = ( NZL_GIP(-1)  + ( NZL_GDN(-1) - NZL_GDN(-2) ) * NZL_GINT(-1) / 100  + NZL_GDN(-8) / 7 * ( NZL_GINT(-1) / 100 - NZL_GINT(-8) / 100 ) ) * (NZL_GDFXSH * (NZL_EXR / NZL_EXR(-1))  + (1 - NZL_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY NZL_GLN  = NZL_REV  - NZL_EXP

@IDENTITY NZL_GLNRATIO  = NZL_GLN / NZL_YEN * 100

NZL_GLNT  = NZL_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

NZL_TFP  = NZL_LABSH * (NZL_TECHL  - NZL_TECHL(-1))

NZL_LABSH  = NZL_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY NZL_LFN  = NZL_LRX * NZL_POPWA

NZL_LRX  = NZL_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(NZL_YER(-1) / NZL_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY NZL_URX  = (1 - NZL_LNN / NZL_LFN) * 100

NZL_URXF  = NZL_URXF(-1) * NZL_URX / NZL_URX(-1) * NZL_LNN / NZL_LNNF / (NZL_LNN(-1) / NZL_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(NZL_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(NZL_PCR  / NZL_POPT)

NZL_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(NZL_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

NZL_HEAD19  = NZL_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(NZL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (NZL_SDLI^2)  , NZL_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(NZL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (NZL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , NZL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

NZL_HEAD55  = NZL_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(NZL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (NZL_SDLI^2)  , NZL_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(NZL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (NZL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , NZL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(NZL_XTR)  = DLOG(NZL_WDR)  + (1  - NZL_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(NZL_XTDNO$  / NZL_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * NZL_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(NZL_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (NZL_EXPH(-1) / NZL_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (NZL_EXPH(-1) / NZL_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(NZL_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(NZL_PM25)

NZL_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( NZL_EXPSP / NZL_YEN )

DLOG(NZL_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - NZL_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (NZL_FINC - NZL_FINC(-1))

DLOG(NZL_PCR)  =  - 0.155061274490768  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(NZL_PCR(-1))  - LOG(NZL_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (NZL_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(NZL_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(NZL_POPT)  +  - 1 * (DLOG(NZL_HIC)  - NZL_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * NZL_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * NZL_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(NZL_YFT(-1))  - LOG(NZL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(NZL_IPR)  =  - 0.196941426389791  - 0.1 * (LOG(NZL_IPR(-1)  / NZL_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * NZL_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * NZL_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(NZL_PCR  + NZL_GCR(-1) + NZL_IGR(-1) + NZL_XTN  / NZL_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(NZL_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (NZL_USER - NZL_USER(-1))  - (0 * NZL_FUELSH  + 0.26 * NZL_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - NZL_FUELSH - NZL_TOURSH)) * NZL_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * NZL_FUELSH  + 0.26 * NZL_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - NZL_FUELSH - NZL_TOURSH)) * NZL_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(NZL_YFT(-1))  - LOG(NZL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(NZL_MTR)  =  - 0.256204406714988  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(NZL_MTR(-1))  - LOG(NZL_PCR(-1) + NZL_ITR(-1) + NZL_GCR(-1) + NZL_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(NZL_YFT(-1) / NZL_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(NZL_CMUD(-1) * NZL_EXR(-1)  / NZL_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * NZL_OMS * LOG(NZL_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.0991575445923446  * DLOG(NZL_XTR)  + 0.843801574547707  * DLOG(NZL_PCR)  + 0.315874463946131  * DLOG(NZL_IPR)  + 0.303981308591559  * DLOG(NZL_GCR + NZL_IGR)

NZL_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * NZL_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * NZL_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * NZL_OILC

NZL_POIL  = NZL_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( NZL_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - NZL_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

NZL_PG  = NZL_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( NZL_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - NZL_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

NZL_PC  = NZL_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( NZL_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - NZL_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(NZL_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

NZL_PE  = NZL_PE(-1) * ( NZL_OILC(-1) / (NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) * NZL_POIL / NZL_POIL(-1)  + NZL_GASC(-1) / (NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) * NZL_PG / NZL_PG(-1)  + NZL_COALC(-1) / (NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) * NZL_PC / NZL_PC(-1)  + NZL_RC(-1) / (NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) * NZL_PR / NZL_PR(-1) )

D(NZL_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(NZL_PM25)  = 0.2 * (NZL_COALC(-1) / NZL_EC(-1) - NZL_COALC(-2) / NZL_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (NZL_COALC(-2) / NZL_EC(-2) - NZL_COALC(-3) / NZL_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (NZL_OILC(-1) / NZL_EC(-1) - NZL_OILC(-2) / NZL_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (NZL_OILC(-2) / NZL_EC(-2) - NZL_OILC(-3) / NZL_EC(-3))

DLOG(NZL_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(NZL_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(NZL_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(NZL_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(NZL_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NZL_PE * NZL_EXR / NZL_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NZL_PE(-1) * NZL_EXR(-1) / NZL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NZL_PE(-2) * NZL_EXR(-2) / NZL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(NZL_PE(-3) * NZL_EXR(-3) / NZL_HIC(-3))  - (NZL_EFF - NZL_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(NZL_COALC)  = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(NZL_COALC(-1) / NZL_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.354127969470483 * LOG(NZL_PE(-1) / NZL_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) / NZL_EC(-1))

DLOG(NZL_GASC)  = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(NZL_GASC(-1) / NZL_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.188533339938431 * LOG(NZL_PE(-1) / NZL_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) / NZL_EC(-1))

DLOG(NZL_RC)  = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( NZL_RC(-1) / NZL_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.354127969470483 * LOG(NZL_PE(-1) / NZL_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) / NZL_EC(-1))

DLOG(NZL_OILC)  = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( NZL_OILC(-1) / NZL_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.354127969470483 * LOG(NZL_PE(-1) / NZL_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((NZL_COALC(-1) + NZL_GASC(-1) + NZL_OILC(-1) + NZL_RC(-1)) / NZL_EC(-1))

NZL_EXR  = NZL_EXR(-1) * ( ( (NZL_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (NZL_INT  - USA_INT)  - (NZL_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(PAK_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(PAK_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(PAK_MTD)  + 0.4 * (PAK_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (PAK_YER / PAK_YFT  - PAK_YER(-1) / PAK_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + PAK_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + PAK_GCARB / PAK_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (PAK_PREM - PAK_PREM(-1)) / 100

PAK_YED  = PAK_YED(-1) * PAK_HIC / PAK_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_INT  = PAK_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_LTI  = PAK_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (PAK_INT - PAK_INT(-1))  + (PAK_PREM  - PAK_PREM(-1)) / 100

PAK_PREM  = PAK_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (PAK_GDNRATIO(-1)  - PAK_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(PAK_LNN)  = DLOG(PAK_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(PAK_LNN(-1))  - LOG(PAK_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(PAK_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PAK_LNNF)  = DLOG(PAK_LNN)

PAK_FUELSH  = PAK_FUELSH(-1)

PAK_TAXR  = PAK_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( PAK_GLNT(-1)  - PAK_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * PAK_YEN(-1) / ( ( PAK_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (PAK_YER(-2)  + PAK_GDI(-2)) * PAK_YED(-2) * (PAK_LNN(-1) / PAK_LNN(-2)  + PAK_TECHL(-1) - PAK_TECHL(-2) ) ) + PAK_REMIT(-1)  + PAK_EXPSP(-1) ) * PAK_SOLV

PAK_CTAXR  = PAK_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( PAK_GLNT(-1)  - PAK_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * PAK_YEN(-1) / ( PAK_PROF(-1) ) * PAK_SOLV

(PAK_OGC)  = PAK_OGC(-1) * (PAK_YFT / PAK_YFT(-1) * PAK_YED / PAK_YED(-1))

PAK_USER  = (PAK_LTI  - PAK_INFT  + PAK_DEP * 100) / (1  - PAK_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (PAK_GCARB / PAK_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY PAK_XTN  = PAK_XTD$ * PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") * PAK_XTR

@IDENTITY PAK_YEN  = PAK_YER  * PAK_YED

@IDENTITY PAK_MTN  = PAK_MTD  * PAK_MTR

@IDENTITY PAK_XTN$  = PAK_XTN / PAK_EXR

@IDENTITY PAK_YEN$  = PAK_YEN / PAK_EXR

@IDENTITY PAK_MTN$  = PAK_MTN / PAK_EXR

@IDENTITY PAK_MTR$  = PAK_MTR$(-1) * PAK_MTR / PAK_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_XTR$  = PAK_XTR$(-1) * PAK_XTR / PAK_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_YER$  = PAK_YER$(-1) * PAK_YER / PAK_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_YFT$  = PAK_YFT$(-1) * PAK_YFT / PAK_YFT(-1)

PAK_POPT  = PAK_POPT(-1)  - PAK_LIVES

PAK_POPWA  = PAK_POPWA(-1) * PAK_POPT / PAK_POPT(-1)

PAK_SCR  = PAK_SCR(-1)  + ((PAK_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (PAK_YFT(-1) / PAK_YER(-1)  - PAK_YFT(-2) / PAK_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY PAK_ITR  = PAK_IGR  + PAK_IPR

@IDENTITY PAK_YER  = PAK_PCR  + PAK_GCR  + PAK_ITR  + PAK_SCR  + PAK_XTR  - PAK_MTR

@IDENTITY PAK_PROF  = (PAK_YEN - PAK_ITAX) * (1 - PAK_LABSH)

@IDENTITY PAK_GDI  = PAK_YER  - PAK_XTR  + PAK_MTR  + PAK_XTN  / ((PAK_YEN  - PAK_XTN  + PAK_MTN)  / (PAK_YER  - PAK_XTR  + PAK_MTR))  - PAK_MTN  / ((PAK_YEN  - PAK_XTN  + PAK_MTN)  / (PAK_YER  - PAK_XTR  + PAK_MTR))

@IDENTITY PAK_RPDI  = PAK_LABSH * 0.5 * (PAK_YER(-1)  + PAK_GDI(-1)) * PAK_YED(-1) / PAK_HIC(-1) * (PAK_LNN / PAK_LNN(-1)  + PAK_TECHL - PAK_TECHL(-1)) + PAK_REMIT / PAK_HIC  + PAK_EXPSP / PAK_HIC  - PAK_TAX / PAK_HIC

DLOG(PAK_YFT)  = (1 - PAK_ALPHA - PAK_LABSH) * DLOG(PAK_K(-1) / PAK_LFN(-1))  + (1 - PAK_ALPHA) * DLOG(PAK_LFN)  + PAK_LABSH * D(PAK_TECHL)  + PAK_ALPHA * (DLOG(PAK_EC)  + D(PAK_EFF) )  - ( PAK_CLIMLOSS / PAK_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (PAK_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY PAK_K  = PAK_K(-1) * (1 - PAK_DEP) + PAK_ITR

DLOG(PAK_MTD)  = (1  - PAK_OMS) * ( DLOG(PAK_CMUD)  + DLOG(PAK_EXR) )  + PAK_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(PAK_EXR) )

DLOG(PAK_XTD$)  = (1  - PAK_OXS) * DLOG(PAK_XTDNO$)  + PAK_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

PAK_INFT  = 0.95 * PAK_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

PAK_OXS  = PAK_OXS(-1)

PAK_OMS  = PAK_OMS(-1) * ((PAK_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * PAK_EXR(-1) / PAK_MTN(-1)) / (PAK_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * PAK_EXR(-2) / PAK_MTN(-2)))^0.25

PAK_CXS  = PAK_CXS(-1)

PAK_FINC  = PAK_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_CAN  = PAK_XTN / PAK_EXR  - PAK_MTN / PAK_EXR  + PAK_REMIT / PAK_EXR  + PAK_CANOTH

@IDENTITY PAK_CANRATIO  = PAK_CAN / PAK_YEN$ * 100

PAK_CANOTH  = PAK_CANOTH(-1)  + ((PAK_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (PAK_YEN$  / PAK_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + PAK_REVG / PAK_EXR  - PAK_REVG(-1) / PAK_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_GDNRATIO  = PAK_GDN / PAK_YEN * 100

PAK_REVG  = PAK_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (PAK_YER$ / PAK_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - PAK_YER$(-1) / PAK_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * PAK_EXR / PAK_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_GCARB  = PAK_GCARBR * PAK_CO2 * PAK_EXR / 1000

PAK_GCOM  = PAK_GCOM(-1) * ( PAK_OILC / (PAK_OILC + PAK_GASC + PAK_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + PAK_GASC / (PAK_OILC + PAK_GASC + PAK_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + PAK_COALC / (PAK_OILC + PAK_GASC + PAK_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

PAK_GOTH  = PAK_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_EXP  = PAK_EXPE  + PAK_EXPH  + PAK_EXPSP  + PAK_OGC  + PAK_OGI  + PAK_GIP

PAK_EXPE  = PAK_EXPE(-1) * (PAK_YFT / PAK_YFT(-1)) * (PAK_YED / PAK_YED(-1))

PAK_EXPH = PAK_EXPH(-1) * (PAK_YFT / PAK_YFT(-1)) * (PAK_YED / PAK_YED(-1))

PAK_EXPSP  = PAK_EXPSP(-1) * (PAK_YFT / PAK_YFT(-1)) * (PAK_YED / PAK_YED(-1)) * (PAK_POPT - PAK_LNN) / (PAK_POPT(-1) - PAK_LNN(-1))

DLOG(PAK_OGI)  = DLOG(PAK_YFT)  + DLOG(PAK_YED)

PAK_GCR  = PAK_GCR(-1)  + ( PAK_OGC / PAK_YED - PAK_OGC(-1) / PAK_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (PAK_EXPH ) / PAK_YED  - (PAK_EXPH(-1) ) / PAK_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (PAK_EXPE ) / PAK_YED  - (PAK_EXPE(-1) ) / PAK_YED(-1) )

PAK_IGR  = PAK_IGR(-1) + (PAK_OGI / PAK_YED - PAK_OGI(-1) / PAK_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (PAK_EXPH ) / PAK_YED  - (PAK_EXPH(-1) ) / PAK_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (PAK_EXPE ) / PAK_YED  - (PAK_EXPE(-1) ) / PAK_YED(-1) )

PAK_GIP  = ( PAK_GIP(-1)  + ( PAK_GDN(-1) - PAK_GDN(-2) ) * PAK_GINT(-1) / 100  + PAK_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( PAK_GINT(-1) / 100 - PAK_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (PAK_GDFXSH * (PAK_EXR / PAK_EXR(-1))  + (1 - PAK_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY PAK_GLN  = PAK_REV  - PAK_EXP

@IDENTITY PAK_GLNRATIO  = PAK_GLN / PAK_YEN * 100

PAK_GLNT  = PAK_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

PAK_TFP  = PAK_LABSH * (PAK_TECHL  - PAK_TECHL(-1))

PAK_LABSH  = PAK_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY PAK_LFN  = PAK_LRX * PAK_POPWA

PAK_LRX  = PAK_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(PAK_YER(-1) / PAK_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY PAK_URX  = (1 - PAK_LNN / PAK_LFN) * 100

PAK_URXF  = PAK_URXF(-1) * PAK_URX / PAK_URX(-1) * PAK_LNN / PAK_LNNF / (PAK_LNN(-1) / PAK_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(PAK_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(PAK_PCR  / PAK_POPT)

PAK_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(PAK_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

PAK_HEAD19  = PAK_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PAK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI^2)  , PAK_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PAK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PAK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

PAK_HEAD55  = PAK_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PAK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI^2)  , PAK_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PAK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PAK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(PAK_XTR)  = DLOG(PAK_WDR)  + (1  - PAK_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(PAK_XTDNO$  / PAK_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * PAK_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(PAK_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (PAK_EXPH(-1) / PAK_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (PAK_EXPH(-1) / PAK_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(PAK_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(PAK_PM25)

PAK_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( PAK_EXPSP / PAK_YEN )

DLOG(PAK_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - PAK_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (PAK_FINC - PAK_FINC(-1))

DLOG(PAK_PCR)  = 0.0410577312828087  +  - 0.130614179437573 * (LOG(PAK_PCR(-1))  - LOG(PAK_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (PAK_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.478319874030993  * DLOG(PAK_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.478319874030993)  * DLOG(PAK_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(PAK_HIC)  - PAK_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * PAK_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * PAK_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(PAK_YFT(-1))  - LOG(PAK_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PAK_IPR)  =  - 0.211455942107432  - 0.1 * (LOG(PAK_IPR(-1)  / PAK_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * PAK_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * PAK_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(PAK_PCR  + PAK_GCR(-1) + PAK_IGR(-1) + PAK_XTN  / PAK_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(PAK_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (PAK_USER - PAK_USER(-1))  - (0 * PAK_FUELSH  + 0.26 * PAK_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - PAK_FUELSH - PAK_TOURSH)) * PAK_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * PAK_FUELSH  + 0.26 * PAK_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - PAK_FUELSH - PAK_TOURSH)) * PAK_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(PAK_YFT(-1))  - LOG(PAK_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PAK_MTR)  =  - 0.227047759247076  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(PAK_MTR(-1))  - LOG(PAK_PCR(-1) + PAK_ITR(-1) + PAK_GCR(-1) + PAK_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(PAK_YFT(-1) / PAK_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(PAK_CMUD(-1) * PAK_EXR(-1)  / PAK_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * PAK_OMS * LOG(PAK_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.305510229022059  * DLOG(PAK_XTR)  + 1  * DLOG(PAK_PCR)  + 0.255484076515273  * DLOG(PAK_IPR)  + 0.267601770644236  * DLOG(PAK_GCR + PAK_IGR)

PAK_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * PAK_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * PAK_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * PAK_OILC

PAK_POIL  = PAK_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( PAK_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - PAK_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

PAK_PG  = PAK_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( PAK_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - PAK_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

PAK_PC  = PAK_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( PAK_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - PAK_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(PAK_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

PAK_PE  = PAK_PE(-1) * ( PAK_OILC(-1) / (PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) * PAK_POIL / PAK_POIL(-1)  + PAK_GASC(-1) / (PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) * PAK_PG / PAK_PG(-1)  + PAK_COALC(-1) / (PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) * PAK_PC / PAK_PC(-1)  + PAK_RC(-1) / (PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) * PAK_PR / PAK_PR(-1) )

D(PAK_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(PAK_PM25)  = 0.2 * (PAK_COALC(-1) / PAK_EC(-1) - PAK_COALC(-2) / PAK_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (PAK_COALC(-2) / PAK_EC(-2) - PAK_COALC(-3) / PAK_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (PAK_OILC(-1) / PAK_EC(-1) - PAK_OILC(-2) / PAK_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (PAK_OILC(-2) / PAK_EC(-2) - PAK_OILC(-3) / PAK_EC(-3))

DLOG(PAK_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(PAK_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(PAK_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(PAK_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(PAK_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PAK_PE * PAK_EXR / PAK_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PAK_PE(-1) * PAK_EXR(-1) / PAK_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PAK_PE(-2) * PAK_EXR(-2) / PAK_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PAK_PE(-3) * PAK_EXR(-3) / PAK_HIC(-3))  - (PAK_EFF - PAK_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(PAK_COALC)  = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(PAK_COALC(-1) / PAK_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.130211475441145 * LOG(PAK_PE(-1) / PAK_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) / PAK_EC(-1))

DLOG(PAK_GASC)  = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(PAK_GASC(-1) / PAK_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.461707711371523 * LOG(PAK_PE(-1) / PAK_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) / PAK_EC(-1))

DLOG(PAK_RC)  = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( PAK_RC(-1) / PAK_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.130211475441145 * LOG(PAK_PE(-1) / PAK_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) / PAK_EC(-1))

DLOG(PAK_OILC)  = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( PAK_OILC(-1) / PAK_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.130211475441145 * LOG(PAK_PE(-1) / PAK_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PAK_COALC(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1) + PAK_OILC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)) / PAK_EC(-1))

PAK_EXR  = PAK_EXR(-1) * ( (PAK_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(PNG_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(PNG_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(PNG_MTD)  + 0.4 * (PNG_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (PNG_YER / PNG_YFT  - PNG_YER(-1) / PNG_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + PNG_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + PNG_GCARB / PNG_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (PNG_PREM - PNG_PREM(-1)) / 100

PNG_YED  = PNG_YED(-1) * PNG_HIC / PNG_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_INT  = PNG_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_LTI  = PNG_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (PNG_INT - PNG_INT(-1))  + (PNG_PREM  - PNG_PREM(-1)) / 100

PNG_PREM  = PNG_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (PNG_GDNRATIO(-1)  - PNG_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(PNG_LNN)  = DLOG(PNG_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(PNG_LNN(-1))  - LOG(PNG_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(PNG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PNG_LNNF)  = DLOG(PNG_LNN)

PNG_FUELSH  = PNG_FUELSH(-1)

PNG_TAXR  = PNG_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( PNG_GLNT(-1)  - PNG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * PNG_YEN(-1) / ( ( PNG_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (PNG_YER(-2)  + PNG_GDI(-2)) * PNG_YED(-2) * (PNG_LNN(-1) / PNG_LNN(-2)  + PNG_TECHL(-1) - PNG_TECHL(-2) ) ) + PNG_REMIT(-1)  + PNG_EXPSP(-1) ) * PNG_SOLV

PNG_CTAXR  = PNG_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( PNG_GLNT(-1)  - PNG_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * PNG_YEN(-1) / ( PNG_PROF(-1) ) * PNG_SOLV

(PNG_OGC)  = PNG_OGC(-1) * (PNG_YFT / PNG_YFT(-1) * PNG_YED / PNG_YED(-1))

PNG_USER  = (PNG_LTI  - PNG_INFT  + PNG_DEP * 100) / (1  - PNG_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (PNG_GCARB / PNG_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY PNG_XTN  = PNG_XTD$ * PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") * PNG_XTR

@IDENTITY PNG_YEN  = PNG_YER  * PNG_YED

@IDENTITY PNG_MTN  = PNG_MTD  * PNG_MTR

@IDENTITY PNG_XTN$  = PNG_XTN / PNG_EXR

@IDENTITY PNG_YEN$  = PNG_YEN / PNG_EXR

@IDENTITY PNG_MTN$  = PNG_MTN / PNG_EXR

@IDENTITY PNG_MTR$  = PNG_MTR$(-1) * PNG_MTR / PNG_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_XTR$  = PNG_XTR$(-1) * PNG_XTR / PNG_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_YER$  = PNG_YER$(-1) * PNG_YER / PNG_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_YFT$  = PNG_YFT$(-1) * PNG_YFT / PNG_YFT(-1)

PNG_POPT  = PNG_POPT(-1)  - PNG_LIVES

PNG_POPWA  = PNG_POPWA(-1) * PNG_POPT / PNG_POPT(-1)

PNG_SCR  = PNG_SCR(-1)  + ((PNG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (PNG_YFT(-1) / PNG_YER(-1)  - PNG_YFT(-2) / PNG_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY PNG_ITR  = PNG_IGR  + PNG_IPR

@IDENTITY PNG_YER  = PNG_PCR  + PNG_GCR  + PNG_ITR  + PNG_SCR  + PNG_XTR  - PNG_MTR

@IDENTITY PNG_PROF  = (PNG_YEN - PNG_ITAX) * (1 - PNG_LABSH)

@IDENTITY PNG_GDI  = PNG_YER  - PNG_XTR  + PNG_MTR  + PNG_XTN  / ((PNG_YEN  - PNG_XTN  + PNG_MTN)  / (PNG_YER  - PNG_XTR  + PNG_MTR))  - PNG_MTN  / ((PNG_YEN  - PNG_XTN  + PNG_MTN)  / (PNG_YER  - PNG_XTR  + PNG_MTR))

@IDENTITY PNG_RPDI  = PNG_LABSH * 0.5 * (PNG_YER(-1)  + PNG_GDI(-1)) * PNG_YED(-1) / PNG_HIC(-1) * (PNG_LNN / PNG_LNN(-1)  + PNG_TECHL - PNG_TECHL(-1)) + PNG_REMIT / PNG_HIC  + PNG_EXPSP / PNG_HIC  - PNG_TAX / PNG_HIC

DLOG(PNG_YFT)  = (1 - PNG_ALPHA - PNG_LABSH) * DLOG(PNG_K(-1) / PNG_LFN(-1))  + (1 - PNG_ALPHA) * DLOG(PNG_LFN)  + PNG_LABSH * D(PNG_TECHL)  + PNG_ALPHA * (DLOG(PNG_EC)  + D(PNG_EFF) )  - ( PNG_CLIMLOSS / PNG_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (PNG_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY PNG_K  = PNG_K(-1) * (1 - PNG_DEP) + PNG_ITR

DLOG(PNG_MTD)  = (1  - PNG_OMS) * ( DLOG(PNG_CMUD)  + DLOG(PNG_EXR) )  + PNG_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(PNG_EXR) )

DLOG(PNG_XTD$)  = (1  - PNG_OXS) * DLOG(PNG_XTDNO$)  + PNG_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

PNG_INFT  = 0.95 * PNG_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

PNG_OXS  = PNG_OXS(-1)

PNG_OMS  = PNG_OMS(-1) * ((PNG_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * PNG_EXR(-1) / PNG_MTN(-1)) / (PNG_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * PNG_EXR(-2) / PNG_MTN(-2)))^0.25

PNG_CXS  = PNG_CXS(-1)

PNG_FINC  = PNG_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_CAN  = PNG_XTN / PNG_EXR  - PNG_MTN / PNG_EXR  + PNG_REMIT / PNG_EXR  + PNG_CANOTH

@IDENTITY PNG_CANRATIO  = PNG_CAN / PNG_YEN$ * 100

PNG_CANOTH  = PNG_CANOTH(-1)  + ((PNG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (PNG_YEN$  / PNG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + PNG_REVG / PNG_EXR  - PNG_REVG(-1) / PNG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(PNG_EFEX)  =  - LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.095086843E-07 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.092156566E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.2596253526 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.290034401E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0006624807682 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002767672704 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001401716936 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.655048527E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1360601956 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001605398465 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000139251714 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003252471149 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0266022677 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01575525144 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.263886946E-06 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.09689830888 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.370066655E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.689525441E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.793440235E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.324563527E-07 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.296797639E-06 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03342996616 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001029810692 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.455047388E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.72499145E-06 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.215389846E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.617954699E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01261787092 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001028197981 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01796278366 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01838368004 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001330239659 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.828326595E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1611679017 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001569244072 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002300689865 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.057681704E-11 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01801793413 * LOG(THA_EXR / 0.003593842652 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03194205922 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009520784873 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_GINT  = PNG_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (PNG_LTI  - PNG_LTI(-1))

PNG_GDN  = PNG_GDN(-1) * (PNG_GDFXSH  * (PNG_EXR  / PNG_EXR(-1))  + (1  - PNG_GDFXSH))  - PNG_GLN

@IDENTITY PNG_GDNRATIO  = PNG_GDN / PNG_YEN * 100

PNG_GDFXSH  = ( PNG_GDFXSH(-1) * (PNG_EXR / PNG_EXR(-1) )) / (PNG_GDFXSH(-1) * (PNG_EXR / PNG_EXR(-1))  + 1 - PNG_GDFXSH(-1) )

PNG_TOURSH  = PNG_TOURSH(-1)

PNG_LOCK  = 0

PNG_GCARBR  = PNG_GCARBR(-1)

PNG_GTRADER  = PNG_GTRADER(-1)

PNG_ITAXR  = PNG_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_REV  = PNG_TAX  + PNG_CTAX  + PNG_ITAX  + PNG_GTRADE  + PNG_REVG  + PNG_GCARB  + PNG_GCOM  + PNG_GOTH

@IDENTITY PNG_TAX  = PNG_TAXR * (PNG_LABSH * 0.5 * (PNG_YER(-1)  + PNG_GDI(-1)) * PNG_YED(-1) * (PNG_LNN / PNG_LNN(-1)  + PNG_TECHL - PNG_TECHL(-1)) + PNG_REMIT  + PNG_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY PNG_CTAX  = PNG_CTAXR * PNG_PROF

@IDENTITY PNG_ITAX  = PNG_ITAXR * (PNG_PCR * PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY PNG_GTRADE  = PNG_GTRADER * PNG_XTN

PNG_REVG  = PNG_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (PNG_YER$ / PNG_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - PNG_YER$(-1) / PNG_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * PNG_EXR / PNG_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_GCARB  = PNG_GCARBR * PNG_CO2 * PNG_EXR / 1000

PNG_GCOM  = PNG_GCOM(-1) * ( PNG_OILC / (PNG_OILC + PNG_GASC + PNG_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + PNG_GASC / (PNG_OILC + PNG_GASC + PNG_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + PNG_COALC / (PNG_OILC + PNG_GASC + PNG_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

PNG_GOTH  = PNG_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_EXP  = PNG_EXPE  + PNG_EXPH  + PNG_EXPSP  + PNG_OGC  + PNG_OGI  + PNG_GIP

PNG_EXPE  = PNG_EXPE(-1) * (PNG_YFT / PNG_YFT(-1)) * (PNG_YED / PNG_YED(-1))

PNG_EXPH = PNG_EXPH(-1) * (PNG_YFT / PNG_YFT(-1)) * (PNG_YED / PNG_YED(-1))

PNG_EXPSP  = PNG_EXPSP(-1) * (PNG_YFT / PNG_YFT(-1)) * (PNG_YED / PNG_YED(-1)) * (PNG_POPT - PNG_LNN) / (PNG_POPT(-1) - PNG_LNN(-1))

DLOG(PNG_OGI)  = DLOG(PNG_YFT)  + DLOG(PNG_YED)

PNG_GCR  = PNG_GCR(-1)  + ( PNG_OGC / PNG_YED - PNG_OGC(-1) / PNG_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (PNG_EXPH ) / PNG_YED  - (PNG_EXPH(-1) ) / PNG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (PNG_EXPE ) / PNG_YED  - (PNG_EXPE(-1) ) / PNG_YED(-1) )

PNG_IGR  = PNG_IGR(-1) + (PNG_OGI / PNG_YED - PNG_OGI(-1) / PNG_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (PNG_EXPH ) / PNG_YED  - (PNG_EXPH(-1) ) / PNG_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (PNG_EXPE ) / PNG_YED  - (PNG_EXPE(-1) ) / PNG_YED(-1) )

PNG_GIP  = ( PNG_GIP(-1)  + ( PNG_GDN(-1) - PNG_GDN(-2) ) * PNG_GINT(-1) / 100  + PNG_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( PNG_GINT(-1) / 100 - PNG_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (PNG_GDFXSH * (PNG_EXR / PNG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - PNG_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY PNG_GLN  = PNG_REV  - PNG_EXP

@IDENTITY PNG_GLNRATIO  = PNG_GLN / PNG_YEN * 100

PNG_GLNT  = PNG_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

PNG_TFP  = PNG_LABSH * (PNG_TECHL  - PNG_TECHL(-1))

PNG_LABSH  = PNG_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY PNG_LFN  = PNG_LRX * PNG_POPWA

PNG_LRX  = PNG_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(PNG_YER(-1) / PNG_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY PNG_URX  = (1 - PNG_LNN / PNG_LFN) * 100

PNG_URXF  = PNG_URXF(-1) * PNG_URX / PNG_URX(-1) * PNG_LNN / PNG_LNNF / (PNG_LNN(-1) / PNG_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(PNG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(PNG_PCR  / PNG_POPT)

PNG_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(PNG_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

PNG_HEAD19  = PNG_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI^2)  , PNG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

PNG_HEAD55  = PNG_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI^2)  , PNG_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(PNG_XTR)  = DLOG(PNG_WDR)  + (1  - PNG_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(PNG_XTDNO$  / PNG_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * PNG_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(PNG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (PNG_EXPH(-1) / PNG_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (PNG_EXPH(-1) / PNG_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(PNG_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(PNG_PM25)

PNG_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( PNG_EXPSP / PNG_YEN )

DLOG(PNG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - PNG_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (PNG_FINC - PNG_FINC(-1))

DLOG(PNG_PCR)  =  - 0.150580135488783  +  - 0.209797750997795 * (LOG(PNG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(PNG_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (PNG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(PNG_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.7)  * DLOG(PNG_POPT)  +  - 0.68254554366906 * (DLOG(PNG_HIC)  - PNG_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * PNG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * PNG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(PNG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(PNG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PNG_IPR)  =  - 0.24177481846023  - 0.1 * (LOG(PNG_IPR(-1)  / PNG_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * PNG_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * PNG_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(PNG_PCR  + PNG_GCR(-1) + PNG_IGR(-1) + PNG_XTN  / PNG_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(PNG_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (PNG_USER - PNG_USER(-1))  - (0 * PNG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * PNG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - PNG_FUELSH - PNG_TOURSH)) * PNG_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * PNG_FUELSH  + 0.26 * PNG_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - PNG_FUELSH - PNG_TOURSH)) * PNG_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(PNG_YFT(-1))  - LOG(PNG_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PNG_MTR)  =  - 0.172896999668496  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(PNG_MTR(-1))  - LOG(PNG_PCR(-1) + PNG_ITR(-1) + PNG_GCR(-1) + PNG_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(PNG_YFT(-1) / PNG_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(PNG_CMUD(-1) * PNG_EXR(-1)  / PNG_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * PNG_OMS * LOG(PNG_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.138849740737893  * DLOG(PNG_XTR)  + 0.492799102696649  * DLOG(PNG_PCR)  + 0.0947334218251228  * DLOG(PNG_IPR)  + 0.182964919297586  * DLOG(PNG_GCR + PNG_IGR)

PNG_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * PNG_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * PNG_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * PNG_OILC

PNG_POIL  = PNG_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( PNG_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - PNG_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

PNG_PG  = PNG_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( PNG_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - PNG_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

PNG_PC  = PNG_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( PNG_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - PNG_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(PNG_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

PNG_PE  = PNG_PE(-1) * ( PNG_OILC(-1) / (PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) * PNG_POIL / PNG_POIL(-1)  + PNG_GASC(-1) / (PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) * PNG_PG / PNG_PG(-1)  + PNG_COALC(-1) / (PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) * PNG_PC / PNG_PC(-1)  + PNG_RC(-1) / (PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) * PNG_PR / PNG_PR(-1) )

D(PNG_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(PNG_PM25)  = 0.2 * (PNG_COALC(-1) / PNG_EC(-1) - PNG_COALC(-2) / PNG_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (PNG_COALC(-2) / PNG_EC(-2) - PNG_COALC(-3) / PNG_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (PNG_OILC(-1) / PNG_EC(-1) - PNG_OILC(-2) / PNG_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (PNG_OILC(-2) / PNG_EC(-2) - PNG_OILC(-3) / PNG_EC(-3))

DLOG(PNG_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(PNG_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(PNG_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(PNG_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(PNG_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PNG_PE * PNG_EXR / PNG_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PNG_PE(-1) * PNG_EXR(-1) / PNG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PNG_PE(-2) * PNG_EXR(-2) / PNG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PNG_PE(-3) * PNG_EXR(-3) / PNG_HIC(-3))  - (PNG_EFF - PNG_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(PNG_COALC)  = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(PNG_COALC(-1) / PNG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.01 * LOG(PNG_PE(-1) / PNG_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) / PNG_EC(-1))

DLOG(PNG_GASC)  = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(PNG_GASC(-1) / PNG_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.115739881120646 * LOG(PNG_PE(-1) / PNG_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) / PNG_EC(-1))

DLOG(PNG_RC)  = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( PNG_RC(-1) / PNG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.523021033142376 * LOG(PNG_PE(-1) / PNG_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) / PNG_EC(-1))

DLOG(PNG_OILC)  = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( PNG_OILC(-1) / PNG_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.523021033142376 * LOG(PNG_PE(-1) / PNG_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PNG_COALC(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1) + PNG_OILC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)) / PNG_EC(-1))

PNG_EXR  = PNG_EXR(-1) * ( (PNG_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(PHL_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(PHL_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(PHL_MTD)  + 0.4 * (PHL_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (PHL_YER / PHL_YFT  - PHL_YER(-1) / PHL_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + PHL_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + PHL_GCARB / PHL_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (PHL_PREM - PHL_PREM(-1)) / 100

PHL_YED  = PHL_YED(-1) * PHL_HIC / PHL_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_INT  = PHL_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_LTI  = PHL_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (PHL_INT - PHL_INT(-1))  + (PHL_PREM  - PHL_PREM(-1)) / 100

PHL_PREM  = PHL_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (PHL_GDNRATIO(-1)  - PHL_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(PHL_LNN)  = DLOG(PHL_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(PHL_LNN(-1))  - LOG(PHL_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(PHL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PHL_LNNF)  = DLOG(PHL_LNN)

PHL_FUELSH  = PHL_FUELSH(-1)

PHL_TAXR  = PHL_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( PHL_GLNT(-1)  - PHL_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * PHL_YEN(-1) / ( ( PHL_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (PHL_YER(-2)  + PHL_GDI(-2)) * PHL_YED(-2) * (PHL_LNN(-1) / PHL_LNN(-2)  + PHL_TECHL(-1) - PHL_TECHL(-2) ) ) + PHL_REMIT(-1)  + PHL_EXPSP(-1) ) * PHL_SOLV

PHL_CTAXR  = PHL_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( PHL_GLNT(-1)  - PHL_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * PHL_YEN(-1) / ( PHL_PROF(-1) ) * PHL_SOLV

(PHL_OGC)  = PHL_OGC(-1) * (PHL_YFT / PHL_YFT(-1) * PHL_YED / PHL_YED(-1))

PHL_USER  = (PHL_LTI  - PHL_INFT  + PHL_DEP * 100) / (1  - PHL_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (PHL_GCARB / PHL_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY PHL_XTN  = PHL_XTD$ * PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") * PHL_XTR

@IDENTITY PHL_YEN  = PHL_YER  * PHL_YED

@IDENTITY PHL_MTN  = PHL_MTD  * PHL_MTR

@IDENTITY PHL_XTN$  = PHL_XTN / PHL_EXR

@IDENTITY PHL_YEN$  = PHL_YEN / PHL_EXR

@IDENTITY PHL_MTN$  = PHL_MTN / PHL_EXR

@IDENTITY PHL_MTR$  = PHL_MTR$(-1) * PHL_MTR / PHL_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_XTR$  = PHL_XTR$(-1) * PHL_XTR / PHL_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_YER$  = PHL_YER$(-1) * PHL_YER / PHL_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_YFT$  = PHL_YFT$(-1) * PHL_YFT / PHL_YFT(-1)

PHL_POPT  = PHL_POPT(-1)  - PHL_LIVES

PHL_POPWA  = PHL_POPWA(-1) * PHL_POPT / PHL_POPT(-1)

PHL_SCR  = PHL_SCR(-1)  + ((PHL_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (PHL_YFT(-1) / PHL_YER(-1)  - PHL_YFT(-2) / PHL_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY PHL_ITR  = PHL_IGR  + PHL_IPR

@IDENTITY PHL_YER  = PHL_PCR  + PHL_GCR  + PHL_ITR  + PHL_SCR  + PHL_XTR  - PHL_MTR

@IDENTITY PHL_PROF  = (PHL_YEN - PHL_ITAX) * (1 - PHL_LABSH)

@IDENTITY PHL_GDI  = PHL_YER  - PHL_XTR  + PHL_MTR  + PHL_XTN  / ((PHL_YEN  - PHL_XTN  + PHL_MTN)  / (PHL_YER  - PHL_XTR  + PHL_MTR))  - PHL_MTN  / ((PHL_YEN  - PHL_XTN  + PHL_MTN)  / (PHL_YER  - PHL_XTR  + PHL_MTR))

@IDENTITY PHL_RPDI  = PHL_LABSH * 0.5 * (PHL_YER(-1)  + PHL_GDI(-1)) * PHL_YED(-1) / PHL_HIC(-1) * (PHL_LNN / PHL_LNN(-1)  + PHL_TECHL - PHL_TECHL(-1)) + PHL_REMIT / PHL_HIC  + PHL_EXPSP / PHL_HIC  - PHL_TAX / PHL_HIC

DLOG(PHL_YFT)  = (1 - PHL_ALPHA - PHL_LABSH) * DLOG(PHL_K(-1) / PHL_LFN(-1))  + (1 - PHL_ALPHA) * DLOG(PHL_LFN)  + PHL_LABSH * D(PHL_TECHL)  + PHL_ALPHA * (DLOG(PHL_EC)  + D(PHL_EFF) )  - ( PHL_CLIMLOSS / PHL_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (PHL_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY PHL_K  = PHL_K(-1) * (1 - PHL_DEP) + PHL_ITR

DLOG(PHL_MTD)  = (1  - PHL_OMS) * ( DLOG(PHL_CMUD)  + DLOG(PHL_EXR) )  + PHL_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(PHL_EXR) )

DLOG(PHL_XTD$)  = (1  - PHL_OXS) * DLOG(PHL_XTDNO$)  + PHL_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

PHL_INFT  = 0.95 * PHL_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

PHL_OXS  = PHL_OXS(-1)

PHL_OMS  = PHL_OMS(-1) * ((PHL_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * PHL_EXR(-1) / PHL_MTN(-1)) / (PHL_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * PHL_EXR(-2) / PHL_MTN(-2)))^0.25

PHL_CXS  = PHL_CXS(-1)

PHL_FINC  = PHL_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_CAN  = PHL_XTN / PHL_EXR  - PHL_MTN / PHL_EXR  + PHL_REMIT / PHL_EXR  + PHL_CANOTH

@IDENTITY PHL_CANRATIO  = PHL_CAN / PHL_YEN$ * 100

PHL_CANOTH  = PHL_CANOTH(-1)  + ((PHL_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (PHL_YEN$  / PHL_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + PHL_REVG / PHL_EXR  - PHL_REVG(-1) / PHL_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(PHL_EFEX)  =  - LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.431911895E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.616743116E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01375948885 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.707479187E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002721799753 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.188341937E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001988887559 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001973625022 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.2021390327 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.306929019E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.408293447E-06 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05553130206 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01506926483 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03219594328 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005397398507 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1143500659 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.312893795E-05 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.942503321E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.975841524E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.362307672E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007066521585 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02313581061 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.857156212E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.387461083E-05 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.667510814E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001870230602 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.050182555E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003226038302 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007635552792 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001967249238 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06303790559 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001291014461 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.658441757E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.08004791559 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.242414408E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003509040274 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.59751357E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05621100174 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001463735423 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.122458593E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009620351768 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.337583612E-08 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.280145201E-06 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.533686138E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01378916892 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1180575636 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03056589886 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00913455879 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007579196434 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004587012332 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01224542685 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006027592137 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003743777791 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05794984691 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001740620822 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0228009682 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02047784719 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02447106363 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(PHL_REFEX )  =  - LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.431911895E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.616743116E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01375948885 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.707479187E-06 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002721799753 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.188341937E-06 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001988887559 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001973625022 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.2021390327 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.306929019E-05 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.408293447E-06 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05553130206 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01506926483 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03219594328 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005397398507 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1143500659 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.312893795E-05 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.942503321E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.975841524E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.362307672E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007066521585 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02313581061 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.857156212E-05 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.387461083E-05 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.667510814E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001870230602 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.050182555E-05 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003226038302 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007635552792 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001967249238 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06303790559 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001291014461 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.658441757E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08004791559 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.242414408E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003509040274 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.59751357E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05621100174 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001463735423 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.122458593E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0009620351768 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.337583612E-08 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.280145201E-06 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.533686138E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01378916892 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1180575636 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03056589886 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00913455879 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007579196434 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004587012332 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01224542685 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006027592137 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003743777791 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05794984691 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001740620822 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0228009682 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02047784719 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02447106363 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

PHL_REMIT  = PHL_REMIT(-1) / PHL_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03081565881 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005505816446 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 2.658563635E-06 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002305389535 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01648669568 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008951893978 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002278492828 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 6.848966318E-05 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02023276279 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02008453882 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004584446476 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002310787919 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02029832573 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03617165872 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 1.974932986E-05 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00761188194 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002404218727 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001682682092 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 1.943836007E-05 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06032881231 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001919837945 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005822699723 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001643245523 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 2.046719859E-05 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00266554106 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 8.228887443E-06 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002400482476 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 9.672107702E-05 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001248282943 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.341222254 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 3.696669436E-05 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 5.317127271E-06 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003297663125 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01945972281 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07440817836 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.3197459153 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * PHL_EXR

PHL_GINT  = PHL_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 12 * (PHL_LTI  - PHL_LTI(-1))

PHL_GDN  = PHL_GDN(-1) * (PHL_GDFXSH  * (PHL_EXR  / PHL_EXR(-1))  + (1  - PHL_GDFXSH))  - PHL_GLN

@IDENTITY PHL_GDNRATIO  = PHL_GDN / PHL_YEN * 100

PHL_GDFXSH  = ( PHL_GDFXSH(-1) * (PHL_EXR / PHL_EXR(-1) )) / (PHL_GDFXSH(-1) * (PHL_EXR / PHL_EXR(-1))  + 1 - PHL_GDFXSH(-1) )

PHL_TOURSH  = PHL_TOURSH(-1)

PHL_LOCK  = 0

PHL_GCARBR  = PHL_GCARBR(-1)

PHL_GTRADER  = PHL_GTRADER(-1)

PHL_ITAXR  = PHL_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_REV  = PHL_TAX  + PHL_CTAX  + PHL_ITAX  + PHL_GTRADE  + PHL_REVG  + PHL_GCARB  + PHL_GCOM  + PHL_GOTH

@IDENTITY PHL_TAX  = PHL_TAXR * (PHL_LABSH * 0.5 * (PHL_YER(-1)  + PHL_GDI(-1)) * PHL_YED(-1) * (PHL_LNN / PHL_LNN(-1)  + PHL_TECHL - PHL_TECHL(-1)) + PHL_REMIT  + PHL_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY PHL_CTAX  = PHL_CTAXR * PHL_PROF

@IDENTITY PHL_ITAX  = PHL_ITAXR * (PHL_PCR * PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY PHL_GTRADE  = PHL_GTRADER * PHL_XTN

PHL_REVG  = PHL_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (PHL_YER$ / PHL_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - PHL_YER$(-1) / PHL_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * PHL_EXR / PHL_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_GCARB  = PHL_GCARBR * PHL_CO2 * PHL_EXR / 1000

PHL_GCOM  = PHL_GCOM(-1) * ( PHL_OILC / (PHL_OILC + PHL_GASC + PHL_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + PHL_GASC / (PHL_OILC + PHL_GASC + PHL_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + PHL_COALC / (PHL_OILC + PHL_GASC + PHL_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

PHL_GOTH  = PHL_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_EXP  = PHL_EXPE  + PHL_EXPH  + PHL_EXPSP  + PHL_OGC  + PHL_OGI  + PHL_GIP

PHL_EXPE  = PHL_EXPE(-1) * (PHL_YFT / PHL_YFT(-1)) * (PHL_YED / PHL_YED(-1))

PHL_EXPH = PHL_EXPH(-1) * (PHL_YFT / PHL_YFT(-1)) * (PHL_YED / PHL_YED(-1))

PHL_EXPSP  = PHL_EXPSP(-1) * (PHL_YFT / PHL_YFT(-1)) * (PHL_YED / PHL_YED(-1)) * (PHL_POPT - PHL_LNN) / (PHL_POPT(-1) - PHL_LNN(-1))

DLOG(PHL_OGI)  = DLOG(PHL_YFT)  + DLOG(PHL_YED)

PHL_GCR  = PHL_GCR(-1)  + ( PHL_OGC / PHL_YED - PHL_OGC(-1) / PHL_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (PHL_EXPH ) / PHL_YED  - (PHL_EXPH(-1) ) / PHL_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (PHL_EXPE ) / PHL_YED  - (PHL_EXPE(-1) ) / PHL_YED(-1) )

PHL_IGR  = PHL_IGR(-1) + (PHL_OGI / PHL_YED - PHL_OGI(-1) / PHL_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (PHL_EXPH ) / PHL_YED  - (PHL_EXPH(-1) ) / PHL_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (PHL_EXPE ) / PHL_YED  - (PHL_EXPE(-1) ) / PHL_YED(-1) )

PHL_GIP  = ( PHL_GIP(-1)  + ( PHL_GDN(-1) - PHL_GDN(-2) ) * PHL_GINT(-1) / 100  + PHL_GDN(-13) / 12 * ( PHL_GINT(-1) / 100 - PHL_GINT(-13) / 100 ) ) * (PHL_GDFXSH * (PHL_EXR / PHL_EXR(-1))  + (1 - PHL_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY PHL_GLN  = PHL_REV  - PHL_EXP

@IDENTITY PHL_GLNRATIO  = PHL_GLN / PHL_YEN * 100

PHL_GLNT  = PHL_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

PHL_TFP  = PHL_LABSH * (PHL_TECHL  - PHL_TECHL(-1))

PHL_LABSH  = PHL_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY PHL_LFN  = PHL_LRX * PHL_POPWA

PHL_LRX  = PHL_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(PHL_YER(-1) / PHL_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY PHL_URX  = (1 - PHL_LNN / PHL_LFN) * 100

PHL_URXF  = PHL_URXF(-1) * PHL_URX / PHL_URX(-1) * PHL_LNN / PHL_LNNF / (PHL_LNN(-1) / PHL_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(PHL_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(PHL_PCR  / PHL_POPT)

PHL_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(PHL_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

PHL_HEAD19  = PHL_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PHL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI^2)  , PHL_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PHL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PHL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

PHL_HEAD55  = PHL_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PHL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI^2)  , PHL_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PHL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PHL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(PHL_XTR)  = DLOG(PHL_WDR)  + (1  - PHL_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(PHL_XTDNO$  / PHL_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * PHL_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(PHL_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (PHL_EXPH(-1) / PHL_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (PHL_EXPH(-1) / PHL_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(PHL_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(PHL_PM25)

PHL_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( PHL_EXPSP / PHL_YEN )

DLOG(PHL_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - PHL_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (PHL_FINC - PHL_FINC(-1))

DLOG(PHL_PCR)  = 0.0173763821687919  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(PHL_PCR(-1))  - LOG(PHL_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (PHL_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(PHL_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(PHL_POPT)  +  - 0.185259584013517 * (DLOG(PHL_HIC)  - PHL_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * PHL_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * PHL_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(PHL_YFT(-1))  - LOG(PHL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PHL_IPR)  =  - 0.138118555984845  - 0.1 * (LOG(PHL_IPR(-1)  / PHL_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * PHL_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * PHL_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(PHL_PCR  + PHL_GCR(-1) + PHL_IGR(-1) + PHL_XTN  / PHL_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(PHL_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (PHL_USER - PHL_USER(-1))  - (0 * PHL_FUELSH  + 0.26 * PHL_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - PHL_FUELSH - PHL_TOURSH)) * PHL_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * PHL_FUELSH  + 0.26 * PHL_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - PHL_FUELSH - PHL_TOURSH)) * PHL_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(PHL_YFT(-1))  - LOG(PHL_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(PHL_MTR)  =  - 0.176473768507117  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(PHL_MTR(-1))  - LOG(PHL_PCR(-1) + PHL_ITR(-1) + PHL_GCR(-1) + PHL_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(PHL_YFT(-1) / PHL_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(PHL_CMUD(-1) * PHL_EXR(-1)  / PHL_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * PHL_OMS * LOG(PHL_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.476413205951914  * DLOG(PHL_XTR)  + 0.748596498652343  * DLOG(PHL_PCR)  + 0.265353403214069  * DLOG(PHL_IPR)  + 0.0524791320877765  * DLOG(PHL_GCR + PHL_IGR)

PHL_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * PHL_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * PHL_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * PHL_OILC

PHL_POIL  = PHL_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( PHL_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - PHL_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

PHL_PG  = PHL_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( PHL_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - PHL_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

PHL_PC  = PHL_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( PHL_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - PHL_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(PHL_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

PHL_PE  = PHL_PE(-1) * ( PHL_OILC(-1) / (PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) * PHL_POIL / PHL_POIL(-1)  + PHL_GASC(-1) / (PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) * PHL_PG / PHL_PG(-1)  + PHL_COALC(-1) / (PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) * PHL_PC / PHL_PC(-1)  + PHL_RC(-1) / (PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) * PHL_PR / PHL_PR(-1) )

D(PHL_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(PHL_PM25)  = 0.2 * (PHL_COALC(-1) / PHL_EC(-1) - PHL_COALC(-2) / PHL_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (PHL_COALC(-2) / PHL_EC(-2) - PHL_COALC(-3) / PHL_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (PHL_OILC(-1) / PHL_EC(-1) - PHL_OILC(-2) / PHL_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (PHL_OILC(-2) / PHL_EC(-2) - PHL_OILC(-3) / PHL_EC(-3))

DLOG(PHL_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(PHL_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(PHL_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(PHL_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(PHL_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PHL_PE * PHL_EXR / PHL_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PHL_PE(-1) * PHL_EXR(-1) / PHL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PHL_PE(-2) * PHL_EXR(-2) / PHL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(PHL_PE(-3) * PHL_EXR(-3) / PHL_HIC(-3))  - (PHL_EFF - PHL_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(PHL_COALC)  = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(PHL_COALC(-1) / PHL_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.116688018996245 * LOG(PHL_PE(-1) / PHL_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) / PHL_EC(-1))

DLOG(PHL_GASC)  = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(PHL_GASC(-1) / PHL_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.0725775316838762 * LOG(PHL_PE(-1) / PHL_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) / PHL_EC(-1))

DLOG(PHL_RC)  = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( PHL_RC(-1) / PHL_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.116688018996245 * LOG(PHL_PE(-1) / PHL_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) / PHL_EC(-1))

DLOG(PHL_OILC)  = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( PHL_OILC(-1) / PHL_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.116688018996245 * LOG(PHL_PE(-1) / PHL_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((PHL_COALC(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1) + PHL_OILC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)) / PHL_EC(-1))

PHL_EXR  = PHL_EXR(-1) * ( ( (PHL_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (PHL_INT  - USA_INT)  - (PHL_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(KOR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(KOR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KOR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (KOR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (KOR_YER / KOR_YFT  - KOR_YER(-1) / KOR_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + KOR_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + KOR_GCARB / KOR_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (KOR_PREM - KOR_PREM(-1)) / 100

KOR_YED  = KOR_YED(-1) * KOR_HIC / KOR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_INT  = KOR_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_LTI  = KOR_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (KOR_INT - KOR_INT(-1))  + (KOR_PREM  - KOR_PREM(-1)) / 100

KOR_PREM  = KOR_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (KOR_GDNRATIO(-1)  - KOR_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(KOR_LNN)  = DLOG(KOR_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(KOR_LNN(-1))  - LOG(KOR_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(KOR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KOR_LNNF)  = DLOG(KOR_LNN)

KOR_FUELSH  = KOR_FUELSH(-1)

KOR_TAXR  = KOR_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KOR_GLNT(-1)  - KOR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KOR_YEN(-1) / ( ( KOR_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (KOR_YER(-2)  + KOR_GDI(-2)) * KOR_YED(-2) * (KOR_LNN(-1) / KOR_LNN(-2)  + KOR_TECHL(-1) - KOR_TECHL(-2) ) ) + KOR_REMIT(-1)  + KOR_EXPSP(-1) ) * KOR_SOLV

KOR_CTAXR  = KOR_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( KOR_GLNT(-1)  - KOR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * KOR_YEN(-1) / ( KOR_PROF(-1) ) * KOR_SOLV

(KOR_OGC)  = KOR_OGC(-1) * (KOR_YFT / KOR_YFT(-1) * KOR_YED / KOR_YED(-1))

KOR_USER  = (KOR_LTI  - KOR_INFT  + KOR_DEP * 100) / (1  - KOR_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (KOR_GCARB / KOR_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY KOR_XTN  = KOR_XTD$ * KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") * KOR_XTR

@IDENTITY KOR_YEN  = KOR_YER  * KOR_YED

@IDENTITY KOR_MTN  = KOR_MTD  * KOR_MTR

@IDENTITY KOR_XTN$  = KOR_XTN / KOR_EXR

@IDENTITY KOR_YEN$  = KOR_YEN / KOR_EXR

@IDENTITY KOR_MTN$  = KOR_MTN / KOR_EXR

@IDENTITY KOR_MTR$  = KOR_MTR$(-1) * KOR_MTR / KOR_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_XTR$  = KOR_XTR$(-1) * KOR_XTR / KOR_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_YER$  = KOR_YER$(-1) * KOR_YER / KOR_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_YFT$  = KOR_YFT$(-1) * KOR_YFT / KOR_YFT(-1)

KOR_POPT  = KOR_POPT(-1)  - KOR_LIVES

KOR_POPWA  = KOR_POPWA(-1) * KOR_POPT / KOR_POPT(-1)

KOR_SCR  = KOR_SCR(-1)  + ((KOR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KOR_YFT(-1) / KOR_YER(-1)  - KOR_YFT(-2) / KOR_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY KOR_ITR  = KOR_IGR  + KOR_IPR

@IDENTITY KOR_YER  = KOR_PCR  + KOR_GCR  + KOR_ITR  + KOR_SCR  + KOR_XTR  - KOR_MTR

@IDENTITY KOR_PROF  = (KOR_YEN - KOR_ITAX) * (1 - KOR_LABSH)

@IDENTITY KOR_GDI  = KOR_YER  - KOR_XTR  + KOR_MTR  + KOR_XTN  / ((KOR_YEN  - KOR_XTN  + KOR_MTN)  / (KOR_YER  - KOR_XTR  + KOR_MTR))  - KOR_MTN  / ((KOR_YEN  - KOR_XTN  + KOR_MTN)  / (KOR_YER  - KOR_XTR  + KOR_MTR))

@IDENTITY KOR_RPDI  = KOR_LABSH * 0.5 * (KOR_YER(-1)  + KOR_GDI(-1)) * KOR_YED(-1) / KOR_HIC(-1) * (KOR_LNN / KOR_LNN(-1)  + KOR_TECHL - KOR_TECHL(-1)) + KOR_REMIT / KOR_HIC  + KOR_EXPSP / KOR_HIC  - KOR_TAX / KOR_HIC

DLOG(KOR_YFT)  = (1 - KOR_ALPHA - KOR_LABSH) * DLOG(KOR_K(-1) / KOR_LFN(-1))  + (1 - KOR_ALPHA) * DLOG(KOR_LFN)  + KOR_LABSH * D(KOR_TECHL)  + KOR_ALPHA * (DLOG(KOR_EC)  + D(KOR_EFF) )  - ( KOR_CLIMLOSS / KOR_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (KOR_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY KOR_K  = KOR_K(-1) * (1 - KOR_DEP) + KOR_ITR

DLOG(KOR_MTD)  = (1  - KOR_OMS) * ( DLOG(KOR_CMUD)  + DLOG(KOR_EXR) )  + KOR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KOR_EXR) )

DLOG(KOR_XTD$)  = (1  - KOR_OXS) * DLOG(KOR_XTDNO$)  + KOR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

KOR_INFT  = 0.95 * KOR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

KOR_OXS  = KOR_OXS(-1)

KOR_OMS  = KOR_OMS(-1) * ((KOR_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * KOR_EXR(-1) / KOR_MTN(-1)) / (KOR_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * KOR_EXR(-2) / KOR_MTN(-2)))^0.25

KOR_CXS  = KOR_CXS(-1)

KOR_FINC  = KOR_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_CAN  = KOR_XTN / KOR_EXR  - KOR_MTN / KOR_EXR  + KOR_REMIT / KOR_EXR  + KOR_CANOTH

@IDENTITY KOR_CANRATIO  = KOR_CAN / KOR_YEN$ * 100

KOR_CANOTH  = KOR_CANOTH(-1)  + ((KOR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KOR_YEN$  / KOR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KOR_REVG / KOR_EXR  - KOR_REVG(-1) / KOR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(KOR_EFEX)  =  - LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.630852709E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.813392668E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  +
