0.02795023896 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01016660838 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01450219062 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007458868749 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008045166072 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002655641323 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003666996884 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02699996562 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009847508787 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04405235888 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04900649183 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08232320764 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

KOR_REMIT  = KOR_REMIT(-1) / KOR_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04122402747 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001422675406 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004024458424 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 1.381600788E-05 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001413399587 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.08299910725 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01312780064 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007870693029 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008065177958 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 8.177583044E-05 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001880892671 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01042063059 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002103204039 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001585778622 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.2667500209 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00708537161 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 9.745886642E-05 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 2.128412025E-05 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005996894232 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001834168398 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002716300764 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01001813447 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002594422237 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 9.559183832E-05 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001345753849 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005440146455 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 9.932589451E-05 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00028378827 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4493821781 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006426310694 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 5.750446524E-05 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 7.841517988E-06 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007385963133 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01481052842 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06179746932 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000521647649 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * KOR_EXR

KOR_GINT  = KOR_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (KOR_LTI  - KOR_LTI(-1))

KOR_GDN  = KOR_GDN(-1) * (KOR_GDFXSH  * (KOR_EXR  / KOR_EXR(-1))  + (1  - KOR_GDFXSH))  - KOR_GLN

@IDENTITY KOR_GDNRATIO  = KOR_GDN / KOR_YEN * 100

KOR_GDFXSH  = ( KOR_GDFXSH(-1) * (KOR_EXR / KOR_EXR(-1) )) / (KOR_GDFXSH(-1) * (KOR_EXR / KOR_EXR(-1))  + 1 - KOR_GDFXSH(-1) )

KOR_TOURSH  = KOR_TOURSH(-1)

KOR_LOCK  = 0

KOR_GCARBR  = KOR_GCARBR(-1)

KOR_GTRADER  = KOR_GTRADER(-1)

KOR_ITAXR  = KOR_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_REV  = KOR_TAX  + KOR_CTAX  + KOR_ITAX  + KOR_GTRADE  + KOR_REVG  + KOR_GCARB  + KOR_GCOM  + KOR_GOTH

@IDENTITY KOR_TAX  = KOR_TAXR * (KOR_LABSH * 0.5 * (KOR_YER(-1)  + KOR_GDI(-1)) * KOR_YED(-1) * (KOR_LNN / KOR_LNN(-1)  + KOR_TECHL - KOR_TECHL(-1)) + KOR_REMIT  + KOR_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY KOR_CTAX  = KOR_CTAXR * KOR_PROF

@IDENTITY KOR_ITAX  = KOR_ITAXR * (KOR_PCR * KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY KOR_GTRADE  = KOR_GTRADER * KOR_XTN

KOR_REVG  = KOR_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (KOR_YER$ / KOR_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - KOR_YER$(-1) / KOR_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * KOR_EXR / KOR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_GCARB  = KOR_GCARBR * KOR_CO2 * KOR_EXR / 1000

KOR_GCOM  = KOR_GCOM(-1) * ( KOR_OILC / (KOR_OILC + KOR_GASC + KOR_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + KOR_GASC / (KOR_OILC + KOR_GASC + KOR_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + KOR_COALC / (KOR_OILC + KOR_GASC + KOR_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

KOR_GOTH  = KOR_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_EXP  = KOR_EXPE  + KOR_EXPH  + KOR_EXPSP  + KOR_OGC  + KOR_OGI  + KOR_GIP

KOR_EXPE  = KOR_EXPE(-1) * (KOR_YFT / KOR_YFT(-1)) * (KOR_YED / KOR_YED(-1))

KOR_EXPH = KOR_EXPH(-1) * (KOR_YFT / KOR_YFT(-1)) * (KOR_YED / KOR_YED(-1))

KOR_EXPSP  = KOR_EXPSP(-1) * (KOR_YFT / KOR_YFT(-1)) * (KOR_YED / KOR_YED(-1)) * (KOR_POPT - KOR_LNN) / (KOR_POPT(-1) - KOR_LNN(-1))

DLOG(KOR_OGI)  = DLOG(KOR_YFT)  + DLOG(KOR_YED)

KOR_GCR  = KOR_GCR(-1)  + ( KOR_OGC / KOR_YED - KOR_OGC(-1) / KOR_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (KOR_EXPH ) / KOR_YED  - (KOR_EXPH(-1) ) / KOR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KOR_EXPE ) / KOR_YED  - (KOR_EXPE(-1) ) / KOR_YED(-1) )

KOR_IGR  = KOR_IGR(-1) + (KOR_OGI / KOR_YED - KOR_OGI(-1) / KOR_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (KOR_EXPH ) / KOR_YED  - (KOR_EXPH(-1) ) / KOR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (KOR_EXPE ) / KOR_YED  - (KOR_EXPE(-1) ) / KOR_YED(-1) )

KOR_GIP  = ( KOR_GIP(-1)  + ( KOR_GDN(-1) - KOR_GDN(-2) ) * KOR_GINT(-1) / 100  + KOR_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( KOR_GINT(-1) / 100 - KOR_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (KOR_GDFXSH * (KOR_EXR / KOR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KOR_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY KOR_GLN  = KOR_REV  - KOR_EXP

@IDENTITY KOR_GLNRATIO  = KOR_GLN / KOR_YEN * 100

KOR_GLNT  = KOR_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

KOR_TFP  = KOR_LABSH * (KOR_TECHL  - KOR_TECHL(-1))

KOR_LABSH  = KOR_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY KOR_LFN  = KOR_LRX * KOR_POPWA

KOR_LRX  = KOR_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(KOR_YER(-1) / KOR_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY KOR_URX  = (1 - KOR_LNN / KOR_LFN) * 100

KOR_URXF  = KOR_URXF(-1) * KOR_URX / KOR_URX(-1) * KOR_LNN / KOR_LNNF / (KOR_LNN(-1) / KOR_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(KOR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KOR_PCR  / KOR_POPT)

KOR_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(KOR_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

KOR_HEAD19  = KOR_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KOR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI^2)  , KOR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KOR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KOR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

KOR_HEAD55  = KOR_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KOR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI^2)  , KOR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KOR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KOR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(KOR_XTR)  = DLOG(KOR_WDR)  + (1  - KOR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(KOR_XTDNO$  / KOR_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * KOR_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(KOR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (KOR_EXPH(-1) / KOR_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (KOR_EXPH(-1) / KOR_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(KOR_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(KOR_PM25)

KOR_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( KOR_EXPSP / KOR_YEN )

DLOG(KOR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - KOR_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (KOR_FINC - KOR_FINC(-1))

DLOG(KOR_PCR)  =  - 0.492119536969998  +  - 0.306426261851933 * (LOG(KOR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KOR_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (KOR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KOR_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(KOR_POPT)  +  - 0.239828529133296 * (DLOG(KOR_HIC)  - KOR_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * KOR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * KOR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KOR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KOR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KOR_IPR)  =  - 0.147227965164191  - 0.1 * (LOG(KOR_IPR(-1)  / KOR_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * KOR_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * KOR_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(KOR_PCR  + KOR_GCR(-1) + KOR_IGR(-1) + KOR_XTN  / KOR_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(KOR_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (KOR_USER - KOR_USER(-1))  - (0 * KOR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KOR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KOR_FUELSH - KOR_TOURSH)) * KOR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * KOR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * KOR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - KOR_FUELSH - KOR_TOURSH)) * KOR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(KOR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(KOR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(KOR_MTR)  =  - 0.130818156481782  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(KOR_MTR(-1))  - LOG(KOR_PCR(-1) + KOR_ITR(-1) + KOR_GCR(-1) + KOR_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(KOR_YFT(-1) / KOR_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(KOR_CMUD(-1) * KOR_EXR(-1)  / KOR_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * KOR_OMS * LOG(KOR_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.312316726700507  * DLOG(KOR_XTR)  + 0.518346144429005  * DLOG(KOR_PCR)  + 0.342391552198479  * DLOG(KOR_IPR)  + 0.00527631833580642  * DLOG(KOR_GCR + KOR_IGR)

KOR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * KOR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * KOR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * KOR_OILC

KOR_POIL  = KOR_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( KOR_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - KOR_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

KOR_PG  = KOR_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( KOR_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - KOR_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

KOR_PC  = KOR_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( KOR_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - KOR_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(KOR_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

KOR_PE  = KOR_PE(-1) * ( KOR_OILC(-1) / (KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) * KOR_POIL / KOR_POIL(-1)  + KOR_GASC(-1) / (KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) * KOR_PG / KOR_PG(-1)  + KOR_COALC(-1) / (KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) * KOR_PC / KOR_PC(-1)  + KOR_RC(-1) / (KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) * KOR_PR / KOR_PR(-1) )

D(KOR_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(KOR_PM25)  = 0.2 * (KOR_COALC(-1) / KOR_EC(-1) - KOR_COALC(-2) / KOR_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (KOR_COALC(-2) / KOR_EC(-2) - KOR_COALC(-3) / KOR_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (KOR_OILC(-1) / KOR_EC(-1) - KOR_OILC(-2) / KOR_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (KOR_OILC(-2) / KOR_EC(-2) - KOR_OILC(-3) / KOR_EC(-3))

DLOG(KOR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(KOR_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(KOR_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(KOR_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(KOR_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KOR_PE * KOR_EXR / KOR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KOR_PE(-1) * KOR_EXR(-1) / KOR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KOR_PE(-2) * KOR_EXR(-2) / KOR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(KOR_PE(-3) * KOR_EXR(-3) / KOR_HIC(-3))  - (KOR_EFF - KOR_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(KOR_COALC)  = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KOR_COALC(-1) / KOR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.13059544104963 * LOG(KOR_PE(-1) / KOR_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) / KOR_EC(-1))

DLOG(KOR_GASC)  = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(KOR_GASC(-1) / KOR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.162868134151063 * LOG(KOR_PE(-1) / KOR_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) / KOR_EC(-1))

DLOG(KOR_RC)  = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KOR_RC(-1) / KOR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.13059544104963 * LOG(KOR_PE(-1) / KOR_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) / KOR_EC(-1))

DLOG(KOR_OILC)  = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( KOR_OILC(-1) / KOR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.13059544104963 * LOG(KOR_PE(-1) / KOR_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((KOR_COALC(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1) + KOR_OILC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)) / KOR_EC(-1))

KOR_EXR  = KOR_EXR(-1) * ( ( (KOR_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (KOR_INT  - USA_INT)  - (KOR_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(RUS_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(RUS_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(RUS_MTD)  + 0.4 * (RUS_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (RUS_YER / RUS_YFT  - RUS_YER(-1) / RUS_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + RUS_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + RUS_GCARB / RUS_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (RUS_PREM - RUS_PREM(-1)) / 100

RUS_YED  = RUS_YED(-1) * RUS_HIC / RUS_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_INT  = RUS_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_LTI  = RUS_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (RUS_INT - RUS_INT(-1))  + (RUS_PREM  - RUS_PREM(-1)) / 100

RUS_PREM  = RUS_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (RUS_GDNRATIO(-1)  - RUS_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(RUS_LNN)  = DLOG(RUS_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(RUS_LNN(-1))  - LOG(RUS_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(RUS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(RUS_LNNF)  = DLOG(RUS_LNN)

RUS_FUELSH  = RUS_FUELSH(-1)

RUS_TAXR  = RUS_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( RUS_GLNT(-1)  - RUS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * RUS_YEN(-1) / ( ( RUS_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (RUS_YER(-2)  + RUS_GDI(-2)) * RUS_YED(-2) * (RUS_LNN(-1) / RUS_LNN(-2)  + RUS_TECHL(-1) - RUS_TECHL(-2) ) ) + RUS_REMIT(-1)  + RUS_EXPSP(-1) ) * RUS_SOLV

RUS_CTAXR  = RUS_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( RUS_GLNT(-1)  - RUS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * RUS_YEN(-1) / ( RUS_PROF(-1) ) * RUS_SOLV

(RUS_OGC)  = RUS_OGC(-1) * (RUS_YFT / RUS_YFT(-1) * RUS_YED / RUS_YED(-1))

RUS_USER  = (RUS_LTI  - RUS_INFT  + RUS_DEP * 100) / (1  - RUS_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (RUS_GCARB / RUS_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY RUS_XTN  = RUS_XTD$ * RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") * RUS_XTR

@IDENTITY RUS_YEN  = RUS_YER  * RUS_YED

@IDENTITY RUS_MTN  = RUS_MTD  * RUS_MTR

@IDENTITY RUS_XTN$  = RUS_XTN / RUS_EXR

@IDENTITY RUS_YEN$  = RUS_YEN / RUS_EXR

@IDENTITY RUS_MTN$  = RUS_MTN / RUS_EXR

@IDENTITY RUS_MTR$  = RUS_MTR$(-1) * RUS_MTR / RUS_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_XTR$  = RUS_XTR$(-1) * RUS_XTR / RUS_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_YER$  = RUS_YER$(-1) * RUS_YER / RUS_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_YFT$  = RUS_YFT$(-1) * RUS_YFT / RUS_YFT(-1)

RUS_POPT  = RUS_POPT(-1)  - RUS_LIVES

RUS_POPWA  = RUS_POPWA(-1) * RUS_POPT / RUS_POPT(-1)

RUS_SCR  = RUS_SCR(-1)  + ((RUS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (RUS_YFT(-1) / RUS_YER(-1)  - RUS_YFT(-2) / RUS_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY RUS_ITR  = RUS_IGR  + RUS_IPR

@IDENTITY RUS_YER  = RUS_PCR  + RUS_GCR  + RUS_ITR  + RUS_SCR  + RUS_XTR  - RUS_MTR

@IDENTITY RUS_PROF  = (RUS_YEN - RUS_ITAX) * (1 - RUS_LABSH)

@IDENTITY RUS_GDI  = RUS_YER  - RUS_XTR  + RUS_MTR  + RUS_XTN  / ((RUS_YEN  - RUS_XTN  + RUS_MTN)  / (RUS_YER  - RUS_XTR  + RUS_MTR))  - RUS_MTN  / ((RUS_YEN  - RUS_XTN  + RUS_MTN)  / (RUS_YER  - RUS_XTR  + RUS_MTR))

@IDENTITY RUS_RPDI  = RUS_LABSH * 0.5 * (RUS_YER(-1)  + RUS_GDI(-1)) * RUS_YED(-1) / RUS_HIC(-1) * (RUS_LNN / RUS_LNN(-1)  + RUS_TECHL - RUS_TECHL(-1)) + RUS_REMIT / RUS_HIC  + RUS_EXPSP / RUS_HIC  - RUS_TAX / RUS_HIC

DLOG(RUS_YFT)  = (1 - RUS_ALPHA - RUS_LABSH) * DLOG(RUS_K(-1) / RUS_LFN(-1))  + (1 - RUS_ALPHA) * DLOG(RUS_LFN)  + RUS_LABSH * D(RUS_TECHL)  + RUS_ALPHA * (DLOG(RUS_EC)  + D(RUS_EFF) )  - ( RUS_CLIMLOSS / RUS_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (RUS_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY RUS_K  = RUS_K(-1) * (1 - RUS_DEP) + RUS_ITR

DLOG(RUS_MTD)  = (1  - RUS_OMS) * ( DLOG(RUS_CMUD)  + DLOG(RUS_EXR) )  + RUS_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(RUS_EXR) )

DLOG(RUS_XTD$)  = (1  - RUS_OXS) * DLOG(RUS_XTDNO$)  + RUS_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

RUS_INFT  = 0.95 * RUS_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

RUS_OXS  = RUS_OXS(-1)

RUS_OMS  = RUS_OMS(-1) * ((RUS_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * RUS_EXR(-1) / RUS_MTN(-1)) / (RUS_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * RUS_EXR(-2) / RUS_MTN(-2)))^0.25

RUS_CXS  = RUS_CXS(-1)

RUS_FINC  = RUS_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_CAN  = RUS_XTN / RUS_EXR  - RUS_MTN / RUS_EXR  + RUS_REMIT / RUS_EXR  + RUS_CANOTH

@IDENTITY RUS_CANRATIO  = RUS_CAN / RUS_YEN$ * 100

RUS_CANOTH  = RUS_CANOTH(-1)  + ((RUS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (RUS_YEN$  / RUS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + RUS_REVG / RUS_EXR  - RUS_REVG(-1) / RUS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(RUS_EFEX)  =  - LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002787754486 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003726082259 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007557039122 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02171105991 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01100149677 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002668770557 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.043902897 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05264587545 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 7.186058834E-07 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0006328852347 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4683175462 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.008711551693 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01224857505 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * RUS_EXR

RUS_GINT  = RUS_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 12 * (RUS_LTI  - RUS_LTI(-1))

RUS_GDN  = RUS_GDN(-1) * (RUS_GDFXSH  * (RUS_EXR  / RUS_EXR(-1))  + (1  - RUS_GDFXSH))  - RUS_GLN

@IDENTITY RUS_GDNRATIO  = RUS_GDN / RUS_YEN * 100

RUS_GDFXSH  = ( RUS_GDFXSH(-1) * (RUS_EXR / RUS_EXR(-1) )) / (RUS_GDFXSH(-1) * (RUS_EXR / RUS_EXR(-1))  + 1 - RUS_GDFXSH(-1) )

RUS_TOURSH  = RUS_TOURSH(-1)

RUS_LOCK  = 0

RUS_GCARBR  = RUS_GCARBR(-1)

RUS_GTRADER  = RUS_GTRADER(-1)

RUS_ITAXR  = RUS_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_REV  = RUS_TAX  + RUS_CTAX  + RUS_ITAX  + RUS_GTRADE  + RUS_REVG  + RUS_GCARB  + RUS_GCOM  + RUS_GOTH

@IDENTITY RUS_TAX  = RUS_TAXR * (RUS_LABSH * 0.5 * (RUS_YER(-1)  + RUS_GDI(-1)) * RUS_YED(-1) * (RUS_LNN / RUS_LNN(-1)  + RUS_TECHL - RUS_TECHL(-1)) + RUS_REMIT  + RUS_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY RUS_CTAX  = RUS_CTAXR * RUS_PROF

@IDENTITY RUS_ITAX  = RUS_ITAXR * (RUS_PCR * RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY RUS_GTRADE  = RUS_GTRADER * RUS_XTN

RUS_REVG  = RUS_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (RUS_YER$ / RUS_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - RUS_YER$(-1) / RUS_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * RUS_EXR / RUS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_GCARB  = RUS_GCARBR * RUS_CO2 * RUS_EXR / 1000

RUS_GCOM  = RUS_GCOM(-1) * ( RUS_OILC / (RUS_OILC + RUS_GASC + RUS_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + RUS_GASC / (RUS_OILC + RUS_GASC + RUS_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + RUS_COALC / (RUS_OILC + RUS_GASC + RUS_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

RUS_GOTH  = RUS_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_EXP  = RUS_EXPE  + RUS_EXPH  + RUS_EXPSP  + RUS_OGC  + RUS_OGI  + RUS_GIP

RUS_EXPE  = RUS_EXPE(-1) * (RUS_YFT / RUS_YFT(-1)) * (RUS_YED / RUS_YED(-1))

RUS_EXPH = RUS_EXPH(-1) * (RUS_YFT / RUS_YFT(-1)) * (RUS_YED / RUS_YED(-1))

RUS_EXPSP  = RUS_EXPSP(-1) * (RUS_YFT / RUS_YFT(-1)) * (RUS_YED / RUS_YED(-1)) * (RUS_POPT - RUS_LNN) / (RUS_POPT(-1) - RUS_LNN(-1))

DLOG(RUS_OGI)  = DLOG(RUS_YFT)  + DLOG(RUS_YED)

RUS_GCR  = RUS_GCR(-1)  + ( RUS_OGC / RUS_YED - RUS_OGC(-1) / RUS_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (RUS_EXPH ) / RUS_YED  - (RUS_EXPH(-1) ) / RUS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (RUS_EXPE ) / RUS_YED  - (RUS_EXPE(-1) ) / RUS_YED(-1) )

RUS_IGR  = RUS_IGR(-1) + (RUS_OGI / RUS_YED - RUS_OGI(-1) / RUS_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (RUS_EXPH ) / RUS_YED  - (RUS_EXPH(-1) ) / RUS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (RUS_EXPE ) / RUS_YED  - (RUS_EXPE(-1) ) / RUS_YED(-1) )

RUS_GIP  = ( RUS_GIP(-1)  + ( RUS_GDN(-1) - RUS_GDN(-2) ) * RUS_GINT(-1) / 100  + RUS_GDN(-13) / 12 * ( RUS_GINT(-1) / 100 - RUS_GINT(-13) / 100 ) ) * (RUS_GDFXSH * (RUS_EXR / RUS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - RUS_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY RUS_GLN  = RUS_REV  - RUS_EXP

@IDENTITY RUS_GLNRATIO  = RUS_GLN / RUS_YEN * 100

RUS_GLNT  = RUS_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

RUS_TFP  = RUS_LABSH * (RUS_TECHL  - RUS_TECHL(-1))

RUS_LABSH  = RUS_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY RUS_LFN  = RUS_LRX * RUS_POPWA

RUS_LRX  = RUS_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(RUS_YER(-1) / RUS_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY RUS_URX  = (1 - RUS_LNN / RUS_LFN) * 100

RUS_URXF  = RUS_URXF(-1) * RUS_URX / RUS_URX(-1) * RUS_LNN / RUS_LNNF / (RUS_LNN(-1) / RUS_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(RUS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(RUS_PCR  / RUS_POPT)

RUS_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(RUS_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

RUS_HEAD19  = RUS_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(RUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI^2)  , RUS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(RUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , RUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

RUS_HEAD55  = RUS_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(RUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI^2)  , RUS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(RUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , RUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(RUS_XTR)  = DLOG(RUS_WDR)  + (1  - RUS_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(RUS_XTDNO$  / RUS_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * RUS_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(RUS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (RUS_EXPH(-1) / RUS_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (RUS_EXPH(-1) / RUS_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(RUS_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(RUS_PM25)

RUS_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( RUS_EXPSP / RUS_YEN )

DLOG(RUS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - RUS_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (RUS_FINC - RUS_FINC(-1))

DLOG(RUS_PCR)  =  - 0.0838150039827791  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(RUS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(RUS_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (RUS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.372428601732229  * DLOG(RUS_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.372428601732229)  * DLOG(RUS_POPT)  +  - 0.639358972047712 * (DLOG(RUS_HIC)  - RUS_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * RUS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * RUS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(RUS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(RUS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(RUS_IPR)  =  - 0.161741076356764  - 0.1 * (LOG(RUS_IPR(-1)  / RUS_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * RUS_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * RUS_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(RUS_PCR  + RUS_GCR(-1) + RUS_IGR(-1) + RUS_XTN  / RUS_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(RUS_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (RUS_USER - RUS_USER(-1))  - (0 * RUS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * RUS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - RUS_FUELSH - RUS_TOURSH)) * RUS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * RUS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * RUS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - RUS_FUELSH - RUS_TOURSH)) * RUS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(RUS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(RUS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(RUS_MTR)  =  - 0.248843949431877  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(RUS_MTR(-1))  - LOG(RUS_PCR(-1) + RUS_ITR(-1) + RUS_GCR(-1) + RUS_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(RUS_YFT(-1) / RUS_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(RUS_CMUD(-1) * RUS_EXR(-1)  / RUS_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * RUS_OMS * LOG(RUS_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.779274992795993  * DLOG(RUS_XTR)  + 0.933911918233878  * DLOG(RUS_PCR)  + 0.312480801945176  * DLOG(RUS_IPR)  + 0.303155135985311  * DLOG(RUS_GCR + RUS_IGR)

RUS_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * RUS_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * RUS_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * RUS_OILC

RUS_POIL  = RUS_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( RUS_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - RUS_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

RUS_PG  = RUS_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( RUS_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - RUS_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

RUS_PC  = RUS_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( RUS_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - RUS_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(RUS_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

RUS_PE  = RUS_PE(-1) * ( RUS_OILC(-1) / (RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) * RUS_POIL / RUS_POIL(-1)  + RUS_GASC(-1) / (RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) * RUS_PG / RUS_PG(-1)  + RUS_COALC(-1) / (RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) * RUS_PC / RUS_PC(-1)  + RUS_RC(-1) / (RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) * RUS_PR / RUS_PR(-1) )

D(RUS_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(RUS_PM25)  = 0.2 * (RUS_COALC(-1) / RUS_EC(-1) - RUS_COALC(-2) / RUS_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (RUS_COALC(-2) / RUS_EC(-2) - RUS_COALC(-3) / RUS_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (RUS_OILC(-1) / RUS_EC(-1) - RUS_OILC(-2) / RUS_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (RUS_OILC(-2) / RUS_EC(-2) - RUS_OILC(-3) / RUS_EC(-3))

DLOG(RUS_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(RUS_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(RUS_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(RUS_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(RUS_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(RUS_PE * RUS_EXR / RUS_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(RUS_PE(-1) * RUS_EXR(-1) / RUS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(RUS_PE(-2) * RUS_EXR(-2) / RUS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(RUS_PE(-3) * RUS_EXR(-3) / RUS_HIC(-3))  - (RUS_EFF - RUS_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(RUS_COALC)  = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(RUS_COALC(-1) / RUS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.121185827085504 * LOG(RUS_PE(-1) / RUS_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) / RUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(RUS_GASC)  = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(RUS_GASC(-1) / RUS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.536663286922807 * LOG(RUS_PE(-1) / RUS_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) / RUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(RUS_RC)  = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( RUS_RC(-1) / RUS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.121185827085504 * LOG(RUS_PE(-1) / RUS_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) / RUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(RUS_OILC)  = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( RUS_OILC(-1) / RUS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.121185827085504 * LOG(RUS_PE(-1) / RUS_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((RUS_COALC(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1) + RUS_OILC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)) / RUS_EC(-1))

DLOG(RUS_EXR) = LOG(((RUS_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.354815963604207*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((RUS_INT - USA_INT) - (RUS_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@INNOV RUS_EXR  0.287398643056789

DLOG(WSM_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(WSM_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(WSM_MTD)  + 0.4 * (WSM_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (WSM_YER / WSM_YFT  - WSM_YER(-1) / WSM_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + WSM_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + WSM_GCARB / WSM_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (WSM_PREM - WSM_PREM(-1)) / 100

WSM_YED  = WSM_YED(-1) * WSM_HIC / WSM_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_INT  = WSM_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_LTI  = WSM_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (WSM_INT - WSM_INT(-1))  + (WSM_PREM  - WSM_PREM(-1)) / 100

WSM_PREM  = WSM_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (WSM_GDNRATIO(-1)  - WSM_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(WSM_LNN)  = DLOG(WSM_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(WSM_LNN(-1))  - LOG(WSM_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(WSM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(WSM_LNNF)  = DLOG(WSM_LNN)

WSM_FUELSH  = WSM_FUELSH(-1)

WSM_TAXR  = WSM_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( WSM_GLNT(-1)  - WSM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * WSM_YEN(-1) / ( ( WSM_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (WSM_YER(-2)  + WSM_GDI(-2)) * WSM_YED(-2) * (WSM_LNN(-1) / WSM_LNN(-2)  + WSM_TECHL(-1) - WSM_TECHL(-2) ) ) + WSM_REMIT(-1)  + WSM_EXPSP(-1) ) * WSM_SOLV

WSM_CTAXR  = WSM_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( WSM_GLNT(-1)  - WSM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * WSM_YEN(-1) / ( WSM_PROF(-1) ) * WSM_SOLV

(WSM_OGC)  = WSM_OGC(-1) * (WSM_YFT / WSM_YFT(-1) * WSM_YED / WSM_YED(-1))

WSM_USER  = (WSM_LTI  - WSM_INFT  + WSM_DEP * 100) / (1  - WSM_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (WSM_GCARB / WSM_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY WSM_XTN  = WSM_XTD$ * WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") * WSM_XTR

@IDENTITY WSM_YEN  = WSM_YER  * WSM_YED

@IDENTITY WSM_MTN  = WSM_MTD  * WSM_MTR

@IDENTITY WSM_XTN$  = WSM_XTN / WSM_EXR

@IDENTITY WSM_YEN$  = WSM_YEN / WSM_EXR

@IDENTITY WSM_MTN$  = WSM_MTN / WSM_EXR

@IDENTITY WSM_MTR$  = WSM_MTR$(-1) * WSM_MTR / WSM_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_XTR$  = WSM_XTR$(-1) * WSM_XTR / WSM_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_YER$  = WSM_YER$(-1) * WSM_YER / WSM_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_YFT$  = WSM_YFT$(-1) * WSM_YFT / WSM_YFT(-1)

WSM_POPT  = WSM_POPT(-1)  - WSM_LIVES

WSM_POPWA  = WSM_POPWA(-1) * WSM_POPT / WSM_POPT(-1)

WSM_SCR  = WSM_SCR(-1)  + ((WSM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (WSM_YFT(-1) / WSM_YER(-1)  - WSM_YFT(-2) / WSM_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY WSM_ITR  = WSM_IGR  + WSM_IPR

@IDENTITY WSM_YER  = WSM_PCR  + WSM_GCR  + WSM_ITR  + WSM_SCR  + WSM_XTR  - WSM_MTR

@IDENTITY WSM_PROF  = (WSM_YEN - WSM_ITAX) * (1 - WSM_LABSH)

@IDENTITY WSM_GDI  = WSM_YER  - WSM_XTR  + WSM_MTR  + WSM_XTN  / ((WSM_YEN  - WSM_XTN  + WSM_MTN)  / (WSM_YER  - WSM_XTR  + WSM_MTR))  - WSM_MTN  / ((WSM_YEN  - WSM_XTN  + WSM_MTN)  / (WSM_YER  - WSM_XTR  + WSM_MTR))

@IDENTITY WSM_RPDI  = WSM_LABSH * 0.5 * (WSM_YER(-1)  + WSM_GDI(-1)) * WSM_YED(-1) / WSM_HIC(-1) * (WSM_LNN / WSM_LNN(-1)  + WSM_TECHL - WSM_TECHL(-1)) + WSM_REMIT / WSM_HIC  + WSM_EXPSP / WSM_HIC  - WSM_TAX / WSM_HIC

DLOG(WSM_YFT)  = (1 - WSM_ALPHA - WSM_LABSH) * DLOG(WSM_K(-1) / WSM_LFN(-1))  + (1 - WSM_ALPHA) * DLOG(WSM_LFN)  + WSM_LABSH * D(WSM_TECHL)  + WSM_ALPHA * (DLOG(WSM_EC)  + D(WSM_EFF) )  - ( WSM_CLIMLOSS / WSM_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (WSM_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY WSM_K  = WSM_K(-1) * (1 - WSM_DEP) + WSM_ITR

DLOG(WSM_MTD)  = (1  - WSM_OMS) * ( DLOG(WSM_CMUD)  + DLOG(WSM_EXR) )  + WSM_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(WSM_EXR) )

DLOG(WSM_XTD$)  = (1  - WSM_OXS) * DLOG(WSM_XTDNO$)  + WSM_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

WSM_INFT  = 0.95 * WSM_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

WSM_OXS  = WSM_OXS(-1)

WSM_OMS  = WSM_OMS(-1) * ((WSM_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * WSM_EXR(-1) / WSM_MTN(-1)) / (WSM_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * WSM_EXR(-2) / WSM_MTN(-2)))^0.25

WSM_CXS  = WSM_CXS(-1)

WSM_FINC  = WSM_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_CAN  = WSM_XTN / WSM_EXR  - WSM_MTN / WSM_EXR  + WSM_REMIT / WSM_EXR  + WSM_CANOTH

@IDENTITY WSM_CANRATIO  = WSM_CAN / WSM_YEN$ * 100

WSM_CANOTH  = WSM_CANOTH(-1)  + ((WSM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (WSM_YEN$  / WSM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + WSM_REVG / WSM_EXR  - WSM_REVG(-1) / WSM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_GDNRATIO  = WSM_GDN / WSM_YEN * 100

WSM_GDFXSH  = ( WSM_GDFXSH(-1) * (WSM_EXR / WSM_EXR(-1) )) / (WSM_GDFXSH(-1) * (WSM_EXR / WSM_EXR(-1))  + 1 - WSM_GDFXSH(-1) )

WSM_TOURSH  = WSM_TOURSH(-1)

WSM_LOCK  = 0

@IDENTITY WSM_REV  = WSM_TAX  + WSM_CTAX  + WSM_ITAX  + WSM_GTRADE  + WSM_REVG  + WSM_GCARB  + WSM_GCOM  + WSM_GOTH

@IDENTITY WSM_TAX  = WSM_TAXR * (WSM_LABSH * 0.5 * (WSM_YER(-1)  + WSM_GDI(-1)) * WSM_YED(-1) * (WSM_LNN / WSM_LNN(-1)  + WSM_TECHL - WSM_TECHL(-1)) + WSM_REMIT  + WSM_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY WSM_CTAX  = WSM_CTAXR * WSM_PROF

@IDENTITY WSM_ITAX  = WSM_ITAXR * (WSM_PCR * WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY WSM_GTRADE  = WSM_GTRADER * WSM_XTN

WSM_REVG  = WSM_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (WSM_YER$ / WSM_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - WSM_YER$(-1) / WSM_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * WSM_EXR / WSM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_GCARB  = WSM_GCARBR * WSM_CO2 * WSM_EXR / 1000

WSM_GCOM  = WSM_GCOM(-1) * ( WSM_OILC / (WSM_OILC + WSM_GASC + WSM_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + WSM_GASC / (WSM_OILC + WSM_GASC + WSM_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + WSM_COALC / (WSM_OILC + WSM_GASC + WSM_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

WSM_GOTH  = WSM_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_EXP  = WSM_EXPE  + WSM_EXPH  + WSM_EXPSP  + WSM_OGC  + WSM_OGI  + WSM_GIP

WSM_EXPE  = WSM_EXPE(-1) * (WSM_YFT / WSM_YFT(-1)) * (WSM_YED / WSM_YED(-1))

WSM_EXPH = WSM_EXPH(-1) * (WSM_YFT / WSM_YFT(-1)) * (WSM_YED / WSM_YED(-1))

WSM_EXPSP  = WSM_EXPSP(-1) * (WSM_YFT / WSM_YFT(-1)) * (WSM_YED / WSM_YED(-1)) * (WSM_POPT - WSM_LNN) / (WSM_POPT(-1) - WSM_LNN(-1))

DLOG(WSM_OGI)  = DLOG(WSM_YFT)  + DLOG(WSM_YED)

WSM_GCR  = WSM_GCR(-1)  + ( WSM_OGC / WSM_YED - WSM_OGC(-1) / WSM_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (WSM_EXPH ) / WSM_YED  - (WSM_EXPH(-1) ) / WSM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (WSM_EXPE ) / WSM_YED  - (WSM_EXPE(-1) ) / WSM_YED(-1) )

WSM_IGR  = WSM_IGR(-1) + (WSM_OGI / WSM_YED - WSM_OGI(-1) / WSM_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (WSM_EXPH ) / WSM_YED  - (WSM_EXPH(-1) ) / WSM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (WSM_EXPE ) / WSM_YED  - (WSM_EXPE(-1) ) / WSM_YED(-1) )

WSM_GIP  = ( WSM_GIP(-1)  + ( WSM_GDN(-1) - WSM_GDN(-2) ) * WSM_GINT(-1) / 100  + WSM_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( WSM_GINT(-1) / 100 - WSM_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (WSM_GDFXSH * (WSM_EXR / WSM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - WSM_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY WSM_GLN  = WSM_REV  - WSM_EXP

@IDENTITY WSM_GLNRATIO  = WSM_GLN / WSM_YEN * 100

WSM_GLNT  = WSM_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

WSM_TFP  = WSM_LABSH * (WSM_TECHL  - WSM_TECHL(-1))

WSM_LABSH  = WSM_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY WSM_LFN  = WSM_LRX * WSM_POPWA

WSM_LRX  = WSM_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(WSM_YER(-1) / WSM_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY WSM_URX  = (1 - WSM_LNN / WSM_LFN) * 100

WSM_URXF  = WSM_URXF(-1) * WSM_URX / WSM_URX(-1) * WSM_LNN / WSM_LNNF / (WSM_LNN(-1) / WSM_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(WSM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(WSM_PCR  / WSM_POPT)

WSM_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(WSM_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

WSM_HEAD19  = WSM_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(WSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI^2)  , WSM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(WSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , WSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

WSM_HEAD55  = WSM_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(WSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI^2)  , WSM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(WSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , WSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(WSM_XTR)  = DLOG(WSM_WDR)  + (1  - WSM_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(WSM_XTDNO$  / WSM_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * WSM_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(WSM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (WSM_EXPH(-1) / WSM_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (WSM_EXPH(-1) / WSM_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(WSM_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(WSM_PM25)

WSM_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( WSM_EXPSP / WSM_YEN )

DLOG(WSM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - WSM_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (WSM_FINC - WSM_FINC(-1))

DLOG(WSM_PCR)  =  - 0.0389445394405763  +  - 0.106864760571152 * (LOG(WSM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(WSM_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (WSM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(WSM_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(WSM_POPT)  +  - 0.142806796825551 * (DLOG(WSM_HIC)  - WSM_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * WSM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * WSM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(WSM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(WSM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(WSM_IPR)  =  - 0.278340527418064  - 0.1 * (LOG(WSM_IPR(-1)  / WSM_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * WSM_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * WSM_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(WSM_PCR  + WSM_GCR(-1) + WSM_IGR(-1) + WSM_XTN  / WSM_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(WSM_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (WSM_USER - WSM_USER(-1))  - (0 * WSM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * WSM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - WSM_FUELSH - WSM_TOURSH)) * WSM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * WSM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * WSM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - WSM_FUELSH - WSM_TOURSH)) * WSM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(WSM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(WSM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(WSM_MTR)  =  - 0.147584379056393  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(WSM_MTR(-1))  - LOG(WSM_PCR(-1) + WSM_ITR(-1) + WSM_GCR(-1) + WSM_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(WSM_YFT(-1) / WSM_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(WSM_CMUD(-1) * WSM_EXR(-1)  / WSM_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * WSM_OMS * LOG(WSM_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.333729855636175  * DLOG(WSM_XTR)  + 0.693369141202038  * DLOG(WSM_PCR)  + 0.0615939069780996  * DLOG(WSM_IPR)  + 0.137704750696508  * DLOG(WSM_GCR + WSM_IGR)

WSM_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * WSM_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * WSM_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * WSM_OILC

WSM_POIL  = WSM_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( WSM_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - WSM_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

WSM_PG  = WSM_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( WSM_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - WSM_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

WSM_PC  = WSM_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( WSM_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - WSM_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(WSM_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

WSM_PE  = WSM_PE(-1) * ( WSM_OILC(-1) / (WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) * WSM_POIL / WSM_POIL(-1)  + WSM_GASC(-1) / (WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) * WSM_PG / WSM_PG(-1)  + WSM_COALC(-1) / (WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) * WSM_PC / WSM_PC(-1)  + WSM_RC(-1) / (WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) * WSM_PR / WSM_PR(-1) )

D(WSM_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(WSM_PM25)  = 0.2 * (WSM_COALC(-1) / WSM_EC(-1) - WSM_COALC(-2) / WSM_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (WSM_COALC(-2) / WSM_EC(-2) - WSM_COALC(-3) / WSM_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (WSM_OILC(-1) / WSM_EC(-1) - WSM_OILC(-2) / WSM_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (WSM_OILC(-2) / WSM_EC(-2) - WSM_OILC(-3) / WSM_EC(-3))

DLOG(WSM_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(WSM_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(WSM_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(WSM_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(WSM_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WSM_PE * WSM_EXR / WSM_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WSM_PE(-1) * WSM_EXR(-1) / WSM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WSM_PE(-2) * WSM_EXR(-2) / WSM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WSM_PE(-3) * WSM_EXR(-3) / WSM_HIC(-3))  - (WSM_EFF - WSM_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(WSM_COALC)  = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(WSM_COALC(-1) / WSM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(WSM_PE(-1) / WSM_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) / WSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(WSM_GASC)  = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(WSM_GASC(-1) / WSM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(WSM_PE(-1) / WSM_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) / WSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(WSM_RC)  = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( WSM_RC(-1) / WSM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.341963228898687 * LOG(WSM_PE(-1) / WSM_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) / WSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(WSM_OILC)  = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( WSM_OILC(-1) / WSM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.341963228898687 * LOG(WSM_PE(-1) / WSM_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((WSM_COALC(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1) + WSM_OILC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)) / WSM_EC(-1))

DLOG(WSM_EXR)  = 0.432472115177761 * LOG(1)  + 0.274240971732554 * DLOG(AUS_EXR)  + 0.292647397790988 * DLOG(NZL_EXR)  + 0.000639515298696564 * DLOG(EMU_EXR)

DLOG(SGP_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(SGP_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(SGP_MTD)  + 0.4 * (SGP_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (SGP_YER / SGP_YFT  - SGP_YER(-1) / SGP_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + SGP_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + SGP_GCARB / SGP_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (SGP_PREM - SGP_PREM(-1)) / 100

SGP_YED  = SGP_YED(-1) * SGP_HIC / SGP_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_INT  = SGP_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_LTI  = SGP_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (SGP_INT - SGP_INT(-1))  + (SGP_PREM  - SGP_PREM(-1)) / 100

SGP_PREM  = SGP_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (SGP_GDNRATIO(-1)  - SGP_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(SGP_LNN)  = DLOG(SGP_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(SGP_LNN(-1))  - LOG(SGP_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(SGP_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(SGP_LNNF)  = DLOG(SGP_LNN)

SGP_FUELSH  = SGP_FUELSH(-1)

SGP_TAXR  = SGP_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( SGP_GLNT(-1)  - SGP_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * SGP_YEN(-1) / ( ( SGP_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (SGP_YER(-2)  + SGP_GDI(-2)) * SGP_YED(-2) * (SGP_LNN(-1) / SGP_LNN(-2)  + SGP_TECHL(-1) - SGP_TECHL(-2) ) ) + SGP_REMIT(-1)  + SGP_EXPSP(-1) ) * SGP_SOLV

SGP_CTAXR  = SGP_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( SGP_GLNT(-1)  - SGP_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * SGP_YEN(-1) / ( SGP_PROF(-1) ) * SGP_SOLV

(SGP_OGC)  = SGP_OGC(-1) * (SGP_YFT / SGP_YFT(-1) * SGP_YED / SGP_YED(-1))

SGP_USER  = (SGP_LTI  - SGP_INFT  + SGP_DEP * 100) / (1  - SGP_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (SGP_GCARB / SGP_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY SGP_XTN  = SGP_XTD$ * SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") * SGP_XTR

@IDENTITY SGP_YEN  = SGP_YER  * SGP_YED

@IDENTITY SGP_MTN  = SGP_MTD  * SGP_MTR

@IDENTITY SGP_XTN$  = SGP_XTN / SGP_EXR

@IDENTITY SGP_YEN$  = SGP_YEN / SGP_EXR

@IDENTITY SGP_MTN$  = SGP_MTN / SGP_EXR

@IDENTITY SGP_MTR$  = SGP_MTR$(-1) * SGP_MTR / SGP_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_XTR$  = SGP_XTR$(-1) * SGP_XTR / SGP_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_YER$  = SGP_YER$(-1) * SGP_YER / SGP_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_YFT$  = SGP_YFT$(-1) * SGP_YFT / SGP_YFT(-1)

SGP_POPT  = SGP_POPT(-1)  - SGP_LIVES

SGP_POPWA  = SGP_POPWA(-1) * SGP_POPT / SGP_POPT(-1)

SGP_SCR  = SGP_SCR(-1)  + ((SGP_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (SGP_YFT(-1) / SGP_YER(-1)  - SGP_YFT(-2) / SGP_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY SGP_ITR  = SGP_IGR  + SGP_IPR

@IDENTITY SGP_YER  = SGP_PCR  + SGP_GCR  + SGP_ITR  + SGP_SCR  + SGP_XTR  - SGP_MTR

@IDENTITY SGP_PROF  = (SGP_YEN - SGP_ITAX) * (1 - SGP_LABSH)

@IDENTITY SGP_GDI  = SGP_YER  - SGP_XTR  + SGP_MTR  + SGP_XTN  / ((SGP_YEN  - SGP_XTN  + SGP_MTN)  / (SGP_YER  - SGP_XTR  + SGP_MTR))  - SGP_MTN  / ((SGP_YEN  - SGP_XTN  + SGP_MTN)  / (SGP_YER  - SGP_XTR  + SGP_MTR))

@IDENTITY SGP_RPDI  = SGP_LABSH * 0.5 * (SGP_YER(-1)  + SGP_GDI(-1)) * SGP_YED(-1) / SGP_HIC(-1) * (SGP_LNN / SGP_LNN(-1)  + SGP_TECHL - SGP_TECHL(-1)) + SGP_REMIT / SGP_HIC  + SGP_EXPSP / SGP_HIC  - SGP_TAX / SGP_HIC

DLOG(SGP_YFT)  = (1 - SGP_ALPHA - SGP_LABSH) * DLOG(SGP_K(-1) / SGP_LFN(-1))  + (1 - SGP_ALPHA) * DLOG(SGP_LFN)  + SGP_LABSH * D(SGP_TECHL)  + SGP_ALPHA * (DLOG(SGP_EC)  + D(SGP_EFF) )  - ( SGP_CLIMLOSS / SGP_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (SGP_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY SGP_K  = SGP_K(-1) * (1 - SGP_DEP) + SGP_ITR

DLOG(SGP_MTD)  = (1  - SGP_OMS) * ( DLOG(SGP_CMUD)  + DLOG(SGP_EXR) )  + SGP_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(SGP_EXR) )

DLOG(SGP_XTD$)  = (1  - SGP_OXS) * DLOG(SGP_XTDNO$)  + SGP_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

SGP_INFT  = 0.95 * SGP_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

SGP_OXS  = SGP_OXS(-1)

SGP_OMS  = SGP_OMS(-1) * ((SGP_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * SGP_EXR(-1) / SGP_MTN(-1)) / (SGP_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * SGP_EXR(-2) / SGP_MTN(-2)))^0.25

SGP_CXS  = SGP_CXS(-1)

SGP_FINC  = SGP_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_CAN  = SGP_XTN / SGP_EXR  - SGP_MTN / SGP_EXR  + SGP_REMIT / SGP_EXR  + SGP_CANOTH

@IDENTITY SGP_CANRATIO  = SGP_CAN / SGP_YEN$ * 100

SGP_CANOTH  = SGP_CANOTH(-1)  + ((SGP_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (SGP_YEN$  / SGP_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + SGP_REVG / SGP_EXR  - SGP_REVG(-1) / SGP_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(SGP_EFEX)  =  - LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.030341829E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.61457448E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02788260461 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001666463851 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003223198496 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.203209924E-05 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001706608413 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001409034263 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1524105684 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003299210571 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.878530977E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06223852839 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03963499793 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05510390432 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009562469263 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07526430639 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001576276495 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.34905366E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.621142977E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001448438014 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005832158316 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07885852009 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000421294216 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 7.536736834E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000163589742 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002820961217 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001611193639 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004294397806 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001112790478 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003645709575 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01653361415 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0429965701 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004600659878 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.224837944E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.918237892E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002248682315 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.575264767E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03590902411 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003032999354 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.05004492E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001565471358 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.570028777E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.154143249E-06 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.46107963E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0163231116 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.08955129711 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02527314126 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01988858896 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01885376016 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00425545778 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02310703773 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.007766878008 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01132139435 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04572533088 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00658312874 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04158472716 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02097721737 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.05157697541 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(SGP_REFEX )  =  - LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.030341829E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.61457448E-06 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02788260461 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001666463851 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003223198496 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.203209924E-05 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001706608413 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001409034263 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1524105684 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003299210571 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.878530977E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06223852839 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03963499793 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05510390432 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0009562469263 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07526430639 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001576276495 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.34905366E-06 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.621142977E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001448438014 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005832158316 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07885852009 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000421294216 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 7.536736834E-06 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000163589742 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002820961217 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001611193639 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004294397806 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001112790478 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003645709575 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01653361415 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0429965701 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004600659878 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.224837944E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.918237892E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002248682315 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.575264767E-07 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03590902411 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003032999354 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.05004492E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001565471358 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.570028777E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.154143249E-06 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.46107963E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0163231116 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08955129711 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02527314126 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01988858896 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01885376016 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00425545778 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02310703773 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007766878008 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01132139435 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04572533088 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00658312874 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04158472716 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02097721737 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05157697541 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

SGP_REMIT  = 0

SGP_GINT  = SGP_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (SGP_LTI  - SGP_LTI(-1))

SGP_GDN  = SGP_GDN(-1) * (SGP_GDFXSH  * (SGP_EXR  / SGP_EXR(-1))  + (1  - SGP_GDFXSH))  - SGP_GLN

@IDENTITY SGP_GDNRATIO  = SGP_GDN / SGP_YEN * 100

SGP_GDFXSH  = ( SGP_GDFXSH(-1) * (SGP_EXR / SGP_EXR(-1) )) / (SGP_GDFXSH(-1) * (SGP_EXR / SGP_EXR(-1))  + 1 - SGP_GDFXSH(-1) )

SGP_TOURSH  = SGP_TOURSH(-1)

SGP_LOCK  = 0

SGP_GCARBR  = SGP_GCARBR(-1)

SGP_GTRADER  = SGP_GTRADER(-1)

SGP_ITAXR  = SGP_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_REV  = SGP_TAX  + SGP_CTAX  + SGP_ITAX  + SGP_GTRADE  + SGP_REVG  + SGP_GCARB  + SGP_GCOM  + SGP_GOTH

@IDENTITY SGP_TAX  = SGP_TAXR * (SGP_LABSH * 0.5 * (SGP_YER(-1)  + SGP_GDI(-1)) * SGP_YED(-1) * (SGP_LNN / SGP_LNN(-1)  + SGP_TECHL - SGP_TECHL(-1)) + SGP_REMIT  + SGP_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY SGP_CTAX  = SGP_CTAXR * SGP_PROF

@IDENTITY SGP_ITAX  = SGP_ITAXR * (SGP_PCR * SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY SGP_GTRADE  = SGP_GTRADER * SGP_XTN

SGP_REVG  = SGP_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (SGP_YER$ / SGP_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - SGP_YER$(-1) / SGP_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * SGP_EXR / SGP_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_GCARB  = SGP_GCARBR * SGP_CO2 * SGP_EXR / 1000

SGP_GCOM  = SGP_GCOM(-1) * ( SGP_OILC / (SGP_OILC + SGP_GASC + SGP_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + SGP_GASC / (SGP_OILC + SGP_GASC + SGP_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + SGP_COALC / (SGP_OILC + SGP_GASC + SGP_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

SGP_GOTH  = SGP_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_EXP  = SGP_EXPE  + SGP_EXPH  + SGP_EXPSP  + SGP_OGC  + SGP_OGI  + SGP_GIP

SGP_EXPE  = SGP_EXPE(-1) * (SGP_YFT / SGP_YFT(-1)) * (SGP_YED / SGP_YED(-1))

SGP_EXPH = SGP_EXPH(-1) * (SGP_YFT / SGP_YFT(-1)) * (SGP_YED / SGP_YED(-1))

SGP_EXPSP  = SGP_EXPSP(-1) * (SGP_YFT / SGP_YFT(-1)) * (SGP_YED / SGP_YED(-1)) * (SGP_POPT - SGP_LNN) / (SGP_POPT(-1) - SGP_LNN(-1))

DLOG(SGP_OGI)  = DLOG(SGP_YFT)  + DLOG(SGP_YED)

SGP_GCR  = SGP_GCR(-1)  + ( SGP_OGC / SGP_YED - SGP_OGC(-1) / SGP_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (SGP_EXPH ) / SGP_YED  - (SGP_EXPH(-1) ) / SGP_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (SGP_EXPE ) / SGP_YED  - (SGP_EXPE(-1) ) / SGP_YED(-1) )

SGP_IGR  = SGP_IGR(-1) + (SGP_OGI / SGP_YED - SGP_OGI(-1) / SGP_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (SGP_EXPH ) / SGP_YED  - (SGP_EXPH(-1) ) / SGP_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (SGP_EXPE ) / SGP_YED  - (SGP_EXPE(-1) ) / SGP_YED(-1) )

SGP_GIP  = ( SGP_GIP(-1)  + ( SGP_GDN(-1) - SGP_GDN(-2) ) * SGP_GINT(-1) / 100  + SGP_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( SGP_GINT(-1) / 100 - SGP_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (SGP_GDFXSH * (SGP_EXR / SGP_EXR(-1))  + (1 - SGP_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY SGP_GLN  = SGP_REV  - SGP_EXP

@IDENTITY SGP_GLNRATIO  = SGP_GLN / SGP_YEN * 100

SGP_GLNT  = SGP_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

SGP_TFP  = SGP_LABSH * (SGP_TECHL  - SGP_TECHL(-1))

SGP_LABSH  = SGP_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY SGP_LFN  = SGP_LRX * SGP_POPWA

SGP_LRX  = SGP_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(SGP_YER(-1) / SGP_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY SGP_URX  = (1 - SGP_LNN / SGP_LFN) * 100

SGP_URXF  = SGP_URXF(-1) * SGP_URX / SGP_URX(-1) * SGP_LNN / SGP_LNNF / (SGP_LNN(-1) / SGP_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(SGP_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(SGP_PCR  / SGP_POPT)

SGP_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(SGP_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

SGP_HEAD19  = SGP_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SGP_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI^2)  , SGP_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SGP_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SGP_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

SGP_HEAD55  = SGP_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SGP_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI^2)  , SGP_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SGP_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SGP_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(SGP_XTR)  = DLOG(SGP_WDR)  + (1  - SGP_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(SGP_XTDNO$  / SGP_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * SGP_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(SGP_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (SGP_EXPH(-1) / SGP_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (SGP_EXPH(-1) / SGP_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(SGP_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(SGP_PM25)

SGP_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( SGP_EXPSP / SGP_YEN )

DLOG(SGP_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - SGP_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (SGP_FINC - SGP_FINC(-1))

DLOG(SGP_PCR)  =  - 0.184853017908445  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(SGP_PCR(-1))  - LOG(SGP_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (SGP_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(SGP_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(SGP_POPT)  +  - 0.118314738456485 * (DLOG(SGP_HIC)  - SGP_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * SGP_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * SGP_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(SGP_YFT(-1))  - LOG(SGP_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(SGP_IPR)  =  - 0.143706929343051  - 0.1 * (LOG(SGP_IPR(-1)  / SGP_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * SGP_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * SGP_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(SGP_PCR  + SGP_GCR(-1) + SGP_IGR(-1) + SGP_XTN  / SGP_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(SGP_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (SGP_USER - SGP_USER(-1))  - (0 * SGP_FUELSH  + 0.26 * SGP_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - SGP_FUELSH - SGP_TOURSH)) * SGP_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * SGP_FUELSH  + 0.26 * SGP_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - SGP_FUELSH - SGP_TOURSH)) * SGP_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(SGP_YFT(-1))  - LOG(SGP_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(SGP_MTR)  =  - 0.0693397756438642  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(SGP_MTR(-1))  - LOG(SGP_PCR(-1) + SGP_ITR(-1) + SGP_GCR(-1) + SGP_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(SGP_YFT(-1) / SGP_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(SGP_CMUD(-1) * SGP_EXR(-1)  / SGP_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * SGP_OMS * LOG(SGP_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.7052335974004  * DLOG(SGP_XTR)  + 0.0969030828799949  * DLOG(SGP_PCR)  + 0.0731663225208754  * DLOG(SGP_IPR)  + 0.00104275989275982  * DLOG(SGP_GCR + SGP_IGR)

SGP_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * SGP_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * SGP_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * SGP_OILC

SGP_POIL  = SGP_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( SGP_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - SGP_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

SGP_PG  = SGP_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( SGP_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - SGP_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

SGP_PC  = SGP_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( SGP_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - SGP_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(SGP_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

SGP_PE  = SGP_PE(-1) * ( SGP_OILC(-1) / (SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) * SGP_POIL / SGP_POIL(-1)  + SGP_GASC(-1) / (SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) * SGP_PG / SGP_PG(-1)  + SGP_COALC(-1) / (SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) * SGP_PC / SGP_PC(-1)  + SGP_RC(-1) / (SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) * SGP_PR / SGP_PR(-1) )

D(SGP_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(SGP_PM25)  = 0.2 * (SGP_COALC(-1) / SGP_EC(-1) - SGP_COALC(-2) / SGP_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (SGP_COALC(-2) / SGP_EC(-2) - SGP_COALC(-3) / SGP_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (SGP_OILC(-1) / SGP_EC(-1) - SGP_OILC(-2) / SGP_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (SGP_OILC(-2) / SGP_EC(-2) - SGP_OILC(-3) / SGP_EC(-3))

DLOG(SGP_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(SGP_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(SGP_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(SGP_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(SGP_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SGP_PE * SGP_EXR / SGP_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SGP_PE(-1) * SGP_EXR(-1) / SGP_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SGP_PE(-2) * SGP_EXR(-2) / SGP_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SGP_PE(-3) * SGP_EXR(-3) / SGP_HIC(-3))  - (SGP_EFF - SGP_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(SGP_COALC)  = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(SGP_COALC(-1) / SGP_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(SGP_PE(-1) / SGP_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) / SGP_EC(-1))

DLOG(SGP_GASC)  = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(SGP_GASC(-1) / SGP_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.129217771254471 * LOG(SGP_PE(-1) / SGP_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) / SGP_EC(-1))

DLOG(SGP_RC)  = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( SGP_RC(-1) / SGP_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(SGP_PE(-1) / SGP_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) / SGP_EC(-1))

DLOG(SGP_OILC)  = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( SGP_OILC(-1) / SGP_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.01 * LOG(SGP_PE(-1) / SGP_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SGP_COALC(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1) + SGP_OILC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)) / SGP_EC(-1))

SGP_EXR  = SGP_EXR(-1) * ( (SGP_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(SLB_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(SLB_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(SLB_MTD)  + 0.4 * (SLB_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (SLB_YER / SLB_YFT  - SLB_YER(-1) / SLB_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + SLB_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + SLB_GCARB / SLB_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (SLB_PREM - SLB_PREM(-1)) / 100

SLB_YED  = SLB_YED(-1) * SLB_HIC / SLB_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_INT  = SLB_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_LTI  = SLB_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (SLB_INT - SLB_INT(-1))  + (SLB_PREM  - SLB_PREM(-1)) / 100

SLB_PREM  = SLB_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (SLB_GDNRATIO(-1)  - SLB_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(SLB_LNN)  = DLOG(SLB_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(SLB_LNN(-1))  - LOG(SLB_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(SLB_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(SLB_LNNF)  = DLOG(SLB_LNN)

SLB_FUELSH  = SLB_FUELSH(-1)

SLB_TAXR  = SLB_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( SLB_GLNT(-1)  - SLB_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * SLB_YEN(-1) / ( ( SLB_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (SLB_YER(-2)  + SLB_GDI(-2)) * SLB_YED(-2) * (SLB_LNN(-1) / SLB_LNN(-2)  + SLB_TECHL(-1) - SLB_TECHL(-2) ) ) + SLB_REMIT(-1)  + SLB_EXPSP(-1) ) * SLB_SOLV

SLB_CTAXR  = SLB_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( SLB_GLNT(-1)  - SLB_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * SLB_YEN(-1) / ( SLB_PROF(-1) ) * SLB_SOLV

(SLB_OGC)  = SLB_OGC(-1) * (SLB_YFT / SLB_YFT(-1) * SLB_YED / SLB_YED(-1))

SLB_USER  = (SLB_LTI  - SLB_INFT  + SLB_DEP * 100) / (1  - SLB_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (SLB_GCARB / SLB_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY SLB_XTN  = SLB_XTD$ * SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") * SLB_XTR

@IDENTITY SLB_YEN  = SLB_YER  * SLB_YED

@IDENTITY SLB_MTN  = SLB_MTD  * SLB_MTR

@IDENTITY SLB_XTN$  = SLB_XTN / SLB_EXR

@IDENTITY SLB_YEN$  = SLB_YEN / SLB_EXR

@IDENTITY SLB_MTN$  = SLB_MTN / SLB_EXR

@IDENTITY SLB_MTR$  = SLB_MTR$(-1) * SLB_MTR / SLB_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_XTR$  = SLB_XTR$(-1) * SLB_XTR / SLB_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_YER$  = SLB_YER$(-1) * SLB_YER / SLB_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_YFT$  = SLB_YFT$(-1) * SLB_YFT / SLB_YFT(-1)

SLB_POPT  = SLB_POPT(-1)  - SLB_LIVES

SLB_POPWA  = SLB_POPWA(-1) * SLB_POPT / SLB_POPT(-1)

SLB_SCR  = SLB_SCR(-1)  + ((SLB_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (SLB_YFT(-1) / SLB_YER(-1)  - SLB_YFT(-2) / SLB_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY SLB_ITR  = SLB_IGR  + SLB_IPR

@IDENTITY SLB_YER  = SLB_PCR  + SLB_GCR  + SLB_ITR  + SLB_SCR  + SLB_XTR  - SLB_MTR

@IDENTITY SLB_PROF  = (SLB_YEN - SLB_ITAX) * (1 - SLB_LABSH)

@IDENTITY SLB_GDI  = SLB_YER  - SLB_XTR  + SLB_MTR  + SLB_XTN  / ((SLB_YEN  - SLB_XTN  + SLB_MTN)  / (SLB_YER  - SLB_XTR  + SLB_MTR))  - SLB_MTN  / ((SLB_YEN  - SLB_XTN  + SLB_MTN)  / (SLB_YER  - SLB_XTR  + SLB_MTR))

@IDENTITY SLB_RPDI  = SLB_LABSH * 0.5 * (SLB_YER(-1)  + SLB_GDI(-1)) * SLB_YED(-1) / SLB_HIC(-1) * (SLB_LNN / SLB_LNN(-1)  + SLB_TECHL - SLB_TECHL(-1)) + SLB_REMIT / SLB_HIC  + SLB_EXPSP / SLB_HIC  - SLB_TAX / SLB_HIC

DLOG(SLB_YFT)  = (1 - SLB_ALPHA - SLB_LABSH) * DLOG(SLB_K(-1) / SLB_LFN(-1))  + (1 - SLB_ALPHA) * DLOG(SLB_LFN)  + SLB_LABSH * D(SLB_TECHL)  + SLB_ALPHA * (DLOG(SLB_EC)  + D(SLB_EFF) )  - ( SLB_CLIMLOSS / SLB_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (SLB_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY SLB_K  = SLB_K(-1) * (1 - SLB_DEP) + SLB_ITR

DLOG(SLB_MTD)  = (1  - SLB_OMS) * ( DLOG(SLB_CMUD)  + DLOG(SLB_EXR) )  + SLB_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(SLB_EXR) )

DLOG(SLB_XTD$)  = (1  - SLB_OXS) * DLOG(SLB_XTDNO$)  + SLB_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

SLB_INFT  = 0.95 * SLB_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

SLB_OXS  = SLB_OXS(-1)

SLB_OMS  = SLB_OMS(-1) * ((SLB_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * SLB_EXR(-1) / SLB_MTN(-1)) / (SLB_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * SLB_EXR(-2) / SLB_MTN(-2)))^0.25

SLB_CXS  = SLB_CXS(-1)

SLB_FINC  = SLB_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_CAN  = SLB_XTN / SLB_EXR  - SLB_MTN / SLB_EXR  + SLB_REMIT / SLB_EXR  + SLB_CANOTH

@IDENTITY SLB_CANRATIO  = SLB_CAN / SLB_YEN$ * 100

SLB_CANOTH  = SLB_CANOTH(-1)  + ((SLB_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (SLB_YEN$  / SLB_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + SLB_REVG / SLB_EXR  - SLB_REVG(-1) / SLB_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(SLB_EFEX)  =  - LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.197587588E-10 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.393159452E-07 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  +
