0.06543788889 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02439034833 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00792659081 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002728138231 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01053941546 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01341424959 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00289659826 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009263009767 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003275168929 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004708373637 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

SLB_REMIT  = SLB_REMIT(-1) / SLB_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.8181441374 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00897719186 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007045864575 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001212984323 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001682850566 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005719459864 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04774369525 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005172230708 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005571829584 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04409996375 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01941798871 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002814131081 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001232624998 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02707747864 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01544349341 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * SLB_EXR

SLB_GINT  = SLB_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (SLB_LTI  - SLB_LTI(-1))

SLB_GDN  = SLB_GDN(-1) * (SLB_GDFXSH  * (SLB_EXR  / SLB_EXR(-1))  + (1  - SLB_GDFXSH))  - SLB_GLN

@IDENTITY SLB_GDNRATIO  = SLB_GDN / SLB_YEN * 100

SLB_GDFXSH  = ( SLB_GDFXSH(-1) * (SLB_EXR / SLB_EXR(-1) )) / (SLB_GDFXSH(-1) * (SLB_EXR / SLB_EXR(-1))  + 1 - SLB_GDFXSH(-1) )

SLB_TOURSH  = SLB_TOURSH(-1)

SLB_LOCK  = 0

SLB_GCARBR  = SLB_GCARBR(-1)

SLB_GTRADER  = SLB_GTRADER(-1)

SLB_ITAXR  = SLB_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_REV  = SLB_TAX  + SLB_CTAX  + SLB_ITAX  + SLB_GTRADE  + SLB_REVG  + SLB_GCARB  + SLB_GCOM  + SLB_GOTH

@IDENTITY SLB_TAX  = SLB_TAXR * (SLB_LABSH * 0.5 * (SLB_YER(-1)  + SLB_GDI(-1)) * SLB_YED(-1) * (SLB_LNN / SLB_LNN(-1)  + SLB_TECHL - SLB_TECHL(-1)) + SLB_REMIT  + SLB_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY SLB_CTAX  = SLB_CTAXR * SLB_PROF

@IDENTITY SLB_ITAX  = SLB_ITAXR * (SLB_PCR * SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY SLB_GTRADE  = SLB_GTRADER * SLB_XTN

SLB_REVG  = SLB_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (SLB_YER$ / SLB_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - SLB_YER$(-1) / SLB_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * SLB_EXR / SLB_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_GCARB  = SLB_GCARBR * SLB_CO2 * SLB_EXR / 1000

SLB_GCOM  = SLB_GCOM(-1) * ( SLB_OILC / (SLB_OILC + SLB_GASC + SLB_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + SLB_GASC / (SLB_OILC + SLB_GASC + SLB_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + SLB_COALC / (SLB_OILC + SLB_GASC + SLB_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

SLB_GOTH  = SLB_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_EXP  = SLB_EXPE  + SLB_EXPH  + SLB_EXPSP  + SLB_OGC  + SLB_OGI  + SLB_GIP

SLB_EXPE  = SLB_EXPE(-1) * (SLB_YFT / SLB_YFT(-1)) * (SLB_YED / SLB_YED(-1))

SLB_EXPH = SLB_EXPH(-1) * (SLB_YFT / SLB_YFT(-1)) * (SLB_YED / SLB_YED(-1))

SLB_EXPSP  = SLB_EXPSP(-1) * (SLB_YFT / SLB_YFT(-1)) * (SLB_YED / SLB_YED(-1)) * (SLB_POPT - SLB_LNN) / (SLB_POPT(-1) - SLB_LNN(-1))

DLOG(SLB_OGI)  = DLOG(SLB_YFT)  + DLOG(SLB_YED)

SLB_GCR  = SLB_GCR(-1)  + ( SLB_OGC / SLB_YED - SLB_OGC(-1) / SLB_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (SLB_EXPH ) / SLB_YED  - (SLB_EXPH(-1) ) / SLB_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (SLB_EXPE ) / SLB_YED  - (SLB_EXPE(-1) ) / SLB_YED(-1) )

SLB_IGR  = SLB_IGR(-1) + (SLB_OGI / SLB_YED - SLB_OGI(-1) / SLB_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (SLB_EXPH ) / SLB_YED  - (SLB_EXPH(-1) ) / SLB_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (SLB_EXPE ) / SLB_YED  - (SLB_EXPE(-1) ) / SLB_YED(-1) )

SLB_GIP  = ( SLB_GIP(-1)  + ( SLB_GDN(-1) - SLB_GDN(-2) ) * SLB_GINT(-1) / 100  + SLB_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( SLB_GINT(-1) / 100 - SLB_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (SLB_GDFXSH * (SLB_EXR / SLB_EXR(-1))  + (1 - SLB_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY SLB_GLN  = SLB_REV  - SLB_EXP

@IDENTITY SLB_GLNRATIO  = SLB_GLN / SLB_YEN * 100

SLB_GLNT  = SLB_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

SLB_TFP  = SLB_LABSH * (SLB_TECHL  - SLB_TECHL(-1))

SLB_LABSH  = SLB_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY SLB_LFN  = SLB_LRX * SLB_POPWA

SLB_LRX  = SLB_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(SLB_YER(-1) / SLB_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY SLB_URX  = (1 - SLB_LNN / SLB_LFN) * 100

SLB_URXF  = SLB_URXF(-1) * SLB_URX / SLB_URX(-1) * SLB_LNN / SLB_LNNF / (SLB_LNN(-1) / SLB_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(SLB_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(SLB_PCR  / SLB_POPT)

SLB_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(SLB_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

SLB_HEAD19  = SLB_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SLB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI^2)  , SLB_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SLB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SLB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

SLB_HEAD55  = SLB_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SLB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI^2)  , SLB_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SLB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SLB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(SLB_XTR)  = DLOG(SLB_WDR)  + (1  - SLB_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(SLB_XTDNO$  / SLB_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * SLB_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(SLB_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (SLB_EXPH(-1) / SLB_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (SLB_EXPH(-1) / SLB_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(SLB_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(SLB_PM25)

SLB_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( SLB_EXPSP / SLB_YEN )

DLOG(SLB_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - SLB_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (SLB_FINC - SLB_FINC(-1))

DLOG(SLB_PCR)  =  - 0.090895500471718  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(SLB_PCR(-1))  - LOG(SLB_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (SLB_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.417647036164493  * DLOG(SLB_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.417647036164493)  * DLOG(SLB_POPT)  +  - 0.312546987092379 * (DLOG(SLB_HIC)  - SLB_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * SLB_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * SLB_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(SLB_YFT(-1))  - LOG(SLB_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(SLB_IPR)  =  - 0.212572210021981  - 0.1 * (LOG(SLB_IPR(-1)  / SLB_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * SLB_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * SLB_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(SLB_PCR  + SLB_GCR(-1) + SLB_IGR(-1) + SLB_XTN  / SLB_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(SLB_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (SLB_USER - SLB_USER(-1))  - (0 * SLB_FUELSH  + 0.26 * SLB_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - SLB_FUELSH - SLB_TOURSH)) * SLB_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * SLB_FUELSH  + 0.26 * SLB_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - SLB_FUELSH - SLB_TOURSH)) * SLB_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(SLB_YFT(-1))  - LOG(SLB_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(SLB_MTR)  =  - 0.144418730698364  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(SLB_MTR(-1))  - LOG(SLB_PCR(-1) + SLB_ITR(-1) + SLB_GCR(-1) + SLB_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(SLB_YFT(-1) / SLB_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(SLB_CMUD(-1) * SLB_EXR(-1)  / SLB_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * SLB_OMS * LOG(SLB_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.339845166138402  * DLOG(SLB_XTR)  + 0.339026446553878  * DLOG(SLB_PCR)  + 0.0972333691803167  * DLOG(SLB_IPR)  + 0.233023014704348  * DLOG(SLB_GCR + SLB_IGR)

SLB_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * SLB_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * SLB_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * SLB_OILC

SLB_POIL  = SLB_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( SLB_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - SLB_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

SLB_PG  = SLB_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( SLB_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - SLB_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

SLB_PC  = SLB_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( SLB_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - SLB_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(SLB_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

SLB_PE  = SLB_PE(-1) * ( SLB_OILC(-1) / (SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) * SLB_POIL / SLB_POIL(-1)  + SLB_GASC(-1) / (SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) * SLB_PG / SLB_PG(-1)  + SLB_COALC(-1) / (SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) * SLB_PC / SLB_PC(-1)  + SLB_RC(-1) / (SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) * SLB_PR / SLB_PR(-1) )

D(SLB_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(SLB_PM25)  = 0.2 * (SLB_COALC(-1) / SLB_EC(-1) - SLB_COALC(-2) / SLB_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (SLB_COALC(-2) / SLB_EC(-2) - SLB_COALC(-3) / SLB_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (SLB_OILC(-1) / SLB_EC(-1) - SLB_OILC(-2) / SLB_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (SLB_OILC(-2) / SLB_EC(-2) - SLB_OILC(-3) / SLB_EC(-3))

DLOG(SLB_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(SLB_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(SLB_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(SLB_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(SLB_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SLB_PE * SLB_EXR / SLB_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SLB_PE(-1) * SLB_EXR(-1) / SLB_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SLB_PE(-2) * SLB_EXR(-2) / SLB_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(SLB_PE(-3) * SLB_EXR(-3) / SLB_HIC(-3))  - (SLB_EFF - SLB_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(SLB_COALC)  = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(SLB_COALC(-1) / SLB_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.01 * LOG(SLB_PE(-1) / SLB_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) / SLB_EC(-1))

DLOG(SLB_GASC)  = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(SLB_GASC(-1) / SLB_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.2 / 0.01 * LOG(SLB_PE(-1) / SLB_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) / SLB_EC(-1))

DLOG(SLB_RC)  = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( SLB_RC(-1) / SLB_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.630704886693273 * LOG(SLB_PE(-1) / SLB_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) / SLB_EC(-1))

DLOG(SLB_OILC)  = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( SLB_OILC(-1) / SLB_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.2 / 0.630704886693273 * LOG(SLB_PE(-1) / SLB_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((SLB_COALC(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1) + SLB_OILC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)) / SLB_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY SLB_EXR  = SLB_EXR(-1)

DLOG(LKA_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(LKA_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(LKA_MTD)  + 0.4 * (LKA_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (LKA_YER / LKA_YFT  - LKA_YER(-1) / LKA_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + LKA_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + LKA_GCARB / LKA_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (LKA_PREM - LKA_PREM(-1)) / 100

LKA_YED  = LKA_YED(-1) * LKA_HIC / LKA_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_INT  = LKA_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_LTI  = LKA_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (LKA_INT - LKA_INT(-1))  + (LKA_PREM  - LKA_PREM(-1)) / 100

LKA_PREM  = LKA_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (LKA_GDNRATIO(-1)  - LKA_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(LKA_LNN)  = DLOG(LKA_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(LKA_LNN(-1))  - LOG(LKA_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(LKA_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(LKA_LNNF)  = DLOG(LKA_LNN)

LKA_FUELSH  = LKA_FUELSH(-1)

LKA_TAXR  = LKA_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( LKA_GLNT(-1)  - LKA_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * LKA_YEN(-1) / ( ( LKA_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (LKA_YER(-2)  + LKA_GDI(-2)) * LKA_YED(-2) * (LKA_LNN(-1) / LKA_LNN(-2)  + LKA_TECHL(-1) - LKA_TECHL(-2) ) ) + LKA_REMIT(-1)  + LKA_EXPSP(-1) ) * LKA_SOLV

LKA_CTAXR  = LKA_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( LKA_GLNT(-1)  - LKA_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * LKA_YEN(-1) / ( LKA_PROF(-1) ) * LKA_SOLV

(LKA_OGC)  = LKA_OGC(-1) * (LKA_YFT / LKA_YFT(-1) * LKA_YED / LKA_YED(-1))

LKA_USER  = (LKA_LTI  - LKA_INFT  + LKA_DEP * 100) / (1  - LKA_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (LKA_GCARB / LKA_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY LKA_XTN  = LKA_XTD$ * LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") * LKA_XTR

@IDENTITY LKA_YEN  = LKA_YER  * LKA_YED

@IDENTITY LKA_MTN  = LKA_MTD  * LKA_MTR

@IDENTITY LKA_XTN$  = LKA_XTN / LKA_EXR

@IDENTITY LKA_YEN$  = LKA_YEN / LKA_EXR

@IDENTITY LKA_MTN$  = LKA_MTN / LKA_EXR

@IDENTITY LKA_MTR$  = LKA_MTR$(-1) * LKA_MTR / LKA_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_XTR$  = LKA_XTR$(-1) * LKA_XTR / LKA_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_YER$  = LKA_YER$(-1) * LKA_YER / LKA_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_YFT$  = LKA_YFT$(-1) * LKA_YFT / LKA_YFT(-1)

LKA_POPT  = LKA_POPT(-1)  - LKA_LIVES

LKA_POPWA  = LKA_POPWA(-1) * LKA_POPT / LKA_POPT(-1)

LKA_SCR  = LKA_SCR(-1)  + ((LKA_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (LKA_YFT(-1) / LKA_YER(-1)  - LKA_YFT(-2) / LKA_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY LKA_ITR  = LKA_IGR  + LKA_IPR

@IDENTITY LKA_YER  = LKA_PCR  + LKA_GCR  + LKA_ITR  + LKA_SCR  + LKA_XTR  - LKA_MTR

@IDENTITY LKA_PROF  = (LKA_YEN - LKA_ITAX) * (1 - LKA_LABSH)

@IDENTITY LKA_GDI  = LKA_YER  - LKA_XTR  + LKA_MTR  + LKA_XTN  / ((LKA_YEN  - LKA_XTN  + LKA_MTN)  / (LKA_YER  - LKA_XTR  + LKA_MTR))  - LKA_MTN  / ((LKA_YEN  - LKA_XTN  + LKA_MTN)  / (LKA_YER  - LKA_XTR  + LKA_MTR))

@IDENTITY LKA_RPDI  = LKA_LABSH * 0.5 * (LKA_YER(-1)  + LKA_GDI(-1)) * LKA_YED(-1) / LKA_HIC(-1) * (LKA_LNN / LKA_LNN(-1)  + LKA_TECHL - LKA_TECHL(-1)) + LKA_REMIT / LKA_HIC  + LKA_EXPSP / LKA_HIC  - LKA_TAX / LKA_HIC

DLOG(LKA_YFT)  = (1 - LKA_ALPHA - LKA_LABSH) * DLOG(LKA_K(-1) / LKA_LFN(-1))  + (1 - LKA_ALPHA) * DLOG(LKA_LFN)  + LKA_LABSH * D(LKA_TECHL)  + LKA_ALPHA * (DLOG(LKA_EC)  + D(LKA_EFF) )  - ( LKA_CLIMLOSS / LKA_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (LKA_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY LKA_K  = LKA_K(-1) * (1 - LKA_DEP) + LKA_ITR

DLOG(LKA_MTD)  = (1  - LKA_OMS) * ( DLOG(LKA_CMUD)  + DLOG(LKA_EXR) )  + LKA_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(LKA_EXR) )

DLOG(LKA_XTD$)  = (1  - LKA_OXS) * DLOG(LKA_XTDNO$)  + LKA_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

LKA_INFT  = 0.95 * LKA_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

LKA_OXS  = LKA_OXS(-1)

LKA_OMS  = LKA_OMS(-1) * ((LKA_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * LKA_EXR(-1) / LKA_MTN(-1)) / (LKA_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * LKA_EXR(-2) / LKA_MTN(-2)))^0.25

LKA_CXS  = LKA_CXS(-1)

LKA_FINC  = LKA_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_CAN  = LKA_XTN / LKA_EXR  - LKA_MTN / LKA_EXR  + LKA_REMIT / LKA_EXR  + LKA_CANOTH

@IDENTITY LKA_CANRATIO  = LKA_CAN / LKA_YEN$ * 100

LKA_CANOTH  = LKA_CANOTH(-1)  + ((LKA_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (LKA_YEN$  / LKA_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + LKA_REVG / LKA_EXR  - LKA_REVG(-1) / LKA_EXR(-1)

LKA_GTRADER  = LKA_GTRADER(-1)

LKA_ITAXR  = LKA_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_REV  = LKA_TAX  + LKA_CTAX  + LKA_ITAX  + LKA_GTRADE  + LKA_REVG  + LKA_GCARB  + LKA_GCOM  + LKA_GOTH

@IDENTITY LKA_TAX  = LKA_TAXR * (LKA_LABSH * 0.5 * (LKA_YER(-1)  + LKA_GDI(-1)) * LKA_YED(-1) * (LKA_LNN / LKA_LNN(-1)  + LKA_TECHL - LKA_TECHL(-1)) + LKA_REMIT  + LKA_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY LKA_CTAX  = LKA_CTAXR * LKA_PROF

@IDENTITY LKA_ITAX  = LKA_ITAXR * (LKA_PCR * LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY LKA_GTRADE  = LKA_GTRADER * LKA_XTN

LKA_REVG  = LKA_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (LKA_YER$ / LKA_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - LKA_YER$(-1) / LKA_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * LKA_EXR / LKA_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_GCARB  = LKA_GCARBR * LKA_CO2 * LKA_EXR / 1000

LKA_GCOM  = LKA_GCOM(-1) * ( LKA_OILC / (LKA_OILC + LKA_GASC + LKA_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + LKA_GASC / (LKA_OILC + LKA_GASC + LKA_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + LKA_COALC / (LKA_OILC + LKA_GASC + LKA_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

LKA_GOTH  = LKA_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_EXP  = LKA_EXPE  + LKA_EXPH  + LKA_EXPSP  + LKA_OGC  + LKA_OGI  + LKA_GIP

LKA_EXPE  = LKA_EXPE(-1) * (LKA_YFT / LKA_YFT(-1)) * (LKA_YED / LKA_YED(-1))

LKA_EXPH = LKA_EXPH(-1) * (LKA_YFT / LKA_YFT(-1)) * (LKA_YED / LKA_YED(-1))

LKA_EXPSP  = LKA_EXPSP(-1) * (LKA_YFT / LKA_YFT(-1)) * (LKA_YED / LKA_YED(-1)) * (LKA_POPT - LKA_LNN) / (LKA_POPT(-1) - LKA_LNN(-1))

DLOG(LKA_OGI)  = DLOG(LKA_YFT)  + DLOG(LKA_YED)

LKA_GCR  = LKA_GCR(-1)  + ( LKA_OGC / LKA_YED - LKA_OGC(-1) / LKA_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (LKA_EXPH ) / LKA_YED  - (LKA_EXPH(-1) ) / LKA_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (LKA_EXPE ) / LKA_YED  - (LKA_EXPE(-1) ) / LKA_YED(-1) )

LKA_IGR  = LKA_IGR(-1) + (LKA_OGI / LKA_YED - LKA_OGI(-1) / LKA_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (LKA_EXPH ) / LKA_YED  - (LKA_EXPH(-1) ) / LKA_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (LKA_EXPE ) / LKA_YED  - (LKA_EXPE(-1) ) / LKA_YED(-1) )

LKA_GIP  = ( LKA_GIP(-1)  + ( LKA_GDN(-1) - LKA_GDN(-2) ) * LKA_GINT(-1) / 100  + LKA_GDN(-7) / 6 * ( LKA_GINT(-1) / 100 - LKA_GINT(-7) / 100 ) ) * (LKA_GDFXSH * (LKA_EXR / LKA_EXR(-1))  + (1 - LKA_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY LKA_GLN  = LKA_REV  - LKA_EXP

@IDENTITY LKA_GLNRATIO  = LKA_GLN / LKA_YEN * 100

LKA_GLNT  = LKA_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

LKA_TFP  = LKA_LABSH * (LKA_TECHL  - LKA_TECHL(-1))

LKA_LABSH  = LKA_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY LKA_LFN  = LKA_LRX * LKA_POPWA

LKA_LRX  = LKA_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(LKA_YER(-1) / LKA_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY LKA_URX  = (1 - LKA_LNN / LKA_LFN) * 100

LKA_URXF  = LKA_URXF(-1) * LKA_URX / LKA_URX(-1) * LKA_LNN / LKA_LNNF / (LKA_LNN(-1) / LKA_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(LKA_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(LKA_PCR  / LKA_POPT)

LKA_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(LKA_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

LKA_HEAD19  = LKA_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LKA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI^2)  , LKA_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LKA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LKA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

LKA_HEAD55  = LKA_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LKA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI^2)  , LKA_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LKA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LKA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(LKA_XTR)  = DLOG(LKA_WDR)  + (1  - LKA_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(LKA_XTDNO$  / LKA_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * LKA_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(LKA_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (LKA_EXPH(-1) / LKA_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (LKA_EXPH(-1) / LKA_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(LKA_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(LKA_PM25)

LKA_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( LKA_EXPSP / LKA_YEN )

DLOG(LKA_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - LKA_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (LKA_FINC - LKA_FINC(-1))

DLOG(LKA_PCR)  =  - 0.043156540396214  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(LKA_PCR(-1))  - LOG(LKA_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (LKA_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(LKA_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(LKA_POPT)  +  - 0.165769126367045 * (DLOG(LKA_HIC)  - LKA_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * LKA_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * LKA_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(LKA_YFT(-1))  - LOG(LKA_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(LKA_IPR)  =  - 0.13969650207216  - 0.1 * (LOG(LKA_IPR(-1)  / LKA_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * LKA_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * LKA_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(LKA_PCR  + LKA_GCR(-1) + LKA_IGR(-1) + LKA_XTN  / LKA_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(LKA_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (LKA_USER - LKA_USER(-1))  - (0 * LKA_FUELSH  + 0.26 * LKA_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - LKA_FUELSH - LKA_TOURSH)) * LKA_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * LKA_FUELSH  + 0.26 * LKA_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - LKA_FUELSH - LKA_TOURSH)) * LKA_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(LKA_YFT(-1))  - LOG(LKA_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(LKA_MTR)  =  - 0.18315479173319  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(LKA_MTR(-1))  - LOG(LKA_PCR(-1) + LKA_ITR(-1) + LKA_GCR(-1) + LKA_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(LKA_YFT(-1) / LKA_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(LKA_CMUD(-1) * LKA_EXR(-1)  / LKA_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * LKA_OMS * LOG(LKA_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.422883730259133  * DLOG(LKA_XTR)  + 0.733934133343828  * DLOG(LKA_PCR)  + 0.309960653896371  * DLOG(LKA_IPR)  + 0.12850488193063  * DLOG(LKA_GCR + LKA_IGR)

LKA_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * LKA_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * LKA_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * LKA_OILC

LKA_POIL  = LKA_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( LKA_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - LKA_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

LKA_PG  = LKA_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( LKA_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - LKA_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

LKA_PC  = LKA_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( LKA_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - LKA_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(LKA_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

LKA_PE  = LKA_PE(-1) * ( LKA_OILC(-1) / (LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) * LKA_POIL / LKA_POIL(-1)  + LKA_GASC(-1) / (LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) * LKA_PG / LKA_PG(-1)  + LKA_COALC(-1) / (LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) * LKA_PC / LKA_PC(-1)  + LKA_RC(-1) / (LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) * LKA_PR / LKA_PR(-1) )

D(LKA_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(LKA_PM25)  = 0.2 * (LKA_COALC(-1) / LKA_EC(-1) - LKA_COALC(-2) / LKA_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (LKA_COALC(-2) / LKA_EC(-2) - LKA_COALC(-3) / LKA_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (LKA_OILC(-1) / LKA_EC(-1) - LKA_OILC(-2) / LKA_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (LKA_OILC(-2) / LKA_EC(-2) - LKA_OILC(-3) / LKA_EC(-3))

DLOG(LKA_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(LKA_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(LKA_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(LKA_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(LKA_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LKA_PE * LKA_EXR / LKA_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LKA_PE(-1) * LKA_EXR(-1) / LKA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LKA_PE(-2) * LKA_EXR(-2) / LKA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(LKA_PE(-3) * LKA_EXR(-3) / LKA_HIC(-3))  - (LKA_EFF - LKA_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(LKA_COALC)  = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(LKA_COALC(-1) / LKA_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.133685792601144 * LOG(LKA_PE(-1) / LKA_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) / LKA_EC(-1))

DLOG(LKA_GASC)  = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(LKA_GASC(-1) / LKA_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.01 * LOG(LKA_PE(-1) / LKA_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) / LKA_EC(-1))

DLOG(LKA_RC)  = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( LKA_RC(-1) / LKA_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.133685792601144 * LOG(LKA_PE(-1) / LKA_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) / LKA_EC(-1))

DLOG(LKA_OILC)  = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( LKA_OILC(-1) / LKA_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.133685792601144 * LOG(LKA_PE(-1) / LKA_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((LKA_COALC(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1) + LKA_OILC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)) / LKA_EC(-1))

LKA_EXR  = LKA_EXR(-1) * ( (LKA_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(TJK_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(TJK_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TJK_MTD)  + 0.4 * (TJK_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (TJK_YER / TJK_YFT  - TJK_YER(-1) / TJK_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + TJK_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + TJK_GCARB / TJK_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (TJK_PREM - TJK_PREM(-1)) / 100

TJK_YED  = TJK_YED(-1) * TJK_HIC / TJK_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_INT  = TJK_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_LTI  = TJK_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (TJK_INT - TJK_INT(-1))  + (TJK_PREM  - TJK_PREM(-1)) / 100

TJK_PREM  = TJK_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (TJK_GDNRATIO(-1)  - TJK_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(TJK_LNN)  = DLOG(TJK_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(TJK_LNN(-1))  - LOG(TJK_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(TJK_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TJK_LNNF)  = DLOG(TJK_LNN)

TJK_FUELSH  = TJK_FUELSH(-1)

TJK_TAXR  = TJK_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TJK_GLNT(-1)  - TJK_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TJK_YEN(-1) / ( ( TJK_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (TJK_YER(-2)  + TJK_GDI(-2)) * TJK_YED(-2) * (TJK_LNN(-1) / TJK_LNN(-2)  + TJK_TECHL(-1) - TJK_TECHL(-2) ) ) + TJK_REMIT(-1)  + TJK_EXPSP(-1) ) * TJK_SOLV

TJK_CTAXR  = TJK_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TJK_GLNT(-1)  - TJK_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TJK_YEN(-1) / ( TJK_PROF(-1) ) * TJK_SOLV

(TJK_OGC)  = TJK_OGC(-1) * (TJK_YFT / TJK_YFT(-1) * TJK_YED / TJK_YED(-1))

TJK_USER  = (TJK_LTI  - TJK_INFT  + TJK_DEP * 100) / (1  - TJK_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (TJK_GCARB / TJK_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY TJK_XTN  = TJK_XTD$ * TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") * TJK_XTR

@IDENTITY TJK_YEN  = TJK_YER  * TJK_YED

@IDENTITY TJK_MTN  = TJK_MTD  * TJK_MTR

@IDENTITY TJK_XTN$  = TJK_XTN / TJK_EXR

@IDENTITY TJK_YEN$  = TJK_YEN / TJK_EXR

@IDENTITY TJK_MTN$  = TJK_MTN / TJK_EXR

@IDENTITY TJK_MTR$  = TJK_MTR$(-1) * TJK_MTR / TJK_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_XTR$  = TJK_XTR$(-1) * TJK_XTR / TJK_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_YER$  = TJK_YER$(-1) * TJK_YER / TJK_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_YFT$  = TJK_YFT$(-1) * TJK_YFT / TJK_YFT(-1)

TJK_POPT  = TJK_POPT(-1)  - TJK_LIVES

TJK_POPWA  = TJK_POPWA(-1) * TJK_POPT / TJK_POPT(-1)

TJK_SCR  = TJK_SCR(-1)  + ((TJK_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TJK_YFT(-1) / TJK_YER(-1)  - TJK_YFT(-2) / TJK_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY TJK_ITR  = TJK_IGR  + TJK_IPR

@IDENTITY TJK_YER  = TJK_PCR  + TJK_GCR  + TJK_ITR  + TJK_SCR  + TJK_XTR  - TJK_MTR

@IDENTITY TJK_PROF  = (TJK_YEN - TJK_ITAX) * (1 - TJK_LABSH)

@IDENTITY TJK_GDI  = TJK_YER  - TJK_XTR  + TJK_MTR  + TJK_XTN  / ((TJK_YEN  - TJK_XTN  + TJK_MTN)  / (TJK_YER  - TJK_XTR  + TJK_MTR))  - TJK_MTN  / ((TJK_YEN  - TJK_XTN  + TJK_MTN)  / (TJK_YER  - TJK_XTR  + TJK_MTR))

@IDENTITY TJK_RPDI  = TJK_LABSH * 0.5 * (TJK_YER(-1)  + TJK_GDI(-1)) * TJK_YED(-1) / TJK_HIC(-1) * (TJK_LNN / TJK_LNN(-1)  + TJK_TECHL - TJK_TECHL(-1)) + TJK_REMIT / TJK_HIC  + TJK_EXPSP / TJK_HIC  - TJK_TAX / TJK_HIC

DLOG(TJK_YFT)  = (1 - TJK_ALPHA - TJK_LABSH) * DLOG(TJK_K(-1) / TJK_LFN(-1))  + (1 - TJK_ALPHA) * DLOG(TJK_LFN)  + TJK_LABSH * D(TJK_TECHL)  + TJK_ALPHA * (DLOG(TJK_EC)  + D(TJK_EFF) )  - ( TJK_CLIMLOSS / TJK_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (TJK_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY TJK_K  = TJK_K(-1) * (1 - TJK_DEP) + TJK_ITR

DLOG(TJK_MTD)  = (1  - TJK_OMS) * ( DLOG(TJK_CMUD)  + DLOG(TJK_EXR) )  + TJK_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TJK_EXR) )

DLOG(TJK_XTD$)  = (1  - TJK_OXS) * DLOG(TJK_XTDNO$)  + TJK_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

TJK_INFT  = 0.95 * TJK_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

TJK_OXS  = TJK_OXS(-1)

TJK_OMS  = TJK_OMS(-1) * ((TJK_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * TJK_EXR(-1) / TJK_MTN(-1)) / (TJK_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * TJK_EXR(-2) / TJK_MTN(-2)))^0.25

TJK_CXS  = TJK_CXS(-1)

TJK_FINC  = TJK_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_CAN  = TJK_XTN / TJK_EXR  - TJK_MTN / TJK_EXR  + TJK_REMIT / TJK_EXR  + TJK_CANOTH

@IDENTITY TJK_CANRATIO  = TJK_CAN / TJK_YEN$ * 100

TJK_CANOTH  = TJK_CANOTH(-1)  + ((TJK_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TJK_YEN$  / TJK_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TJK_REVG / TJK_EXR  - TJK_REVG(-1) / TJK_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(TJK_EFEX)  =  - LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005086290438 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000187148487 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.887098731E-05 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001706467882 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004612254124 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.49105034E-11 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.207928062E-06 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.250654483E-07 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.3085139042 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.530225885E-08 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001421643048 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002169176868 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005823514969 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002489988758 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04493464567 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009098977321 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.08112587772 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.586491268E-11 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005329003704 * TJK_GINT  = TJK_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (TJK_LTI  - TJK_LTI(-1))

TJK_GDN  = TJK_GDN(-1) * (TJK_GDFXSH  * (TJK_EXR  / TJK_EXR(-1))  + (1  - TJK_GDFXSH))  - TJK_GLN

@IDENTITY TJK_GDNRATIO  = TJK_GDN / TJK_YEN * 100

TJK_GDFXSH  = ( TJK_GDFXSH(-1) * (TJK_EXR / TJK_EXR(-1) )) / (TJK_GDFXSH(-1) * (TJK_EXR / TJK_EXR(-1))  + 1 - TJK_GDFXSH(-1) )

TJK_TOURSH  = TJK_TOURSH(-1)

TJK_LOCK  = 0

TJK_GCARBR  = TJK_GCARBR(-1)

TJK_GTRADER  = TJK_GTRADER(-1)

TJK_ITAXR  = TJK_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_REV  = TJK_TAX  + TJK_CTAX  + TJK_ITAX  + TJK_GTRADE  + TJK_REVG  + TJK_GCARB  + TJK_GCOM  + TJK_GOTH

@IDENTITY TJK_TAX  = TJK_TAXR * (TJK_LABSH * 0.5 * (TJK_YER(-1)  + TJK_GDI(-1)) * TJK_YED(-1) * (TJK_LNN / TJK_LNN(-1)  + TJK_TECHL - TJK_TECHL(-1)) + TJK_REMIT  + TJK_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY TJK_CTAX  = TJK_CTAXR * TJK_PROF

@IDENTITY TJK_ITAX  = TJK_ITAXR * (TJK_PCR * TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY TJK_GTRADE  = TJK_GTRADER * TJK_XTN

TJK_REVG  = TJK_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (TJK_YER$ / TJK_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - TJK_YER$(-1) / TJK_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * TJK_EXR / TJK_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_GCARB  = TJK_GCARBR * TJK_CO2 * TJK_EXR / 1000

TJK_GCOM  = TJK_GCOM(-1) * ( TJK_OILC / (TJK_OILC + TJK_GASC + TJK_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + TJK_GASC / (TJK_OILC + TJK_GASC + TJK_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + TJK_COALC / (TJK_OILC + TJK_GASC + TJK_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

TJK_GOTH  = TJK_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_EXP  = TJK_EXPE  + TJK_EXPH  + TJK_EXPSP  + TJK_OGC  + TJK_OGI  + TJK_GIP

TJK_EXPE  = TJK_EXPE(-1) * (TJK_YFT / TJK_YFT(-1)) * (TJK_YED / TJK_YED(-1))

TJK_EXPH = TJK_EXPH(-1) * (TJK_YFT / TJK_YFT(-1)) * (TJK_YED / TJK_YED(-1))

TJK_EXPSP  = TJK_EXPSP(-1) * (TJK_YFT / TJK_YFT(-1)) * (TJK_YED / TJK_YED(-1)) * (TJK_POPT - TJK_LNN) / (TJK_POPT(-1) - TJK_LNN(-1))

DLOG(TJK_OGI)  = DLOG(TJK_YFT)  + DLOG(TJK_YED)

TJK_GCR  = TJK_GCR(-1)  + ( TJK_OGC / TJK_YED - TJK_OGC(-1) / TJK_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (TJK_EXPH ) / TJK_YED  - (TJK_EXPH(-1) ) / TJK_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TJK_EXPE ) / TJK_YED  - (TJK_EXPE(-1) ) / TJK_YED(-1) )

TJK_IGR  = TJK_IGR(-1) + (TJK_OGI / TJK_YED - TJK_OGI(-1) / TJK_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (TJK_EXPH ) / TJK_YED  - (TJK_EXPH(-1) ) / TJK_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TJK_EXPE ) / TJK_YED  - (TJK_EXPE(-1) ) / TJK_YED(-1) )

TJK_GIP  = ( TJK_GIP(-1)  + ( TJK_GDN(-1) - TJK_GDN(-2) ) * TJK_GINT(-1) / 100  + TJK_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( TJK_GINT(-1) / 100 - TJK_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (TJK_GDFXSH * (TJK_EXR / TJK_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TJK_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY TJK_GLN  = TJK_REV  - TJK_EXP

@IDENTITY TJK_GLNRATIO  = TJK_GLN / TJK_YEN * 100

TJK_GLNT  = TJK_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

TJK_TFP  = TJK_LABSH * (TJK_TECHL  - TJK_TECHL(-1))

TJK_LABSH  = TJK_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY TJK_LFN  = TJK_LRX * TJK_POPWA

TJK_LRX  = TJK_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(TJK_YER(-1) / TJK_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY TJK_URX  = (1 - TJK_LNN / TJK_LFN) * 100

TJK_URXF  = TJK_URXF(-1) * TJK_URX / TJK_URX(-1) * TJK_LNN / TJK_LNNF / (TJK_LNN(-1) / TJK_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(TJK_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TJK_PCR  / TJK_POPT)

TJK_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(TJK_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

TJK_HEAD19  = TJK_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TJK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI^2)  , TJK_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TJK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TJK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

TJK_HEAD55  = TJK_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TJK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI^2)  , TJK_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TJK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TJK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(TJK_XTR)  = DLOG(TJK_WDR)  + (1  - TJK_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(TJK_XTDNO$  / TJK_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * TJK_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(TJK_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (TJK_EXPH(-1) / TJK_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (TJK_EXPH(-1) / TJK_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(TJK_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(TJK_PM25)

TJK_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( TJK_EXPSP / TJK_YEN )

DLOG(TJK_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - TJK_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (TJK_FINC - TJK_FINC(-1))

DLOG(TJK_PCR)  =  - 0.00352953661223582  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(TJK_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TJK_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (TJK_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(TJK_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.7)  * DLOG(TJK_POPT)  +  - 0.783003479935828 * (DLOG(TJK_HIC)  - TJK_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * TJK_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * TJK_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TJK_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TJK_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TJK_IPR)  =  - 0.245550400203692  - 0.1 * (LOG(TJK_IPR(-1)  / TJK_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * TJK_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * TJK_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(TJK_PCR  + TJK_GCR(-1) + TJK_IGR(-1) + TJK_XTN  / TJK_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(TJK_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (TJK_USER - TJK_USER(-1))  - (0 * TJK_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TJK_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TJK_FUELSH - TJK_TOURSH)) * TJK_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * TJK_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TJK_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TJK_FUELSH - TJK_TOURSH)) * TJK_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TJK_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TJK_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TJK_MTR)  =  - 0.174223814494642  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(TJK_MTR(-1))  - LOG(TJK_PCR(-1) + TJK_ITR(-1) + TJK_GCR(-1) + TJK_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(TJK_YFT(-1) / TJK_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(TJK_CMUD(-1) * TJK_EXR(-1)  / TJK_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * TJK_OMS * LOG(TJK_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.146545161026605  * DLOG(TJK_XTR)  + 0.606082303096277  * DLOG(TJK_PCR)  + 0.00883059338063843  * DLOG(TJK_IPR)  + 0.101861846748305  * DLOG(TJK_GCR + TJK_IGR)

TJK_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * TJK_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * TJK_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * TJK_OILC

TJK_POIL  = TJK_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( TJK_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - TJK_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

TJK_PG  = TJK_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( TJK_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - TJK_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

TJK_PC  = TJK_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( TJK_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - TJK_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(TJK_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

TJK_PE  = TJK_PE(-1) * ( TJK_OILC(-1) / (TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) * TJK_POIL / TJK_POIL(-1)  + TJK_GASC(-1) / (TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) * TJK_PG / TJK_PG(-1)  + TJK_COALC(-1) / (TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) * TJK_PC / TJK_PC(-1)  + TJK_RC(-1) / (TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) * TJK_PR / TJK_PR(-1) )

D(TJK_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(TJK_PM25)  = 0.2 * (TJK_COALC(-1) / TJK_EC(-1) - TJK_COALC(-2) / TJK_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (TJK_COALC(-2) / TJK_EC(-2) - TJK_COALC(-3) / TJK_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (TJK_OILC(-1) / TJK_EC(-1) - TJK_OILC(-2) / TJK_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (TJK_OILC(-2) / TJK_EC(-2) - TJK_OILC(-3) / TJK_EC(-3))

DLOG(TJK_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(TJK_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(TJK_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(TJK_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TJK_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TJK_PE * TJK_EXR / TJK_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TJK_PE(-1) * TJK_EXR(-1) / TJK_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TJK_PE(-2) * TJK_EXR(-2) / TJK_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TJK_PE(-3) * TJK_EXR(-3) / TJK_HIC(-3))  - (TJK_EFF - TJK_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(TJK_COALC)  = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TJK_COALC(-1) / TJK_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.444921438729686 * LOG(TJK_PE(-1) / TJK_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) / TJK_EC(-1))

DLOG(TJK_GASC)  = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TJK_GASC(-1) / TJK_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TJK_PE(-1) / TJK_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) / TJK_EC(-1))

DLOG(TJK_RC)  = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TJK_RC(-1) / TJK_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.444921438729686 * LOG(TJK_PE(-1) / TJK_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) / TJK_EC(-1))

DLOG(TJK_OILC)  = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TJK_OILC(-1) / TJK_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.444921438729686 * LOG(TJK_PE(-1) / TJK_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TJK_COALC(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1) + TJK_OILC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)) / TJK_EC(-1))

TJK_EXR  = TJK_EXR(-1) * ( (TJK_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(THA_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(THA_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(THA_MTD)  + 0.4 * (THA_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (THA_YER / THA_YFT  - THA_YER(-1) / THA_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + THA_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + THA_GCARB / THA_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (THA_PREM - THA_PREM(-1)) / 100

THA_YED  = THA_YED(-1) * THA_HIC / THA_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_INT  = THA_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_LTI  = THA_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (THA_INT - THA_INT(-1))  + (THA_PREM  - THA_PREM(-1)) / 100

THA_PREM  = THA_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (THA_GDNRATIO(-1)  - THA_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(THA_LNN)  = DLOG(THA_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(THA_LNN(-1))  - LOG(THA_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(THA_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(THA_LNNF)  = DLOG(THA_LNN)

THA_FUELSH  = THA_FUELSH(-1)

THA_TAXR  = THA_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( THA_GLNT(-1)  - THA_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * THA_YEN(-1) / ( ( THA_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (THA_YER(-2)  + THA_GDI(-2)) * THA_YED(-2) * (THA_LNN(-1) / THA_LNN(-2)  + THA_TECHL(-1) - THA_TECHL(-2) ) ) + THA_REMIT(-1)  + THA_EXPSP(-1) ) * THA_SOLV

THA_CTAXR  = THA_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( THA_GLNT(-1)  - THA_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * THA_YEN(-1) / ( THA_PROF(-1) ) * THA_SOLV

(THA_OGC)  = THA_OGC(-1) * (THA_YFT / THA_YFT(-1) * THA_YED / THA_YED(-1))

THA_USER  = (THA_LTI  - THA_INFT  + THA_DEP * 100) / (1  - THA_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (THA_GCARB / THA_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY THA_XTN  = THA_XTD$ * THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") * THA_XTR

@IDENTITY THA_YEN  = THA_YER  * THA_YED

@IDENTITY THA_MTN  = THA_MTD  * THA_MTR

@IDENTITY THA_XTN$  = THA_XTN / THA_EXR

@IDENTITY THA_YEN$  = THA_YEN / THA_EXR

@IDENTITY THA_MTN$  = THA_MTN / THA_EXR

@IDENTITY THA_MTR$  = THA_MTR$(-1) * THA_MTR / THA_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_XTR$  = THA_XTR$(-1) * THA_XTR / THA_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_YER$  = THA_YER$(-1) * THA_YER / THA_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_YFT$  = THA_YFT$(-1) * THA_YFT / THA_YFT(-1)

THA_POPT  = THA_POPT(-1)  - THA_LIVES

THA_POPWA  = THA_POPWA(-1) * THA_POPT / THA_POPT(-1)

THA_SCR  = THA_SCR(-1)  + ((THA_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (THA_YFT(-1) / THA_YER(-1)  - THA_YFT(-2) / THA_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY THA_ITR  = THA_IGR  + THA_IPR

@IDENTITY THA_YER  = THA_PCR  + THA_GCR  + THA_ITR  + THA_SCR  + THA_XTR  - THA_MTR

@IDENTITY THA_PROF  = (THA_YEN - THA_ITAX) * (1 - THA_LABSH)

@IDENTITY THA_GDI  = THA_YER  - THA_XTR  + THA_MTR  + THA_XTN  / ((THA_YEN  - THA_XTN  + THA_MTN)  / (THA_YER  - THA_XTR  + THA_MTR))  - THA_MTN  / ((THA_YEN  - THA_XTN  + THA_MTN)  / (THA_YER  - THA_XTR  + THA_MTR))

@IDENTITY THA_RPDI  = THA_LABSH * 0.5 * (THA_YER(-1)  + THA_GDI(-1)) * THA_YED(-1) / THA_HIC(-1) * (THA_LNN / THA_LNN(-1)  + THA_TECHL - THA_TECHL(-1)) + THA_REMIT / THA_HIC  + THA_EXPSP / THA_HIC  - THA_TAX / THA_HIC

DLOG(THA_YFT)  = (1 - THA_ALPHA - THA_LABSH) * DLOG(THA_K(-1) / THA_LFN(-1))  + (1 - THA_ALPHA) * DLOG(THA_LFN)  + THA_LABSH * D(THA_TECHL)  + THA_ALPHA * (DLOG(THA_EC)  + D(THA_EFF) )  - ( THA_CLIMLOSS / THA_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (THA_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY THA_K  = THA_K(-1) * (1 - THA_DEP) + THA_ITR

DLOG(THA_MTD)  = (1  - THA_OMS) * ( DLOG(THA_CMUD)  + DLOG(THA_EXR) )  + THA_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(THA_EXR) )

DLOG(THA_XTD$)  = (1  - THA_OXS) * DLOG(THA_XTDNO$)  + THA_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

THA_INFT  = 0.95 * THA_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

THA_OXS  = THA_OXS(-1)

THA_OMS  = THA_OMS(-1) * ((THA_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * THA_EXR(-1) / THA_MTN(-1)) / (THA_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * THA_EXR(-2) / THA_MTN(-2)))^0.25

THA_CXS  = THA_CXS(-1)

THA_FINC  = THA_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_CAN  = THA_XTN / THA_EXR  - THA_MTN / THA_EXR  + THA_REMIT / THA_EXR  + THA_CANOTH

@IDENTITY THA_CANRATIO  = THA_CAN / THA_YEN$ * 100

THA_CANOTH  = THA_CANOTH(-1)  + ((THA_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (THA_YEN$  / THA_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + THA_REVG / THA_EXR  - THA_REVG(-1) / THA_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(THA_EFEX)  =  - LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.588109223E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.092130821E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03476154669 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000629767578 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00216234456 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.668821019E-05 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001284607958 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008447959648 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1643044548 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001535146558 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.155130551E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04521695532 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02771601223 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03492230868 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001559829066 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1126249949 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001213681887 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.19326823E-05 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.480952126E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01267499913 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008929614763 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04332374318 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002781232197 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001406403328 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.892587484E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01081852791 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001532796342 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004761989545 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002190149396 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007676756516 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02186796398 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02734495813 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006946533781 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.486221806E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06763521218 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.892438923E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001112511158 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.231135081E-06 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.711631639E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.96861958E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003185817551 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.6892636E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.75925734E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.556376437E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02619223152 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.08447302915 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02337908097 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009614412105 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01403699179 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006904979924 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0102230446 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00225455586 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01479795207 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0227959205 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01387570938 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02843728776 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03361106939 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06840962487 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(THA_REFEX )  =  - LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.588109223E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.092130821E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03476154669 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000629767578 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00216234456 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.668821019E-05 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001284607958 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008447959648 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1643044548 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001535146558 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.155130551E-05 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04521695532 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02771601223 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03492230868 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001559829066 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1126249949 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001213681887 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.19326823E-05 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.480952126E-06 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01267499913 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008929614763 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04332374318 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002781232197 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001406403328 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.892587484E-05 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01081852791 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001532796342 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004761989545 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002190149396 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007676756516 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02186796398 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02734495813 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006946533781 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.486221806E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06763521218 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.892438923E-05 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001112511158 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.231135081E-06 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.711631639E-05 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.96861958E-05 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003185817551 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.6892636E-05 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.75925734E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.556376437E-05 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02619223152 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08447302915 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02337908097 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009614412105 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01403699179 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006904979924 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0102230446 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00225455586 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01479795207 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0227959205 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01387570938 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02843728776 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03361106939 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06840962487 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

THA_REMIT  = THA_REMIT(-1) / THA_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05697645646 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009038041074 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02498785583 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 5.761718448E-05 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02063140629 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02039037239 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.09440293817 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0173318301 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04070433526 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01970857122 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01718126981 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001856204781 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009036383143 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04569852862 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02747466712 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03311358851 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001442175587 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001110548688 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001099964431 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0871422977 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01358122677 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007493551947 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002985617741 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001915572136 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01948272623 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001353130848 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002002537376 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.276559947 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004469696735 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009974679727 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.09456667393 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01285793578 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.04479273047 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * THA_EXR

THA_GINT  = THA_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (THA_LTI  - THA_LTI(-1))

THA_GDN  = THA_GDN(-1) * (THA_GDFXSH  * (THA_EXR  / THA_EXR(-1))  + (1  - THA_GDFXSH))  - THA_GLN

@IDENTITY THA_GDNRATIO  = THA_GDN / THA_YEN * 100

THA_GDFXSH  = ( THA_GDFXSH(-1) * (THA_EXR / THA_EXR(-1) )) / (THA_GDFXSH(-1) * (THA_EXR / THA_EXR(-1))  + 1 - THA_GDFXSH(-1) )

THA_TOURSH  = THA_TOURSH(-1)

THA_LOCK  = 0

THA_GCARBR  = THA_GCARBR(-1)

THA_GTRADER  = THA_GTRADER(-1)

THA_ITAXR  = THA_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_REV  = THA_TAX  + THA_CTAX  + THA_ITAX  + THA_GTRADE  + THA_REVG  + THA_GCARB  + THA_GCOM  + THA_GOTH

@IDENTITY THA_TAX  = THA_TAXR * (THA_LABSH * 0.5 * (THA_YER(-1)  + THA_GDI(-1)) * THA_YED(-1) * (THA_LNN / THA_LNN(-1)  + THA_TECHL - THA_TECHL(-1)) + THA_REMIT  + THA_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY THA_CTAX  = THA_CTAXR * THA_PROF

@IDENTITY THA_ITAX  = THA_ITAXR * (THA_PCR * THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY THA_GTRADE  = THA_GTRADER * THA_XTN

THA_REVG  = THA_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (THA_YER$ / THA_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - THA_YER$(-1) / THA_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * THA_EXR / THA_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_GCARB  = THA_GCARBR * THA_CO2 * THA_EXR / 1000

THA_GCOM  = THA_GCOM(-1) * ( THA_OILC / (THA_OILC + THA_GASC + THA_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + THA_GASC / (THA_OILC + THA_GASC + THA_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + THA_COALC / (THA_OILC + THA_GASC + THA_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

THA_GOTH  = THA_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_EXP  = THA_EXPE  + THA_EXPH  + THA_EXPSP  + THA_OGC  + THA_OGI  + THA_GIP

THA_EXPE  = THA_EXPE(-1) * (THA_YFT / THA_YFT(-1)) * (THA_YED / THA_YED(-1))

THA_EXPH = THA_EXPH(-1) * (THA_YFT / THA_YFT(-1)) * (THA_YED / THA_YED(-1))

THA_EXPSP  = THA_EXPSP(-1) * (THA_YFT / THA_YFT(-1)) * (THA_YED / THA_YED(-1)) * (THA_POPT - THA_LNN) / (THA_POPT(-1) - THA_LNN(-1))

DLOG(THA_OGI)  = DLOG(THA_YFT)  + DLOG(THA_YED)

THA_GCR  = THA_GCR(-1)  + ( THA_OGC / THA_YED - THA_OGC(-1) / THA_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (THA_EXPH ) / THA_YED  - (THA_EXPH(-1) ) / THA_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (THA_EXPE ) / THA_YED  - (THA_EXPE(-1) ) / THA_YED(-1) )

THA_IGR  = THA_IGR(-1) + (THA_OGI / THA_YED - THA_OGI(-1) / THA_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (THA_EXPH ) / THA_YED  - (THA_EXPH(-1) ) / THA_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (THA_EXPE ) / THA_YED  - (THA_EXPE(-1) ) / THA_YED(-1) )

THA_GIP  = ( THA_GIP(-1)  + ( THA_GDN(-1) - THA_GDN(-2) ) * THA_GINT(-1) / 100  + THA_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( THA_GINT(-1) / 100 - THA_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (THA_GDFXSH * (THA_EXR / THA_EXR(-1))  + (1 - THA_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY THA_GLN  = THA_REV  - THA_EXP

@IDENTITY THA_GLNRATIO  = THA_GLN / THA_YEN * 100

THA_GLNT  = THA_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

THA_TFP  = THA_LABSH * (THA_TECHL  - THA_TECHL(-1))

THA_LABSH  = THA_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY THA_LFN  = THA_LRX * THA_POPWA

THA_LRX  = THA_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(THA_YER(-1) / THA_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY THA_URX  = (1 - THA_LNN / THA_LFN) * 100

THA_URXF  = THA_URXF(-1) * THA_URX / THA_URX(-1) * THA_LNN / THA_LNNF / (THA_LNN(-1) / THA_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(THA_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(THA_PCR  / THA_POPT)

THA_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(THA_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

THA_HEAD19  = THA_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(THA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI^2)  , THA_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(THA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , THA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

THA_HEAD55  = THA_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(THA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI^2)  , THA_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(THA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , THA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(THA_XTR)  = DLOG(THA_WDR)  + (1  - THA_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(THA_XTDNO$  / THA_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * THA_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(THA_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (THA_EXPH(-1) / THA_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (THA_EXPH(-1) / THA_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(THA_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(THA_PM25)

THA_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( THA_EXPSP / THA_YEN )

DLOG(THA_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - THA_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (THA_FINC - THA_FINC(-1))

DLOG(THA_PCR)  =  - 0.0865660815924033  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(THA_PCR(-1))  - LOG(THA_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (THA_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(THA_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(THA_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(THA_HIC)  - THA_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * THA_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * THA_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(THA_YFT(-1))  - LOG(THA_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(THA_IPR)  =  - 0.183232609640406  - 0.1 * (LOG(THA_IPR(-1)  / THA_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * THA_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * THA_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(THA_PCR  + THA_GCR(-1) + THA_IGR(-1) + THA_XTN  / THA_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(THA_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (THA_USER - THA_USER(-1))  - (0 * THA_FUELSH  + 0.26 * THA_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - THA_FUELSH - THA_TOURSH)) * THA_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * THA_FUELSH  + 0.26 * THA_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - THA_FUELSH - THA_TOURSH)) * THA_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(THA_YFT(-1))  - LOG(THA_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(THA_MTR)  =  - 0.134668385568489  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(THA_MTR(-1))  - LOG(THA_PCR(-1) + THA_ITR(-1) + THA_GCR(-1) + THA_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(THA_YFT(-1) / THA_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(THA_CMUD(-1) * THA_EXR(-1)  / THA_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * THA_OMS * LOG(THA_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.726777598591907  * DLOG(THA_XTR)  + 0.35611405755817  * DLOG(THA_PCR)  + 0.159382904216334  * DLOG(THA_IPR)  + 0.0293539269799165  * DLOG(THA_GCR + THA_IGR)

THA_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * THA_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * THA_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * THA_OILC

THA_POIL  = THA_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( THA_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - THA_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

THA_PG  = THA_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( THA_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - THA_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

THA_PC  = THA_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( THA_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - THA_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(THA_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

THA_PE  = THA_PE(-1) * ( THA_OILC(-1) / (THA_OILC(-1) + THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) * THA_POIL / THA_POIL(-1)  + THA_GASC(-1) / (THA_OILC(-1) + THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) * THA_PG / THA_PG(-1)  + THA_COALC(-1) / (THA_OILC(-1) + THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) * THA_PC / THA_PC(-1)  + THA_RC(-1) / (THA_OILC(-1) + THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) * THA_PR / THA_PR(-1) )

D(THA_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(THA_PM25)  = 0.2 * (THA_COALC(-1) / THA_EC(-1) - THA_COALC(-2) / THA_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (THA_COALC(-2) / THA_EC(-2) - THA_COALC(-3) / THA_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (THA_OILC(-1) / THA_EC(-1) - THA_OILC(-2) / THA_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (THA_OILC(-2) / THA_EC(-2) - THA_OILC(-3) / THA_EC(-3))

DLOG(THA_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(THA_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(THA_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(THA_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(THA_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(THA_PE * THA_EXR / THA_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(THA_PE(-1) * THA_EXR(-1) / THA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(THA_PE(-2) * THA_EXR(-2) / THA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(THA_PE(-3) * THA_EXR(-3) / THA_HIC(-3))  - (THA_EFF - THA_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(THA_COALC)  = DLOG(THA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(THA_COALC(-1) / THA_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.0618475411371967 * LOG(THA_PE(-1) / THA_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_OILC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) / THA_EC(-1))

DLOG(THA_GASC)  = DLOG(THA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(THA_GASC(-1) / THA_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.25 / 0.325950766102473 * LOG(THA_PE(-1) / THA_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_OILC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) / THA_EC(-1))

DLOG(THA_RC)  = DLOG(THA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( THA_RC(-1) / THA_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.0618475411371967 * LOG(THA_PE(-1) / THA_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_OILC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) / THA_EC(-1))

DLOG(THA_OILC)  = DLOG(THA_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( THA_OILC(-1) / THA_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.25 / 0.0618475411371967 * LOG(THA_PE(-1) / THA_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((THA_COALC(-1) + THA_GASC(-1) + THA_OILC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)) / THA_EC(-1))

THA_EXR  = THA_EXR(-1) * ( ( (THA_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (THA_INT  - USA_INT)  - (THA_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(TLS_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(TLS_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TLS_MTD)  + 0.4 * (TLS_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (TLS_YER / TLS_YFT  - TLS_YER(-1) / TLS_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + TLS_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + TLS_GCARB / TLS_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (TLS_PREM - TLS_PREM(-1)) / 100

TLS_YED  = TLS_YED(-1) * TLS_HIC / TLS_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_INT  = TLS_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_LTI  = TLS_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (TLS_INT - TLS_INT(-1))  + (TLS_PREM  - TLS_PREM(-1)) / 100

TLS_PREM  = TLS_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (TLS_GDNRATIO(-1)  - TLS_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(TLS_LNN)  = DLOG(TLS_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(TLS_LNN(-1))  - LOG(TLS_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(TLS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TLS_LNNF)  = DLOG(TLS_LNN)

TLS_FUELSH  = TLS_FUELSH(-1)

TLS_TAXR  = TLS_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TLS_GLNT(-1)  - TLS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TLS_YEN(-1) / ( ( TLS_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (TLS_YER(-2)  + TLS_GDI(-2)) * TLS_YED(-2) * (TLS_LNN(-1) / TLS_LNN(-2)  + TLS_TECHL(-1) - TLS_TECHL(-2) ) ) + TLS_REMIT(-1)  + TLS_EXPSP(-1) ) * TLS_SOLV

TLS_CTAXR  = TLS_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TLS_GLNT(-1)  - TLS_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TLS_YEN(-1) / ( TLS_PROF(-1) ) * TLS_SOLV

(TLS_OGC)  = TLS_OGC(-1) * (TLS_YFT / TLS_YFT(-1) * TLS_YED / TLS_YED(-1))

TLS_USER  = (TLS_LTI  - TLS_INFT  + TLS_DEP * 100) / (1  - TLS_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (TLS_GCARB / TLS_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY TLS_XTN  = TLS_XTD$ * TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") * TLS_XTR

@IDENTITY TLS_YEN  = TLS_YER  * TLS_YED

@IDENTITY TLS_MTN  = TLS_MTD  * TLS_MTR

@IDENTITY TLS_XTN$  = TLS_XTN / TLS_EXR

@IDENTITY TLS_YEN$  = TLS_YEN / TLS_EXR

@IDENTITY TLS_MTN$  = TLS_MTN / TLS_EXR

@IDENTITY TLS_MTR$  = TLS_MTR$(-1) * TLS_MTR / TLS_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_XTR$  = TLS_XTR$(-1) * TLS_XTR / TLS_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_YER$  = TLS_YER$(-1) * TLS_YER / TLS_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_YFT$  = TLS_YFT$(-1) * TLS_YFT / TLS_YFT(-1)

TLS_POPT  = TLS_POPT(-1)  - TLS_LIVES

TLS_POPWA  = TLS_POPWA(-1) * TLS_POPT / TLS_POPT(-1)

TLS_SCR  = TLS_SCR(-1)  + ((TLS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TLS_YFT(-1) / TLS_YER(-1)  - TLS_YFT(-2) / TLS_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY TLS_ITR  = TLS_IGR  + TLS_IPR

@IDENTITY TLS_YER  = TLS_PCR  + TLS_GCR  + TLS_ITR  + TLS_SCR  + TLS_XTR  - TLS_MTR

@IDENTITY TLS_PROF  = (TLS_YEN - TLS_ITAX) * (1 - TLS_LABSH)

@IDENTITY TLS_GDI  = TLS_YER  - TLS_XTR  + TLS_MTR  + TLS_XTN  / ((TLS_YEN  - TLS_XTN  + TLS_MTN)  / (TLS_YER  - TLS_XTR  + TLS_MTR))  - TLS_MTN  / ((TLS_YEN  - TLS_XTN  + TLS_MTN)  / (TLS_YER  - TLS_XTR  + TLS_MTR))

@IDENTITY TLS_RPDI  = TLS_LABSH * 0.5 * (TLS_YER(-1)  + TLS_GDI(-1)) * TLS_YED(-1) / TLS_HIC(-1) * (TLS_LNN / TLS_LNN(-1)  + TLS_TECHL - TLS_TECHL(-1)) + TLS_REMIT / TLS_HIC  + TLS_EXPSP / TLS_HIC  - TLS_TAX / TLS_HIC

DLOG(TLS_YFT)  = (1 - TLS_ALPHA - TLS_LABSH) * DLOG(TLS_K(-1) / TLS_LFN(-1))  + (1 - TLS_ALPHA) * DLOG(TLS_LFN)  + TLS_LABSH * D(TLS_TECHL)  + TLS_ALPHA * (DLOG(TLS_EC)  + D(TLS_EFF) )  - ( TLS_CLIMLOSS / TLS_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (TLS_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY TLS_K  = TLS_K(-1) * (1 - TLS_DEP) + TLS_ITR

DLOG(TLS_MTD)  = (1  - TLS_OMS) * ( DLOG(TLS_CMUD)  + DLOG(TLS_EXR) )  + TLS_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TLS_EXR) )

DLOG(TLS_XTD$)  = (1  - TLS_OXS) * DLOG(TLS_XTDNO$)  + TLS_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

TLS_INFT  = 0.95 * TLS_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

TLS_OXS  = TLS_OXS(-1)

TLS_OMS  = TLS_OMS(-1) * ((TLS_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * TLS_EXR(-1) / TLS_MTN(-1)) / (TLS_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * TLS_EXR(-2) / TLS_MTN(-2)))^0.25

TLS_CXS  = TLS_CXS(-1)

TLS_FINC  = TLS_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_CAN  = TLS_XTN / TLS_EXR  - TLS_MTN / TLS_EXR  + TLS_REMIT / TLS_EXR  + TLS_CANOTH

@IDENTITY TLS_CANRATIO  = TLS_CAN / TLS_YEN$ * 100

TLS_CANOTH  = TLS_CANOTH(-1)  + ((TLS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TLS_YEN$  / TLS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TLS_REVG / TLS_EXR  - TLS_REVG(-1) / TLS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(TLS_EFEX)  =  - LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.560831025E-10 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009186774221 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.860327206E-06 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001028827391 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.61894027E-05 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(TLS_REFEX )  =  - LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.560831025E-10 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC ,
