@ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1319559254 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04641927571 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003376273608 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003469160567 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002995741074 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01999134955 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001427424007 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001377856752 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003404054563 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04399607971 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08155138471 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.00622129996 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03727899999 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

TLS_REMIT  = TLS_REMIT(-1) / TLS_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4093831239 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002414946756 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 3.532837537E-05 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.5170521705 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001936847247 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0009259485785 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003652234581 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.000243624731 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00717189954 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001000212973 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05813927139 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001910283922 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 5.072212592E-05 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * TLS_EXR

TLS_GINT  = TLS_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (TLS_LTI  - TLS_LTI(-1))

TLS_GDN  = TLS_GDN(-1) * (TLS_GDFXSH  * (TLS_EXR  / TLS_EXR(-1))  + (1  - TLS_GDFXSH))  - TLS_GLN

@IDENTITY TLS_GDNRATIO  = TLS_GDN / TLS_YEN * 100

TLS_GDFXSH  = ( TLS_GDFXSH(-1) * (TLS_EXR / TLS_EXR(-1) )) / (TLS_GDFXSH(-1) * (TLS_EXR / TLS_EXR(-1))  + 1 - TLS_GDFXSH(-1) )

TLS_TOURSH  = TLS_TOURSH(-1)

TLS_LOCK  = 0

TLS_GCARBR  = TLS_GCARBR(-1)

TLS_GTRADER  = TLS_GTRADER(-1)

TLS_ITAXR  = TLS_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_REV  = TLS_TAX  + TLS_CTAX  + TLS_ITAX  + TLS_GTRADE  + TLS_REVG  + TLS_GCARB  + TLS_GCOM  + TLS_GOTH

@IDENTITY TLS_TAX  = TLS_TAXR * (TLS_LABSH * 0.5 * (TLS_YER(-1)  + TLS_GDI(-1)) * TLS_YED(-1) * (TLS_LNN / TLS_LNN(-1)  + TLS_TECHL - TLS_TECHL(-1)) + TLS_REMIT  + TLS_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY TLS_CTAX  = TLS_CTAXR * TLS_PROF

@IDENTITY TLS_ITAX  = TLS_ITAXR * (TLS_PCR * TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY TLS_GTRADE  = TLS_GTRADER * TLS_XTN

TLS_REVG  = TLS_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (TLS_YER$ / TLS_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - TLS_YER$(-1) / TLS_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * TLS_EXR / TLS_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_GCARB  = TLS_GCARBR * TLS_CO2 * TLS_EXR / 1000

TLS_GCOM  = TLS_GCOM(-1) * ( TLS_OILC / (TLS_OILC + TLS_GASC + TLS_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + TLS_GASC / (TLS_OILC + TLS_GASC + TLS_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + TLS_COALC / (TLS_OILC + TLS_GASC + TLS_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

TLS_GOTH  = TLS_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_EXP  = TLS_EXPE  + TLS_EXPH  + TLS_EXPSP  + TLS_OGC  + TLS_OGI  + TLS_GIP

TLS_EXPE  = TLS_EXPE(-1) * (TLS_YFT / TLS_YFT(-1)) * (TLS_YED / TLS_YED(-1))

TLS_EXPH = TLS_EXPH(-1) * (TLS_YFT / TLS_YFT(-1)) * (TLS_YED / TLS_YED(-1))

TLS_EXPSP  = TLS_EXPSP(-1) * (TLS_YFT / TLS_YFT(-1)) * (TLS_YED / TLS_YED(-1)) * (TLS_POPT - TLS_LNN) / (TLS_POPT(-1) - TLS_LNN(-1))

DLOG(TLS_OGI)  = DLOG(TLS_YFT)  + DLOG(TLS_YED)

TLS_GCR  = TLS_GCR(-1)  + ( TLS_OGC / TLS_YED - TLS_OGC(-1) / TLS_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (TLS_EXPH ) / TLS_YED  - (TLS_EXPH(-1) ) / TLS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TLS_EXPE ) / TLS_YED  - (TLS_EXPE(-1) ) / TLS_YED(-1) )

TLS_IGR  = TLS_IGR(-1) + (TLS_OGI / TLS_YED - TLS_OGI(-1) / TLS_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (TLS_EXPH ) / TLS_YED  - (TLS_EXPH(-1) ) / TLS_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TLS_EXPE ) / TLS_YED  - (TLS_EXPE(-1) ) / TLS_YED(-1) )

TLS_GIP  = ( TLS_GIP(-1)  + ( TLS_GDN(-1) - TLS_GDN(-2) ) * TLS_GINT(-1) / 100  + TLS_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( TLS_GINT(-1) / 100 - TLS_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (TLS_GDFXSH * (TLS_EXR / TLS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TLS_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY TLS_GLN  = TLS_REV  - TLS_EXP

@IDENTITY TLS_GLNRATIO  = TLS_GLN / TLS_YEN * 100

TLS_GLNT  = TLS_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

TLS_TFP  = TLS_LABSH * (TLS_TECHL  - TLS_TECHL(-1))

TLS_LABSH  = TLS_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY TLS_LFN  = TLS_LRX * TLS_POPWA

TLS_LRX  = TLS_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(TLS_YER(-1) / TLS_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY TLS_URX  = (1 - TLS_LNN / TLS_LFN) * 100

TLS_URXF  = TLS_URXF(-1) * TLS_URX / TLS_URX(-1) * TLS_LNN / TLS_LNNF / (TLS_LNN(-1) / TLS_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(TLS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TLS_PCR  / TLS_POPT)

TLS_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(TLS_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

TLS_HEAD19  = TLS_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TLS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI^2)  , TLS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TLS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TLS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

TLS_HEAD55  = TLS_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TLS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI^2)  , TLS_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TLS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TLS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(TLS_XTR)  = DLOG(TLS_WDR)  + (1  - TLS_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(TLS_XTDNO$  / TLS_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * TLS_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(TLS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (TLS_EXPH(-1) / TLS_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (TLS_EXPH(-1) / TLS_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(TLS_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(TLS_PM25)

TLS_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( TLS_EXPSP / TLS_YEN )

DLOG(TLS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - TLS_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (TLS_FINC - TLS_FINC(-1))

DLOG(TLS_PCR)  =  - 0.193831527602777  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(TLS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TLS_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (TLS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TLS_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(TLS_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(TLS_HIC)  - TLS_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * TLS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * TLS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TLS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TLS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TLS_IPR)  =  - 0.14885340846788  - 0.1 * (LOG(TLS_IPR(-1)  / TLS_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * TLS_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * TLS_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(TLS_PCR  + TLS_GCR(-1) + TLS_IGR(-1) + TLS_XTN  / TLS_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(TLS_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (TLS_USER - TLS_USER(-1))  - (0 * TLS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TLS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TLS_FUELSH - TLS_TOURSH)) * TLS_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * TLS_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TLS_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TLS_FUELSH - TLS_TOURSH)) * TLS_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TLS_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TLS_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TLS_MTR)  =  - 0.140059957622333  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(TLS_MTR(-1))  - LOG(TLS_PCR(-1) + TLS_ITR(-1) + TLS_GCR(-1) + TLS_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(TLS_YFT(-1) / TLS_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(TLS_CMUD(-1) * TLS_EXR(-1)  / TLS_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * TLS_OMS * LOG(TLS_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.124115204475155  * DLOG(TLS_XTR)  + 0.238627838787328  * DLOG(TLS_PCR)  + 0.13180152608141  * DLOG(TLS_IPR)  + 0.222969139058484  * DLOG(TLS_GCR + TLS_IGR)

TLS_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * TLS_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * TLS_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * TLS_OILC

TLS_POIL  = TLS_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( TLS_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - TLS_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

TLS_PG  = TLS_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( TLS_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - TLS_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

TLS_PC  = TLS_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( TLS_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - TLS_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(TLS_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

TLS_PE  = TLS_PE(-1) * ( TLS_OILC(-1) / (TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) * TLS_POIL / TLS_POIL(-1)  + TLS_GASC(-1) / (TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) * TLS_PG / TLS_PG(-1)  + TLS_COALC(-1) / (TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) * TLS_PC / TLS_PC(-1)  + TLS_RC(-1) / (TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) * TLS_PR / TLS_PR(-1) )

D(TLS_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(TLS_PM25)  = 0.2 * (TLS_COALC(-1) / TLS_EC(-1) - TLS_COALC(-2) / TLS_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (TLS_COALC(-2) / TLS_EC(-2) - TLS_COALC(-3) / TLS_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (TLS_OILC(-1) / TLS_EC(-1) - TLS_OILC(-2) / TLS_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (TLS_OILC(-2) / TLS_EC(-2) - TLS_OILC(-3) / TLS_EC(-3))

DLOG(TLS_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(TLS_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(TLS_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(TLS_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TLS_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TLS_PE * TLS_EXR / TLS_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TLS_PE(-1) * TLS_EXR(-1) / TLS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TLS_PE(-2) * TLS_EXR(-2) / TLS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TLS_PE(-3) * TLS_EXR(-3) / TLS_HIC(-3))  - (TLS_EFF - TLS_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(TLS_COALC)  = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TLS_COALC(-1) / TLS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TLS_PE(-1) / TLS_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) / TLS_EC(-1))

DLOG(TLS_GASC)  = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TLS_GASC(-1) / TLS_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TLS_PE(-1) / TLS_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) / TLS_EC(-1))

DLOG(TLS_RC)  = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TLS_RC(-1) / TLS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.181554975982709 * LOG(TLS_PE(-1) / TLS_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) / TLS_EC(-1))

DLOG(TLS_OILC)  = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TLS_OILC(-1) / TLS_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.181554975982709 * LOG(TLS_PE(-1) / TLS_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TLS_COALC(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1) + TLS_OILC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)) / TLS_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY TLS_EXR  = 1

DLOG(TON_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(TON_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TON_MTD)  + 0.4 * (TON_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (TON_YER / TON_YFT  - TON_YER(-1) / TON_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + TON_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + TON_GCARB / TON_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (TON_PREM - TON_PREM(-1)) / 100

TON_YED  = TON_YED(-1) * TON_HIC / TON_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_INT  = TON_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_LTI  = TON_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (TON_INT - TON_INT(-1))  + (TON_PREM  - TON_PREM(-1)) / 100

TON_PREM  = TON_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (TON_GDNRATIO(-1)  - TON_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(TON_LNN)  = DLOG(TON_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(TON_LNN(-1))  - LOG(TON_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(TON_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TON_LNNF)  = DLOG(TON_LNN)

TON_FUELSH  = TON_FUELSH(-1)

TON_TAXR  = TON_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TON_GLNT(-1)  - TON_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TON_YEN(-1) / ( ( TON_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (TON_YER(-2)  + TON_GDI(-2)) * TON_YED(-2) * (TON_LNN(-1) / TON_LNN(-2)  + TON_TECHL(-1) - TON_TECHL(-2) ) ) + TON_REMIT(-1)  + TON_EXPSP(-1) ) * TON_SOLV

TON_CTAXR  = TON_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TON_GLNT(-1)  - TON_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TON_YEN(-1) / ( TON_PROF(-1) ) * TON_SOLV

(TON_OGC)  = TON_OGC(-1) * (TON_YFT / TON_YFT(-1) * TON_YED / TON_YED(-1))

TON_USER  = (TON_LTI  - TON_INFT  + TON_DEP * 100) / (1  - TON_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (TON_GCARB / TON_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY TON_XTN  = TON_XTD$ * TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") * TON_XTR

@IDENTITY TON_YEN  = TON_YER  * TON_YED

@IDENTITY TON_MTN  = TON_MTD  * TON_MTR

@IDENTITY TON_XTN$  = TON_XTN / TON_EXR

@IDENTITY TON_YEN$  = TON_YEN / TON_EXR

@IDENTITY TON_MTN$  = TON_MTN / TON_EXR

@IDENTITY TON_MTR$  = TON_MTR$(-1) * TON_MTR / TON_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_XTR$  = TON_XTR$(-1) * TON_XTR / TON_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_YER$  = TON_YER$(-1) * TON_YER / TON_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_YFT$  = TON_YFT$(-1) * TON_YFT / TON_YFT(-1)

TON_POPT  = TON_POPT(-1)  - TON_LIVES

TON_POPWA  = TON_POPWA(-1) * TON_POPT / TON_POPT(-1)

TON_SCR  = TON_SCR(-1)  + ((TON_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TON_YFT(-1) / TON_YER(-1)  - TON_YFT(-2) / TON_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY TON_ITR  = TON_IGR  + TON_IPR

@IDENTITY TON_YER  = TON_PCR  + TON_GCR  + TON_ITR  + TON_SCR  + TON_XTR  - TON_MTR

@IDENTITY TON_PROF  = (TON_YEN - TON_ITAX) * (1 - TON_LABSH)

@IDENTITY TON_GDI  = TON_YER  - TON_XTR  + TON_MTR  + TON_XTN  / ((TON_YEN  - TON_XTN  + TON_MTN)  / (TON_YER  - TON_XTR  + TON_MTR))  - TON_MTN  / ((TON_YEN  - TON_XTN  + TON_MTN)  / (TON_YER  - TON_XTR  + TON_MTR))

@IDENTITY TON_RPDI  = TON_LABSH * 0.5 * (TON_YER(-1)  + TON_GDI(-1)) * TON_YED(-1) / TON_HIC(-1) * (TON_LNN / TON_LNN(-1)  + TON_TECHL - TON_TECHL(-1)) + TON_REMIT / TON_HIC  + TON_EXPSP / TON_HIC  - TON_TAX / TON_HIC

DLOG(TON_YFT)  = (1 - TON_ALPHA - TON_LABSH) * DLOG(TON_K(-1) / TON_LFN(-1))  + (1 - TON_ALPHA) * DLOG(TON_LFN)  + TON_LABSH * D(TON_TECHL)  + TON_ALPHA * (DLOG(TON_EC)  + D(TON_EFF) )  - ( TON_CLIMLOSS / TON_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (TON_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY TON_K  = TON_K(-1) * (1 - TON_DEP) + TON_ITR

DLOG(TON_MTD)  = (1  - TON_OMS) * ( DLOG(TON_CMUD)  + DLOG(TON_EXR) )  + TON_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TON_EXR) )

DLOG(TON_XTD$)  = (1  - TON_OXS) * DLOG(TON_XTDNO$)  + TON_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

TON_INFT  = 0.95 * TON_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

TON_OXS  = TON_OXS(-1)

TON_OMS  = TON_OMS(-1) * ((TON_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * TON_EXR(-1) / TON_MTN(-1)) / (TON_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * TON_EXR(-2) / TON_MTN(-2)))^0.25

TON_CXS  = TON_CXS(-1)

TON_FINC  = TON_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_CAN  = TON_XTN / TON_EXR  - TON_MTN / TON_EXR  + TON_REMIT / TON_EXR  + TON_CANOTH

@IDENTITY TON_CANRATIO  = TON_CAN / TON_YEN$ * 100

TON_CANOTH  = TON_CANOTH(-1)  + ((TON_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TON_YEN$  / TON_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TON_REVG / TON_EXR  - TON_REVG(-1) / TON_EXR(-1)

+ 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * TON_EXR

TON_GINT  = TON_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (TON_LTI  - TON_LTI(-1))

TON_GDN  = TON_GDN(-1) * (TON_GDFXSH  * (TON_EXR  / TON_EXR(-1))  + (1  - TON_GDFXSH))  - TON_GLN

@IDENTITY TON_GDNRATIO  = TON_GDN / TON_YEN * 100

TON_GDFXSH  = ( TON_GDFXSH(-1) * (TON_EXR / TON_EXR(-1) )) / (TON_GDFXSH(-1) * (TON_EXR / TON_EXR(-1))  + 1 - TON_GDFXSH(-1) )

TON_TOURSH  = TON_TOURSH(-1)

TON_LOCK  = 0

TON_GCARBR  = TON_GCARBR(-1)

TON_GTRADER  = TON_GTRADER(-1)

TON_ITAXR  = TON_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_REV  = TON_TAX  + TON_CTAX  + TON_ITAX  + TON_GTRADE  + TON_REVG  + TON_GCARB  + TON_GCOM  + TON_GOTH

@IDENTITY TON_TAX  = TON_TAXR * (TON_LABSH * 0.5 * (TON_YER(-1)  + TON_GDI(-1)) * TON_YED(-1) * (TON_LNN / TON_LNN(-1)  + TON_TECHL - TON_TECHL(-1)) + TON_REMIT  + TON_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY TON_CTAX  = TON_CTAXR * TON_PROF

@IDENTITY TON_ITAX  = TON_ITAXR * (TON_PCR * TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY TON_GTRADE  = TON_GTRADER * TON_XTN

TON_REVG  = TON_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (TON_YER$ / TON_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - TON_YER$(-1) / TON_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * TON_EXR / TON_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_GCARB  = TON_GCARBR * TON_CO2 * TON_EXR / 1000

TON_GCOM  = TON_GCOM(-1) * ( TON_OILC / (TON_OILC + TON_GASC + TON_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + TON_GASC / (TON_OILC + TON_GASC + TON_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + TON_COALC / (TON_OILC + TON_GASC + TON_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

TON_GOTH  = TON_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_EXP  = TON_EXPE  + TON_EXPH  + TON_EXPSP  + TON_OGC  + TON_OGI  + TON_GIP

TON_EXPE  = TON_EXPE(-1) * (TON_YFT / TON_YFT(-1)) * (TON_YED / TON_YED(-1))

TON_EXPH = TON_EXPH(-1) * (TON_YFT / TON_YFT(-1)) * (TON_YED / TON_YED(-1))

TON_EXPSP  = TON_EXPSP(-1) * (TON_YFT / TON_YFT(-1)) * (TON_YED / TON_YED(-1)) * (TON_POPT - TON_LNN) / (TON_POPT(-1) - TON_LNN(-1))

DLOG(TON_OGI)  = DLOG(TON_YFT)  + DLOG(TON_YED)

TON_GCR  = TON_GCR(-1)  + ( TON_OGC / TON_YED - TON_OGC(-1) / TON_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (TON_EXPH ) / TON_YED  - (TON_EXPH(-1) ) / TON_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TON_EXPE ) / TON_YED  - (TON_EXPE(-1) ) / TON_YED(-1) )

TON_IGR  = TON_IGR(-1) + (TON_OGI / TON_YED - TON_OGI(-1) / TON_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (TON_EXPH ) / TON_YED  - (TON_EXPH(-1) ) / TON_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TON_EXPE ) / TON_YED  - (TON_EXPE(-1) ) / TON_YED(-1) )

TON_GIP  = ( TON_GIP(-1)  + ( TON_GDN(-1) - TON_GDN(-2) ) * TON_GINT(-1) / 100  + TON_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( TON_GINT(-1) / 100 - TON_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (TON_GDFXSH * (TON_EXR / TON_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TON_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY TON_GLN  = TON_REV  - TON_EXP

@IDENTITY TON_GLNRATIO  = TON_GLN / TON_YEN * 100

TON_GLNT  = TON_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

TON_TFP  = TON_LABSH * (TON_TECHL  - TON_TECHL(-1))

TON_LABSH  = TON_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY TON_LFN  = TON_LRX * TON_POPWA

TON_LRX  = TON_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(TON_YER(-1) / TON_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY TON_URX  = (1 - TON_LNN / TON_LFN) * 100

TON_URXF  = TON_URXF(-1) * TON_URX / TON_URX(-1) * TON_LNN / TON_LNNF / (TON_LNN(-1) / TON_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(TON_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TON_PCR  / TON_POPT)

TON_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(TON_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

TON_HEAD19  = TON_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TON_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI^2)  , TON_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TON_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TON_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

TON_HEAD55  = TON_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TON_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI^2)  , TON_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TON_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TON_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(TON_XTR)  = DLOG(TON_WDR)  + (1  - TON_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(TON_XTDNO$  / TON_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * TON_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(TON_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (TON_EXPH(-1) / TON_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (TON_EXPH(-1) / TON_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(TON_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(TON_PM25)

TON_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( TON_EXPSP / TON_YEN )

DLOG(TON_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - TON_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (TON_FINC - TON_FINC(-1))

DLOG(TON_PCR)  =  - 0.0535782005144335  +  - 0.130728582137515 * (LOG(TON_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TON_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (TON_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TON_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(TON_POPT)  +  - 0.209840750294087 * (DLOG(TON_HIC)  - TON_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * TON_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * TON_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TON_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TON_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TON_IPR)  =  - 0.142629534483112  - 0.1 * (LOG(TON_IPR(-1)  / TON_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * TON_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * TON_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(TON_PCR  + TON_GCR(-1) + TON_IGR(-1) + TON_XTN  / TON_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(TON_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (TON_USER - TON_USER(-1))  - (0 * TON_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TON_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TON_FUELSH - TON_TOURSH)) * TON_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * TON_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TON_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TON_FUELSH - TON_TOURSH)) * TON_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TON_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TON_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TON_MTR)  =  - 0.144893581299008  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(TON_MTR(-1))  - LOG(TON_PCR(-1) + TON_ITR(-1) + TON_GCR(-1) + TON_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(TON_YFT(-1) / TON_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(TON_CMUD(-1) * TON_EXR(-1)  / TON_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * TON_OMS * LOG(TON_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.173778000306297  * DLOG(TON_XTR)  + 0.638805517896683  * DLOG(TON_PCR)  + 0.160221448556993  * DLOG(TON_IPR)  + 0.0236201111320676  * DLOG(TON_GCR + TON_IGR)

TON_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * TON_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * TON_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * TON_OILC

TON_POIL  = TON_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( TON_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - TON_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

TON_PG  = TON_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( TON_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - TON_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

TON_PC  = TON_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( TON_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - TON_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(TON_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

TON_PE  = TON_PE(-1) * ( TON_OILC(-1) / (TON_OILC(-1) + TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) * TON_POIL / TON_POIL(-1)  + TON_GASC(-1) / (TON_OILC(-1) + TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) * TON_PG / TON_PG(-1)  + TON_COALC(-1) / (TON_OILC(-1) + TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) * TON_PC / TON_PC(-1)  + TON_RC(-1) / (TON_OILC(-1) + TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) * TON_PR / TON_PR(-1) )

D(TON_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(TON_PM25)  = 0.2 * (TON_COALC(-1) / TON_EC(-1) - TON_COALC(-2) / TON_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (TON_COALC(-2) / TON_EC(-2) - TON_COALC(-3) / TON_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (TON_OILC(-1) / TON_EC(-1) - TON_OILC(-2) / TON_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (TON_OILC(-2) / TON_EC(-2) - TON_OILC(-3) / TON_EC(-3))

DLOG(TON_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(TON_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(TON_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(TON_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TON_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TON_PE * TON_EXR / TON_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TON_PE(-1) * TON_EXR(-1) / TON_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TON_PE(-2) * TON_EXR(-2) / TON_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TON_PE(-3) * TON_EXR(-3) / TON_HIC(-3))  - (TON_EFF - TON_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(TON_COALC)  = DLOG(TON_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TON_COALC(-1) / TON_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TON_PE(-1) / TON_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_OILC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) / TON_EC(-1))

DLOG(TON_GASC)  = DLOG(TON_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TON_GASC(-1) / TON_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TON_PE(-1) / TON_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_OILC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) / TON_EC(-1))

DLOG(TON_RC)  = DLOG(TON_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TON_RC(-1) / TON_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0187271687625083 * LOG(TON_PE(-1) / TON_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_OILC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) / TON_EC(-1))

DLOG(TON_OILC)  = DLOG(TON_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TON_OILC(-1) / TON_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.0187271687625083 * LOG(TON_PE(-1) / TON_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TON_COALC(-1) + TON_GASC(-1) + TON_OILC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)) / TON_EC(-1))

DLOG(TON_EXR) = 0.227272156708121*LOG(1) + (1 - 0.227272156708121)*DLOG(AUS_EXR)
@INNOV TON_EXR  0.0355504013907372

DLOG(TUR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(TUR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TUR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (TUR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (TUR_YER / TUR_YFT  - TUR_YER(-1) / TUR_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + TUR_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + TUR_GCARB / TUR_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (TUR_PREM - TUR_PREM(-1)) / 100

TUR_YED  = TUR_YED(-1) * TUR_HIC / TUR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_INT  = TUR_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_LTI  = TUR_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (TUR_INT - TUR_INT(-1))  + (TUR_PREM  - TUR_PREM(-1)) / 100

TUR_PREM  = TUR_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (TUR_GDNRATIO(-1)  - TUR_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(TUR_LNN)  = DLOG(TUR_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(TUR_LNN(-1))  - LOG(TUR_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(TUR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TUR_LNNF)  = DLOG(TUR_LNN)

TUR_FUELSH  = TUR_FUELSH(-1)

TUR_TAXR  = TUR_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TUR_GLNT(-1)  - TUR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TUR_YEN(-1) / ( ( TUR_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (TUR_YER(-2)  + TUR_GDI(-2)) * TUR_YED(-2) * (TUR_LNN(-1) / TUR_LNN(-2)  + TUR_TECHL(-1) - TUR_TECHL(-2) ) ) + TUR_REMIT(-1)  + TUR_EXPSP(-1) ) * TUR_SOLV

TUR_CTAXR  = TUR_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TUR_GLNT(-1)  - TUR_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TUR_YEN(-1) / ( TUR_PROF(-1) ) * TUR_SOLV

(TUR_OGC)  = TUR_OGC(-1) * (TUR_YFT / TUR_YFT(-1) * TUR_YED / TUR_YED(-1))

TUR_USER  = (TUR_LTI  - TUR_INFT  + TUR_DEP * 100) / (1  - TUR_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (TUR_GCARB / TUR_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY TUR_XTN  = TUR_XTD$ * TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") * TUR_XTR

@IDENTITY TUR_YEN  = TUR_YER  * TUR_YED

@IDENTITY TUR_MTN  = TUR_MTD  * TUR_MTR

@IDENTITY TUR_XTN$  = TUR_XTN / TUR_EXR

@IDENTITY TUR_YEN$  = TUR_YEN / TUR_EXR

@IDENTITY TUR_MTN$  = TUR_MTN / TUR_EXR

@IDENTITY TUR_MTR$  = TUR_MTR$(-1) * TUR_MTR / TUR_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_XTR$  = TUR_XTR$(-1) * TUR_XTR / TUR_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_YER$  = TUR_YER$(-1) * TUR_YER / TUR_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_YFT$  = TUR_YFT$(-1) * TUR_YFT / TUR_YFT(-1)

TUR_POPT  = TUR_POPT(-1)  - TUR_LIVES

TUR_POPWA  = TUR_POPWA(-1) * TUR_POPT / TUR_POPT(-1)

TUR_SCR  = TUR_SCR(-1)  + ((TUR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TUR_YFT(-1) / TUR_YER(-1)  - TUR_YFT(-2) / TUR_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY TUR_ITR  = TUR_IGR  + TUR_IPR

@IDENTITY TUR_YER  = TUR_PCR  + TUR_GCR  + TUR_ITR  + TUR_SCR  + TUR_XTR  - TUR_MTR

@IDENTITY TUR_PROF  = (TUR_YEN - TUR_ITAX) * (1 - TUR_LABSH)

@IDENTITY TUR_GDI  = TUR_YER  - TUR_XTR  + TUR_MTR  + TUR_XTN  / ((TUR_YEN  - TUR_XTN  + TUR_MTN)  / (TUR_YER  - TUR_XTR  + TUR_MTR))  - TUR_MTN  / ((TUR_YEN  - TUR_XTN  + TUR_MTN)  / (TUR_YER  - TUR_XTR  + TUR_MTR))

@IDENTITY TUR_RPDI  = TUR_LABSH * 0.5 * (TUR_YER(-1)  + TUR_GDI(-1)) * TUR_YED(-1) / TUR_HIC(-1) * (TUR_LNN / TUR_LNN(-1)  + TUR_TECHL - TUR_TECHL(-1)) + TUR_REMIT / TUR_HIC  + TUR_EXPSP / TUR_HIC  - TUR_TAX / TUR_HIC

DLOG(TUR_YFT)  = (1 - TUR_ALPHA - TUR_LABSH) * DLOG(TUR_K(-1) / TUR_LFN(-1))  + (1 - TUR_ALPHA) * DLOG(TUR_LFN)  + TUR_LABSH * D(TUR_TECHL)  + TUR_ALPHA * (DLOG(TUR_EC)  + D(TUR_EFF) )  - ( TUR_CLIMLOSS / TUR_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (TUR_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY TUR_K  = TUR_K(-1) * (1 - TUR_DEP) + TUR_ITR

DLOG(TUR_MTD)  = (1  - TUR_OMS) * ( DLOG(TUR_CMUD)  + DLOG(TUR_EXR) )  + TUR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TUR_EXR) )

DLOG(TUR_XTD$)  = (1  - TUR_OXS) * DLOG(TUR_XTDNO$)  + TUR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

TUR_INFT  = 0.95 * TUR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

TUR_OXS  = TUR_OXS(-1)

TUR_OMS  = TUR_OMS(-1) * ((TUR_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * TUR_EXR(-1) / TUR_MTN(-1)) / (TUR_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * TUR_EXR(-2) / TUR_MTN(-2)))^0.25

TUR_CXS  = TUR_CXS(-1)

TUR_FINC  = TUR_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_CAN  = TUR_XTN / TUR_EXR  - TUR_MTN / TUR_EXR  + TUR_REMIT / TUR_EXR  + TUR_CANOTH

@IDENTITY TUR_CANRATIO  = TUR_CAN / TUR_YEN$ * 100

TUR_CANOTH  = TUR_CANOTH(-1)  + ((TUR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TUR_YEN$  / TUR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TUR_REVG / TUR_EXR  - TUR_REVG(-1) / TUR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(TUR_EFEX)  =  - LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004754748691 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001755362148 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004262130992 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01000451294 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002479558988 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.870271454E-07 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.398372651E-05 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.119082586E-05 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0560900498 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.640650234E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004230198322 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003819226676 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01939174229 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003985757683 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.03768986692 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.00889157878 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005488112334 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.524959224E-07 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008677609569 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.070899787E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001076521175 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004909309299 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000124465068 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.352671951E-08 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001155696436 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.570997179E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002359918175 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000612999067 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001473605208 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.67462452E-05 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000454663583 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01819772119 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06647634533 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.171171523E-06 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003582008179 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , 0.1139160878 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04030995475 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04979381047 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05135632694 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01891797937 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004415671877 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01568445929 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1845096049 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02380893647 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1375492509 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

TUR_REMIT  = TUR_REMIT(-1) / TUR_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005392101694 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.01372572687 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0004912207624 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02770491843 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005216239892 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.4815272555 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0.08350980319 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02633107707 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002930036465 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 3.21916519E-05 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003911350388 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0007266967347 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006549332042 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.02545018347 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003481467539 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 5.782574509E-05 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 4.241910607E-06 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.06587818407 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0002637927031 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002955074417 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 2.98070851E-07 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0001946402657 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003433776203 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.03516108018 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002221522052 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003713962803 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.1449833128 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.009293689144 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07013003942 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * TUR_EXR

TUR_GINT  = TUR_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 11 * (TUR_LTI  - TUR_LTI(-1))

TUR_GDN  = TUR_GDN(-1) * (TUR_GDFXSH  * (TUR_EXR  / TUR_EXR(-1))  + (1  - TUR_GDFXSH))  - TUR_GLN

@IDENTITY TUR_GDNRATIO  = TUR_GDN / TUR_YEN * 100

TUR_GDFXSH  = ( TUR_GDFXSH(-1) * (TUR_EXR / TUR_EXR(-1) )) / (TUR_GDFXSH(-1) * (TUR_EXR / TUR_EXR(-1))  + 1 - TUR_GDFXSH(-1) )

TUR_TOURSH  = TUR_TOURSH(-1)

TUR_LOCK  = 0

TUR_GCARBR  = TUR_GCARBR(-1)

TUR_GTRADER  = TUR_GTRADER(-1)

TUR_ITAXR  = TUR_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_REV  = TUR_TAX  + TUR_CTAX  + TUR_ITAX  + TUR_GTRADE  + TUR_REVG  + TUR_GCARB  + TUR_GCOM  + TUR_GOTH

@IDENTITY TUR_TAX  = TUR_TAXR * (TUR_LABSH * 0.5 * (TUR_YER(-1)  + TUR_GDI(-1)) * TUR_YED(-1) * (TUR_LNN / TUR_LNN(-1)  + TUR_TECHL - TUR_TECHL(-1)) + TUR_REMIT  + TUR_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY TUR_CTAX  = TUR_CTAXR * TUR_PROF

@IDENTITY TUR_ITAX  = TUR_ITAXR * (TUR_PCR * TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY TUR_GTRADE  = TUR_GTRADER * TUR_XTN

TUR_REVG  = TUR_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (TUR_YER$ / TUR_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - TUR_YER$(-1) / TUR_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * TUR_EXR / TUR_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_GCARB  = TUR_GCARBR * TUR_CO2 * TUR_EXR / 1000

TUR_GCOM  = TUR_GCOM(-1) * ( TUR_OILC / (TUR_OILC + TUR_GASC + TUR_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + TUR_GASC / (TUR_OILC + TUR_GASC + TUR_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + TUR_COALC / (TUR_OILC + TUR_GASC + TUR_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

TUR_GOTH  = TUR_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_EXP  = TUR_EXPE  + TUR_EXPH  + TUR_EXPSP  + TUR_OGC  + TUR_OGI  + TUR_GIP

TUR_EXPE  = TUR_EXPE(-1) * (TUR_YFT / TUR_YFT(-1)) * (TUR_YED / TUR_YED(-1))

TUR_EXPH = TUR_EXPH(-1) * (TUR_YFT / TUR_YFT(-1)) * (TUR_YED / TUR_YED(-1))

TUR_EXPSP  = TUR_EXPSP(-1) * (TUR_YFT / TUR_YFT(-1)) * (TUR_YED / TUR_YED(-1)) * (TUR_POPT - TUR_LNN) / (TUR_POPT(-1) - TUR_LNN(-1))

DLOG(TUR_OGI)  = DLOG(TUR_YFT)  + DLOG(TUR_YED)

TUR_GCR  = TUR_GCR(-1)  + ( TUR_OGC / TUR_YED - TUR_OGC(-1) / TUR_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (TUR_EXPH ) / TUR_YED  - (TUR_EXPH(-1) ) / TUR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TUR_EXPE ) / TUR_YED  - (TUR_EXPE(-1) ) / TUR_YED(-1) )

TUR_IGR  = TUR_IGR(-1) + (TUR_OGI / TUR_YED - TUR_OGI(-1) / TUR_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (TUR_EXPH ) / TUR_YED  - (TUR_EXPH(-1) ) / TUR_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TUR_EXPE ) / TUR_YED  - (TUR_EXPE(-1) ) / TUR_YED(-1) )

TUR_GIP  = ( TUR_GIP(-1)  + ( TUR_GDN(-1) - TUR_GDN(-2) ) * TUR_GINT(-1) / 100  + TUR_GDN(-12) / 11 * ( TUR_GINT(-1) / 100 - TUR_GINT(-12) / 100 ) ) * (TUR_GDFXSH * (TUR_EXR / TUR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TUR_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY TUR_GLN  = TUR_REV  - TUR_EXP

@IDENTITY TUR_GLNRATIO  = TUR_GLN / TUR_YEN * 100

TUR_GLNT  = TUR_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

TUR_TFP  = TUR_LABSH * (TUR_TECHL  - TUR_TECHL(-1))

TUR_LABSH  = TUR_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY TUR_LFN  = TUR_LRX * TUR_POPWA

TUR_LRX  = TUR_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(TUR_YER(-1) / TUR_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY TUR_URX  = (1 - TUR_LNN / TUR_LFN) * 100

TUR_URXF  = TUR_URXF(-1) * TUR_URX / TUR_URX(-1) * TUR_LNN / TUR_LNNF / (TUR_LNN(-1) / TUR_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(TUR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TUR_PCR  / TUR_POPT)

TUR_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(TUR_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

TUR_HEAD19  = TUR_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TUR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI^2)  , TUR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TUR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TUR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

TUR_HEAD55  = TUR_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TUR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI^2)  , TUR_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TUR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TUR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(TUR_XTR)  = DLOG(TUR_WDR)  + (1  - TUR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(TUR_XTDNO$  / TUR_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * TUR_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(TUR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (TUR_EXPH(-1) / TUR_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (TUR_EXPH(-1) / TUR_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(TUR_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(TUR_PM25)

TUR_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( TUR_EXPSP / TUR_YEN )

DLOG(TUR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - TUR_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (TUR_FINC - TUR_FINC(-1))

DLOG(TUR_PCR)  =  - 0.110794802465131  +  - 0.176400125629927 * (LOG(TUR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TUR_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (TUR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TUR_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(TUR_POPT)  +  - 0.425755608082308 * (DLOG(TUR_HIC)  - TUR_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * TUR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * TUR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TUR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TUR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TUR_IPR)  =  - 0.140611987896849  - 0.1 * (LOG(TUR_IPR(-1)  / TUR_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * TUR_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * TUR_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(TUR_PCR  + TUR_GCR(-1) + TUR_IGR(-1) + TUR_XTN  / TUR_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(TUR_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (TUR_USER - TUR_USER(-1))  - (0 * TUR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TUR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TUR_FUELSH - TUR_TOURSH)) * TUR_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * TUR_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TUR_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TUR_FUELSH - TUR_TOURSH)) * TUR_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TUR_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TUR_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TUR_MTR)  =  - 0.264298237581376  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(TUR_MTR(-1))  - LOG(TUR_PCR(-1) + TUR_ITR(-1) + TUR_GCR(-1) + TUR_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(TUR_YFT(-1) / TUR_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(TUR_CMUD(-1) * TUR_EXR(-1)  / TUR_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * TUR_OMS * LOG(TUR_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.0899993305205861  * DLOG(TUR_XTR)  + 0.924597899174094  * DLOG(TUR_PCR)  + 0.458460458835686  * DLOG(TUR_IPR)  + 0.268636248847815  * DLOG(TUR_GCR + TUR_IGR)

TUR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * TUR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * TUR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * TUR_OILC

TUR_POIL  = TUR_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( TUR_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - TUR_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

TUR_PG  = TUR_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( TUR_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - TUR_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

TUR_PC  = TUR_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( TUR_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - TUR_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(TUR_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

TUR_PE  = TUR_PE(-1) * ( TUR_OILC(-1) / (TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) * TUR_POIL / TUR_POIL(-1)  + TUR_GASC(-1) / (TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) * TUR_PG / TUR_PG(-1)  + TUR_COALC(-1) / (TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) * TUR_PC / TUR_PC(-1)  + TUR_RC(-1) / (TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) * TUR_PR / TUR_PR(-1) )

D(TUR_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(TUR_PM25)  = 0.2 * (TUR_COALC(-1) / TUR_EC(-1) - TUR_COALC(-2) / TUR_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (TUR_COALC(-2) / TUR_EC(-2) - TUR_COALC(-3) / TUR_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (TUR_OILC(-1) / TUR_EC(-1) - TUR_OILC(-2) / TUR_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (TUR_OILC(-2) / TUR_EC(-2) - TUR_OILC(-3) / TUR_EC(-3))

DLOG(TUR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(TUR_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(TUR_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(TUR_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TUR_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TUR_PE * TUR_EXR / TUR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TUR_PE(-1) * TUR_EXR(-1) / TUR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TUR_PE(-2) * TUR_EXR(-2) / TUR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TUR_PE(-3) * TUR_EXR(-3) / TUR_HIC(-3))  - (TUR_EFF - TUR_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(TUR_COALC)  = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TUR_COALC(-1) / TUR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.185737472135134 * LOG(TUR_PE(-1) / TUR_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) / TUR_EC(-1))

DLOG(TUR_GASC)  = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TUR_GASC(-1) / TUR_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.239732293907848 * LOG(TUR_PE(-1) / TUR_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) / TUR_EC(-1))

DLOG(TUR_RC)  = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TUR_RC(-1) / TUR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.185737472135134 * LOG(TUR_PE(-1) / TUR_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) / TUR_EC(-1))

DLOG(TUR_OILC)  = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TUR_OILC(-1) / TUR_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.185737472135134 * LOG(TUR_PE(-1) / TUR_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TUR_COALC(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1) + TUR_OILC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)) / TUR_EC(-1))

TUR_EXR  = TUR_EXR(-1) * ( ( (TUR_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (TUR_INT  - USA_INT)  - (TUR_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(TKM_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(TKM_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TKM_MTD)  + 0.4 * (TKM_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (TKM_YER / TKM_YFT  - TKM_YER(-1) / TKM_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + TKM_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + TKM_GCARB / TKM_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (TKM_PREM - TKM_PREM(-1)) / 100

TKM_YED  = TKM_YED(-1) * TKM_HIC / TKM_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_INT  = TKM_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_LTI  = TKM_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (TKM_INT - TKM_INT(-1))  + (TKM_PREM  - TKM_PREM(-1)) / 100

TKM_PREM  = TKM_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (TKM_GDNRATIO(-1)  - TKM_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(TKM_LNN)  = DLOG(TKM_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(TKM_LNN(-1))  - LOG(TKM_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(TKM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TKM_LNNF)  = DLOG(TKM_LNN)

TKM_FUELSH  = TKM_FUELSH(-1)

TKM_TAXR  = TKM_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TKM_GLNT(-1)  - TKM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TKM_YEN(-1) / ( ( TKM_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (TKM_YER(-2)  + TKM_GDI(-2)) * TKM_YED(-2) * (TKM_LNN(-1) / TKM_LNN(-2)  + TKM_TECHL(-1) - TKM_TECHL(-2) ) ) + TKM_REMIT(-1)  + TKM_EXPSP(-1) ) * TKM_SOLV

TKM_CTAXR  = TKM_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( TKM_GLNT(-1)  - TKM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * TKM_YEN(-1) / ( TKM_PROF(-1) ) * TKM_SOLV

(TKM_OGC)  = TKM_OGC(-1) * (TKM_YFT / TKM_YFT(-1) * TKM_YED / TKM_YED(-1))

TKM_USER  = (TKM_LTI  - TKM_INFT  + TKM_DEP * 100) / (1  - TKM_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (TKM_GCARB / TKM_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY TKM_XTN  = TKM_XTD$ * TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") * TKM_XTR

@IDENTITY TKM_YEN  = TKM_YER  * TKM_YED

@IDENTITY TKM_MTN  = TKM_MTD  * TKM_MTR

@IDENTITY TKM_XTN$  = TKM_XTN / TKM_EXR

@IDENTITY TKM_YEN$  = TKM_YEN / TKM_EXR

@IDENTITY TKM_MTN$  = TKM_MTN / TKM_EXR

@IDENTITY TKM_MTR$  = TKM_MTR$(-1) * TKM_MTR / TKM_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_XTR$  = TKM_XTR$(-1) * TKM_XTR / TKM_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_YER$  = TKM_YER$(-1) * TKM_YER / TKM_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_YFT$  = TKM_YFT$(-1) * TKM_YFT / TKM_YFT(-1)

TKM_POPT  = TKM_POPT(-1)  - TKM_LIVES

TKM_POPWA  = TKM_POPWA(-1) * TKM_POPT / TKM_POPT(-1)

TKM_SCR  = TKM_SCR(-1)  + ((TKM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TKM_YFT(-1) / TKM_YER(-1)  - TKM_YFT(-2) / TKM_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY TKM_ITR  = TKM_IGR  + TKM_IPR

@IDENTITY TKM_YER  = TKM_PCR  + TKM_GCR  + TKM_ITR  + TKM_SCR  + TKM_XTR  - TKM_MTR

@IDENTITY TKM_PROF  = (TKM_YEN - TKM_ITAX) * (1 - TKM_LABSH)

@IDENTITY TKM_GDI  = TKM_YER  - TKM_XTR  + TKM_MTR  + TKM_XTN  / ((TKM_YEN  - TKM_XTN  + TKM_MTN)  / (TKM_YER  - TKM_XTR  + TKM_MTR))  - TKM_MTN  / ((TKM_YEN  - TKM_XTN  + TKM_MTN)  / (TKM_YER  - TKM_XTR  + TKM_MTR))

@IDENTITY TKM_RPDI  = TKM_LABSH * 0.5 * (TKM_YER(-1)  + TKM_GDI(-1)) * TKM_YED(-1) / TKM_HIC(-1) * (TKM_LNN / TKM_LNN(-1)  + TKM_TECHL - TKM_TECHL(-1)) + TKM_REMIT / TKM_HIC  + TKM_EXPSP / TKM_HIC  - TKM_TAX / TKM_HIC

DLOG(TKM_YFT)  = (1 - TKM_ALPHA - TKM_LABSH) * DLOG(TKM_K(-1) / TKM_LFN(-1))  + (1 - TKM_ALPHA) * DLOG(TKM_LFN)  + TKM_LABSH * D(TKM_TECHL)  + TKM_ALPHA * (DLOG(TKM_EC)  + D(TKM_EFF) )  - ( TKM_CLIMLOSS / TKM_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (TKM_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY TKM_K  = TKM_K(-1) * (1 - TKM_DEP) + TKM_ITR

DLOG(TKM_MTD)  = (1  - TKM_OMS) * ( DLOG(TKM_CMUD)  + DLOG(TKM_EXR) )  + TKM_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TKM_EXR) )

DLOG(TKM_XTD$)  = (1  - TKM_OXS) * DLOG(TKM_XTDNO$)  + TKM_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

TKM_INFT  = 0.95 * TKM_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

TKM_OXS  = TKM_OXS(-1)

TKM_OMS  = TKM_OMS(-1) * ((TKM_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * TKM_EXR(-1) / TKM_MTN(-1)) / (TKM_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * TKM_EXR(-2) / TKM_MTN(-2)))^0.25

TKM_CXS  = TKM_CXS(-1)

TKM_FINC  = TKM_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_CAN  = TKM_XTN / TKM_EXR  - TKM_MTN / TKM_EXR  + TKM_REMIT / TKM_EXR  + TKM_CANOTH

@IDENTITY TKM_CANRATIO  = TKM_CAN / TKM_YEN$ * 100

TKM_CANOTH  = TKM_CANOTH(-1)  + ((TKM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TKM_YEN$  / TKM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TKM_REVG / TKM_EXR  - TKM_REVG(-1) / TKM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(TKM_EFEX)  =  - LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02492315775 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009489057574 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.000137137105 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009131024926 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008919220365 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.542502918E-11 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.691865907E-09 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.85054062E-06 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.4709679076 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.43899494E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006712777118 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0003219505611 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.005168276701 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005624883487 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.06097132172 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.008438776456 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0116167074 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.555843307E-12 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004018440379 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.093038013E-11 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.555344759E-07 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007870499976 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.968920094E-11 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.664839286E-06 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.935240637E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.45285197E-08 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.9649077E-06 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001138438106 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015"))  + 9.712354703E-08 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.096370086E-07 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01215796251 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.04637426217 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.155005E-11 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008106697543 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.367694E-09 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.550085031E-05 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004695246272 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0005653373067 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.327613163E-11 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.1093716778 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015"))  + 1.284344977E-11 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 6.83019212E-12 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0008312881511 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.009695344142 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02065702483 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.006767765583 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004495139054 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.02809596365 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.003174364523 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0009739193121 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001039799399 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001332742746 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001569492292 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.058581717 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.001368098469 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.07881180196 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015"))

@IDENTITY LOG(TKM_REFEX )  =  - LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02492315775 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015") / (AFG_HIC / @ELEM(AFG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0009489057574 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015") / (ARM_HIC / @ELEM(ARM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.000137137105 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015") / (AUS_HIC / @ELEM(AUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009131024926 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015") / (AZE_HIC / @ELEM(AZE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008919220365 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015") / (BGD_HIC / @ELEM(BGD_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.542502918E-11 * LOG(BTN_EXR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015") / (BTN_HIC / @ELEM(BTN_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.691865907E-09 * LOG(BRN_EXR / @ELEM(BRN_EXR , "2015") / (BRN_HIC / @ELEM(BRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.85054062E-06 * LOG(KHM_EXR / @ELEM(KHM_EXR , "2015") / (KHM_HIC / @ELEM(KHM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.4709679076 * LOG(CHN_EXR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015") / (CHN_HIC / @ELEM(CHN_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.43899494E-06 * LOG(FJI_EXR / @ELEM(FJI_EXR , "2015") / (FJI_HIC / @ELEM(FJI_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006712777118 * LOG(GEO_EXR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015") / (GEO_HIC / @ELEM(GEO_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0003219505611 * LOG(HKG_EXR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015") / (HKG_HIC / @ELEM(HKG_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005168276701 * LOG(IND_EXR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015") / (IND_HIC / @ELEM(IND_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005624883487 * LOG(IDN_EXR / @ELEM(IDN_EXR , "2015") / (IDN_HIC / @ELEM(IDN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06097132172 * LOG(IRN_EXR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015") / (IRN_HIC / @ELEM(IRN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008438776456 * LOG(JPN_EXR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015") / (JPN_HIC / @ELEM(JPN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0116167074 * LOG(KAZ_EXR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015") / (KAZ_HIC / @ELEM(KAZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.555843307E-12 * LOG(KIR_EXR / @ELEM(KIR_EXR , "2015") / (KIR_HIC / @ELEM(KIR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0004018440379 * LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015") / (KGZ_HIC / @ELEM(KGZ_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.093038013E-11 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015") / (LAO_HIC / @ELEM(LAO_HIC , "2015")))  + 3.555344759E-07 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015") / (MAC_HIC / @ELEM(MAC_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007870499976 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @ELEM(MYS_EXR , "2015") / (MYS_HIC / @ELEM(MYS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.968920094E-11 * LOG(MDV_EXR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015") / (MDV_HIC / @ELEM(MDV_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(FSM_EXR / @ELEM(FSM_EXR , "2015") / (FSM_HIC / @ELEM(FSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.664839286E-06 * LOG(MNG_EXR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015") / (MNG_HIC / @ELEM(MNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 4.935240637E-05 * LOG(MMR_EXR / @ELEM(MMR_EXR , "2015") / (MMR_HIC / @ELEM(MMR_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.45285197E-08 * LOG(NPL_EXR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015") / (NPL_HIC / @ELEM(NPL_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.9649077E-06 * LOG(NZL_EXR / @ELEM(NZL_EXR , "2015") / (NZL_HIC / @ELEM(NZL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001138438106 * LOG(PAK_EXR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015") / (PAK_HIC / @ELEM(PAK_HIC , "2015")))  + 9.712354703E-08 * LOG(PNG_EXR / @ELEM(PNG_EXR , "2015") / (PNG_HIC / @ELEM(PNG_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.096370086E-07 * LOG(PHL_EXR / @ELEM(PHL_EXR , "2015") / (PHL_HIC / @ELEM(PHL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01215796251 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04637426217 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.155005E-11 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008106697543 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 5.367694E-09 * LOG(SLB_EXR / @ELEM(SLB_EXR , "2015") / (SLB_HIC / @ELEM(SLB_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.550085031E-05 * LOG(LKA_EXR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015") / (LKA_HIC / @ELEM(LKA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004695246272 * LOG(TJK_EXR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015") / (TJK_HIC / @ELEM(TJK_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0005653373067 * LOG(THA_EXR / @ELEM(THA_EXR , "2015") / (THA_HIC / @ELEM(THA_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.327613163E-11 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1093716778 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.284344977E-11 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 6.83019212E-12 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0008312881511 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.009695344142 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02065702483 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.006767765583 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004495139054 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02809596365 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003174364523 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0009739193121 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001039799399 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001332742746 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0001569492292 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.058581717 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001368098469 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07881180196 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

TKM_REMIT  = TKM_REMIT(-1) / TKM_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 1 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * TKM_EXR

TKM_GINT  = TKM_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (TKM_LTI  - TKM_LTI(-1))

TKM_GDN  = TKM_GDN(-1) * (TKM_GDFXSH  * (TKM_EXR  / TKM_EXR(-1))  + (1  - TKM_GDFXSH))  - TKM_GLN

@IDENTITY TKM_GDNRATIO  = TKM_GDN / TKM_YEN * 100

TKM_GDFXSH  = ( TKM_GDFXSH(-1) * (TKM_EXR / TKM_EXR(-1) )) / (TKM_GDFXSH(-1) * (TKM_EXR / TKM_EXR(-1))  + 1 - TKM_GDFXSH(-1) )

TKM_TOURSH  = TKM_TOURSH(-1)

TKM_LOCK  = 0

TKM_GCARBR  = TKM_GCARBR(-1)

TKM_GTRADER  = TKM_GTRADER(-1)

TKM_ITAXR  = TKM_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_REV  = TKM_TAX  + TKM_CTAX  + TKM_ITAX  + TKM_GTRADE  + TKM_REVG  + TKM_GCARB  + TKM_GCOM  + TKM_GOTH

@IDENTITY TKM_TAX  = TKM_TAXR * (TKM_LABSH * 0.5 * (TKM_YER(-1)  + TKM_GDI(-1)) * TKM_YED(-1) * (TKM_LNN / TKM_LNN(-1)  + TKM_TECHL - TKM_TECHL(-1)) + TKM_REMIT  + TKM_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY TKM_CTAX  = TKM_CTAXR * TKM_PROF

@IDENTITY TKM_ITAX  = TKM_ITAXR * (TKM_PCR * TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY TKM_GTRADE  = TKM_GTRADER * TKM_XTN

TKM_REVG  = TKM_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (TKM_YER$ / TKM_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - TKM_YER$(-1) / TKM_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * TKM_EXR / TKM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_GCARB  = TKM_GCARBR * TKM_CO2 * TKM_EXR / 1000

TKM_GCOM  = TKM_GCOM(-1) * ( TKM_OILC / (TKM_OILC + TKM_GASC + TKM_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + TKM_GASC / (TKM_OILC + TKM_GASC + TKM_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + TKM_COALC / (TKM_OILC + TKM_GASC + TKM_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

TKM_GOTH  = TKM_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_EXP  = TKM_EXPE  + TKM_EXPH  + TKM_EXPSP  + TKM_OGC  + TKM_OGI  + TKM_GIP

TKM_EXPE  = TKM_EXPE(-1) * (TKM_YFT / TKM_YFT(-1)) * (TKM_YED / TKM_YED(-1))

TKM_EXPH = TKM_EXPH(-1) * (TKM_YFT / TKM_YFT(-1)) * (TKM_YED / TKM_YED(-1))

TKM_EXPSP  = TKM_EXPSP(-1) * (TKM_YFT / TKM_YFT(-1)) * (TKM_YED / TKM_YED(-1)) * (TKM_POPT - TKM_LNN) / (TKM_POPT(-1) - TKM_LNN(-1))

DLOG(TKM_OGI)  = DLOG(TKM_YFT)  + DLOG(TKM_YED)

TKM_GCR  = TKM_GCR(-1)  + ( TKM_OGC / TKM_YED - TKM_OGC(-1) / TKM_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (TKM_EXPH ) / TKM_YED  - (TKM_EXPH(-1) ) / TKM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TKM_EXPE ) / TKM_YED  - (TKM_EXPE(-1) ) / TKM_YED(-1) )

TKM_IGR  = TKM_IGR(-1) + (TKM_OGI / TKM_YED - TKM_OGI(-1) / TKM_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (TKM_EXPH ) / TKM_YED  - (TKM_EXPH(-1) ) / TKM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (TKM_EXPE ) / TKM_YED  - (TKM_EXPE(-1) ) / TKM_YED(-1) )

TKM_GIP  = ( TKM_GIP(-1)  + ( TKM_GDN(-1) - TKM_GDN(-2) ) * TKM_GINT(-1) / 100  + TKM_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( TKM_GINT(-1) / 100 - TKM_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (TKM_GDFXSH * (TKM_EXR / TKM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TKM_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY TKM_GLN  = TKM_REV  - TKM_EXP

@IDENTITY TKM_GLNRATIO  = TKM_GLN / TKM_YEN * 100

TKM_GLNT  = TKM_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

TKM_TFP  = TKM_LABSH * (TKM_TECHL  - TKM_TECHL(-1))

TKM_LABSH  = TKM_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY TKM_LFN  = TKM_LRX * TKM_POPWA

TKM_LRX  = TKM_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(TKM_YER(-1) / TKM_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY TKM_URX  = (1 - TKM_LNN / TKM_LFN) * 100

TKM_URXF  = TKM_URXF(-1) * TKM_URX / TKM_URX(-1) * TKM_LNN / TKM_LNNF / (TKM_LNN(-1) / TKM_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(TKM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TKM_PCR  / TKM_POPT)

TKM_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(TKM_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

TKM_HEAD19  = TKM_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TKM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI^2)  , TKM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TKM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TKM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

TKM_HEAD55  = TKM_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TKM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI^2)  , TKM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TKM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TKM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(TKM_XTR)  = DLOG(TKM_WDR)  + (1  - TKM_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(TKM_XTDNO$  / TKM_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * TKM_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(TKM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (TKM_EXPH(-1) / TKM_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (TKM_EXPH(-1) / TKM_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(TKM_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(TKM_PM25)

TKM_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( TKM_EXPSP / TKM_YEN )

DLOG(TKM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - TKM_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (TKM_FINC - TKM_FINC(-1))

DLOG(TKM_PCR)  =  - 0.413466562590975  +  - 0.268851180793517 * (LOG(TKM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TKM_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (TKM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TKM_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(TKM_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(TKM_HIC)  - TKM_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * TKM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * TKM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TKM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TKM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TKM_IPR)  =  - 0.0377394801280916  - 0.1 * (LOG(TKM_IPR(-1)  / TKM_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * TKM_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * TKM_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(TKM_PCR  + TKM_GCR(-1) + TKM_IGR(-1) + TKM_XTN  / TKM_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(TKM_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (TKM_USER - TKM_USER(-1))  - (0 * TKM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TKM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TKM_FUELSH - TKM_TOURSH)) * TKM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * TKM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * TKM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - TKM_FUELSH - TKM_TOURSH)) * TKM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(TKM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(TKM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(TKM_MTR)  =  - 0.140530762048359  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(TKM_MTR(-1))  - LOG(TKM_PCR(-1) + TKM_ITR(-1) + TKM_GCR(-1) + TKM_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(TKM_YFT(-1) / TKM_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(TKM_CMUD(-1) * TKM_EXR(-1)  / TKM_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * TKM_OMS * LOG(TKM_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.706429007354586  * DLOG(TKM_XTR)  + 0.0999388339096412  * DLOG(TKM_PCR)  + 0.0414712159398822  * DLOG(TKM_IPR)  + 0.00498162023102224  * DLOG(TKM_GCR + TKM_IGR)

TKM_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * TKM_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * TKM_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * TKM_OILC

TKM_POIL  = TKM_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( TKM_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - TKM_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

TKM_PG  = TKM_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( TKM_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - TKM_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

TKM_PC  = TKM_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( TKM_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - TKM_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(TKM_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

TKM_PE  = TKM_PE(-1) * ( TKM_OILC(-1) / (TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) * TKM_POIL / TKM_POIL(-1)  + TKM_GASC(-1) / (TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) * TKM_PG / TKM_PG(-1)  + TKM_COALC(-1) / (TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) * TKM_PC / TKM_PC(-1)  + TKM_RC(-1) / (TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) * TKM_PR / TKM_PR(-1) )

D(TKM_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(TKM_PM25)  = 0.2 * (TKM_COALC(-1) / TKM_EC(-1) - TKM_COALC(-2) / TKM_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (TKM_COALC(-2) / TKM_EC(-2) - TKM_COALC(-3) / TKM_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (TKM_OILC(-1) / TKM_EC(-1) - TKM_OILC(-2) / TKM_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (TKM_OILC(-2) / TKM_EC(-2) - TKM_OILC(-3) / TKM_EC(-3))

DLOG(TKM_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(TKM_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(TKM_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(TKM_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TKM_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TKM_PE * TKM_EXR / TKM_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TKM_PE(-1) * TKM_EXR(-1) / TKM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TKM_PE(-2) * TKM_EXR(-2) / TKM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(TKM_PE(-3) * TKM_EXR(-3) / TKM_HIC(-3))  - (TKM_EFF - TKM_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(TKM_COALC)  = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TKM_COALC(-1) / TKM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TKM_PE(-1) / TKM_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) / TKM_EC(-1))

DLOG(TKM_GASC)  = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(TKM_GASC(-1) / TKM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.782385598053642 * LOG(TKM_PE(-1) / TKM_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) / TKM_EC(-1))

DLOG(TKM_RC)  = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TKM_RC(-1) / TKM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TKM_PE(-1) / TKM_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) / TKM_EC(-1))

DLOG(TKM_OILC)  = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( TKM_OILC(-1) / TKM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(TKM_PE(-1) / TKM_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((TKM_COALC(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1) + TKM_OILC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)) / TKM_EC(-1))

@IDENTITY TKM_EXR  = TKM_EXR(-1)

DLOG(UZB_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(UZB_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(UZB_MTD)  + 0.4 * (UZB_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (UZB_YER / UZB_YFT  - UZB_YER(-1) / UZB_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + UZB_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + UZB_GCARB / UZB_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (UZB_PREM - UZB_PREM(-1)) / 100

UZB_YED  = UZB_YED(-1) * UZB_HIC / UZB_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_INT  = UZB_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_LTI  = UZB_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (UZB_INT - UZB_INT(-1))  + (UZB_PREM  - UZB_PREM(-1)) / 100

UZB_PREM  = UZB_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (UZB_GDNRATIO(-1)  - UZB_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(UZB_LNN)  = DLOG(UZB_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(UZB_LNN(-1))  - LOG(UZB_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(UZB_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(UZB_LNNF)  = DLOG(UZB_LNN)

UZB_FUELSH  = UZB_FUELSH(-1)

UZB_TAXR  = UZB_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( UZB_GLNT(-1)  - UZB_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * UZB_YEN(-1) / ( ( UZB_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (UZB_YER(-2)  + UZB_GDI(-2)) * UZB_YED(-2) * (UZB_LNN(-1) / UZB_LNN(-2)  + UZB_TECHL(-1) - UZB_TECHL(-2) ) ) + UZB_REMIT(-1)  + UZB_EXPSP(-1) ) * UZB_SOLV

UZB_CTAXR  = UZB_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( UZB_GLNT(-1)  - UZB_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * UZB_YEN(-1) / ( UZB_PROF(-1) ) * UZB_SOLV

(UZB_OGC)  = UZB_OGC(-1) * (UZB_YFT / UZB_YFT(-1) * UZB_YED / UZB_YED(-1))

UZB_USER  = (UZB_LTI  - UZB_INFT  + UZB_DEP * 100) / (1  - UZB_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (UZB_GCARB / UZB_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY UZB_XTN  = UZB_XTD$ * UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") * UZB_XTR

@IDENTITY UZB_YEN  = UZB_YER  * UZB_YED

@IDENTITY UZB_MTN  = UZB_MTD  * UZB_MTR

@IDENTITY UZB_XTN$  = UZB_XTN / UZB_EXR

@IDENTITY UZB_YEN$  = UZB_YEN / UZB_EXR

@IDENTITY UZB_MTN$  = UZB_MTN / UZB_EXR

@IDENTITY UZB_MTR$  = UZB_MTR$(-1) * UZB_MTR / UZB_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_XTR$  = UZB_XTR$(-1) * UZB_XTR / UZB_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_YER$  = UZB_YER$(-1) * UZB_YER / UZB_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_YFT$  = UZB_YFT$(-1) * UZB_YFT / UZB_YFT(-1)

UZB_POPT  = UZB_POPT(-1)  - UZB_LIVES

UZB_POPWA  = UZB_POPWA(-1) * UZB_POPT / UZB_POPT(-1)

UZB_SCR  = UZB_SCR(-1)  + ((UZB_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (UZB_YFT(-1) / UZB_YER(-1)  - UZB_YFT(-2) / UZB_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY UZB_ITR  = UZB_IGR  + UZB_IPR

@IDENTITY UZB_YER  = UZB_PCR  + UZB_GCR  + UZB_ITR  + UZB_SCR  + UZB_XTR  - UZB_MTR

@IDENTITY UZB_PROF  = (UZB_YEN - UZB_ITAX) * (1 - UZB_LABSH)

@IDENTITY UZB_GDI  = UZB_YER  - UZB_XTR  + UZB_MTR  + UZB_XTN  / ((UZB_YEN  - UZB_XTN  + UZB_MTN)  / (UZB_YER  - UZB_XTR  + UZB_MTR))  - UZB_MTN  / ((UZB_YEN  - UZB_XTN  + UZB_MTN)  / (UZB_YER  - UZB_XTR  + UZB_MTR))

@IDENTITY UZB_RPDI  = UZB_LABSH * 0.5 * (UZB_YER(-1)  + UZB_GDI(-1)) * UZB_YED(-1) / UZB_HIC(-1) * (UZB_LNN / UZB_LNN(-1)  + UZB_TECHL - UZB_TECHL(-1)) + UZB_REMIT / UZB_HIC  + UZB_EXPSP / UZB_HIC  - UZB_TAX / UZB_HIC

DLOG(UZB_YFT)  = (1 - UZB_ALPHA - UZB_LABSH) * DLOG(UZB_K(-1) / UZB_LFN(-1))  + (1 - UZB_ALPHA) * DLOG(UZB_LFN)  + UZB_LABSH * D(UZB_TECHL)  + UZB_ALPHA * (DLOG(UZB_EC)  + D(UZB_EFF) )  - ( UZB_CLIMLOSS / UZB_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (UZB_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY UZB_K  = UZB_K(-1) * (1 - UZB_DEP) + UZB_ITR

DLOG(UZB_MTD)  = (1  - UZB_OMS) * ( DLOG(UZB_CMUD)  + DLOG(UZB_EXR) )  + UZB_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(UZB_EXR) )

DLOG(UZB_XTD$)  = (1  - UZB_OXS) * DLOG(UZB_XTDNO$)  + UZB_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

UZB_INFT  = 0.95 * UZB_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

UZB_OXS  = UZB_OXS(-1)

UZB_OMS  = UZB_OMS(-1) * ((UZB_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * UZB_EXR(-1) / UZB_MTN(-1)) / (UZB_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * UZB_EXR(-2) / UZB_MTN(-2)))^0.25

UZB_CXS  = UZB_CXS(-1)

UZB_FINC  = UZB_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_CAN  = UZB_XTN / UZB_EXR  - UZB_MTN / UZB_EXR  + UZB_REMIT / UZB_EXR  + UZB_CANOTH

@IDENTITY UZB_CANRATIO  = UZB_CAN / UZB_YEN$ * 100

UZB_CANOTH  = UZB_CANOTH(-1)  + ((UZB_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (UZB_YEN$  / UZB_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + UZB_REVG / UZB_EXR  - UZB_REVG(-1) / UZB_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY LOG(UZB_EFEX)  =  - LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.01894476123 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002373745488 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  +
