LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07064614069 * LOG(TUR_EXR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015") / (TUR_HIC / @ELEM(TUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 2.17686926E-11 * LOG(TKM_EXR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015") / (TKM_HIC / @ELEM(TKM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 8.45913668E-12 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.001554068228 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01168037085 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0226207252 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01341137989 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002842312608 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008572697123 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.003613928347 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0007797068689 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1561331756 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0004227933867 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0004454230383 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05284122168 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002344343487 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.05534574375 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

UZB_REMIT  = UZB_REMIT(-1) / UZB_EXR(-1) * (  + 0 * AFG_YEN$ / AFG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ARM_YEN$ / ARM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AZE_YEN$ / AZE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BGD_YEN$ / BGD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BRN_YEN$ / BRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * BTN_YEN$ / BTN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FJI_YEN$ / FJI_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * FSM_YEN$ / FSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * GEO_YEN$ / GEO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * HKG_YEN$ / HKG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IDN_YEN$ / IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 1 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * UZB_EXR

UZB_GINT  = UZB_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (UZB_LTI  - UZB_LTI(-1))

UZB_GDN  = UZB_GDN(-1) * (UZB_GDFXSH  * (UZB_EXR  / UZB_EXR(-1))  + (1  - UZB_GDFXSH))  - UZB_GLN

@IDENTITY UZB_GDNRATIO  = UZB_GDN / UZB_YEN * 100

UZB_GDFXSH  = ( UZB_GDFXSH(-1) * (UZB_EXR / UZB_EXR(-1) )) / (UZB_GDFXSH(-1) * (UZB_EXR / UZB_EXR(-1))  + 1 - UZB_GDFXSH(-1) )

UZB_TOURSH  = UZB_TOURSH(-1)

UZB_LOCK  = 0

UZB_GCARBR  = UZB_GCARBR(-1)

UZB_GTRADER  = UZB_GTRADER(-1)

UZB_ITAXR  = UZB_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_REV  = UZB_TAX  + UZB_CTAX  + UZB_ITAX  + UZB_GTRADE  + UZB_REVG  + UZB_GCARB  + UZB_GCOM  + UZB_GOTH

@IDENTITY UZB_TAX  = UZB_TAXR * (UZB_LABSH * 0.5 * (UZB_YER(-1)  + UZB_GDI(-1)) * UZB_YED(-1) * (UZB_LNN / UZB_LNN(-1)  + UZB_TECHL - UZB_TECHL(-1)) + UZB_REMIT  + UZB_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY UZB_CTAX  = UZB_CTAXR * UZB_PROF

@IDENTITY UZB_ITAX  = UZB_ITAXR * (UZB_PCR * UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY UZB_GTRADE  = UZB_GTRADER * UZB_XTN

UZB_REVG  = UZB_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (UZB_YER$ / UZB_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - UZB_YER$(-1) / UZB_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * UZB_EXR / UZB_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_GCARB  = UZB_GCARBR * UZB_CO2 * UZB_EXR / 1000

UZB_GCOM  = UZB_GCOM(-1) * ( UZB_OILC / (UZB_OILC + UZB_GASC + UZB_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + UZB_GASC / (UZB_OILC + UZB_GASC + UZB_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + UZB_COALC / (UZB_OILC + UZB_GASC + UZB_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

UZB_GOTH  = UZB_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_EXP  = UZB_EXPE  + UZB_EXPH  + UZB_EXPSP  + UZB_OGC  + UZB_OGI  + UZB_GIP

UZB_EXPE  = UZB_EXPE(-1) * (UZB_YFT / UZB_YFT(-1)) * (UZB_YED / UZB_YED(-1))

UZB_EXPH = UZB_EXPH(-1) * (UZB_YFT / UZB_YFT(-1)) * (UZB_YED / UZB_YED(-1))

UZB_EXPSP  = UZB_EXPSP(-1) * (UZB_YFT / UZB_YFT(-1)) * (UZB_YED / UZB_YED(-1)) * (UZB_POPT - UZB_LNN) / (UZB_POPT(-1) - UZB_LNN(-1))

DLOG(UZB_OGI)  = DLOG(UZB_YFT)  + DLOG(UZB_YED)

UZB_GCR  = UZB_GCR(-1)  + ( UZB_OGC / UZB_YED - UZB_OGC(-1) / UZB_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (UZB_EXPH ) / UZB_YED  - (UZB_EXPH(-1) ) / UZB_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (UZB_EXPE ) / UZB_YED  - (UZB_EXPE(-1) ) / UZB_YED(-1) )

UZB_IGR  = UZB_IGR(-1) + (UZB_OGI / UZB_YED - UZB_OGI(-1) / UZB_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (UZB_EXPH ) / UZB_YED  - (UZB_EXPH(-1) ) / UZB_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (UZB_EXPE ) / UZB_YED  - (UZB_EXPE(-1) ) / UZB_YED(-1) )

UZB_GIP  = ( UZB_GIP(-1)  + ( UZB_GDN(-1) - UZB_GDN(-2) ) * UZB_GINT(-1) / 100  + UZB_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( UZB_GINT(-1) / 100 - UZB_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (UZB_GDFXSH * (UZB_EXR / UZB_EXR(-1))  + (1 - UZB_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY UZB_GLN  = UZB_REV  - UZB_EXP

@IDENTITY UZB_GLNRATIO  = UZB_GLN / UZB_YEN * 100

UZB_GLNT  = UZB_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

UZB_TFP  = UZB_LABSH * (UZB_TECHL  - UZB_TECHL(-1))

UZB_LABSH  = UZB_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY UZB_LFN  = UZB_LRX * UZB_POPWA

UZB_LRX  = UZB_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(UZB_YER(-1) / UZB_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY UZB_URX  = (1 - UZB_LNN / UZB_LFN) * 100

UZB_URXF  = UZB_URXF(-1) * UZB_URX / UZB_URX(-1) * UZB_LNN / UZB_LNNF / (UZB_LNN(-1) / UZB_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(UZB_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(UZB_PCR  / UZB_POPT)

UZB_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(UZB_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

UZB_HEAD19  = UZB_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(UZB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI^2)  , UZB_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(UZB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , UZB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

UZB_HEAD55  = UZB_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(UZB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI^2)  , UZB_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(UZB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , UZB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(UZB_XTR)  = DLOG(UZB_WDR)  + (1  - UZB_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(UZB_XTDNO$  / UZB_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * UZB_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(UZB_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (UZB_EXPH(-1) / UZB_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (UZB_EXPH(-1) / UZB_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(UZB_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(UZB_PM25)

UZB_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( UZB_EXPSP / UZB_YEN )

DLOG(UZB_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - UZB_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (UZB_FINC - UZB_FINC(-1))

DLOG(UZB_PCR)  =  - 0.034073387748333  +  - 0.138515443492897 * (LOG(UZB_PCR(-1))  - LOG(UZB_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (UZB_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.46484510519205  * DLOG(UZB_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.46484510519205)  * DLOG(UZB_POPT)  +  - 1 * (DLOG(UZB_HIC)  - UZB_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * UZB_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * UZB_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(UZB_YFT(-1))  - LOG(UZB_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(UZB_IPR)  =  - 0.08850947947272  - 0.1 * (LOG(UZB_IPR(-1)  / UZB_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * UZB_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * UZB_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(UZB_PCR  + UZB_GCR(-1) + UZB_IGR(-1) + UZB_XTN  / UZB_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(UZB_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (UZB_USER - UZB_USER(-1))  - (0 * UZB_FUELSH  + 0.26 * UZB_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - UZB_FUELSH - UZB_TOURSH)) * UZB_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * UZB_FUELSH  + 0.26 * UZB_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - UZB_FUELSH - UZB_TOURSH)) * UZB_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(UZB_YFT(-1))  - LOG(UZB_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(UZB_MTR)  =  - 0.228335161800457  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(UZB_MTR(-1))  - LOG(UZB_PCR(-1) + UZB_ITR(-1) + UZB_GCR(-1) + UZB_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(UZB_YFT(-1) / UZB_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(UZB_CMUD(-1) * UZB_EXR(-1)  / UZB_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * UZB_OMS * LOG(UZB_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.568561398991904  * DLOG(UZB_XTR)  + 0.185763738762199  * DLOG(UZB_PCR)  + 0.0658733437740592  * DLOG(UZB_IPR)  + 0.355458189600977  * DLOG(UZB_GCR + UZB_IGR)

UZB_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * UZB_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * UZB_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * UZB_OILC

UZB_POIL  = UZB_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( UZB_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - UZB_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

UZB_PG  = UZB_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( UZB_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - UZB_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

UZB_PC  = UZB_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( UZB_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - UZB_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(UZB_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

UZB_PE  = UZB_PE(-1) * ( UZB_OILC(-1) / (UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) * UZB_POIL / UZB_POIL(-1)  + UZB_GASC(-1) / (UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) * UZB_PG / UZB_PG(-1)  + UZB_COALC(-1) / (UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) * UZB_PC / UZB_PC(-1)  + UZB_RC(-1) / (UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) * UZB_PR / UZB_PR(-1) )

D(UZB_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(UZB_PM25)  = 0.2 * (UZB_COALC(-1) / UZB_EC(-1) - UZB_COALC(-2) / UZB_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (UZB_COALC(-2) / UZB_EC(-2) - UZB_COALC(-3) / UZB_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (UZB_OILC(-1) / UZB_EC(-1) - UZB_OILC(-2) / UZB_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (UZB_OILC(-2) / UZB_EC(-2) - UZB_OILC(-3) / UZB_EC(-3))

DLOG(UZB_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(UZB_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(UZB_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(UZB_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(UZB_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(UZB_PE * UZB_EXR / UZB_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(UZB_PE(-1) * UZB_EXR(-1) / UZB_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(UZB_PE(-2) * UZB_EXR(-2) / UZB_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(UZB_PE(-3) * UZB_EXR(-3) / UZB_HIC(-3))  - (UZB_EFF - UZB_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(UZB_COALC)  = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(UZB_COALC(-1) / UZB_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.0325042271966846 * LOG(UZB_PE(-1) / UZB_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) / UZB_EC(-1))

DLOG(UZB_GASC)  = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(UZB_GASC(-1) / UZB_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.05 / 0.876208170935724 * LOG(UZB_PE(-1) / UZB_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) / UZB_EC(-1))

DLOG(UZB_RC)  = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( UZB_RC(-1) / UZB_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0325042271966846 * LOG(UZB_PE(-1) / UZB_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) / UZB_EC(-1))

DLOG(UZB_OILC)  = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( UZB_OILC(-1) / UZB_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.05 / 0.0325042271966846 * LOG(UZB_PE(-1) / UZB_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((UZB_COALC(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1) + UZB_OILC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)) / UZB_EC(-1))

UZB_EXR  = UZB_EXR(-1) * ( (UZB_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(VUT_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(VUT_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(VUT_MTD)  + 0.4 * (VUT_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (VUT_YER / VUT_YFT  - VUT_YER(-1) / VUT_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + VUT_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + VUT_GCARB / VUT_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (VUT_PREM - VUT_PREM(-1)) / 100

VUT_YED  = VUT_YED(-1) * VUT_HIC / VUT_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_INT  = VUT_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_LTI  = VUT_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (VUT_INT - VUT_INT(-1))  + (VUT_PREM  - VUT_PREM(-1)) / 100

VUT_PREM  = VUT_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (VUT_GDNRATIO(-1)  - VUT_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(VUT_LNN)  = DLOG(VUT_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(VUT_LNN(-1))  - LOG(VUT_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(VUT_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(VUT_LNNF)  = DLOG(VUT_LNN)

VUT_FUELSH  = VUT_FUELSH(-1)

VUT_TAXR  = VUT_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( VUT_GLNT(-1)  - VUT_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * VUT_YEN(-1) / ( ( VUT_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (VUT_YER(-2)  + VUT_GDI(-2)) * VUT_YED(-2) * (VUT_LNN(-1) / VUT_LNN(-2)  + VUT_TECHL(-1) - VUT_TECHL(-2) ) ) + VUT_REMIT(-1)  + VUT_EXPSP(-1) ) * VUT_SOLV

VUT_CTAXR  = VUT_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( VUT_GLNT(-1)  - VUT_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * VUT_YEN(-1) / ( VUT_PROF(-1) ) * VUT_SOLV

(VUT_OGC)  = VUT_OGC(-1) * (VUT_YFT / VUT_YFT(-1) * VUT_YED / VUT_YED(-1))

VUT_USER  = (VUT_LTI  - VUT_INFT  + VUT_DEP * 100) / (1  - VUT_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (VUT_GCARB / VUT_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY VUT_XTN  = VUT_XTD$ * VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") * VUT_XTR

@IDENTITY VUT_YEN  = VUT_YER  * VUT_YED

@IDENTITY VUT_MTN  = VUT_MTD  * VUT_MTR

@IDENTITY VUT_XTN$  = VUT_XTN / VUT_EXR

@IDENTITY VUT_YEN$  = VUT_YEN / VUT_EXR

@IDENTITY VUT_MTN$  = VUT_MTN / VUT_EXR

@IDENTITY VUT_MTR$  = VUT_MTR$(-1) * VUT_MTR / VUT_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_XTR$  = VUT_XTR$(-1) * VUT_XTR / VUT_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_YER$  = VUT_YER$(-1) * VUT_YER / VUT_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_YFT$  = VUT_YFT$(-1) * VUT_YFT / VUT_YFT(-1)

VUT_POPT  = VUT_POPT(-1)  - VUT_LIVES

VUT_POPWA  = VUT_POPWA(-1) * VUT_POPT / VUT_POPT(-1)

VUT_SCR  = VUT_SCR(-1)  + ((VUT_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (VUT_YFT(-1) / VUT_YER(-1)  - VUT_YFT(-2) / VUT_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY VUT_ITR  = VUT_IGR  + VUT_IPR

@IDENTITY VUT_YER  = VUT_PCR  + VUT_GCR  + VUT_ITR  + VUT_SCR  + VUT_XTR  - VUT_MTR

@IDENTITY VUT_PROF  = (VUT_YEN - VUT_ITAX) * (1 - VUT_LABSH)

@IDENTITY VUT_GDI  = VUT_YER  - VUT_XTR  + VUT_MTR  + VUT_XTN  / ((VUT_YEN  - VUT_XTN  + VUT_MTN)  / (VUT_YER  - VUT_XTR  + VUT_MTR))  - VUT_MTN  / ((VUT_YEN  - VUT_XTN  + VUT_MTN)  / (VUT_YER  - VUT_XTR  + VUT_MTR))

@IDENTITY VUT_RPDI  = VUT_LABSH * 0.5 * (VUT_YER(-1)  + VUT_GDI(-1)) * VUT_YED(-1) / VUT_HIC(-1) * (VUT_LNN / VUT_LNN(-1)  + VUT_TECHL - VUT_TECHL(-1)) + VUT_REMIT / VUT_HIC  + VUT_EXPSP / VUT_HIC  - VUT_TAX / VUT_HIC

DLOG(VUT_YFT)  = (1 - VUT_ALPHA - VUT_LABSH) * DLOG(VUT_K(-1) / VUT_LFN(-1))  + (1 - VUT_ALPHA) * DLOG(VUT_LFN)  + VUT_LABSH * D(VUT_TECHL)  + VUT_ALPHA * (DLOG(VUT_EC)  + D(VUT_EFF) )  - ( VUT_CLIMLOSS / VUT_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (VUT_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY VUT_K  = VUT_K(-1) * (1 - VUT_DEP) + VUT_ITR

DLOG(VUT_MTD)  = (1  - VUT_OMS) * ( DLOG(VUT_CMUD)  + DLOG(VUT_EXR) )  + VUT_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(VUT_EXR) )

DLOG(VUT_XTD$)  = (1  - VUT_OXS) * DLOG(VUT_XTDNO$)  + VUT_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

VUT_INFT  = 0.95 * VUT_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

VUT_OXS  = VUT_OXS(-1)

VUT_OMS  = VUT_OMS(-1) * ((VUT_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * VUT_EXR(-1) / VUT_MTN(-1)) / (VUT_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * VUT_EXR(-2) / VUT_MTN(-2)))^0.25

VUT_CXS  = VUT_CXS(-1)

VUT_FINC  = VUT_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_CAN  = VUT_XTN / VUT_EXR  - VUT_MTN / VUT_EXR  + VUT_REMIT / VUT_EXR  + VUT_CANOTH

@IDENTITY VUT_CANRATIO  = VUT_CAN / VUT_YEN$ * 100

VUT_CANOTH  = VUT_CANOTH(-1)  + ((VUT_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (VUT_YEN$  / VUT_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + VUT_REVG / VUT_EXR  - VUT_REVG(-1) / VUT_EXR(-1)

IDN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IND_YEN$ / IND_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0003913237358 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * IRN_YEN$ / IRN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.007010184338 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KAZ_YEN$ / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KGZ_YEN$ / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KHM_YEN$ / KHM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KIR_YEN$ / KIR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LAO_YEN$ / LAO_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MAC_YEN$ / MAC_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MDV_YEN$ / MDV_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MMR_YEN$ / MMR_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNG_YEN$ / MNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MYS_YEN$ / MYS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004089697975 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NPL_YEN$ / NPL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PAK_YEN$ / PAK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PHL_YEN$ / PHL_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * PNG_YEN$ / PNG_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002511285961 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * SGP_YEN$ / SGP_YEN$(-1)  + 0.07170793917 * SLB_YEN$ / SLB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TJK_YEN$ / TJK_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TKM_YEN$ / TKM_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TLS_YEN$ / TLS_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * TON_YEN$ / TON_YEN$(-1)  + 0.001137870451 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.05802374209 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * UZB_YEN$ / UZB_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * VNM_YEN$ / VNM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0005418735958 * VUT_YEN$ / VUT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.00391036634 * WSM_YEN$ / WSM_YEN$(-1)  + 0.005228181588 * AFR_YEN$ / AFR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006604832109 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.0506039817 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1) ) * VUT_EXR

VUT_GINT  = VUT_GINT(-1)  + 1 / 5 * (VUT_LTI  - VUT_LTI(-1))

VUT_GDN  = VUT_GDN(-1) * (VUT_GDFXSH  * (VUT_EXR  / VUT_EXR(-1))  + (1  - VUT_GDFXSH))  - VUT_GLN

@IDENTITY VUT_GDNRATIO  = VUT_GDN / VUT_YEN * 100

VUT_GDFXSH  = ( VUT_GDFXSH(-1) * (VUT_EXR / VUT_EXR(-1) )) / (VUT_GDFXSH(-1) * (VUT_EXR / VUT_EXR(-1))  + 1 - VUT_GDFXSH(-1) )

VUT_TOURSH  = VUT_TOURSH(-1)

VUT_LOCK  = 0

VUT_GCARBR  = VUT_GCARBR(-1)

VUT_GTRADER  = VUT_GTRADER(-1)

VUT_ITAXR  = VUT_ITAXR(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_REV  = VUT_TAX  + VUT_CTAX  + VUT_ITAX  + VUT_GTRADE  + VUT_REVG  + VUT_GCARB  + VUT_GCOM  + VUT_GOTH

@IDENTITY VUT_TAX  = VUT_TAXR * (VUT_LABSH * 0.5 * (VUT_YER(-1)  + VUT_GDI(-1)) * VUT_YED(-1) * (VUT_LNN / VUT_LNN(-1)  + VUT_TECHL - VUT_TECHL(-1)) + VUT_REMIT  + VUT_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY VUT_CTAX  = VUT_CTAXR * VUT_PROF

@IDENTITY VUT_ITAX  = VUT_ITAXR * (VUT_PCR * VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , 2015))

@IDENTITY VUT_GTRADE  = VUT_GTRADER * VUT_XTN

VUT_REVG  = VUT_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (VUT_YER$ / VUT_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - VUT_YER$(-1) / VUT_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * VUT_EXR / VUT_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_GCARB  = VUT_GCARBR * VUT_CO2 * VUT_EXR / 1000

VUT_GCOM  = VUT_GCOM(-1) * ( VUT_OILC / (VUT_OILC + VUT_GASC + VUT_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + VUT_GASC / (VUT_OILC + VUT_GASC + VUT_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + VUT_COALC / (VUT_OILC + VUT_GASC + VUT_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

VUT_GOTH  = VUT_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_EXP  = VUT_EXPE  + VUT_EXPH  + VUT_EXPSP  + VUT_OGC  + VUT_OGI  + VUT_GIP

VUT_EXPE  = VUT_EXPE(-1) * (VUT_YFT / VUT_YFT(-1)) * (VUT_YED / VUT_YED(-1))

VUT_EXPH = VUT_EXPH(-1) * (VUT_YFT / VUT_YFT(-1)) * (VUT_YED / VUT_YED(-1))

VUT_EXPSP  = VUT_EXPSP(-1) * (VUT_YFT / VUT_YFT(-1)) * (VUT_YED / VUT_YED(-1)) * (VUT_POPT - VUT_LNN) / (VUT_POPT(-1) - VUT_LNN(-1))

DLOG(VUT_OGI)  = DLOG(VUT_YFT)  + DLOG(VUT_YED)

VUT_GCR  = VUT_GCR(-1)  + ( VUT_OGC / VUT_YED - VUT_OGC(-1) / VUT_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (VUT_EXPH ) / VUT_YED  - (VUT_EXPH(-1) ) / VUT_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (VUT_EXPE ) / VUT_YED  - (VUT_EXPE(-1) ) / VUT_YED(-1) )

VUT_IGR  = VUT_IGR(-1) + (VUT_OGI / VUT_YED - VUT_OGI(-1) / VUT_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (VUT_EXPH ) / VUT_YED  - (VUT_EXPH(-1) ) / VUT_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (VUT_EXPE ) / VUT_YED  - (VUT_EXPE(-1) ) / VUT_YED(-1) )

VUT_GIP  = ( VUT_GIP(-1)  + ( VUT_GDN(-1) - VUT_GDN(-2) ) * VUT_GINT(-1) / 100  + VUT_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( VUT_GINT(-1) / 100 - VUT_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (VUT_GDFXSH * (VUT_EXR / VUT_EXR(-1))  + (1 - VUT_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY VUT_GLN  = VUT_REV  - VUT_EXP

@IDENTITY VUT_GLNRATIO  = VUT_GLN / VUT_YEN * 100

VUT_GLNT  = VUT_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

VUT_TFP  = VUT_LABSH * (VUT_TECHL  - VUT_TECHL(-1))

VUT_LABSH  = VUT_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY VUT_LFN  = VUT_LRX * VUT_POPWA

VUT_LRX  = VUT_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(VUT_YER(-1) / VUT_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY VUT_URX  = (1 - VUT_LNN / VUT_LFN) * 100

VUT_URXF  = VUT_URXF(-1) * VUT_URX / VUT_URX(-1) * VUT_LNN / VUT_LNNF / (VUT_LNN(-1) / VUT_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(VUT_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(VUT_PCR  / VUT_POPT)

VUT_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(VUT_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

VUT_HEAD19  = VUT_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VUT_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI^2)  , VUT_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VUT_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VUT_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

VUT_HEAD55  = VUT_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VUT_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI^2)  , VUT_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VUT_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VUT_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(VUT_XTR)  = DLOG(VUT_WDR)  + (1  - VUT_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(VUT_XTDNO$  / VUT_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * VUT_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(VUT_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (VUT_EXPH(-1) / VUT_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (VUT_EXPH(-1) / VUT_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(VUT_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(VUT_PM25)

VUT_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( VUT_EXPSP / VUT_YEN )

DLOG(VUT_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - VUT_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (VUT_FINC - VUT_FINC(-1))

DLOG(VUT_PCR)  =  - 0.0445416900271343  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(VUT_PCR(-1))  - LOG(VUT_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (VUT_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(VUT_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(VUT_POPT)  +  - 1 * (DLOG(VUT_HIC)  - VUT_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * VUT_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * VUT_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(VUT_YFT(-1))  - LOG(VUT_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(VUT_IPR)  =  - 0.133063926356345  - 0.1 * (LOG(VUT_IPR(-1)  / VUT_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * VUT_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * VUT_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(VUT_PCR  + VUT_GCR(-1) + VUT_IGR(-1) + VUT_XTN  / VUT_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(VUT_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (VUT_USER - VUT_USER(-1))  - (0 * VUT_FUELSH  + 0.26 * VUT_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - VUT_FUELSH - VUT_TOURSH)) * VUT_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * VUT_FUELSH  + 0.26 * VUT_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - VUT_FUELSH - VUT_TOURSH)) * VUT_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(VUT_YFT(-1))  - LOG(VUT_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(VUT_MTR)  =  - 0.0946558183080917  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(VUT_MTR(-1))  - LOG(VUT_PCR(-1) + VUT_ITR(-1) + VUT_GCR(-1) + VUT_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(VUT_YFT(-1) / VUT_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(VUT_CMUD(-1) * VUT_EXR(-1)  / VUT_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * VUT_OMS * LOG(VUT_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.344081669801307  * DLOG(VUT_XTR)  + 0.054599252466972  * DLOG(VUT_PCR)  + 0.170513908463775  * DLOG(VUT_IPR)  + 0.134370090117397  * DLOG(VUT_GCR + VUT_IGR)

VUT_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * VUT_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * VUT_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * VUT_OILC

VUT_POIL  = VUT_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( VUT_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - VUT_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

VUT_PG  = VUT_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( VUT_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - VUT_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

VUT_PC  = VUT_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( VUT_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - VUT_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(VUT_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

VUT_PE  = VUT_PE(-1) * ( VUT_OILC(-1) / (VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) * VUT_POIL / VUT_POIL(-1)  + VUT_GASC(-1) / (VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) * VUT_PG / VUT_PG(-1)  + VUT_COALC(-1) / (VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) * VUT_PC / VUT_PC(-1)  + VUT_RC(-1) / (VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) * VUT_PR / VUT_PR(-1) )

D(VUT_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(VUT_PM25)  = 0.2 * (VUT_COALC(-1) / VUT_EC(-1) - VUT_COALC(-2) / VUT_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (VUT_COALC(-2) / VUT_EC(-2) - VUT_COALC(-3) / VUT_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (VUT_OILC(-1) / VUT_EC(-1) - VUT_OILC(-2) / VUT_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (VUT_OILC(-2) / VUT_EC(-2) - VUT_OILC(-3) / VUT_EC(-3))

DLOG(VUT_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(VUT_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(VUT_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(VUT_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(VUT_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VUT_PE * VUT_EXR / VUT_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VUT_PE(-1) * VUT_EXR(-1) / VUT_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VUT_PE(-2) * VUT_EXR(-2) / VUT_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VUT_PE(-3) * VUT_EXR(-3) / VUT_HIC(-3))  - (VUT_EFF - VUT_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(VUT_COALC)  = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(VUT_COALC(-1) / VUT_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(VUT_PE(-1) / VUT_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) / VUT_EC(-1))

DLOG(VUT_GASC)  = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(VUT_GASC(-1) / VUT_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.15 / 0.01 * LOG(VUT_PE(-1) / VUT_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) / VUT_EC(-1))

DLOG(VUT_RC)  = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( VUT_RC(-1) / VUT_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.359757239725771 * LOG(VUT_PE(-1) / VUT_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) / VUT_EC(-1))

DLOG(VUT_OILC)  = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( VUT_OILC(-1) / VUT_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.15 / 0.359757239725771 * LOG(VUT_PE(-1) / VUT_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VUT_COALC(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1) + VUT_OILC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)) / VUT_EC(-1))

VUT_EXR  = VUT_EXR(-1) * ( (VUT_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(VNM_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(VNM_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(VNM_MTD)  + 0.4 * (VNM_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (VNM_YER / VNM_YFT  - VNM_YER(-1) / VNM_YFT(-1))  + DLOG(1 + VNM_ITAXR)  + 0.5 * DLOG(1 + VNM_GCARB / VNM_YEN(-1))  + 0.01 * (VNM_PREM - VNM_PREM(-1)) / 100

VNM_YED  = VNM_YED(-1) * VNM_HIC / VNM_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_INT  = VNM_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_LTI  = VNM_LTI(-1)  + 0.5 * (VNM_INT - VNM_INT(-1))  + (VNM_PREM  - VNM_PREM(-1)) / 100

VNM_PREM  = VNM_PREM(-1) * (1  + 3 * (VNM_GDNRATIO(-1)  - VNM_GDNRATIO(-2)) / 100)

DLOG(VNM_LNN)  = DLOG(VNM_LFN )  - 0.1 * (LOG(VNM_LNN(-1))  - LOG(VNM_LFN(-1) ) )  + 0.3 * (DLOG(VNM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(VNM_LNNF)  = DLOG(VNM_LNN)

VNM_FUELSH  = VNM_FUELSH(-1)

VNM_TAXR  = VNM_TAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( VNM_GLNT(-1)  - VNM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * VNM_YEN(-1) / ( ( VNM_LABSH(-1) * 0.5 * (VNM_YER(-2)  + VNM_GDI(-2)) * VNM_YED(-2) * (VNM_LNN(-1) / VNM_LNN(-2)  + VNM_TECHL(-1) - VNM_TECHL(-2) ) ) + VNM_REMIT(-1)  + VNM_EXPSP(-1) ) * VNM_SOLV

VNM_CTAXR  = VNM_CTAXR(-1)  + 0.1 * ( VNM_GLNT(-1)  - VNM_GLNRATIO(-1) ) / 100 * VNM_YEN(-1) / ( VNM_PROF(-1) ) * VNM_SOLV

(VNM_OGC)  = VNM_OGC(-1) * (VNM_YFT / VNM_YFT(-1) * VNM_YED / VNM_YED(-1))

VNM_USER  = (VNM_LTI  - VNM_INFT  + VNM_DEP * 100) / (1  - VNM_CTAXR )  + 0.5 * (VNM_GCARB / VNM_YEN(-1) ) * 100

@IDENTITY VNM_XTN  = VNM_XTD$ * VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") * VNM_XTR

@IDENTITY VNM_YEN  = VNM_YER  * VNM_YED

@IDENTITY VNM_MTN  = VNM_MTD  * VNM_MTR

@IDENTITY VNM_XTN$  = VNM_XTN / VNM_EXR

@IDENTITY VNM_YEN$  = VNM_YEN / VNM_EXR

@IDENTITY VNM_MTN$  = VNM_MTN / VNM_EXR

@IDENTITY VNM_MTR$  = VNM_MTR$(-1) * VNM_MTR / VNM_MTR(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_XTR$  = VNM_XTR$(-1) * VNM_XTR / VNM_XTR(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_YER$  = VNM_YER$(-1) * VNM_YER / VNM_YER(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_YFT$  = VNM_YFT$(-1) * VNM_YFT / VNM_YFT(-1)

VNM_POPT  = VNM_POPT(-1)  - VNM_LIVES

VNM_POPWA  = VNM_POPWA(-1) * VNM_POPT / VNM_POPT(-1)

VNM_SCR  = VNM_SCR(-1)  + ((VNM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (VNM_YFT(-1) / VNM_YER(-1)  - VNM_YFT(-2) / VNM_YER(-2) ) )

@IDENTITY VNM_ITR  = VNM_IGR  + VNM_IPR

@IDENTITY VNM_YER  = VNM_PCR  + VNM_GCR  + VNM_ITR  + VNM_SCR  + VNM_XTR  - VNM_MTR

@IDENTITY VNM_PROF  = (VNM_YEN - VNM_ITAX) * (1 - VNM_LABSH)

@IDENTITY VNM_GDI  = VNM_YER  - VNM_XTR  + VNM_MTR  + VNM_XTN  / ((VNM_YEN  - VNM_XTN  + VNM_MTN)  / (VNM_YER  - VNM_XTR  + VNM_MTR))  - VNM_MTN  / ((VNM_YEN  - VNM_XTN  + VNM_MTN)  / (VNM_YER  - VNM_XTR  + VNM_MTR))

@IDENTITY VNM_RPDI  = VNM_LABSH * 0.5 * (VNM_YER(-1)  + VNM_GDI(-1)) * VNM_YED(-1) / VNM_HIC(-1) * (VNM_LNN / VNM_LNN(-1)  + VNM_TECHL - VNM_TECHL(-1)) + VNM_REMIT / VNM_HIC  + VNM_EXPSP / VNM_HIC  - VNM_TAX / VNM_HIC

DLOG(VNM_YFT)  = (1 - VNM_ALPHA - VNM_LABSH) * DLOG(VNM_K(-1) / VNM_LFN(-1))  + (1 - VNM_ALPHA) * DLOG(VNM_LFN)  + VNM_LABSH * D(VNM_TECHL)  + VNM_ALPHA * (DLOG(VNM_EC)  + D(VNM_EFF) )  - ( VNM_CLIMLOSS / VNM_CLIMLOSS(-1)  - 1 ) * (VNM_DAMAGE / 100)

@IDENTITY VNM_K  = VNM_K(-1) * (1 - VNM_DEP) + VNM_ITR

DLOG(VNM_MTD)  = (1  - VNM_OMS) * ( DLOG(VNM_CMUD)  + DLOG(VNM_EXR) )  + VNM_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(VNM_EXR) )

DLOG(VNM_XTD$)  = (1  - VNM_OXS) * DLOG(VNM_XTDNO$)  + VNM_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

VNM_INFT  = 0.95 * VNM_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

VNM_OXS  = VNM_OXS(-1)

VNM_OMS  = VNM_OMS(-1) * ((VNM_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1) * VNM_EXR(-1) / VNM_MTN(-1)) / (VNM_OILC(-2) * WLD_POIL(-2) * VNM_EXR(-2) / VNM_MTN(-2)))^0.25

VNM_CXS  = VNM_CXS(-1)

VNM_FINC  = VNM_FINC(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_CAN  = VNM_XTN / VNM_EXR  - VNM_MTN / VNM_EXR  + VNM_REMIT / VNM_EXR  + VNM_CANOTH

@IDENTITY VNM_CANRATIO  = VNM_CAN / VNM_YEN$ * 100

VNM_CANOTH  = VNM_CANOTH(-1)  + ((VNM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (VNM_YEN$  / VNM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + VNM_REVG / VNM_EXR  - VNM_REVG(-1) / VNM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_GTRADE  = VNM_GTRADER * VNM_XTN

VNM_REVG  = VNM_REVG(-1) * ( 0.201 * USA_YEN$ / USA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.14 * DEU_YEN$ / DEU_YEN$(-1)  + 0.135 * EUR_YEN$ / EUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.114 * GBR_YEN$ / GBR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.071 * FRA_YEN$ / FRA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.069 * JPN_YEN$ / JPN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.056 * MNA_YEN$ / MNA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.051 * TUR_YEN$ / TUR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.031 * NLD_YEN$ / NLD_YEN$(-1)  + 0.028 * ITA_YEN$ / ITA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.027 * LAT_YEN$ / LAT_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * AUS_YEN$ / AUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.018 * CHE_YEN$ / CHE_YEN$(-1)  + 0.015 * KOR_YEN$ / KOR_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * IRL_YEN$ / IRL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.006 * RUS_YEN$ / RUS_YEN$(-1)  + 0.004 * CHN_YEN$ / CHN_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * NZL_YEN$ / NZL_YEN$(-1)  + 0.003 * THA_YEN$ / THA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * LKA_YEN$ / LKA_YEN$(-1)  + 0.002 * TWN_YEN$ / TWN_YEN$(-1)  - 0.01 * (VNM_YER$ / VNM_POPT / (WLD_YER$ / WLD_POPT)  - VNM_YER$(-1) / VNM_POPT(-1) / (WLD_YER$(-1) / WLD_POPT(-1)) )) * VNM_EXR / VNM_EXR(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_GCARB  = VNM_GCARBR * VNM_CO2 * VNM_EXR / 1000

VNM_GCOM  = VNM_GCOM(-1) * ( VNM_OILC / (VNM_OILC + VNM_GASC + VNM_COALC) * (WLD_OILC * WLD_POIL) / (WLD_OILC(-1) * WLD_POIL(-1))  + VNM_GASC / (VNM_OILC + VNM_GASC + VNM_COALC) * (WLD_GASC * WLD_PG) / (WLD_GASC(-1) * WLD_PG(-1))  + VNM_COALC / (VNM_OILC + VNM_GASC + VNM_COALC) * (WLD_COALC * WLD_PC) / (WLD_COALC(-1) * WLD_PC(-1)) )

VNM_GOTH  = VNM_GOTH(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_EXP  = VNM_EXPE  + VNM_EXPH  + VNM_EXPSP  + VNM_OGC  + VNM_OGI  + VNM_GIP

VNM_EXPE  = VNM_EXPE(-1) * (VNM_YFT / VNM_YFT(-1)) * (VNM_YED / VNM_YED(-1))

VNM_EXPH = VNM_EXPH(-1) * (VNM_YFT / VNM_YFT(-1)) * (VNM_YED / VNM_YED(-1))

VNM_EXPSP  = VNM_EXPSP(-1) * (VNM_YFT / VNM_YFT(-1)) * (VNM_YED / VNM_YED(-1)) * (VNM_POPT - VNM_LNN) / (VNM_POPT(-1) - VNM_LNN(-1))

DLOG(VNM_OGI)  = DLOG(VNM_YFT)  + DLOG(VNM_YED)

VNM_GCR  = VNM_GCR(-1)  + ( VNM_OGC / VNM_YED - VNM_OGC(-1) / VNM_YED(-1) )  + 0.75 * ( (VNM_EXPH ) / VNM_YED  - (VNM_EXPH(-1) ) / VNM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (VNM_EXPE ) / VNM_YED  - (VNM_EXPE(-1) ) / VNM_YED(-1) )

VNM_IGR  = VNM_IGR(-1) + (VNM_OGI / VNM_YED - VNM_OGI(-1) / VNM_YED(-1))  + 0.25 * ( (VNM_EXPH ) / VNM_YED  - (VNM_EXPH(-1) ) / VNM_YED(-1) )  + 0.5 * ( (VNM_EXPE ) / VNM_YED  - (VNM_EXPE(-1) ) / VNM_YED(-1) )

VNM_GIP  = ( VNM_GIP(-1)  + ( VNM_GDN(-1) - VNM_GDN(-2) ) * VNM_GINT(-1) / 100  + VNM_GDN(-6) / 5 * ( VNM_GINT(-1) / 100 - VNM_GINT(-6) / 100 ) ) * (VNM_GDFXSH * (VNM_EXR / VNM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - VNM_GDFXSH))

@IDENTITY VNM_GLN  = VNM_REV  - VNM_EXP

@IDENTITY VNM_GLNRATIO  = VNM_GLN / VNM_YEN * 100

VNM_GLNT  = VNM_GLNT(-1) * 0.95  - 0.05 * 2

VNM_TFP  = VNM_LABSH * (VNM_TECHL  - VNM_TECHL(-1))

VNM_LABSH  = VNM_LABSH(-1)

@IDENTITY VNM_LFN  = VNM_LRX * VNM_POPWA

VNM_LRX  = VNM_LRX(-1)  + 0.3 * LOG(VNM_YER(-1) / VNM_YFT(-1))

@IDENTITY VNM_URX  = (1 - VNM_LNN / VNM_LFN) * 100

VNM_URXF  = VNM_URXF(-1) * VNM_URX / VNM_URX(-1) * VNM_LNN / VNM_LNNF / (VNM_LNN(-1) / VNM_LNNF(-1))

DLOG(VNM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(VNM_PCR  / VNM_POPT)

VNM_SDLI  = 2 * (@QGAMMA(VNM_GINI_DISP / 100 , 1 , 0.5))^0.5

VNM_HEAD19  = VNM_HEAD19(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VNM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI^2)  , VNM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VNM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VNM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

VNM_HEAD55  = VNM_HEAD55(-1)  * ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VNM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI^2)  , VNM_SDLI )  * 100 ) / ( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VNM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VNM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )

DLOG(VNM_XTR)  = DLOG(VNM_WDR)  + (1  - VNM_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(VNM_XTDNO$  / VNM_CXUD) )  +  - 0.77 * VNM_TOURSH * WLD_LOCK / 100

D(VNM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22 * (VNM_EXPH(-1) / VNM_YEN(-1))  - 0.029 * (VNM_EXPH(-1) / VNM_YEN(-1))^2  +  - 0.0127503807928701 * D(VNM_GINI_DISP)  - 0.0033 * D(VNM_PM25)

VNM_REL_RED  =  + 5.7453643863536  + 90.2965265758529 * ( VNM_EXPSP / VNM_YEN )

DLOG(VNM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.784799699529425 * DLOG(1 - VNM_REL_RED / 100)  +  - 0.000176634194283627 * (VNM_FINC - VNM_FINC(-1))

DLOG(VNM_PCR)  = 0.021304643538339  +  - 0.1 * (LOG(VNM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(VNM_RPDI(-1))  - 0.0182864470659255 * (VNM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(VNM_RPDI)  + (1 - 0.3)  * DLOG(VNM_POPT)  +  - 0.1 * (DLOG(VNM_HIC)  - VNM_INFT / 100 )  - 0.239704 * VNM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * 0.239704 * VNM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(VNM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(VNM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(VNM_IPR)  =  - 0.16368425040165  - 0.1 * (LOG(VNM_IPR(-1)  / VNM_YFT(-1))  + 0.01 * VNM_USER(-1)  - 0.00301044334553174 * VNM_FINC(-1) )  + 0.4 * DLOG(VNM_PCR  + VNM_GCR(-1) + VNM_IGR(-1) + VNM_XTN  / VNM_YED )  + 0.2 * DLOG(VNM_IPR(-1))  - 0.002 * (VNM_USER - VNM_USER(-1))  - (0 * VNM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * VNM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - VNM_FUELSH - VNM_TOURSH)) * VNM_LOCK / 100  - 0.49 * (0 * VNM_FUELSH  + 0.26 * VNM_TOURSH + 0.06 * (1 - VNM_FUELSH - VNM_TOURSH)) * VNM_LOCK(-1) / 100  + 0.1 * (LOG(VNM_YFT(-1))  - LOG(VNM_YER(-1)) )

DLOG(VNM_MTR)  =  - 0.00298561216370681  +  - 0.152986408545611  * ( LOG(VNM_MTR(-1))  - LOG(VNM_PCR(-1) + VNM_ITR(-1) + VNM_GCR(-1) + VNM_XTR(-1) )  + LOG(VNM_YFT(-1) / VNM_YER(-1) )  + 0.0879572709820191 * LOG(VNM_CMUD(-1) * VNM_EXR(-1)  / VNM_YED(-1))  - 0.25 * VNM_OMS * LOG(VNM_OILC(-1)) )  + 0.604532336814892  * DLOG(VNM_XTR)  + 0.279148232559581  * DLOG(VNM_PCR)  + 0.00887925517675983  * DLOG(VNM_IPR)  + 0.0015452301608694  * DLOG(VNM_GCR + VNM_IGR)

VUT_XTDNO$  = VUT_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.529724413635699  * (DLOG(VUT_YED(-1) / VUT_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.529724413635699 )  * (DLOG(VUT_CXUD(-1))  + 1) ) * (1 + VUT_GTRADER) / (1 + VUT_GTRADER(-1))

VNM_XTDNO$  = VNM_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.448334660955031  * (DLOG(VNM_YED(-1) / VNM_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.448334660955031 )  * (DLOG(VNM_CXUD(-1))  + 1) ) * (1 + VNM_GTRADER) / (1 + VNM_GTRADER(-1))

USA_XTDNO$  = USA_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.6  * (DLOG(USA_YED(-1) / USA_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.6 )  * (DLOG(USA_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

DEU_XTDNO$  = DEU_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.1  * (DLOG(DEU_YED(-1) / DEU_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.1 )  * (DLOG(DEU_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

FRA_XTDNO$  = FRA_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.1  * (DLOG(FRA_YED(-1) / FRA_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.1 )  * (DLOG(FRA_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

GBR_XTDNO$  = GBR_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.192911931708509  * (DLOG(GBR_YED(-1) / GBR_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.192911931708509 )  * (DLOG(GBR_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

ITA_XTDNO$  = ITA_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.1  * (DLOG(ITA_YED(-1) / ITA_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.1 )  * (DLOG(ITA_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

NLD_XTDNO$  = NLD_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.100000000000001  * (DLOG(NLD_YED(-1) / NLD_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.100000000000001 )  * (DLOG(NLD_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

IRL_XTDNO$  = IRL_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.196881251604775  * (DLOG(IRL_YED(-1) / IRL_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.196881251604775 )  * (DLOG(IRL_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

CHE_XTDNO$  = CHE_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.100000000000001  * (DLOG(CHE_YED(-1) / CHE_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.100000000000001 )  * (DLOG(CHE_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

TWN_XTDNO$  = TWN_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.6  * (DLOG(TWN_YED(-1) / TWN_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.6 )  * (DLOG(TWN_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

AFR_XTDNO$  = AFR_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.145367617785722  * (DLOG(AFR_YED(-1) / AFR_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.145367617785722 )  * (DLOG(AFR_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

EUR_XTDNO$  = EUR_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.1  * (DLOG(EUR_YED(-1) / EUR_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.1 )  * (DLOG(EUR_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

LAT_XTDNO$  = LAT_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.100000000000001  * (DLOG(LAT_YED(-1) / LAT_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.100000000000001 )  * (DLOG(LAT_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

MNA_XTDNO$  = MNA_XTDNO$(-1) * ( 0.1  * (DLOG(MNA_YED(-1) / MNA_EXR(-1))  + 1)  + (1 - 0.1 )  * (DLOG(MNA_CXUD(-1))  + 1) )

VNM_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * VNM_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * VNM_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * VNM_OILC

VNM_POIL  = VNM_POIL(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + ( VNM_GCARBR * 67.3944990593688 / 1000  - VNM_GCARBR(-1) * 67.3944990593688 / 1000 )

VNM_PG  = VNM_PG(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + ( VNM_GCARBR * 57.1898042275623 / 1000  - VNM_GCARBR(-1) * 57.1898042275623 / 1000 )

VNM_PC  = VNM_PC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + ( VNM_GCARBR * 95.9924025698793 / 1000  - VNM_GCARBR(-1) * 95.9924025698793 / 1000 )

DLOG(VNM_PR)  = DLOG( WLD_PR )

VNM_PE  = VNM_PE(-1) * ( VNM_OILC(-1) / (VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) * VNM_POIL / VNM_POIL(-1)  + VNM_GASC(-1) / (VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) * VNM_PG / VNM_PG(-1)  + VNM_COALC(-1) / (VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) * VNM_PC / VNM_PC(-1)  + VNM_RC(-1) / (VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) * VNM_PR / VNM_PR(-1) )

D(VNM_DEP)  = 0.0479891161065229 * DLOG(WLD_CO2)

DLOG(VNM_PM25)  = 0.2 * (VNM_COALC(-1) / VNM_EC(-1) - VNM_COALC(-2) / VNM_EC(-2))  + 0.1 * (VNM_COALC(-2) / VNM_EC(-2) - VNM_COALC(-3) / VNM_EC(-3))  + 0.12 * (VNM_OILC(-1) / VNM_EC(-1) - VNM_OILC(-2) / VNM_EC(-2))  + 0.06 * (VNM_OILC(-2) / VNM_EC(-2) - VNM_OILC(-3) / VNM_EC(-3))

DLOG(VNM_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(VNM_YER)  + 0.25 * DLOG(VNM_YER(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(VNM_YER(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(VNM_YER(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VNM_PE * VNM_EXR / VNM_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VNM_PE(-1) * VNM_EXR(-1) / VNM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VNM_PE(-2) * VNM_EXR(-2) / VNM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(VNM_PE(-3) * VNM_EXR(-3) / VNM_HIC(-3))  - (VNM_EFF - VNM_EFF(-1) )

DLOG(VNM_COALC)  = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(VNM_COALC(-1) / VNM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.152163605915989 * LOG(VNM_PE(-1) / VNM_PC(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) / VNM_EC(-1))

DLOG(VNM_GASC)  = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG(VNM_GASC(-1) / VNM_EC(-1) )  +  - 0.4 / 0.0861098986148086 * LOG(VNM_PE(-1) / VNM_PG(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) / VNM_EC(-1))

DLOG(VNM_RC)  = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( VNM_RC(-1) / VNM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.152163605915989 * LOG(VNM_PE(-1) / VNM_PR(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) / VNM_EC(-1))

DLOG(VNM_OILC)  = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1) )  - 0.1 * ( LOG( VNM_OILC(-1) / VNM_EC(-1) ) +  - 0.4 / 0.152163605915989 * LOG(VNM_PE(-1) / VNM_POIL(-1)) )  - 1.7 * LOG((VNM_COALC(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1) + VNM_OILC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)) / VNM_EC(-1))

VNM_EXR  = VNM_EXR(-1) * ( (VNM_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(USA_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(USA_DD$(-1))  - LOG(USA_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(USA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(USA_HIC)  - USA_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * USA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * USA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(USA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(USA_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(USA_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(USA_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(USA_MTD)  + 0.4 * (USA_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (USA_YER$ / USA_YFT$  - USA_YER$(-1) / USA_YFT$(-1))

USA_YED  = USA_YED(-1) * USA_HIC / USA_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY USA_XTN$  = USA_XTD$ * USA_XTR$

@IDENTITY USA_YEN$  = USA_YER$ * USA_YED / USA_EXR * @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY USA_MTN$  = USA_MTR$ * USA_MTD / USA_EXR  * @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY USA_YER$  = USA_DD$  + USA_XTR$  - USA_MTR$

@IDENTITY USA_GDI$  = USA_DD$  + USA_XTN$  / ((USA_YEN$  - USA_XTN$  + USA_MTN$)  / (USA_YER$  - USA_XTR$  + USA_MTR$))  - USA_MTN$  / ((USA_YEN$  - USA_XTN$  + USA_MTN$)  / (USA_YER$  - USA_XTR$  + USA_MTR$))

DLOG(USA_MTD)  = (1  - USA_OMS) * ( DLOG(USA_CMUD)  + DLOG(USA_EXR) )  + USA_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(USA_EXR) )

DLOG(USA_XTD$)  = (1  - USA_OXS) * DLOG(USA_XTDNO$)  + USA_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

USA_INFT  = 0.95 * USA_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

USA_OXS  = USA_OXS(-1)

USA_OMS  = USA_OMS(-1)

USA_CXS  = USA_CXS(-1)

USA_LOCK  = 0

D(USA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(USA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (USA_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(USA_YFT$) = (1 - USA_ALPHA) * DLOG(USA_POPWA)  + D(USA_TECHL)  + USA_ALPHA * (DLOG(USA_EC)  + D(USA_EFF) )

@IDENTITY USA_INT  = USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(USA_XTR$)  = DLOG(USA_WDR)  + (1  - USA_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(USA_XTDNO$  / USA_CXUD) )

DLOG(USA_MTR$) = -0.305153504358819 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(USA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(USA_DD$( - 1) + USA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(USA_CMUD( - 1)*USA_EXR( - 1)/USA_YED( - 1))) + 0.804529142000389*0.308348050767945*DLOG(USA_XTR$) + 6.66870081464537*0.173941495515681*DLOG(USA_DD$)
@INNOV USA_MTR$  0.00411601894972988

USA_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * USA_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * USA_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * USA_OILC

DLOG(USA_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(USA_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(USA_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(USA_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(USA_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * USA_EXR / USA_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * USA_EXR(-1) / USA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * USA_EXR(-2) / USA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * USA_EXR(-3) / USA_HIC(-3))  - (USA_EFF - USA_EFF(-1) )

USA_COALC  = USA_COALC(-1) * (USA_EC / USA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

USA_GASC  = USA_GASC(-1) * (USA_EC / USA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

USA_RC  = USA_RC(-1) * (USA_EC / USA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

USA_OILC  = USA_EC  - USA_COALC  - USA_RC  - USA_GASC

@IDENTITY USA_EXR  = 1

DLOG(DEU_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(DEU_DD$(-1))  - LOG(DEU_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(DEU_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(DEU_HIC)  - DEU_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * DEU_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * DEU_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(DEU_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(DEU_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(DEU_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(DEU_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(DEU_MTD)  + 0.4 * (DEU_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (DEU_YER$ / DEU_YFT$  - DEU_YER$(-1) / DEU_YFT$(-1))

DEU_YED  = DEU_YED(-1) * DEU_HIC / DEU_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY DEU_XTN$  = DEU_XTD$ * DEU_XTR$

@IDENTITY DEU_YEN$  = DEU_YER$ * DEU_YED / DEU_EXR * @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY DEU_MTN$  = DEU_MTR$ * DEU_MTD / DEU_EXR  * @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY DEU_YER$  = DEU_DD$  + DEU_XTR$  - DEU_MTR$

@IDENTITY DEU_GDI$  = DEU_DD$  + DEU_XTN$  / ((DEU_YEN$  - DEU_XTN$  + DEU_MTN$)  / (DEU_YER$  - DEU_XTR$  + DEU_MTR$))  - DEU_MTN$  / ((DEU_YEN$  - DEU_XTN$  + DEU_MTN$)  / (DEU_YER$  - DEU_XTR$  + DEU_MTR$))

DLOG(DEU_MTD)  = (1  - DEU_OMS) * ( DLOG(DEU_CMUD)  + DLOG(DEU_EXR) )  + DEU_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(DEU_EXR) )

DLOG(DEU_XTD$)  = (1  - DEU_OXS) * DLOG(DEU_XTDNO$)  + DEU_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

DEU_INFT  = 0.95 * DEU_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

DEU_OXS  = DEU_OXS(-1)

DEU_OMS  = DEU_OMS(-1)

DEU_CXS  = DEU_CXS(-1)

DEU_LOCK  = 0

D(DEU_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(DEU_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (DEU_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(DEU_YFT$) = (1 - DEU_ALPHA) * DLOG(DEU_POPWA)  + D(DEU_TECHL)  + DEU_ALPHA * (DLOG(DEU_EC)  + D(DEU_EFF) )

LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02182050169 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

@IDENTITY DEU_INT  = DEU_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(DEU_XTR$)  = DLOG(DEU_WDR)  + (1  - DEU_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(DEU_XTDNO$  / DEU_CXUD) )

DLOG(DEU_MTR$) = -0.173879887369124 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(DEU_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(DEU_DD$( - 1) + DEU_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(DEU_CMUD( - 1)*DEU_EXR( - 1)/DEU_YED( - 1))) + 1.17428747533481*0.308348050767945*DLOG(DEU_XTR$) + 2.31906458488044*0.173941495515681*DLOG(DEU_DD$)
@INNOV DEU_MTR$  0.00725053150242769

DEU_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * DEU_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * DEU_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * DEU_OILC

DLOG(DEU_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(DEU_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(DEU_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(DEU_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(DEU_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * DEU_EXR / DEU_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * DEU_EXR(-1) / DEU_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * DEU_EXR(-2) / DEU_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * DEU_EXR(-3) / DEU_HIC(-3))  - (DEU_EFF - DEU_EFF(-1) )

DEU_COALC  = DEU_COALC(-1) * (DEU_EC / DEU_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

DEU_GASC  = DEU_GASC(-1) * (DEU_EC / DEU_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

DEU_RC  = DEU_RC(-1) * (DEU_EC / DEU_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

DEU_OILC  = DEU_EC  - DEU_COALC  - DEU_RC  - DEU_GASC

@IDENTITY DEU_EXR  = EMU_EXR

DLOG(FRA_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(FRA_DD$(-1))  - LOG(FRA_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(FRA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(FRA_HIC)  - FRA_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * FRA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * FRA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(FRA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(FRA_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(FRA_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(FRA_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(FRA_MTD)  + 0.4 * (FRA_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (FRA_YER$ / FRA_YFT$  - FRA_YER$(-1) / FRA_YFT$(-1))

FRA_YED  = FRA_YED(-1) * FRA_HIC / FRA_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY FRA_XTN$  = FRA_XTD$ * FRA_XTR$

@IDENTITY FRA_YEN$  = FRA_YER$ * FRA_YED / FRA_EXR * @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY FRA_MTN$  = FRA_MTR$ * FRA_MTD / FRA_EXR  * @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY FRA_YER$  = FRA_DD$  + FRA_XTR$  - FRA_MTR$

@IDENTITY FRA_GDI$  = FRA_DD$  + FRA_XTN$  / ((FRA_YEN$  - FRA_XTN$  + FRA_MTN$)  / (FRA_YER$  - FRA_XTR$  + FRA_MTR$))  - FRA_MTN$  / ((FRA_YEN$  - FRA_XTN$  + FRA_MTN$)  / (FRA_YER$  - FRA_XTR$  + FRA_MTR$))

DLOG(FRA_MTD)  = (1  - FRA_OMS) * ( DLOG(FRA_CMUD)  + DLOG(FRA_EXR) )  + FRA_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(FRA_EXR) )

DLOG(FRA_XTD$)  = (1  - FRA_OXS) * DLOG(FRA_XTDNO$)  + FRA_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

FRA_INFT  = 0.95 * FRA_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

FRA_OXS  = FRA_OXS(-1)

FRA_OMS  = FRA_OMS(-1)

FRA_CXS  = FRA_CXS(-1)

FRA_LOCK  = 0

D(FRA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(FRA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (FRA_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(FRA_YFT$) = (1 - FRA_ALPHA) * DLOG(FRA_POPWA)  + D(FRA_TECHL)  + FRA_ALPHA * (DLOG(FRA_EC)  + D(FRA_EFF) )

FRA_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * FRA_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * FRA_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * FRA_OILC

DLOG(FRA_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(FRA_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(FRA_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(FRA_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(FRA_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * FRA_EXR / FRA_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * FRA_EXR(-1) / FRA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * FRA_EXR(-2) / FRA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * FRA_EXR(-3) / FRA_HIC(-3))  - (FRA_EFF - FRA_EFF(-1) )

FRA_COALC  = FRA_COALC(-1) * (FRA_EC / FRA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

FRA_GASC  = FRA_GASC(-1) * (FRA_EC / FRA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

FRA_RC  = FRA_RC(-1) * (FRA_EC / FRA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

FRA_OILC  = FRA_EC  - FRA_COALC  - FRA_RC  - FRA_GASC

@IDENTITY FRA_EXR  = EMU_EXR

DLOG(GBR_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(GBR_DD$(-1))  - LOG(GBR_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(GBR_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(GBR_HIC)  - GBR_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * GBR_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * GBR_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(GBR_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(GBR_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(GBR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(GBR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(GBR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (GBR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (GBR_YER$ / GBR_YFT$  - GBR_YER$(-1) / GBR_YFT$(-1))

GBR_YED  = GBR_YED(-1) * GBR_HIC / GBR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY GBR_XTN$  = GBR_XTD$ * GBR_XTR$

@IDENTITY GBR_YEN$  = GBR_YER$ * GBR_YED / GBR_EXR * @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY GBR_MTN$  = GBR_MTR$ * GBR_MTD / GBR_EXR  * @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY GBR_YER$  = GBR_DD$  + GBR_XTR$  - GBR_MTR$

@IDENTITY GBR_GDI$  = GBR_DD$  + GBR_XTN$  / ((GBR_YEN$  - GBR_XTN$  + GBR_MTN$)  / (GBR_YER$  - GBR_XTR$  + GBR_MTR$))  - GBR_MTN$  / ((GBR_YEN$  - GBR_XTN$  + GBR_MTN$)  / (GBR_YER$  - GBR_XTR$  + GBR_MTR$))

DLOG(GBR_MTD)  = (1  - GBR_OMS) * ( DLOG(GBR_CMUD)  + DLOG(GBR_EXR) )  + GBR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(GBR_EXR) )

DLOG(GBR_XTD$)  = (1  - GBR_OXS) * DLOG(GBR_XTDNO$)  + GBR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

GBR_INFT  = 0.95 * GBR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

GBR_OXS  = GBR_OXS(-1)

GBR_OMS  = GBR_OMS(-1)

GBR_CXS  = GBR_CXS(-1)

GBR_LOCK  = 0

D(GBR_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(GBR_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (GBR_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(GBR_YFT$) = (1 - GBR_ALPHA) * DLOG(GBR_POPWA)  + D(GBR_TECHL)  + GBR_ALPHA * (DLOG(GBR_EC)  + D(GBR_EFF) )

@IDENTITY LOG(GBR_EFEX)  =  - LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0002067336172 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 5.867906352E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + LOG(KGZ_EXR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015"))  + 3.883916592E-05 * LOG(LAO_EXR / @ELEM(LAO_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004134180367 * LOG(MAC_EXR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.002997545933 * LOG(MYS_EXR / @IDENTITY GBR_INT  = GBR_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(GBR_XTR$)  = DLOG(GBR_WDR)  + (1  - GBR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(GBR_XTDNO$  / GBR_CXUD) )

DLOG(GBR_MTR$) = -0.21946578642263 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(GBR_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(GBR_DD$( - 1) + GBR_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(GBR_CMUD( - 1)*GBR_EXR( - 1)/GBR_YED( - 1))) + 0.952502109831947*0.308348050767945*DLOG(GBR_XTR$) + 3.44268653196758*0.173941495515681*DLOG(GBR_DD$)
@INNOV GBR_MTR$  0.00715638562265149

GBR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * GBR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * GBR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * GBR_OILC

DLOG(GBR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(GBR_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(GBR_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(GBR_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(GBR_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * GBR_EXR / GBR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * GBR_EXR(-1) / GBR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * GBR_EXR(-2) / GBR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * GBR_EXR(-3) / GBR_HIC(-3))  - (GBR_EFF - GBR_EFF(-1) )

GBR_COALC  = GBR_COALC(-1) * (GBR_EC / GBR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

GBR_GASC  = GBR_GASC(-1) * (GBR_EC / GBR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

GBR_RC  = GBR_RC(-1) * (GBR_EC / GBR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

GBR_OILC  = GBR_EC  - GBR_COALC  - GBR_RC  - GBR_GASC

GBR_EXR  = GBR_EXR(-1) * ( ( (GBR_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (GBR_INT  - USA_INT)  - (GBR_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(ITA_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(ITA_DD$(-1))  - LOG(ITA_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(ITA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(ITA_HIC)  - ITA_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * ITA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * ITA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(ITA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(ITA_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(ITA_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(ITA_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(ITA_MTD)  + 0.4 * (ITA_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (ITA_YER$ / ITA_YFT$  - ITA_YER$(-1) / ITA_YFT$(-1))

ITA_YED  = ITA_YED(-1) * ITA_HIC / ITA_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY ITA_XTN$  = ITA_XTD$ * ITA_XTR$

@IDENTITY ITA_YEN$  = ITA_YER$ * ITA_YED / ITA_EXR * @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY ITA_MTN$  = ITA_MTR$ * ITA_MTD / ITA_EXR  * @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY ITA_YER$  = ITA_DD$  + ITA_XTR$  - ITA_MTR$

@IDENTITY ITA_GDI$  = ITA_DD$  + ITA_XTN$  / ((ITA_YEN$  - ITA_XTN$  + ITA_MTN$)  / (ITA_YER$  - ITA_XTR$  + ITA_MTR$))  - ITA_MTN$  / ((ITA_YEN$  - ITA_XTN$  + ITA_MTN$)  / (ITA_YER$  - ITA_XTR$  + ITA_MTR$))

DLOG(ITA_MTD)  = (1  - ITA_OMS) * ( DLOG(ITA_CMUD)  + DLOG(ITA_EXR) )  + ITA_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(ITA_EXR) )

DLOG(ITA_XTD$)  = (1  - ITA_OXS) * DLOG(ITA_XTDNO$)  + ITA_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

ITA_INFT  = 0.95 * ITA_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

ITA_OXS  = ITA_OXS(-1)

ITA_OMS  = ITA_OMS(-1)

ITA_CXS  = ITA_CXS(-1)

ITA_LOCK  = 0

D(ITA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(ITA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (ITA_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(ITA_YFT$) = (1 - ITA_ALPHA) * DLOG(ITA_POPWA)  + D(ITA_TECHL)  + ITA_ALPHA * (DLOG(ITA_EC)  + D(ITA_EFF) )

@IDENTITY LOG(ITA_EFEX)  =  - LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015"))  + 2.652762741E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0001689686737 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + @IDENTITY ITA_INT  = ITA_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(ITA_XTR$)  = DLOG(ITA_WDR)  + (1  - ITA_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(ITA_XTDNO$  / ITA_CXUD) )

DLOG(ITA_MTR$) = -0.214437527368532 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(ITA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(ITA_DD$( - 1) + ITA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(ITA_CMUD( - 1)*ITA_EXR( - 1)/ITA_YED( - 1))) + 1.09945063225858*0.308348050767945*DLOG(ITA_XTR$) + 3.54078933983182*0.173941495515681*DLOG(ITA_DD$)
@INNOV ITA_MTR$  0.00847021966459778

ITA_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * ITA_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * ITA_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * ITA_OILC

DLOG(ITA_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(ITA_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(ITA_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(ITA_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(ITA_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * ITA_EXR / ITA_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * ITA_EXR(-1) / ITA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * ITA_EXR(-2) / ITA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * ITA_EXR(-3) / ITA_HIC(-3))  - (ITA_EFF - ITA_EFF(-1) )

ITA_COALC  = ITA_COALC(-1) * (ITA_EC / ITA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

ITA_GASC  = ITA_GASC(-1) * (ITA_EC / ITA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

ITA_RC  = ITA_RC(-1) * (ITA_EC / ITA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

ITA_OILC  = ITA_EC  - ITA_COALC  - ITA_RC  - ITA_GASC

@IDENTITY ITA_EXR  = EMU_EXR

DLOG(NLD_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(NLD_DD$(-1))  - LOG(NLD_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(NLD_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(NLD_HIC)  - NLD_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * NLD_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * NLD_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(NLD_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(NLD_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(NLD_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(NLD_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(NLD_MTD)  + 0.4 * (NLD_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (NLD_YER$ / NLD_YFT$  - NLD_YER$(-1) / NLD_YFT$(-1))

NLD_YED  = NLD_YED(-1) * NLD_HIC / NLD_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY NLD_XTN$  = NLD_XTD$ * NLD_XTR$

@IDENTITY NLD_YEN$  = NLD_YER$ * NLD_YED / NLD_EXR * @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY NLD_MTN$  = NLD_MTR$ * NLD_MTD / NLD_EXR  * @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY NLD_YER$  = NLD_DD$  + NLD_XTR$  - NLD_MTR$

@IDENTITY NLD_GDI$  = NLD_DD$  + NLD_XTN$  / ((NLD_YEN$  - NLD_XTN$  + NLD_MTN$)  / (NLD_YER$  - NLD_XTR$  + NLD_MTR$))  - NLD_MTN$  / ((NLD_YEN$  - NLD_XTN$  + NLD_MTN$)  / (NLD_YER$  - NLD_XTR$  + NLD_MTR$))

DLOG(NLD_MTD)  = (1  - NLD_OMS) * ( DLOG(NLD_CMUD)  + DLOG(NLD_EXR) )  + NLD_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(NLD_EXR) )

DLOG(NLD_XTD$)  = (1  - NLD_OXS) * DLOG(NLD_XTDNO$)  + NLD_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

NLD_INFT  = 0.95 * NLD_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

NLD_OXS  = NLD_OXS(-1)

NLD_OMS  = NLD_OMS(-1)

NLD_CXS  = NLD_CXS(-1)

NLD_LOCK  = 0

D(NLD_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(NLD_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (NLD_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(NLD_YFT$) = (1 - NLD_ALPHA) * DLOG(NLD_POPWA)  + D(NLD_TECHL)  + NLD_ALPHA * (DLOG(NLD_EC)  + D(NLD_EFF) )

@IDENTITY LOG(NLD_EFEX)  =  - LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.669894962E-05 * LOG(AFG_EXR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015"))  + 8.35815283E-05 * LOG(ARM_EXR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.004920269176 * LOG(AUS_EXR / @ELEM(AUS_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0004149914785 * LOG(AZE_EXR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015"))  + 0.0007411625237 * LOG(BGD_EXR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015"))  + 4.940882326E-06 * @IDENTITY NLD_INT  = NLD_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(NLD_XTR$)  = DLOG(NLD_WDR)  + (1  - NLD_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(NLD_XTDNO$  / NLD_CXUD) )

DLOG(NLD_MTR$) = -0.109233745855374 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(NLD_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(NLD_DD$( - 1) + NLD_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(NLD_CMUD( - 1)*NLD_EXR( - 1)/NLD_YED( - 1))) + 1.14060189110017*0.308348050767945*DLOG(NLD_XTR$) + 1.23376789761551*0.173941495515681*DLOG(NLD_DD$)
@INNOV NLD_MTR$  0.0407805666310919

NLD_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * NLD_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * NLD_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * NLD_OILC

DLOG(NLD_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(NLD_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(NLD_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(NLD_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(NLD_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * NLD_EXR / NLD_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * NLD_EXR(-1) / NLD_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * NLD_EXR(-2) / NLD_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * NLD_EXR(-3) / NLD_HIC(-3))  - (NLD_EFF - NLD_EFF(-1) )

NLD_COALC  = NLD_COALC(-1) * (NLD_EC / NLD_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

NLD_GASC  = NLD_GASC(-1) * (NLD_EC / NLD_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

NLD_RC  = NLD_RC(-1) * (NLD_EC / NLD_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

NLD_OILC  = NLD_EC  - NLD_COALC  - NLD_RC  - NLD_GASC

@IDENTITY NLD_EXR  = EMU_EXR

DLOG(IRL_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(IRL_DD$(-1))  - LOG(IRL_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(IRL_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(IRL_HIC)  - IRL_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * IRL_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * IRL_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(IRL_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(IRL_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(IRL_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(IRL_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IRL_MTD)  + 0.4 * (IRL_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (IRL_YER$ / IRL_YFT$  - IRL_YER$(-1) / IRL_YFT$(-1))

IRL_YED  = IRL_YED(-1) * IRL_HIC / IRL_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY IRL_XTN$  = IRL_XTD$ * IRL_XTR$

@IDENTITY IRL_YEN$  = IRL_YER$ * IRL_YED / IRL_EXR * @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY IRL_MTN$  = IRL_MTR$ * IRL_MTD / IRL_EXR  * @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY IRL_YER$  = IRL_DD$  + IRL_XTR$  - IRL_MTR$

@IDENTITY IRL_GDI$  = IRL_DD$  + IRL_XTN$  / ((IRL_YEN$  - IRL_XTN$  + IRL_MTN$)  / (IRL_YER$  - IRL_XTR$  + IRL_MTR$))  - IRL_MTN$  / ((IRL_YEN$  - IRL_XTN$  + IRL_MTN$)  / (IRL_YER$  - IRL_XTR$  + IRL_MTR$))

DLOG(IRL_MTD)  = (1  - IRL_OMS) * ( DLOG(IRL_CMUD)  + DLOG(IRL_EXR) )  + IRL_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IRL_EXR) )

DLOG(IRL_XTD$)  = (1  - IRL_OXS) * DLOG(IRL_XTDNO$)  + IRL_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

IRL_INFT  = 0.95 * IRL_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

IRL_OXS  = IRL_OXS(-1)

IRL_OMS  = IRL_OMS(-1)

IRL_CXS  = IRL_CXS(-1)

IRL_LOCK  = 0

D(IRL_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(IRL_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (IRL_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(IRL_YFT$) = (1 - IRL_ALPHA) * DLOG(IRL_POPWA)  + D(IRL_TECHL)  + IRL_ALPHA * (DLOG(IRL_EC)  + D(IRL_EFF) )

@IDENTITY IRL_INT  = IRL_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(IRL_XTR$)  = DLOG(IRL_WDR)  + (1  - IRL_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(IRL_XTDNO$  / IRL_CXUD) )

DLOG(IRL_MTR$) = -0.0602742610537973 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(IRL_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(IRL_DD$( - 1) + IRL_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(IRL_CMUD( - 1)*IRL_EXR( - 1)/IRL_YED( - 1))) + 1.2738027676737*0.308348050767945*DLOG(IRL_XTR$) + 0.774042690783274*0.173941495515681*DLOG(IRL_DD$)
@INNOV IRL_MTR$  0.0811849535951491

IRL_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * IRL_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * IRL_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * IRL_OILC

DLOG(IRL_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(IRL_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(IRL_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(IRL_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(IRL_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * IRL_EXR / IRL_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * IRL_EXR(-1) / IRL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * IRL_EXR(-2) / IRL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * IRL_EXR(-3) / IRL_HIC(-3))  - (IRL_EFF - IRL_EFF(-1) )

IRL_COALC  = IRL_COALC(-1) * (IRL_EC / IRL_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

IRL_GASC  = IRL_GASC(-1) * (IRL_EC / IRL_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

IRL_RC  = IRL_RC(-1) * (IRL_EC / IRL_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

IRL_OILC  = IRL_EC  - IRL_COALC  - IRL_RC  - IRL_GASC

@IDENTITY IRL_EXR  = EMU_EXR

DLOG(CHE_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(CHE_DD$(-1))  - LOG(CHE_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(CHE_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(CHE_HIC)  - CHE_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * CHE_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * CHE_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(CHE_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(CHE_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(CHE_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(CHE_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(CHE_MTD)  + 0.4 * (CHE_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (CHE_YER$ / CHE_YFT$  - CHE_YER$(-1) / CHE_YFT$(-1))

CHE_YED  = CHE_YED(-1) * CHE_HIC / CHE_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY CHE_XTN$  = CHE_XTD$ * CHE_XTR$

@IDENTITY CHE_YEN$  = CHE_YER$ * CHE_YED / CHE_EXR * @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY CHE_MTN$  = CHE_MTR$ * CHE_MTD / CHE_EXR  * @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY CHE_YER$  = CHE_DD$  + CHE_XTR$  - CHE_MTR$

@IDENTITY CHE_GDI$  = CHE_DD$  + CHE_XTN$  / ((CHE_YEN$  - CHE_XTN$  + CHE_MTN$)  / (CHE_YER$  - CHE_XTR$  + CHE_MTR$))  - CHE_MTN$  / ((CHE_YEN$  - CHE_XTN$  + CHE_MTN$)  / (CHE_YER$  - CHE_XTR$  + CHE_MTR$))

DLOG(CHE_MTD)  = (1  - CHE_OMS) * ( DLOG(CHE_CMUD)  + DLOG(CHE_EXR) )  + CHE_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(CHE_EXR) )

DLOG(CHE_XTD$)  = (1  - CHE_OXS) * DLOG(CHE_XTDNO$)  + CHE_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

CHE_INFT  = 0.95 * CHE_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

CHE_OXS  = CHE_OXS(-1)

CHE_OMS  = CHE_OMS(-1)

CHE_CXS  = CHE_CXS(-1)

CHE_LOCK  = 0

D(CHE_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(CHE_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (CHE_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(CHE_YFT$) = (1 - CHE_ALPHA) * DLOG(CHE_POPWA)  + D(CHE_TECHL)  + CHE_ALPHA * (DLOG(CHE_EC)  + D(CHE_EFF) )

@IDENTITY CHE_INT  = CHE_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(CHE_XTR$)  = DLOG(CHE_WDR)  + (1  - CHE_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(CHE_XTDNO$  / CHE_CXUD) )

DLOG(CHE_MTR$) = -0.171906766506051 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(CHE_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(CHE_DD$( - 1) + CHE_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(CHE_CMUD( - 1)*CHE_EXR( - 1)/CHE_YED( - 1))) + 1.24983442317127*0.308348050767945*DLOG(CHE_XTR$) + 1.72579400895739*0.173941495515681*DLOG(CHE_DD$)
@INNOV CHE_MTR$  0.0345188986044833

CHE_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * CHE_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * CHE_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * CHE_OILC

DLOG(CHE_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(CHE_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(CHE_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(CHE_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(CHE_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * CHE_EXR / CHE_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * CHE_EXR(-1) / CHE_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * CHE_EXR(-2) / CHE_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * CHE_EXR(-3) / CHE_HIC(-3))  - (CHE_EFF - CHE_EFF(-1) )

CHE_COALC  = CHE_COALC(-1) * (CHE_EC / CHE_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

CHE_GASC  = CHE_GASC(-1) * (CHE_EC / CHE_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

CHE_RC  = CHE_RC(-1) * (CHE_EC / CHE_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

CHE_OILC  = CHE_EC  - CHE_COALC  - CHE_RC  - CHE_GASC

CHE_EXR  = CHE_EXR(-1) * ( ( (CHE_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1) ) * ((  - 5  * ( (CHE_INT  - USA_INT)  - (CHE_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)

DLOG(TWN_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(TWN_DD$(-1))  - LOG(TWN_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(TWN_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(TWN_HIC)  - TWN_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * TWN_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * TWN_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(TWN_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(TWN_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(TWN_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(TWN_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TWN_MTD)  + 0.4 * (TWN_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (TWN_YER$ / TWN_YFT$  - TWN_YER$(-1) / TWN_YFT$(-1))

TWN_YED  = TWN_YED(-1) * TWN_HIC / TWN_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY TWN_XTN$  = TWN_XTD$ * TWN_XTR$

@IDENTITY TWN_YEN$  = TWN_YER$ * TWN_YED / TWN_EXR * @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY TWN_MTN$  = TWN_MTR$ * TWN_MTD / TWN_EXR  * @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY TWN_YER$  = TWN_DD$  + TWN_XTR$  - TWN_MTR$

@IDENTITY TWN_GDI$  = TWN_DD$  + TWN_XTN$  / ((TWN_YEN$  - TWN_XTN$  + TWN_MTN$)  / (TWN_YER$  - TWN_XTR$  + TWN_MTR$))  - TWN_MTN$  / ((TWN_YEN$  - TWN_XTN$  + TWN_MTN$)  / (TWN_YER$  - TWN_XTR$  + TWN_MTR$))

DLOG(TWN_MTD)  = (1  - TWN_OMS) * ( DLOG(TWN_CMUD)  + DLOG(TWN_EXR) )  + TWN_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TWN_EXR) )

DLOG(TWN_XTD$)  = (1  - TWN_OXS) * DLOG(TWN_XTDNO$)  + TWN_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

TWN_INFT  = 0.95 * TWN_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

TWN_OXS  = TWN_OXS(-1)

TWN_OMS  = TWN_OMS(-1)

TWN_CXS  = TWN_CXS(-1)

TWN_LOCK  = 0

D(TWN_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(TWN_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (TWN_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(TWN_YFT$) = (1 - TWN_ALPHA) * DLOG(TWN_POPWA)  + D(TWN_TECHL)  + TWN_ALPHA * (DLOG(TWN_EC)  + D(TWN_EFF) )

@IDENTITY TWN_INT  = TWN_INT(-1)  + USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1)

DLOG(TWN_XTR$)  = DLOG(TWN_WDR)  + (1  - TWN_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(TWN_XTDNO$  / TWN_CXUD) )

DLOG(TWN_MTR$) = -0.105215276954368 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(TWN_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(TWN_DD$( - 1) + TWN_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(TWN_CMUD( - 1)*TWN_EXR( - 1)/TWN_YED( - 1))) + 1.23569811167481*0.308348050767945*DLOG(TWN_XTR$) + 1.5260173067467*0.173941495515681*DLOG(TWN_DD$)
@INNOV TWN_MTR$  0.0138353342855564

TWN_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * TWN_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * TWN_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * TWN_OILC

DLOG(TWN_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(TWN_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(TWN_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(TWN_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(TWN_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * TWN_EXR / TWN_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * TWN_EXR(-1) / TWN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * TWN_EXR(-2) / TWN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * TWN_EXR(-3) / TWN_HIC(-3))  - (TWN_EFF - TWN_EFF(-1) )

TWN_COALC  = TWN_COALC(-1) * (TWN_EC / TWN_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

TWN_GASC  = TWN_GASC(-1) * (TWN_EC / TWN_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

TWN_RC  = TWN_RC(-1) * (TWN_EC / TWN_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

TWN_OILC  = TWN_EC  - TWN_COALC  - TWN_RC  - TWN_GASC

TWN_EXR  = TWN_EXR(-1) * ( (TWN_INFT  - USA_INFT) / 100  + 1)

DLOG(AFR_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(AFR_DD$(-1))  - LOG(AFR_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(AFR_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(AFR_HIC)  - AFR_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * AFR_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * AFR_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(AFR_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(AFR_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(AFR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(AFR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AFR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (AFR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (AFR_YER$ / AFR_YFT$  - AFR_YER$(-1) / AFR_YFT$(-1))

AFR_YED  = AFR_YED(-1) * AFR_HIC / AFR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY AFR_XTN$  = AFR_XTD$ * AFR_XTR$

@IDENTITY AFR_YEN$  = AFR_YER$ * AFR_YED / AFR_EXR * @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY AFR_MTN$  = AFR_MTR$ * AFR_MTD / AFR_EXR  * @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY AFR_YER$  = AFR_DD$  + AFR_XTR$  - AFR_MTR$

@IDENTITY AFR_GDI$  = AFR_DD$  + AFR_XTN$  / ((AFR_YEN$  - AFR_XTN$  + AFR_MTN$)  / (AFR_YER$  - AFR_XTR$  + AFR_MTR$))  - AFR_MTN$  / ((AFR_YEN$  - AFR_XTN$  + AFR_MTN$)  / (AFR_YER$  - AFR_XTR$  + AFR_MTR$))

DLOG(AFR_MTD)  = (1  - AFR_OMS) * ( DLOG(AFR_CMUD)  + DLOG(AFR_EXR) )  + AFR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AFR_EXR) )

DLOG(AFR_XTD$)  = (1  - AFR_OXS) * DLOG(AFR_XTDNO$)  + AFR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

AFR_INFT  = 0.95 * AFR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

AFR_OXS  = AFR_OXS(-1)

AFR_OMS  = AFR_OMS(-1)

AFR_CXS  = AFR_CXS(-1)

AFR_LOCK  = 0

D(AFR_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(AFR_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (AFR_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(AFR_YFT$) = (1 - AFR_ALPHA) * DLOG(AFR_POPWA)  + D(AFR_TECHL)  + AFR_ALPHA * (DLOG(AFR_EC)  + D(AFR_EFF) )

"2015")))  + 0.01458934049 * LOG(KOR_EXR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015") / (KOR_HIC / @ELEM(KOR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.004691943549 * LOG(RUS_EXR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015") / (RUS_HIC / @ELEM(RUS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.636905738E-05 * LOG(WSM_EXR / @ELEM(WSM_EXR , "2015") / (WSM_HIC / @ELEM(WSM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.008241936589 * LOG(SGP_EXR / @ELEM(SGP_EXR , "2015") / (SGP_HIC / @ELEM(SGP_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002043860305 * LOG(TLS_EXR / @ELEM(TLS_EXR , "2015") / (TLS_HIC / @ELEM(TLS_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.894776477E-06 * LOG(TON_EXR / @ELEM(TON_EXR , "2015") / (TON_HIC / @ELEM(TON_HIC , "2015")))  + 1.448927611E-05 * LOG(UZB_EXR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015") / (UZB_HIC / @ELEM(UZB_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0002909270194 * LOG(VUT_EXR / @ELEM(VUT_EXR , "2015") / (VUT_HIC / @ELEM(VUT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005428751945 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.06366759411 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03257765826 * LOG(GBR_EXR / @ELEM(GBR_EXR , "2015") / (GBR_HIC / @ELEM(GBR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01686712847 * LOG(ITA_EXR / @ELEM(ITA_EXR , "2015") / (ITA_HIC / @ELEM(ITA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02555941456 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.007265694556 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01706520062 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.005059850883 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1961170318 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.08580631792 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.03485601814 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07208469941 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

DLOG(AFR_XTR$)  = DLOG(AFR_WDR)  + (1  - AFR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(AFR_XTDNO$  / AFR_CXUD) )

DLOG(AFR_MTR$) = -0.257302486261672 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(AFR_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(AFR_DD$( - 1) + AFR_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(AFR_CMUD( - 1)*AFR_EXR( - 1)/AFR_YED( - 1))) + 0.850902912647739*0.308348050767945*DLOG(AFR_XTR$) + 3.87105032114367*0.173941495515681*DLOG(AFR_DD$)
@INNOV AFR_MTR$  0.0215579782416612

AFR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * AFR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * AFR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * AFR_OILC

DLOG(AFR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(AFR_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(AFR_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(AFR_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(AFR_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * AFR_EXR / AFR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * AFR_EXR(-1) / AFR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * AFR_EXR(-2) / AFR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * AFR_EXR(-3) / AFR_HIC(-3))  - (AFR_EFF - AFR_EFF(-1) )

AFR_COALC  = AFR_COALC(-1) * (AFR_EC / AFR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

AFR_GASC  = AFR_GASC(-1) * (AFR_EC / AFR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

AFR_RC  = AFR_RC(-1) * (AFR_EC / AFR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

AFR_OILC  = AFR_EC  - AFR_COALC  - AFR_RC  - AFR_GASC

DLOG(AFR_EXR) = LOG(((AFR_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.129164826586091*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC)
@INNOV AFR_EXR  0.0749088910803144

DLOG(EUR_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(EUR_DD$(-1))  - LOG(EUR_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(EUR_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(EUR_HIC)  - EUR_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * EUR_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * EUR_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(EUR_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(EUR_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(EUR_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(EUR_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(EUR_MTD)  + 0.4 * (EUR_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (EUR_YER$ / EUR_YFT$  - EUR_YER$(-1) / EUR_YFT$(-1))

EUR_YED  = EUR_YED(-1) * EUR_HIC / EUR_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY EUR_XTN$  = EUR_XTD$ * EUR_XTR$

@IDENTITY EUR_YEN$  = EUR_YER$ * EUR_YED / EUR_EXR * @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY EUR_MTN$  = EUR_MTR$ * EUR_MTD / EUR_EXR  * @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY EUR_YER$  = EUR_DD$  + EUR_XTR$  - EUR_MTR$

@IDENTITY EUR_GDI$  = EUR_DD$  + EUR_XTN$  / ((EUR_YEN$  - EUR_XTN$  + EUR_MTN$)  / (EUR_YER$  - EUR_XTR$  + EUR_MTR$))  - EUR_MTN$  / ((EUR_YEN$  - EUR_XTN$  + EUR_MTN$)  / (EUR_YER$  - EUR_XTR$  + EUR_MTR$))

DLOG(EUR_MTD)  = (1  - EUR_OMS) * ( DLOG(EUR_CMUD)  + DLOG(EUR_EXR) )  + EUR_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(EUR_EXR) )

DLOG(EUR_XTD$)  = (1  - EUR_OXS) * DLOG(EUR_XTDNO$)  + EUR_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

EUR_INFT  = 0.95 * EUR_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

EUR_OXS  = EUR_OXS(-1)

EUR_OMS  = EUR_OMS(-1)

EUR_CXS  = EUR_CXS(-1)

EUR_LOCK  = 0

D(EUR_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(EUR_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (EUR_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(EUR_YFT$) = (1 - EUR_ALPHA) * DLOG(EUR_POPWA)  + D(EUR_TECHL)  + EUR_ALPHA * (DLOG(EUR_EC)  + D(EUR_EFF) )

"2015")))  + 0.002695252166 * LOG(VNM_EXR / @ELEM(VNM_EXR , "2015") / (VNM_HIC / @ELEM(VNM_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.04826567082 * LOG(USA_EXR / @ELEM(USA_EXR , "2015") / (USA_HIC / @ELEM(USA_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.1790529221 * LOG(DEU_EXR / @ELEM(DEU_EXR , "2015") / (DEU_HIC / @ELEM(DEU_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.07175034835 * LOG(FRA_EXR / @ELEM(FRA_EXR , "2015") / (FRA_HIC / @ELEM(FRA_HIC , "2015")))
