0.05084930298 * LOG(NLD_EXR / @ELEM(NLD_EXR , "2015") / (NLD_HIC / @ELEM(NLD_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01962657348 * LOG(IRL_EXR / @ELEM(IRL_EXR , "2015") / (IRL_HIC / @ELEM(IRL_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01989431323 * LOG(CHE_EXR / @ELEM(CHE_EXR , "2015") / (CHE_HIC / @ELEM(CHE_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.002605727106 * LOG(TWN_EXR / @ELEM(TWN_EXR , "2015") / (TWN_HIC / @ELEM(TWN_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.01174740444 * LOG(AFR_EXR / @ELEM(AFR_EXR , "2015") / (AFR_HIC / @ELEM(AFR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.2955380833 * LOG(EUR_EXR / @ELEM(EUR_EXR , "2015") / (EUR_HIC / @ELEM(EUR_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.0268830388 * LOG(LAT_EXR / @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015") / (LAT_HIC / @ELEM(LAT_HIC , "2015")))  + 0.02839209873 * LOG(MNA_EXR / @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015") / (MNA_HIC / @ELEM(MNA_HIC , "2015")))

DLOG(EUR_XTR$)  = DLOG(EUR_WDR)  + (1  - EUR_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(EUR_XTDNO$  / EUR_CXUD) )

DLOG(EUR_MTR$) = -0.14749424495822 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(EUR_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(EUR_DD$( - 1) + EUR_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(EUR_CMUD( - 1)*EUR_EXR( - 1)/EUR_YED( - 1))) + 1.06039482776553*0.308348050767945*DLOG(EUR_XTR$) + 1.96567653255493*0.173941495515681*DLOG(EUR_DD$)
@INNOV EUR_MTR$  0.00555330309771086

EUR_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * EUR_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * EUR_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * EUR_OILC

DLOG(EUR_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(EUR_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(EUR_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(EUR_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(EUR_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * EUR_EXR / EUR_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * EUR_EXR(-1) / EUR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * EUR_EXR(-2) / EUR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * EUR_EXR(-3) / EUR_HIC(-3))  - (EUR_EFF - EUR_EFF(-1) )

EUR_COALC  = EUR_COALC(-1) * (EUR_EC / EUR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

EUR_GASC  = EUR_GASC(-1) * (EUR_EC / EUR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

EUR_RC  = EUR_RC(-1) * (EUR_EC / EUR_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

EUR_OILC  = EUR_EC  - EUR_COALC  - EUR_RC  - EUR_GASC

@IDENTITY EUR_EXR  = EUR_EXR(-1) * EMU_EXR / EMU_EXR(-1)

DLOG(LAT_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(LAT_DD$(-1))  - LOG(LAT_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(LAT_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(LAT_HIC)  - LAT_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * LAT_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * LAT_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(LAT_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(LAT_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(LAT_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(LAT_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(LAT_MTD)  + 0.4 * (LAT_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (LAT_YER$ / LAT_YFT$  - LAT_YER$(-1) / LAT_YFT$(-1))

LAT_YED  = LAT_YED(-1) * LAT_HIC / LAT_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY LAT_XTN$  = LAT_XTD$ * LAT_XTR$

@IDENTITY LAT_YEN$  = LAT_YER$ * LAT_YED / LAT_EXR * @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY LAT_MTN$  = LAT_MTR$ * LAT_MTD / LAT_EXR  * @ELEM(LAT_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY LAT_YER$  = LAT_DD$  + LAT_XTR$  - LAT_MTR$

@IDENTITY LAT_GDI$  = LAT_DD$  + LAT_XTN$  / ((LAT_YEN$  - LAT_XTN$  + LAT_MTN$)  / (LAT_YER$  - LAT_XTR$  + LAT_MTR$))  - LAT_MTN$  / ((LAT_YEN$  - LAT_XTN$  + LAT_MTN$)  / (LAT_YER$  - LAT_XTR$  + LAT_MTR$))

DLOG(LAT_MTD)  = (1  - LAT_OMS) * ( DLOG(LAT_CMUD)  + DLOG(LAT_EXR) )  + LAT_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(LAT_EXR) )

DLOG(LAT_XTD$)  = (1  - LAT_OXS) * DLOG(LAT_XTDNO$)  + LAT_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

LAT_INFT  = 0.95 * LAT_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

LAT_OXS  = LAT_OXS(-1)

LAT_OMS  = LAT_OMS(-1)

LAT_CXS  = LAT_CXS(-1)

LAT_LOCK  = 0

D(LAT_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(LAT_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (LAT_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(LAT_YFT$) = (1 - LAT_ALPHA) * DLOG(LAT_POPWA)  + D(LAT_TECHL)  + LAT_ALPHA * (DLOG(LAT_EC)  + D(LAT_EFF) )

DLOG(LAT_XTR$)  = DLOG(LAT_WDR)  + (1  - LAT_CXS) * (-0.294971888299424 * DLOG(LAT_XTDNO$  / LAT_CXUD) )

DLOG(LAT_MTR$) = -0.250775621156779 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(LAT_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(LAT_DD$( - 1) + LAT_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(LAT_CMUD( - 1)*LAT_EXR( - 1)/LAT_YED( - 1))) + 0.847344894867567*0.308348050767945*DLOG(LAT_XTR$) + 3.67225716612493*0.173941495515681*DLOG(LAT_DD$)
@INNOV LAT_MTR$  0.0322005930401567

LAT_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * LAT_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * LAT_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * LAT_OILC

DLOG(LAT_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(LAT_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(LAT_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(LAT_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(LAT_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * LAT_EXR / LAT_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * LAT_EXR(-1) / LAT_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * LAT_EXR(-2) / LAT_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * LAT_EXR(-3) / LAT_HIC(-3))  - (LAT_EFF - LAT_EFF(-1) )

LAT_COALC  = LAT_COALC(-1) * (LAT_EC / LAT_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

LAT_GASC  = LAT_GASC(-1) * (LAT_EC / LAT_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

LAT_RC  = LAT_RC(-1) * (LAT_EC / LAT_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

LAT_OILC  = LAT_EC  - LAT_COALC  - LAT_RC  - LAT_GASC

DLOG(LAT_EXR) = LOG(((LAT_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.146488372426753*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC)
@INNOV LAT_EXR  0.0642769657404492

DLOG(MNA_DD$)  =  - 0.1 * (LOG(MNA_DD$(-1))  - LOG(MNA_YFT$(-1) ) ) + 0.5 * (DLOG(MNA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(MNA_HIC)  - MNA_INFT  / 100 )  - 0.239704  * MNA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * MNA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(MNA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(MNA_YER$(-1)) )

DLOG(MNA_HIC)  = 0.5 * DLOG(MNA_HIC(-1))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MNA_MTD)  + 0.4 * (MNA_INFT / 100)  + 0.375 * (MNA_YER$ / MNA_YFT$  - MNA_YER$(-1) / MNA_YFT$(-1))

MNA_YED  = MNA_YED(-1) * MNA_HIC / MNA_HIC(-1)

@IDENTITY MNA_XTN$  = MNA_XTD$ * MNA_XTR$

@IDENTITY MNA_YEN$  = MNA_YER$ * MNA_YED / MNA_EXR * @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY MNA_MTN$  = MNA_MTR$ * MNA_MTD / MNA_EXR  * @ELEM(MNA_EXR , "2015")

@IDENTITY MNA_YER$  = MNA_DD$  + MNA_XTR$  - MNA_MTR$

@IDENTITY MNA_GDI$  = MNA_DD$  + MNA_XTN$  / ((MNA_YEN$  - MNA_XTN$  + MNA_MTN$)  / (MNA_YER$  - MNA_XTR$  + MNA_MTR$))  - MNA_MTN$  / ((MNA_YEN$  - MNA_XTN$  + MNA_MTN$)  / (MNA_YER$  - MNA_XTR$  + MNA_MTR$))

DLOG(MNA_MTD)  = (1  - MNA_OMS) * ( DLOG(MNA_CMUD)  + DLOG(MNA_EXR) )  + MNA_OMS * ( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MNA_EXR) )

DLOG(MNA_XTD$)  = (1  - MNA_OXS) * DLOG(MNA_XTDNO$)  + MNA_OXS * DLOG(WLD_POIL)

MNA_INFT  = 0.95 * MNA_INFT(-1)  + 0.05 * 2

MNA_OXS  = MNA_OXS(-1)

MNA_OMS  = MNA_OMS(-1)

MNA_CXS  = MNA_CXS(-1)

MNA_LOCK  = 0

D(MNA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(MNA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (MNA_TECHL(-1))  - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )

DLOG(MNA_YFT$) = (1 - MNA_ALPHA) * DLOG(MNA_POPWA)  + D(MNA_TECHL)  + MNA_ALPHA * (DLOG(MNA_EC)  + D(MNA_EFF) )

DLOG(MNA_MTR$) = -0.192123409136437 +- 0.152986408545611*(LOG(MNA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(MNA_DD$( - 1) + MNA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.0879572709820191*LOG(MNA_CMUD( - 1)*MNA_EXR( - 1)/MNA_YED( - 1))) + 1.05018590712276*0.308348050767945*DLOG(MNA_XTR$) + 2.41530169832086*0.173941495515681*DLOG(MNA_DD$)
@INNOV MNA_MTR$  0.0282306071565197

MNA_CO2  = 95.9924025698793 * MNA_COALC  + 57.1898042275623 * MNA_GASC  + 67.3944990593688 * MNA_OILC

DLOG(MNA_EC) = 0.5 * DLOG(MNA_YER$)  + 0.25 * DLOG(MNA_YER$(-1))  + 0.15 * DLOG(MNA_YER$(-2))  + 0.1 * DLOG(MNA_YER$(-3))  - 0.5 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE * MNA_EXR / MNA_HIC)  - 0.25 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-1) * MNA_EXR(-1) / MNA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-2) * MNA_EXR(-2) / MNA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1 * 0.146545463115108 * DLOG(WLD_PE(-3) * MNA_EXR(-3) / MNA_HIC(-3))  - (MNA_EFF - MNA_EFF(-1) )

MNA_COALC  = MNA_COALC(-1) * (MNA_EC / MNA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

MNA_GASC  = MNA_GASC(-1) * (MNA_EC / MNA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  - 0.4) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(- - 0.4 / 3))

MNA_RC  = MNA_RC(-1) * (MNA_EC / MNA_EC(-1)) * ( (WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3))  * ( (WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1))^(  -  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1))^(-  - 0.4 / 3) ) * ( (WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1))^(-0.4))

MNA_OILC  = MNA_EC  - MNA_COALC  - MNA_RC  - MNA_GASC

@IDENTITY MNA_EXR  = MNA_EXR(-1)

SSW_CO2  =  + AFG_CO2  + BGD_CO2  + BTN_CO2  + IND_CO2  + IRN_CO2  + MDV_CO2  + NPL_CO2  + PAK_CO2  + LKA_CO2  + TUR_CO2

SSW_YER$  =  + AFG_YER$  + BGD_YER$  + BTN_YER$  + IND_YER$  + IRN_YER$  + MDV_YER$  + NPL_YER$  + PAK_YER$  + LKA_YER$  + TUR_YER$

SSW_XTR$  =  + AFG_XTR$  + BGD_XTR$  + BTN_XTR$  + IND_XTR$  + IRN_XTR$  + MDV_XTR$  + NPL_XTR$  + PAK_XTR$  + LKA_XTR$  + TUR_XTR$

SSW_LNN  =  + AFG_LNN  + BGD_LNN  + BTN_LNN  + IND_LNN  + IRN_LNN  + MDV_LNN  + NPL_LNN  + PAK_LNN  + LKA_LNN  + TUR_LNN

SSW_CAN  =  + AFG_CAN  + BGD_CAN  + BTN_CAN  + IND_CAN  + IRN_CAN  + MDV_CAN  + NPL_CAN  + PAK_CAN  + LKA_CAN  + TUR_CAN

SSW_LFN  =  + AFG_LFN  + BGD_LFN  + BTN_LFN  + IND_LFN  + IRN_LFN  + MDV_LFN  + NPL_LFN  + PAK_LFN  + LKA_LFN  + TUR_LFN

SSW_PCR$  =  + AFG_PCR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + BGD_PCR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015")  + BTN_PCR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015")  + IND_PCR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015")  + IRN_PCR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015")  + MDV_PCR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015")  + NPL_PCR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015")  + PAK_PCR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015")  + LKA_PCR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015")  + TUR_PCR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015")

SSW_GCR$  =  + AFG_GCR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + BGD_GCR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015")  + BTN_GCR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015")  + IND_GCR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015")  + IRN_GCR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015")  + MDV_GCR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015")  + NPL_GCR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015")  + PAK_GCR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015")  + LKA_GCR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015")  + TUR_GCR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015")

SSW_IGR$  =  + AFG_IGR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + BGD_IGR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015")  + BTN_IGR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015")  + IND_IGR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015")  + IRN_IGR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015")  + MDV_IGR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015")  + NPL_IGR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015")  + PAK_IGR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015")  + LKA_IGR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015")  + TUR_IGR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015")

SSW_IPR$  =  + AFG_IPR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + BGD_IPR / @ELEM(BGD_EXR , "2015")  + BTN_IPR / @ELEM(BTN_EXR , "2015")  + IND_IPR / @ELEM(IND_EXR , "2015")  + IRN_IPR / @ELEM(IRN_EXR , "2015")  + MDV_IPR / @ELEM(MDV_EXR , "2015")  + NPL_IPR / @ELEM(NPL_EXR , "2015")  + PAK_IPR / @ELEM(PAK_EXR , "2015")  + LKA_IPR / @ELEM(LKA_EXR , "2015")  + TUR_IPR / @ELEM(TUR_EXR , "2015")

SSW_GDN$  =  + AFG_GDN / AFG_EXR  + BGD_GDN / BGD_EXR  + BTN_GDN / BTN_EXR  + IND_GDN / IND_EXR  + IRN_GDN / IRN_EXR  + MDV_GDN / MDV_EXR  + NPL_GDN / NPL_EXR  + PAK_GDN / PAK_EXR  + LKA_GDN / LKA_EXR  + TUR_GDN / TUR_EXR

SSW_POOR55  =  + AFG_HEAD55 / 100 * AFG_POPT  + BGD_HEAD55 / 100 * BGD_POPT  + BTN_HEAD55 / 100 * BTN_POPT  + IND_HEAD55 / 100 * IND_POPT  + IRN_HEAD55 / 100 * IRN_POPT  + MDV_HEAD55 / 100 * MDV_POPT  + NPL_HEAD55 / 100 * NPL_POPT  + PAK_HEAD55 / 100 * PAK_POPT  + LKA_HEAD55 / 100 * LKA_POPT  + TUR_HEAD55 / 100 * TUR_POPT

SSW_INFL  = (  + AFG_HIC / AFG_HIC(-1) * AFG_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + BGD_HIC / BGD_HIC(-1) * BGD_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + BTN_HIC / BTN_HIC(-1) * BTN_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + IND_HIC / IND_HIC(-1) * IND_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + IRN_HIC / IRN_HIC(-1) * IRN_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + MDV_HIC / MDV_HIC(-1) * MDV_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + NPL_HIC / NPL_HIC(-1) * NPL_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + PAK_HIC / PAK_HIC(-1) * PAK_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + LKA_HIC / LKA_HIC(-1) * LKA_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  + TUR_HIC / TUR_HIC(-1) * TUR_YEN$ / SSW_YEN$  - 1) * 100

SSW_LNNF  =  + AFG_LNNF  + BGD_LNNF  + BTN_LNNF  + IND_LNNF  + IRN_LNNF  + MDV_LNNF  + NPL_LNNF  + PAK_LNNF  + LKA_LNNF  + TUR_LNNF

SSW_GINI_DISP_AVE  = (  + AFG_GINI_DISP  + BGD_GINI_DISP  + BTN_GINI_DISP  + IND_GINI_DISP  + IRN_GINI_DISP  + MDV_GINI_DISP  + NPL_GINI_DISP  + PAK_GINI_DISP  + LKA_GINI_DISP  + TUR_GINI_DISP ) / 10

SSW_GINI_DISP_WGT  = (  + AFG_GINI_DISP * AFG_POPT  + BGD_GINI_DISP * BGD_POPT  + BTN_GINI_DISP * BTN_POPT  + IND_GINI_DISP * IND_POPT  + IRN_GINI_DISP * IRN_POPT  + MDV_GINI_DISP * MDV_POPT  + NPL_GINI_DISP * NPL_POPT  + PAK_GINI_DISP * PAK_POPT  + LKA_GINI_DISP * LKA_POPT  + TUR_GINI_DISP * TUR_POPT ) / SSW_POPT

SSW_GDNRATIO  = SSW_GDN$ / SSW_YEN$ * 100

SSW_GLNRATIO  = SSW_GLN$ / SSW_YEN$ * 100

SSW_CANRATIO  = SSW_CAN / SSW_YEN$ * 100

SSW_URX  = (1 - SSW_LNN / SSW_LFN) * 100

SSW_HEAD19  = SSW_POOR19 / SSW_POPT * 100

SSW_HEAD55  = SSW_POOR55 / SSW_POPT * 100

PAC_CO2  =  + AUS_CO2  + FJI_CO2  + KIR_CO2  + FSM_CO2  + NZL_CO2  + PNG_CO2  + WSM_CO2  + SLB_CO2  + TON_CO2  + VUT_CO2

PAC_INFL  = (  + AUS_HIC / AUS_HIC(-1) * AUS_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + FJI_HIC / FJI_HIC(-1) * FJI_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + KIR_HIC / KIR_HIC(-1) * KIR_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + FSM_HIC / FSM_HIC(-1) * FSM_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + NZL_HIC / NZL_HIC(-1) * NZL_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + PNG_HIC / PNG_HIC(-1) * PNG_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + WSM_HIC / WSM_HIC(-1) * WSM_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + SLB_HIC / SLB_HIC(-1) * SLB_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + TON_HIC / TON_HIC(-1) * TON_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  + VUT_HIC / VUT_HIC(-1) * VUT_YEN$ / PAC_YEN$  - 1) * 100

NCA_POPT  =  + ARM_POPT  + AZE_POPT  + GEO_POPT  + KAZ_POPT  + KGZ_POPT  + RUS_POPT  + TJK_POPT  + TKM_POPT  + UZB_POPT

NCA_POPWA  =  + ARM_POPWA  + AZE_POPWA  + GEO_POPWA  + KAZ_POPWA  + KGZ_POPWA  + RUS_POPWA  + TJK_POPWA  + TKM_POPWA  + UZB_POPWA

NCA_LNN  =  + ARM_LNN  + AZE_LNN  + GEO_LNN  + KAZ_LNN  + KGZ_LNN  + RUS_LNN  + TJK_LNN  + TKM_LNN  + UZB_LNN

NCA_CAN  =  + ARM_CAN  + AZE_CAN  + GEO_CAN  + KAZ_CAN  + KGZ_CAN  + RUS_CAN  + TJK_CAN  + TKM_CAN  + UZB_CAN

NCA_LFN  =  + ARM_LFN  + AZE_LFN  + GEO_LFN  + KAZ_LFN  + KGZ_LFN  + RUS_LFN  + TJK_LFN  + TKM_LFN  + UZB_LFN

NCA_PCR$  =  + ARM_PCR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015")  + AZE_PCR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015")  + GEO_PCR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015")  + KAZ_PCR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015")  + KGZ_PCR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015")  + RUS_PCR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_PCR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")  + TKM_PCR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015")  + UZB_PCR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015")

NCA_GCR$  =  + ARM_GCR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015")  + AZE_GCR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015")  + GEO_GCR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015")  + KAZ_GCR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015")  + KGZ_GCR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015")  + RUS_GCR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_GCR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")  + TKM_GCR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015")  + UZB_GCR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015")

NCA_IGR$  =  + ARM_IGR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015")  + AZE_IGR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015")  + GEO_IGR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015")  + KAZ_IGR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015")  + KGZ_IGR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015")  + RUS_IGR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_IGR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")  + TKM_IGR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015")  + UZB_IGR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015")

NCA_IPR$  =  + ARM_IPR / @ELEM(ARM_EXR , "2015")  + AZE_IPR / @ELEM(AZE_EXR , "2015")  + GEO_IPR / @ELEM(GEO_EXR , "2015")  + KAZ_IPR / @ELEM(KAZ_EXR , "2015")  + KGZ_IPR / @ELEM(KGZ_EXR , "2015")  + RUS_IPR / @ELEM(RUS_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_IPR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")  + TKM_IPR / @ELEM(TKM_EXR , "2015")  + UZB_IPR / @ELEM(UZB_EXR , "2015")

NCA_GDN$  =  + ARM_GDN / ARM_EXR  + AZE_GDN / AZE_EXR  + GEO_GDN / GEO_EXR  + KAZ_GDN / KAZ_EXR  + KGZ_GDN / KGZ_EXR  + RUS_GDN / RUS_EXR  + TJK_GDN / TJK_EXR  + TKM_GDN / TKM_EXR  + UZB_GDN / UZB_EXR

NCA_GLN$  =  + ARM_GLN / ARM_EXR  + AZE_GLN / AZE_EXR  + GEO_GLN / GEO_EXR  + KAZ_GLN / KAZ_EXR  + KGZ_GLN / KGZ_EXR  + RUS_GLN / RUS_EXR  + TJK_GLN / TJK_EXR  + TKM_GLN / TKM_EXR  + UZB_GLN / UZB_EXR

NCA_POOR19  =  + ARM_HEAD19 / 100 * ARM_POPT  + AZE_HEAD19 / 100 * AZE_POPT  + GEO_HEAD19 / 100 * GEO_POPT  + KAZ_HEAD19 / 100 * KAZ_POPT  + KGZ_HEAD19 / 100 * KGZ_POPT  + RUS_HEAD19 / 100 * RUS_POPT  + TJK_HEAD19 / 100 * TJK_POPT  + TKM_HEAD19 / 100 * TKM_POPT  + UZB_HEAD19 / 100 * UZB_POPT

NCA_POOR55  =  + ARM_HEAD55 / 100 * ARM_POPT  + AZE_HEAD55 / 100 * AZE_POPT  + GEO_HEAD55 / 100 * GEO_POPT  + KAZ_HEAD55 / 100 * KAZ_POPT  + KGZ_HEAD55 / 100 * KGZ_POPT  + RUS_HEAD55 / 100 * RUS_POPT  + TJK_HEAD55 / 100 * TJK_POPT  + TKM_HEAD55 / 100 * TKM_POPT  + UZB_HEAD55 / 100 * UZB_POPT

NCA_INFL  = (  + ARM_HIC / ARM_HIC(-1) * ARM_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + AZE_HIC / AZE_HIC(-1) * AZE_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + GEO_HIC / GEO_HIC(-1) * GEO_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + KAZ_HIC / KAZ_HIC(-1) * KAZ_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + KGZ_HIC / KGZ_HIC(-1) * KGZ_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + RUS_HIC / RUS_HIC(-1) * RUS_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + TJK_HIC / TJK_HIC(-1) * TJK_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + TKM_HIC / TKM_HIC(-1) * TKM_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  + UZB_HIC / UZB_HIC(-1) * UZB_YEN$ / NCA_YEN$  - 1) * 100

NCA_LNNF  =  + ARM_LNNF  + AZE_LNNF  + GEO_LNNF  + KAZ_LNNF  + KGZ_LNNF  + RUS_LNNF  + TJK_LNNF  + TKM_LNNF  + UZB_LNNF

NCA_GINI_DISP_AVE  = (  + ARM_GINI_DISP  + AZE_GINI_DISP  + GEO_GINI_DISP  + KAZ_GINI_DISP  + KGZ_GINI_DISP  + RUS_GINI_DISP  + TJK_GINI_DISP  + TKM_GINI_DISP  + UZB_GINI_DISP ) / 9

NCA_GINI_DISP_WGT  = (  + ARM_GINI_DISP * ARM_POPT  + AZE_GINI_DISP * AZE_POPT  + GEO_GINI_DISP * GEO_POPT  + KAZ_GINI_DISP * KAZ_POPT  + KGZ_GINI_DISP * KGZ_POPT  + RUS_GINI_DISP * RUS_POPT  + TJK_GINI_DISP * TJK_POPT  + TKM_GINI_DISP * TKM_POPT  + UZB_GINI_DISP * UZB_POPT ) / NCA_POPT

NCA_PM25_AVE  = (  + ARM_PM25  + AZE_PM25  + GEO_PM25  + KAZ_PM25  + KGZ_PM25  + RUS_PM25  + TJK_PM25  + TKM_PM25  + UZB_PM25 ) / 9

NCA_PM25_WGT  = (  + ARM_PM25 * ARM_POPT  + AZE_PM25 * AZE_POPT  + GEO_PM25 * GEO_POPT  + KAZ_PM25 * KAZ_POPT  + KGZ_PM25 * KGZ_POPT  + RUS_PM25 * RUS_POPT  + TJK_PM25 * TJK_POPT  + TKM_PM25 * TKM_POPT  + UZB_PM25 * UZB_POPT ) / NCA_POPT

NCA_LIVES  =  + ARM_LIVES  + AZE_LIVES  + GEO_LIVES  + KAZ_LIVES  + KGZ_LIVES  + RUS_LIVES  + TJK_LIVES  + TKM_LIVES  + UZB_LIVES

NCA_CLIMLOSS  =  + ARM_CLIMLOSS / ARM_EXR  + AZE_CLIMLOSS / AZE_EXR  + GEO_CLIMLOSS / GEO_EXR  + KAZ_CLIMLOSS / KAZ_EXR  + KGZ_CLIMLOSS / KGZ_EXR  + RUS_CLIMLOSS / RUS_EXR  + TJK_CLIMLOSS / TJK_EXR  + TKM_CLIMLOSS / TKM_EXR  + UZB_CLIMLOSS / UZB_EXR

NCA_GDNRATIO  = NCA_GDN$ / NCA_YEN$ * 100

NCA_GLNRATIO  = NCA_GLN$ / NCA_YEN$ * 100

NCA_CANRATIO  = NCA_CAN / NCA_YEN$ * 100

NCA_URX  = (1 - NCA_LNN / NCA_LFN) * 100

NCA_HEAD19  = NCA_POOR19 / NCA_POPT * 100

NCA_HEAD55  = NCA_POOR55 / NCA_POPT * 100

SEA_CO2  =  + BRN_CO2  + KHM_CO2  + IDN_CO2  + LAO_CO2  + MYS_CO2  + MMR_CO2  + PHL_CO2  + SGP_CO2  + THA_CO2  + TLS_CO2  + VNM_CO2

SEA_INFL  = (  + BRN_HIC / BRN_HIC(-1) * BRN_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + KHM_HIC / KHM_HIC(-1) * KHM_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + IDN_HIC / IDN_HIC(-1) * IDN_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + LAO_HIC / LAO_HIC(-1) * LAO_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + MYS_HIC / MYS_HIC(-1) * MYS_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + MMR_HIC / MMR_HIC(-1) * MMR_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + PHL_HIC / PHL_HIC(-1) * PHL_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + SGP_HIC / SGP_HIC(-1) * SGP_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + THA_HIC / THA_HIC(-1) * THA_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + TLS_HIC / TLS_HIC(-1) * TLS_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  + VNM_HIC / VNM_HIC(-1) * VNM_YEN$ / SEA_YEN$  - 1) * 100

SEA_LNNF  =  + BRN_LNNF  + KHM_LNNF  + IDN_LNNF  + LAO_LNNF  + MYS_LNNF  + MMR_LNNF  + PHL_LNNF  + SGP_LNNF  + THA_LNNF  + TLS_LNNF  + VNM_LNNF

SEA_GINI_DISP_AVE  = (  + BRN_GINI_DISP  + KHM_GINI_DISP  + IDN_GINI_DISP  + LAO_GINI_DISP  + MYS_GINI_DISP  + MMR_GINI_DISP  + PHL_GINI_DISP  + SGP_GINI_DISP  + THA_GINI_DISP  + TLS_GINI_DISP  + VNM_GINI_DISP ) / 11

SEA_GINI_DISP_WGT  = (  + BRN_GINI_DISP * BRN_POPT  + KHM_GINI_DISP * KHM_POPT  + IDN_GINI_DISP * IDN_POPT  + LAO_GINI_DISP * LAO_POPT  + MYS_GINI_DISP * MYS_POPT  + MMR_GINI_DISP * MMR_POPT  + PHL_GINI_DISP * PHL_POPT  + SGP_GINI_DISP * SGP_POPT  + THA_GINI_DISP * THA_POPT  + TLS_GINI_DISP * TLS_POPT  + VNM_GINI_DISP * VNM_POPT ) / SEA_POPT

SEA_HEAD55  = SEA_POOR55 / SEA_POPT * 100

ENE_IGR$  =  + CHN_IGR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015")  + HKG_IGR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015")  + JPN_IGR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015")  + MAC_IGR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015")  + MNG_IGR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015")  + KOR_IGR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015")

ENE_IPR$  =  + CHN_IPR / @ELEM(CHN_EXR , "2015")  + HKG_IPR / @ELEM(HKG_EXR , "2015")  + JPN_IPR / @ELEM(JPN_EXR , "2015")  + MAC_IPR / @ELEM(MAC_EXR , "2015")  + MNG_IPR / @ELEM(MNG_EXR , "2015")  + KOR_IPR / @ELEM(KOR_EXR , "2015")

ENE_GDN$  =  + CHN_GDN / CHN_EXR  + HKG_GDN / HKG_EXR  + JPN_GDN / JPN_EXR  + MAC_GDN / MAC_EXR  + MNG_GDN / MNG_EXR  + KOR_GDN / KOR_EXR

ENE_GLN$  =  + CHN_GLN / CHN_EXR  + HKG_GLN / HKG_EXR  + JPN_GLN / JPN_EXR  + MAC_GLN / MAC_EXR  + MNG_GLN / MNG_EXR  + KOR_GLN / KOR_EXR

ENE_POOR19  =  + CHN_HEAD19 / 100 * CHN_POPT  + HKG_HEAD19 / 100 * HKG_POPT  + JPN_HEAD19 / 100 * JPN_POPT  + MAC_HEAD19 / 100 * MAC_POPT  + MNG_HEAD19 / 100 * MNG_POPT  + KOR_HEAD19 / 100 * KOR_POPT

ENE_POOR55  =  + CHN_HEAD55 / 100 * CHN_POPT  + HKG_HEAD55 / 100 * HKG_POPT  + JPN_HEAD55 / 100 * JPN_POPT  + MAC_HEAD55 / 100 * MAC_POPT  + MNG_HEAD55 / 100 * MNG_POPT  + KOR_HEAD55 / 100 * KOR_POPT

ENE_INFL  = (  + CHN_HIC / CHN_HIC(-1) * CHN_YEN$ / ENE_YEN$  + HKG_HIC / HKG_HIC(-1) * HKG_YEN$ / ENE_YEN$  + JPN_HIC / JPN_HIC(-1) * JPN_YEN$ / ENE_YEN$  + MAC_HIC / MAC_HIC(-1) * MAC_YEN$ / ENE_YEN$  + MNG_HIC / MNG_HIC(-1) * MNG_YEN$ / ENE_YEN$  + KOR_HIC / KOR_HIC(-1) * KOR_YEN$ / ENE_YEN$  - 1) * 100

ENE_LNNF  =  + CHN_LNNF  + HKG_LNNF  + JPN_LNNF  + MAC_LNNF  + MNG_LNNF  + KOR_LNNF

ENE_GINI_DISP_AVE  = (  + CHN_GINI_DISP  + HKG_GINI_DISP  + JPN_GINI_DISP  + MAC_GINI_DISP  + MNG_GINI_DISP  + KOR_GINI_DISP ) / 6

ENE_GINI_DISP_WGT  = (  + CHN_GINI_DISP * CHN_POPT  + HKG_GINI_DISP * HKG_POPT  + JPN_GINI_DISP * JPN_POPT  + MAC_GINI_DISP * MAC_POPT  + MNG_GINI_DISP * MNG_POPT  + KOR_GINI_DISP * KOR_POPT ) / ENE_POPT

ENE_PM25_AVE  = (  + CHN_PM25  + HKG_PM25  + JPN_PM25  + MAC_PM25  + MNG_PM25  + KOR_PM25 ) / 6

ENE_PM25_WGT  = (  + CHN_PM25 * CHN_POPT  + HKG_PM25 * HKG_POPT  + JPN_PM25 * JPN_POPT  + MAC_PM25 * MAC_POPT  + MNG_PM25 * MNG_POPT  + KOR_PM25 * KOR_POPT ) / ENE_POPT

ENE_LIVES  =  + CHN_LIVES  + HKG_LIVES  + JPN_LIVES  + MAC_LIVES  + MNG_LIVES  + KOR_LIVES

ENE_GDNRATIO  = ENE_GDN$ / ENE_YEN$ * 100

ENE_GLNRATIO  = ENE_GLN$ / ENE_YEN$ * 100

ENE_CANRATIO  = ENE_CAN / ENE_YEN$ * 100

ENE_URX  = (1 - ENE_LNN / ENE_LFN) * 100

ENE_HEAD19  = ENE_POOR19 / ENE_POPT * 100

ENE_HEAD55  = ENE_POOR55 / ENE_POPT * 100

NCAXR_POOR19  =  + ARM_HEAD19 / 100 * ARM_POPT  + AZE_HEAD19 / 100 * AZE_POPT  + GEO_HEAD19 / 100 * GEO_POPT  + KAZ_HEAD19 / 100 * KAZ_POPT  + KGZ_HEAD19 / 100 * KGZ_POPT  + TJK_HEAD19 / 100 * TJK_POPT  + TKM_HEAD19 / 100 * TKM_POPT  + UZB_HEAD19 / 100 * UZB_POPT

NCAXR_INFL  = (  + ARM_HIC / ARM_HIC(-1) * ARM_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + AZE_HIC / AZE_HIC(-1) * AZE_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + GEO_HIC / GEO_HIC(-1) * GEO_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + KAZ_HIC / KAZ_HIC(-1) * KAZ_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + KGZ_HIC / KGZ_HIC(-1) * KGZ_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + TJK_HIC / TJK_HIC(-1) * TJK_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + TKM_HIC / TKM_HIC(-1) * TKM_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  + UZB_HIC / UZB_HIC(-1) * UZB_YEN$ / NCAXR_YEN$  - 1) * 100

CSN_INFL  = (  + AFG_HIC / AFG_HIC(-1) * AFG_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + ARM_HIC / ARM_HIC(-1) * ARM_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + AZE_HIC / AZE_HIC(-1) * AZE_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + BGD_HIC / BGD_HIC(-1) * BGD_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + BTN_HIC / BTN_HIC(-1) * BTN_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + KHM_HIC / KHM_HIC(-1) * KHM_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + FJI_HIC / FJI_HIC(-1) * FJI_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + KAZ_HIC / KAZ_HIC(-1) * KAZ_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + KIR_HIC / KIR_HIC(-1) * KIR_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + KGZ_HIC / KGZ_HIC(-1) * KGZ_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + LAO_HIC / LAO_HIC(-1) * LAO_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + MDV_HIC / MDV_HIC(-1) * MDV_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + FSM_HIC / FSM_HIC(-1) * FSM_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + MNG_HIC / MNG_HIC(-1) * MNG_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + MMR_HIC / MMR_HIC(-1) * MMR_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + NPL_HIC / NPL_HIC(-1) * NPL_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + PNG_HIC / PNG_HIC(-1) * PNG_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + WSM_HIC / WSM_HIC(-1) * WSM_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + SLB_HIC / SLB_HIC(-1) * SLB_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + TJK_HIC / TJK_HIC(-1) * TJK_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + TLS_HIC / TLS_HIC(-1) * TLS_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + TON_HIC / TON_HIC(-1) * TON_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + TKM_HIC / TKM_HIC(-1) * TKM_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + UZB_HIC / UZB_HIC(-1) * UZB_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  + VUT_HIC / VUT_HIC(-1) * VUT_YEN$ / CSN_YEN$  - 1) * 100

G20_POOR19  =  + AUS_HEAD19 / 100 * AUS_POPT  + CHN_HEAD19 / 100 * CHN_POPT  + IND_HEAD19 / 100 * IND_POPT  + IDN_HEAD19 / 100 * IDN_POPT  + JPN_HEAD19 / 100 * JPN_POPT  + KOR_HEAD19 / 100 * KOR_POPT  + RUS_HEAD19 / 100 * RUS_POPT  + TUR_HEAD19 / 100 * TUR_POPT

G20_INFL  = (  + AUS_HIC / AUS_HIC(-1) * AUS_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + CHN_HIC / CHN_HIC(-1) * CHN_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + IND_HIC / IND_HIC(-1) * IND_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + IDN_HIC / IDN_HIC(-1) * IDN_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + JPN_HIC / JPN_HIC(-1) * JPN_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + KOR_HIC / KOR_HIC(-1) * KOR_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + RUS_HIC / RUS_HIC(-1) * RUS_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  + TUR_HIC / TUR_HIC(-1) * TUR_YEN$ / G20_YEN$  - 1) * 100

DVG_PM25_AVE  = (  + AFG_PM25  + ARM_PM25  + AZE_PM25  + BGD_PM25  + BTN_PM25  + BRN_PM25  + KHM_PM25  + CHN_PM25  + FJI_PM25  + GEO_PM25  + HKG_PM25  + IND_PM25  + IDN_PM25  + IRN_PM25  + KAZ_PM25  + KIR_PM25  + KGZ_PM25  + LAO_PM25  + MAC_PM25  + MYS_PM25  + MDV_PM25  + FSM_PM25  + MNG_PM25  + MMR_PM25  + NPL_PM25  + PAK_PM25  + PNG_PM25  + PHL_PM25  + KOR_PM25  + RUS_PM25  + WSM_PM25  + SGP_PM25  + SLB_PM25  + LKA_PM25  + TJK_PM25  + THA_PM25  + TLS_PM25  + TON_PM25  + TUR_PM25  + TKM_PM25  + UZB_PM25  + VUT_PM25  + VNM_PM25 ) / 43

DVG_GDNRATIO  = DVG_GDN$ / DVG_YEN$ * 100

DVG_GLNRATIO  = DVG_GLN$ / DVG_YEN$ * 100

DVG_CANRATIO  = DVG_CAN / DVG_YEN$ * 100

DVG_URX  = (1 - DVG_LNN / DVG_LFN) * 100

DVG_HEAD19  = DVG_POOR19 / DVG_POPT * 100

DVG_HEAD55  = DVG_POOR55 / DVG_POPT * 100

LOW_CO2  =  + AFG_CO2  + TJK_CO2

LOW_YER$  =  + AFG_YER$  + TJK_YER$

LOW_XTR$  =  + AFG_XTR$  + TJK_XTR$

LOW_MTR$  =  + AFG_MTR$  + TJK_MTR$

LOW_YEN$  =  + AFG_YEN$  + TJK_YEN$

LOW_YFT$  =  + AFG_YFT$  + TJK_YFT$

LOW_POPT  =  + AFG_POPT  + TJK_POPT

LOW_POPWA  =  + AFG_POPWA  + TJK_POPWA

LOW_LNN  =  + AFG_LNN  + TJK_LNN

LOW_CAN  =  + AFG_CAN  + TJK_CAN

LOW_LFN  =  + AFG_LFN  + TJK_LFN

LOW_PCR$  =  + AFG_PCR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_PCR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")

LOW_GCR$  =  + AFG_GCR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_GCR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")

LOW_IGR$  =  + AFG_IGR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_IGR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")

LOW_IPR$  =  + AFG_IPR / @ELEM(AFG_EXR , "2015")  + TJK_IPR / @ELEM(TJK_EXR , "2015")

LOW_GDN$  =  + AFG_GDN / AFG_EXR  + TJK_GDN / TJK_EXR

LOW_GLN$  =  + AFG_GLN / AFG_EXR  + TJK_GLN / TJK_EXR

LOW_POOR19  =  + AFG_HEAD19 / 100 * AFG_POPT  + TJK_HEAD19 / 100 * TJK_POPT

LOW_POOR55  =  + AFG_HEAD55 / 100 * AFG_POPT  + TJK_HEAD55 / 100 * TJK_POPT

LOW_INFL  = (  + AFG_HIC / AFG_HIC(-1) * AFG_YEN$ / LOW_YEN$  + TJK_HIC / TJK_HIC(-1) * TJK_YEN$ / LOW_YEN$  - 1) * 100

LOW_LNNF  =  + AFG_LNNF  + TJK_LNNF

LOW_GINI_DISP_AVE  = (  + AFG_GINI_DISP  + TJK_GINI_DISP ) / 2

LOW_GINI_DISP_WGT  = (  + AFG_GINI_DISP * AFG_POPT  + TJK_GINI_DISP * TJK_POPT ) / LOW_POPT

LOW_PM25_AVE  = (  + AFG_PM25  + TJK_PM25 ) / 2

LOW_PM25_WGT  = (  + AFG_PM25 * AFG_POPT  + TJK_PM25 * TJK_POPT ) / LOW_POPT

LOW_LIVES  =  + AFG_LIVES  + TJK_LIVES

LOW_CLIMLOSS  =  + AFG_CLIMLOSS / AFG_EXR  + TJK_CLIMLOSS / TJK_EXR

LOW_GDNRATIO  = LOW_GDN$ / LOW_YEN$ * 100

LOW_GLNRATIO  = LOW_GLN$ / LOW_YEN$ * 100

LOW_CANRATIO  = LOW_CAN / LOW_YEN$ * 100

LOW_URX  = (1 - LOW_LNN / LOW_LFN) * 100

LOW_HEAD55  = LOW_POOR55 / LOW_POPT * 100

UPPM_POOR55  =  + ARM_HEAD55 / 100 * ARM_POPT  + AZE_HEAD55 / 100 * AZE_POPT  + CHN_HEAD55 / 100 * CHN_POPT  + FJI_HEAD55 / 100 * FJI_POPT  + GEO_HEAD55 / 100 * GEO_POPT  + IDN_HEAD55 / 100 * IDN_POPT  + IRN_HEAD55 / 100 * IRN_POPT  + KAZ_HEAD55 / 100 * KAZ_POPT  + MYS_HEAD55 / 100 * MYS_POPT  + MDV_HEAD55 / 100 * MDV_POPT  + RUS_HEAD55 / 100 * RUS_POPT  + WSM_HEAD55 / 100 * WSM_POPT  + THA_HEAD55 / 100 * THA_POPT  + TON_HEAD55 / 100 * TON_POPT  + TUR_HEAD55 / 100 * TUR_POPT  + TKM_HEAD55 / 100 * TKM_POPT

UPPM_INFL  = (  + ARM_HIC / ARM_HIC(-1) * ARM_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + AZE_HIC / AZE_HIC(-1) * AZE_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + CHN_HIC / CHN_HIC(-1) * CHN_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + FJI_HIC / FJI_HIC(-1) * FJI_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + GEO_HIC / GEO_HIC(-1) * GEO_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + IDN_HIC / IDN_HIC(-1) * IDN_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + IRN_HIC / IRN_HIC(-1) * IRN_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + KAZ_HIC / KAZ_HIC(-1) * KAZ_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + MYS_HIC / MYS_HIC(-1) * MYS_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + MDV_HIC / MDV_HIC(-1) * MDV_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + RUS_HIC / RUS_HIC(-1) * RUS_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + WSM_HIC / WSM_HIC(-1) * WSM_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + THA_HIC / THA_HIC(-1) * THA_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + TON_HIC / TON_HIC(-1) * TON_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + TUR_HIC / TUR_HIC(-1) * TUR_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  + TKM_HIC / TKM_HIC(-1) * TKM_YEN$ / UPPM_YEN$  - 1) * 100

D(WLD_TECHL)  = 0.8 * D(WLD_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2 * (0.017  + 0.05 * DLOG(WLD_XTR$) )

DLOG(WLD_POIL)  = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))

DLOG(WLD_PC)  = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))

DLOG(WLD_PR)  = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))

DLOG(WLD_PG)  = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))

WLD_DD$  = WLD_YER$  - WLD_XTR$  + WLD_MTR$

WLD_PE  = WLD_PE(-1) * ( WLD_OILC(-1) / WLD_EC(-1) * WLD_POIL / WLD_POIL(-1)  + WLD_GASC(-1) / WLD_EC(-1) * WLD_PG / WLD_PG(-1)  + WLD_COALC(-1) / WLD_EC(-1) * WLD_PC / WLD_PC(-1)  + WLD_RC(-1) / WLD_EC(-1) * WLD_PR / WLD_PR(-1) )

DEBTD_PM25_WGT  = (  + AZE_PM25 * AZE_POPT  + IRN_PM25 * IRN_POPT  + KAZ_PM25 * KAZ_POPT  + MNG_PM25 * MNG_POPT  + RUS_PM25 * RUS_POPT  + TKM_PM25 * TKM_POPT  + UZB_PM25 * UZB_POPT ) / DEBTD_POPT

DEBTD_LIVES  =  + AZE_LIVES  + IRN_LIVES  + KAZ_LIVES  + MNG_LIVES  + RUS_LIVES  + TKM_LIVES  + UZB_LIVES

DEBTD_CLIMLOSS  =  + AZE_CLIMLOSS / AZE_EXR  + IRN_CLIMLOSS / IRN_EXR  + KAZ_CLIMLOSS / KAZ_EXR  + MNG_CLIMLOSS / MNG_EXR  + RUS_CLIMLOSS / RUS_EXR  + TKM_CLIMLOSS / TKM_EXR  + UZB_CLIMLOSS / UZB_EXR

DEBTD_GDNRATIO  = DEBTD_GDN$ / DEBTD_YEN$ * 100

DEBTD_GLNRATIO  = DEBTD_GLN$ / DEBTD_YEN$ * 100

DEBTD_CANRATIO  = DEBTD_CAN / DEBTD_YEN$ * 100

DEBTD_URX  = (1 - DEBTD_LNN / DEBTD_LFN) * 100

DEBTD_HEAD19  = DEBTD_POOR19 / DEBTD_POPT * 100

DEBTD_HEAD55  = DEBTD_POOR55 / DEBTD_POPT * 100
